quran[6236]{c,v,t}:
  1,1,"He innde Allah jurumdeero jormotooЙ—o oo"
  1,2,"Denndaangal jettooЙ—e ngoodanii joom binnde."
  1,3,"Jurumdeero jurmotooЙ—o"
  1,4,"JeyЙ—o Гұalngu njoЙ“di"
  1,5,"Ko Aan tan min ndewata te ko Aan tan min mballintoo."
  1,6,"Feewnu min e laawol pooctingol"
  1,7,"Laawol Й“een Й“e neemin-Й—aa Й“e ngonaa tikkanaaЙ“e te Й“e majjaani."
  2,1,"Alif, Laam, Miim."
  2,2,"Ndeen deftere sikke alaa he mayre, ko nde peewal wonande hulЙ“e Й“ee"
  2,3,"ЖҒeen goongЙ—inooЙ“e mbirniindi eЙ“e ГұiiЙ“na juulde eЙ“e nafga he ko Min njeЙ—i Й“e."
  2,4,"E Й“een goongЙ—inooЙ“e ko jippini dow maa e ko jippinaa ado ma, eЙ“e njananaa Гұalaande wattan."
  2,5,"ЖҒeen dey ngoni ko e peewal iwngal e Joomii Й“e, ko kamЙ“e ngoni daЙ—ooЙ“e."
  2,6,"ЖҒeen yedduЙ“e foti a jeertinii Й“e wolla a jeertinaani, fof foti he mum maЙ“Й“e."
  2,7,"Alla muppi Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e, wirngallo woni e noppi e gite maЙ“Й“e lette mawЙ—e na woodani Й“e."
  2,8,"Na woodi heen yimЙ“e wi'ooЙ“e min ngoongЙ—inii Alla e Гұalaande wattan, tawa Й“e ngoongЙ—inaani."
  2,9,"EЙ“e koda Alla e goongЙ—inЙ“e Й“e, alaa mbo Й“e kodata so wonaa ko'e maЙ“Й“e tawa Й“e tinaani."
  2,10,"Ko Гұawu woni he Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e, Alla Й“eydani Й“e Гұawu , maa lette muusЙ—e njan he mum en sabu ko Й“e penannoo."
  2,11,"So Й“e mbi'aama hoto mbonnee he lesdi ndii Й“e mbi'a minen ko min moЖҙЖҙinooЙ“e."
  2,12,"Ko kamЙ“e tigi ngoni bonnooЙ“e kono Й“e tinataa Й—um."
  2,13,"So Й“e mbi'aama ngoongЙ—inee wano yimЙ“e Й“ee ngoongЙ—iniri nii, Й“e mbi'a mbela min ngoongЙ—inat wano Й—aayЙ“e Й“ee ngoongЙ—iniri nii, kono ko kamЙ“e tigi ngoni Й—aayЙ“e kono Й“e nganndaa."
  2,14,"So tawii Й“e kawrii he goonЙ—inЙ“e Й“ee, Й“e mbi'a: min ngoongЙ—inii, so Й“e njeewdii e seyЙ—anooji maЙ“Й“e Й—ii Й“e mbi'a: minen ko onon min ngonndi min njalkitat tan."
  2,15,"Alla na jalkita Й“e O Й“eydana Й“e bewre Й“e ngona e wemmbere."
  2,16,"Ko Й“een ngoni soodirЙ“e peewal majjere njulaagu maЙ“Й“e alaa tono, te Й“e peewaano."
  2,17,"ЖҒe nanndi ko he kuЙ“Й“uЙ—o jayngol nde ngol yaynii Alla nawi ooyre maЙ“Й“e O acci Й“e e niЙ“Й“e Й“e nji'ataa hay huunde."
  2,18,"Ko fahЙ—uЙ“e muumЙ—uЙ“e wumЙ“e Й“e nduttotaako"
  2,19,"Wolla wano toЙ“o iwde asamaan waЙ—ngo niЙ“Й“e e digaali e maje Й“e cukka noppi maЙ“Й“e sabu kartaali (parГұite) ngam reentaade maayde , Alla noon Ombo fiiltii geЙ—e heeferЙ“e."
  2,20,"Majal ngal na Й—eЙ“a diftaade gite maЙ“Й“e kala nde ngal yaynii Й“e njaha heen so niЙ“Й“iЙ—ii Й“e ndaroo, so Alla welano nawa nanЙ—e e gite maЙ“Й“e sabu Alla ko kattanЙ—o kala huunde."
  2,21,"Onon yimЙ“e ndewee Joom mon tagЙ—o on tagi adiiЙ“e on mbela joo kulon Alla."
  2,22,"Oon baЙ—anЙ—o on lesdi ndi mbertu O waЙ—i Asamaan o mahoodi tiiЙ—ndi O jippini ndiyam iwde e Asamaan O yaltini heen Й“iЙ“Й“e leЙ—Й—e woni njeЙ—u mon, taa mbaЙ—anee Alla nanndidiiЙ“e te oЙ—on nganndi goonga oo."
  2,23,"So tawii oЙ—on cikkitii e Kur'aana mbo Min njippini dow jeyaaЙ—o Amen oo, ngaddee simoore nanndunde hembo, noddee wallidiiЙ“e mon gaa Alla so tawii oЙ—on ngoongЙ—i e nodditaandu mon ndu."
  2,24,"So tawii on mbaЙ—aani Й—um -te on mbaЙ—ataa Й—um - kulee jayngol kuЙ“Й“irtengol yimЙ“e e kaaЖҙe, ngol heblanaa ko heeferЙ“e Й“ee."
  2,25,"Weltin Й“een goongЙ—inЙ“e Й“e ngolli moЖҙЖҙe wonde eЙ“e keЙ“a aljannaaji caalli na ndonga les majji kala nde Й“e njeЙ—aa toon Й“iЙ“Й“e leЙ—Й—e Й“e mbi'a ko Й—ee min njeЙ—anoo ko adii, Й“e totteeЙ—e he nanndal, eЙ“e keЙ“a toon rewЙ“e laaЙ“Й“e Й“e ГұiiЙ“ida toon."
  2,26,"Alla aamantaa addude yeru hay so wonii wano Й“owngu e ko Й“uri Й—um, so tawii ko goonЙ—inЙ“e eЙ“e nganndi ko goonga iwЙ—o e Joom maЙ“Й“e, so tawii ko yedduЙ“e Й“e mbi'a holko Alla yiЙ—i he oo yeru Ombo majjina heewЙ“e O feewna heen heewЙ“e, alaa majjinteeЙ—o heen so wonaa yaltuЙ“e Й—oftaare."
  2,27,"ЖҒeen firtooЙ“e aadi Alla Й“aawo tiiЙ—neede mbo eЙ“e taЖҙa ko Alla yamiri yo jokke eЙ“e mbonna ka lesdi , ko kamЙ“e ngoni rusЙ“iiЙ“e (pertuЙ“e)"
  2,28,"Holno njeddirton Alla tawi on ngoodaano O woodni on rewi heen O wara on rewa heen O wuurtina on Й“aawo Й—uum ko he Makko nduttoto-Й—on."
  2,29,"Kanko tagani on kala ko woni he lesdi ndii Й“aawo Й—uum O fa'ndii asamaan oo fotndi mbo asamaaji jeeЙ—iЙ—i , ko o gannduЙ—o kala huunde."
  2,30,"Nde Joom maa wiy maleykaaji Й—ii maa Mi waЙ— lomto Am he lesdi (leydi) ndii, Й“e mbi'i mbela a waЙ—at heen bonnoowo dufoowo ЖҙiiЖҙe , tawa minen ko Aan tan min njettata mi-Й—en cennu maa, O wi'i Miin MiЙ—o anndi ko on nganndaa."
  2,31,"O anndini Aadama inЙ—e Й—ee fof, rewi heen O holli Й—e malaykaaЙ“e Й“e O wi' kaalanee Kam inЙ—e Й“ee Й—oo so tawii oЙ—on ngoongЙ—i."
  2,32,"ЖҒe mbi'i senaande woodanii Ma alaa ko min nganndi so wonaa ko nganndin-Й—aa min ko Aan tan woni ganndidЙ—o kala huunde ГұeeГұЙ—uЙ—o."
  2,33,"O wi'i aan Aadama anndin Й“e inЙ—e majji nde o anndini Й“e inЙ—e Й—ee O wi'i mbela Mi wi'aano on Miin MiЙ—o anndi mbirniindi asamanji e lesdi MiЙ—o anndi ko peГұГұinton e ko cuuЙ—oton fof."
  2,34,"Nde Min mbi'i malaykaaЙ“e Й“ee cujjanee Aadama Й“e cujji so wonaa Ibliisa o salii o mawnikinii ndeen o jeyaa e yedduЙ“e."
  2,35,"Min mbii aan Aadama yah hoЙ—oy aljanna aan e debbo maa Гұaamee toon ko welata on kala Й—o mbela-Й—on taa Й“ado-Й—ee kii lekki ndeen on jeyete e tooГұЙ“e."
  2,36,"SeyЙ—aane hoomti Й“e haa yaltini Й“e e moЖҙЖҙere nde Й“e ngonndoo Min mbi'i Й“e njippo-Й—ee ngonon aГұondirЙ“e keЙ“on ГұiiЙ“al dow lesdi ndii e dakmitaare haa happu yonta."
  2,37,"Aadama heЙ“i konngi iwde e Joom mum O accani mo ko Kanko woni jaafotooЙ—o jurmotooЙ—o."
  2,38,"Min mbi'i njippo-Й—ee toon onon fof so tawii Mi addii e mon peewal kala dewЙ—o peewal am Й“een dey kulol alanaa Й“e kadi Й“e cunotaako."
  2,39,"ЖҒeen yedduЙ“e penni maandeeji amen ko Й“een ngoni yimЙ“e jayngol ko toon Й“e ГұiiЙ“ata."
  2,40,"Onon Й“iЙ“Й“e Isra'iil ciftoree moЖҙЖҙere am nde mbaЙ—an-mi on njottinee aadi am Mi yottina aadi mon te kulon Kam Miin tan."
  2,41,"NgoongЙ—inee ko njippin-mi na goongЙ—ini ko njogi-Й—on koo, taa ngonee adiiЙ“e yeddude Й—um wota on eto soodirde aayeeje am Й—ee coodgu hoyngu, kulee kam Miin tan."
  2,42,"Taa jiiЙ“indiree goonga he fenaande oЙ—on cuuЙ—a goonga oo tawa oЙ—on nganndi mbo."
  2,43,"Г‘iiЙ“nee juulde tottiron asakal Й—igganon njankinano-Й—on Alla."
  2,44,"Mbela on njamirat yimЙ“e Й“ee Й—iggere njejjiton ko'e mon tawa oЙ—on njannga deftere ndee, mbela on kakkilantaa Й—um."
  2,45,"Mballitoree muГұal e juulde, pellet ende saЙ—ti so wonaa he Й“een yankiniiЙ“e Й“ee."
  2,46,"ЖҒeen yananaaЙ“e maa kawru e joom maЙ“Й“e ko he Makko Й“e nduttotoo"
  2,47,"Onon Й“iЙ“Й“e Isra'iil ciftoree neemaaji am Й—i neemin-mi on, ko miin tigi Й“urni on he dow winndere dee."
  2,48,"Kulee Гұande fittaandu alaa ko waawani fittandu woЙ—ndu , ndu jaЙ“antaake tefangol goЙ—Й—o coodtiigu kadi jaЙ“etaake Й“e keЙ“ataa ballo."
  2,49,"Tuma Min ndaЙ—ndii on he yimЙ“e Fir'awna, Й“e mbaЙ—ii on lette bonЙ—e Й“e kirsa Й“iЙ“Й“e mon Й“e ngoppa rewЙ“e mon nguura, ina he Й—uum lette mawЙ—e iwde ga Joom mon."
  2,50,"Nde Min peccani on maayo ngo min ndaЙ—ndi on min njooli yimЙ“e Fir'awna oЙ—on ndaarda gite mon ЕӢaas."
  2,51,"Nde min podani Muusaa jammaaji capanЙ—e nayi fawii heen ndew-Й—on gool oo caggal makko, onon ko on tooГұooЙ“e."
  2,52,"Fawii heen min ngaccani on Й“aawo Й—uum mbela joo njetton."
  2,53,"Nde Min ngaddani Muusa deftere ndee e seerndirde ndee mbela joo peewon."
  2,54,"Nde Muusaa wi' yimЙ“e makko onon yimЙ“e am on tooГұii ko'e mon nde ndew-Й—on gool oo, nduttoЙ—ee to tagЙ—o on oo, mbarto-Й—on Й—uum Й“uri moЖҙЖҙande on to Joom mon O accana on Kanko woni gaccanoowo jurmotooЙ—o."
  2,55,"Nde mbi'-Й—on Muusaa min ngoongЙ—itaa haa min nji'a Alla ko laaЙ“i ndeen hartaango (jayngol iwde asamaan) Й“ami on oЙ—on ndaarda gite mon."
  2,56,"Fawii heen min nguurtini on Й“aawo nde maay-Й—on mbela joo njetton."
  2,57,"Min Й—uwdini on duule Min njippinani on njuumri ndakmundi e colli juЙ—aaЙ—i Гұaamee e belЙ—i ko min njeЙ—i on, wonaa Minen Й“e tooГұi ko ko'e maЙ“Й“e Й“e tooГұatnoo."
  2,58,"Min mbi' naatee ndee sahre Гұaamon heen ko mbela-Й—on mbeltoron naatee damal ngal oЙ—on njankinii mbi'on accan min ndeen min njaafoo on goopi mon min Й“eydana moЖҙЖҙinЙ“e Й“ee moЖҙЖҙereeji."
  2,59,"TooГұЙ“e Й“ee mbayliti konngol ngol Й“e mbi'anoo ndeen min njippini dow tooГұooЙ“e Й“ee lette sabu ko Й“e ngonnoo koo faasiqeebe."
  2,60,"Nde Muusaa toranii yimЙ“e mum ndiyam min mbi'i fiyu haayre ndee sawru maa nduu ndeen gite ndiyam sappo e Й—iЙ—i puccitii heen yimЙ“e Й“ee fof keЙ“i yarde, Гұaamee njaree e njeЙ—u Alla taa mbaЙ—ee bonannde dow lesdi ndi."
  2,61,"Nde mbi'-Й—on aan Muusaa min njondintaako e Гұaamdu wooturu torano min Joom maa O yaltinana min puЙ—i lesdi gila he kappe e haakooji e Laaj e Гұebbe e basalle (jabaa) mayri o, wi'i mbela on njiЙ— lomtinde ko Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude koo, keЙ“on ko Й“uri jaasde Й—uum njippo-Й—ee Misara maa on keЙ“ ko tori-Й—on koo Й“e pawaa koyeera e woroЙ—de Й“e nduttorii e tikkere Alla sabu Й“e njedduno aayeeje eЙ“e mbara AnnabaaЙ“e ko aldaa e goonga Й—uum noon ko goopi e tooГұe maЙ“Й“e."
  2,62,"ЖҒeen goongЙ—inЙ“e e Й“een yahodinЙ“e e nasaara en, e Й“e ngalaa diine en ,kala goongЙ—inЙ—o Alla e Гұalaande wattan o golli ko moЖҙЖҙi Й“een keЙ“ata njoЙ“di to Joom maЙ“Й“e kulol alanaa Й“e te kamЙ“e Й“e cunotaako."
  2,63,"Nde min Й“ami aadi mon min ummini fello Tuur dow mon , Жҙettee ko min ngddani on he semmbe ciftoree ko woni heen mbela joo kulon Alla."
  2,64,"Fawii heen caggal Й—uum nduЕӢti-Й—on so wonaano Й“ural Alla e yurmeende Makko dow mon maa on njeye e bonnoraaЙ“e."
  2,65,"On nganndii Й“een tooГұЙ“e he mon Гұande hoore-biir (samdi) min mbi'i Й“e ngontee baaЙ—i booraaЙ—i."
  2,66,"Min mbaЙ—i Й—um woni maande teskuye wonande Й“e e aroyooЙ“e e tinndinoore wonande hulЙ“e Alla Й“e."
  2,67,"Muusaa wi'i yimЙ“e makko Alla yamirii on nde kirsoton nagge Й“e mbii mbela nanngir-Й—aa min ko Й—aayЙ“e? o wi'i: miЙ—o moolii Alla jeyeede e majjuЙ“e."
  2,68,"ЖҒe mbi'i du'ano min Joom maa o laЙ“Й“inana min no nge wa'i. O wi'i: ko nagge nge wonaa nayeewe wonaa Гұale ko hakindiinge mbaЙ—ee ko njamira-Й—on koo."
  2,69,"ЖҒe mbi'i torano min Joom maa o laЙ“Й“inana min ngoobu (kulor) magge ? O wii: Oon wi'i ko sooye no feewi enge weli laarde."
  2,70,"ЖҒe mbi'i du'ano min Joom maa o laЙ“Й“inana min no nge wa'i sabu na'i Й—ii nanndirii min maa min njiytu nge."
  2,71,"O wi'i Kanko dey o wi'i ko nagge ne'iraange golle remru ngesa, kono wonaa yarnude gese, ko hisnge nge jillaani, Й“e mbi'i jooni dey a addii goonga Й“e kirsi nge kono Й“e Й—eЙ“aani waЙ—de yamiroore ndee."
  2,72,"Nde mbar-Й—on feЙ—taandu ngon-Й—on he tuumondirde, ko Alla yaltini ko cuuЙ—no-Й—on."
  2,73,"Min mbii tappindiree Й—i ko noon Alla wuurtinirta maayЙ“e o holla on kaawase Makko mbela joo kakkilon."
  2,74,"Fawii heen Й“erЙ—e mon Й—ee njoori Й“aawo Й—uum Й—e mba'i no kaaЖҙe maa Й“ura noon, sabu kaaЖҙe na ngoodi jaltinooje caalli goЙ—Й—e na peecoo njaltina ndiyam goЙ—Й—e kadi njowtoo njana sabu hulde Alla, Alla noon yeebotaako ko ngolloton koo."
  2,75,"Mbela oЙ—on Й—aminii maa Й“e ngoonЙ—inan on tawa na woodi e maЙ“Й“e sete nanoowo haala Alla Й“e mbaylita ka caggal nde Й“e paami Й“e nganndi ka."
  2,76,"So Й“e kawri e goonЙ—inЙ“e Й“ee Й“e mbi'a min ngoonЙ—inii so Й“e njeewdii Й“e mbi'a mbela on kaalanat Й“e ko Alla udditani on, Й“e kujjoroo on Й—um to Joom mon, mbela on kakkilantaa"
  2,77,"Mbela Й“e nganndataa wonde Alla Mbo anndi ko Й“e cuuЙ—ta e ko Й“e Й“aЕӢnginta."
  2,78,"Na woodi he maЙ“Й“e humambinneeЙ“e Й“e nganndaa he deftere ndee sonaa janngugol penaale Й—e Й“e nganndinaa, Й“e ngonaani so wonaa sikkude tan."
  2,79,"Bone woodanii Й“een winndirooЙ“e deftere nde juuЙ—e maЙ“Й“e eЙ“e mbi'a Й—um ko to Alla iwri haa Й“e coodira nde coodgu hoyngu, yoo bone wonan Й“e he ko juuЙ—e maЙ“Й“e mbinndi e kala ko Й“e paggitii heen."
  2,80,"ЖҒe mbi'i jayngol memataa min sinaa balЙ—e seeЙ—a wi' Й“e mbela on keЙ“ii fodoore Alla te Alla luutndotaako aadi Makko wolla ngon-Й—on ko haalde he Alla ko on nganndanaa."
  2,81,"Ko goonga kala mbo faggitii bonannde bonЙ—i makko piilii mo, ko Й“een ngoni yimЙ“e jayngol luttooЙ“e toon."
  2,82,"ЖҒeen goongЙ—inЙ“e Й“e ngolli moЖҙЖҙereeji ko Й“een ngoni yimЙ“e aljanna luttooЙ“e toon."
  2,83,"Min Й“amii fodoore he Й“iЙ“Й“e Isra'iil taa ndewee sonaa Alla , moЖҙЖҙon he jibnaaЙ“e e jiidaaЙ“e e waayЙ—uЙ“e e waasЙ“e oЙ—on kaalana yimЙ“e Й“ee ko moЖҙЖҙi ndarnon juulde tottiron asakal Й“aawo Й—uum cali-Й—on Й—uurni-Й—on so wonaa seeЙ—a he mooЙ—on."
  2,84,"Nde min Жҙetti fodoore mon wota on nduf ЖҙiiЖҙe mon taa on njaltin ko'e mon galleeji mon Й—ii ndeen njaЙ“-Й—on ceediЙ—on Й—um."
  2,85,"Rewi heen onon Й“ee oЙ—on mbara ko'e mon oЙ—on njaltina yimЙ“e e mon galleeji maЙ“Й“e, oЙ—on peГұГұina tooГұe mon e maЙ“Й“e, si Й“e arii e mon dahaaЙ“e coodtiЙ—on Й“e yaltingol Й“e na harmi he mon, mbela on goongЙ—inat yoga he deftere ndee njeddon yoga heen kala he mon waЙ—ooЙ“e Й—um njoЙ“di maЙ“Й“e ko koyeera weejo aduna Гұande darnga Й“e nduttee he lette Й“urЙ—e bonde Alla noon yeebotaako ko ngolloton koo."
  2,86,"ЖҒeen soodirЙ“e laakara nguurndam aduna Й“e koynantaake lette Й“e keЙ“ataa ballo."
  2,87,"Min ngaddanii Muusaa deftere nde , Й“aawo makko min ndewni heen nulaaЙ“e min ngaddanii Iisaa Й“iy Maryam laЙ“Й“inale Min cemmbiniri mo wonki tedduki mbela kala nde nulaaЙ—o addi he mon ko welaani pittaali mon mawnikino-Й—on yoga heen njeddon Й“e yoga heen mbaron Й“e."
  2,88,"ЖҒe mbi'i Й“erЙ—e amen Й—ee ko uddiiЙ—e, accu tan ko Alla huЙ—i Й“e sabu keefeeru maЙ“Й“e, na famЙ—i ko Й“e ngoongЙ—inta."
  2,89,"Nde deftere ari e maЙ“Й“e iwde e Alla, ende nuunЙ—ina ko Й“e njogii ado Й—uum Й“e ngonndoo ko wallitoraade Й—um dow Й“een yedduЙ“e nde ko Й“e nganndi ko ari he maЙ“Й“e Й“e njeddi Й—um, yo kuЙ—di Alla won he heeferЙ“e."
  2,90,"Bone wonii he koЙ“e coodiri ko'e maЙ“Й“e nde Й“e njeddi -e tooГұe- ko Alla jippini , Alla jippinta Й“ural Makko dow mbo O welaa e jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“e kaandii e tikkere mawnde, heeferЙ“e Й“ee na keЙ“a lette bonЙ—e."
  2,91,"Si Й“e mbi'aama ngoongЙ—inee ko Alla jippini koo Й“e mbi'a min ngoongЙ—inii ko jippinaa he amen Й“e njedda ko wonaa Й—uum te ko Й—uum woni goonga nuunЙ—inЙ—o ko Й“e njogii, wi' Й“e ko waЙ—i oЙ—on mbarannoo (mbaratnoo) annabaaЙ“e Alla Й“ee so tawno oЙ—on ngoongЙ—ini."
  2,92,"Nde Muusaa addani on laЙ“Й“inale njogiti-Й—on gool oo Й“aawo makko onon ko on tooГұooЙ“e."
  2,93,"Min Й“amii he mon fodoore min Й“amti dow mon haayre Tuur Жҙettiree ko min ngaddani on koo he semmbe nanee, Й“e mbi'i min nanii min ngoopi , Й“erЙ—e mum en Й—e keewi dak rewde gool oo he keefeeru maЙ“Й“e, wiy bone wonii he ko goongЙ—ingol mon yamiri on so tawno oЙ—on ngoongЙ—ini."
  2,94,"Wi' so tawii ko onon tan keЙ“ata aljanna to laakara njeloЙ—ee maayde so tawii ko on goongЙ—uЙ“e."
  2,95,"ЖҒe njelotaako nde muk sabu ko juuЙ—e maЙ“Й“e ngardini , Alla Ombo anndi tooГұooЙ“e Й“ee."
  2,96,"Ma a taw ko kamЙ“e Й“uri reerЙ—ude he nguurndam e Й“een renndinЙ“e e Alla, gooto he maЙ“Й“e ina yiЙ—i wuurde duuЙ“e ujunere wuurde mbo ko juuti woЙ—Й—intaa mo lette Alla mo yi'a golle maЙ“Й“e."
  2,97,"Wiy kala gonЙ—o gaГұo Jibriilu yo anndu ko kanko yottini Kur'aana nder Й“ernde maa e yamiroore Alla nde nuunЙ—ini defte Й—e Й“e njogii ko nde peewal e malu goongЙ—inЙ“e."
  2,98,"Kala gonЙ—o gaГұo Alla e malaykaaЙ“e Makko e nulaaЙ“e Makko e Jibriil e Miika'il Alla dey ko gaГұo heeferЙ“e Й“ee."
  2,99,"Min njippinii he maa maandeeji laЙ“Й“inooji alaa jeddoowo Й—i sonaa faasigeeЙ“e Й“ee."
  2,100,"Wolla kala nde Й“e piЙ“i aadi wooda e maЙ“Й“e firtuЙ“e mbo accu tan Й“urЙ“e heewde e maЙ“Й“e ngoongЙ—inaani."
  2,101,"Nde NulaaЙ—o Alla ari e maЙ“Й“e ombo goongЙ—ina ko Й“e njogii koo, woodi heen sete salii rontii deftere Alla nde wa'i no Й“e nganndaa nii."
  2,102,"ЖҒe ndewi ko seyЙ—aneeji njannganta he laamu Suleymaan , Suleymaanu yeddaani kono ko seyЙ—aneeji Й—i njeddi eЙ—i nganndina yimЙ“e mbilewu he ko jippinaa dow malaykaaЙ“e Й—iЙ—o to Baabil , Haaruut e Maaruut kala nde Й“e nganndini goЙ—Й—o Й“e mbi'a minen dey ko min fitina taa yeddu, Й“e njnnga he maЙ“Й“e no Й“e ceerndirta neЙ—Й—o e debbo mum, Й“e lorataa hay gooto sinaa e yamiroore Alla, eЙ“e njannga ko bonnanta Й“e nafataa Й“e, Й“e nganndii kala battindirЙ—o Й—um alaa geЙ—al to laakara , ndaw ko bone ko Й“e mbattiti ko'e maЙ“Й“e tawiino Й“e nganndi."
  2,103,"Sinndo Й“e ngoongЙ—iniino Й“e kuli Alla ko mbarjaari immorde he Alla Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude so Й“e ngannduno."
  2,104,"Onon goongЙ—inЙ“e taa mbi'ee aynu min mbi'ee ndaar (fadir) min nanee, heeferЙ“e Й“ee na keЙ“a lette. muusЙ—e."
  2,105,""ЖҒeen yimЙ“e deftere yedduЙ“e e renndinЙ“e e Alla njiЙ—ataa joom mon jippina he mon moЖҙЖҙere, Alla noon ko mbo o welaa o heertinta yurmeend makko, Allah ko joom Й“ural mawngal.""
  2,106,"Kala nde Min itti aaye maa min momti mbo Min ngadda Й“urЙ—o mbo maa wano mbo mbela a anndaa Alla mo waawi kala huunde"
  2,107,"Mbela a anndaa wonde ko Alla jeyi laamu asamaanji e lesdi on ngalaa keedanoowo mon wolla ballo sonaa Alla."
  2,108,"Wolla njiЙ—-Й—on ko naamnaade nulaaЙ—o mon o wano (hono) no Muusaa naamnoranoo ko adi,i kala mbo wattiti goongЙ—ingol keefeeru oon o majjii laawol peewngol."
  2,109,"HeewЙ“e e yimЙ“e deftere ina njiЙ—i ruttude on heeferЙ“e Й“aawo goongЙ—ingol mon sabu ngaГұgu pittaali mumen caggal nde Й“e laaЙ“aa goonga oo , njaafee ngaccanon haa yamiroore Alla ara , Alla ko kattanЙ—o kala huunde."
  2,110,"Г‘iiЙ“nee juulde tottiree asakal kala moЖҙЖҙere nde ngardinan-Й—on ko'e mon maa on tawnde to Alla ko Kanko Alla woni ji'oowo ko ngolloton."
  2,111,"ЖҒe mbi'i alaa naatoowo aljanna sonaa Yahuude maa nasaaraajo Й—uum woni muuyaande maЙ“Й“e, wiy Й“e ngaddee finnde mooЙ—on so tawii ko on goongЙ—uЙ“e."
  2,112,"Ko goonga kala mbo totti yeeso makko Alla o mo woni moЖҙЖҙinЙ—o, ina woodani mo mbarjaari Й—o joom makko, kulol alanaa Й“e Й“e cunotaako."
  2,113,"Yahuud en mbi'i nasaara en ngonaani he hay huunde nasaara en mbii yahuud en ngonaani he hay huunde, tawa eЙ“e njannga deftere nde, ko hono ngol konngol Й“e nganndaa Й“ee mbi'noo ko Alla Гұaawata luural hakkunde maЙ“Й“e Гұande darnga."
  2,114,"Hombo Й“uri tooГұde oon kaЙ—oowo yoo innde Alla jante nder juulirЙ—e ombo daranii bonnude Й—e , Й“een potaani naatde Й—e so wonaa e kulol, Й“e keЙ“a koyeera e aduna Й“e keЙ“a lette mawЙ—e to laakara."
  2,115,"FuЙ—naange e hirnaange ko Alla woodani kala heen Й—o kuccit-Й—on, toon ko yeeso Alla, pellet Alla noon ko jaajЙ—o e ganngal Makko piiltingal."
  2,116,"ЖҒe mbi'i Alla mo jogitii Й“iЙ—Й—o senaande woodanii mo, nganndee kala ko woni e asamaanji e lesdi ko Kanko woodani fof na Й—oftoo mo."
  2,117,"PuЙ—Й—uЙ—o asamaanji (ndowguuji ) Й—ii e lesdi ndi, so o Гұaawii huunde o wi'ata Й—um tan ko: won Й—um wona."
  2,118,"ЖҒe nganndaa Й“ee mbi'a mate Alla haaldataa he min wolla o addana min maande, ko noon adinooЙ“e maЙ“Й“e mbi'noo Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e nanndii , goonga tigi min laЙ“Й“inii maandeeji Й—ii wonande yimЙ“e yananaaЙ“e Й“ee ."
  2,119,"Minen min nelirii ma goonga ngonaa beltinoowo jeertinoowo, a naamnetaake yimЙ“e jayngol Jahannama."
  2,120,"Yahuud e nasaara en mbeletaake ma haa njokkaa laawol maЙ“Й“e , wi' Й“e nganndee ko peewal Alla woni peewal so a jokkii beleeЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й“aawo nde keЙ“Й—aa ganndal ,ndeen woodantaa ma to Allah keedo wonaa ballo ne ."
  2,121,"ЖҒeen Й“e min ngaddani deftere ndee eЙ“e nde njannga no haaniri ko Й“een tigi ngoongЙ—ini nde, kala mbo yeddi nde ko Й“een tigi ngoni bonnoraaЙ“e."
  2,122,"Onon Й“iЙ“Й“e Isra'iil ciftoree moЖҙЖҙereeji am Й—i mi waЙ—anii on, Miin tigi waЙ—i on Й“urЙ“e he winndere ndee."
  2,123,"Kulee Гұande fittaandu alaa ko waawani fittaandu woЙ—ndu te ndu jaЙ“antaake coodtiigu kadi tefaneede nafataa ndu, Й“e keЙ“ataa ballo."
  2,124,"Nde Alla humpitori Ibrahiima konngi o timmini Й—i, o wi'i: Miin Mi waЙ—at ma gardotooЙ—o yimЙ“e Й“e, Ibarahiima wi'i waЙ— Й—um kadi he Й“esngu am o wi'i tooГұooЙ“e Й“ee keЙ“ataa fodoore am."
  2,125,"Nde min mbaЙ—i suudu nduu ruttorde yimЙ“e e hoolaare , njokito-Й—ee darnde Ibrahiima wona juulirde, min ngaadanii Ibrahiima e Ismaa'iila yo Й“e laЙ“Й“in suudu am nduu ngam wanngotooЙ“e e ufnotooЙ“e e juulooЙ“e."
  2,126,"Nde Ibrahiima wi'i joom am waЙ—an min nduu suudu leydi hoolniindi njeЙ—aa yimЙ“e mayru Й“iЙ“Й“e leЙ—Й—e wonande goongЙ—inЙ“e Alla e Гұande wattan O wi'i kala jedduЙ—o mi weltina mo seeЙ—a fawoo heen mi fa'na mon lette jayngol e battane bonЙ—e."
  2,127,"Nde Ibrahiima e Isma'iila Й“amtatnoo dosЙ—e suudu ndu eЙ“e mbi'a Jooma amen jaЙ“an min ko Aan woni nanoowo gannduЙ—o fof."
  2,128,"Jooma amen waЙ— min jebbiliiЙ“e mbaЙ—aa he Й“esngu amen leГұol juulЙ“e yo a hollu min tinndinorЙ—e dewe amen njaafo-Й—aa min ko Aan tigi woni jaafotooЙ—o jurmotooЙ—o."
  2,129,"Jooma amen waЙ— e maЙ“Й“e nulaaЙ—o ombo janngina Й“e aayeeje maa o anndina Й“e Kur'aana maa oo e sunna oo, o laЙ“Й“ina Й“e ko Aaan tigi woni jaaliiЙ—o ГұeeГұЙ—uЙ—o."
  2,130,"Alaa Й—uurnotooЙ—o (calotooЙ—o) laawol Ibrahiima sonaa mbo fittaandu makko Й—aayi nganndee min cuЙ“iima mo he aduna kanko o jeyaa ko he moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e to laakara."
  2,131,"Nde Joom mum wi'i mo jaЙ“an am ngonaa juulЙ—o o wi'i mi jaЙ“anii Joom binnde Й—ee."
  2,132,"Ibrahiima wagganiino Й—i Й“iЙ“Й“e mum, Yaakuub kadi waЙ—i noon, onon Й“iЙ“Й“e am Alla suЙ“aniima on diine Й—e taa maayee sonaa ko on juulЙ“e."
  2,133,"Mbela on ceediima nde maayde arani Yaakuuba nde o wi'i Й“iЙ“Й“e makko Й“ee holko ndewoton caggal am Й“e mbi'i min ndewata ko deweteeЙ—o maa oo e deweteeЙ—o baabiraaЙ“e maa Ibrahiima e Isma'iila e Ishaak deweteeЙ—o gooto minen ko oon min njebbilanii."
  2,134,"Ngool ko leГұol jawtungol engol heЙ“a ko ngol fagginoo, onon ne oЙ—on keЙ“a ko paggi-Й—on on naamnetaake ko Й“e ngollatnoo."
  2,135,"Yahuud e Nasaara en mbi'i ngonee Yahuuda maa Nasaara ndeen peewon wi': -aan annabiijo- accu dey min ngonata ko he diine Ibrahiima peewЙ—o oo ,etee o jeyanooka e sirkuЙ“e Й“ee."
  2,136,"Mbi'ee min ngoongЙ—inii Alla e ko jippinaa dow amen e ko jippinaa dow Ibrahiima e Isma'iila e Ishaak e Yaakuub e Asbaat e ko Muusaa e Iisaa okkaa e ko annabaaЙ“e Й“ee okkaa iwde to joomiraawo maЙ“Й“e min ceerndataa hay gooto e maЙ“Й“e ko kamЙ“e min njebbilanii."
  2,137,"So tawii Й“e ngoonЙ—inii wano (hono) ko ngoonЙ—in-Й—on koo ndeen tawa Й“e peewii so Й“e Й—uurniima ndeen Й“e ngoni ko he luutndaade maa Alla suran ma Й“e ko Kanko woni nanoowo ngannduЙ—o fof."
  2,138,"Diine Alla neesuyaЕӢkeejo alaa diine ba'Й—e no diine Alla Й—ee, minen ko Kanko min ndewata."
  2,139,"Wiy mbela on njeddondirat he amen fii Alla te ko Kanko woni joome amen e joome mon, min keЙ“at golle amen keЙ“on golle mon minen ko Kanko min laaЙ“anta."
  2,140,"Mbela on njiЙ— wi'de wonde Ibrahiima e Isma'iila e Ishaaka e Yaakuub e Asbaat Й“e ngonndoo ko yahudeeЙ“e maa nasaaraЙ“e, wi' mbela ko onon Й“uri anndude Alla, hol mbo Й“uri tooГұde oon cuuЙ—oowo seedanfaagu iwde he Alla, Alla noon yeebotaako ko Й“e ngollata koo."
  2,141,"Ngool ko leГұol jawtungol engol heЙ“a ko ngol, fagginoo onon ne oЙ—on keЙ“a ko paggi-Й—on on naamnetaake ko Й“e ngollatnoo."
  2,142,"Maa Й“een YimЙ“e Й—aayЙ“e mbi': " hol ko woppani Й“e huccitirde maЙ“Й“e nde Й“e ngonndoo ndee , wi' Й“e : "Ko Alla woodani (jeyi) fuЙ—naange e hiirnaange, himo Feewna mo o muuyaa fa'de laawol pooctingo"
  2,143,"Ko wano nii min mbaЙ—iri on leГұol kakindiingol fii yo on laato seedoytooЙ“e e dow yimЙ“e Й“en, NulaaЙ—o oo seeditoyoo e dow mon. Min mbaЙ—iraani ndee hoccotirde nde ngonndo-Й—aa he mayre si wonaa min ngannda oon jokkoowo NulaaЙ—o oo e oon ruttotooЙ—o batte bonnere mu'un, hay si tawii Й—um laatike ko sattu-Й—um, si wanaa e dow Й“een Й“e Allah feewni. Woodanaani Alla yeebaade liimanaaku mooЙ—on .Pellet, Allah ko HinnotooЙ—o yimЙ“e Й“ee jurmotooЙ—o."
  2,144,"Tigi min njiyii baylitogol yeeso maa ngoo he ndowgu (kammu) nguu . Maa min kuccitn ma hoccotirde weloore ma , hoccotin yeeso maa ngoo bannge Juulirde Hoormaande ndee . kala Й—o ngon-Й—on, kuccinee geece (jeese) mon Й—ee bannge mayre , Pellet, Й“een rokkaaЙ“e defte Й“ee eЙ“e nganndi [Al Qur'aanaare nden] ko nde goonga immorde ka (to) Joomi maЙ“Й“e, Alla wonaa belsintooЙ—o ko Й“e ngollotoo koo ."
  2,145,"Mi woondii si a addanii Й“een rokkaaЙ“e deftere ndee kala maande, Й“e jokkataa (ndewataa) Qibla (huccorde) maa oo,a wonaa jokkoowo Qibla maЙ“Й“e oo ,yoga he maЙ“Й“e wonaanii jokkooЙ“e Qibla yoga.mi Woondii si a okkii beleeЙ—e maaЙ“e Й“aawo nde ari he maa e anndal, pellet, aan oon tuma a jeyaama e tooГұuЙ“e Й“ee."
  2,146,"ЖҒen (Й“een) Й“e Men (min)Rokki deftere nden hiЙ“e nganndiri Й—um wano Й“e nganndiri Й“iЙ“Й“e maЙ“Й“e; pellet, fedde goo e maЙ“Й“e hino suuЙ—ude goonga kan hara hiЙ“e nganndi."
  2,147,"Goonga kan (kaa ) ko ko ummori ko Joomi maa, wata a laatodu e Й“en sikkitiiЙ“e."
  2,148,"Ena woodani mo kala baЕӢЕӢe Й—e o feewtata e mun.Adondiree he moЖҙЖҙereeji,nokku kala ka laati-Й—on, Allah artiray on denndaangal mon . Pellet,Allah ko hattanЙ—o kala huunde."
  2,149,"Nokku kala ka yaltirЙ—aa, feewtinir yeeso maa ngon (ngoo )baЕӢЕӢe Suudu Hormorteendu ndun, pellet, Й—um ko goonga ummoraade Joomi maa, Allah Wonaali (wonaani) WelsindiiЙ—o e kon ko gollo-ton."
  2,150,"Nokku kala ka (Й—o) yaltir-Й—aa, feewtinir yeeso maa ngon baЕӢЕӢe Suudu Hormorteendu ndun, nokku kala ka ngonЙ—on, fewtiniree geece (jeece) mon Й—en baЕӢЕӢe mayru fii wata wonan yimЙ“e Й“en hujja e hoore mo'on - so wanaa Й“en tooГұuЙ“e he maЙ“Й“e. Wata non on huluЙ“e, Hulee Lam, fii no mi timminira neema am On (oo) e mo'on, mbele joo on feeway."
  2,151,"Wano no men Nuliri non e mo'on NulaaЙ—o ummoraade e mo'on, himo janngana on aayeeje amen,himo laЙ“Й“ina on,himo anndina on deftere nden,o anndina on ko on anndaano."
  2,152,"JaЕӢtee lam (njaЕӢte-Й—ee kam), mi anndita on; jaarnee Lam wata on yeddam."
  2,153,"Heey mon gomЙ—imЙ“e (goongЙ—inЙ“e), wallitoree muГұГұaare (muГұal) e juulde. Pellet, Allah Hino Wonndi he muГұГұiiЙ“e Й“en."
  2,154,"Wata on wi'an Й“en wariraaЙ“e fii Allah Й“en: "ko Й“e maayЙ“e". Ko woni, Й“en ko wuurЙ“e, kono on so'aa anndude."
  2,155,"Ma Men njarriboro on huunde, he kulol, e heege, e Й—uytagol (ustogol) jawle, e woЕӢkiiji, e dimЙ—e; Wewlin (weltin) muГұГұiiЙ“e Й“en."
  2,156,"ЖҒen Й“e nganndan-Й—aa si musiibo heЙ“iiЙ“e, Й“e wi'a: "Menen dey ko Allah jeyi men, pellet to makko men ruttotoo"."
  2,157,"ЖҒen Й—on, hino he dow maЙ“Й“e toraaje e yurmeende ummoraade ka (to ) Joomi maЙ“Й“e, ko kamЙ“e ngoni feewuЙ“e Й“en."
  2,158,"Pellet,Safaa e Marwa ko jeyaaЙ—e e maandeeji [diine] Allah.Kala on hajjuЙ—o ka suudu [Kaaba], maa o waЙ—i Umra,ella woo (foo) fawaaki mo nde o wanngotoo hakkunde majji.On mo gattii moЖҙЖҙere,pellet Allah ko Jaarnoowo AnnduЙ—o."
  2,159,"Pellet, Й“en suuЙ—ooЙ“e kon ko Men Jippini immorde he Й“anngannduyeeji (laЙ“Й“inaaЙ—e) e peewal, Й“aawo nde Men ЖҒannginani Й—um yimЙ“e Й“en ka deftere, Й“en Й—on, Allah ena HuЙ—ude Й“e, huЙ—ooЙ“e Й“en na huЙ—ude Й“e."
  2,160,"Si wanaa Й“en tuubuЙ“e Й“e moЖҙЖҙini Й“e Й“aЕӢngini: Mi JaЙ“anay Й“en Й—on tuubuubuyee, ko miin woni JaЙ“oowo tuubabuya, yurmotooЙ—o."
  2,161,"Pellet, Й“en yedduЙ“e Й“e maayi ko Й“e heeferaaЙ“e, Й“en Й—on ena fawiiЙ“e kuЙ—di Allah ndin e malaa'ika en e yimЙ“e Й“en denndaangal"
  2,162,"Ko Й“e luttooЙ“e (saasooЙ“e) e magge. ЖҒe hayfinaЕӢtaake leЙ“te Й—en, Й“e wonaali nennanaЕӢteeЙ“e (muГұanteeЙ“e)."
  2,163,"ReweteeЙ—o mon on ko ReweteeЙ—o Gooto. ReweteeЙ—o Alaa tanaa kanko, Jurumdeero jurmotooЙ—o."
  2,164,"Pellet hino e ndeer tagugol kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin, e luutondiral jemma e Гұalorma on, e laaЙ—e dogooje Й—ee he maaje kaaЙ—Й—e nafugol yimЙ“e Й“en, e ko Allah Jippini to kammu ( ndowgu), he ndiyam, o wurniri Й—am leydi ndin Й“aawo maayugol mayri o Saakti he mayri kala daaba, e waylitugol keneeli Й—in e duule eltaaЙ—e Й—en hakkunde leydi e kammu, maandeeji wonannde yimЙ“e hakkilooЙ“e ."
  2,165,"Hino he yimЙ“e Й“ee jogitiiЙ“e ko woori Allah yerodiiЙ“e, eЙ“e njiЙ—i Й“e wano no Allah yiЙ—irtee, [ko] Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“uri saЙ—tude giggol (yiЙ—de) wonande Allah. Hara Й“en tooГұuЙ“e annduno tuma Й“e nji'oyta lepte Й—en, wonde doole Й—en fof ko Allah heeranii, e wonde Allah ko saЙ—tuЙ—o lepte!."
  2,166,"Tuma nde hisnii jokkanooЙ“e Й“en jokkunooЙ“e Й“en, Й“e nji'i lepte Й—en, jokkorЙ—e Й—ee taЖҙiri Й“e."
  2,167,"JokkunooЙ“e Й“en (rewnooЙ“e Й“ee) mbi'a: "Hara fehre ruttagol no woodannoo men, men pottitora Й“e wano Й“e pottitori men nii". Ko wano nii Allah Hollirta Й“e golleeji maЙ“Й“e Й—in; hayrere e dow maЙ“Й“e, Й“e ngonaali njaltooЙ“e e yiite ngen."
  2,168,"Heey mo yimЙ“e! Г‘aamee yoga he ko woni ka leydi koo, dagii ko laaЙ“i, wata on jokku juri=taaЙ“e (taaЙ“e) seytaane Й—in : Pellet, ko o gaГұo mo'on feeГұuЙ—o."
  2,169,"Anndee ko o yamirta on ko bone e paЕӢkare, e nde wowloton he Allah ko on anndaa."
  2,170,"Si Й“e wi'amaa:"Jokkee kon ko Allah Jippini", Й“e mbi'a:"Ko woni, men njokkay ko men tawri kon baabiraaЙ“e amen"; si tawii noon baabiraaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en hakkilataa hay e huunde Й“e peewataa?!"
  2,171,"Yeru Й“en yedduЙ“e hono ono ewnotooЙ—o kon ko nanataa si wanaa noddaandu e ewnal. Ko fahЙ—uЙ“e, mumЙ—uЙ“e, wumЙ“e Й“e kakkiltaa."
  2,172,"Heey mon gomЙ—imЙ“e! Г‘amee immorde he laaЙ“uЙ—i Й—i men Arsiki on, jaarnon Allah si on wonii ko kanko rewoton."
  2,173,"Anndee ko o Harminani on, ko jiibe (jiiba), e ЖҙiiЖҙam, e teewu kose, e [huunde hirsiraande] daginiraande ko woori Allah. Kala on duГұaaЙ—o [e Гұaamugol Й—um] hara wanaa Й“ewЙ—o wanaa jaggituЙ—o, bakkaatu fawaaki mo. Pellet Allah ko ya'fotooЙ—o YurmotooЙ—o."
  2,174,"Pellet Й“en suuЙ—ooЙ“e ko Allah Jippini kon e deftere nden, hiЙ“e soodira Й—um cogguwel famЙ—ungel. ЖҒen Й—on alaa waЙ—ude ka deedi maЙ“Й“e si wanaa yiite ngen; Allah haaldataa he maЙ“Й“e Гұalnde darngal, o LaЙ“Й“iЕӢtaa Й“e, hino woodani Й“e lepte muusuЙ—e."
  2,175,"Ko Й“en ngoni soodirЙ“e majjere peewal, e lepte ya'fuya. kaawse ko muГұГұoriЙ“e ka yiite!"
  2,176,"ЖҠuum noon, ko fii Allah Jippinirii deftere ndee goonga. pellet Й“een luutondirЙ“e e deftere ndee ,eЙ“e he luural woЙ—Й—ungal."
  2,177,"Dewal ngal wonaali fewtiЕӢgol geece mon Й—en Й“aЕӢnge fuЙ—naange e hiirnaange. Ko woni tun dewal ngal: ko oon gomЙ—inЙ—o Alla e Гұalaande sakkitiinde nden, e malaa'ika en, e deftere nden, e annabaaЙ“e Й“en; o okki jawdi - e hoore yiЙ—ugol ndi- joomiraaЙ“e Й“adondiral, e wonduЙ“e Й“en, e Й“illiiЙ“e Й“en, e Й“ii hoore-laawol, e Й“en torotooЙ“e, e fii rinЙ—inngol daaЙ—e; o niiЙ“ni (ГұiiЙ“ni) juulde, o totti asakal, e Й“en hunnooЙ“e aadondiral maЙ“Й“e si Й“e haldidaama, e Й“en muГұГұitooЙ“e ka baasi (caЙ—eele ) e ka lorra, e fewndo gowole. Ko Й“en ngoni goonguЙ“e Й“en, ko Й“en kadi ngoni gomЙ—uЙ“e."
  2,178,"Heey mon gomЙ—imЙ“e,njottiigu farlaama he mo'on:dimo sabu dimo, jeyaaЙ—o sabu jeyaaЙ—o,deyel sabu deyel.Kala ya'fanaaЙ—o goЙ—Й—um he musiЙ—Й—o makko,ko jokkitirogol no moЖҙЖҙiri tottira e makko no moЖҙЖҙiri.ЖҠum Й—oo ko hoynaneede immorde e Joomi mo'on e yurmeende.Kala oon tooГұЙ—o Й“aawo Й—uum,no woodani mo lepte muusuЙ—e."
  2,179,"No woodani on ka (he) njoЙ“tiigu nguurdam, onon joomiraaЙ“e hakkilaaji. Mbela joo ngonon gomЙ—uЙ“e."
  2,180,"Farlaama he mo'on:si maayde nden arii he mo'on, si o accii jawle: wasiyanagol jibinЙ“e mo Й“en, e Й“adondiraaЙ“e Й“en no moЖҙЖҙiri.Ko hannduyee he dow reentiiЙ“e Й“en."
  2,181,"Kala on waylituЙ—o Й—um Й“aawo nde o nani Й—um , pellet bakkaatu mun on ko Й“en waylituЙ“e fawii. Allah ko nanoowo AnnduЙ—o."
  2,182,"On mo huli ooГұaare immorde e wasiyiiЙ—o maa bakkaatu o moЖҙЖҙini hakkunde maЙ“Й“e,bakkaatu fawaaki mo.Pellet Alla ko YaafotooЙ—o YurmotooЙ—o."
  2,183,"Heey mon gomЙ—imЙ“e, koorka kan farlaama he mo'on wano ka farliranoo he Й“en (Й“een) adinooЙ“e on, mbele laatoЙ—on gomЙ—uЙ“e."
  2,184,"Г‘alЙ—i limtaaЙ—i. Kala e mo'on (mooЙ—on) laatiiЙ—o dafaaЙ—o maa e hoore-jahal: ko limtugol ГұalЙ—i goo. No fawii Й“en haЙ—tanЙ“e ka, Гұammingol Й“iliiЙ—o. Kala on gattuЙ—o moЖҙЖҙere Й—um no moЖҙЖҙani mo. Ko nde hooroton Й“uri moЖҙЖҙannde on, si wonii hiЙ—on nganndi."
  2,185,"Lewru koorka ndun, ndu Alqur'aanaare nden jippinaa he mu'un (mon ), ko ndu peewal wonannde yimЙ“e Й“en e Й“angannduyeeji (Й“annginaaЙ—e) immorde e peewal e serndugol. On e mo'on (kala he mon) seediiЙ—o lewru ndun, yo o hooru ndu. On tawЙ—o no nawni (faawni) maa himo e hoore-jahal, ko limtugol e ГұalЙ—i goo. Alla no Fa'danii on neweende O Faandanaaki on saЙ—teende; e fii yo on timmin limoore nden e no mawninirЙ—on Alla no o Fewniri on, mbela joo oЙ—on jaarna mo."
  2,186,"Si jeyaaЙ“e am Й“en lamndike lan , hary miin: Ko mi Й“aЙ—iiЙ—o. MiЙ—o Jaaboo toraare torotooЙ—o si o torike Lam. Yo Й“e nooto Lam, e yo Й“e gomЙ—in am, mbele joo Й“e peewa."
  2,187,"On dagnanaama he jemma koorka yiidugol e rewЙ“e mon Й“en. Ko Й“e koltu mo'on ko on koltu maЙ“Й“e. Alla anndii wonde on laatinoke jaЕӢfotooЙ“e koye mon, o JaЙ“anii on tuubuubuyee o Ya'fiima on.Jooni noon,soccondiree he maЙ“Й“e Й—aЙ“Й“on ko Alla winndani on.Г‘aamee yaron haa gaarawol danewol ngol Й“aЕӢngirana on Й“alewol ngol ka peeral, refti timminiron koorka kan jemma. Wata on soccondir e maЙ“Й“e hara ko on ufniiЙ“e ka juulirЙ—e.ЖҠum ko keeri Allah, wata on Й“aЙ—to Й—i.Ko wano nii Alla Й“aЕӢnginiraЕӢta yimЙ“e Й“en aayeeje makko Й—en, bela jo'o Й“e wona reentiiЙ“e."
  2,188,"Wata on Гұaamir jawle (jawЙ—eele ) mon Й—en hakkunde mon he mehre, werloron Й—e e ГұaawooЙ“e Й“en fii yo fedde goo Гұaamira e jawle yimЙ“e Й“en bakkaatu, hara hiЙ—on nganndi."
  2,189,"HiЙ“e naamno maa fii darorЙ—e lebbi, wi'u: "ЖҠin ko tumaaji yimЙ“e e fii hajju".Dewal ngal wonaali nde naatirto cuuЙ—i Й—in immorde ka babbe (dame) majji, si ko woni dewal ngal: ko on (oon) gomЙ—uЙ—o.Ngardee cuuЙ—i Й—in ka dame majji.Hulon Allah,belaj joo male-Й—on."
  2,190,"HaЙ“ee fii laawol Alla ngol Й“en haЙ“atooЙ“e on, wata tooГұee. Pellet, Alla yiЙ—aa tooГұooЙ“e Й“en."
  2,191,"waree Й“e nokku kala ka taw-Й—on Й“e, yaltinee Й“e nokku ka Й“e yaltiniri on: ko geddi Й—in Й“uri mawnude he dii warngo . Wota kaЙ“oЙ—ee Й“e Й—o juulirde hormaande ndee haa Й“e haЙ“a on he mayre. Si Й“e haЙ“iima on haЙ“ee he maЙ“Й“e. Ko hono nii woni njoЙ“di heeferЙ“e Й“en."
  2,192,"Si Й“e haЙ—itike, pellet, Alla ko o Hafroowo jurmotooЙ—o"
  2,193,"KaЙ“oЙ—ee Й“e haa waasa laataade fitina, diina kan laatanoo Alla. Si Й“e haЙ—itike, haray jaggitere alanaa si wanaa Й“en tooГұooЙ“e"
  2,194,"Si Й“e haЙ“ii he mon he lewru hormaandu nduu, haЙ“ee he maЙ“Й“e e lewru hormaandu nduu, kormaaЙ—i Й—ii ko njoЙ“tiigu. Kala tooГұЙ—o njoЙ“to-Й—ee fotde ko o tooГұi on . Hulee Alla anndon pellet Alla no wondi he Й“en gomЙ—uЙ“e."
  2,195,"MbaЙ—ee e fii laawol Alla, wata on bugor juuЙ—e mon Й—en fa'de he halkaare. MoЖҙЖҙinee, pellet Alla no YiЙ—i moЖҙЖҙinayЙ“e Й“en."
  2,196,"Timminiree hajju oo e umra oo fii Alla. Si on sakkaama: fawike on ittugol kon ko newii e kirse, wata on femmbu ko'e mon Й—en haa kirse Й—en (baraaЙ—i) yottoo nokku majje. Kala dafaaЙ—o (naawnuЙ—o) walla lor heЙ“i mo ka hoore, yo o soodtoro koorka, maa sadak maa dammol. Si on wonii he hoolaare, on mo dakmitori umra haa ka hajju: fawike mo ittugol ko newii he kirse. Mo heЙ“aali (heЙ“aani ), ko hoorugol balЙ—e tati ka hajju e jeeЙ—iЙ—i si on ruttike; Й—uum ko sappo timmuЙ—e. Ko jaЕӢtaa koo, ko fii on tawЙ—o Й“eynguure mun nden laataaki hoЙ—uЙ“e ka juulirde hormaande ndee. Hulee Alla, anndon pellet Alla ko saЙ—tuЙ—o lepte."
  2,197,"Hajju ngun (hajju oo):ko lebbi anndaaЙ—i. Mo anniyike he nder majji hajju,renndugol he debbo alaa,wanaa faasoqingol wanaa kadi yeddondiro ka hajju.Kala ko mbaЙ—-Й—on he moЖҙЖҙere Alla (Geno) na anndi Й—um .YooЙ“ee (njooЙ“o-Й—ee),ko Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude he njooЙ“a, ko deentol. Hulee Lam joomiraaЙ“e hakkillaaji."
  2,198,"Bakkaatu fawaaki on nde Й—aЙ“Й“oton arsike immorde he Joomi mon. Si on iwtii 'Aarafaat, JaЕӢtee innde Alla ka nokku horminannde. NjaЕӢte-Й—ee mo wano (hono) no o feewniri on nii, hari on laatinooma ado ko on jeyaaЙ“e he majjuЙ“e."
  2,199,"Refti yahron ka yimЙ“e Й“en yahri Й—on, Imsino-Й—on Й—o Alla. Pellet Alla ko YaafotooЙ—o jurmotooЙ—o."
  2,200,"Si on gaynii dewe hajju mon ngun, njaЕӢto-Й—ee innde Alla wano no njaЕӢtorton baabiraaЙ“e mon, maa ko Й“uri Й—uum tiiЙ—ude. No woodi he yimЙ“e Й“en wi'ooЙ“e: "Joomi amen rokku men ka aduna", alanaa mo ka (to) laakara geЙ—al moЖҙЖҙal."
  2,201,"No he maЙ“Й“e wi'ooЙ“e: Joomi amen, okku min moЖҙЖҙere aduna e laakara, ndanndaa min lebte jayngol"
  2,202,"ЖҒen (Й“een) Й—oon, no woodani Й“e geЙ—al moЖҙЖҙal he ko Й“e faggitii. Alla ko YaawuЙ—o hasboore"
  2,203,"JaЕӢtee Innde Alla he ГұalЙ—i limtaaЙ—i. On yaccinЙ—o he nder balЙ—e Й—iЙ—i, bakkaatu fawaaki mo; on neЙ“tinЙ—o kadi, bakkaatu fawaaki mo.Wonande on deentiiЙ—o . Hulee Alla, nganndon pellet Й—o makko mooЙ“indiroyte-Й—on."
  2,204,"No he yimЙ“e Й“ee oon mo konngol makko haawat maa ka nguurdam aduna, himo seedna Alla ko woni he nder Й“ernde makko, hara non ko kaЕӢko Й“uri saЙ—tude weejnde."
  2,205,"Si (So) o ruЕӢtiima , o yaha ka leydi fii o bonna he mayri, o halka gese e geГұГұi (geГұli). Alla YiЙ—aa bononnda."
  2,206,"Si o wi'aama: "Hulu Alla", mawnikinaare heЙ“a mo sabu bakkaatu. Jahannama yonii mo, e nge bonii ndaЙ—Й—udi!"
  2,207,"No woodi he yimЙ“e Й“ee oon coodtotooЙ—o wonki mun kii Й—aЙ“Й“ugol yarluye Alla. Alla ko HilnotooЙ—o (kinnotooЙ—o) jeyaaЙ“e makko Й“en (Й“ee)."
  2,208,"Heey mon gomЙ—imЙ“e, naatee he kisal denndanngal, wata on jokku juri (taaЙ“e) seytaane Й—in (Й—ee). On ko gaГұo mooЙ—on Й“aЕӢnguЙ—o."
  2,209,"Si on ooГұike Й“aawo ko ari on he Й“annginaaЙ—e (laЙ“Й“inaaЙ—e), nganndee pellet, Alla ko fooluЙ—o Г‘eeГұuЙ—o (ГұeeГұЙ—uЙ—o)."
  2,210,"Mbele wonaa Й“e padi ko haa nde Alla (Geno) ari he maЙ“Й“e he nder niЙ“Й“e duule wondude e Maalaa'ika en; fiyaaku nguu Гұaawaama. ka (Й—o) Alla woni ruttorde fiyakuuji Й—in."
  2,211,"Naamno Й“iЙ—Й“e Israa'iila ko jelu men rokki Й“e e maandeeji Й“aЕӢnguЙ—i! Kala battuЙ—o neema Alla oo Й“aawo nde o ari he makko, pellet, Alla ko caЙ—tuЙ—o lepte"
  2,212,"Nguurdam aduna Й—am cuЙ—inanaama Й“eya heeferЙ“e, hiЙ“e jalkita Й“en goongЙ—imЙ“e. ЖҒen goongЙ—uЙ“e wonoyay dow maЙ“Й“e Гұalnde darngal. Alla no Arsikira on mo o Muuyi, ko aldaa e hasboore."
  2,213,"YimЙ“e Й“en laatino mofte goote. Allaahu On Nuli AnnabaaЙ“e Й“en, wewlinooЙ“e e jeertinooЙ“e, O Jippindini e maЙ“Й“e Deftere nden hoore goonga, fii yo o Гұaawu hakkunde yimЙ“e Й“en kon ko Й“e luuondiri e muuЙ—um. Luutondiraali e muuЙ—um, si wanaa Й“en rokkaaЙ“e nde, Й“aawo kon ko ari Й“e e Й“aЕӢngannduyeeji; ka bewre hakkunde maЙ“Й“e. Allah Fewniri duЕӢyee Makko Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e e kon ko Й“e luutondiri e muuЙ—um, immorde e goonga. Alla No Fewna on Mo O Muuyi, faade e laawol focciingol."
  2,214,"Kaa on sikku on naatay aljanna hara araali on sugu kon ko arunoo Й“en wuliiЙ“e on? HeЙ“iino Й“en saЙ—tteende e lorra, Й“e dillinaa haa NulaaЙ—o wi'i, e Й“en goongЙ—inЙ“e wondude he makko: "Ko honnde tuma woni ballal Alla ngal?", hey, pellte ballal Alla ngal ko Й“aЙ—tiingal."
  2,215,"ЖҒe ngaray naamnaade ma ko honЙ—um Й“e sakkotoo, wi'u: "Si won ko sakkiЙ—on e moЖҙЖҙere, ko fii jibinЙ“e on, e Й“adondiraaЙ“e Й“en, e waayЙ—uЙ“e Й“en, e Й“iliiЙ“e Й“en, e Й“iЙ—Й—o laawol (Й—atniiЙ—o). kalako golluЙ—on e moЖҙЖҙere, pellet Alla ko AnnduЙ—o Й—um"."
  2,216,"Hare nden farlaama e mo'on; nden non ko aГұaande e mo'on,no tijjaa ka aГұoton huunde hara ko nde moЖҙЖҙere mon, no tijjaa kadi ka yiЙ—oton huunde hara ko nde bone mon. Alla no Anndi onon on nganndaa."
  2,217,"HiЙ“e naamno maa fii lewru hormaЕӢte ndun, haЙ“ugol e mayru, maaku: "HaЙ“ugol e mayru ko mawnu-Й—um. Ko sakkagol e laawol Alla ngol e yeddugol Mo e Misiide hormorde nden e yaltingol yimЙ“e mayre Й“en e mayre, Й“uri mawnude ka Alla. Ko shirku on kadi Й“uri mawnude dii wargol ngol; Й“e seerataa hiЙ“e haЙ“a on haa Й“e rutta on e diina mon, si Й“e haaЙ—tanii. Kala e mo'on yaltondirЙ—o e diina mu'un, o maayi ko o keefeero: Й“en Й—on, golle maЙ“Й“e Й—en bonii aduna e laakara; ko Й“en ngoni yimЙ“e yiite, Й“en ko luttooЙ“e ton."
  2,218,"Pellet, Й“en goongЙ—imЙ“e e Й“en feruЙ“e haЙ“iri fii laawol Alla, Й“en Й—on no jortii Yurmeende Alla; Alla ko Ya'fotooЙ—o HuuЙ“uЙ—o-yurmeende"
  2,219,"HiЙ“e naamno maa fi sanngara e karte, maaku: "No e Й—in Й—iЙ—i bakkaatu mawЙ—o e nafawoy wonannde yimЙ“e Й“en, ko bakkaatu majji noon Й“uri mawnude e nafawoy majji ". HiЙ“e naamno maa kadi hol ko Й“e sakkotoo? Maaku: "yaafuya , Ko wano nii Alla ЖҒaЕӢnginiraЕӢta on Aayeeje Й—en, mbele joo oЙ—on miijitoto."
  2,220,"Fii aduna on e laakara on, hiЙ“e naamno maa fii wonduЙ“e Й“en, maaku: "Ko moЖҙЖҙagol e maЙ“Й“e Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude". Si on jillondirii e maЙ“Й“e, ko musiЙ—Й“e mo'on. Alla no Anndi on moЖҙЖҙinoowo e on bonnoowo. Si Alla muuyuno, O ЖҒiЙ—tinanayno on. Pellet Alla ko FooluЙ—o Г‘eeГұuЙ—o."
  2,221,"Wata on resu Й“en rewЙ“e sirkayЙ“e haa Й“e goongЙ—ina: Mi woondii ko korЙ—o goongЙ—inЙ—o Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude debbo sirkoowo hay si o haawnii on. wata on resin Й“en worЙ“e shirkooЙ“e haa Й“e gomЙ—ina: Mi woondii ko maccuЙ—o gomЙ—inЙ—o Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude dimo shirkoowo hay si o haawnii on.ЖҒen Й—on hiЙ“e nodda faade e yiite, Alla No Noddude e Aljanna e haforanal, e duЕӢyee makko. himo Й“aЕӢngina Aayeeje Makko Й—en wonannde yimЙ“e Й“en, belajo'o Й“e wa'ajitoto."
  2,222,"HiЙ“e naamno maa fii fiilordu, maaku: ЖҠum ko nefinii Й—um; luncitee rewЙ“e Й“en fewndo fiilordu, wata on Й“aЙ—to Й“e haa Й“e laaЙ“a. Si Й“e laaЙ“ii, ngaree e maЙ“Й“e nokku ka Alla Yamiri on Й—on. Pellet Alla No YiЙ—i tuubayaЙ“e Й“en Himo YiЙ—i kadi Й“en laЙ“Й“inotooЙ“e."
  2,223,"RewЙ“e mon Й“en ko gese mo'on. Ngardee e ngesa mon mbam nokku kala ka faaliraЙ—on, ngardinanee woЕӢkiiji mon Й—in. Hulee Alla, nganndon ko on kawrooЙ“e e makko. Weltin goongЙ—imЙ“e Й“en."
  2,224,"Wata on waЙ—u Alla heedo fii ngoondooje mon Й—en; nde Й—iggoton, ndeento-Й—on hulon moЖҙЖҙinon hakkunde yimЙ“e Й“en. Alla ko Nanoowo annduЙ—o."
  2,225,"Alla Nanngitirtaa on gardambi=bolle mehre ka ngoondooje mo'on, kono himo Nanngitira on ko Й“erЙ—e mon Й—en faggitii. Alla ko Hafroowo MuГұГұiiЙ—o."
  2,226,"No woodani Й“en woondirooЙ“e suddiiЙ“e mun Й“en: habbitagol lebbi nayi. Si Й“e ruttike, pellet Alla ko haforoowo jurmotooЙ—o."
  2,227,"Si Й“e fellitii ceergal ngal, pellet Alla ko Nanoowo AnnduЙ—o"
  2,228,"SeeraaЙ“e Й“en yo habbiЕӢtin ko'e maЙ“Й“e Й—en laaЙ“e tati; dagaЕӢtaako Й“e suuЙ—ugol kon ko Alla Tagi ka ndeer renngaaji maЙ“Й“e, si wonii hiЙ“e gomЙ—imЙ“e Alla e Гұalaande sakkitiinde. Ko moodiЙ“Й“e maЙ“Й“e jojjidi ruttugol Й“e e Й—um, si hawrii hiЙ“e faalaa weldital. No woodani Й“en [rewЙ“e] yeru kon ko fawiiЙ“e, no moЖҙЖҙiri. No woodani worЙ“e Й“en: Й“ural e dow maЙ“Й“e. Alla ko fooluЙ—o ГұeeГұЙ—uЙ—o."
  2,229,"Ceergal, ko laaЙ“i Й—iЙ—: ko jogitorgol no moЖҙЖҙiri maa accitira no moЖҙЖҙiri. DagaЕӢtaako on Жҙettitugol huunde e kon ko rokku-Й—on Й“e, si wanaa hara Й“e hulii [kamЙ“e Й—iЙ—o] nde Й“e niiЙ“nataa keeri Alla Й—in. Si on hulii roЕӢkude ГұiiЙ“nude keeri Alla Й—in, goopi alanaa Й“e e kon ko debbo on soktori. ЖҠin ko keeri Alla, wata on jaggitu-Й—i. kala jaggituЙ—o keeri Alla Й—in, ko Й“en ngoni tooГұooЙ“e Й“en"
  2,230,"Si o seerii mo, [debbo] dagitaЕӢtaako mo Й“aawo Й—u'um, haa o resindira e gorko goЙ—Й—o. Si oon [gorko] seerii mo, goopi fawaaki Й“e nde Й“e ruttondira, si Й“e fellitii ГұiiЙ“nugol keeri Alla Й—in.ЖҠin ko keeri Allah, himo Й“aЕӢnginana Й—i Й“en yimЙ“e ngannduЙ“e."
  2,231,"Si on seerii rewЙ“e Й“en, laje maЙ“Й“e Й—en yottike: jogitoree Й“e no moЖҙЖҙiri maa accitoron Й“e no moЖҙЖҙiri. wata on jogitor Й“e lorrugol nde jaggitoton. Kala waЙ—uЙ—o Й—um, gomЙ—ii o tooГұii hoore-makko. Wata on jogitor aayeeje Alla Й—en jalnori. Annditee neemaaji Alla Й—i O Neemini e mo'on, e ko o jippini e mo'on immorde e Deftere e Г‘eeГұal; himo wa'ajora Й—um. Hulle Alla, nganndon pellet Alla ko annduЙ—o kala huunde."
  2,232,"Si on seerii rewЙ“e Й“en, laje maЙ“Й“e Й—en yottike, wata on laagu Й“e nde moodiЙ“Й“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en resata Й“e; si Й“e welondirii hakkunde maЙ“Й“e no moЖҙЖҙiri. ЖҠum no waajoree on tawЙ—o e mo'on no gomЙ—ini Alla e Г‘alaande Sakkitiinde. Ko jaЕӢtanaЙ—on koo Й“uri moЖҙЖҙannde on, Й“uri laaЙ“aande. Alla No Anndi onon on nganndaa."
  2,233,"JibimЙ“e Й“en yo muynin Й“iЙ—Й“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en duuЙ“i Й—iЙ—i timmuЙ—i; wonannde on faandiiЙ—o timminde muyninngol ngol.No fawii jibinanaaЙ—o on, Гұammingol holitinira [rewЙ“e] Й“en no moЖҙЖҙiri. WoЕӢkii woo fawaaka si wanaa ko ki waawata. Wata jibinЙ—o on lorrire sabu Й“iЙ—Й—o makko on, wanaa jibinanaaЙ—o on kadi lorrirtee sabu Й“iЙ—Й—o makko on; no fawii ronoowo on yeru Й—um. Si Й“e faandike entude e hoore yarlondiral hakkunde maЙ“Й“e e diisondiral, bakkaatu fawaaki Й“e. Si on faandike Й—aЙ“Й“ude muyninanoowo on Й“iЙ—Й“e mon Й“en, bakkaatu fawaakii on, si on jonnirii kon ko Й“en [muyninooЙ“e] hanndi e moЖҙЖҙere.hulee Alla, nganndon ko o reenuЙ—o kala ko golloton."
  2,234,"ЖҒen maayooЙ“e e mo'on Й“e acca suddiiЙ“e: yo Й“en habbiЕӢtin ko'e maЙ“Й“e lebbi nayi e balЙ—e sappo. Si Й“e yottike laje maЙ“Й“e Й—en, bakkaatu fawaaki on e kon ko Й“e waЙ—ani ko'e maЙ“Й“e no moЖҙЖҙiri. Alla Ko humpitiiЙ—o kon ko golloton."
  2,235,"Bakkaatu fawaaki on e kon ko weeЙ“itoton, e sabboyde suddiiЙ“e Й“en, maa suuЙ—uЙ—on Й—um ka woЕӢkiiji mo'on. Alla No Anndi aray ka annditon fii maЙ“Й“e, ko woni tun, wata on fodondir e maЙ“Й“e [desal] e gunndoo: si wanaa nde wowloton koЕӢngol moЖҙЖҙol, wata on fellitu humugol dewgal ngal haa lajal edda ngal yottoo. Ngande pellet Alla No anndi ko woni e woЕӢkiiji mo'on, reЕӢtee e makko, nganndon pellet Alla ko haforoowo muГұГұiiЙ—o"
  2,236,"Bakkaatu fawaaki on si on seerii suddiiЙ“e Й“en ado on renndude e maЙ“Й“e maa jaЕӢtanagol Й“e teЕӢe, dakmitee Й“e , no fawii galo on yeru makko, no fawii kadi baydoolo on yeru makko.Dakmitirgol Й“e no moЖҙЖҙiri. Hannduyee fawiiЙ—o moЖҙimЙ“e Й“en"
  2,237,"Si on seerii suddiiЙ“e Й“en ado on meemude Й“e, tawa on jaЕӢtanike Й“e teЕӢe: ko feccere kon ko jaЕӢti-Й—on, si wanaa hara Й“e ya'afi maa on mo dewgal woni e juuЙ—e mu'un ya'afii. Ko nde ya'afotoЙ—on Й“urata Й“aЙ—tinnde gomЙ—al. Wata on yejjitu Й“ural ngal hakkunde mo'on. pellet Alla ko reenuЙ—o kala ko golloton"
  2,238,"Reenee juulЙ—e Й—en, e juulde hakkundeere nden. DaranoЙ—on Alla ko o toЖҙЖҙiniiЙ“e"
  2,239,"Si on hulii, juulee ko on seppayЙ“e maa waЙ—Й—iiЙ“e. Si on hoolike, jaЕӢtee Innde Alla nden wano no anndiniri on kon ko on nganndaano"
  2,240,"ЖҒen maayooЙ“e e mo'on Й“e acca suddiiЙ“e: ko wasiyanagol suddiiЙ“e Й“en dakmitorЙ—um haa hitaande nden timma, ko aldaa e yaltiЕӢgol Й“e. Si Й“e yaltii, bakkaatu fawaaki on e kon ko Й“e waЙ—ani ko'e maЙ“Й“e e moЖҙЖҙere. Alla ko fooluЙ—o ГұeeГұuЙ—o."
  2,241,"No woodani Й“en seeraaЙ“e: dakamitorgol no moЖҙЖҙiri. ko goonga fawiiЙ—o goongЙ—uЙ“e Й“en."
  2,242,"Ko wano nii Alla ЖҒaЕӢnginiraЕӢta on Aayeeje makko Й—en, mbela joo on haqqilay."
  2,243,"E a tinaali Й“en njaltunooЙ“e e galleeji mu'un, kamЙ“e ko Й“e guluuje (ujunaaji ), ngam reenagol maayde, Allaahu on daalani Й“e: "Maayee", refti o wuurniti Й“e? Pellet Alla ko Jom Й“ural e dow yimЙ“e Й“en, ko woni tun, ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e yimЙ“e Й“en njaanataa (njettataa) [Alla]."
  2,244,"HaЙ“ee fii laawol Alla ngol, nagndon pellet Alla ko nanoowo annduЙ—o"
  2,245,"Ko hombo woni on Гұawloowo Alla Гұamaande moЖҙЖҙere, o sowitana mo nde cowalle Й—uuЙ—uЙ—e? Alla no Й“iЙ—ttina himo YaГұГұa, ko fa'de ka nakko ruttoto-Й—on."
  2,246,"E a tinaali ngun mbatu Й“iЙ—Й“e Israa'ila, Й“aawo Muusaa, tuma nde Й“e wi'annoo Annabaajo maЙ“Й“e on: "Imminan men lamЙ—o, men haЙ“a fii laawol Alla ngol?" O maaki: "Hara on tijjaaki si hare nden farlaama e mo'on nde roЕӢkoton haЙ“ude?" Й“e mbi'i: "Ko haЙ—ata men haЙ“ugol e fii laawol Alla ngol, gomЙ—ii men njaltinaama e galleeji amen e Й“iЙ—Й“e amen?" Nde hare nden farlanoo e maЙ“Й“e, Й“e hucciti, si wanaa seeЙ—aaЙ“e e maЙ“Й“e. Alla ko annduЙ—o tooГұooЙ“e Й“en"
  2,247,"Annabaajo maЙ“Й“e on maakani Й“e:"Alla Imminanii on Taaluuta laamЙ—o". ЖҒe mbi'i:"Hol no laamu laatoraЕӢta mo e hoore amen,ko menen Й“uri mo haandude e laamu,o rokkaaka yaajeende jawdi?" O maaki:"Alla SuЙ“ike mo e dow mo'on,O ЖҒeydi mo yaajeende ka ganndal e ka Й“anndu". Alla no rokka laamu makko ngun on mo o muuyi,Alla ko yaajuЙ—o [Й“ural] annduЙ—o."
  2,248,"Annabaajo maЙ“Й“e on maakani Й“e: "Nganndee naande Alla nden, ko nde arkawal ngal arata on; deeЖҙere no e ndeer maggal, immorde ka Joomi mo'on, e ko heddinoo ko aalo Muusaa e aalo Haaruuna en acci, hara Malaa'ika en no ronndii ngal. Pellet no e koo ko jaЕӢtaa Й—oo, maande wonannde on; si o laatike gomЙ—imЙ“e"."
  2,249,"Nde Taaluuta yaltidunoo e konu ngun, o maaki: "Alla no Jarribora on caangol: kala yarЙ—o e maggol o jeyaaka e am, kala mo meЙ—aali ngol ko on Й—on jeyaa e am, si wanaa on ГұeЙ—irЙ—o junngo mun ГұeЙ—annde". ЖҒe yari e caangol ngol si wanaa seeЙ—aaЙ“e e maЙ“Й“e. Nde o lummbunoo ngol, kaЕӢko e Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e wonduЙ“e e makko, Й“en mbi'i: "Feere alanaa en e Jaaluuta e konu mun ngun". ЖҒen fellituЙ“e hawray e Alla Й“en mbi'i: "Heewii ka fedde tokosere fooliri fedde Й—uuЙ—unde, duЕӢayee Alla". Pellet Alla No wondi e muГұГұiiЙ“e Й“en."
  2,250,"Nde Й“e feeГұannoo Jaaluuta e konu mun ngun, Й“e mbi'i: "Joomi amen, rufu muГұal e dow amen, TabiЕӢtinaa teppe amen, Faabo-Й—aa men e Й“ee heeferЙ“e"."
  2,251,"ЖҒe fooliriЙ“e duЕӢayee Alla: Daawuuda wari Jaaluuta, Alla rokki mo laamu e annabaaku, o anndini mo kon ko o muuyi. Si wanaano Ko Alla duГұirnoo yimЙ“e Й“en yoga e dow yoga, leydi ndin bonayno. Kono Alla Ko Jom Й“ural e dow winndere nden"
  2,252,"ЖҠen ko Aayeeje Alla, meЙ—en JaЕӢnga Й—e e dow maaЙ—a wondude e goonga, Pellet ko a jeyaaЙ—o e nulaaЙ“e Й“en"
  2,253,"ЖҒen NulaaЙ“e, men Й“urnii yoga maЙ“Й“e e dow yoga : no he maЙ“Й“e yeewtiduЙ“e e Alla, o Й“aЕӢti darjaaji yoga he maЙ“Й“e; men rokki Iisaa, Й“iЙ—Й—o Maryama on, Й“anngannduyeeji men semmbiniri mo fittaandu laaЙ“undu ndun. Si Alla muuyuno, womЙ“e Й“aawo maЙ“Й“e Й“en wartindirtaano Й“aawo nde Й“anngannduyeeji Й—in ari maabЙ“e. Kono Й“e luutondiri: no he maЙ“Й“e Й“en goongЙ—imЙ“e, no he maЙ“Й“e yedduЙ“e. Si Alla muuyuno, Й“e wartindirtaano, kono Alla no waЙ—a kon ko o yiЙ—i."
  2,254,"Heey mon goongЙ—imЙ“e, sakkee he ko men arsikii on adii Гұalaande arde; nde ngeyngu alaa e mayre, wanaa sehilaaku, wanaa tefoore. Ko heeferЙ“e Й“en woni tooГұooЙ“e Й“en."
  2,255,"Alla, alaa reweteeЙ—o si wanaa kanko, wuurЙ—o ГұiiЙ“uЙ—o. ЕӢoЕӢre nanngataa mo, wanaa kadi Й—oyngol. ko kanko Jeyi huunde ko woni ka kammuuli e huunde ko woni ka leydi. Ko hommbo woni on tefoowo ka makko si wanaa e duЕӢayee nakko? Himo anndi ko woni yeeso maЙ“Й“e, e ko woni Й“aawo maЙ“Й“e. ЖҒe huЙ“indotaako huunde e anndal nakko ngal si wanaa ko o muuyi. Jullere makko nden no yaaji Й“uri kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin. Reenugol Й—i aaninaa mo. Ko Kano woni toowuЙ—o mawЙ—o on."
  2,256,"Doolugol (waawnere) alaa ka diina. GoongЙ—ii peewal ngal Й“anngii immorde e majjere nden. Kala yedduЙ—o bewreeru ndun o goongЙ—ini Alla, haray o jogitike Й“oggi finnde hoolaare Й—in, firtagol alanaa Й—i. Alla ko nanoowo annduЙ—o."
  2,257,"Alla woni keedo goongЙ—inЙ“e Й“en: Himo yaltina Й“e he niЙ“Й“e, o naЙ“a Й“e e ndaygu. ЖҒeya yedduЙ“e, heedЙ“e maЙ“Й“e ko Й—uuЙ—a bewreeji Й—in: HiЙ—i yaltina Й“e e ndaygu naЙ“a Й“e e niЙ“Й“e. ЖҒen ko yimЙ“e yiite, luttooЙ“e e magge."
  2,258,"E a yi'aali on wennjondirЙ—o he Ibraahiima e fii JeyЙ—o mo on, fii Alla no yeЙ—i mo laamu, nde Ibraahiima maakunoo: "JeyЙ—o lam on, ko on wuurnata wara". [WennjodiiЙ—o on] wi'i: "miin kadi miЙ—o wuurna wara". Ibraahiima maaki: "Pellet Alla no addira naange ngen fuЙ—naange, addir nge hiirnaange".YedduЙ—o on mugaa. Alla fewnataa yimЙ“e tooГұooЙ“e Й“en"
  2,259,"Wolla ko hono oon birtiiЙ—o wuro yeewngo ngo mahdi mum e mbildi mum yirbi o wi'i hono Alla wuurtaninta Й—um caggal maayde mum? Alla wari mbo o lelii duuЙ“i teemedere o ummini mbo o daali hono foti ГұiiЙ“Й—a o wi'i Гұalawma maa feccere Гұalawma, o daali alaa a duumiima Й—o duuЙ“i teemedere Жҙeew Гұaamdu maa e njaram maa waylaaki ndaaru mbabba maa baa, ngam min mbaЙ— ma maande wonande yimЙ“e, Жҙeew Жҙi'e Й—ee no min ceЕӢondirta Й—e refti min muurda Й—e teewu, nde Й—uum feeГұi mbo o wi'i mi anndi Alla na hattani kala huunde."
  2,260,"Nde Ibraahiima maaki joom am hollu am na nguurtanirta maayЙ“e, o daali mate a goongЙ—inaani? o maaki oho kay kono ko haa Й“ernde am deeЖҙa , O daali nanngu colli nay tappuЙ—i fa'de e maa refti mbaЙ—a e kala tulde feccere e colli he refti nodduЙ—i Й—i ngara e ma hoЙ—i njaha anndu Alla ko pooloowo mbo fooletaake ko o ГұeeГұo."
  2,261,"Yeru Й“een nafkooЙ“e e laawol Alla ko hono abbere fuЙ—nunde butaali njeeЙ—iЙ—i ina he wutaandu fof teemedere abbere Alla na sowana mo o welaa Alla ko jaacЙ—o ganndo."
  2,262,"NafkooЙ“e jawdi mum en e laawol Alla refti Й“e ndewnataa e ko Й“e nafki koo wajde wolla lor woodanii Й“e njobdi mumen ka joomi mumen kulol alanaa Й“e ,Й“e ngona sunotooЙ“e."
  2,263,"Konngol lobbol Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude e sadaka dewnateeЙ—o lorla, Alla ko galo yondaniiЙ—o muГұoowo."
  2,264,"Eehey mon goongЙ—inЙ“e wotee mbonniree sadakuuji mon wajde e lorlude hono oon tottirЙ—o jawdi mum yeengo yimЙ“e o goongЙ—inaani Alla e Гұalngu cakkatiingu o wayi kono haaЖҙre Й—aatnde toЙ“o yani e mayre acci nde honde wa'i e teeleende Й“een kattantaa hay huunde e ko Й“e paggatii koo, Alla feewnataa heefereeЙ“e ."
  2,265,"Yeru Й“een nafkooЙ“e jawdi mumen ngam Й—aЙ“Й“ude welu Alla e tabatinde pittaali mumen ko hono ngesa ngonba e dow tulde toЙ“o heewngo heewngo yani he heba , ba addi cowe Й—iЙ—e ko ba addatnoo si ba toЙ“aaka waame ba toЙ“ee Гұuur Гұuur ( Гұeek Гұeek ) Alla no yiya ko mbaЙ—aton koo."
  2,266,"Mbela gooto ve mon na yiЙ—i nde o daГұata ngesa tamaro e inabeeje na ila e les mabba caatli te homba jogii e heba kala Й“eynaaЙ—e, o naywi hombo jogii Й“eyngu lohngu henndu wondundu e yiite yana e ngesa hee ba suma, ko hona nih min Й“annganirta kaawisaaji Й—ii mbela miijta-Й—on."
  2,267,"Eehey mon goongЙ—inЙ“e tottiree ko laaЙ“i ummaade ko paggiti-Й—on e ko min njaltinani on ka leydi, wotee pa'nde ko soЙ“i koo ngam nafkude heen on ngonaa nanngooЙ“e Й—um si wonaa on meerni heen, ngannde Alla ko yondaniiЙ—o mantaaЙ—o."
  2,268,"Seytaane na fodana on baasal o yamira on pankare, Alla noon na fodana on yaafuya ummaade e makko e Й“ural Alla ko jaajЙ—o ko o ganndo."
  2,269,"Hombo totta ГұeeГұal mbo o welaa kala tottaaЙ—o ГұeeГұal o tottaa ma moЖҙЖҙere mawnde, siftortaa Й—um si wonaa joom hakkiillaaji en."
  2,270,"Kala ko tottirЙ—-on he nafake wolla takku-Й—on e takkere pellet Alla na anndi Й—uum, woodanaani tooГұooЙ“e wallooЙ“e."
  2,271,"Si on Й“annginii sadakeeji na moЖҙЖҙi si on cuuЙ—i Й—i tottu-Й—on Й—i waasЙ“e ko Й—uum Й“uri on moЖҙЖҙande on , o hafrana on bonЙ—i mon Alla na humpitii ko golloton koo."
  2,272,"A fawaaka peewal mumen kono ko Alla feewnata mbo o faala, kala ko tottir-Й—on e moЖҙЖҙere ko ko'e mon woodani, on nafkataa si wonaa ngam Alla kala ko tottir-Й—on he moЖҙЖҙere tottitee Й—um e mba'di timmundi taw on tooГұetaake."
  2,273,"Woodanii waasЙ“e suraaЙ“e gaa e laawol Alla Й“e mbaawah yaade e leydi hee, majjuЙ“e na cikka koЙ“e alЙ—uЙ“e sabu Й—uurnaade aduna ana anndiraЙ“e maandeeji mum en Й“e Гұaagataaka yimЙ“e e mbaadi cattundi kala ko tottirЙ—on Alla na anndi Й—um."
  2,274,"TottirooЙ“e jawdi mumen jemma e Гұalawma e mba'di mbirniindi e mba'di Й“anngundi, Й“een de woodaniiЙ“e njobdi mumen ummaade ka joomi mumen kulol woodanaani Й“e Й“e ngonaa sunatooЙ“e."
  2,275,"Й“een ГұaamooЙ“e riba Й“e ummataako si wonaa no mbo seytaani memi Й—uum noon ko sabu wi'de Й“e pellet njeegu wa'i kono ribaa, Alla noon daknii njeeygu O harmini ribaa, kala mbo waaju ummmarii mbo ka Alla o acci woodanii mbo o Й“enni koo, fiyaaku makko he Alla fawii, kala duttiiЙ—o noon ko Й“een ngoni joom en yiite saasooЙ“e he maggge haa pooma."
  2,276,"Alla na momta riba na Й“amta sadakuuji Alla yiЙ—aa kala keewЙ—o keefeeru e bakkadinoowo sanne."
  2,277,"Й“een goongЙ—inЙ“e ngolli ko moЖҙЖҙi Й“e darni juulde Й“e tottiri askal woodaniiЙ“e njobdi mumen ummaade ko joomi mumen kulol alanaaЙ“e Й“e ngonaa sunatooЙ“e."
  2,278,"Eehey mon goongЙ—inЙ“e kulee Alla accon ko heddii koo e ribaa si on ngonii goongЙ—uЙ“e."
  2,279,"Si on mbaЙ—aani Й—uum kolliree hare ummorde e Alla e nelaaЙ—o makko, si on tuubii woodanii on koye jawЙ—eele mon, on tooГұataa on tooГұotaake."
  2,280,"Si tawii o wonii he satteende yo o muГұane haa e yaajeende,nde cakkorton Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude he mon si on ngonii annduЙ“e."
  2,281,"Kulee Гұalngu ngu nduttoto-Й—on ka Alla refti yoЙ“ee kala fittaandu ko ndu faggitii koo , etee Й“e tooГұetaake."
  2,282,"Eehey mon goongЙ—inЙ“e si on Гұamlandiri Гұamaande fa'de happu dottaaЙ—o mbinndee nde, yo nuunЙ—uЙ—o winndu hakkunde mon, woto binndoowo sala winndude yo o winndu no Alla anndiniri mbo nih , yo o winndu yo mbo hakke woni dow mum winndu yo o hul joomiiko , woto o ustu heen hay huunde, si wonii mbo hakke woni e dow mum oo ko Й—aayЙ—o wolla lohЙ—o wollo o waawaa fidde, yo keedo makko fidir nuunЙ—al, ceednee seedeeЙ“e Й—iЙ—o e worЙ“e mon, si worЙ“e Й—iЙ—o ngalaa ko gorko e rewЙ“e Й—iЙ—o Й“e mbelete-Й—on e seedeeli ngam si gooto he maЙ“Й“e yejjitii goЙ—Й—o o siftirina mbo, woto seedeeli cala siЙ“e noddaama, wote kaaste winndude ko famЙ—i maa ko heewi fa'de e happu mum, ko Й—uum Й“uri nuunЙ—ude ka Alla Й“uri fooccaade wonande seede Й“uri kadi Й“adaade waasde mon sikkitaade, si wonaa kommersaagu ngonaangu ngu yiilaton hakkunde mon, ndeen noon bakkaat alaa he mon nde mbaasaton Й—um winndude, ceednee si on yeeyandiri woto binndoowo e seede lore, si on waЙ—ii Й—uum pellet Й—uum ko faasikaagal e mon, kulee Alla o anndina on Alla ko kattanЙ—o kala huunde."
  2,283,"Si on ngonii e Й—atngal on keЙ“aani binndoowo tottiree jukunnde tamaande, si on koolandirii, oon tottaaЙ—o hoolaare yo tottit hoolaare nde, yo o hul Alla joom makko, wotee cuuЙ—e seedanfaagu kala cuuЙ—o ngu pellet oon Й“ernde makko ko bakkadinnde, Alla na anndi ko ngollaton ko."
  2,284,"Woodanii Alla ko woni ka kammuuli e ka leydi si on Й“annginii ko e pittaali mon wolla on cuuЙ—i ma Alla haasbu mon sabu mum, o yaafoo o lepta mbo wela, Alla ko kattanЙ—o kala huunde."
  2,285,"NulaaЙ—o goongЙ—anii ko jippinaa koo he makko ummade e Joom makko, e goonginЙ“e Й“ee fof Й“e goongЙ—anii Alla e malaykaaji makko e defte makko e nulaaЙ“e makko, min ceerndataa hay gooto e nulaaЙ“e makko, Й“e wi'i min nanii min Й—oftiima hafran amen Joomi amen ko maa woni ruttorde."
  2,286,"Alla fawataa fittaandu kondu hattanaani,woodanii ndu kondu faggii, fawiima e dow mayru kondu faggitii,Joomi amen woto nanngir min ko min njejjitii koo wollo ko min ngoopi koo, woto a faw he amen tampere hono no ndoondirna-Й—aa Й“een adiiЙ“e amen, Joomi amen woto faw min ko min kattanaani, yaafa amin cuura bakkatuuJi amen njurma-Й—aa min ko aan woni keedo amin wollu min e dow yimЙ“e heefereeЙ“e Й“ee."
  3,1,"Alif, Laam, Miim."
  3,2,"Alla: reweteeЙ—o woo alaa si wanaa KaЕӢko. Ko o wuurЙ—o, ГұiiЙ“uЙ—o."
  3,3,"O Jippinirii deftere nden dow maaЙ—a e goonga, goonginnde ko adii nde o Jippini Tawreeta e Linnjiila."
  3,4,"Ko adii, fii fewnugol yimЙ“e Й“en, o Jippini AlQur'aana. Pellet yedduЙ“e aayeeje Alla Й—en, hino woodani Й“e leЙ“te saЙ—tuЙ—e. Alla ko fooluЙ—o, Joom njoЙ“tiigu."
  3,5,"Pellet, Alla, huunde suuЙ—otaako mo ka leydi wanaa ka kammu."
  3,6,"Ko kaЕӢko woni mba'dinoowo on ka renngaaji no o muuyiri. ReweteeЙ—o woo alaa si wanaa kaЕӢko, fooluЙ—o, ГұeeГұuЙ—o."
  3,7,"Ko KaЕӢko Woni JippinЙ—o Deftere nden e maaЙ—a, no e mayre aayeeje Й“aЕӢnguЙ—e; ko kanje woni neene deftere nden, e goЙ—Й—e goo nannduЙ—e. Ammaa Й“en Й“e ooГұaare woni e nder Й“erЙ—e mun, hiЙ“e jokka ko nanndi kon e majje Й—aЙ“Й“ugol fitina e Й—aЙ“ugol firtugol Й—e. Anndataa firo majje si wanaa Alla. TutiiЙ“e Й“en e ganndal no wi'a: "Men gomЙ—inii nde, kala mun ko immorde ka Joomi amen". Waajitotaako si wanaa joomiraaЙ“e haqqillaaji Й“en."
  3,8,"joomi amen, wata ooГұu Й“erЙ—e amen Й—en Й“aawo nde fewnu-Й—aa men, yeЙ—u men yurmeende immorde ka maaЙ—a.Pellet ko aan woni dokko."
  3,9,"Joomi amen, pellet ko a mooЙ“oyoowo yimЙ“e Й“en Гұalnde nde sikke alaa he mun pellet Alla luutintaa fodoore nden."
  3,10,"Pellet Й“en yedduЙ“e, jawle maЙ“Й“e e Й“iЙ—Й“e maЙ“Й“e duncaЕӢtaaЙ“e leЙ“te Alla Й—en hay huunde. Ko Й“en woni carmale yiite ngen."
  3,11,"Wano mbowdi yimЙ“e Fir'awna e Й“en adinooЙ“e Й“ee. ЖҒe fennii aayeeje amen Й—en, Alla nanngitiri Й“e bakkatuuji maЙ“Й“e Й—in. Alla ko saЙ—tuЙ—o leЙ“te."
  3,12,"Maakan Й“en yedduЙ“e: "on fooloyte mooЙ“oye-Й—on ka jahannama". Nge bonii ndaЙ—Й—udi."
  3,13,"GoongЙ—ii laatanike on aaya e Й—in feddeejji Й—iЙ—i fottuЙ—i fii haЙ“ugol: fedde goo no haЙ“a e laawol Alla, wonnde goo ko yeddunde, hiЙ“e yi'iraЙ“e yeru maЙ“Й“e laawЙ“i Й—iЙ—i giiЙ—e gite. Alla no Semmbinira balla makko ngal o mo o muuyi. Pellet, no e Й—um waaju wonannde joomiraaЙ“e haqqillaaji."
  3,14,"YimЙ“e Й“en cuЙ—inanaama yiЙ—ugol tuuyooji: immorde he rewЙ“e e Й“iЙ—Й“e worЙ“e, e jawle tuginidiraaЙ—e, immorde e kaЕӢЕӢe e kaalise, e pucci ЕӢarЙ—iЙ—aaЙ—i, e neemoraaЙ—i, e remuru. ЖҠum Й—on, ko dakamme nguurdam aduna. Alla, no ka makko moЖҙЖҙuЙ—um ruttorde."
  3,15,"Maaku: "E yo mi humpitu on ko Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude e Й—um mon?". No woodani Й“en huluЙ“e ka Joomi maЙ“Й“e, aljannaaji, no ila senngo ley majji, caalli: ko Й“e luttooЙ“e ton, wondude e sonnaaЙ“e laЙ“Й“inaaЙ“e, e yerluyee immorde ka Alla. Alla ko ReЕӢtuЙ—o jeyaaЙ“e Й“en."
  3,16,"ЖҒen wi'ooЙ“e: "Joomi amen, menen men goongЙ—inii, yaafa men junubaaji amen, daЙ—ndaa men leЙ“te yiite"."
  3,17,"MuГұГұiiЙ“e Й“en e goonguЙ“e Й“en e Й—oftiiЙ“e Й“en e wiЕӢtooЙ“e e nafkoobe Й“en e insinotooЙ“e Й“en ka weetndogaaji."
  3,18,"Alla Seedike wonde reweteeЙ—o alaa si wanaa kaЕӢko, Malaa'ika en kadi, e joomiraaЙ“e ganndal Й“en, ko o daraniiЙ—o nunЙ—al. reweteeЙ—o alaa si wanaa KaЕӢko, on fooluЙ—o ГұeeГұuЙ—o."
  3,19,"Pellet diine oo to Alla, ko lislaamu o. OkkaaЙ“e Defte Й“en lurraali si wonaa caggal de ganndal ngal ari ema66e; ko bewre hakkunde maЙ“Й“e. Kala jedduЙ—o aayeeje Alla Й—en, pellet Alla ko jaawuЙ—o hasboore."
  3,20,"Si Й“e njeddandiri e ma, wii: "Mi jebbilanii yeeso am ngo e Alla min e 6een jokku6e e am ". Wii Й“en okkaaЙ“e Defte e humam binne en 6e: " E on njebbilima?" Si Й“e njebbilima, goongo Й“e 6eewii, si Й“e ndunitiima, enee, ko fawi maa ko yottin de. Alla ko jioowo jeyaaЙ“e Й“e."
  3,21,"Pellet, Й“en yeddooЙ“e aayeeje Alla Й—ee, heЙ“e mbara AnnabaaЙ“e Й“e ko aldaa e goonga, Й“e mbara Й“een yamirooЙ“e nunЙ—al, welitinir Й“e lepte muusЙ—e."
  3,22,"Ko Й“en woni Й“e golleeji mun boni Й“en ka aduna e ka laakara, Й“e alaa wallooЙ“e."
  3,23,"E a yi'aali okkaaЙ“e geЙ—al e deftere nden, hiЙ“e noddee e deftere Alla nden fii no nde Гұaawira hakkunde maЙ“Й“e, refti fedde he maЙ“Й“e ko ruЕӢtiiЙ“e tawi ko Й“e Й—uurniiЙ“e?!"
  3,24,"WaЙ—i noon Й“e wi'ii: "Yiite ngen meemataa men si wanaa ГұalЙ—i limtaaЙ—i". hoomtiiЙ“e he diina maЙ“Й“e kan, huunde nde Й“e fefindotonoo."
  3,25,"E ko hol no si men mooЙ“oyii Й“e e Г‘alaande nde sikke alaa e mu'un, woЕӢkii kala hunanee ko ki faggitii kon? Tawi Й“e tooГұetaake."
  3,26,"Maaku: "Yaa Aan LaamЙ—o JeyЙ—o laamu, hiЙ—a okka laamu on mo muuyu-Й—aa, HiЙ—a Й“oora laamu on mo Muuyu-Й—aa, hiЙ—a teddina on mo muuyu-Й—aa, hiЙ—a hoyna on mo muuyu-Й—aa. MoЖҙЖҙere nden ko e junngo maaЙ—a woni, pellet, aan e huunde kala, ko a kattanЙ—o:"
  3,27,"HaЙ—a Naatna jehma on ndeer Гұalawma he, HaЙ—a Naatna Гұalawma o ndeer jehma he. HaЙ—a Yaltina ko wuuri immorde e ko maayi, yaltinaa ko maayi immorde e ko wuuri. HaЙ—a Arsikina on mbo MuuyЙ—aa ko aldaa e limoore."
  3,28,"Wata juul6e 6e njogitor heeferЙ“e Й“e yiЙ—aaЙ“e Й“e ngacca gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“e. Kalo mbo waЙ—ii Й—uum, o laataaki jeyaaЙ—o e diine Alla he hay e huunde, si wanaa nde kulaton e maЙ“Й“e bone. Alla homba on Reentina Hoore-Mun. Ko faade to Alla woni ruttorde nden."
  3,29,"Wii:Si on cuuЙ—ii ko woni e Й“erЙ—e mon maa si on peГұГұali Й—um,Alla homba Й—um anndi,Hombo Anndi ko woni ka kammuuli e ko woni e leydi Alla ko kattan-Й—o kala huunde."
  3,30,"Г‘ande kala woЕӢkii tawata ko ki gollun ko e moЖҙЖҙere hino Й“annaa, e huunde ko ki golle e bone, ki yeloo sinno wonayno hakkunde makki e majje dumunne woЙ—Й—uЙ—o. Alla no Reeentina on Hoore Mun. Alla ko jurmotooЙ—o jeyaaЙ“e Й“e."
  3,31,"wii si onngonii hoЙ—on njidi Alla, cukke e am, Alla yiЙ—a on yaafo mon bakkatuuji mon, Alla ko kafroowo jurmotooЙ—o."
  3,32,"Wii: "ЖҠoftee Alla e NulaaЙ—o on", si Й“e huccitii to, pellet, Alla yiЙ—aa yedduЙ“e Й“en."
  3,33,"Pellet, Alla SuЙ“iima Aadama e Nuuhu e yimЙ“e Ibraahiima Й“een e yimЙ“e Imraana Й“ee e hoore tagoore hee:"
  3,34,"Jurriiya=genyol yoga e maЙ“Й“e iwii e yoga. Alla ko Nanoowo gannduЙ—o."
  3,35,"Tumo de debbo Imraana on wi'noo: "Joomi am, min mi takkanii Ma ko woni ko nder reedu am, ko rimЙ—inaa Й—um, jaЙ“anam, pellet, An woni Nanoowo gannduЙ—o"."
  3,36,"Nde o jibinnoo mo o wi'i: "Min mi jibinii mo ko o deyel", ko Alla Й“uri Anndude ko O jibini, gorko laataaki wano debbo. "Min mi innii mo Maryama, min mi moolii mbo e MaaЙ—a e 6esngu makko o immorde seytaane diiwaaЙ—o diddaaЙ—o o"."
  3,37,"Joomi makko JaЙ“iani mbo jaЙ“annde moЖҙЖҙere,O Neiri mo needi moЖҙЖҙundi,O Halfini mo Jakariya.Tuma kala Jakariya naati e nokku makko e Mihraab,o tawda mo e arsike,o wi'a:Hey, Mariyam hol no heЙ“irЙ—aa Й—um?O jaaboo:ЖҠum ko ta Alla iwri.Pellet,no Arsika on O Muuyi ko aldaa e limoore."
  3,38,"Ko ton Jakariraa'u noddi Jooma mun o maaki: "Joomi am, YeЙ—am immorde ka MaaЙ—a, jurriiya laaЙ“uЙ—o, pellet, An ko A Nanoowo noddaandu"."
  3,39,"Maleykaji en noddi mo hawri homo darii hombo juula to ganngunal, won de: "Alla No WewliniramaYahyaa, goonginЙ—o Konngol iwrungol ka Alla: koohoojo, e reenaaЙ—o [e tuuyo], e Annabaajo jeyaaЙ—o e moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e""
  3,40,"O wii: "Joomam, hol no Й“iЙ—Й—o laatorantoomi, gomЙ—ii mi nawyii, debbo am on ko dimaro?" O wii: "Ko wano noon Alla WaЙ—irta ko O Muuyi [waЙ—de]"."
  3,41,"O wii: "Joomi, WaЙ—anam maande". O wii: "Maande maa nde, ko nde a haaldotaa e yimЙ“e Й“e Й“alЙ—e tati si wonaa e joopagol. JaЕӢtoЙ—aa Joom maaЙ—a ko heewi: subbunhino-Й—aa kiiki e bimmbi"."
  3,42,"Tuma nde Maleykaaji en mbinoo: "Hey Maryama, pellet Alla SuЙ“imaa ma, O LaЙ“Й“inii ma [O SuЙ“ii]maa e dow rewЙ“e winndere he"."
  3,43,"Hey Maryam, toЖҙЖҙinano Joomi maa, sujjaa ndukЖҙЖҙidaa e rukЖҙЖҙooЙ“e Й“en."
  3,44,"ЖҠum Й—oo, ko jeyaaЙ—um e kumpite birniiЙ—e, MeЙ—en Wahayina Й—e e maaЙ—a. A tawanooka e maЙ“Й“e nde Й“e weddotonoo kuЙ—i maЙ“Й“e Й—in: ko hommbo e maЙ“Й“e ne'ata Maryama; a tawanooka e maЙ“Й“e kadi nde Й“e wennjaynoo."
  3,45,"Nde Maleykaaji en mbi'noo: "Hey Maryama, Alla no Wewlinirmaa Konngol immorde e Maako: Innde makko, ko meema-sella, Iisaa geЙ—al Maryama, koohoojo aduna e laakara, jeyaaЙ—a e Й“aЙ—tinaaЙ“e [ka Alla].""
  3,46,"Hombo yeewtida e yimЙ“e Й“e ka woofordu=tiggu e ka sagatalaaku, ko o jeyaaЙ—o e moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e Й“en."
  3,47,"O wi'i: "Joom am, hol no Й“iЙ—Й—o laatoraЕӢta am, Й“anndiЕӢke meemaani kam?". O Daali: "Ko wano non. Alla no Taga ko O Muuyi. Si O Г‘aawii fiyaake, O Daalanay mo [tun]: "Laato! o laatoo"."
  3,48,"Hombo Anndina mo Deftere nde e Г‘eeГұal ngal e Tawreeta e Linnjiila."
  3,49,"E NulaaЙ—o faade e Й“iЙ“Й“e Israa'iila en, wonnde: "GomЙ—ii mi addanii on maande immorde ka Joomi mon. Wonnde miЙ—o tagana on immorde e loopal ko wa'i wa sonndu, mi wutta e muuЙ—um woЕӢtira sonndu e DuЕӢayee Alla. Mi wumtina bunЙ—o, mi sellina baadaaЙ—o, mi wuurnitira maayЙ“e e duЕӢayee Alla. Mi humpita on ko Гұaamoton e ko maroton ka cuuЙ—i mon. Pellet, hino e Й—um, maande wonanannde on si on laatike gomЙ—imЙ“e,"
  3,50,"e goonginЙ—o ko woni yeeso am immorde e Tawreeta, e no mi daknanana on yoga e ko harmannoo on, mi addanii on maande immorde ka Joom mon. kulee Alla Й—oftoЙ—on kam."
  3,51,"Pellet, ko Alla Woni Joomi am e Joomi mon, ndewee Mo. Ko Й—um woni laawol focciingol"."
  3,52,"Tuma nde Iisaa so'unoo keeferaaku ngu e maЙ“Й“e, o wii: "Ko hommbo wallata kam e [diina] Alla [kan]?". HawaaruyaЕӢko en wi'i: "Menen ko men wallooЙ“e [e diina] Alla [kan], men gomЙ—inii Alla, seedo won de ko men jebbiiliiЙ“e"."
  3,53,"Joomi amen, min gomЙ—inii ko nJipinЙ—aa Kon, men jokkii NulaaЙ—o on, Winndu amen e seediiЙ“e Й“en."
  3,54,"ЖҒe pewji Alla Kadi Fewji. Ko Alla Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude e fewjooЙ“e Й“e."
  3,55,"Tuma Alla winoo: "Hey Iisaa, Min ko mi Hunnoowo ma e ЖҒamtoowo ma faade ta Am, e LaЙ“Й“inoowo ma immorde e Й“en yedduЙ“e, e WaЙ—a Й“en jokkuЙ“e ma e dow Й“een yedduЙ“e haa Г‘ande Darngal. Refti ko faade ka Am woni ruttorde mon, Mi Г‘aawa hakkunde mon ko luutondirayno-Й—on e muuЙ—um."
  3,56,"Ammaa Й“en yedduЙ“e, Mi Lepta Й“e Й—on lepte muuuЙ—e ka aduna e ka laakara, alanaaЙ“e faabotooЙ“e."
  3,57,"Ammaa Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“e golli golle-moЖҙЖҙe, O timminanay Й“e njo6di maЙ“Й“e ndin. Alla YiЙ—aa tooГұooЙ“e Й“en"."
  3,58,"ЖҠuum Й—o, MiЙ—en Janngana maa Й—um, immorde e Aayeeje e JaЕӢtoore Г‘eeГұЙ—unde."
  3,59,"Pellet, sifa Iisaa ka Alla, ko sifa Aadama; O Tagii mo immorde e leydi, refti O Daalani mo: "Laato!" o laatii."
  3,60,"Goonga kan ko ko immori ko Joomi maa, wata a laatodo e Й“en sikkitiiЙ“e."
  3,61,"Kala wennjuЙ—o ma fii makko Й“aawo kon ko ar e maa e ganndal, maaku: "Aree nodden Й“iЙ—Й“e amen e Й“iЙ—Й“e mo'on, e rewЙ“e amen e rewЙ“e mo'on, e ko'e amen e ko'e mo'on, refti ГұaagoЙ—en mbaЙ—en kuddi Alla ndin e hoore fenooЙ“e Й“en"."
  3,62,"Pellet Й—um Й—oo, ko Й—um woni fillayee goonga. Alaa deweteeЙ—o si wanaa Alla, pellet, Alla ko KaЕӢko Woni FooluЙ—o Г‘eeГұuЙ—o."
  3,63,"Si Й“e huccitii, pellet Alla ko gannduЙ—o bonnooЙ“e Й“en."
  3,64,"Maaku: "Hey yimЙ“e Defte, aree faade e konngol fotatngol hakkunde amen e mo'on : won de en ndewataa si wanaa Alla, en kafidataa Mo e huunde, wata yoga e me'en jogito yoga joomiraaЙ“e ko woori Alla". Si Й“e huccitii, wi'ee: "Seeditee won de menen ko men jebbiliiЙ“e"."
  3,65,"Ee hey mon yimЙ“e deftete, ko mbeeГұdaton e geЙ—e Ibraahiima, Tawreeta e Linnjiila njppinaaka si wonaa Й“aawo makko : e on kaqqiltaa!."
  3,66,"Hey ko onon Й“ee, on wennjii kon ko ganndal woodani on e mu'un, ko wennjaЕӢton ko danndal alanaa on e mu'un? Alla no Anndi onon on nganndaa."
  3,67,"Ibraahiima laatanooki AlyahuuyaЕӢke wonaana kadi Annasaaraajo, si ko woni, o laatinoke ooГұiiЙ—o [e kala diina] jebbilaniiЙ—o [Diina Lislaamu], o laatanooki jeyaaЙ—o e shirkooЙ“e Й“en."
  3,68,"Pellet, ko Й“uri haadude e Ibraahiima e yimЙ“e Й“en : ko Й“en jokkuЙ“e mo, e oo Annabiijo, e Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e. Alla ko GiЙ—o gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en."
  3,69,"Fedde goo e yimЙ“e Defte Й“en njidi nde Й“e majjina on, Й“e majjiЕӢtaa si wanaa ko'e maЙ“Й“e Й—en Й“e so'aa anndude."
  3,70,"Hey mon yimЙ“e Defte, e ko njeddaЕӢton Aayeeje Alla ЖҠen tara onon ko on seediiЙ“e?"
  3,71,"Hey mon yimЙ“e Defte, e ko jillaЕӢton goonga kan e meh-re nden hoЙ—on cuuЙ—a goonga kan tara onon hoЙ—on ganndi?"
  3,72,"Fedde goo jeyaande e yimЙ“e Defte Й“en wi'i: "GomЙ—inee ko jippinaa kon e Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e ka arannde Гұallal, yeddon ka sakkitoode mayre, bela jo'o, Й“e ruttoo."
  3,73,"Wato on gomЙ—in si wonaa on jokkuЙ—o diina mon kan". Maaku: "Pellet, ko Peewal Alla ngal woni Peewal". [Ko kulil fii ] wata goЙ—Й—o goo okke yeu ko okkaЙ—on kon maa Й“e wennjiroya on Й—um ko Joomi mon. Maaku: "Pellet Й“ural ngal ko e Junngo Alla woni, Homo weeЙ—a ngal on Mo O Muuyi". Alla ko jaacЙ—o [Й“ural] AnnduЙ—o."
  3,74,"Hombo Hertinana Yurmeende Makko nde on mo o muuyi. Alla ko Jom Й“uural Mawngal."
  3,75,"No e yimЙ“e Defte Й“en, on mo kalfiЕӢtaa jawdi wonayndi KINTAAR, on jonnite ndi; hino e maЙ“Й“e kadi, on mo kalfiЕӢtaa "diinaaru", on jonnitataa ma ndu si wanaa a darani mo daЕӢkaranni-Й—aa. ЖҠum non, ko tawde kamЙ“e Й“e wi'i: "Laatanaaki men e humammbinneeЙ“e Й“en laawol"; hiЙ“e taЖҙa penaale huma e Alla hara kamЙ“e heЙ“e nganndi."
  3,76,"Aa'a, kala kuu6nuЙ—o ahadi mu'un o huli, pellet, Alla no YiЙ—i hulooЙ“e Mo Й“en."
  3,77,"ЖҒen wostoratЙ“e ahadi Alla ndin e goondooje maЙ“Й“e coggeloy pamЙ—ukoy, Й“en Й—on, geЙ“al alanaa Й“e ka laakara, Alla yeewtidataa e maЙ“Й“e, O Ndaaroytaa Й“e Г‘ande Darngal, O LaЙ“Й“iЕӢtaa Й“e, no woodani Й“e lepte muusuЙ—e."
  3,78,"No e maЙ“Й“e fedde : hiЙ“e ooГұira Й—emЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en e Deftere nden no sikkiron Й—um ko jeyaaЙ—um e Deftere nden, Й—um le jeyaaka e Deftere nden; hiЙ“e wi'a : "ЖҠum ko ko iwri ka Alla", Й—um le wanaa ka Alla iwri; hiЙ“e takka penaale hoore Alla hara kamЙ“e hiЙ“e ngnndi."
  3,79,"Laatanaaki Й“anndiЕӢke nde Alla Okkata mo Deftere e fahmu e Annabaaku, refti o wi'ana yimЙ“e Й“en: "Laatee jeyaaЙ“e am ko woori Alla", si ko woni: "Laatoree tutiiЙ“e-e-gannde-diina, ko laatinoЙ—on hiЙ—on janngina Deftere nden e ko laatiЙ—on hiЙ—on jannga""
  3,80,"Wanaa nde o yamirta on jogitorgol Maleykaaji en e AnnabaaЙ“e Й“en reweteeЙ“e. E o yamiray on keeferaaku Й“aawo nde wonЙ—on julЙ“e?!"
  3,81,"Tuma nde Alla Жҙettunoo ahadi e AnnabaaЙ“e Й“en : "Si Mi Addanii on Deftere e fahmu, refti NulaaЙ—o ari e mo'on goonginЙ—o kon ko jogiЙ—on, ma on gomЙ—in mo wallitoЙ—on mo". O Daali: "E on qirritike Й—um, on Жҙettii e hoore mun ahadi?". ЖҒe wi'i: "Men qirritike". O Daali: "Seeditee, MiЙ—o wondi e mo'on ka seeditiiЙ“e"."
  3,82,"On huccituЙ—o Й“aawo Й—um, ko Й“en woni yalu6e e dowitaare Й“en."
  3,83,"E ko woori Diina Alla kan Й“e Й—aЙ“Й“ata? Hino woodani mo jebbilaare Й“een won Й“e ka kammuuli e ka leydi, Й—oftaare maa waawneede, ko fa`ade ka Makko Й“e nduttotoo."
  3,84,"Maaku: "Men gomЙ—inii Alla e ko jippinaa dow amen e ko jippinaa dow Ibrahiima e Isma'iila e Ishaaqa e Yaaquuba e TaaniraaЙ“e Й“en e ko Muusaa e Iisaa okkaa e AnnabaaЙ“e Й“en immorde ka Joomi maЙ“Й“e. Men serndataa hakkunde gooto e maЙ“Й“e, Menen wonan de Mo ko men jebbiliiЙ“e"."
  3,85,"Kala Й—aЙ“Й“uЙ—o ko woori Lislaamu on Diina, o jaЙ“aЕӢtaake Й—um, on Й—on ka laakara, ko o jeyaaЙ—o e pertuЙ“e Й“en."
  3,86,"Hol no Alla Fewnirta yimЙ“e yedduЙ“e Й“aawo gomЙ—inal maЙ“Й“e Й“e seedii won de NulaaЙ—o on ko goonga, Й“anngannduyeeji Й—in arii Й“e? Alla Fewnataa yimЙ“e tooГұooЙ“e Й“en."
  3,87,"ЖҒen Й—on, joЙ“di maЙ“Й“e ndin, ko no fawii Й“e kuddi Alla ndin e Maleykaaji en e yimЙ“e Й“en Й“e denndaangal."
  3,88,"Ko Й“e luttooЙ“e e magge. ЖҒe hayfinaЕӢtaake lepte Й—en, Й“e wonaali nee6nanteeЙ“e."
  3,89,"Si wonaa Й“een tuubuЙ“e Й“aawo Й—uum Й“e moЖҙЖҙini. Pellet, Alla ko jaafotooЙ—o jurmotooЙ—o."
  3,90,"Pellet, Й“een yedduЙ“e Й“aawo gooЕӢЙ—inal maЙ“Й“e, refti Й“e Й“eydorii keeferaaku, tuubugol maЙ“Й“e jaЙ“etaake; ko Й“een Й—on noni majjuЙ“e Й“een."
  3,91,"Pellet, Й“en yedduЙ“e Й“e maayi ko Й“e heererЙ“e, gooto e maЙ“Й“e jaЙ“aЕӢtaake, leydi ndin tew kaЕӢЕӢe; hay si o sootorii Й—um. ЖҒen Й—on, no woodani Й“e lepte muusuЙ—e, Й“e alaa wallooЙ“e."
  3,92,"On keЙ“ataa moЖҙЖҙere nden haa wiЕӢtoЙ—on e ko Й“uruЙ—on yiЙ—ude kon. Kala woo ko wiЕӢtiЙ—on, pellet Alla no Anndi Й—um"
  3,93,"Kalo Гұamri laatino koko daganii Й“iЙ—Й“e Israa'iila en, si wonaa ko Israa'iila harminanno hoore-mun ko adii Tawreeta Jippaade. Maaku: "ngaddee Tawreetaare nden jnanngon nde, si on laatiima gooЕӢguЙ“e"."
  3,94,"Kala pekindiiЙ—o fenaande [dammbi] e Alla Й“aawo Й—um, ko Й“en Й—on woni tooГұooЙ“e Й“en."
  3,95,"Maaku: "Alla gooЕӢЙ—ii. Njokke diina Ibraahiima kan; ooГұiika [gaa diinaaji mehre], o laatanooki jeyaaЙ—o e Й“en sirkooЙ“e."
  3,96,"Pellet, aranndu e Suudu waЙ—anaandu yimЙ“e Й“en, ko ndun wondu Bakkata; barkinaandu e peewal wonan de Winndere nden."
  3,97,"Ino e mayru kaawisaaji Й“annguЙ—e : darorde Ibraahiima nden. Kala naatuЙ—o e mayru, o laatoo kooliiЙ—o. No woodani Alla e dow yimЙ“e Й“en hajjugol ka Suudu [hormaandu], wona nde on hattanЙ—o e mayru laawol. Kala on yedduЙ—o, pellet, Alla ko YonndiniiЙ—o e winndere nden."
  3,98,"Maaku: "Hey mon yimЙ“e Defte, e ko njeddanton Aayeeje Alla Й—iin, Alla ko ceediiЙ—o ko ngolloton kon?"."
  3,99,"Maaku: "Hey mon yimЙ“e Defte, ko falotoЙ—on e laawol Alla ngol, on gomЙ—inЙ—o HoЙ—on Й—aЙ“Й“ana ngol ooГұanЙ—e tara ko on seediiЙ“e! Alla wonaali WelsindiiЙ—o e ko ngolloton kon"."
  3,100,"Hey mon gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e, si on Й—oftike fedde e Й“en okkaaЙ“e defte, Й“e nduttay on heeferЙ“e Й“aawo gooЕӢЙ—inal mon."
  3,101,"E ko honno njeddirton nde tawnoo Aayeeje Alla Й—en no janngeede e dow mooЙ—on, NulaaЙ—o Makko on kadi no hakkunde mo'on? Kala on mooliiЙ—o e Alla, gomЙ—ii o fewnaama e laawol foccii ngol."
  3,102,"Hey mon gomЙ—imЙ“e, kuliree Alla no O Haaniri hulireede, wata on maayu dey, si wanaa hara ko on jebbiliiЙ“e."
  3,103,"Jogitee Й“oggol Alla ngol on denndaangal, wata on certu. JaЕӢtoЙ—on dokkeAlla on e dow mooЙ—on nde laatinoЙ—on ayruЙ“e, O Woowindiri hakkunde Й“erЙ—e mon Й—en woЕӢtirЙ—on e dokke Makko koo on musiЙ—Й“e; on laatioke e tonndu ngayka yiite, O DaЙ—ndi on e magge. ko wano nii Alla ЖҒannginiraЕӢta on Aayeeje Makko Й—en, bela jo'o, on feeway."
  3,104,"Yo laato e mooЙ—on mofte : noddooje e moЖҙЖҙere, yamirooЙ“e ko moЖҙЖҙi haЙ—ooЙ“e ko aГұinii. Ko Й“en Й—on ngoni malaaЙ“e Й“en."
  3,105,"Wata on laato hona Й“en sertuЙ“e lurri Й“aawo nde laaЙ“tuЙ—iЙ—in ari e maЙ“Й“e. ЖҒen Й—on, no woodani Й“e lepte muusuЙ—e."
  3,106,"Г‘ande jeece rawnata geece goo Й“awla. Si ko Й“en Й“e jeece mu'un Й“awli : "e on yeddu Й“aawo gomЙ—inal mon? MeeЙ—iree lepte Й—en sabu ko laatinoЙ—on hiЙ—on njedda"."
  3,107,"Si tawii ko Й“een Й“e jeece mun ndanwni, Й“e ngonii e ndeer Yurmeende Alla, kamЙ“e ko Й“e saasooЙ“e toon."
  3,108,"ЖҠee Й—oo, ko Aayeeje Alla, MiЙ—en Janngira Й—e e dow maaЙ—a e goonga. Alla wonaani muuyoowo tooГұde e winndere he."
  3,109,"Ko Alla Woodani kala ko woni deer kammuuji e leydi, ko faade ka Alla woni ruttorde fiyakuuji Й—in."
  3,110,"On laatike leГұol Й“urngol moЖҙЖҙude yaltinanaangol yimЙ“e Й“en:hiЙ—on njamiraa ko moЖҙЖҙi haЙ—on ko kaЙ—o, koh bonii hoЙ—on goЕӢЙ—ini AllaSi yimЙ“e Defte Й“en gooЕӢЙ—inno,Й—um laatotono moЖҙЖҙere wonannde Й“e.No e maЙ“Й“e goЕӢЙ—inЙ“e, kono ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude ko e maЙ“Й“e ko yaluЙ“eЙ—oftaare"
  3,111,"ЖҒe lorrirtaa on si wanaa lorra [Й—emЙ—e]. Si Й“e kaЙ“iimaЙ“ii on , maaЙ“e nduЕӢtu Й“aawoo maЙ“Й“ea refti, ho Й“e mballetaake."
  3,112,"Koyeera faЕӢtike Й“e nokku kala ka Й“e tawaa, si wanaa Й“e Жҙettu ahadi ka Alla e ka yimЙ“e Й“en. ЖҒe hootidi e tikkere immorde ka Alla Й“e huuЙ“iЕӢtiniraa baasal : Й—um non, ko tawde Й“e laatinoke hiЙ“e yedda Aayeeje Alla Й—en, Й“e wara AnnabaaЙ“e Й“en ko aldaa e goonga. ЖҠum non, ko sabu ko Й“e njeddi kon, Й“e laatii jaggitooЙ“e."
  3,113,"ЖҒe ngona fotatЙ“e. No e yimЙ“e defte Й“een fedde feewunde : heЙ“e njannga Aayeeje Alla Й—e saangaaji jemma, heЙ“e cujja."
  3,114,"HiЙ“e ngooЕҠЙ—ina Alla e Г‘annde Sakkitiinde nden, hiЙ“e njamira ko moЖҙЖҙi kaЙ—a ko bonii, hiЙ“e yaccoo e moЖҙЖҙereeje. ЖҒen ko jeyaaЙ“e e moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e Й“en."
  3,115,"Huunde fof ko Й“e mbaЙ—i e moЖҙЖҙere, Й“e njeddantaake Й—um. Alla ko gannduЙ—o hulooЙ“e Й“en."
  3,116,"Pellet, Й“en yedduЙ“e, jawЙ—eele maЙ“Й“e e Й“iЙ“Й“e maЙ“Й“e dunncantaa- Й“e lepte Alla Й—en hay huunde. Ko Й“en Й—on woni yimЙ“e yiite Й“en : kamЙ“e ko Й“e luttooЙ“e ton."
  3,117,"Sifa ko Й“e nafqata kon e Й—am nguurndam aduna; no wa'i wa henndu, no e mayru Й“uuЙ“ol, ndu hawri e coГұal yimЙ“e tooГұooЙ“e, ndu halka mba[ngesa]. Alla TooГұaani Й“e, si ko woni, ko ko'e maЙ“Й“e Й“e tooГұi."
  3,118,"Hey mon yo goЕӢЙ—inЙ“e, wata on jogito weldiiЙ“e ko woori on : Й“e raЙ“Й“ikintaako on e fii bonnugol on. ЖҒe yelike nde tampoton. GooЕӢЙ—ii ngaГұgu ngun feeГұirii ka kunndule maЙ“Й“e, ko ko Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en cuuЙ—i kon Й“uri mawnude.GoЕӢЙ—ii Men ЖҒannginanii on Aayeeje Й—en, si on laatike haqqilooЙ“e."
  3,119,"Onon Й“ee, hiЙ—on yiЙ—i Й“e kamЙ“e Й“e yiЙ—aa on. HiЙ—on goЕӢЙ—ini Deftere nden fow, si Й“e hawrii e mo'on, Й“e wi'a: "Men gooЕӢЙ—inii", si Й“e weddike, Й“e ЕӢatana on kolli immorde e tikkere. Maaku: "Maayee e tikkere mon", pellet, Alla ko AnnduЙ—o ko woni e Й“erЙ—e."
  3,120,"Si moЖҙЖҙere heЙ“ii on, metta Й“e, si bone kadi heЙ“ii on, Й“e mbeltora Й—um. Si on muГұГұike on gomЙ—ii, pewje maЙ“Й“e Й—en lorrataa on hay huunde. Pellet, Alla ko HuuЙ“itiiЙ—o golle maЙ“Й“e."
  3,121,"Tuma nde dawnoЙ—aa ka Й“eynguure maaЙ—a, haЙ—a werna gooЕӢЙ—uЙ“eЙ“e tommborЙ—e hare. Alla ko Nanoowo gannduЙ—o."
  3,122,"Tuma nde feddeeji Й—iЙ—i e mo'on himmu no, nde cooyato, ko Alla non woni GiЙ—o maЙ“Й“e. Ko Alla woni ko goЕӢЙ—imЙ“e Й“en haani hoolorde."
  3,123,"GooЕӢЙ—ii Alla Wallii on Гұande Badri, tawi ko on hoyЙ“e. Kulee Alla, belajo'o on yettay [Mo]."
  3,124,"Nde maakanaynoЙ—aa gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“en: "Enee, yonaЕӢtaa on nde Joomi mo'on Й“eydanta on Malaa'ikaaЙ“e guluuje tato jippinaaЙ“e?"."
  3,125,"Pellet, si on muГұГұike on gomЙ—ii, e arday on hawjere maЙ“Й“e, Й—um Й—oo, Joomi mo'on no ЖҒeydira on guluuje jowi Malaa'ika maandinaaЙ“e."
  3,126,"Alla WaЙ—iraani Й—um si wanaa wewlere wonannde on, e no Й“erЙ—e mon Й—en Й—eeЖҙira Й—um. Ballal iwrataa si wanaa ka Alla, On pooluЙ—o, Г‘eeГұuЙ—o."
  3,127,"Ko fii yo O tayЖҙu fedde e Й“en yedduЙ“e maa O Wirta Й“e, Й“e nduttoo ko Й“e sooyuЙ“e."
  3,128,"Laatanaaki ma e fiyaake on hay e huunde : maa O JaЙ“an Й“e tuubuubuyee, maa O Lepto Й“e, pellet, kamЙ“e ko Й“e tooГұooЙ“e."
  3,129,"Ko Alla Woodani kala ko woni ka kammuuli e ka leydi. Himo Haforana on mo O Muuyi, O Lepta on mo O Muuyi. Alla ko Haforoowo YurmeteeЙ—o."
  3,130,"Hey mon yo goЕӢЙ—imЙ“e, wata on Гұaamu ribaa, cowalle sowaaЙ—e. Kulee Alla, belajo'o, on malete."
  3,131,"kulee ngen yiite maranaange Й“en heeferЙ“e."
  3,132,"ЖҠoftee Alla e NulaaЙ—o on, belajo'o, on njurmete."
  3,133,"Yaccee faade e haforanal immorde ka Joomi mo'on e Aljanna, yaajeendi Makko ndin no fota [e yaajeendi] kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin, o maranaama Й“en gomЙ—uЙ“e."
  3,134,"ЖҒen nafqooЙ“e ka neweende e ka saЙ—teende neweende, e Й“en suuЙ—ooЙ“e tikkere, e Й“en yaafotooЙ“e yimЙ“e Й“en. Alla no YiЙ—i moЖҙЖҙinooЙ“e Й“en."
  3,135,"e Й“en tawЙ“e si Й“e mbaЙ—ii panЕӢkare maa Й“e tooГұii ko'e maЙ“Й“e, Й“e nganndita Alla Й“e insinanoo jbakkatuuji maЙ“Й“e Й—in . E ko hommbo haforata si wanaa Alla? Hara Й“e deppitaaki e ko Й“e mbaЙ—i kon, tawa hiЙ“e nganndi."
  3,136,"ЖҒen Й—on, njoЙ“di maЙ“Й“e ndin ko yaafuyee immorde ka Joomi maЙ“Й“e, e Aljannaaji : no ila e ley majji, caatli, duumotooЙ“e ton. MoЖҙЖҙii mbarjaari gollooЙ“e Й“en."
  3,137,"GomЙ—ii yawtii ado mon Й—ate. Njahee ka leydi ndaaron hol no battane fennunooЙ“e Й“en laatornoo .!"
  3,138,"ЖҠum Й—oo, ko ЖҒanngannduyee wonannde yimЙ“e Й“en, e peewal e waaju wonannde gooЕӢЙ—uЙ“e Й“en."
  3,139,"Wata on lo'ino, wata on cuno, ko onon woni toowuЙ“e Й“en, si on laatike gooЕӢЙ—uЙ“e."
  3,140,"Si barme heЙ“ii on, goЕӢЙ—ii barme sugu mun heЙ“ii yimЙ“e Й“en. ЖҠii ГұalЙ—i, MeЙ—en Yiltindira Й—i hakkunde yimЙ“e Й“en, e fii no Alla Anndira gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“en, O Jogitoo e mooЙ—on seedatooЙ“e. Alla YiЙ—aa tooГұooЙ“e Й“en."
  3,141,"e fii yo Alla LaЙ“Й“in Й“en gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e O Halka heeferЙ“e Й“en."
  3,142,"Kaa on cikku on naatay Aljanna hara Alla Anndaali Й“en tiЙ—niiЙ“e e mooЙ—on O Annda muГұГұiiЙ“e Й“en?"
  3,143,"GooЕӢЙ—ii on laatike hiЙ—on yeloo maayde nden ado on hawrude e mayre, gooЕӢЙ—ii on yi'ii nde hiЙ—on ndaara."
  3,144,"Muhammadu wonaani si wanaa NulaaЙ—o : gooЕӢЙ—ii feЖҙЖҙii ko adii mo NulaaЙ“e. E si o faatike maa o waraama, on waylitoto e baЙ—te [keeferaaku] mo'on ? Kala waylitiiЙ—o e baЙ—te mu'un, o lorrirtaa Alla hay e huunde, arma Alla YoЙ“ita Й“en jaarnooЙ“e [Mo]."
  3,145,"Laatanaaki woЕӢki nde ki maayata si wanaa e duЕӢayee Alla. Ko winndaaЙ—um [waЙ—anaa] lajal. Mo faandike njoЙ“di aduna, Men Okkay mo e mayri, mo faandi kadi njoЙ“di laakara, Men Okkay mo e mayri, ma Men njoЙ“ jaarnooЙ“e Й“en."
  3,146,"Heewii e AnnabaaЙ“e Й“e haЙ“i wondude e maЙ“Й“e jamaaji Й—uuЙ—uЙ—i, Й“e lo'inanooki sabu ko heЙ“i Й“e kon e laawol Alla, Й“e lo'aano Й“e jaasiЕӢkinaaki. Alla no YiЙ—i muГұГұotooЙ“e Й“en."
  3,147,"Konngol maЙ“Й“e laataaki si wanaa wi'ugol: "Joomi amen, haforan men bakkatuuji amen e fantingol amen nder fiyaake amen, tabiЕӢtinaa teppe amen, wallaa men e dow yimЙ“e heeferЙ“e Й“en"."
  3,148,"Alla Okki Й“e mbarjaari aduna ndin e moЖҙЖҙere mbarjaari laakara. Alla no YiЙ—i moЖҙЖҙinooЙ“e Й“en."
  3,149,"Hey mon yo goЕӢЙ—imЙ“e, si on Й—oftike Й“en heeferЙ“e, Й“e ruttay on e batte [kaaferaaku] mon, waylitoЙ—on ko on hayruЙ“e(pertube)."
  3,150,"Si ko woni, ko Alla woni GiЙ—o mon, ko KaЕӢko woni Й“urЙ—o moЖҙЖҙuЙ—o e wallooЙ“e Й“e."
  3,151,"Arma Men mberoo kulol e nder Й“erЙ—e Й“en heeferЙ“e, sabu ko Й“e kafidi Alla e kon ko O Jippinanaali hujja. JaaЖҙnde maЙ“Й“e ko ka yiite, bonii jaaЖҙnde Й“en tooГұooЙ“e."
  3,152,"GoЕӢЙ—ii Alla Goonginanii on Fodoore Makko nden tuma nde waraynoЙ—on Й“e e DuЕӢayee Makko, haa nde cooyЙ—on lurruЙ—on e fiyaake Й—en, yedduЙ—on Й“aawo o hollii on ko yiЙ—uЙ—on. No e mon Й“en faalaaЙ“e aduna, no e mon kadi Й“en faalaaЙ“e laakara. Hooti O Yiili on e maЙ“Й“e fii yo O Ndaarndo on. GoЕӢЙ—ii O Yaafanike on. Alla ko Jom ЖҒural e dow goЕӢЙ—imЙ“e Й“en."
  3,153,"Tuma nde dogaynoЙ—on on yeЖҙЖҙitaako hay e gooto, NulaaЙ—o on no noddira on Й“aawo mon. Suno e hoore suno heЙ“i on fii wata on cuno e kon ko laawii on wanaa e kon ko heЙ“i on. Alla ko kumpitiiЙ—o e ko. Ngolloton ko"
  3,154,"Refti O Jippini e mo'on Й“aawo annde nden, hoolaare : ЕӢoЕӢre, hende sudda fedde e mo'on ; fedde goo, pittaali maЙ“Й“e no aanini Й“e, hiЙ“e sikka Alla ko wanaa goonga ; sikke yimЙ“e majjere, heЙ“e mbia: "mbele no woodani men e fiyaake Й—en goЙ—Й—um ?" Maaku: "Pellet, fiyaake Й—en fof ko Alla woodani". HiЙ“e cuuЙ—a e pittaali maЙ“Й“e Й—in ko Й“e feГұГұinantaa ma, hiЙ“e mbi'a: "Si tawno no woodannoo men e fiyaake Й—en goЙ—Й—um, men mbaretanooke Й—oo". Maaku: "Hay si tawno on ngonno ka cuuЙ—i mon, feeГұayno Й“een Й“e Alla Winndi e dow mun maayde ka lelorЙ—e maЙ“Й“e", e fii yo O LaЙ“Й“in ko woni Й“erЙ—e mon. Alla ko AnnduЙ—o ko woni e Й“erЙ—e."
  3,155,"Pellet, Й“en doknooЙ“e e mo'on Гұande koneeli Й—in Й—iЙ—i fottunoo, anndu pellet, ko seytaane fergitiЙ“e sabu yoga e ko Й“e faggitii. GooЕӢЙ—ii Alla Yaafike Й“e. Pellet, Alla ko YaafotooЙ—o MuГұoowo."
  3,156,"Hey mon yo goЕӢЙ—inЙ“e, wata on wa'u wa Й“en heeferЙ“e Й“e wi'ani siЙ—Й“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en : "Si Й“e njehii ka leydi, maa Й“e laatike haЙ“ooЙ“e, si Й“e laatino ka amen goo, Й“e waretanooke", ko fii yo Alla WaЙ—ir Й—um Й—on nimse ka Й“erЙ—e mo'on, Alla ko jioowo ko golloton kon."
  3,157,"Hay si on mbara e fii laawol Alla maa on maayii, ko yaafuyee immorde ka Alla e yurmeende Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude ko Й“e mooЙ“ata."
  3,158,"Si on maayii maa on mbraama, pellet, ko ka Alla mooЙ“eteЙ—on."
  3,159,"Ko sabu yurmeende imoorde ka Alla newaniЙ—aa Й“e. Si laatino saЙ—tuЙ—o tikka Й“erndeejo, Й“e lancotono Й“e iwa takko maa. Yaafo Й“e imsinanoЙ—aa Й“e, diisinoЙ—aa Й“e e fiyaake Й—en. Si a fellitii, fawo e Alla. Pellet, Alla no YiЙ—i fawotooЙ“e Й“en [e Makko]."
  3,160,"Si Alla Wallii on pooloowo on alaa., si O Hoynii on ko hommbo wallata on Й“aawo Makko? Ko e Alla woni ko goЕӢЙ—imЙ“e Й“en haani fawaade."
  3,161,"Laatanaaki Annabaajo woo nde o jamfotoo. Kala jamfiiЙ—o o addoyay ko o jamfii kon Г‘ande Darngal.Hooti woЕӢkii kala yoЙ“ee njoЙ“di ko ki faggitii, kamЙ“e Й“e tooГұetaake."
  3,162,"E ko on jokkuЙ—o welayee Alla on wa'ata wa on duttodiiЙ—o e tikkere immornde ka Alla kadi jaaЖҙnde makko nden ko jahannama? nge bonii ruttorde."
  3,163,"KamЙ“e ko Й“e darjaaji ka Alla, Alla ko ji*oowo ko Й“e ngollata kon."
  3,164,"GoЕӢЙ—ii Alla MoЖҙЖҙike e goЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“en, tuma nde O Imminnoo e maЙ“Й“e NulaaЙ—o jeyaaЙ—o e maЙ“Й“e, himo janngana Й“e Aayeeje Makko, himo laЙ“Й“ina Й“e, himo anndina Й“e Deftere nden e Г‘eeГұal ngal, hay si Й“e woniino adii nder majjere Й“anngunde."
  3,165,"E nde musiiba heЙ“unoo on, goЕӢЙ—ii on heЙ“iino yeru mun Й—iЙ—i, wi'uЙ—on: "No Й—um woniri?!" Maaku: "ЖҠum ko immorde e pittaali mo'on". Pellet, Alla ko kaЙ—tanЙ—o kala huunde."
  3,166,"Ko heЙ“i on kon Гұande dente Й—en Й—iЙ—e fottunoo, ko e DuЕӢayee(sakkitoore) Alla, e fii no Alla Anndira goЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“en."
  3,167,"e no O Anndira Й“en naafiqiiЙ“e, Й“e wi'anaa: "ngaree kaЙ“eЙ—on fii laawol Alla ngol maa duГұon". ЖҒe wi'i: "Si meЙ—en ganndunoo hare men jokkay on". KamЙ“e nden Гұande heen, ko keeferaaku ngun Й“urnoo Й“aЙ—taade e dii goЕӢЙ—inal ngal : hiЙ“e wowlira kunnduЙ—e maЙ“Й“e ko alaa e Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e. Ko Alla ЖҒuri Anndude ko Й“e soomi."
  3,168,"ЖҒeen wi'anЙ“e musiЙ—Й“e maЙ“Й“e, Й“e njooЙ—ii: "Si tawno Й“e Й—oftino men, Й“e mbaretanooke". Makku: "Pottinee maayde nden e pittaali mo'on si on laatike gooЕӢЙ—uЙ“e!"."
  3,169,"Wata a sikku Й“en waraaЙ“e fii laawol Alla ngol ko maayuЙ“e, ko woni: ko wuuruЙ“e ka Joomi maЙ“Й“e hiЙ“e arsikinee,"
  3,170,"hiЙ“e mbeltori ko Alla Okki Й“e kon e ЖҒural Makko, hiЙ“e mbeltina Й“en [siЙ—Й“e] maЙ“Й“e Й“e Й“e hawraani e mu'un Й“aawo maЙ“Й“e, wonnde kulol alanaa Й“e, wanaa kamЙ“e woni ko sunoytoo."
  3,171,"HiЙ“e mbeltora( weltoro) dokke immo rde ka Alla e Й“ural. E wonnde pellet, Alla yeebataako njoЙ“di goЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“en."
  3,172,"ЖҒen nootiiЙ“e Alla e NulaaЙ—o on Й“aawo nde barmeere nden heЙ“i Й“e. Hino woodani Й“en moЖҙЖҙinЙ“e e maЙ“Й“e Й“e kulii Alla, njoЙ“di mawndi."
  3,173,"ЖҒen Й“e yimЙ“e Й“en wi'annoo: "Pellet yimЙ“e Й“en mooЙ“anike on, kuleeЙ“e". ЖҠum Й“eydi Й“e goЕӢЙ—inal, Й“e wi': "Alla yonii men, O moЖҙЖҙii yonndinoraaЙ—o"."
  3,174,"ЖҒe ruttodi e dokke immorde ka Alla e Й“ural, bone hewtaali Й“e, Й“e jokki yarluyee Alla on. Alla ko Jom-Й“ural mawngal."
  3,175,"Nganndee pellet, Й—um mo'on ko seytaane : himo hulЙ“inira Й—um weldiiЙ“e makko Й“en. Wata on kul Й“e, kulee Lam, si on laatike goЕӢЙ—imЙ“e."
  3,176,"Wata sunine Й“en yaccotooЙ“e e keeferaaku, pellet, Й“en lorrataa Alla hay huunde. Alla YiЙ—i ko nde o waa-sata WaЙ—annde geЙ—al ka laakara. No woodani Й“e lepte mawЙ—e."
  3,177,"Pellet, Й“en sottitoriiЙ“e keeferaaku ngun goЕӢЙ—inal, Й“e lorrataa Alla hay huunde. Hino woodani Й“e lepte muusuЙ—e."
  3,178,"Wota Й“een yedduЙ“e cikku won de ko Min NeeЙ“nirani Й“e kon ko moЖҙЖҙere pittaali Й—in. Anndu pellet, ko Min NeeЙ“irani Й“e ko no Й“e Й“eydora bakkaat. Hino woodani Й“e lepte hkynayЙ—e."
  3,179,"Laatanaaki Alla nde O Accata goЕӢЙ—imЙ“e Й“en e hoore ko wonЙ—on e mun kon haa O Senndindira soЙ“uЙ—o e laaЙ“uЙ—o. Laatanaaki Alla kadi nde O ЖіelliЕӢta on e ko wirnii kon, si ko woni, Alla no SuЙ“ora e NulaaЙ“e Makko Й“en on mo O Muuyi. nGooЕӢЙ—inee Alla e NulaaЙ“e Makko Й“en, si on goЕӢЙ—inii on goЕӢЙ—ii, hino woodani on njoЙ“di mawndi."
  3,180,"Wata Й“en wuddirooЙ“e ko Alla Okki Й“e kon e ЖҒural Makko sikku Й—um ko moЖҙЖҙere wonannde Й“e. Si ko woni, Й—um ko bone wonannde Й“e. Arma Й“e ЕӢannanoye ko Й“e wuddiri kon Г‘ande Darngal. Ko Alla woodani ndonndi kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin. Alla ko HumpitiiЙ—o ko golloton."
  3,181,"GooЕӢЙ—ii Allaahu on Nanii konngol Й“en wi'uЙ“e: "Alla ko baasЙ—o menen ko men alЙ—uЙ“e!". Arma Men winnda ko Й“e wowli kon e wargol Й“e ngol AnnabaaЙ“e Й“en ko aldaa e goonga, Men Daala: "MeeЙ—ee lepte sunna-royta""
  3,182,"ЖҠuym waЙ—irii sabu ko juuЙ—e mon Й—en ngardini kon. E won de pellet, Alla Wonaani tooГұoowo jeyaaЙ“e Й“en."
  3,183,"ЖҒen wi'uЙ“e: "Alla Ahodii e amen wota men goЕӢЙ—in NulaaЙ—o woo haa on addana men Й“aЙ—torЙ—um, yiite no Гұaama Й—um". Maaku: "GoЕӢЙ—ii NulaaЙ“e goo ado am addaniino on Й“anngannduyeeji e kon ko wi'uЙ—on, e ko waranЙ—on Й“en si on laatike goognuЙ“e?"."
  3,184,"Si Й“e njeddii ma, gooЕӢЙ—ii NulaaЙ“e goo ado maa pennanooma, Й“e ngadduno e ЖҒanngannduyeeji (peeГұЙ—i) ЖҠeri e Deftere jalbuunde."
  3,185,"Kala woЕӢkii meeЙ—ay maayde. Pellet, ko on hunnaЕӢteeЙ“e njoЙ“diiji mon Й—in Г‘ande Darngal. Kala on pottinaaЙ—o e yiite ngen o naadaa Aljanna, goЕӢЙ—ii o malaama. Nguurda aduna Й—am wonaani si wanaa dakammehun hodaykun."
  3,186,"Ma on njarribore jawЙ—eele mon Й—en e pittaali mon Й—in, ma on nanir Й“en okkaaЙ“e Defte Й“en ado mooЙ—o e Й“en sirkuЙ“e lorra Й—uЙ—uka. Si on muГұГұike on goЕӢЙ—ii, pellet, nganndee Й—um, ko jeyaaЙ—um e pellite fiyakuuji."
  3,187,"JaЕӢtii tuma nde Alla Жіettunoo Ahadi e okkaaЙ“e Deftere Й“en : "Ma on Й“annginannde yimЙ“e hara on cuuЙ—aani nde". ЖҒe mbernii ndi Й“aawo maЙ“Й“e Й“e sodtitori ndi coggel pamarel! Bonii ko Й“e soЙ—titori!"
  3,188,"Wata sikke Й“en weltorayЙ“e huunde nde Й“e okkaa, hiЙ“e yiЙ—i nde Й“e yettirtee ko Й“e mbaЙ—aani, wata sikku Й“en ko daЙ—ayЙ“e lepte Й—en. Hino woodani Й“e lepte muusuЙ—e."
  3,189,"Ko Alla Woodani Laamu kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin. Alla ko kattanЙ—o kala huunde."
  3,190,"Pellet, no e tagugol kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin e luutondirgol jemma e Гұalawma ngol, ko Aayeeje wonannde Й“en haqqilooЙ“e."
  3,191,"ЖҒen annditooЙ“e Alla ka Й“e darii e ka Й“e jooЙ—ii e ka Й“e lelori becce maЙ“Й“e, hiЙ“e miijitoo fii takgol kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin : "Joomi amen, A Tagiraani Й—um meere, senayee woodanii Ma, ЖҠaЙ—ndu men lepte yiite"."
  3,192,"Joomo amen, pellet, An, Mo NaaduЙ—aa yiite, goЕӢЙ—ii A Hoynii mo. Alanaa tooГұooЙ“e Й“en wallooЙ“e."
  3,193,"Joomi amen, menen men nanii noddoowo no nodda e goЕӢЙ—inal wonnde : "GoЕӢЙ—inee Joomi mon", men gomЙ—ini. Joomi amen, Haforan men junuubi amen, Motanaa men boneeji amen, mbarda men e Й—igguЙ“e Й“en."
  3,194,"Joomi amen, Okku men ko poduЙ—aa men kon e dow NulaaЙ“e Maa Й“en, wata A Hoynu men Г‘ande Darngal. Pellet, An A Lunndotaako fodoore."
  3,195,"Joomi maЙ“Й“e Jaabinani Й“e : Min Mi Yeebataa golle golloowo e mooЙ—on, woni gorko maa debbo, yoga e mooЙ—on iwde e yoga. ЖҒen ferЙ“e yaltinaa ka galleeji mun,Й“e lorraa e Laawol Am ngol, Й“e kaЙ“aa Й“e mbaraa, ko pellet Min hafratЙ“e bonЙ—i maЙ“Й“e Й—in, e ko pellet Mi Naatnay Й“e Aljanna Й—i caatli no ila e mun, Й—um ko njoЙ“di immorde ka Alla, No ka Alla njoЙ“di moЖҙЖҙundi."
  3,196,"Wata hode yiltondirgol Й“en heeferЙ“e ka leydi ."
  3,197,"dakammeyon pamaroy, hooti jaaЖҙnde maЙ“Й“e nden ko jahannama, nge bonii ndaЙ—Й—o!"
  3,198,"Kono Й“en huluЙ“e Joomi maЙ“Й“e, hino woodani Й“e Aljannaaji, hino ila ley majji caatli; ko Й“e duumotooЙ“e nder majji, Й—um ko jipporde immorde ka Alla. Ko woni ka Alla Й“uri moЖҙЖҙani Й—igguЙ“e Й“en."
  3,199,"Pellet, no e yimЙ“e Defte Й“en, on goЕӢЙ—inЙ—o Alla e ko Jippinaa e mon kon, e ko Jippinaa e maЙ“Й“e kon ; yaЕӢkinanii Й“e Alla, Й“e waЙ—titirtaa Aayeeje Alla Й—en coggeloy pamaroy. ЖҒen, hino woodani Й“e njoЙ“di maЙ“Й“e ndin ka Joomi maЙ“Й“e. Pellet, Alla ko YaawuЙ—o Гұaawoore."
  3,200,"Ko onon yo goЕӢЙ—inЙ“e, muГұГұee, fooliron muГұal, tuuntondЙ—on, kulon Alla, belajo'o on maloyete."
  4,1,"EEHEY mon yimЙ“e! Kulee Joomi mon On TakЙ—o on immorde e woЕӢkii goooti, O Tagi immorde e makki debbo makki, O Saaki immorde e Й“en Й—iЙ—o worЙ“e Й—uuЙ—uЙ“e e rewЙ“e. KUlee Alla On Mo naamnanirton sabu mun, [rentoЙ—on kadi] e enЙ—ammaaje Й—en. Pellet, Alla Laatike e dow mon Deenoowo."
  4,2,"Jonne wonduЙ“e Й“en jawЙ—eele maЙ“Й“e Й—en. Wata on waostondir soЙ“e Й—en ko laaЙ“i. Wata on Гұaamu jawle maЙ“Й“e Й—en [waЙ—ton Й—um] e jawle maЙ“Й“e Й—en. Pellet, Й—um laatike bakkaatu mawЙ—o."
  4,3,"Si on kulii roЕӢkugol nunЙ—ude e wonduЙ“e Й“en, ndeesee ko laaЙ“ani on e rewЙ“e, Й—iЙ—o e tato e nayo. Si on kulii roЕӢkugol nunЙ—ude, waЙ—ee gooto maa Й“e jeyruЙ—on Гұaame mon ; ko Й—um Й“uri Й“aЙ—taade nde on tooГұu."
  4,4,"Jonniree rewЙ“e Й“en teЕӢe maЙ“Й“e Й—en dokkal. Si Й“e anniyanike on goЙ—Й—um e Й—en [teЕӢe] e hoore laaЙ“al woЕӢkii, Гұaamee Й—um, no newanii on Й“uuЙ“ani on."
  4,5,"Wata on jonnitu Й—ayЙ“e Й“e jawЙ—ele mon Й—en Й—e Alla WaЙ—irani on dartorЙ—e. Г‘amminee Й“e e majje, koltinon Й“e, wowlanon Й“e konngol moЖҙЖҙol."
  4,6,"Njarribee wonduЙ“e Й“en si Й“e yottike desal, si on so'ii e maЙ“Й“e peewal, njonniteeЙ“e jawЙ—eele maЙ“e Й—en, wata on Гұaamir Й—e faЕӢtinngol e heЙ—oo yo Й“e mawnude. On tawЙ—o ko o galo, yo o naЕӢto, on tawЙ—o ko o baaso, yo o Гұaamir no moЖҙЖҙiri. Si on jonnitiiЙ“e jawle maЙ“Й“e Й—en, seedinee e dow maЙ“Й“e. Alla Yonii Hasboowo."
  4,7,"Hino woodani worЙ“e Й“en : geЙ—al immorde e kon ko neene e baaba acci e Й“adondiraaЙ“e Й“en, hino woodani kadi rewЙ“e Й“en : geЙ—al e kon ko neene e baaba acci e Й“adondiraaЙ“e Й“en ; Й—uuЙ—i famЙ—i e mun, ko geЙ—al parlaangal."
  4,8,"Si joomiraaЙ“e Й“adondiral en e wonduЙ“e Й“en e waasuЙ“e tawaama peccugol ngol okkoreeЙ“e e mun, wowlanon Й“e konngol moЖҙЖҙol."
  4,9,"Yo hulu Й“en, si tawno ko kamЙ“e angaccunoo Й“aawo maЙ“Й“e ngeГұcudi lo'uЙ“e, Й“e kultana Й“en, yo Й“e kulu Alla Й“e wowla konngol sawaaba=peewngol."
  4,10,"Pellet, Й“en ГұaamirooЙ“e jawЙ—eele yimЙ“e Й“en e hoore tooГұee, pellet ko Й“e woni Гұaamude kon Й“e waЙ—a e deedi maЙ“Й“e, ko yiite, arma Й“e naata huЙ“Й“unge."
  4,11,"Alla no Yamira on e fii Й“iЙ—Й“e mon Й“en : hino woodani gorko yeru ngeЙ—u rewЙ“e Й—iЙ—o. Si Й“e laatike rewЙ“e Й“urЙ“e Й—iЙ—o, hino woodani Й“e tataЙ“e Й—iЙ—i e ko o acci. Si o laatike gooto, hino woodani mo feccere. Hino woodani neene e baaba makko gooto kala e maЙ“Й“e jeegoЙ“al, immorde e ko o acci, si tawii himo mari Й“iЙ—Й—o. Si o maraa Й“iЙ—Й—o, jipnaaЙ“e makko Й“en roni mo, hino woodani yumma makko tataЙ“al. Si tawii himo mari neene-gootooЙ“e, hino woodani yumma makko jeegaЙ“al. ЖҒaawo siinugol wasiyee mo o wasiyii maa yoЙ“ugol Гұamaande nde o Гұamlinoo. BaabiraaЙ“e mon Й“en e Й“iЙ—Й“e mon Й“en, on nganndaa ko hommbo e maЙ“Й“e Й“uri Й“adoraade on nafoore. ЖҠum ko farilla immorde ka Alla. Pellet, Alla Laatike AnnduЙ—o Г‘eeГұuЙ—o."
  4,12,"Hino woodani on feccere e ko rewЙ“e mon ngacci, si tawii Й“e maraa Й“iЙ—Й—o. Si tawii hiЙ“e mari Й“iЙ—Й—o, hino woodani on nayaЙ“al e kon ko Й“e aaci, Й“aawo siinugol wasiyee mo Й“e wasiyii maa yoЙ“ugol Гұamaande [maЙ“Й“e]. Hino woodani rewЙ“e mon Й“en nayaЙ“al e kon ko ngaccuЙ—on, si tawii Й“iЙ—Й—o alanaa on. Si tawii hiЙ—on mari Й“iЙ—Й—o, hino woodani Й“e jeetataЙ“al e kon ko ngaccuЙ—on, Й“aawo siinugol wasiyee mo mbasiyiЙ—on maa yoЙ“ugol Гұamaande [mon]. Si wonii gorko no ronee (annda)debb o, hara himo mari banndiraawo debbo, maa musЙ—Й—o hino woodani kala maЙ“Й“e jeegaЙ“al. Si Й“e laatike Й“urЙ“e Й—um e Й—uuЙ—ude, kamЙ“e ko hawtuЙ“e ka tataЙ“al, Й“aawo wasiyee wasiyaaЙ—o maa yoЙ“ugol Гұamaande nde wonaa lorraynde. ЖҠum ko Wasiyee immorde ka Alla. Alla ko ganduЙ—o MuГұГұiiЙ—o."
  4,13,"ЖҠin ko Keeri Alla. Kala Й—oftiiЙ—o Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on, o naaday mo Aljannaaji, caatlii no ila e ley majji : ko Й“e duumotooЙ“e ton. Ko Й—um woni malal mawngal."
  4,14,"Kala mo woopi Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on, o taЖҙci Keeri Makko Й—in, O Naatnay mo yiite nge o luttata e muuЙ—um ; hino woodani mo lepte koynooje."
  4,15,"ЖҒen waЙ—ooЙ“e paЕӢkare immorde e rewЙ“e mon Й“en, ceetnee e maЙ“Й“e nayo jeyaaЙ“e e mo'on. Si Й“e ceedike, jogiteeЙ“e ka cuuЙ—i haa maayde nden waro Й“e, maa Alla WaЙ—ane Й“e laawol [yaltirngol]."
  4,16,"ЖҒen Й—iЙ—o gollooЙ“e fijuЙ“e [paЕӢkare Й—en] e mo'on, lorree Й“en. Si Й“e tuubii Й“e moЖҙЖҙinii, Й—uurnoЙ—on e maЙ“Й“e. Pellet, Alla Laatike JaЙ“oowo tuubuubuyee jurmotooЙ—o."
  4,17,"Ganndee tuubuubuyee on ka Alla, ko wonannde Й“en gollirooЙ“e bone sabu majjere, refti Й“e tuuba ka Й“adii. ЖҒen Й—on, Alla JaЙ“anay Й“e tuubuubuyee. Alla Laatike gannduЙ—o Г‘eeГұuЙ—o."
  4,18,"Tuubuubuyee alanaa Й“en gollirooЙ“e bone haa tuma maayde nden arani gooto e maЙ“Й“e o wi'a : "Min mi tuubii jooni", wanaa kadi Й“en maayooЙ“e hara kamЙ“e ko Й“e heeferaaЙ“e. ЖҒen Й—on, Men keplanii Й“e lepte muusuЙ—e."
  4,19,"Ko onon yo goЕӢЙ—inЙ“e, dakantaako on nde ronirton rewЙ“e Й“en e Й“ur, dooleyaagu wata on l aagu Й“e fii yo on keЙ“tu yoga e ko okkunoЙ—on Й“e, si wanaa hara Й“e waЙ—u paЕӢkare Й“annguЙ—o. Wonndiree e maЙ“Й“e no moЖҙЖҙiri. Si on aГұii Й“e, hino jortaa nde ngaГұoton huunde, Alla WaЙ—a e mayre moЖҙЖҙere Й—uuЙ—unde."
  4,20,"Si on njiЙ—ii waЙ—titude debbo nokku debbo goo, hara hiЙ—on jonni goЙ—Й—o e maЙ“Й“e jawdi [heewundi], wata on jaЙ“itu e mayri hay e huunde. E on jaЙ“irayndi tooГұdee bakkaatu Й“annguЙ—o?"
  4,21,"Ko honno Жҙettirton ndi, gooЕӢЙ—ii yoga e mon yottike e yoga, Й“e jogitike e mon ahadi tekkundi?"
  4,22,"Wata on nes Й“en Й“e baabiraaЙ“e mon ndesno e suddiiЙ“e si wanaa Й—um ko feЖҙЖҙunoo. Pellet, Й—um laatinoke paЕӢkare e hutaare e bonde laawol."
  4,23,"Harminanaama on : neeniraaЙ“e mon Й“en, e jiwЙ“e mon Й“en, e banndiraaЙ“e mon rewЙ“e Й“en, e yaayiraaЙ“e mon Й“en, e neeniraaЙ“e mon Й“en ka dewol, e jiwЙ“e yumma gooto mon [gorko], e jiwЙ“e banndiraawo mon rewЙ“e, e neeniraaЙ“e mon muynimЙ“e on, e banndiraaЙ“e mon Й“en ka muynan, e neeniraaЙ“e Й“eynguuli mon, e njutteeЙ“e mon won Й“e ka cuuЙ—i mon iwЙ“e e Й“eynguuli mon Й“e naatiduЙ—on e suudu ; si tawii non on naatidaali e maЙ“Й“e suudu, bakkaatu fawaaki on [e resugol Й“en], e [rewЙ“e] daganiiЙ“e Й“iЙ—Й“e mon Й“en iwЙ“e ka keeci, e nde mooЙ“indirton hakkunde neene-gootooЙ“e Й—iЙ—o, si wanaa Й—um ko yawtunoo. Pellet, Alla Laatike Haforoowo HinnotooЙ—o."
  4,24,"E Й“een saЕӢiiЙ“e Й“en ummorde e rewЙ“e, si wonaa Й“een Й“e njeyruЙ—on Гұaame mon. ЖҠum ko Farilla Alla e dow mooЙ—on. Daginanaama on ko woni Й“aawo Й“en Й—on, nde Й—aЙ“Й“irtonЙ“e jawЙ—eele mon hara ko on saЕӢiiЙ“e tawa on ngonaa jinooЙ“e. Kala mo ndakmitorЙ—on e maЙ“Й“e desal : njonniteeЙ“e teЕӢe maЙ“Й“e Й—en. Ko farilla. Bakkaatu fawaaki e fii ko yarlondirЙ—on e mun Й“aawo farilla on. Pellet, Alla Laatike gannduЙ—o Г‘eeГұuЙ—o."
  4,25,"Kala e mooЙ—on mo hattaaaki feere resde saЕӢiiЙ“e gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e, ko [resugol] Й“en Й“e njeyirЙ—on Гұaame mon, immorde e boomi mon gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e. Alla no Anndi gooЕӢЙ—inal mon ngal. Yoga e mon ko e yoga ndesireeЙ“e yamiroore yimЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en, njonniron Й“e teЕӢe maЙ“Й“e Й—en no moЖҙЖҙiri. SaЕӢiiЙ“e hara wanaa jinndooЙ“e njaatoo. Si Й“e saЕӢiike Й“e ngaddii paЕӢkare, no fawii emaЙ“Й“e feccere ko fawii dow saЕӢiiЙ“e rimЙ“e Й“en e lepte. ЖҠum, ko fii on kulЙ—o e mo'on yanugol e jinaa. Ko nde muГұГұotoЙ—on Й“uri moЖҙЖҙannde on. Alla jaafotooЙ—o jurmtooЙ—o."
  4,26,"Allaahu O o faala ЖҒann laЙ“Й“inanade on O Feewna on e laabi Й“eya adinooЙ“e on, O JaЙ“ana on tuubuubuyee. Alla ko gannduЙ—o, Г‘eeГұЙ—o."
  4,27,"Alla no Faala de O JaЙ“anta on tuubuubuyee, Й“een jokkuЙ“e beleeЙ—e faalaa de ooГұorton ooГұannde mawnde."
  4,28,"Alla no YiЙ—i de Hayfinanta on, neЙ—Й—aЕӢke tagaama ko o lo'uЙ—o."
  4,29,"Eehey yo mon gooЕӢЙ—ininЙ“e, wata on Гұaamir jawlЙ—eele mon Й—en hakkunde mooЙ—on e mehre, si wanaa hara ko e njulaaku ngu welaЙ—on e muuЙ—um. Wata on mbar pittaali mon Й—in. Pellet, Alla seerani koH innotkoooЙ—o on."
  4,30,"kala golluЙ—o Й—um e hoore ngaГұngu e tooГұange, aray Men Naatna mo yiite : Й—um wonii newaniiЙ—um Alla."
  4,31,"Si on woЙ—Й—itike [bakkaatu] mawЙ—i Й—i haЙ—aЙ—on Й—in e mun, Mein poppanat on bonЙ—i mon Й—in, Min Naatnira on e naatirgal teddungal."
  4,32,"Wata on njelo ko Alla ЖҒurniri yoga e mon dow yoga. Hino woodani worЙ“e Й“en geЙ—al e ko Й“e paggatii kon, hino woodani kadi rewbe begeЙ“al e kon ko Й“e paggatii. Tororee Alla e ЖҒural Makko he. Pellet, Alla Laatima (seerani)ko gannduЙ—a kala huunde."
  4,33,"Wonan de mo kala Min mbaЙ—anii Й—um ronooЙ“e [heftuЙ“e] e Й—um ko jipnaaЙ“e Й“en ngacci, e Й“adondiraaЙ“e ; e Й“en Й“e ahodunoЙ—on e mun : njonneeЙ“e geЙ—al maЙ“Й“e ngal. Pellet, Alla Laatima (seeraani) cediiЙ—o e kala huunde."
  4,34,"WorЙ“e Й“en ko fawaЙ“e [e daranaade daЕӢkiitag ol] rewЙ“e Й“en, sabu ko Alla ЖҒurniri kon yoga maЙ“Й“e e dow yoga, e sabu kon ko nafki jawЙ—eele maЙ“Й“e. [rewЙ“e] moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e Й“en, ko yaЕӢkiniiЙ“e reenotooЙ“e ka wirnii, sabu kon ko Alla Reenini Й“e.ЖҒen [rewЙ“e] Й“e kuloton dartagol(cuwtagol) mun : mbaajeeЙ“e, peronЙ“e ka mbalndiji, piyonЙ“e. Si Й“e Й—oftike on, wata on Й—Й“Й“ir e dow maЙ“Й“e laawol ! Pellet, Alla Laama seeraani(ToowuЙ—o), ko MawЙ—o."
  4,35,"Si on kulii lurral hakkunde maЙ“Й“e, imminee Гұaawoowo immorЙ—o ka yimЙ“e gorko on e Гұaawoowo immorЙ—o ka yimЙ“e debbo on. Si Й“e faandike moЖҙЖҙinngol, Alla Hawrindinay hakkunde maЙ“Й“e. Pellet, Alla Laatima gannduЙ—o, kumpitiiЙ—o."
  4,36,"Ndewee Alla wata on kafidu e Makko hay huunde. JibipnaaЙ“e mon Й“en moЖҙЖҙoЙ—on e maЙ“Й“e, e joomiraaЙ“e Й“adondiral'en, e wonduЙ“e Й“en, e waasЙ“e Й“en, e koЙ—diijo jom-Й“aЙ—londiraaЙ—o, e koЙ—diijo baЕӢЕӢe (goЙ—Й—uЙ—o,) e wonndiЙ—Й—o baЕӢЕӢe, e Й—atniino, e Й“en Й“e jeyruЙ—on Гұaame mon. Pellet, Alla YiЙ—aa kala on laatiiЙ—o ГұaaЖҙoowo mantotooЙ—o :"
  4,37,"ЖҒen Й“e no ngorЙ—ira, Й“e yamira yimЙ“e Й“en ngorЙ—ir, Й“e suuЙ—a kon ko Alla okki Й“e e ЖҒural Makko. Men Maranii heeferЙ“e Й“en lepte hoynooje."
  4,38,"E Й“en Й“e no nafqira jawlЙ—eee mun Й—en ka yeengo e yimЙ“e Й“en, Й“e gooЕӢЙ—iЕӢtaa Alla wanaa Г‘alaande Sakkitiinde nden. Kala on mo seytaane wonani Й—um cinndodiijo : haray o bonii cinndodiijo!"
  4,39,"E ko honЙ—um fawinoo Й“e si Й“e gooЕӢЙ—inno Alla e Г‘alaande Sakkitiinde nden Й“e nafqi e kon ko Alla Arsike Й“e ? Alla seeraani ko gannduЙ—o Й“e."
  4,40,"Pellet, Alla TooГұataa hay fotde gabbel- jarra si wonii ko moЖҙЖҙere, O Soway nde, O Okka immorde ka Mokko njoЙ“di mawndi."
  4,41,"Ko honno si tawii Men ngaddoyii immorde e kala leГұol ceeditotooЙ—o, Min ngadduma ha ngonaa ceeditotooЙ—o e dow ? ЖҒee(leГұolma).."
  4,42,"Г‘aЙ—nde, hee heeferЙ“e Й“ee woopnooЙ“e Й“en NulaaЙ—o on yeloto hara nun Й“e fonndeteno e leydi ndin, Й“e suuЙ—ataa Alla hay konngol"
  4,43,"Ee hey mon gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e, wata on Й“aЙ—to juulde den hara ko on siwruЙ“e haa aganndon ko wowloton ; wanaa de ngonduЙ—on e janaaba, ha lootoЙ—on maa ko on taЖҙitooЙ“e laawol haa laЙ“Й“inoЙ—on. Si on laatike nawnuЙ“e, maa hiЙ—on e hoore jahal, maa Й“aawo hoggo arii goЙ—Й—o e mon(yaadon dow wuro), maa on soccondirii e rewЙ“e Й“en on heЙ“aali ndiyam, taamoree mbullaari(leydi) laaЙ“undi : mowlon geece mon Й—en e juuЙ—e mon Й—en. Pellet, Alla Laatike jaafotooЙ—o Cuhroowo"
  4,44,"E a yi'aali faade e Й“en okkaaЙ“e geЙ—al e Й—efte Й—en, hiЙ“e cooda majjere nden, hiЙ“e faalaa nde majjoton laawol [poccingol] ngol ?"
  4,45,"Ko Alla ЖҒuri Anndude aГұЙ“e mon Й“en. Alla yonii GiЙ—o, Alla yonii Ballo."
  4,46,"Hino e Й“eya alyahuudaaЙ“e waylooЙ“e konngol ngol e nokku maggol Й“e wi'a: "Men nanii men yeddii ; heЙ—o ko wanaa nannateeЙ—o, aynu men", ka hallugol Й—emЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en e yuwugol ka diina. Hara nun Й“e wi'ayno : "Men nanii men Й—oftike nanu ndaaraa", ko Й—um Й“uraynoo moЖҙЖҙannde Й“e, Й“ura foccaade. Ko woni tun, Alla HuЙ—irii Й“e geddi maЙ“Й“e Й—in, Й“e gomЙ—iЕӢtaa si wanaa seeЙ—aa."
  4,47,"Eehey mon okkanooЙ“e Defte, gooЕӢЙ—inee Й—uum komin njippini hina gooЕӢЙ—ina nden won dunde e mon, ado Men Mehude jeece [mon Й—en] Men RuttiraЙ—e Й“abbe majje, maa Men meska Й“e on wano Men meskirnoo non yimЙ“e asewe Й“en. Fiyaake Alla on Laatke golloteeЙ—o."
  4,48,"Pellet, Alla yaafotaka kafidoowo Mo e goЙ—Й—um, Himo Yaafo ko jaasi Й—um wonan de on Mo O Muuyi. Kala on kafiduЙ—o Alla e goЙ—Й—um, gooЕӢЙ—ii o fekandiima bakkaatu mawЙ—o."
  4,49,"E a yi'aali Й“en Й“e no laЙ“Й“ina (mbuppa)ko`e maЙ“Й“e ? Ko woni, Ko Alla LaЙ“Й“inta (wuppata)on mo Muuyi, Й“e tooГұetaake yeru gurun tamaro."
  4,50,"Ndaarii ko hol no Й“e woni fekindoraade e Alla fenaade ! ЖҠum Й—on yonii bakkaatu feeГұuЙ—o."
  4,51,"E mati a yiani Й“een okkanooЙ“e geЙ—al ka Deftere, hiЙ“e gooЕӢЙ—ina sanamuuji e bewinayЙ—i Й—in, hiЙ“e wi'ana Й“en heeferЙ“e : "Ko Й“ee Й—oo Й“uri feewde laawol e dii Й“eya gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e ? !"."
  4,52,"Ko Й“een woni Й“e Alla HuЙ—i Й“e, kala mo Alla HuЙ—i noon, a heЙ“antaa mo balloowo."
  4,53,"Kaa hinaЙ“e woodani geЙ—al e laamu ? Oon tuma, Й“e okkataa yimЙ“e Й“e yeru gufel tamaroore."
  4,54,"Kaa Й“e aГұanat yimЙ“e Й“ee (nelaaЙ—o)Alla juul e mum. Hisna Й—um.)koAlla Okki Й“e kon e ЖҒural Makko ? GooЕӢЙ—ii Men Okkii Й“eynguure Ibraahiima nden Defte e ganndal (ГұeeГұal, )Men Okki Й“e Laamu Mawngu."
  4,55,"Hino e maЙ“Й“e on gooЕӢЙ—inЙ—o nde, no e maЙ“Й“e kadi on paddiiЙ—o nde. Jahannama yonii kuЙ“Й“ugole."
  4,56,"Pellet, Й“en yedduЙ“e aayeeje Amen Й—en, aray Men NaatnaЙ“e Й“e yiite : tuma kala guri maЙ“Й“e Й—in Й“enndi, Men WaЙ—titana Й“e guri goЙ—Й—i fii no Й“e meeЙ—ira lepte Й—en. Pellet, Alla Laatike jaaliiЙ—o, (elaamumum)Г‘eeГұuЙ—o."
  4,57,"ЖҒen goooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“e golli golle moЖҙЖҙe, aray Men NaanatЙ“e Aljannaaji Й—i no ila e ley majji caatlii, ko Й“e duumotooЙ“e ndeer toon hino woodani Й“e toon rewЙ“e laЙ“Й“inaaЙ“e Min NaatnaЙ“e Й“e Й—owdi duumiindi."
  4,58,"Pellet, Alla no Yamira on tottoton koolaaje Й—en faade e joom ma je Й“en, e si on Гұaaway hakkunde yimЙ“e Й“en nde Гұaawirton nunЙ—al. Pellet, ko Alla Waajorta on kon labaama. Pellet, Alla Laatike Nanoowo, Yi'oowo."
  4,59,"Eehey mon gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e, Й—oftee Alla Й—oftoЙ—on NulaaЙ—o on e joomiraaЙ“e fiyaake e mooЙ—on. Si on luutri e huunde, ruttee nde ka Alla e ka sunna NulaaЙ—o on, si on laatike gooЕӢЙ—imЙ“e Alla e Г‘alaande Sakkitiinde nden. Ko Й—um Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude Й“uri labeede battane."
  4,60,"E a yi'aali Й“en Й“e no nodditooЙ“e wonnde kamЙ“e Й“e gooЕӢЙ—iniЙ—inii kon ko Jippinaa e maaЙ—a e kon ko Jippinaa ado maaЙ—a? HiЙ“e faalaa nde Й“e Гұaawinoytoo ka bewinayЙ—i Й—in, gooЕӢЙ—ii heЙ“e njamiraama nde Й“e njeddata Й—i. Seytaane non hino faalaa majjinnde Й“e majjere woЙ—Й—unde."
  4,61,"Si Й“e mbiaama: "ngaree faade e kon ko Alla Jippini e faade e NulaaЙ—o on", a yi'ay naafigee6e Й“e no paddo e maaЙ—a kala paddagol."
  4,62,"Ko honno [wonirta] si tawii musiiba heЙ“irii Й“e sabu ko Й“e ardiniri juuЙ—e maЙ“Й“e, refti Й“e ngara e maaЙ—a hiЙ“e ngooЙ—dira Alla : "Min paandaaki si wanaa moЖҙЖҙinngol e kawrinndinal?!"."
  4,63,"Ko Й“een ngoni Й“e Alla homba Anndi ko woni ndeer Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e, Й—uurnoЙ“e , mbaajoЙ—aa Й“e, kaalonaaЙ“e konngol jottotongol ka pittaali maЙ“Й“e."
  4,64,"Min Nuliraali NulaaЙ—o [woo] si wanaa fii yo o Й—ofte e e sakkiroore Alla. Hara nun tuma Й“e tooГұunoo pittaali maЙ“Й“e Й—in, Й“e ngarno ema Й“e imsinii e Alla, NulaaЙ—o on imsinanii Й“e, Й“e tawayno Alla ko JaЙ“oowo tuubuubuyee, jurmotoodo."
  4,65,"Hey, Mi WooЙ—ndirii Joomi maaЙ—a, Й“e ngooЕӢЙ—Й—ntaa haa Й“e Гұaawinora maa huunde ko yani hakkunde maЙ“Й“e, refti Й“e keЙ“ataa Й“itteende ka pittaali maЙ“Й“e e kon ko ГұaawuЙ—aa, Й“e njebbiloo kala jebbilagol."
  4,66,"So tawno min parluno e maЙ“Й“e won de : "mbaree pittaali mon Й—in", maa "njalton e galleeji mon", Й“e mbЙ—ataano Й—um si wanaa seeЙ—aa e maЙ“Й“e. Sinno kamЙ“e Й“e mbaЙ—no kon ko Й“e mbaajoranoo, Й—um laatotono moЖҙЖҙere wonan de Й“e, Й“ura tiiЙ—ude kadi tabital :"
  4,67,"Nden tuma, min ngokkatnoЙ“e immorde ka amen, njoЙ“di mawndi,"
  4,68,"Min pewno Й“e laawol poЖҙcingol."
  4,69,"Kala Й—oftiiЙ—o Alla e NulaaЙ—o on : Й“een Й—oon ngondoyta Й“een Й“e Alla waЙ—i dookem dowe muen gila e annabaaЙ“e, ha e goonguЙ“e, e sahiddinnooЙ“e, e moЖҙЖҙube. ЖҒen Й—on moЖҙЖҙii wonndiiЙ“e !"
  4,70,"Ngal Й—on ЖҒural ko immorde ka Alla, Alla Yonii gannduЙ—o !"
  4,71,"Ee hey mon gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e, njogitee deentorЙ—i mon Й—in, ndunnjon ko on seertuЙ“e maa runnjon on rentuЙ“e."
  4,72,"Hino e mon neeЙ“notooЙ“e, si musiiba heЙ“ii on, o wi'a : "GooЕӢЙ—ii Alla Neeminii e am, nde tawnoo mi mi wone daano e maЙ“Й“ e ceediiЙ—o ! "."
  4,73,"Si tawii heЙ“ii on Й“ural immorde ka Alla, ma o wi'a waona si tawii meeЙ—aa laataade hakkunde mon giЙ—li: "Ee jalla am si mi tawdano e maЙ“Й“e ! mi malee malal manngal !"."
  4,74,"Yo haЙ“e fii laawol Alla ngol, Й“en Й“e no soottira nguurdam aduna Й—am laakara on ! Kala on kaЙ“aaЙ—o fii laawol Alla ngol o waraa maa o fooli, arma min ngokku mo njoЙ“di mawndi."
  4,75,"E ko heЙ“i on, on kaЙ“etaake fii laawol Alla ngol ? e Lo'inaaЙ“e Й“een ka worЙ“e, e ka rewЙ“e, e ka sukkeЙ“e Й“en Й“e no mbia: "Joom amen, Yaltin min e ndee saare nde yimЙ“e mun tooГұi, WaЙ—anaa min immorde ka MaaЙ—a giЙ—o, WaЙ—anaa Min immorde ka MaaЙ—a balloowo"."
  4,76,"ЖҒeen gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e heЙ“e kaЙ“ee fii laawol Alla ngol, Й“eya heeferЙ“e heЙ“e kaЙ“ee e laawol Й“ewnatЙ—i Й—in. KaЙ“ee weldiiЙ“e seytaane Й“een : pellet, pewje seytaane Й—en laatike lo'uЙ—e."
  4,77,"E a yi'aali Й“en wi'ananooЙ“e : "curee juuЙ—e mon Й—en, ГұiЙ“non juulde, njonnon asakal". Tuma hare nden farlanoo e maЙ“Й“e, e ndeke fedde goo e maЙ“Й“e hino hulira yimЙ“e Й“e wano no Alla hulirtee, maa ko Й“uri sattudee e kulol, Й“e mbi "Joomi amen, ko saabi haa parluЙ—aa e dow amen hare ? Ko haЙ—noo NeeЙ“tinanaa min Й—uum haa e lajal Й“attingal ?" Maaku : "Dakamme aduna on ko seeЙ—a, ko laakara on Й“uri moЖҙЖҙannde on kulЙ—o [Alla], on tooГұetaake fotde e gufel tamaroore"
  4,78,"Nokku wof to laatiЙ—on maayde nden heЙ“toto on, hay si on laatike e nder tataaji mahaaЙ—i. Si moЖҙЖҙere heЙ“ii Й“e, Й“e mbia "ЖҠum Й—oo ko immorde ka Alla" Si bone heЙ“ii Й“e, Й“e mbia :"ЖҠum Й—oo ko immorde e maaЙ—a !" Maaku: "Kala e majji ko immorde ka Alla". E ko nanngi Й“ee yimЙ“e Й“e Й—eЙ“ataa faamude yeewtere?!"
  4,79,"Huunde fofko heЙ“maa e moЖҙЖҙere ko immorde ka Alla, huunde fofko heЙ“maa e bone ko immorde e woЕӢkii maa kin. Mon Nulii ma wonan de yimЙ“e Й“e NulaaЙ—o. Alla Yonii Seede."
  4,80,"Kalomo Й—ofti NulaaЙ—o oo gooЕӢЙ—ii Й—oftimo Alla. Kalo, ruЕӢtii noon min nuliraanima dow maЙ“Й“e denoowo."
  4,81,"HeЙ“e mbia "Й—oftaare!", si Й“e njaltii ka maaЙ—a, fedde e maЙ“Й“e waaliday [e miijo( ngo] wonaa ngo maakuЙ—aa. Alla no Winnda Й—uum koЙ“e mbaaldata e mun. ЖҠuurno Й“e pawoЙ—aa e Alla. Alla Yonii koolorЙ—o."
  4,82,"E mati Й“e teskitortaa alqur'aana o ? Sinno mbo iwruna Й—o wonaa to Alla, Й“e tawatno e ehembo luurre Й—uuЙ—uЙ—e."
  4,83,"Si arii Й“e e fiyaake jeyaaЙ—o e hoolaare, maa kulol, Й“e lollina Й—um. Sinno Й“e nduttuno Й—um e NulaaЙ—o on e Й“en fewjooЙ“e fii maЙ“Й“e, Й“een Й“ullitooЙ“e e maЙ“Й“e ganndatno Й—um. Si wanaano Й“ural Alla ngal e dow mooЙ—on e Yurmeende Makko nden, on njokkatno seytaane si wonaa seeЙ—a e mon."
  4,84,"HaЙ“e e laawol Alla he, a defaaka si wonaa hoore-maa. hijin gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“en, arma Alla nde Surata bone heeferЙ“e Й“e Ko Alla Й“uri SaЙ—tude doole, ko KaЕӢko Й“uri SaЙ—tude muusnugol."
  4,85,"Kala tefniiЙ—o tefnoore labaande wonay mo geЙ—al e mayre, kala kadi on tefniiЙ—o tefnoore bonnde wonany mo e mayre geЙ—al. Alla seerani kattanЙ—o kala huunde."
  4,86,"Si on calominaama salminaango, calmitoЙ—ee ko Й“uri nduun Й—oon maa ndutton ngo. Pellet, Alla woni e dow kala huunde ko o kasboowo."
  4,87,"Alla, deweteeЙ—o alaa si wonaa KaЕӢko, ma o MooЙ“i on Гұande Darngal, sikke alaa e mayre. Alaa Й“urЙ—o gooЕӢuЙ—ude Alla yeewtere ?"
  4,88,"Ko waЙ—i on e fii Й“ee naafiqiiЙ“e peЙ—le Й—iЙ—i ?! Ko Alla woni UgginЙ—o Й“e sabu ko Й“e faggitii. E on paala feewnude oon mbo Alla Majjini ? Kala on mo Alla majjini, a heЙ“antaa mo laawol.peewal"
  4,89,"HeЙ“e ngooЙ—e sinno on njedduno wano noЙ“e njddiri nih, laatoЙ—on fotЙ“e.e maЙ“Й“e wota on njogito e maЙ“Й“e weldiiЙ“e haa Й“e pera e laawol Alla ngol. Si Й“e nduЕӢitii, nanngee Й“e mbaron Й“e nokku kala ka tawЙ—on Й“e.Wata on njogito e maЙ“Й“e weldiЙ—Й—o wonaa balloowo"
  4,90,"Si wanaa Й“en Й“e hino njokkoo faade e yimЙ“e Й“e ahadi woni hakkunde mon e maЙ“Й“e, maaЙ—uum Й“e ngarii emon Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en no Й“iЙ—tanii kaЙ“agol on, maa Й“e kaЙ“a e yimЙ“e maЙ“Й“e. Si Alla Haajuno, O Wurtayno Й“e e dow mooЙ—on, Й“e kaЙ“o on. Si Й“e pottitike on, Й“e kaЙ“aaki on, Й“e werlike kisal e mon, haray Alla WaЙ—anaali on e dow maЙ“Й“e laawol."
  4,91,"Arma tawon woЙ—Й“e goo muuyЙ“e nde Й“e koolnorata on koolnora yimЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en. Tuma kala nde Й“e nduttaa e geddi Й—in,Й“e cuЖҙЖҙitee e nder majji. Si Й“e ngaccani on, Й“e mberloo kisal e mon, Й“e curi juuЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en, nanngee Й“e mbaron Й“e nokku kala ka tawЙ—on Й“e. Ko Й“en Й—on mooЙ—on, [woni ke Min] mbaЙ—ani on e maЙ“Й“e hujja Й“annguЙ—o."
  4,92,"Haananaa gooЕӢЙ—inЙ—o nde o warata gooЕӢЙ—inЙ—o si wanaa [hara ko] faljere. On barЙ—o gooЙ—inЙ—o, yo rimЙ—in daande gooЕӢЙ—innde e diya jonneteeЙ—o yimЙ“e makko Й“een : si wonaa hara Й“en sakkii. Si wonii ko jeyaaЙ—o e yimЙ“e aГұЙ“e mon, hara kaЕӢko ko o gooЕӢЙ—inЙ—o, ko rimЙ—ingol daande gooЕӢЙ—innde. Si wonii ko jeyaaЙ—o e yimЙ“e Й“e ahadi woni hakkunde mon e maЙ“Й“e, ko diya jonneteeЙ—o yimЙ“e makko Й“en, e rimЙ—ingol daande gooЕӢЙ—innde. On mo hebaali ko : koorgol lebbi Й—iЙ—i jokkondirЙ—i tuubuubuyee immorde ka Alla. Alla seeraani ko gannnduЙ—o, Г‘eeГұЙ—o."
  4,93,"Kala mo wari gooЕӢЙ—inЙ—o e hoore tewaaЙ—e, njoЙ“di makko ndin ko Jahannama, luttoowo e nder magge ; Alla Tikkanii mo, O HuЙ—ii mo, O heplanii mo lepte mawЙ—e."
  4,94,"Ee hey mon gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e, si on njaahii e Й—atngal Й“annginee [tefon] wata on mbi'an on berliiЙ—o e mon kisal : "Wanaa a gooЕӢЙ—inЙ—o", hiЙ—on Й—aЙ“Й“a jawdi nguurdam aduna, ko ka Alla konhoyri Й—uuЙ—undi woni. Ko wano non laatornoЙ—on ko adii, Alla dokkei e mon. ЖҒannginee. Pellet, Alla Laatike kumpitiiЙ—o ko ngolloton."
  4,95,"GoooЕӢЙ—imЙ“e jooЙ—iiЙ“e Й“en, hara wanaa joomiraaЙ“e lorra Й“en, potataa e Й“en tiiЙ—nortooЙ“e e laawol Alla ngol jawle maЙ“Й“e Й—en e woЕӢkiiji maЙ“e Й—in. Alla Й“urnirii tiiЙ—norЙ“e jawЙ—eele mun Й—en e woЕӢkiiji mun Й—in, e dow jooЙ—iiiiЙ“e Й“en, darja. ЖҒe fow maЙ“Й“e Alla Fodii Й“e moЖҙЖҙere, Alla Й“urnirii tiiЙ—notooЙ“e Й“en e dow jooЙ—iiЙ“e Й“en njoЙ“di mawndi."
  4,96,"Darjaaji immorde ka Makko, e yaafuyol, e yurmeende. Alla Laatike jaafotooЙ—o, jurmotooЙ—o."
  4,97,"Pellet, Й“en Й“e maleykaaji Й—in no mbara hara ko Й“e tooГұuЙ“e pittaali maЙ“Й“e Й—in, Й“e mbi'a : "Ko e holЙ—um ngonnoЙ—on ?!". ЖҒe mbi'a : "Min laatinoke lo'inanooЙ“e ka leydi". ЖҒe mbi'a : "Leydi Alla ndin laatanooki yaajundi hanno feron e mayri ?". ЖҒen Й—on, jaaЖҙnde maЙ“Й“e nden ko Jahannama, nge bonii ruttorde !"
  4,98,"Si wanaa Й“en lo'inaaЙ“e immorde ka worЙ“e, e ka rewЙ“e, e ka sukaaЙ“e Й“e kattanaa yahdu, Й“e peewataa e laawol."
  4,99,"ЖҒen Й—on, arma Alla Yaafanoo Й“e. Alla seerani jaafotooЙ—o, cuhroowo."
  4,100,"Kalomo feri e laawol Alla ngol o taway ka leydi yolЙ—ere Й—uuЙ—unde e yaajeende. Kala jaltuЙ—o e suudu mu'un ko o perЙ—o faade e Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on, maayde nden heЙ“ti mo, gooЕӢЙ—ii njoЙ“di makko ndin tabitii ka Alla. Alla seeraani jaafotooЙ—o, jurmtooЙ—o."
  4,101,"Si on njaltii, waЙ—oyde jahaadi bakkat alanaa on nde ngstoton juulde nde, si on kulii nde yedduЙ“e Й“en pitninta on. Pellet, heeferЙ“e Й“en ngonani on aГұЙ“e feeГұЙ“e."
  4,102,"Si a tawdaama e maЙ“Й“e a darnanii Й“e julude, yo fedde goo e maЙ“Й“e darodo e maaЙ—a yo Й“e jogito njogaaji maЙ“Й“e Й—iin ; si Й“e cujjii, yo Й“e ngn Й“aawo mon, yo fedde ndeya nde juulaalni ar, yoo Й“e njuuldu e maaЙ—a yo Й“e njogito denetorЙ—i maЙ“Й“e Й—in e kaЙ“orЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—e YedduЙ“e Й“e nos ngooЙ—e sinno on mbelsindotono e njoktaaje mon Й—e doЕӢle mon Й—e, Й“e ooГұoo e mooЙ—on ooГұannde wootere. bakkaat fawaaki on si Й—on ngonndi e lorra immorde e toЙ“o, maa on laatike Г‘awЙ“e nde mballinton njogaaji mon Й—i. nJogitee deenorЙ—i mon Й—i. Pellet, Alla heplanii heeferЙ“e Й“en lepte koynooje."
  4,103,"Si on gaynii juulde nde, jaЕӢtoree Alla e darnnde, e jonЙ—de e ka hoore baЕӢЕӢeeje mon. Si on ndeeЖҙii, ГұiiЙ“nee juude nde Pellet, juulde nde woni e dow gooЙ—inЙ“e Й“efarilla mbo waktu dottaaЙ—o"
  4,104,"Wata on lo*u e nder Й—aЙ“Й“itgol yimЙ“e Й“e. Si tawii hoЙ—on mu'usee, kamЙ“e kadi heЙ“e mu'usee wano mu'usirteЙ—on, hoЙ—on njortii immorde e Alla ko Й“e njortaaki. Pellet, Alla seeraabi gannduЙ—o, Г‘eeГұЙ—o."
  4,105,"Minen min njippinirii Deftere nde e maaЙ—aa e hoore goonga fii yo a Гұaawir hakkunde yimЙ“e Й“en kon ko Alla Hollu maa. Wata on wonan jamfotooЙ“e Й“en beeГұdoowo."
  4,106,"Imsino e Alla. Pellet, Alla seeraani jaafotooЙ—o, jurmotooЙ—o."
  4,107,"Wata a weeГұdondire gah Й“een jamfotooЙ“e pittaali muen. Pellet, Alla YiЙ—aa on keeЙ—o jamfo, keewЙ—o : bakkatuuji"
  4,108,"HeЙ“e cuuЙ—oo yimЙ“e Й“en Й“e cuuЙ—otaako Alla, Homo Wonndi e maЙ“Й“e tuma Й“e waalaynoo fewjude kon ko O Welaaka e konngol. Alla seeraani kumpitiiЙ—o kon ko Й“e ngollata."
  4,109,"Hino mon yo e on mbeГұjii fii maЙ“Й“e e Й—am nguurdam aduna, e ko hommbo weГұdoyta e Alla fii maЙ“Й“e Г‘ande Darngal, kaa ko hommbo laatanoytooЙ“e fawtiiЙ—o?!"
  4,110,"Kalo golluЙ—o bone maa o tooГұi hoore makko, refti o imsinii e Alla, o tawat Alla ko jaafotooЙ—o, jurmotooЙ—o."
  4,111,"Kala kadi paggitiiЙ—o bakkaat, pellet, ko e hoore makko o woni faggitaade Й—um. Alla seeraani gannduЙ—o, Г‘eeГұЙ—o."
  4,112,"Kala paggitiiЙ—o goopol maa bakkaa refti bugii Й—um e hoore daЙ—ndiiЙ—o, gooЕӢЙ—ii o ronnditike fenaande e bakkaat Й“annguЙ—o."
  4,113,"Si wanaano Й“ural Alla ngal e dow maaЙ—a e Yurmeende Makko nden, fedde goo e maЙ“Й“e himmirayno majjinngol ma, Й“e alaa e majjinnde si wanaa pittaali maЙ“Й“e Й—in, Й“e lorrirtaama hay e huunde. Alla Jippinii e maaЙ—a Deftere nden e Г‘eeГұal ngal, O Anndinii ma huunde nden a anndaano. Й“ural Alla ngal e dow maaЙ—a laatike mawnungal."
  4,114,"MoЖҙЖҙere alaa e ko heewi e ndeeyuuji maЙ“Й“e Й—i, si wonaa oon jamirЙ—o sadaka, maa moЖҙЖҙere maa moЖҙЖҙiЕӢtingol hakkunde yimЙ“e Й“en. Kala baЙ—irЙ—o Й—um Й—aЙ“Й“ugol weluya Alla, arma min ngokka mo njoЙ“di mawndi."
  4,115,"Kala luutndiiЙ—o NulaaЙ—o on Й“aawo nde paawal ngal Й“anngani mo, o jokki ko wanaa laawol gooЕҠЙ—inЙ“e Й“en, Men kuccintinay mo e kon ko o hucciti, min naatnЙ—um Jahannama, nge bonii ruttorde !"
  4,116,"Pellet, Alla Yafatako waЙ—deedel mo e goЙ—Й—um, Homo yaafo ko jaasi Й—um wonan de on mo o muuyi. Kala denndinЙ—o Alla e goЙ—Й—um, gooЕӢЙ—ii o majjii majjere woЙ—Й—oynde."
  4,117,"ЖҒe ndewaani ko woori Alla, si wonaa [sanamuuji] dewЙ—inaaЙ—i, Й“e ndwaani si wanaa seytaane canndalinЙ—o."
  4,118,"Alla HuЙ—ii mbo: owi"mami jogito e jeyaaЙ“e maa Й“en geЙ—al ganndangal"
  4,119,"ma mi majjinЙ“e, ma mi yelinoyЙ“e, ma mi yamirЙ“e, ma Й“e taЖҙ noppi neemoraaЙ—i Й—in, ma mi yamirЙ“e, ma Й“e mbaylu tagoore Alla nde !". Kala jogitiiЙ—o seytaane giЙ—o ko woori Alla, gooЕӢЙ—ii o perti perte Й“anngunde."
  4,120,"Hombo Й“ef odana homo yelina Й“e, seytaane fodanani Й“e si wanaa hodo.(koomte)."
  4,121,"ЖҒeen Й—on jaaЖҙndee maЙ“Й“e nde ko Jahannama, Й“e keЙ“ataa gaa nge daЙ—irde."
  4,122,"ЖҒeen gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“e ngolli golle moЖҙЖҙe, aray Min naatantЙ“ee Aljannaaji Й—i no ila e ley majji caatli : ko Й“e duumotooЙ“e nder ton poomaa. Fodoore Alla nde ko goonga. Ko alaa mo Й“uri Alla gooЕӢЙ—ude konngol ?"
  4,123,"Wonaa e yelaaji mon Й—in wanaa yelaaji joom defte en. Kala golluЙ—o bone o yoЙ“ete Й—um, o heЙ“ataa ko woori Alla giЙ—o wonaa balloowo."
  4,124,"Kalo golluЙ—o e moЖҙЖҙi Й—in, fota ko gorko maa ko debbo, hara ko o goooЕӢЙ—inЙ—o, Й“een Й—oon naatata Aljanna Й“e tooГұetaake kona fota gufel [tamaroore]."
  4,125,"Alaa Й“urЙ—o moЖҙЖҙude diine haa hewti on jebbilanЙ—o yeeso mum ngo Alla, hara ko o moЖҙЖҙinЙ—o, o rewi e diine Ibraahiima ooГұiiiiЙ—o kala.diineeji Й—i peewa Alla Jogitima Ibraahiima sehil."
  4,126,"Ko Alla Woodani kala ko woni ka kammuuli e ka leydi. Alla seeraani ko piiltiiЙ—o kala huunde."
  4,127,"HeЙ“e naamnoma maa fii rewЙ“e Й“een, maaku : "Alla no saggitude on fii Й“e[rewЙ“e], e kon ko jaЕӢngetee e dow mooЙ—on ka deftere fii Й“en rewЙ“e wonЙ—uЙ“e, Й“e Й“e on njonnataa Й“e Й—uum ko Й“e parlanaaa, hoЙ—on ndeerЙ—a fii resde Й“e, e Й“en lo'inaaЙ“e ummorde e sukaaЙ“e, e nde ndarantoЙ—on wonduЙ“e Й“en e nuunЙ—al. Kala ko ngolluЙ—on e moЖҙЖҙer e, pellet, Alla seeraani ko gannduЙ—o Й—um."
  4,128,"Si wonii debbo hulii moodi makko e suwtaade maa Й—uurnaare, bakkaat fawaaki Й“e nde Й“e moЖҙЖҙiЕӢtinirta hakkunde maЙ“Й“e kalo moЖҙЖҙingol.Ko moЖҙЖҙingol on Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude, Pittaali Й—in tawdanaama ndeereraagu.Si on moЖҙЖҙinii on gooЕӢЙ—ii, pellet Alla seeraani kumpitiiЙ—o ko golloton."
  4,129,"On mbaawataa nuunЙ—ude hakkunde rewЙ“e Й“en hay si on ndeerЙ—ii. Wata on ngooГұo kala ooГұannde, ngaccon mo wa jowaaЙ—o. Si on moЖҙЖҙinii on gooЕӢЙ—ii, pellet, Alla seerani jaafotooЙ—o jurmotooЙ—o"
  4,130,"Si Й“e ceetii, Alla AlЙ—iniroyay kala maЙ“Й“e immorde e Yaajeende Makko nden. Alla seeraani jaacЙ—o [Й“ural], Г‘eeГұЙ—o."
  4,131,"Ko Alla Woodani kala ko woni ndeer kammuuji ko e ko woni ndeer leydi. GooЕӢЙ—ii Min mbasoyinoomo Й“eya okkaaЙ“e defte ko adi mon, e onon : "kulee Alla !". Si on njeddii, pellet, ko Alla Woodani kala ko woni ndeer kammuuli e ka leydi. Alla seeraani ko Galo, jettaaЙ—o."
  4,132,"Ko Alla Woodani kala ko woni ndeer kammuuli e ndeer leydi. Alla Yonii FawtiiЙ—o."
  4,133,"Si o muuyii, O naЙ“at on, onon yo yimЙ“e, O Adda woЙ—Й“e goo. Alla serani katta nЙ—o e dow Й—um."
  4,134,"Kala laatiiЙ—o o yiЙ—i koa njoЙ“di aduna, ko Alla jogi njoЙ“di aduna e laakara woni. Alla seeraani ko nanoowo , Yi'oowo."
  4,135,"Eehey mon goomЙ—inЙ“e ngonee, ГұiiЙ“uЙ“e e nunЙ—al seedeeЙ“e Alla, hay si ko e dow pittaali mon, maa jipnaaaЙ“e mon Й“e maa banndiraaЙ“e Й“e. Si wonii ko o galo maaЙ—um baaso, ko Alla Й“uri Haan dude e maЙ“Й“e. Wata on njokku mbelaaЙ—e,mon nde nuunЙ—oton. Si on mbaylii maa on Й—uurnima, pellet, Alla seeraani kumpitiiЙ—o ko ngolloton."
  4,136,"Ee hey mon gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e, ngooЕӢЙ—inee Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on, e deftere nde O Jippini e NulaaЙ—o Makko on, e Й—en defte Й—e O Jippini ko adii. Kala jedduЙ—o Alla, e maleykaaji Makko Й—i, e defte Makko Й—e, e NulaaЙ“e Makko Й“e e Г‘alaande Sakkitiinde nden, gooЕӢЙ—ii o majjii majjere woЙ—Й—unde."
  4,137,"Pellet, Й“een gooЙ—inЙ“e, refti Й“e njeddi, refti Й“e ngooЕӢЙ—ini, reftiti Й“e njeddi, reftiti Й“e Й“eydorii keeferaagu, Alla wonataa mbo yaafooЙ“e wonaa mbo Fewnoowo Й“e e laawol.paawngol,."
  4,138,"Weltinir naafigeeЙ“e Й“e, won de no woodaniЙ“e lepte muusЙ—e."
  4,139,"ЖҒeen Й“e no njogitoo heeferЙ“e Й“en yiЙ—Й“e ko gah gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“en, e Й“e Й—aЙ“Й“ay e juuЙ—e maЙ“Й“e semmbel ? Pellet, semmbe fof ko Alla woodanii."
  4,140,"GooЕӢЙ—ii o Jippinii e mon ka nder deftere Si on nanii Aayeeje Alla Й—e no njeddee Й—e jalikitee, wata on njooЙ—oЙ—odo e maЙ“Й“e haa Й“e jumpana yewtere woЙ—nde ko woori nden Й—oon, si on mbaЙ—ii Й—uum on potii e maЙ“Й“e". Pellet, Alla ko denndinoowo naafigeeЙ“e Й“e e heeferЙ“e Й“e ndeerJahannama Й“e denndaangal."
  4,141,"ЖҒen habbitantooЙ“e on, si uddital laataniima on immorde e Alla, Й“e mbia : "E, min ngonndaano e mo'on ?", Si geЙ—al laatanike heeferaaЙ“e Й“en, Й“e mbia : "E min poolnaano e mooЙ—on men kaЙ—ani on immorde e gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“en ?" Alla ko Г‘aawoowo hakkunde mon Г‘ande Darngal, Alla WaЙ—antaa heeferЙ“e Й“en laawol e hoore gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“en."
  4,142,"Pellet, naafigeeЙ“eЙ“e Й“en heЙ“e njamfoo Alla, KaЕӢko kadi ko jamfotooЙ—o Й“e. Si Й“e immiimo fa'ade , e juulde koЙ“e aamЙ“e, heЙ“e ngolliro ha yimЙ“e Й“e njia, Й“e (ye'engo) Й“e a njaЕӢtotaako Alla si wonaa seeЙ—a."
  4,143,"HeЙ“e naЙ“a artira hakkunde Й—um, Й“e ngalaa e Й“ee Й—oo Й“e ngalaa e Й“ee Й—aa. Kala on mo Alla Majjini, a heЙ“antaa mo laawol. Peewal"
  4,144,"Eehey mon yo gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e, wata on njogitor heeferЙ“e Й“en weldiiЙ“e ko wanaa gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“en. E on faala nde mbЙ—anton Alla e dow mooЙ—on hujja Й“annguЙ—o ."
  4,145,"Pellet, naafigeeЙ“eЙ“e Й“en no ka neaandi yiite, a heЙ“antaa Й“e balloowo !"
  4,146,"Si wanaa Й“een tuupЙ“e, Й“e moЖҙЖҙini, Й“e njogitii [diina] Alla Й“e laЙ“Й“ini diina maЙ“Й“e kan : Й“en Й—on ngon di ko e gooЕӢЙ—imЙ“e Й“en. Arma Alla weeЙ—aa gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“en njoЙ“di mawndi."
  4,147,"Ko holЙ—uum Alla WaЙ—ata e leptugol on, si on njettii [Mo] on gooЕӢЙ—inii [Mo] ? Alla seeraani JaarnaaЙ—o ko gannduЙ—o."
  4,148,"Alla YiЙ—aa ko feeГұi ko e bone immorde e koЕӢngol, si wanaa on tooГұaaЙ—o. Alla seeraani ko nanoow ko gannduЙ—o."
  4,149,"Si on peГұГұinii moЖҙЖҙere, maa on cuuЙ—ii nde maa on njaafima gah e bone, pellet, Alla seeraani jaafotooЙ—o kattanЙ—o."
  4,150,"Pellet, Й“een won Й“e e yeddude Alla e NulaaЙ“e Makko Й“een, heЙ“e paala nde Й“e ceernndata hakkunde Alla e NulaaЙ“e Makko Й“een, heЙ“e mbia :"MiЙ—en gooЕӢЙ—ina yoga min njedda yoga", heЙ“e paala jogitaade hakkunde Й—uum Й—oon laawol."
  4,151,"ЖҒeen Й—oon ko kamЙ“e tigi ngoni yedduЙ“e Й“een tigiri. Min kplalanii heeferЙ“e Й“e lepte koynooje."
  4,152,"ЖҒeen gooЙ—inЙ“e Alla e NulaaЙ“e Makko Й“e, Й“e ceerndaani hakkunde gooto e maЙ“Й“e, Й“een Й—oon, arma o weeЙ— Й“e njoЙ“di maЙ“Й“e ndi. Alla seeraani jaafoto oЙ—o jurmotooЙ—o."
  4,153,"YimЙ“e Defte Й“e no naamnoma nde njippintaa e dow maЙ“Й“e deftere immorde e ka kammu ! GooЕӢЙ—ii Й“e naamninooma Muusaa ko Й“uri Й—uum mawnude : Й“e mbi'i : "Hollu amen Alla gite". ЕҠa'as Ha'acaango ngo nanngiri Й“e sabu tooГұannge maЙ“Й“e nge. refti Й“e njogitii ngaari ndi(peeГұЙ—i) Й“aawo nde ko ari eheЙ“e e Й“anngan- nduyeeji. Min njaafii gaay Й—um Min ngokki Muusaa hujja Й“annguЙ—o.(peeГұЙ—o)"
  4,154,"Min Й“amtir dow maЙ“Й“e Tuur fello ngo sabu ahadi maЙ“Й“e ndii, min mbiani Й“e :"naatiree ka damal ko on naayiiЙ“e", Min mbi'ani Й“e : "Wata on njawtu(keerol) e asewe on", min nanngi e maЙ“Й“e ahadi tekkundi."
  4,155,"Ko sabu firtugol Й“e ahadi maЙ“Й“e ndi, e jeddugol Й“e Aayeeje Alla Й—ee, e bargol Й“e AnnabaaЙ“e Й“e ko aldaa e goonga e biigol Й“e :"Й“erЙ—e amen Й—e no cokii". Si ko woni, Alla notii e majje sabu keefe-raagu maЙ“Й“e nguu -Й“e gooЕӢЙ—intaa si wanaa seeЙ—a"
  4,156,"e sabu keeferaagu maЙ“Й“e nguu, e koЕӢngol maЙ“Й“e ngol dow Maryama fenaande mawnde"
  4,157,"e bi'ugol Й“e : "Minen min mbarii Iisaa Meme-sella, Й“iЙ—Й—o Maryama, NulaaЙ—o Alla on". Й“e mbaraani mo, Й“e peЕӢaan mo, ko woni, o nanndinana Й“e. Pellet Й“een Й“e luutondirЙ“e fii makko :Й“e ngonii e sikkitaare fii makko. Alanaa Й“e e fii Й—uum ganndal, si wanaa jokku- gol sikke, Й“e mbaraano mo e taЖҙoral(yananeede)."
  4,158,"Accu Ko woni, Alla Й“amtu mo fa'ade e Makko. Alla seeraan pooluЙ—o, Г‘eeГұЙ—uЙ—o."
  4,159,"Alaa hay gooto e yimЙ“e defte Й“een, si wonaa o gooЕӢЙ—inat mo ko adii maayde makko nden. Г‘ande Dargal o laatoto ceedotooЙ—o e dow maЙ“Й“e."
  4,160,"Ko sabu tooГұannge immorde e Й“een AlyahuudaaЙ“e, Min karmiannooЙ“e laaЙ“Й—i Й—i Й“e ndaknananoo e sabu sakkagol(paddagol)e laawol Alla ngol ko Й—uuЙ—i.(heewi)."
  4,161,"e nanngugol Й“e ngol ribaa, gooЕӢЙ—ii Й“e haЙ—aama e Й—uum, e Гұaamugol jawЙ—eele yimЙ“e Й“e e hoore mehre. Min kebilanii heeferЙ“e Й“een lepte mu'usЙ—e."
  4,162,"Kono tutiiЙ“e Й“en e ganndal e maЙ“Й“e e gooЕӢЙ—iЙ—inЙ“e Й“en, hiЙ“e gooЕӢЙ—ini ko Jippinaa ko e maaЙ—a e kon ko Jippinaa ado maaЙ—a. E ГұiiЙ“nooЙ“e juulde Й“een, etottooЙ“e asakal Й“een, e gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Alla e Г‘alaande Sakkitiinde nden, Й“een Й—oon, arma Min ngokka Й“e njoЙ“di mawndi."
  4,163,"Minen min mbahyinii e maaЙ—a wano no inn mbahyiniri e Nuuhu e AnnabaaЙ“e Й“een Й“aawo makko. Min mbahyini fa'ade e Ibraahiima, e Ismaa'iila, e Ishaaqa, e Yaaquuba, TaaniraaЙ“e Й“een, e Iisaa, e Ayyuuba, e Yuunusa, e Haaruuna, e Sulaymaana. Men ngoki Daawuuda Jabuura."
  4,164,"E NulaaЙ“e Й“e min pillani maa fii muen ko adii e NulaaЙ“e Й“e min poillanaaki ma fii muen. Alla Yewtidii e Muusaa kala jeeewtugol"
  4,165,"NulaaЙ“e wewlinooЙ“e e jertinooЙ“e fii wota hujja wonan yimЙ“e Й“en e hoore Alla Й“aawo NulaaЙ“e Й“en. Alla seerani koo poolЙ—o, Г‘eeГұЙ—uЙ—o."
  4,166,"Kono Alla no Seedii kon ko O Jippini e maaЙ—a, O Jippinirii Й—um ganndal Makko, maleykaaji Й—i no ceeditoo. Alla Yonii Seedee."
  4,167,"Pellet, Й“een yedduЙ“e, Й“e fpddii gah e laawol Alla ngol, gooЕӢЙ—ii Й“e majjii majjere woЙ—Й—unde."
  4,168,"Pellet, Й“een yedduЙ“e Й“e tooГұi, Alla Laatataaka jafatooЙ—o Й“e, wanaa nde O Feewnata Й“e laawol.peewal"
  4,169,"Si wanaa laawol Jahannama ngol, ko saasooЙ“e nder magge cay. Й—uum laatike newiiЙ—um e dow Alla."
  4,170,"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e ! GooЕӢЙ—ii NulaaЙ—o on ardirii e mon goonga immorde e Joomi mon, ngooЕӢЙ—inee ko moЖҙЖҙere mon. Si on njddii, pellet, ko Alla Woodani kala ko woni kammuuli e ka leydi. Alla seeraani gannduЙ—o, Г‘eeГұuЙ—o."
  4,171,"Eehey mon yimЙ“e defte, wata on Й“urtin ka diina mon, wata on wowlu e hoore Alla si wanaa goonga. Pellet, Mema-sella Iisaa Й“iЙ—Й—o Maryama on, ko NulaaЙ—o Alla e koЕӢngol Makko ngol O Werni e Maryama e ruuhu immorde ka Makko. ngooЕӢЙ—inee Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on, wata on mbi'u [Alla ko] :"Tato". KaЙ—itee, ko Й—uum Й“uri moЖҙЖҙannde on. Ngnndee Alla ko deweteeЙ—o Gooto. Senayee woodanii Mo nde Й“iЙ—Й—o laatantoo Mo ! Ko Kamko Woodani ko woni ka kammuuli e ka leydi. Alla Yonii koolorteeЙ—o."
  4,172,"Mema-sella on mawnitaaki nde o laatotoo jeyaaЙ—a Alla, wanaa maleykaajiЙ—i Й“attinaaЙ—iЙ—i . Kala Й“urnitiiЙ—o gaa e dewugol Mo o mawnintinii, ma O MooЙ“itoyЙ“e fa'ade ka Makko Й“e denndaangal."
  4,173,"Si tawii ko Й“een gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“e ngolli moЖҙЖҙuЙ—i, O Timminanay Й“e njoЙ“di maЙ“Й“e ndi, O Й“eydana e Й“ural Makko ngal.. Й“eya Й“urnitiiЙ“e mawnintinii, O LeptayЙ“e lepte mu'usЙ—e, Й“e keЙ“anoytaake gah Alla, giЙ—o wanaa balloowo"
  4,174,"Eehay mon yimЙ“e ! GooЕӢЙ—ii hujja arii e mooЙ—on immorde ka Joom mon, min njippinii fa'ade e mooЙ—on annoore Й“annguЙ—o.(feeГұnde)."
  4,175,"Si tawii ko Й“een gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Alla Й“e njogiitii nde, arma o naatnu Й“e e Yurmeende immorde ka Makko e Й“ural, O Fewna Й“e faade e Makko laawol po'occiingol."
  4,176,"HeЙ“e faltino maa. Maaku : "Alla no Falta on fii rone : annda si neЙ—Й—o maayii o alaa Й“iЙ—Й—o himo mari banndiraawo [debbo], no woodani on feccere e kon ko o acci. Kamko kadi o ronay mo si tawii o alaa Й“iЙ—Й—o. Si Й“e laatike Й—iЙ—o, hino woodani Й“e tataЙ“e Й—iЙ—i e kon ko o acci. Si Й“e laatike musЙ—Й“e worЙ“e e rewЙ“e, hino woodani gorko on geЙ—al rewЙ“e Й—iЙ—o. Alla no ЖҒannginannde(laЙ“Й“inana) on fii wata on majju. Alla ko gnnduЙ—o kala huunde"."
  5,1,"Een hey y mon gooЕӢЙ—iЙ“e, kuuЙ“nee piЙ“e ahadiiji Й—in. One ndknanama neemoraajiЙ—i mummunteeji Й—ii si wonaa ko Й—uume ko no dursitee dow, mon tawa wona on dakintinЙ“e baaГұugol tawa hoЙ—on korminii. Pellet, Alla no Г‘aawa Й—uum ko o Faalaa."
  5,2,"Eeheh mon gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e, wata on ndaknu maandeeji Alla Й—i, wanaa lebbi korminaaЙ—i Й—i, wonaa haddiyaaji Й—in neldaaЙ—i, wanaa Й—in meedaaЙ—iЙ—i, waoaa Й“en fa'andiiЙ“e [faandii] Suudu jormanteeru ndu heЙ“e Й—aЙ“Й“a Й“ural immorde ka Joom maЙ“Й“e e weluya. Si on ndaktiniima [ehajju maa e 'umra], mbaaГұee. Wota ngaГұngu yimЙ“e duГұu on fii Й“e paddima on ga e Suudu hormateery ndun, nde njellinton. (keeri) mbaallindireee dow Й—iggere e kulol Wota on mballindir e hoore bakkaate e ngaГұngul. Kulee Alla. Pellet, Alla ko caЙ—tuЙ—o lepte."
  5,3,"Harminaama e dow mooЙ—on : jiibe, e ЖҙiiЖҙam, e teewu ngiroowu(mbaba Tuga) kala ko ewnoraa ko wanaa Innde Alla e kirsol, e Й—eЙ—Й—ii ngol, e luubaa(lukkangol) ngol, e pukiii ngol, e kawa ngol, e ko Гұanfenji Й—in Гұaami -si wanaa ko kirsuЙ—on, e ko hirsanaa sanamuuji Й—in, e nde ceetndinorton payanЙ—e Й—en. ЖҠum mooЙ—on ko yaltude. Й—oftaare Hannde yedduЙ“e Й“en taЖҙike e diine mon o, wota on kulee Й“e, kulee kam. Hannde Mi timminanii on diine mon oo mi timminii e dow mooЙ—on dokkam Й—e. Mi welanaama on Lislaamu on diine. Kala on Й“ittiiЙ—o e heege hara wanaa o jawtuЙ—o [ooГұii] e bakkaatu on, pellet, Alla ko kafrowo, jurmotooЙ—o."
  5,4,"HeЙ“e naamnomaa ko holЙ—uum Й“e ndaknanaa ? Maaku : "on ndaknanaama laaЙ“Й—i Й—i n, e ko ganndinЙ—on immorde e barminayЙ—i, hiЙ—on nganndina Й—i ko Alla Anndini on ; Гұaamee e ko Й—i nanngani on, njaЕӢtoЙ—on Innde Alla e dow muuЙ—um. Kulee Alla. Pellet, Alla seeraani jaawuЙ—o hasboore."
  5,5,"Hannde on ndagknanaama laaЙ“Й—i Й—in. Г‘aamde nde okkaaЙ“e defte Й“en no daganii on, Гұaamde mon no daganii Й“e. E saЕӢiiЙ“e gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“ee, e saЕӢiiЙ“e okkaaЙ“e defte Й“ee ko adii mon, si on njonnii Й“e teЕӢeeji maЙ“Й“e Й—i, [wonon] saЕӢiiЙ“e tawa wonaa jinooЙ“e, wonaa jogitotooЙ“e njaatigi. Kala yeddu- Й—o gooЕӢЙ—inal ngal, gooЕӢЙ—ii golle makko Й—en mbonii, on Й—on ka laakara ko o jeyaaЙ—o e hayruЙ“e(pertube) Й“e."
  5,6,"Eehey mon yo gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e, si on ngummiima fa'adee e juulde, lootee jeece mon Й—e e juuЙ—e mon Й—en haa ka coЙ“Й“uli, meskon ko'e mon Й—e e koyЙ—e mon Й—e haa ka kolЙ“ule. Si on laatike won duЙ“e e janaaba laЙ“Й“intoЙ—ee. Si on laatike ГұawnЙ“e, maa e hoore laawol,(Й—atngal )maa arii gooto e mooЙ—on,dow wuro maa on memondirii e rewЙ“e Й“en on keЙ“aani ndiyam, taamee e leydii laaЙ“ndi : mashiron ndi jeece mon e juuЙ—e mon. Alla Fa'andaaki nde o waЙ—ata e dow mooЙ—on Й“itteende, ko woni, Ko O Fa'andii, ko laЙ“Й“ingol on, e nde O timminta dokke Makko Й—ed ow mooЙ—on, mbelejo'o, on njettat [Mo]."
  5,7,"Nganditee dokke Alla on e dow mooЙ—on e Ahadi Makko ndi o aadondiri e mooЙ—on tuma mbii'noЙ—on : "min nanii men Й—oftiima". Kulee Alla. Pellet, Alla ko ganduЙ—o ko woni e Й“erЙ—e Й—en."
  5,8,"Eehey mon yo gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e, laatee ГұiiЙ“uЙ“e wona nde Alla seedoratЙ“e nuunЙ—al. Wata tikkangol yimЙ“e duГұ on e dow nde on nuunЙ—ataa. NuunЙ—ee, ko Й—uum Й“uri Й“aЙ—taade gooЕӢЙ—al ngal. Kulee Alla, pellet, Alla seeraani kumpiti iЙ—o kon ko ngolloton."
  5,9,"Alla Fodiini Й“een gooЙ—inЙ“e Й“e ngolli golle moЖҙЖҙe, no woodani yaafuyo e njoЙ“di mawnndi."
  5,10,"ЖҒeen heeferЙ“e Й“e yedduЙ“e Aayeeje amen Й—e, Й“en Й—on, ko yimЙ“e Jahiimi."
  5,11,"Eehey mon gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e, njaЕӢtee dokke Alla on e dow mooЙ—on tuma nde yimЙ“e himmirnoo nde Й“e mbertata e dow mooЙ—on juuЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—e Alla Suri juuЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—e ga e mooЙ—on. Kulee Alla. Ko e Alla gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“en yowitotoo."
  5,12,"Wollahi Alla Nanngi ahadi Й“iЙ—Й“e Israa'iila Й“en, minn Immini e maЙ“Й“e gori sappo e Й—iЙ—i. Allaahu On Daali : "Min MiЙ—o Wonndi e mooЙ—on : si on ГұiiЙ“nii juulde nden, on njonnii asakal ngal, on gooЕӢЙ—inii NulaaЙ“e Am Й“en, o teddinii Й“e, on Гұamlii Alla Гұamaande moЖҙЖҙunde, Ma Mi heefan on bonЙ—i mon Й—in, Ma mi naatnuon Aljannaaji Й—i no ila e ley majji caatli. Kala on jedduЙ—o e mooЙ—on Й“aawo Й—um, gooЕӢЙ—ii on majjii laawol po'oЖҙcingol ngol"."
  5,13,"Ko sabu pirtugol maЙ“Й“e ahadi maЙ“Й“e ndin men kuЙ—irnoo Й“e, min mbaЙ—i Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en jo'oruЙ—e : heЙ“e mbaylita koЕӢngol ngol ga e nokku maggol, Й“e njejjiti geЙ—al e kon ko Й“e ciftinorananoo e mum .A seerataa haЙ—a Жҙellitoo e dow jamfa iwruka e maЙ“Й“e, si wonaa seeЙ—aaЙ“e e maЙ“Й“e.Yaafano Й“e laaЙ“anaa [Й“e]. Pellet, Alla no YiЙ—i moЖҙЖҙinooЙ“e Й“en."
  5,14,"E Й“een wi'uЙ“e : "minen ko min Annasaara", min nanngii ahadi maЙ“Й“e ndin, Й“e njejjiti kobe Й“e nganndintinanoo e mum. min ngurti hakkunde maЙ“Й“e ngaГұngu e konnaagu haa Г‘ande Darngal. Arma Alla humpita Й“e kon ko ngollaynoo."
  5,15,"Eehey mon yimЙ“e Defte, gooЕӢЙ—ii NulaaЙ—o Amen on arii on homo Й“annginana on ko Й—uuЙ—i e ko laatinoЙ—on hiЙ—on cuuЙ—a ka deftere, Homo Yaafoo ga e ko Й—uuЙ—i. GooЕӢЙ—ii arii e mooЙ—on Annoora, e deftere Й“anngunde. (FeeГұnde)"
  5,16,"Alla no Fewnira nde on jokkuЙ—o weluya makko on laabih kisal, Homo Yaltina Й“e e niЙ“e fa'ade e Annoora e DuЕӢayee(sakkitoore) Makko, O Feewnna Й“e fa'ade e laawol po'occiingol."
  5,17,"Wollahi yeddii Й“een wi'iЙ“e : "Allaahu kamko woni Mem a-sella Й“iЙ—Й—o Maryama on". Maaku : "Ko hommbo waawi e Alla huunde si o Fa'andike nde o hallkata Mema-sella Й“iЙ—Й—o Maryama on, e yumma makko, e ko woni ka leydi kon fof ?" Ko Alla Woodani Laamu kammuuli Й—in, e leydi ndin, e ko woni hakkunde majji. Homo Taga ko O Muuyi. Alla ko kattanЙ—o kala huunde."
  5,18,"Alyahuuda e Annasaara'en mbi'i : "minen ko min Й“iЙ—Й“e Alla e yiЙ—Й“e Makko"! Maaku: "Awa ko fii holЙ—um O Leptirta on bakkatuujii mon Й—in?" Ko woni, onon ko on Й“anndiyaЕӢkooЙ“e jeyaaЙ“e e kon ko O Tagi". Homo yaafo o mo O muuyi, oLepta on o muuyi. Ko Alla woodani Laamu kammuuli Й—in, e leydi ndin, e ko woni hakkunde majji kon. Ko Fa'ade ka makko woni ruttorde nde."
  5,19,"Eehey mon yo yimЙ“e defte, gooЕӢЙ—ii nulaaЙ—o amen o arii e mon hombo feГұГұinana on e dow taЖҙontinnde(fatra) immorde e nulaaЙ“e, fii wata on mbi'i: "Araani e amen beltinoowo, wonaa jeertinoowo". GooЕӢЙ—ii arii e mon beltinoowo, e jeertinoowo. Alla ko kattanЙ—o kala huunde."
  5,20,"Tuma nde Muusaa maakannoo yimЙ“e makko Й“e : "Eehey mon yimЙ“e, gannditee dokke Alla e dow mooЙ—on, tuma nde o WaЙ—noo e mooЙ—on AnnabaaЙ“e, o waЙ—i on laamЙ“e, o okki on kon ko o okkaali hay gooto e winndere he"
  5,21,"Eehey mon yimЙ“e, naatee ka leydi laЙ“Й“inaandi ndi Alla winndani on, wata on njiltor Й“aawo e dow gaЙ—a-teppe mo'on nduttitoЙ—on hayruЙ“e(.pertuЙ“e)"
  5,22,"ЖҒe mbi'i : "Pellet, hino e mayri yimЙ“e dunndaranke, menen men naatataa e mayri haa Й“e njalta ton, si Й“e njaltii e mayri, pellet ko min naatooЙ“e"."
  5,23,"WorЙ“e Й—iЙ—o jeyaaЙ“e e hulЙ“e, Й“e Alla waЙ—i e dokkem eheЙ“e mbi'i : "NaatiraneeЙ“e ka damal, si on naatirii e maggal, pellet, onon ko o foolooЙ“e. Ko e Alla fawotoЙ—on si on laatike gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e"."
  5,24,"ЖҒe mbi'i: "Eehey ma yo Muusaa, minen min naatataa ton poomaa fodde hiЙ“e ton. Yah an e Joom maaЙ—a haЙ“on. Minen Й—oo ko min jooЙ—iiЙ“e"."
  5,25,"O Maaki : "Joomam, min mi jeytanaa si wonaa hoore-am e mawnam Haaruuna. Seerndu hakkunde amen e Й“e yimЙ“e yaltuЙ“e Й—oftaaree"."
  5,26,"O Daali : "Pellet, ndii [leydi] harminaama e dow maЙ“Й“e duuЙ“i cappanЙ—e nayi. HeЙ“e mbeema ka leydi. Wata a suno e Й“een yaltuЙ“e. Й—oftaare."
  5,27,"Janngu e dow maЙ“Й“e kumpitaol Й“iЙ—Й“e-Aadma Й—iЙ—o, e goonga, nde Й“e Й“aЙ—tornoo Й“aЙ—tordi, gooto e maЙ“Й“e jaЙ“anaa, goЙ—Й—a jaЙ“anaaka. On wi'i : "ma mi warma". O wi'i : "Anndu ka Alla JaЙ“anta, ko gooЕӢЙ—uЙ“e Й“een(.hulЙ“e Alla)"
  5,28,"Si a fortii junngo maa ngo e am fii yo a waram, mi mi wonaali portoowo juungu am e maa fii yo mi ware. Min miЙ—o hula Alla JeyЙ—o winndere nde."
  5,29,"Miin miЙ—o yiЙ—i nde nduttortaa e bakkaat am on e bakkaat maa on, laatodaa e yimЙ“e yiite ngen. Ko Й—uum woni njoЙ“di tooГұooЙ“e Й“e."
  5,30,"Wonkii makko kin suЙ—ani mo bargol musiЙ—Й—o makko neene-gooto on, o wari mo, o waЙ—tini jeyaaЙ—o e hayruЙ“e Й“een.(pertuЙ“e Й“e)"
  5,31,"Alla Nuli kaakaaru(Jeyyal) hino wiЙ—oo ka leydi fii yo ndu hollu mo honno o wirnirta Й“anndu musiЙ—Й—o makko neene-gooto on. O wi'i : "E bone am ! E mi ronkay wa'ade na nduu kaakaaru mi wirna Й“anndu musiЙ—Й—am neene-gooto am on ?". O WaЙ—tini jeyaaЙ—o e ninsuЙ“e Й“een."
  5,32,"Ko sabu Й—um min parliri e Й“iЙ—Й“e Israa'iila Й“en, wonnde : "Kala barЙ—o woЕӢkii awaa wanaa joftanagol- gol woЕӢkii maa bonni ka leydi, tawat o waЙ—ii wa barЙ—o yimЙ“e Й“een fof, mo wuurnii ki kadi, o wa'ii wa on guurnuЙ—o yimЙ“e Й“en fof". GooЕӢЙ—ii NulaaЙ“e amen Й“e gaddanii Й“e Й“anngannduyeeji, refti pellet, ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e maЙ“Й“e Й“aawo Й—um, ko Й“e fantimЙ“e( Й“urtinooЙ“e)ka leydi."
  5,33,"Ngandee njoЙ“di Й“een haЙ“ooЙ“e Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on, hiЙ“e yaha bonna ka leydi, ko nde Й“e mbaretee, maa Й“e dummbee, maa juuЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en e koyЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en taЖҙee luutindiree, maa Й“e ndiiwee e leydi ndin. ЖҠuum Й—on, no woodani Й“e koyeera ka aduna ; no woodani Й“e kadi ka laakara, lepte mawЙ—e."
  5,34,"Si wanaa Й“en tuubuЙ“e ko adii on heЙ“ude feere maЙ“Й“e. Anndee pellet, Alla ko kaforoowo, jurmotooЙ—o."
  5,35,"Eeheymon yo gooЕӢЙ—imЙ“e, kulee Alla, Й—aЙ“Й“iron e Makko jokkorgal, tiiЙ—noЙ—on e Laawol Makko, mbelajo'o, on maloyte."
  5,36,"Pellet, Й“een yedduЙ“e, sinno no woodannoo Й“e denndaagal ko woni ka leydi e yeru mun wonndude e Й—um, fii yo Й“e coottor Й—um immorde e lepte Г‘ande Darngal, Й“e jaЙ“antaake. No woodani Й“e lepte mu'usЙ—e."
  5,37,"HeЙ“e paalaa nde Й“e njaltata ka yiite, Й“e wonaani yaltooЙ“e e magge. Hino woodani Й“e lepte ГұiiЙ“Й—e."
  5,38,"Gujjo [gorko] e gujjo [debbo] : taЖҙee juuЙ—e maЙ“- Й“e Й—en, njoЙ“di ko Й“e faggitii kon, Й—um ko lepte immorde ka Alla. Alla ko pooluЙ—o, Г‘eeГұЙ—o."
  5,39,"Kala tuupЙ—o Й“aawo tooГұe makko Й—en, o moЖҙЖҙini, pellte, Alla JaЙ“anay mo tuubuubuyee. Pellet, Alla ko kafroowo, jurmtooЙ—o."
  5,40,"E a anndaa won de no woodani Alla Laamu kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin, Homo Lepta on mo O muuyi, o yaafo on mo O muuyi. Alla ko kattanЙ—o kala huunde."
  5,41,"Eeheyma aan NulaaЙ—o, wota Й“en yaccotooЙ“e e keeferaaku sunine immorde e Й“een wi'iЙ“e: "min gooЕӢЙ—inii" kunndule maЙ“Й“e, tawi Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—e gooЕӢЙ—inaani E Й“een AlyahuudaaЙ“e heЙ—itantooЙ“e fenaande, heЙ—itantooЙ“e yimЙ“e goo Й“e ngaraani e maaЙ—a : heЙ“e mbayla KoЕӢngolngol gaamb e nokku maggol, heЙ“e mbi'a: "Si on njonnaama Й—um Й—oo Жҙettee, si on njonnaaka Й—um ndeentee". Kala mo Alla Fa'andanii fitina mo, a jeytantaa mo immorde hay e huunde immorde ka Alla. Ko Й“en ngoni Й“e Alla Faalaaka LaЙ“Й“innde Й“erЙ—e muen. Hino woodani Й“e koyeera ka aduna, hino woodani Й“e lepte mawЙ—e ka laakara."
  5,42,"HeЙ—itantooЙ“e fenaande, ГұaamooЙ“e jeeeenaari. Si Й“e ngarii ma, Гұaawu hakkunde maЙ“Й“e maa Й—uurno-Й—aa Й“e. Si a Й—uurnike Й“e, Й“e lorrataa ma hay e huunde. Si a Гұaaway, Гұaawir hakkunde maЙ“Й“e nuunЙ—al. Pellet, Alla no YiЙ—i nuunЙ—uЙ“e Й“e."
  5,43,"E ko honno Й“e Гұaawinoray maa, Tawreeta on no ka maЙ“Й“e, no e mayre Г‘aawoore Alla nden, refti Й“e Й—uurnoo Й“aawo Й—um. ЖҒeen wonaani gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e!"
  5,44,"Minen min njippinii Tawreeta, hino e mayre Peewal e Annoora. Hino Гұaawira nden AnnabaaЙ“e Й“een jebbiliiЙ“e, wonannde Й“een alyahuudaa Й“e, e Й“een rewooЙ“e e jannguЙ“e Й“een, sabu kon ko Й“e reeninaa ka deftere Alla, Й“e laatii e dow Й—uum ko Й“e seediiЙ“e. Wata on kul yimЙ“e Й“e, kulee kam min. Wota on coottiri Aayeeje Am Й—e cogguyel pamaroy. Kala mo Гұaawiraani ko Alla Jippini ko, ko Й“een Й—on ngoni heeferЙ“e Й“en."
  5,45,"Min parlii e maЙ“Й“e ka taTawreeta : won ЕӢki wonkii ko woЕӢkii yoЙ“irtee, yiitere ko yiitere, hinere ko hinere, nofru ko nofru, Гұi'ire ko Гұi'ire, barme Й—en ko ko yoftondirtee. Kala cakkiiЙ—o Й—uum, ko kaffaara wonan de mo. Kala mo Гұaawiraaniko Alla Jippini kon, ko Й“een Й—on ngoni tooГұuЙ“e Й“een."
  5,46,"Min ndewaniie batteeji maЙ“Й“e Iisaa Й“iЙ—Й—o Maryama, gooЕӢginЙ—o Й—uum ko woni yeeso makko immorde e Tawreeta. Minn okki Linjiila, hino e mayre Peewal, e Annoora, gooЕӢЙ—innde kon ko woni yeeso mayre immorde e Tawreeta, ko nde Peewal, e Waaju wonan de gooЕӢЙ—uЙ“e Й“een."
  5,47,"Yo yimЙ“e Linjiila Й“en Гұaawir kon ko Alla Jippini e mayre. Kala mo Гұaawiraali kon ko Alla Jippini, ko Й“een Й—on ngni fyaltuЙ“eЙ“een. Й—oftaare"
  5,48,"Min njippinii deftere nden e maaЙ—a goonga, ko nde gooЕӢЙ—innde ko woni yeeso mayre immorde e dedfte, ko nde Жҙellitiinde e dow majje. Г‘aawir hakkunde maЙ“Й“e kon ko Alla Jippini, wata a jokku belaaЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en ga e kon ko ari emaa e goonga. Min mbaЙ—anii kala e mooЙ—on Sari'a e Laawol. Sinno Alla YiЙ—no, O WaЙ—ayno on leГұol gootol .ko woni, ko fii yo O Ndaarndo on e kon ko O Okki on. Adondiree e moЖҙЖҙi Й—in. Ko faade ka Alla woni ruttorde mon, O kumpita on kon ko luutondiraynoЙ—on fii mun."
  5,49,"Г‘aawir hakkunde maЙ“Й“e kon ko Alla Jippini, wata a jokku belaaЙ—eЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en, rento Й“e nde Й“e pitinintama ga e yoga e kon ko Alla Jippini e maaЙ—a. Si Й“e nduЕӢitima ,anndu si ko woni, Alla Faala nde O Meminta Й“e sabu yoga e junuubi maЙ“Й“e. Pellet, ko heewi e yimЙ“e Й“en ko yatuЙ“ee. Й—oftaare"
  5,50,"E ko Гұaawoore majjuyanko'en Й“e Й—aЙ“Й“ata ? Ko hommbo Й“uri Alla Гұaawoore wonan de yimЙ“e yananaaЙ“e ?"
  5,51,"Eehey mon gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e, wota on njogitor alyahuuda e Annasaara weldiiЙ“e, yoga maЙ“Й“e ko weldiiЙ“e yoga. kala e mo'on belduЙ—o e maЙ“Й“e, oen Й—oon ko e maЙ“Й“e jeyaa. Pellet, Alla Fewnataa yimЙ“e tooГұooЙ“e Й“e."
  5,52,"Tan nji'a Й“een Й“e Гұawu woni e Й“erЙ—e mu'uen no njaaw-no e maЙ“Й“e, heЙ“e mbi'a : "min kuli nde yiiloode heЙ“ata amen". Ar ma Alla Adda Uddital, maa fiyaake immorde ka Makko, Й“e mbattina e kon ko Й“e cuuЙ—i ka pittaali maЙ“Й“e ko Й“e nimsuЙ“e."
  5,53,"GooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“en no mbi'a : "E ko Й“ee Й—oo ngoni Й“een woondirnooЙ“e Alla hattirde woondooje maЙ“Й“e, [wo nde] pellet, hiЙ“e ngnnde e mooЙ—on?" Golle maЙ“Й“e Й—en mbonii, Й“e mbattini ko Й“e hayruЙ“e.(pertuЙ“e)"
  5,54,"Eeheymon yo gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e, kala jartodinЙ—o e mooЙ—on e diine mum arma Alla Adda yimЙ“e Й“eo yiЙ—i kamЙ“e kadi Й“e njiЙ—i mo, tawa ko newaniiЙ“e gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“e, ГұaaЙ—anЙ“e e heeferaaЙ“e Й“e, heЙ“e tiЙ—noo e laawol Alla ngol, Й“e kulataa feloore peloowo. ЖҠuum ko Й“ural Alla, homo weeeЙ—a ngal on Mo o Muuyi. Alla ko YaajuЙ—o [Й“ural], nganduЙ—o."
  5,55,"Ngandee giЙ—o mon on ko Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on e Й“een gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e : tottirooЙ“e juulde, Й“e totta asakal, hara kamЙ“e ko Й“e gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e."
  5,56,"Kalo melduЙ—o e Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko e Й“een gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e : pellet, fedde Alla nden ko Й“een ngni foolooЙ“e Й“e."
  5,57,"Eehey monyo gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e, wata on njogito Й“een jogitoriiЙ“e diine mon o jalnorЙ—i e fijindaaru, immorde e Й“een okkaaЙ“e defte adii mon, e heeferaaЙ“e Й“een weldiiЙ“e. Kulee Alla si on laatike gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e."
  5,58,"Si on noddii faade e juulde, Й“e njogitora nde jalnorЙ—ii e fijindaaru : ko waЙ—i Й—um, kamЙ“e ko Й“e yimЙ“e Й“e kakkiltaa."
  5,59,"Maaku : "Eehey mon yimЙ“e defte, e on njoftoto min fii min gooЙ—inii Alla e kon ko Jippinaa e amen, e kon ko Jippinanoo ko adii, e won de pellet, ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e mon ko yaltuЙ“eЙ—oftaare?!"."
  5,60,"Maaku : "E on ngaccata mi mi humpita on ko Й“uri Й—uum Й—on bon de mbarjaari ka Alla ? Kala mo Alla HuЙ—i, O Tikkani on, owaЙ—i e maЙ“Й“e baaЙ—i e girayЙ—i(girji),(bamЙ—ituga) e rewooЙ“e bewinayЙ—i Й—in. Ko Й“een Й—on Й“uri bon de nokku, Й“uri majjude kadi laawol potondirgol ngol"."
  5,61,"Si Й“e ngarii e mo'on, Й“e mbi'a : "Men gooЕӢЙ—inii". GooЙ—ii non Й“e naatidii e keeferaaku ngu, tawi kamЙ“e Й“e njaltiino e maggu. Ko Alla Й“uri Anndude kon ko Й“e cuuЙ—aynoo."
  5,62,"HaЙ—ayi'a ko heewi e maЙ“Й“e no yaccora e bakkaat,e ngaГұamtumaagu, Гұaamgol Й“e njeenaari. Bonii kon ko Й“e laatinoo heЙ“e ngolla."
  5,63,"Ko haЙ—no Й“ee rewooЙ“e [maЙ“Й“e], e annduЙ“e [maЙ“Й“e] Й“en kaЙ—a Й“e gah e konngol maЙ“Й“e bakkaat ngol e Гұaamgol Й“e njeenaari ndin ? Bonii kon ko Й“e laatinoo heЙ“e ngolla"
  5,64,"Alyahhuda'en mba i': "Junngo Alla ngon ko Гұobbaango JuuЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—een Гұobbaama, Й“e kuЙ—iraama kon ko Й“e kaali ! Si ko woni, JuuЙ—e Makko Й—en [Й—iЙ—i] ko fortaaЙ—e, Homo Nafqira no O Muuyiri. Pellet, ko Jippinaa kon e maa immorde ka Joomi, Й“eyday ko heewi e maЙ“Й“e bewre e keeferaaku. Men Wernii hakkunde maЙ“Й“e ngaГұngu e konnaagu haa Г‘ande Darngal. Tuma kala Й“e kuЙ“Й“i yiite fii hare, Alla ЖҠannina nge. HeЙ“e yaha ka leydi bonnugol. Alla non YiЙ—aa bonnooЙ“e Й“e."
  5,65,"Sinno yimЙ“e defte Й“een ngooЕӢЙ—inno Й“e kuli (Alla), min Heefanayno Й“e boneeji maЙ“Й“e Й—in, min Naatno Й“e kadi Aljannaaji Neema."
  5,66,"Sinno kamЙ“e Й“e ГұiiЙ“nuno Tawreeta e Linjiila, e kon ko Jippinaa faade e maЙ“Й“e immorde e Joomi maЙ“Й“e, Й“e Гұaamirayno senngo dow maЙ“Й“e e ley koyЙ—e maЙ“Й“e. No e maЙ“Й“e leГұol raЙ“Й“indiniiЙ—e, ko Й—uuЙ—i e maЙ“Й“e bonii ko Й“e ngollata."
  5,67,"Eehey ma NulaaЙ—o, yottin kon ko Jippinaa e maaЙ—a immorde ka Joomi maa, si a waЙ—aalni ,haray a yottinaani nulal makko ngal. Alla ko daЙ—ndoowo ma e yimЙ“e Й“een. Pellet, Alla Fewnataa yimЙ“e yeddooЙ“e Й“een."
  5,68,"Maaku : "Eehey mon yimЙ“e defte, on ngonaa e huunde haa ГұiiЙ“non Tawraata e Linjiila e kon ko Jippinaa e mooЙ—on immorde ka Joommon". Ko maa tun ko Jippinaa kon e maaЙ—a immorde ka Joomi maaЙ—a Й“eyda ko Й—uuЙ—i e maЙ“Й“e bewre e keeferaaku. Wata a suno fii yimЙ“e yedduЙ“e Й“e."
  5,69,"Pellet, Й“een gooЙ—inЙ“e, e Й“en AlyahuudaaЙ“e, e Й“ee rewooЙ“e koode, e Annasaara'en, kala on gooЕӢЙ—inЙ—o Alla e Г‘alaande Sakkitiinde nden, o golli golle-moЖҙЖҙe : kulol alanaa Й“e, wanaa kamЙ“e cunoytoo."
  5,70,"Wollahi minЖіetii ahadi Й“iЙ—Й“e Israa'iila Й“een, minn Nuli e maЙ“Й“e NulaaЙ“e. Tuma kala nde NulaaЙ—o addani Й“e kon ko pittaali maЙ“Й“e Й—in mbelaaka : fedde goo Й“e njedda, fedde goo no mbara."
  5,71,"ЖҒe tamЖҙinii fitna laatotaako, Й“e mbumi Й“e pah'Й—i. Refti Alla JaЙ“ani Й“e tuubuubuyee. Refti ko heewi e maЙ“Й“e mbumi Й“e pahaЙ—i. Alla ko reenuЙ—o kon ko Й“e ngollata."
  5,72,"Wollahi Й“een wi'uЙ“e : "Alla ko Almasiihu Й“iЙ—Й—o Maryama on"Й“e keeforini. Almasiihu on maaki : "Eeheymon Й“iЙ—Й“e Israa'iila, ndewee Alla Joomi am e Joomi mon. Pellet, kala sirkanЙ—o Alla, anndu Alla harminanii e mum Aljanna, werde makko nden ko ka yiite. Alanaa tooГұooЙ“e Й“een balloowo."
  5,73,"Willagi yeddii Й“een wi'uЙ“e : "Alla ko tatЙ“itЙ—o (Allaji)tato Alaa deweteeЙ—o si wanaa deweteeЙ—o gooto. Si Й“e kaЙ—itaaki gaa e ko Й“e wowlata, ko maa mema Й“een yedduЙ“e e maЙ“Й“e lepte muusuЙ—e."
  5,74,"E Й“e tuubantaa Alla Й“e imsinoo Mo?! Alla ko kaforoowo, jurmotooЙ—o"
  5,75,"Almasiihi Й“iЙ—Й—o Maryama on wonaani si wonaa NulaaЙ—o, gooЕӢЙ—ii NulaaЙ“e feЖҙЖҙiino ado makko. Neene makko ko goosguЙ—o, kamЙ“e Й—iЙ—o hiЙ“e Гұaamaynoo Гұaametee. Ndaaru ko honno minn ЖҒannginiranta Й“e Aayeeje Й—een, refti ndaaraa ko honno Й“e wonaa fekindoreede."
  5,76,"Maaku : "E on ndeway ko wonaa Alla, kon ko jeytantaa on lorra wanaa nafa?!", Alla non ko Nanoowo, gannduЙ—o."
  5,77,"Maaku : "Eehey mon yimЙ“e defte, wata on Й“urtin e diina mon kan ko woori goonga, wata on njokku beleeЙ—e yimЙ“e [Й“e tawta] gooЕӢЙ—ii Й“e majjii ko adii, Й“e majjini ko Й—uuЙ—i, Й“e majji laawol potondirngol ngol."
  5,78,"ЖҒeen yedduЙ“e e Й“iЙ—Й“e Israa'iila Й“en kuЙ—iraama e Й—emngal Daawuda, e Iisaa Й“iЙ—Й—o Maryama on. ЖҠuum le, ko sabu koЙ“e mboopii kon, Й“e laatii yawtooЙ“e. Keeri ALLA"
  5,79,"ЖҒe kaЙ—indirtaano e bone mo Й“e mbaЙ—i. bonii kon ko Й“e ngollatnoo!"
  5,80,"HaЙ—a yi'a ko Й—uuЙ—i e maЙ“Й“e no mbelda e Й“een yeddu- Й“e. bonii kon ko pittaali maЙ“Й“e Й—in ngrdinani Й“e, nde Alla Tikkani Й“e, ko ka lepte woni kamЙ“e ko Й“e heddotoo.(saasooЙ“e)"
  5,81,"Sinno Й“e gooЕӢЙ—inano Alla, e Annabaajo on e kon ko Jnjppinaa e makko, Й“e njgittonooko Й“en [yedduЙ“e] weldiiЙ“e. Kono ko Й—uuЙ—i e maЙ“Й“e ko yaltuЙ“e Й—oftaare"
  5,82,"A tawat wollahi ko Й“uri aГұde e yimЙ“e he e wonan de Й“een gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e,ko Alyahuuda'en e Й“en sirkooЙ“e.A taway kadi ko Й“uri Й“e Й“aЙ—taade gooЙ—inЙ“e Й“en giggol, ko wi'ooЙ“e Й“e :"minen ko Annasaara".ЖҠuum non,ko tawde hino e maЙ“Й“e annduЙ“e e rewooЙ“e,e won de kamЙ“e Й“e mawnintintaako."
  5,83,"Si Й“e nanii ko Jippinaa kon e NulaaЙ—o on, a yi'ay gite maЙ“Й“e Й—en no yuppoo gonЙ—i, sabu kon ko Й“e anndi e goonga kan. HeЙ“e mbia: "Joom amen, min gooЕӢЙ—inii, Winndidu min e seediiЙ“e Й“en"."
  5,84,"E ko haЙ—ata amen gooЕӢЙ—inde Alla e ko ari e amen kon immorde e goonga, men tamЖҙinoo nde Joomi amen WaЙ—tida men e yimЙ“e moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e Й“een?"."
  5,85,"Alla YoЙ“iri Й“e sabu kon ko Й“e mbi'i : Aljannaaji Й—i caatli ilata senngo ley majji, ko Й“e duumotooЙ“e ton. ЖҠum Й—on ko njoЙ“di moЖҙЖҙinЙ“e Й“e,"
  5,86,"ЖҒeen heeferЙ“e Й“e njeddi Aayeeje amen Й—een, Й“een Й—oon, ko yimЙ“e Jahiimi."
  5,87,"Eehey mon yo gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e, wota on karrmin laaЙ“uЙ—i Й—i Alla dakginani on, wata on njatu. Pe keerol, Alla YiЙ—aa yawtooЙ“e Й“n.keeri Alla"
  5,88,"Г‘aamee e kon ko Alla Arsiki on dagiiЙ—i laaЙ“uЙ—i. Kulon Alla O Mo ngooЕӢЙ—inЙ—on."
  5,89,"Alla Nanngitirtaa on ko faljuЙ—on ka gooЙ—ndooje mon, kono Homo Nanngitira on kon ko piЙ“Й—on e gooЙ—ndoodooje Й—e e muuЙ—um. Kaffaara mum on, ko Гұammingol miskineeЙ“e sappo immorde ko hakindii e ko Гұamminton Й“eynguureeji mon, maa koltu maЙ“Й“e, maa rimЙ—in gol daande. On mo heЙ“aali [Й—uum], ko koorgol Й“alЙ—e tati. ЖҠuum Й—oon ko kaffaara gooЙ—ndooje mon si on ngooЙ—ndii. Ndeenee gooЙ—ndooje mon Й—e .Ko nii Alla ЖҒannginiranta on Aayeeje Makko Й—en, belajo'o, on njetta [Mo]."
  5,90,"Eehey mon gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e, ngannde esiwram= sanngara Й—am, e karte Й—en, e sanamuuji Й—in e payaloy koy [fow] ko soЙ“e jeyaaЙ—um e golle seytaane,ngoЙ—Й—itee Й—um, mbelejo'o, on maloyte."
  5,91,"Nganndee ko seytaane faalaa, ko nde o liЙ“ata ngaГұgu e konnaagu(tikere)hakkunde mo'on ka siwram e ka karte, o faddoo on ga e jaЕӢtagol Alla e juulde nden. Hara onon ko on haЙ—itotooЙ“e ?(woppooЙ“e)?"
  5,92,"ЖҠoftee Alla, Й—oftoЙ—on NulaaЙ—o o, ndeentoЙ—on ! Si on nduЕӢitiim, nganndee pellet, ko fawii NulaaЙ—o Amen on, ko jottingol Й“anngina.(peeГұngol ngol)."
  5,93,"Bakkaat fawaaki Й“een gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“e ngolli golle-moЖҙЖҙe e kon ko Й“e Гұaamuno si Й“e kulii Й“e gooЕӢЙ—inii Й“e golli golle-moЖҙЖҙe, refti Й“e ndeentii Й“e gooЕӢЙ—ini, refti Й“e gooЕӢЙ—i Й“e moЖҙЖҙini. Alla No YiЙ—i moЖҙЖҙinooЙ“e Й“en."
  5,94,"Eehey mon gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e, ma Alla Jarribor on huunde e mbaroodi=raddo, hiЙ—on nanngira Й—um juuЙ—e mon Й—en e gaawe mon Й—en ; fii no Alla Anndira on kuloowo Mo e birnal. Kala jaggituЙ—o (jawtuЙ—o keerolo) Й“awa Й—uum, hino woodani mo lepte muusuЙ—e."
  5,95,"Eehey mon yo gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e, wota on mbar mbaroodi=raddaande hara ko on horminii Й“e. Kala barЙ—o ndi e mooЙ—on ko o tewiiЙ—o, njoЙ“di mum, ko yeru kon ko o wari neemoraaЙ—i, Гұaawa Й—um joomiraaЙ“e nuunЙ—al Й—iЙ—o e mooЙ—on, neldaari yottotoondi Kaaba on, maa kaffaara Гұammingol miskiieeЙ“e, maa ko fotata Й—uum Й—oon koorka fii yo o meeЙ— battane fiyaake makko on. Alla Yaafike kon ko feЖҙЖҙi ; kala duttiiЙ—o, Alla Yoftota e Makko. Alla ko pooluЙ—o, Jom-joftagol."
  5,96,"Daginanaama on baaГұgol ka maayo, Гұaametee mum on ko dakamme wonan de on e setotooЙ“e Й“e. Karminanaama on baaГұugol ka jeeri fodde hiЙ—on kormii. Kulee Alla Oon mo mooЙ“oyteЙ—on to mum."
  5,97,"Alla WaЙ—ii Kaaba on : Suudu Hormanteendu, ГұiiЙ“irndu wonan de yimЙ“e Й“een, e lewru hormante ndu, e neldaari ndi, e meedaaЙ—i Й—in. ЖҠuum Й—on, ko fii yo on nganndu won de Alla no Anndi kon ko woni kammuuli e ka leydi, e wonndi Alla no Anndi kala huunde."
  5,98,"Nganndee won de pellet, Alla ko caЙ—tuЙ—o lepte, e won de pellet, Alla ko kaforoowo, jurmotooЙ—o."
  5,99,"Fawaaki NulaaЙ—o on si wanaa yottingol. Alla no Anndi ko peГұГұinton e ko cuuЙ—oton."
  5,100,"Maaku : "ko soЙ“i kon e ko laaЙ“i kon fotataa, hay si hawnii ma Й—uuЙ—ugol ko soЙ“i kon". Kulee Alla yo joomiraaЙ“e hakkillaaji, mbelejo'o, on maloyte."
  5,101,"Eehey monn gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e ! wata on laЙ“ndo fii piiji, tawi si Й—i peГұГұinanaama on, mettay on. Si on laЙ“ndino fii majji fewndo Alqur'aanaare nden Jippotoo, Й—i peГұГұinante on. Alla Yaafike fii majji. Alla ko kaforoowo, jurmotooЙ—o."
  5,102,"GooЕӢЙ—ii yimЙ“e adinooЙ“e on laЙ“ndinoke fii majji, refti Й“e ngontiri Й—in yedduЙ“e."
  5,103,"Alla WaЙ—aali e jelaaЙ—i Й—in, wanaa accitaaЙ—i, wanaa jokkindirmba debbi, wanaa kalaldi-wa, kono heeferЙ“e Й“e no fekindoo e Alla fenaande, ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e maЙ“Й“e hakkiltaa."
  5,104,"Si Й“e mbiamaa: "ngree e ko Alla Jippini kon e faade e NulaaЙ—o on", Й“e mbi'a:"Yonii min ko min tawri baabiraaЙ“e amen Й“e", e hay si baabiraaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“e ngandaa hay e huunde Й“e peewataa?!"
  5,105,"Eeheymon gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e ! Hino fawii on pittaali mon Й—in! Lorratah on majjuЙ—o si on peewi. Ko faade ka Alla woni ruttorde mon on denndaangal; O Humpita on kon ko ngollatnoЙ—on."
  5,106,"Eeheymon yo gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e ! MbaЙ—ee seedee hakkunde mon, si maayde nden arii goЙ—Й—o e mon, tuma wasiyagol, [seedeeЙ“e] Й—iЙ—o nuunЙ—uЙ“e jeyaaЙ“e e mo'on, si tawii on yehii ka leydi masiibo maayde yanii e mon. Darnon Й“e ka batte julude, Й“e ngooЙ—ndira Alla, si on ciikkatikm Й“e ngostotaako fii Й—uum coggu, hay si laatike joomiraawo badindiral, "min cuuЙ—ataa seedee Alla on, minen ontuma [si min mbaЙ—ii Й—um], haray men njeyaama e bakkondinЙ“e Й“e"."
  5,107,"Si tawaama won de Й“e kaan di e bakkaatu, ko woЙ—Й“e Й—iЙ—o darotoo darnde maЙ“Й“e nden, hara ko jeyaaЙ“e e haanduЙ“e e hettugol , Й“e ngooЙ—ndira Alla : "Pellet, ko seedee amen on Й“uri jojjude seedee maЙ“Й“e on ; min njawtaani keeri. Minen ontuma [si men mbaЙ—ii Й—um], haray men njeyaama e tooГұooЙ“e Й“en"."
  5,108,"Ko Й—um Й—oo Й“uri Й“aЙ—taade nde Й“e ngaddata seedee e hoore nden Й—on, maa Й“e kula nde woondoore ruttetee Й“aawo woondoore maЙ“Й“e nden. Alla Fewnataa yaltuЙ“e Й—oftaare Й“e"
  5,109,"Г‘aande Alla MooЙ“oyta NulaaЙ“e Й“en, O Daala: "Ko holЙ—um njaabanoЙ—on?" Й“e maaka: "ganndal alanaa amen, pellet, An, ko An woni gannduЙ—o ko wirnii"."
  5,110,"Tuma nde Alla Daalunoo : "Ko an yo Iisaa Й“iЙ—Й—o Maryama, siftor dokkam Й—e e dow maaЙ—a e dow yumma maaЙ—a, tuma nde Mi Semmbinirno maa fittaandu laaЙ“unde ndun, haЙ—a yeewta yimЙ“e Й“en ka penuyaagal e ka ЖҙaЖҙЖҙurmayaagal. E tuma nde mi Anndinno maa binndugol ngol e ГұeГұЖҙangal ngal, e Tawreeta e Linjiila. E tuma tagaynoЙ—aa e loope wano mbaadi sonndu e DuЕӢayee An ; nguttaa e mayru ndu laatoo sonndu e DuЕӢayee Am Sellinaa bunЙ—o e Й—amaaЙ—o e DuЕӢayee Am. E tuma nde yaltinanynoЙ—aa maayЙ“e e DuЕӢayee Am. E tuma nde Mi Surnoo Й“iЙ—Й“e Israa'iila Й“en e maaЙ—a nde ngddannoЙ—aa Й“e Й“anngannduyeeji (peeГұЙ—i)Й—i,yedduЙ“e Й“e e maЙ“Й“e mbi'i: "Й—um wonaali si wanaa mbilewu peeГұungu"."
  5,111,"Tuma nde mbahyiimi e laaЙ“amЙ“e ma Й“en, si ko woni: "ngooЕӢЙ—inee kam in e NulaaЙ—o Am o", Й“e mbi'i: "min gooЕӢЙ—inii, seedito won de pellet, ko min jebbiliiЙ“e"."
  5,112,"Tuma nde laaЙ“amЙ“e [ma] Й“en mbinoo: "Ko an yo Iisaa, Й“iЙ—Й—o Maryama, hara Joomi maa hino waawi nde O jippinanta men kooliwal immorde ka kammu?" O maaki: "kulee Alla, si on laatike gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e"."
  5,113,"ЖҒe mb'i: "minn faala Гұaamde e maggal, Й“erЙ—e amen Й—en deeЖҙa, min gannda gooЕӢЙ—ii a goonganii amen, mn ngona e maggal jeyaaЙ“e e seeditiiЙ“e"."
  5,114,"Iisaa Й“iЙ—Й—o Maryama on maaki: "Yaa An Alla, Joomi amen, Jippinan amen kooliwal immorde ka kammu, ngal wonana men iidi wonan de aramЙ“e amen e sakkitiiЙ“e amen, e maande immorde ka MaaЙ—a. Arsikaa men: ko An woni MoЖҙЖҙo Arsikoowo"."
  5,115,"Allaahu On Daali : "Min, ko Mi Jippinanoowo on ngal. Kono kala jedduЙ—o e mo'on Й“aawo Й—um, Min, Mi leptay mo lepte Й—e Mi leptataa hay gooto e tagoore nden"."
  5,116,"E tuma nde Alla Daaloyte : "Ko an yo Iisaa geЙ—al Maryama, e ko an wi'i yimЙ“e Й“en : "njogitee kam min e yumma am reweteeЙ“e Й—iЙ—o ko wanaa Alla?" O maaka : "Senaadee woodanii Ma! Haananaa kam nde mi yeetotooЙ“e ko alanaa kam e mun geЙ“al ! Si wonii mi wowlanii Й—um, haray pellet, A Anndii Й—um. HaЙ—a Anndi ko woni e woЕӢkii am, mi anndaa ko woni e WoЕӢkii Maa. Pellet, An, ko An woni gannduЙ—o mbirniiЙ—i Й—in"."
  5,117,"Mi wowlanaali Й“e si wanaa kon ko njamiirЙ—aa kam, won de : "ndeewee Alla Joomi am e Joomi mon". Min laatino e dow maЙ“Й“e seeditiiЙ—o yeru ko mi wonnoo. Й“aawo nde hunnuЙ—aa mi, wonuЙ—aa An, TommbiiЙ—o e dow maЙ“Й“e. An ko A SeediiЙ—o e kala huunde."
  5,118,"Si a leptii Й“e, pelletn kamЙ“e ko Й“e jeyaaЙ“e MaaЙ—a. Si A Haforanii Й“e, pellet, An, ko An woni pooluЙ—o, Г‘eeГұuЙ—o."
  5,119,"Alla Daali : "Ndee ko Гұalaande nde goonga nafata gooЕӢЙ—Й“e Й“en goonga maЙ“Й“e on : hino woodani Й“e Aljannaaji no ila e ley majji caaЙ—i, ko Й“e duumotooЙ“e e majji poomaa". Alla Welaama Й“e kamЙ“e kadi Й“e weltorii Mo. Ko Й—um woni polagal mawngal ngal."
  5,120,"Ko Alla woodani laamu kammuuli Й—in, e leydi ndin e ko woni nder majji. Kanko ko O kattanЙ—o kala huunde."
  6,1,"Gjettooje ngoodanii Alla on TakЙ—o kammuuli Й—iin e leydi ndin,o waЙ—i niЙ“e Й—een e annoora on.refti Й“en yedduЙ“e Joom maЙ“Й“e on hobe firlito gaa mum."
  6,2,"Ko Kamko woni TagkЙ—o on immorde e loopal, refti O Г‘aawi [gooto kala] lajal, e lajal innaangal ka Makko, refti onon hoЙ—on cikkitoo."
  6,3,"Ko KaЕӢko kadi woni Alla ka kammuuli e ka leydi. Homo Anndi ko cuuЙ—on e mon, homo Anndi kadi ko peГұГұilЙ—on."
  6,4,"Aaya arataa e maЙ“Й“e immorde e Aayeeje Joomi maЙ“Й“e, si wanaa Й“e Й—uurnoto ga e majje."
  6,5,"GooЕӢЙ—ii Й“e njeddi goonga kan nde ka ari e maЙ“Й“e. Arma ara e maЙ“Й“e kumpite Й—e Й“e laatinoo heЙ“e njalkita."
  6,6,"E Й“e nji'aaniЙ—uuЙ—ii ko min kalkunoo ado maЙ“Й“e, immorde e gire? Min Newinanno Й“e ka leydi ko min Newinanaano on ; min Nuliri kammu ngun e maЙ“Й“e yuppagol, Min mbaЙ—i caati Й—in no ila senngo ley maЙ“Й“e. Min kalkiri Й“e bakkatuujimaЙ“Й“e Й—ii ; min cinci Й“aawo maЙ“Й“e gire goЙ—Й—e."
  6,7,"Sinno min njppinno e dow maaЙ—a deftere e nder Й—eri, Й“e meemiri nde juuЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en, yedduЙ“e Й“en mbayno : "Й—um wonaanisi wanaa mbilehu Й“anngu ngu".(peeГұЙ—o)."
  6,8,"ЖҒe mb'i : "Ko haЙ—no Maleyka jippinee e makko?" Sinno min njippinno maleyka, fiyaaku on gasayno ; hooti (refti)Й“e neeЙ“antaake."
  6,9,"Sinno minn mbaЙ—no mo maleyko, Men mbaЙ—ayno mo gorko, Men njillindirayno Й“e kadi kon ko Й“e njillindirta."
  6,10,"GooЕӢЙ—ii NulaaЙ“e woЙ—Й“e njalkitanooma adii maaЙ—a, jippii e Й“en jalkituЙ“e ko Й“e laatinoo heЙ“e njalkita."
  6,11,"Maaku : "njehee ka leydi refti ndaaron ko honno battane jeddunooЙ“e Й“en laatornoo"."
  6,12,"Maaku : "Ko hommbo woodani ko woni ko ka kammuuli e ka leydi?" Maaku : "Ko Alla!" O WaЙ—Й—inii e Hoore-Makko yurmeende. Pellet, O MooЙ“indiroyay on Г‘ande Darngal : nde sikke alaa e mu'm. Й“een hayruЙ“e=pertinbe pittaali mu'uen, kamЙ“e Й“e ngooЕӢЙ—intaa."
  6,13,"Ko KaЕӢko woodani ko deeЖҙi nder jemma e Гұalama. Ko KaЕӢko woni Nanoowo, gannduЙ—o."
  6,14,"Maaku : "E ko ko woori Alla mi jogitotoo giЙ—o? TakЙ—o Kammuulu Й—in e leydi ndin, KaЕӢko homo Г‘ammina O Гұammintaake". Maaku : "Min, Mi yamiraama nde mi wonata arano jebbiliiЙ—o". Wata a jeye dey e sirkooЙ“e Й“en."
  6,15,"Maaku : "Min miЙ—o huli si mi yeddii Joomi am, lepte Г‘alamo MawnЙ—o"."
  6,16,"On mo lepte Й—en firlitaa e mum nden Г‘alnde, haray gooЕӢЙ—ii [Alla] Yurmaama mo, ko Й—uum woni malal Й“anngu ngal."
  6,17,"Si Alla memnii ma lorra, kuГұcoowo ka alaa si wanaa KaЕӢko. Si o memnii ma kadi moЖҙЖҙere, KaЕӢko e dow kala huunde ko o kattanЙ—o."
  6,18,"Ko KaЕӢko woni poolЙ—o e hoore jeyaaЙ“e makko Й“en ; ko KaЕӢko woni Г‘eeГұo, kumpitiiЙ—o."
  6,19,"Maaku : "Ko holЙ—uum e huunde Й“uri mawnude seedee?" Maaku : "Ko Alla, Ko o SeediiЙ—o hakkunde am e mo'on ; ndee alqur'aanaare Wahayinaama e am, fii yo mi rentinir on nde, e kala mo nde hewti". E onon on ceedoto won de no wonndi e deweteeЙ—i goЙ—Й—o? Maaku : "Min mi seedotaako". Maaku : "ngnndee pellet, KaЕӢko ko O deweteeЙ—o bajjo". Min ko mi kisЙ—oЙ—o kon ko kafidoton e makko."
  6,20,"ЖҒeen Й“en minn ndokki deftere nden, heЙ“e nganndiri (NulaaЙ—o) on no Й“e ngandiri Й“iЙ—Й“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en. ЖҒeen hayruЙ“e pittaali muen Й—ii, kamЙ“e Й“e gooЕӢЙ—inta."
  6,21,"Alaa Й“urЙ—o tooГұude haa hewta on pekindiiЙ—o fenaande e hoore Alla, maa o fenni Aayeeje Makko Й—en. Si ko woni, tooГұooЙ“e Й“en maletaake."
  6,22,"Г‘alnde min mooЙ“indirta Й“e denndaangal, refti men mbi'ana Й“en sirkuЙ“e : "Holto kafidiiЙ“e mon Й“een Й“e aaЖҙotonoЙ—on?""
  6,23,"Refti jaabawol maЙ“Й“e ngol laataaki si wanaa nde Й“e mbi'i : "Min ngooЙ—ndirii Alla Joomi amen! Min laatanooki sirkooЙ“e"."
  6,24,"Ndaarii no Й“e peniri e pittaali maЙ“Й“e. Ko Й“e fekindotonoo kon majjirii Й“e."
  6,25,"Hino e maЙ“Й“e oon keЙ—itotooЙ—o ma, Men mbaЙ—ii ka Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e kiЙ“Й“ale fii wata Й“e paamu [alqur'aanaare] nden, e ka noppi maЙ“Й“e teddeendi. Hay si Й“e njii kala Aaya, Й“e gooЕӢЙ—inta Mo. Haa si Й“e ngrii e maa, heЙ“e mbeeГұda e maaЙ—a, yedduЙ“e Й“en mbi'a : "ЖҠum Й—oo wonaani si wanaa tinndi adinooЙ“e"."
  6,26,"KamЙ“e heЙ“e kaЙ—a [yimЙ“e Й“en] gaa e maako, heЙ“e ngoЙ—Й—ioo kadi e makko. ЖҒe alaa e halkude si wanaa pittaali maЙ“Й“e Й—in, kono Й“e so'aa anndude.(Й“e tinaani)"
  6,27,"Sinno a tinno tuma nde Й“e darnanoo ka hoore Yiite, Й“e mbi'a : "Ee haaniinande men nduttetee, hara men njeddataa Aayeeje Joomi amen Й—en, Men njeyee e gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“en"."
  6,28,"Si ko woni, feeГұanii Й“e kon ko Й“e cuuЙ—atnoo ko adii. Sinno Й“e nduttita [aduna], Й“e artay e kon ko Й“e kaЙ—anoo e mum, pellet, kamЙ“e ko Й“e fenooЙ“e."
  6,29,"ЖҒe wmb'i : "ЖҠum wonaani si wanaa nguurdam amen aduna, men wonaali immintinoyteeЙ“e"."
  6,30,"Sinno a tinno tuma nde Й“e ndarnaa yeeso Joomi amЙ“Й“e. O Daala : "ЖҠum laataaki goonga?" ЖҒe mbi'a : "Ko non woniri! Men woondirii Joomi amen!". O Daala : "Awa meeЙ—ee non lepte Й—en sabu kon ko njeddiraynoЙ—on"."
  6,31,"Goonga hayrii Й“een yedduЙ“e hawroygol e Alla. Haa si Darngal ngal arii Й“e e juhal, Й“e mbi'a : "Ee nimse amen e kon ko men mbelsindinoo e Й—am [nguurdam aduna]", hara heЙ“e ndonndorii bakkatuuji maЙ“Й“e Й—in ka Й“abbe maЙ“Й“e. Faamee bonii ko Й“e ndoondoytoo!"
  6,32,"Nguurdam aduna wonaali si wanaa fijindaaru e belaaЙ—e. Ko galle laakara Й—en Й“uri moЖҙЖҙannde Й“een gooЕӢЙ—uЙ“e. E on hakkiltaa?"
  6,33,"GooЕӢЙ—ii MiЙ—en ganndi won de ko Й“e wowlata kon no sunine. Pellet, kamЙ“e Й“e alaa ma e fennude, kono tooГұooЙ“e Й“en ko Aayeeje Alla Й—en woni yeddude."
  6,34,"GooЕӢЙ—ii NulaaЙ“e pennanooma adii maaЙ—a, Й“e muГұГұii e kon ko Й“e pannaa, Й“e lorraa, haa ballal Amen ngal ari e maЙ“Й“e. Alaa batitoowo KonnguЙ—i Alla Й—ii. GooЕӢЙ—ii arii e maaЙ—a kumpite NulaaЙ“e Й“en."
  6,35,"Si tawii Й—uurnagol maЙ“Й“e ngol saЙ—tii e maa, si a hattanii nde Й—aЙ“Й“ataa yolnde ka nder leydi, maa Й“aargal ka kammu addanaaЙ“e Aaya, [haray waЙ—u Й—um]. Si Alla Muuyuno, O MooЙ“ayno Й“e e hoore peewal. Wata a jeye [ko saЙ—ti woo] e majjuЙ“e Й“en."
  6,36,"Anndu ko noototoo, ko Й“een nanooЙ“e. MaayЙ“e Й“e, Alla Immintinoyay Й“e ; refti ko ka Makko Й“e ruttetee."
  6,37,"ЖҒe mbi'i : "Ko haЙ—no Aaya Jippinee e makko?" Maaku : "Alla ko kaЙ—atanЙ—o nde O Jippinta Aaya. Kono Й—uuЙ—uЙ“e e maЙ“Й“e ngnndaa"."
  6,38,"Alaa e duЙ“Й“oowel ka leydi, wanaa sonndu ndu hundu diwira bibje mum Й—iЙ—i, si wanaa ko mofte yeruuje mo'on. Min Accaani huunde ka deftere. Refti ko ka Joomi maЙ“Й“e Й“e mooЙ“oytee=rentite."
  6,39,"ЖҒeen jedduЙ“e Aayeeje Amen Й—e ko fahЙ—uЙ“e muumЙ—uЙ“e e nder majjere. On mo Alla Muuyi majjinnde o Majjinay mo, on mo o muuyi WaЙ—at mo e laawol po'occiingol."
  6,40,"Maaku : "njeewtee kam : si lepte Alla Й—e ngarii on maa Darngal ngal arii on, e ko ko woori Alla noddoton, si on laatike gooЕӢЙ—uЙ“e?"."
  6,41,"Si ko woni, ko KaЕӢko noddoton, o huГұca kon ko noddirton mo e mum, si o muuyii, yejjiton ko cirkoton."
  6,42,"GooЕӢЙ—ii min Nulii e mofte adii maa, min Nanngiri Й“e saЙ—teendde e lorra -beleejo'o, Й“e njakinoto."
  6,43,"Ko haЙ—no nde saЙ—teende amen nden arnoo Й“e, Й“e njakinoo ? Kono Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en njo'orii, seytaane kadi cuЙ—inanii Й“e kon ko ngollaynoo."
  6,44,"Nde Й“e njejjitnoo kon ko Й“e mbaajoraa, min ngdditanno Й“e dame kala huunde ; haa nde Й“e mbeltori kon ko Й“e ngokkaa, min Nanngiri Й“e juhal, e jaka ko Й“e taЖҙiiЙ“e."
  6,45,"Asko yimЙ“e tooГұooЙ“e Й“en taЖҙaa. Jettoore nden ngoodanii Alla, JeyЙ—o Winndere nde."
  6,46,"Maaku : "njeetenee kam! Si Alla nanngi nanЙ—e mon Й—en e ji'iЙ—e mon Й—en, o notii e Й“erЙ—e mon Й—een, ko hommbo e reweteeЙ“e ko woori Alla artiranta on Й—uym? Ndaarii ko holno Min pirlitirta Aayeeje Й—een! Refti heЙ“e Й—uurnoo."
  6,47,"Maaku : "njeetnee kam! Si lepte Alla Й—e ngardirii on e juhal maa e kene, enee, hara halkete si wanaa Й“en tooГұooЙ“e?"."
  6,48,"Min Nuliraali NulaaЙ“e Й“e si wonaa weltinooЙ“e e rentinooЙ“e : Й“en gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“e moЖҙЖҙini, kulol alanaa Й“e wanaa kamЙ“e cunoytoo."
  6,49,"ЖҒeen jedduЙ“e Aayeeje Amen Й—en, lepte Й—e memirayЙ“e kon ko Й“e njaltunoo e Й—oftaare."
  6,50,"Maaku : "Mi wi'ataa on miЙ—o mari ngaluuji Alla Й—ii, mi anndaa kadi ko wirnii, mi wi'ataa on kadi ko mi maleyko. min mi jokkaa si wanaa kon ko wahayinaa e am". Maaku : "Hara bumЙ—o e yi'oowo fotay? E on miijitotaako?"."
  6,51,"Rentinir ndee [Al Qur'aanaare], Й“en hulooЙ“e nde Й“e mooЙ“indiroytee ka Joomi maЙ“Й“e, hara alanaa Й“e ko woori Mo giЙ—o wanaa tefoowo, belajo'o, Й“e kulat ALLA."
  6,52,"Wata a raЙ—or(riddu) Й“een noddayЙ“e Joom maЙ“Й“e bimmbi e kiikiiЙ—e, heЙ“e Й—aЙ“Й“a Yeeso makko ngon. huunde e Гұaawoore maЙ“Й“e fawaaki ma, wonaa kadi huunde e Гұaawoore maa woni ko fawii Й“e sakko raЙ—oЙ—aa Й“e, jeyeЙ—aa e tooГұooЙ“e Й“en."
  6,53,"Ko wano non min njarribornoo yoga maЙ“Й“e yoga, fii yo Й“e mbi'u : "E ko Й“ee Й—oo Alla Neemini(dokke)dow mu'en hakkunde amen?" E Alla wonaali Й“urЙ—o Anndude yettooЙ“e [Mo] Й“en?"
  6,54,"Si arii e maa Й“een gooЕӢЙ—inayЙ“e Aayeeje Amen Й—e, maaku : "Yo kisal won e mo'on! Joomi mon WaЙ—Й—inii e Makko yurmeende nden : wonnde kala golluЙ—o e mo'on bone hara ko e majjere, refti o tuubi Й“aawo Й—uum o moЖҙЖҙini, haray ko o kafroowo, jurmotooЙ—o."
  6,55,"Ko wano non min paccitirta Aayeeje Й—een, fii no laawol bon Й“e Й“e feeГұira."
  6,56,"Maaku : "Min mi haЙ—aama nde mi rewata Й“een Й“e noddoton gah Alla". Maaku : "Mi jokkataa beleeЙ—e mon Й—en : gooЕӢЙ—ii haray mi majjii, haray kadi mi wonaani e feewЙ“e Й“een"."
  6,57,"Maaku : "Min miЙ—o e Й“anngannduyee immorde ka Joomi am, on njeddi Й—um. Mi alaa ko kawjanton kon. Г‘aawoore nden ko Alla woodani : Himo Fillo goonga, ko KaЕӢko Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude e fensitooЙ“e (seerndooЙ“e)goona e fenaande."
  6,58,"Maaku : "Sinno miЙ—o joginoo kon ko kawjiratnoЙ—on, fiyaaku on gasayno hakkunde am e mo'on". Ko Alla Й“uri Anndude tooГұooЙ“e Й“een."
  6,59,"Ko kaГұum jogi coktirЙ—e ko wirnii, anndaa Й—um si wanaa KaЕӢko. Homo Anndi ko woni ka jeeri e ka maayo. Kaakol yanataa si wanaa hara homo Anndi fii maggol, wanaa abbere ka niЙ“e leydi, wanaa keccol wanaa joorungol, si wanaa no e deftere Й“anngunde. (FeeГұnde)."
  6,60,"Ko KaЕӢko woni Жҙettitoowo on jemma, homo Anndi ko faggitiЙ—on Гұalawma. refti o Immintina on ontuma fii timmine lajal innaangal. refti ko ka makko woni ruttorde mon, refti o yeetitoo on kon ko ngollaynoЙ—on."
  6,61,"Ko KaЕӢko woni pooluЙ—o e dow jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“een. Homo Nula e mo'on reenooЙ“e, haa si maayde nden arii goЙ—Й—o e mo'on, nulaaЙ“e amen Й“en Жҙettita mo, kamЙ“e Й“e mbelsintaako."
  6,62,"Refti Й“e ndutte ta Alla, giЙ—o maЙ“Й“e goonga on. Faamee ko KaЕӢko tan Гұaawoore nden woodani, ko KaЕӢko Й“uri yaawude ГұaawooЙ“e."
  6,63,"Maaku : "Ko hommbo daЙ—ndata on niЙ“e jeeri e maayo?" HoЙ—on noddira mo yankinaare e gunndoo : "Si o daЙ—ndii men e Й—um Й—oo, ma men jeye e yettooЙ“e Й“en"."
  6,64,"Maaku : "Ko Alla DaЙ—ndata on e Й—um, e kala ngoЖҙo. Refti onon hoЙ—on cirka"."
  6,65,"Maaku : "Ko O kattanЙ—o nulugol lepte e dow mo'on, maa Й—e iwra les koyde mon, maa o Jillindira on dente-dente, O MeeЙ—na yoga e mo'on lepte yoga". Ndaaru no men pirlitita Aayeeje Й—en, mbelejo'o, Й“e paamat."
  6,66,"YimЙ“e maa Й“en njeddii ndee [Al Qur'aanaare], ko kayre le woni goonga kan. Maaku : "Mi wonaali e dow mon pawtiiЙ—o"(.jogiiЙ—o )"
  6,67,"Kala kumpital no mari ГұiiЙ“irde. Arma nganndoy."
  6,68,"Si a yi'ii Й“en jumpayЙ“e e Aayeeje Amen Й—en, Й—uurno Й“e haa Й“e jumpa e yeewtere woЙ—nde. Si seytaane yejjintinii ma, wata a jooЙ—oo Й“aawo annditugol ngol, e yimЙ“e tooГұooЙ“e Й“een."
  6,69,"Fawaaki Й“een gooЕӢЙ—uЙ“e, hay huunde e Гұaawoore Й“eya nden. Si ko woni, ko waaju, mbeleejo'o, Й“e kulay [Alla]."
  6,70,"Terto Й“een jogitoriiЙ“e diine muen kan fijindaaru e beleeЙ—e, nguurndam aduna Й—am hodi Й“e. Waajor ndee (alqur'aanaare) nde woЕӢkii tigintee ko ki faggitori. Alanaa ki gah Alla giЙ—o wanaa tefnotooЙ—o ; hay si ko sottorii kala cotttorgol, ki Жҙettantaake Й—uum. Ko Й“een ngoni tigintiniraaЙ“e kon ko Й“e paggitii. Hino woodani Й“e njaram ngulЙ—am e lepte muusuЙ—e sabu ko ko Й“e yeddatnoo."
  6,71,"Maaku : "E min nodday gah Alla kon ko nafataa min kadi lorrataa min? Min nduttitee e gaЙ—a-teppe amen Й“aawo nde Alla feewni amen, wano on mo seytaane fijiri ka leydi himo weemi, himo mari won diiЙ“e Й“e no nodda mo e peewal : "Ar e amen"? Maaku : "Pellet, peewal Alla ngal, ko ngaal woni peewal. Min njamiraama jebbilanagol Jom-Winndere ndeen,"
  6,72,"e wonnde ГұiiЙ“nee juulde nde kulon Mo. Ko KaЕӢko woni on mo mooЙ“oyteЙ—on ka Mum."
  6,73,"Ko KaЕӢko woni onn tagirЙ—o kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin goonga. Г‘ande O Daaloyta : "laato!", Й—um laatoo, Daalol Makko ngol ko goonga. Ko KaЕӢko [tan] laamu woodani Г‘ande wuttoytee ka alaadu. gannnduЙ—o ko wirnii e ko feeГұi. Ko KaЕӢko woni Г‘eeГұЙ—o, kumpitiiЙ—o."
  6,74,"JaЕӢto] tuma nde Ibraa hiima maakannoo ben makko Aazara: "Ea jogitoto sanamuuji deweteeЙ—i?" Pellet, min miЙ—o yi'e an e yimЙ“e maa Й“en,e ndeer majjere Й“anngunde!".(feeГұnd)"
  6,75,"Ko wano noon Min kolliri Ibraahiima laamuuji kammuuli Й—iin e leydi ndi, e fii yo o jeye e yananaaЙ“e Й“een."
  6,76,"Nde jemma on niЙ“Й“itunoo e makko, o tini hoodere, o maaki : "Ndee Й—oo ko joomi am!"Й“aawo nde mutii, o maaki : "Mi yiЙ—aa mutooЙ“e Й“een"."
  6,77,"Nde o yii lewru ndu no jalbi, o maaki : "Nduu Й—oo ko joomi am!" Й“aawo ndu mutii, o maaki : "Si Joom am fewnaani kam, ma mi jeye e yimЙ“e majjuЙ“e Й“een"."
  6,78,"Nde o yinoo naange ngen no jalbi, o maaki : "Ngee Й—oo ko joomi am! Ko ngee Й—oo Й“uri mawnude" Й“aawo nge mutii, o maaki : "Ko onon yo yimЙ“e am, min ko mi kisЙ—o e kon ko cikoton"."
  6,79,"Min dey mi fewtinirii yeeso am ngo e on TakЙ—o kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin ; ooГұiiЙ—o=haniifiyanke, min mi jeyaaka e sirkooЙ“e Й“en.(renndinooЙ“e Alla e goЙ—Й—um)."
  6,80,"YimЙ“e makko Й“en mbennji mo ; o maaki : "E on mbennjay kam fii Alla, gooЕӢЙ—ii le o fewnii kam? Mi hulataa kon ko kafidoton e Makko, si wanaa nde Joomi am muuyi huunde. Joomi am yaajanii kala huunde ganndal. E on mbaactotaako?"
  6,81,"Ko holno mi kulirta kon ko kafiduЙ—on on kulaali onon le on kafidii Alla e huunde nde O Jippinanaali on hujja? Ko honnde e peЙ—le Й—iЙ—i Й“uri haan dude e(hoolaare) deeЖҙere? Si on laatike annduЙ“e."
  6,82,"ЖҒeen gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“e njilaali gooЕӢЙ—inal maЙ“Й“e ngal e tooГұe, Й“een Й—oon no woodani Й“e hoolaare, Й“een ko feewЙ“e"."
  6,83,"ЖҠuu ko hujja Amen mo Min ngokki Ibraahiima e dow yimЙ“e Makko Й“en. MiЙ—en Й“amtana darjaaji on mo Min Muuyi. Pellet, Joomi maaЙ—a ko Г‘eeГұo, gannduЙ—o."
  6,84,"Min ngokki mo Ishaaqa e Yaaquuba Min peewni Й“e kala. E Nuuhu min peewni mo ko adii, hino jeyaa e geГұngol makko, Daawuuda e Sulaymaana e Ayyuuba e Yuusufa e Muusaa e Haaruuna. Ko wano nii Min njoЙ“irta moЖҙЖҙinooЙ“e Й“een."
  6,85,"E Zakariyaa e Yahyaa e iisaa e ilyaasa, mo kala maЙ“Й“e ko jeyaaЙ—o e moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e Й“e."
  6,86,"E Ismaa'iila e Alyasa'a e Luutu, kala maЙ“Й“e Men Й“urnii e winndere nden."
  6,87,"E baabiraaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en e geГұЙ—i maЙ“Й“e Й—in e musiЙ—Й“e maЙ“Й“e Й“een, Min cuЙ“ii Й“e, Min peewni Й“e e laawol po'occiingol."
  6,88,"ЖҠuum ko peewal Alla, himo feewnira ngal on mo O muuyi e jeyaaЙ“e makko Й“een. Sinno Й“e cirkuno, mabbatno=yirbatna gaay e maЙ“Й“e kon ko Й“e ngollaaynoo."
  6,89,"Ko Й“een woni Й“e min ngokki deftere nden e Г‘eГұЖҙal ngal e Annabaaku nguu. Si Й“ee jeddii Й—in, gooЕӢЙ—ii Min pawii Й—i yimЙ“e, Й“e laataaki yeddooЙ“e Й—i."
  6,90,"Ko Й“een ngoni Й“e Alla Feewni : ko peewal maЙ“Й“e ngal Гұemtintaa. Maaku : "Mi laЙ“ndotaako e Й—uum njoЙ“di". Nde wonaani si wonaa waaju winndere nden."
  6,91,"ЖҒe mawniniraali Alla no O haani mawninireede non tuma Й“e wmbi'noo : "Alla Jippinaani e neЙ—Й—anke hay huunde". Maaku : "Ko hommno jippini deftere nde Muusaa addi nden, ko nde annoora e peewal wonan de yimЙ“e Й“en? HoЙ—on mbaЙ—a ndee Й—eri, peГұГұinon goЙ—Й—um e majji, cuuЙ—on ko heewi.ngandinaЙ—on ko onon ngndaano onon, wanaa baabiraaЙ“e mo'on. Maaku : "Ko Alla". Refti accaaЙ“e e jumpougol maЙ“Й“e heЙ“e pija."
  6,92,"Ndee Й—oo ko deftere nde min njppini : barkinaande, gooЕӢЙ—inde ko woni yeesi mayre, e fii yo a waajor nde yimЙ“e Makka Й“ee e Й“en won Й“e takko Й—oon. ЖҒen gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e laakara, hino ngooЕӢini nde, kamЙ“e heЙ“e ndeenoo e juulde maЙ“Й“e nde."
  6,93,"Alaa Й“urЙ—o tooГұde haa foti wa on pekindiiЙ—o e Alla fenaande maa o wi'i : "Wahayinaama e am", hara hay huunde wahayinaaka e makko. E on bii'Й—o : "Mi jippinay sifa kon ko Alla Jippini". Sinno a tinno nde tooГұooЙ“e Й“en woni e paЙ—Й—e maayde, hara MaleykaajiЙ—i heЙ“e porti juuЙ—e maЙ“e Й—en (no mbi'a): "Yaltinee pittaali mon Й—in. Hannde on njoЙ“ete lepte koynooje sabu kon ko kaalaynoЙ—on e Alla ko wanaa goonga, laatiЙ—on gaay e Aayeeje Makko Й—en hoЙ—on mawnintinoo."
  6,94,"GooЕӢЙ—ii on ngardirii min telЙ—ugol, wano min Tagirnoo on arannde laawol, on ngaccii kon ko min njeynunoo on Й“aawo mon. Min njiidaani e mon tefnotooЙ“e mon Й“een Й“e ngaaЖҙinoЙ—on won de kamЙ“e e mooЙ—on ko Й“e kafiduЙ“e. GooЕӢЙ—ii taЖҙondiral waЙ—ii hakkunde mo'on : majjirii on kon ko laatinoЙ—on hiЙ—on ngaaЖҙoo."
  6,95,"Pellet, ko Alla woni peccuЙ—o abbere e kundin :(aalundere) himo yaltina ko wuuri e immorde e ko maayi, ko O yaltinoowo ka maayi immorde e ko wuuri. O mo'on ko Alla. Ko holno wonaЙ—on fefindoreede?(ferondiiЙ“e)ga goonga."
  6,96,"PeccuЙ—o subakaaji Й—in, O waЙ—i jemma on deeЖҙirde, naange ngen e lewru ndun limirЙ—i. ЖҠuum ko hoddiroore(eЙ“Й“ugol )On pooluЙ—o, gannduЙ—o."
  6,97,"Ko KaЕӢko woni baЙ—anЙ—o on koode Й—ee fii yo on peewnitorЙ—e(ma'alitorЙ—e) ka niЙ“e jeeri e ka maayo. GooЕӢЙ—ii Min fensitii (pacciri)Aayeeje Й—e wonan de yimЙ“e anndooЙ“e."
  6,98,"Ko Kanko woni puЙ—Й—uЙ—o on immorde e woЕӢkii gooti, ko ГұiiЙ“irde e marorde. GooЕӢЙ—ii Min fensitii Aayeeje Й—en wonande yimЙ“e faamooЙ“e."
  6,99,"Ko KaЕӢko woni oon jippinЙ—o ndiyam immorde ka kammu, min njltini e majjam puЙ—i kala huunde, min njaltini e majjam e Й—in (puЙ—i) keccum, miЙ—en njaltina e mum gabbe fawondirЙ—e ; e ka tamrooje immorde e piindi majje on dukke Й“attiiЙ—e, e gese immorde e inabuuje e nebbanteeje e rummaanaaje, nannduЙ—e e Й—e nanndaa. Ndaaree dimЙ—e(Й“esnooj) mun Й—een si Й—e rimii e Й“enndugol mum. Pellet, no e Й—um Й—oon mooЙ—on, kaawisaaji wonan de yimЙ“e gooЕӢЙ—inooЙ“e."
  6,100,"ЖҒe mbaЙ—anii Alla jinnaaji kafidiiЙ—i, tawi le o tagii Й“e. Й“e mbaЙ—ani Mo Й“iЙ—Й“e worЙ“e e rewЙ“e ko aldaa e ganndal! Senaare woodanii Mo, O WoЙ—Й—ike (diwi)gah e ko Й“e sifotoo koon."
  6,101,"PuЙ—Й—uЙ—o kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin. Ko holno woodiranta Mo Й“iЙ—Й—o O maraa debbo?! O tagii kala huunde, KaЕӢko ko O gannduЙ—o kala huunde."
  6,102,"Oon mon ko Alla, Joomi mon! deweteeЙ—o alaa (e goonga) si wanaa KaЕӢko, TakЙ—o kala huunde. ndewee Mo. KaЕӢko e dow kala huunde ko O fawtiiЙ—o.(deenЙ—o)."
  6,103,"GiiЙ—e Й—en kuЙ“indotaako Mo, KaЕӢko himo HuЙ“indoo giiЙ—e Й—een. Ko KaЕӢko woni NewiiЙ—o, kumpitiiЙ—o."
  6,104,"GooЕӢЙ—ii hujjaaji ngrii e mon immorde ka Joom mon : kala jaЙ“uЙ—o yi'ide ko hoore-makko [o yi'ani], kala kadi bumkiniiЙ—o ko hoore-makko [o wumanii]. Mi wonaani e dow mooЙ—on deenoowo."
  6,105,"Ko wano non min pirtiirta Aayeeje Й—en, e fii no Й“e mbi'ira : "A janngu", e fii yo min peГұГұinan Й—um yimЙ“e anndooЙ“e."
  6,106,"Jokku ko Wahyinaa kon e maa immorde ka Joomi maa. Alaa deweteeЙ—o (e goonga) si wanaa KaЕӢko. ЖҠuurno gah e sirkooЙ“e Й“een."
  6,107,"Sinno Alla muuyuno, Й“e ciirkataano! min mbaЙ—aani ma e dow maЙ“Й“e deewnoowo ; a wonaani kadi e dow maЙ“Й“e pawtiiЙ—o.(deenoowo)"
  6,108,"Wata on on njennu Й“een rewooЙ“e gah Alla, sakko Й“e njnnira Alla yottagol ko aldaa e ganndal. Ko wano nii min CuЙ—irani kala mofte, golle maЙ“Й“e, refti ko ka Joomi maЙ“Й“e woni ruttorde maЙ“Й“e ; O kumpita Й“e kon ko Й“e laatinoo hiЙ“e ngolla."
  6,109,"ЖҒe ngooЙ—nirii Alla hattirde gooЙ—nooje maЙ“Й“e : si Aaya arii e maЙ“Й“e, maa Й“e gooЕӢЙ—in mo. Maaku : "nganndee Aayeeje Й—e ko ka Alla woni". E ko so'ini on won de si Й—e ngarii, Й“e gooЕӢЙ—intaa?"
  6,110,"Min mbaylitiray Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e e jiiЙ—e maЙ“Й“e, wano Й“e gooЕӢЙ—iniraani Й—e ka arannde laawol ; min ngacca Й“e e bewre maЙ“Й“e heЙ“e mbeema."
  6,111,"Sinno Minn njippinno e maЙ“Й“e maleykaaji, maayЙ“e Й“een njeewtidi e maЙ“Й“e, min moooЙ“i e maЙ“Й“e kala huunde yeeso maЙ“Й“e ; Й“e laatotanooko gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e si wonaa nde Alla Muuyi. Kono ko Й—uuЙ—i e maЙ“Й“e hino majjaa."
  6,112,"Ko woni nii min mbaЙ—irani kala Annabaajo gaГұo : seytaaneeji yimЙ“e e jinna ; yoga maЙ“Й“e no wahyina e yoga, cuЙ—aari konngol hodo. Sinno Joomi maa muuyuno, Й“e mbaЙ—ataana Й—um, tertodu Й“e e ko Й“e pekintoo."
  6,113,"E fii yo heЙ—ito Й—uum, Й“erЙ—e Й“en Й“e ngooЕӢЙ—inaa laakara, e fii yo Й“e mbele Й—uum, e fii yo Й“e fefindo huunde nde Й“e fefindotoo."
  6,114,"E ko ko woori Alla mi Й—aЙ“Й“ata Гұaawoowo, ko KaЕӢko woni JippinЙ—o e mo'on ndee deftere fensitaande? ЖҒeen Й“e min ngokki defte Й“een, heЙ“e anndi won de ko nde Jippinaande immorde ka Joomi maaЙ—a goonga. Wata a jeye e sikkitiiЙ“e Й“en."
  6,115,"Konngol Joomi maaЙ—a ngol timmirii goonga e nuunЙ—al. Alaa battitoowo konnguЙ—i makko Й—in. Ko KaЕӢko woni Nanoowo, gannduЙ—o."
  6,116,"Si a Й—oftike ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e won Й“e ka leydi Й“een, Й“e majjinte e laawol Alla ngol : Й“e wonaani heЙ“e njokka si wonaa sikke, Й“e ngonaani si wanaa hottotooЙ“e."
  6,117,"Pellet, ko Joomi maa Й“uri Anndude on majjuЙ—o laawol makko ngol, ko KaЕӢko kadi Й“uri Anndude feewuЙ“e Й“een."
  6,118,"Г‘aamee kon ko Innde Alla jaЕӢtaa e mum si on laatike gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Aayeeje Makko Й—een."
  6,119,"E ko haЙ—ata on nde on Гұaamataa kon ko Innde Alla jaЕӢtaa e mum? GooЕӢЙ—ii O Fensitanii (facciranii)on kon ko O Harmini e mon, si wanaa kon ko Й“ittorЙ—on e mum. Pellet, ko Й—uuЙ—i [e sirkooЙ“e Й“en] hino majjira belaaЙ—e mu'um ko aldaa e ganndal. Pellet, ko Joomi Й“uri Anndude jaggitooЙ“e (jawtooЙ“e )keerol."
  6,120,"Tertee ko feeГұi e bakkaatu e ko wirnii e mum, Pellet, Й“een faggitotooЙ“e bakkaatu, Й“e yoЙ“oyte kon ko laatinoo heЙ“e fefindoo(.fekintonoo)"
  6,121,"Wata on Гұaam kon ko Innde Alla jaЕӢtaaka e mum, pellet, (salagol) Й—um ko yaltude Й—oftaare. E pellet, seytaaneeji Й—in no sowonsina(woswisina) e weldiiЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en no Й“e mbeeГұdira on. Si on Й—oftike Й“e, haray pellet, ko on sirkooЙ“e."
  6,122,"E ko on laatinooЙ—o maayЙ—o, min nguurniti mbo min mbaЙ—ani mo annoore homo yaara nde hakkunde yimЙ“e Й“een, wa'ata wa on gonЙ—on e niЙ“e mo wanaa jaltoowo toon? Ko wano noon heeferЙ“e Й“een cuЙ—iranaa ko Й“e ngollatnoo."
  6,123,"Ko wano noon min mbaЙ—iri e kala hoЙ—o (wuro,) mawЙ“e bon Й“e, fii no Й“e pewjira e mayre. ЖҒe ngalaa e fewjude si wanaa e ko'e maЙ“Й“e, kono Й“e so'aa anndude(.Й“e tinata)"
  6,124,"Si Aaya arii e maЙ“Й“e Й“e mbi'a : "min ngooЕӢЙ—intaa haa min ngokkee sugu ko NulaaЙ“e Alla Й“en okkaa kon". Ko Alla Й“uri Anndude nokku Й—o waЙ—ata Nulal Makko ngal. Aray ka koyeera e lepte tiiЙ—uЙ—e heЙ“a Й“een bon Й“e, sabu kon ko Й“e pewjantnoo."
  6,125,"Kala mo Alla muuyii feewnude, o YaГұГұanay=yaajnat Й“ernde makko nden Lislaamu. Kala kadi mo o muuyi majjinnde, o waЙ—at Й“ernde makko nden faaЙ—nde Й“ittunde ; hara himo wa'i wa ЕӢabboowo yaha ka kammu. Ko wano non Alla WaЙ—irta lepte Й—en e Й“een Й“e ngooЕӢЙ—intaa."
  6,126,"Ko Й—um Й—oo woni laawol Joomi maaЙ—a ngol peewngol. GooЕӢЙ—ii min Fensitii (pirlitii)Aayeeje Й—een woan de yimЙ“e waactotooЙ“e."
  6,127,"Hino woodanibe galle kisal ka Joomi maЙ“Й“e. Ko KaЕӢko woni keedo maЙ“Й“e sabu kon ko Й“e ngollaynoo."
  6,128,"Г‘ande MooЙ“itota Й“e denndaangal : "Ko onon yo onon yo dental jinneeji, gooЕӢЙ—ii on Й—uЙ—Й—inorii (majjingol) yimЙ“e Й“e". WeldiiЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en ka yimЙ“e mbi'a : "Joom amen, yoga amen dakmitorii yoga, men yottike ngal caatal=lajal amen ngal saatinanЙ—aa men". O Daala : "Ko Yiite nge woni jaaЖҙnde mon, ko on luttooЙ“e ton, si wanaa kon ko Alla muuyi". Pellet, Joom maaЙ—a ko Г‘eeГұЙ—o, gannduЙ—o."
  6,129,"Ko wano non minn ngurtirta yoga e tooГұooЙ“e Й“en e hoore yoga ; sabu kon ko Й“e paggitonoo."
  6,130,"Ko onon yo dental jinneeji e yimЙ“e, e araani e mo'on NulaaЙ“e jeyaaЙ“e e mo'on, Й“e no pillanoo on Aayeeje Am Й—e, Й“e ndeentina on kawrugol ndee Й—oo Г‘alaande mon? ЖҒe mbi'a : "min seedike e hoore pittaali amen". Nguurndam aduna Й—am hodi Й“e ; Й“e ceeditii e hoore pittaali maЙ“Й“e Й—in won de Й“e laatino heeferЙ“e."
  6,131,"ЖҠuum ko tawde Joom maa wonaana kalkoowo ce'e sabu tooГұe, hara yimЙ“e majje ko welsindiiЙ“e."
  6,132,"Hino woodani kala en darjaaji kon ko Й“e ngolli. Joomi maa wonaani belsindiiЙ—o e kon ko Й“e ngollata."
  6,133,"Ko Joomi ma woni Galo Jom-Yurmeende. si o muuyii o naЙ“at on, o Lomtina caggal mo'on ko o muuyi ; wano O fuЙ—Й—ornoo on immorde e Й“iЙ—Й“e yimЙ“e woЙ—Й“e."
  6,134,"Pellet, ko podaЙ—on kon ko aray Й—um. On ngonaa roЕӢkinooЙ“e [amen]."
  6,135,"Maaku: "eeymon yimЙ“am, ngollee e nokku mo'on, min ko mi golloowo. On nganndoyat ko hommbo (e men) laatantoo Й—um battane galle ". pellet,O malnatah tooГұooЙ“e Й“een."
  6,136,"ЖҒe mbaЙ—anii Alla geЙ—al e ko o tagi ko immorde e gese e neemoraaЙ—i, Й“e mbi'i : "ЖҠum Й—oo ko Alla -e aaЖҙagol maЙ“Й“e!- ЖҠum Й—oo ko kafidiiЙ—i amen Й—in". Ko wanani kon kafidiiЙ—i maЙ“Й“e Й—in hewtataa Alla, kono ko wonani kon Alla hewtat kadidiiЙ—i maЙ“Й“e Й—in. Ko Й“e Гұaawata ko bonii!"
  6,137,"Ko wano non kafidiiЙ—i ko heewi e sirkooЙ“e Й“en cuЙ—irani Й“e bargol Й“iЙ—Й“e maЙ“Й“e, fii yo Й—i halkuЙ“e e fii yo Й“e njiiЙ“ diine maЙ“Й“e kan. Sinno Alla Muuyuno, Й“e mbaЙ—ataano Й—um. Tertodu Й“e e ko Й“e pekintoo."
  6,138,"ЖҒe mbi'i : "ЖҠii Й—oo ko neemoraaЙ—i e gese feraaЙ—i(kaЙ—aaЙ—i) : Гұaamataa Й—i si wanaa on mo min njiЙ—i."-Ka aaЖҙagol maЙ“Й“e!- E neemoraaЙ—i harminaaЙ—i Й“abbe mun, e neemoraaЙ—i Й—i Й“e jaЕӢtotaako Innde Alla e mum, fekindagol e Makko ; o oyoЙ“oyat Й“e kon ko Й“e fefkndotonoo. Ma Alla yobbe fekindagol mu*en ngol."
  6,139,"ЖҒe mbi'i kadi: "Ko woni kon e deedi Й—ii neemoraaЙ—i, ko heeranii Й—um worЙ“e amen, harmani rewЙ“e amen". Si Й—um wonii ko jiipЙ—um, kamЙ“e ko Й“e kafooЙ“e Й—um. O yoЙ“oyat Й“e ko Й“e hanndi kon. KaЕӢko ko O Г‘eeГұuЙ—o, gannduЙ—o."
  6,140,"GooЕӢЙ—ii sooyii Й“een warirЙ“e Й“iЙ—Й“e mun njofoyaagal(Й—aayre) ko aldaa e ganndal, Й“e karminiri kon ko Alla Arsiki Й“e fekindagol e Alla. GooЕӢЙ—ii Й“e majjii, Й“e ngonaano feewЙ“e."
  6,141,"Ko KaЕӢko woni On piЙ—Й—uЙ—o gese baЙ—aaЙ—e bente e Й—e mbaЙ—aaka bente, e tamarooje, e remuruuji certuЙ—i Гұaamndu mu'um e nebbanteeje, e rummaana nannduЙ—e e Й—e nanndaa. Г‘aamee e dimЙ—e (Й“esnooje) majje si Й—e ndimii, njonnon asakal mun Гұande soГұaa. Wata on Й“urtin, pellet, KaЕӢko O YiЙ—aa Й“urtinooЙ“e Й“en.(bonnooЙ“e)."
  6,142,"Hino e neemoraaЙ—i Й—in ronndotooЙ—i e joltuЙ—i. Г‘aamee e kon ko Alla Arsiki on, wata on njokku taaЙ“e seytaane Й—en, pellet, kaЕӢko ko o gaГұo mon peeГұuЙ—o."
  6,143,"[O Taganii on] nooneeji jeetati : no e baali Й—in Й—iЙ—i, no e be'i Й—in kadi Й—iЙ—i. Maaku : "E ko gori Й—in Й—iЙ—i O Harmini kaa ko deyi Й—in Й—iЙ—i, kaa ko ko woni e nder renngaaji deyi Й—in Й—iЙ—i? Kumpitiree kamm ganndal si on laatike gooЕӢЙ—uЙ“e ;"
  6,144,"No e geelooЙ“ii Й—iin Й—iЙ—i, no e na'i Й—in kadi Й—iЙ—i. Maaku : "E ko gori Й—in Й—iЙ—i O harmini kaa ko deyi Й—in Й—iЙ—i, kaa ko ko woni e nder renngaaji deyi Й—in Й—iЙ—i, kaa on (tawano)ceeedino tuma Alla Wasiyinoo on Й—um?(alaamo"Й“uri) hommbo Й“uri ;tooГұude haa fota wa on fekindiiЙ—o fenaande e Alla fii no o majjiniri yimЙ“e Й“e ko aldaa e ganndal? Pellet, Alla Fewnataa yimЙ“e tooГұooЙ“e Й“en."
  6,145,"Maaku : "Mi tawaani e kon ko wahyinaa e am, ko harminaa e Гұaamoowo mo no Гұaama Й—um, si wanaa nde laatotoo ko maayi (jiibi), maa ЖҙiiЖҙam(puupe) sankotooЙ—am, maa teewu kose (mbaba tuga) -sabu Й—um ko soЙ“e- maa (ko hirsiraa) faasiqiyaagal". Kala on Й“ittiiЙ—o, hara wanaa bewЙ—o, wanaa jaggituЙ—o, haray pellet, Joomi maa ko jaafotooЙ—o, jurmotooЙ—o."
  6,146,"Edow Й“een AlyahuudaaЙ“e (tan) woni ko min karmini kala ko jogii peЙ—aali. Na'i Й—in e dammi Й—in kadi, Men karminii e maЙ“Й“e Й“elle majji Й—en, si wanaa ko Й“abbe majji ronndii, maa tete on, maa ko jillondiri e Жҙi'e. Ko Й—um minn njoЙ“irnoo Й“e berwre maЙ“Й“e nden. Pellet, ko min GoonЕӢЙ—uЙ“e."
  6,147,"Si Й“e njennii ma, maaku : "Joomi mon ko Jom-Yurmeende yaacunde, lepte makko Й—en nduttetaake e yimЙ“e bonЙ“e Й“een"."
  6,148,"Arma sirkuЙ“e Й“een mbi'a : "Sinno Alla Muuyuno, men cirkataano, wanaa baabiraaЙ“e amen Й“en, men karmintaano kadi hay e huunde". Ko non Й“een adinooЙ“e Й“e njeddirnoo haa Й“e meeЙ—i lepte Amen Й—en. Maaku : "Hara ganndal no woodani on njaltinanon amen ngal? Pellet, on jokkaa si wanaa sikke, onon on ngonaani si wanaa fenooЙ“e"."
  6,149,"Maaku : "Ko Alla woodani hujja yottiiЙ—o on.Sinno o muuyuno, O Fewnayno on denndaangal"."
  6,150,"Maaku : "ngaddee seedeeЙ“e mon Й“en, Й“e seedaooЙ“e won de Alla Harminii Й—um Й—oo". Si Й“e ceedike, wata a seedodo e maЙ“Й“e. Wota a jokku mbeleeЙ—e Й“een yedduЙ“e Aayeeje Amen Й—en e Й“en Й“e gooЕӢЙ—inaa laakara, kamЙ“e heЙ“e cirkana Joomi maЙ“Й“e."
  6,151,"Maaku : "ngaree mi janngana on ko Joomi mo Harmini e mon : ko nde kafidoton e Makko huunde, mbaЙ—anon jipnaaЙ“e mon Й“en moЖҙЖҙere. Wata on mbar Й“iЙ—Й“e mon Й“en kulol immorde e baasal. Ko minen Arsikata on e kamЙ“e. Wata on Й“atto pankare Й—en ko feeГұi e majje e ko wirnii. Wata waru woЕӢkii ki Alla Harmini si wanaa e goonga. Ko Й—um mooЙ—on O Wasiyii on ; mbelejo'o, on hakkilat."
  6,152,"Wata on Й“atto jawdi(alyatiim) wonduЙ—o si wanaa hara ko no Й“uri moЖҙЖҙirde, haa o yottoo kellefuyee makko. Timminiree Й“etirЙ—e Й—en e manndikirЙ—e= peesirde Й—en no nuunЙ—iri. Min pawaa woЕӢkii si wanaa ko ki townata. Si on wowlay nuenЙ—ee hay si ko e hoore jom-Й“aЙ—todal. Ahadi Alla ndin hunnon. Ko Й—um mooЙ—on woni ko O Wasiyii on; mbelejo'o, on annditat"
  6,153,""E won de pellet, Й—um Й—oo ko laawol am pocciingol, njokkee ngol ; wata on njokku laawoy senndaykoy on e laawol Makko ngol". Ko Й—um mooЙ—on woni ko O Wasiyii on ; mblejo'o, on ndeentoto."
  6,154,"Refti min ndokki Muusaa deftere nden timmirnde (dokke) mo o moЖҙЖҙiniri, fensitunde kala huunde, ko nde peewal e yurmeende ; mbelejo'o, Й“e ngooЕӢЙ—inay hawroyde e Jommi maЙ“Й“e."
  6,155,"Ndee Й—oo ko deftere (Alqur'aana), min njippiinde ko nde barkinnde - njokkee nde, ndeetoЙ—on ; mbelejo'o, on njurmoyeЙ—on."
  6,156,"Fii wata on mbi'oy : "defte Й—en ko e peЙ—le Й—iЙ—i Jippinaa, adii amen, men laatinoke welsindiiЙ“e janngugol Й—e"."
  6,157,"maa Й—um mb'on : "Sinno minen, deftere ndee Jippinano e amen, min laatotono Й“urЙ“e Й“e feewde". GooЕӢЙ—ii arii on immorde to Joom mon, Й“anngannduyee(peeГұЙ—i), e peewal, e yurmeende. Alaa Й“urЙ—o tooГұde haa hewta on jedduЙ—o Aayeeje Alla Й—ean o Й—uurnii Й—e. Arma Min njoЙ“iroya Й“een Й—uurnotooЙ“e Aayeeje amen Й—een lepte bonЙ—e, sabu ko Й“e laatinoo heЙ“e Й—uurnoo."
  6,158,"Hara Й“ee no habbii si wanaa nde maleykaaji Й—i ngara e maЙ“Й“e? Maa Joomi maa Ara? Maa yoga e Maandeeji Joomi maa ara? Г‘aande yoga e Maandeeji Joomi maa ngari, nafataa woЕӢkii gooЕӢЙ—inal makki, ki laatanooki gooЕӢЙ—inki ko adii, maa ki faggitii e gooЕӢЙ—inal makki moЖҙЖҙere. Maaku : "padee! minen ko min fatndiiЙ“e"."
  6,159,"Pellet, Й“en seennduЙ“e diin muen o, Й“e ngonii fpeЙ—le, a jeyaaka e maЙ“Й“e e huunde : ngandee fiyaaku maЙ“Й“e ko faade ka Alla. Refti o humpita Й“e ko Й“e laatinoo heЙ“e ngolla."
  6,160,"Kala gaЙ—duЙ—o e moЖҙЖҙere hino woodani mo sapdo yeru mayre ; kala kadi gadduЙ—o e bone o yoЙ“itetaake si wanaa yeru makko. KamЙ“e Й“e tooГұetaake."
  6,161,"Maaku : "Min, Joomi am Fewni kam faade e laawol pocciingol, diine ГұiiЙ“uka, diine Ibraahiima, ooГұiiЙ—o [e diineeji meere] ; o jeyanooka e sirkooЙ“e Й“een"."
  6,162,"Maaku : "Pellet, juulde am nden, e kirse am Й—een, e nguurndam am Й—aam, e maayde am ndeen, ko All woodani, JeyЙ—o Winndere ndeen."
  6,163,"KafidiiЙ—o alanaa Mo! Ko Й—um mi yamiraa, ko mi woni arano e jebbiliiЙ“e Й“een"."
  6,164,"Maaku : "E ko wonaa Alla mi Й—aЙ“Й“ata deweteeЙ—o, ko KaЕӢko woni JeyЙ—o kala huunde?! Kala woЕӢkii faggitantaako si wanaa e hoore-makki : woЕӢkii ronndotaako bone woЕӢkii goЙ—ki. Refti ko faade ka Joomi mon woni ruttorde mon, O kumpita on kon ko luutondiraynoЙ—on e mum."
  6,165,"Ko KaЕӢko woni baЙ—Й—Й—o on luutiiЙ“e e leydi, o Й“amtiri yoga mon dow yoga, darjaaji ; fii yo o Jarribo on e ko o okki on. Pellet, Joomi maa ko jaawЙ—o lepte, KaЕӢko kadi, ko o jaafotooЙ—o, jurmotooЙ—o.."
  7,1,"Alif, Laam, Miim, Saad.firo Й—ee alkule wulinoomo efuЙ—Й—oode simoore bakharah(nagge nge)."
  7,2,"ЖҠum de ko deftere Jippinaande e maaЙ—a, wata Й“itteende won e Й“ernde maa e mayre ; fii yo a waajor nde, ko nde waaju wonan de gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“een."
  7,3,"Njokkee ko Jippinaa e mon kon immorde ka Joomi mon, wota on njokku gah Й—uum, weldiiЙ“e, famЙ—ii ko mbaactortoЙ—on."
  7,4,"ЖҠuuЙ—ii e ce'e Й—e min kalki! Lepte Amen Й—en ari e majje jemma hiЙ“e waalii Й—aanii, maa hara ko Й“e fo'ofiiЙ“e Гұalawma."
  7,5,"Noddaandu maЙ“Й“e ndun Й“aawo lepte Amen Й—en arde Й“e, wonaano si naa bi'igol : "Minen min laatino tooГұooЙ“e"."
  7,6,"Wollahi ma min LaЙ“ditoyo Й“een Й“e (Min) Nulnoo e muen, Ma Min LaЙ“nditoyo kadi NulaaЙ“e Й“e."
  7,7,"Ma min pillanoroyo Й“e (golle maЙ“Й“e Й—en) e ganndal. min ngonaano wirniiЙ“e.Й“e (tawtoraaka)"
  7,8,"Manndakke=(pe'esirЙ—i )(Й“etirЙ—i) Г‘ande, ko Й—i goonga. Kala mo manndake (moЖҙЖҙi Й—en) teddi, ko Й“een Й—oon ngoni maloyteeЙ“e Й“en."
  7,9,"Kala mo manndakke (moЖҙЖҙi) mun foygitii=hoyi, ko Й“een Й—oon ngoni sooyinirЙ“e pittaali mu'uen saЙ“u ko Й“e laatinoo heЙ“ee njedda Aayeeje amen Й—een."
  7,10,"Mi wooЙ—niiii minn Newinanii on ke leydi, min mbaЙ—ani on e mayri nguuree. (Kono) famЙ—ii ko njettoton."
  7,11,"Mi wooЙ—ndii min tagii on, refti min mbaadini on, refti min mbi'ani maleykaaji Й—iin : "cujjanee Aadama", Й“e cujji, si wonaa Ibliisa, o jeyanooka e sujjuЙ“e Й“en."
  7,12,"O Daali : "Ko haЙ— maa nde cujjataa nde mi yamir-maa?" owi'i : "miЙ—o Й“uri mo moЖҙЖҙude : A tagii kam immorde e Yiite, A tagii mo immorde e loopal"."
  7,13,"O Daali : "Jippo toon, haananaama nde mawnintintoЙ—aa toon. yaltu, an ko a jeyaaЙ—o e hoyЙ“e Й“een"."
  7,14,"[Ibliisa] wi'i : "NeeЙ“nitanam haa Гұande Й“e immintintee"."
  7,15,"[Alla] Daali : "aan, ko a jeyaaЙ—o e neeЙ“inanteeЙ“e Й“een"."
  7,16,"[Ibliisa] wi'i : "Sabu ko mbewnirЙ—aa kam koo, ma mi jooЙ—ano Й“e ka laawol maa po'ociingol.ngol"
  7,17,"Refti mi ardiranatЙ“e Й“e yeeso maЙ“Й“e e Й“aawo maЙ“Й“e, e ka e Гұaame maЙ“Й“e e ka nane maЙ“Й“e. a tawataa ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e maЙ“Й“e ko yettooЙ“e [Ma]"."
  7,18,"[Alla] Daali : "Yaltu toon, ko a ГұiЕӢaaЙ—o diiwaaЙ—o. Kala jokkuЙ—o ma e maЙ“Й“e, ma Mi kebbiiroye Jahannama onon denndaangal"."
  7,19,""Eeyma yo Aadama, hoЙ— an e Й“eyngu maa ka Aljanna, Гұaamee kala nokku ka njiiЙ—-Й—on ; wota tan on Й“aЙ—to kii Й—oo lekki, sakko laatoЙ—on e tooГұooЙ“e Й“en"."
  7,20,"Seytaane sowinsini Й“e, fii yo o feГұГұinan Й“e ko suuЙ—aa e maЙ“Й“e e awraaji maЙ“Й“e, o wi'i : "Joomi mon haЙ—iraani on ki lekkil si wanaa fii wata on laato maleykaaji maa laatoЙ—on duumotooЙ“e [ka Aljanna]"."
  7,21,"O wooЙ—ndani Й“e o wi'i : "miin komi eЙ“ee laaЙ“anooЙ“e on".deedi"
  7,22,"O hodiri Й“e koomte. Nde Й“e meeЙ—noo elekki he, awraaji maЙ“Й“e Й—iin peeГұani Й“e, Й“e mbaЙ—ti heЙ“e curritora kaaki Aljanna Й—iin. Joomi maЙ“Й“e noddi Й“e : "E Mi haЙ—aano on e ki lekki, Mi wi'ani on : Pellet, seytaane ko gaГұo mon Й“annguЙ—o?!("peeГұЙ—o.)"
  7,23,"ЖҒe mbi'i : "Joomi amen, min tooГұii ko'e amen. Si A yaafaakii amen njurmiЙ—aa amen, ma min njeye e sooyЙ“e Й“een"."
  7,24,"[Alla] Daali : "njippee (ka leydi), yoga mon ko aГұЙ“e yoga. Hino woodani on ka leydi ton ГұiiЙ“irde e dakamme haa saanga"."
  7,25,"[Alla] Daali : "Ko (ka leydi) ton nguuroton, ko ton kadi maayoton, ko e mayri kadi njaltinoyteЙ—on"."
  7,26,"Eehey mon yo Й“iЙ—Й“e Aadam! GooЕӢЙ—ii min njippinii e mo'on comci cuhratЙ—i awraaji mon Й—in e cuЙ—aari. -Ko comci kulol Й—in noon Й“uri muЖҙЖҙude.- Ko Й—uum jeyaaЙ—um e Aayeeje Alla. mbeleejo'o, kamЙ“e Й“e mbaajitoto."
  7,27,"Ko onon yo Й“iЙ—Й“e Aadama! Wata seytaane fitinir on wano o yaltinirnoo baabiraaЙ“e mon Й“en ka Aljanna, homo Й“oora e maЙ“Й“e comci maЙ“Й“e Й—in fii yo hollu Й“e awraaji maЙ“Й“e Й—in. Pellet, homo reeni on kaЕӢko e gorol makko ngol nokku ka on yi'ataa Й“e. minen min mbaЙ—ii seytaaneeji Й—in beldiiЙ—i Й“een Й“en gooЙ—intaa."
  7,28,"Si Й“e mbaЙ—ii paЕӢkare, Й“e mb'a : "min tawru Й—um baabiraaЙ“e amen Й“een, ko Alla yamiri min Й—um". Maaku : "Pellet, Alla yamirtaa paЕӢkare. E on wowlay e hoore Alla ko on nganndaa?!"."
  7,29,"Maaku : "Joomi am yamirii nuunЙ—al. Г‘iiЙ“non jeece mon Й—een nokku kala e ka juuloton, tororon mo laЙ“Й“inangol mo diine kan. Ko wano o FuЙ—Й—ori on non nduЙ—torton"."
  7,30,"Fedde goo o fewnii, fedde goo majjere nden jojji e hoore maЙ“Й“e. KamЙ“e Й“e njogitike seytaaneeji Й—in weldiiЙ“e gaanin Alla, kamЙ“e hiЙ“e cikka ko Й“e feewЙ“e."
  7,31,"Eey mon Й“iЙ—Й“e Aadama, Жҙettee cuЙ—aari mon ndin nokku kala ka njuuloton. Г‘aamee njaron wota on Й“urtin. Pellet, KaЕӢko o yiЙ—aa Й“urtinooЙ“e Й“een."
  7,32,"Maaku : "Ko hommbo harmini cuЙ—aari Alla ndi O Yaltinani jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“een, e laaЙ“uЙ—i Й—in ka arsikeeji?" Maaku : "ЖҠin Й“en gooЕӢЙ—iinЙ“e ka nguurndam aduna woodani, heeraniiЙ—i [Й“e] Г‘ande Darngal". Ko wano non min pirtirta Aayeeje Й—en, wonan de yimЙ“e anndooЙ“e."
  7,33,"Maaku : "Joomi am ko Harmini : ko paaЕӢkare Й—en -ko feeГұi e majje ko suuЙ—ii-, e bakkaat, e bewrugol ko aldaa e goonga, e nde cirkanton Mo kon ko O Jippinanaani Й—uum hujja, e nde wowloton e Alla ko on nganndaa."
  7,34,"Hino woodani kala mofte( leГұol)lajal. Si lajal maЙ“Й“e ngal arii, Й“e neeЙ“titantaake saa'i gooto, Й“e ngardinantaake kadi."
  7,35,"Ehey mon Й“iЙ—Й“e Aadama! Si aroyii e mon NulaaЙ“e jeyaaЙ“e e mo'on, Й“e no fillanoo on Aayeeje Am, kala kulЙ—o [Alla] o moЖҙЖҙini [golle], kulol alanaa Й“en Й—on, wanaa kamЙ“e kadi Й“e cunoytaako."
  7,36,"ЖҒeen yedduЙ“e Aayeeje amen Й—een Й“e townitanii e heЙ—e, ko Й“en ngooni yimЙ“e Yiite, kamЙ“e ko Й“e luttooЙ“e toon."
  7,37,"Alaa Й“urЙ—o tooГұuЙ—o haa hewta on pekindiiЙ—o e Alla fenaande, maa o yeddi Aayeeje Makko Й—en? Й“een keЙ“at Й“e geЙ—al maЙ“Й“e ngal e binndoodi ndin ; haa si NulaaЙ“e amen [warooЙ“e] Й“en ngarii Й“e, Й“e mbara Й“e, Й“e mbia : "Ko hoito kon ko ndewaynoЙ—on gaanin Alla [woni]?!" Й“e mbia : "ЖҠi majjirii amen". ЖҒe ceeditoo e ko'e maЙ“Й“e, won de Й“e laatino yedduЙ“e."
  7,38,"[Maleykaaji] mbi'a : "Naate e moftaaji, gooЕӢЙ—ii yawtii adii mon immorde e jinna e yimЙ“e ka ndeer Yiite". Tuma kala nde leГұol naati, ngol huЙ—a banndu ngol . Haa si Й“e tawtindirii toon Й“e denndaanal, sakkitiiЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“een wi'ana aramЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“een : "Joomi amen! Ko Й“ee majjini min : Okku Й“e lepte cowanЙ—e e Yiite ngen". O Daala : "Hino woodani kala [mon] cowanЙ—e, kono on ganndaa"."
  7,39,"AramЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en mbi'ana sakkitiiЙ“e Й“een : "Alanaa on e dow amen Й“ural, meeЙ—iree lepte Й—en sabu kon ko paggitotonoЙ—on"."
  7,40,"Pellet, Й“een yedduЙ“e Aayeeje amen Й—een, Й“e townitanii Й—e, Й“e udditantaake dame kammuuli Й—in, Й“e naatataa kadi Aljanna haa ngelooba naata e wuddere meselal. Ko wano non Men njoЙ“irto Й“onЙ“e Й“een."
  7,41,"Hino woodani Й“e ka Jahannama ndaЙ—Й—udi, no dow maЙ“Й“e kadi kippoodi. Ko wanon non min njoЙ“irta tooГұooЙ“e Й“een."
  7,42,"ЖҒeen gooЙ—inЙ“e Й“e ngolli moЖҙЖҙuЙ—i - min pawataa woЕӢkii si wanaa ko ki waawi - Ko Й“en Й—on woni yimЙ“e Aljanna : kamЙ“e ko Й“e duumotooЙ“e ton."
  7,43,"Men Й“oori e Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en konnaagu, caatli Й—iin no ila senngo ley maЙ“Й“e, Й“e mbi'a : "jettoorje ngoodani Alla on peewnuЙ—o amen e Й—uum Й—oo, men ngonaano feewooЙ“e si Alla fewnaano amen. GooЕӢЙ—ii NulaaЙ“e Joomi amen Й“een ngaddii goonga". ЖҒe noddee si ko woni : "Oon Й—on mooЙ—on Aljanna, on ndonnaama mo, sabu kon ko ngollatnoЙ—on"."
  7,44,"YimЙ“e Aljanna Й“een noddi yimЙ“e Yiite Й“en, si ko woni : "GooЕӢЙ—ii min tawii ko Joomi amen fodi min kon ko goonga. Onon kadi on tawii ko Joom mon fodi on kon ko goonga?" ЖҒe mbi'i : "Eyyo". Noddoowo nodda hakkunde maЙ“Й“e won de : Kuddi Alla ndin wonii e tooГұooЙ“e Й“een,"
  7,45,"ЖҒeen sakkotooЙ“e=falatoobe gah e laawol Alla ngol, Й“e Й—aЙ“Й“ana ngol ooГұorde, kamЙ“e kadi ko Й“e yedduЙ“e laakara"."
  7,46,"Heedo no hakkunde maЙ“Й“e. Hino e dow tulde La'raafi nden worЙ“e heЙ“e nganndira kala e maande mum ЖҒe nodda yimЙ“e Aljanna Й“een, si ko woni : "Kisial woni e mon!". ЖҒe naataani mo kono heЙ“e tamЖҙinii."
  7,47,"Si jiiЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en pewtiniraa Й“annge yimЙ“e Yiite Й“een, Й“e mbi'a : "Joomi amen! Wata A waЙ—tdu amen e yimЙ“e tooГұooЙ“e Й“een"."
  7,48,"YimЙ“e La'raafi Й“en noddi worЙ“e, hiЙ“e nganndira Й“een maandeeji maЙ“Й“e, Й“e mbia : "Nafaali on mooЙ“ugol mon [jawle], e kon ko laatinoЙ—on hiЙ—on mawnintinoo!"."
  7,49,"E ko Й“ee Й—oo woondirnoЙ—on [won de] Alla memintaa Й“e yurmeende?! Naatee Aljanna! Kulol alanaa on, wanaa onon ngoni ko sunoytooЙ“e."
  7,50,"YimЙ“e Yiite Й“een noddi yimЙ“e Aljanna Й“e, si ko woni : "njuppee e amen ndiyam, maa kon ko Alla arsiki on". ЖҒe mbi'a: "Pellet, Alla harmini Й—in Й—iЙ—i e heeferЙ“e Й“en"
  7,51,"ЖҒeen jogitoriiЙ“e diine mum kan belaaЙ—e e fijindaaru, nguurndam aduna hodi Й“e. hannde min njejjitiray Й“e no Й“e njejjitirnoo hawrugol Г‘alaande maЙ“Й“e ndee, e kon ko Й“e njeddiranoo Aayeeje amen Й—en."
  7,52,"GooЕӢЙ—ii min ngaddanii Й“e deftere, min fpirti nde e dow gaanndal, ko nde peewal e yurmeende Й“en yimЙ“e gooЕӢЙ—inooЙ“e."
  7,53,"Hara heЙ“e kabbii si wanaa battane mum Й—en? Г‘alnde battane (firo) mayre arata, yejjitunooЙ“e Й—um Й“een ko adii wi'ay : "GooЕӢЙ—ii NulaaЙ“e Joomi amen Й“een ngaddii goonga. Hara tefooЙ“e no woodani min Й“e tefana min? Maa min nduttee [aduna] min ngolla ko wanaa ko min ngollaatnoo?" GooЕӢЙ—ii Й“e hayrinii wonkiiji maЙ“Й“e ; kon ko Й“e fekinotonoo majjiriЙ“e."
  7,54,"Pellet, Joomi mon ko Alla, On TakuЙ—o kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin e nder balЙ—e jeegoo, refti O fotondiri ka hoore Arsi. Himo suddira jemma on Гұalawma, hiЙ—i Й—aЙ“Й“indira no yaccorii. Naange ngen e lewru ndun e koode Й—en ko eltiraaЙ—i yamiroore Makko. Paamee ko KaЕӢko heeranii tagoore nde e yamiroore nden. Mawnii mawngu Alla, JeyЙ—o Winndere ndeen."
  7,55,"Noddiiree Joomi mon yaЕӢkinaare e gunndoo. Pellet, KaЕӢko O YiЙ—aa jaggitooЙ“e (Й“enyawtooЙ“e. Keeri)."
  7,56,"Wata on mbonnu ke leydi Й“aawo moЖҙЖҙugol ndi. Noddiree mo kulol e Й—amam'u. Pellet, yurmeende Alla nden no Й“adii moЖҙЖҙimЙ“e Й“en."
  7,57,"Ko KaЕӢko woni Nuloowo keneeli Й—in welo-welo yeeso Yurmeende Makko nden. Haa si ndu ronndike duule teddunde, Men cogga nde e leydi maayndi [yoori], min njippina e mayri ndiyam, min njaltinira Й—am kala dimЙ—e. Ko non min njaltiniroyta maayЙ“e Й“en. mbeleeo'o, on mbaactoto."
  7,58,"Leydi moЖҙЖҙiri ndin, puЙ—i mayri no yaltira duЕӢayee Joomi mayri ; ndin ndi (puЙ—i mum) boni, ndi yaltintaa si wanaa no saЙ—tiri. Ko non min Й“annginirta Aayeeje Й—een woan de yimЙ“e yettooЙ“e [Joomi muen]."
  7,59,"Wollahiii min nulii Nuuhu e yimЙ“e makko Й“en, o maaki : "Ko onon yo yimЙ“e am, ndewee Alla. deweteeЙ—o alanaa on ko woori mo. min miЙ—o hulani on lepte Г‘alaande mawnde"."
  7,60,"HooreeЙ“e mbatu yimЙ“e makko Й“en wi'i : "Minen mЙ—en ma njia e nder majjere Й“anngunde"(.feeГұnde)"
  7,61,"O maaki : "Eey mon yimЙ“e am, majjere (woo) alaa e am ; ko woni min, ko NulaaЙ—o immorde ka JeyЙ—o Winndere nden."
  7,62,"MiЙ—o yottina e mon Nule Joomi am, miЙ—o laaЙ“ana on (reedu), miЙ—o anndi ka Alla ko on nganndaa."
  7,63,"E on kaawa fii waajo no ari on immorde ka Joomi mon e dow gorko jeyaaЙ—o e mo'on?! Fii yo o jertin on e fii yo on ndeento, mbelejo'o, on (keЙ“at) yurmeende [Alla]."
  7,64,"ЖҒe njeddi mo. minn ndaЙ—ndii mo e Й“een won duЙ“e e makko ka laana, min njooli Й“een yedduЙ“e Aayeeje amen Й—een. Pellet, Й“e laatino yimЙ“e wumЙ—uЙ“e."
  7,65,"[min Nulii] kadi fa'ade e AadinkooЙ“e Й“een, musiЙ—Й—o maЙ“Й“e on Huudi. O maaki : "Ko onon yo yimЙ“e am, ndewee Alla, deweteeЙ—o alanaa on ko woori mo. E on kulataa [Mo]?!"."
  7,66,"HooreeЙ“e mbatu Й“en yedduЙ“e e yimЙ“e makko Й“en mbi'i : "minen miЙ—en ma njia'e e Й—ayre, minen miЙ—en cikku maa jeyaaЙ—o e fenooЙ“e Й“een"."
  7,67,"O maaki : "Eey mon yimЙ“e am, Й—ayre (woo) alaa e am ; ko woni min, ko NulaaЙ—o immorde ka JeyЙ—o Winndere ndeen."
  7,68,"MiЙ—o yottina e mo'on Nule Joomi am, min (non) ko mi laaЙ“anoo on (reedu), koolniiЙ—o."
  7,69,"E kaawo fii waajo no ari on immorde ka Joomi mon e dow gorko jeyaaЙ—o e mo'on, fii yo o jeertin on?! ciftoree tuma nde O waЙ—noo on lomtiiЙ“e Й“aawo yimЙ“e Nuuhu Й“en, O Й“eydi on ka tagoore semmbe. ciftoree dokke Alla Й—e mbelejo'o, on malete."
  7,70,"ЖҒe mbi'i : "E a ar e amen fii yo min ndew Alla tan, min ngacca kon ko baabiraaЙ“e amen Й“een ndewatnoo?! Awa addan amen ko podanЙ—aa men kon (e lepte) si tawii ko a jeyaaЙ—o e gooЕӢnuЙ“e Й“een."
  7,71,"O maaki : "GooЕӢЙ—ii yanii e mon immorde ka Joomi mon soЙ“e (lepte) e tikkere. E on mbeeГұdat e am fii inЙ—e Й—e innuЙ—on onon e baabiraaЙ“e mo'on, Alla Jippinaali fii majje hujja?! padee! min, won dude e mo'on, ko mi jeyaaЙ—o e fatЙ“e Й“en"."
  7,72,"Min ndaЙ—niri mo e Й“een won duЙ“e e makko yurmeende amen, men taЖҙi Й“abbe Й“een yedduЙ“e Aayeeje amen Й—een, Й“e laatanooki gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e."
  7,73,"[Men Nulii] kadi faade e Samuuda'en, musiЙ—Й—o maЙ“Й“e on Saalihu, o maaki : "Eehey mon yimЙ“e am, ndewee Alla. deweteeЙ—o alanaa on ko woori mo. GooЕӢЙ—ii arii on Й“anngannduyee immorde ka Joomi mon : mbaa ko ngeelooba Alla ma'ande wonan de on, tertee mba Гұaama ka leydi Alla, wata on memir ba bone sakko lepte muusuЙ—e nannga on"."
  7,74,"Ciftoree tuma nde o waЙ—noo on lomtiiЙ“e AadinkooЙ“e Й“een, o weernii on ka leydi hoЙ—on njogitoo e ndantaaji mayri kuЙ“eeje, hoЙ—on lesa pelle (waЙ—on) cuuЙ—i. Ciftoree dokke Alla Й—een, wota on Й“urtinir ka leydi ko on bonnooЙ“e."
  7,75,"HooreeЙ“e mbatu mawninkiniiЙ“e Й“een e yimЙ“e makko Й“een mbi'ani gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e lo'inaaЙ“e Й“en e maЙ“Й“e : "E hoЙ—on nganndi won de Saalihu ko NulaaЙ—o immorde ka Joomi makko?" ЖҒe mbi'i : minen ko men gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e ko o Nulidaa e mum koon"."
  7,76,"ЖҒen mawnintiniiЙ“e wi'i : "Minen, kon ko ngooЕӢЙ—inЙ—on, ko men yedduЙ“e Й—um"."
  7,77,"ЖҒe mborii ngeelooba ban, Й“e mawninkini gah e yamiroore Joomi maЙ“Й“e ndeen, Й“e mbi'i : "Ko an yo Saalihu, addan amen kon ko podannaЙ—aa amen (e lepte) si tawii ko a jeyaaЙ—o e NulaaЙ“e Й“een"."
  7,78,"Dillaango ngon nanngi Й“e, Й“e mbaЙ—tini ka koЙ—ooli maЙ“Й“e ko Й“e jicciiЙ“e-Й—aanii(.jusЙ“e)"
  7,79,"O ruЕӢtii Й“e o maaki : "eey mon yo yimЙ“e am, gooЕӢЙ—ii mi yottinii e mon Nulal Joomi am ngal mi laaЙ“anii on (reedu), konon, on njiЙ—aa laaЙ“ooЙ“e (reedu) Й“een."
  7,80,"E luuti, tuma nde o maakannoo yimЙ“e makko Й“en : " E o ngaray e paЕӢkare Й—e goЙ—Й—o goo adaaki on e mun e Winndere ndeen?!"
  7,81,"Onon hoЙ—on njottoo e worЙ“e Й“een tuuyo ngaccon rewЙ“e Й“een! Si ko woni, onon ko on yimЙ“e fantimЙ“e(.Й“urtinЙ“e)."
  7,82,"Jaabawol yimЙ“e makko e Й“ee wonaano si wanaa ko Й“e mbi'i : "njaaltinee Й“e ka hoЙ—ordemon ; kamЙ“e ko Й“e yimЙ“e laЙ“Й“intintooЙ“e"."
  7,83,"Min daЙ—ndi mo kaЕӢko e yimЙ“e makko Й“een, si wonaa debbo makko on ; onЙ—on heddodino e (leptaaЙ“e) Й“een."
  7,84,"Min saaЖҙini toЙ“o e maЙ“Й“e. Ndaarii ko holno battane bonЙ“e Й“eЙ—n laatornoo?"
  7,85,"[Men Nulii] kadi faade e Madyana, musiЙ—Й—o maЙ“Й“e on Su'aybu, o maaki : "eehey mon yimЙ“e am, ndewee Alla. deweteeЙ—o alanaa on ko woori mo. GooЕӢЙ—ii Й“anngannduyee arii on immorde ka Joomi mon. Timminee Й“etirЙ—e Й—iin e manndikke Й—een, wata on ustan yimЙ“e Й“een piiji maЙ“Й“e Й—iin, wota on mbonnu ko leydi Й“aawo moЖҙЖҙugol ndi. Ko Й—uum mooЙ—on Й“uri on moЖҙЖҙannde si on laatike gooЕӢЙ—iinЙ“e"."
  7,86,"Wata on njooЙ—o e kala laawol, hoЙ—on kammba, hoЙ—on sakko=paddooo e laawol Alla ngol Й“een gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Mo, hoЙ—on Й—aЙ“Й“ana ngol ooГұaare. ngannditee tuma nde ngonndoЙ—on seeЙ—aaЙ“e o Й—uЙ—Й—ini on. Ndaaree holno battane bonnooЙ“e Й“e laatornoo."
  7,87,"Si wonii fedde e mooЙ—on gooЕӢЙ—inii kon ko Nuliraa e mun, fedde goo gooЕӢЙ—inaani, muГұГұee haa Alla Гұaawa hakkunde me'n. Ko KaЕӢko Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude e ГұaawooЙ“e Й“een."
  7,88,"Mbatu mawnintiniingu e yimЙ“e makko Й“en mbi'i : "Ko maa men yaltine an Su'aybu, e Й“een gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e won dude e maaЙ—a ka saare amen, maa nduttoЙ—on e diina amen". -o maaki : "Hay si tawii ko men aГұuЙ“e [Й—uum]?"."
  7,89,"GooЙ—ii (haray) min pekifindike e hoore Alla fenaande si men nduttike e diina mon Й“aawo nde Alla daЙ—ndi men e makka. Alanaa min ndee men rnduttoo e makka si wanaa nde Alla Joomi amen muuyi. Joomi amen yaajanii kala huunde ganndal. Ko e Alla en pawii. Joomi amen, Гұaawir hakkunde amen e yimЙ“e amen Й“en goonga, ko An woni Й“urЙ—o moЖҙЖҙude e ГұaawooЙ“e Й“een"."
  7,90,"Mbatu Й“en yedduЙ“e e yimЙ“e makko Й“een mb'i : "Pellet, si on njokkii Su'aybu, onon ontuma ko on hayruЙ“e".(pertuЙ“e)"
  7,91,"Dillaango ngoon nanngi Й“e, Й“e waЙ—tini ka koЙ—ooli maЙ“Й“e ko Й“e jicciiЙ“e-Й—aanii."
  7,92,"ЖҒeen yeddnnunooЙ“e Su'aybu, (Й“e kalkorino) wa si Й“e meeЙ—aa wuurude e ngon [hoЙ—o]. ЖҒeen yeddunooЙ“e Su'aybu, Й“e laatino kamЙ“e woni hayruЙ“e Й“en."
  7,93,"O Й—uurni Й“e, o maaki : "eey mon yimЙ“e am, gooЕӢЙ—ii mi njottinii e mo'on Nule Joomi am Й—een mi laaЙ“anii on (reedu). E ko hoolno mi surnortoo e yimЙ“e yedduЙ“e?!"."
  7,94,"Men nulaali e saare hay e Annbaajo, si wanaa minn nanngirii yimЙ“e mayre Й“een saЙ—teende e lorra mbelejo'o, Й“e yankinoto."
  7,95,"Refti min mbaЙ—titiri nokku bone on moЖҙЖҙere, haa Й“e Й—uuЙ—i, Й“e mbi'i : "GooЕӢЙ—ii saЙ—tteende e neweende heЙ“iino baabiraaЙ“e amen Й“een". min nanngiri Й“e e juhal, tawi kamЙ“e Й“e so'aa anndude.(tinaana)."
  7,96,"Sinno yimЙ“e ce'e Й“een ngooЕӢЙ—inno Й“e kuli (Joomi maЙ“Й“e), min udditanayno Й“e moЖҙЖҙereeji immorde ka Kammu e ka leydi. Kono Й“e njedd, min nanngitiri Й“e (lepte Й—een) kon ko Й“e paggittoonoo."
  7,97,"Hara yimЙ“e ce'e Й“ene kooli nde lepte amen Й—en ngarataa Й“e jemma, hara heЙ“e Й—aanii?"
  7,98,"Kaa hara yimЙ“e ce'e Й“een kooli nde lepte amen Й—en ngarataa Й“e ka mbeeto, hara hiЙ“e pija?"
  7,99,"E Й“e kooli pewje Alla Й—een? Hoolotaako pewje Alla Й—een si wanaa yimЙ“e hayruЙ“e Й“een."
  7,100,"E Й“annganaali Й“een ronooЙ“e leydi Й“een Й“aawo (halkagol) yimЙ“e mayri Й“een, won de si min muuyuno min meminirayno Й“e [lepte Й—en] bakkatuji maЙ“Й“e Й—in? min tappa e Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—een hara kamЙ“e Й“e nanataa."
  7,101,"ЖҠeen ce'e, miЙ—en fillano maa kumpite majje. GooЕӢЙ—ii nulaaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en ngaddanii Й“e Й“anngannduyeeji, Й“e ngonaano gooЕӢЙ—inooЙ“e ko Й“e njeddi kon ko adii. Ko wano nii All notirta e Й“erЙ—e heeferЙ“e Й“een."
  7,102,"min tawaano ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e maЙ“Й“e huuЙ“ooЙ“e ahadi ; si ko men tawi, ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e maЙ“Й“e ko yaltuЙ“e. Й—oftaare"
  7,103,"Refti minn Nulidi Й“aawo maЙ“Й“e Muusaa e Maandeeji amen Й—in haa e Fir'awna e mbatu mu'um, Й“e yeddi Й—i. Ndaaru ko honno battane bonnooЙ“e Й“een laatornoo."
  7,104,"Muusaa maaki : "eeheyma Fir'awna, miin komi nulaaЙ—o immorde ka JeyЙ—o winndere ndeen"
  7,105,"No haand i e am nde mi wowlataa e Alla si wanaa goonga. GooЕӢЙ—ii mi addanii on Й“anngannduyee immorde ka Joomi mon. neldu e Й“iЙ—Й“e Israa'iila Й“en."
  7,106,"[Fir'awna] wi'i : "Si tawii a ardii e maande, addu nde si tawii ko a jeyaaЙ—o e gooЕӢЙ—uuЙ“e Й“een"."
  7,107,"O wernii weduru makko ndun, jaka ko ndu mbooЙ—di=ngoolwa Й“anngundi."
  7,108,"O yaltini junngo makko ngon, jaka yoo ko ngo ranwungo wonannde ndaarooЙ“e Й“en."
  7,109,"Mbatu yimЙ“e Fir'awna Й“en mbi'i : "Pellet, oo, ko mbileejo gannduЙ—o"."
  7,110,""O faala yaltinnde on ka leydi mo'on". -"Ko holЙ—um njamirton?""
  7,111,"ЖҒe mbi'i : "NeeЙ“nu mo e musiЙ—Й—o makko on, nulaa e ce'e Й—een mooЙ“ooЙ“e (mbile)".wileeЙ“e"
  7,112,"ЖҒe ngadane kala mbileejo gannduЙ—o."
  7,113,"wileeЙ“e Й“een ari Fir'awna Й“e mbi'i : "Hara njoЙ“di no woodani min, si min ngonii foolЙ“e Й“een?""
  7,114,"O wi'i : "Eyyo, haray on jeyaama e Й“aЙ—tinaaЙ“e Й“een"."
  7,115,"ЖҒe mbi'i : "eehe yma Muusaa, si Й—a yiЙ—i ko nde bugotoЙ—aa, maa men wona (adotooЙ“e) bugagol".(beddagol)"
  7,116,"O maaki : "Bugee(mbedde)". Nde Й“e bugii, (mbeddi )Й“e mbilЙ—ii gite yimЙ“e Й“een, Й“e kulЙ“ini Й“e, Й“e ngddi mbilewu mawnungu."
  7,117,"minn mbahyini e Muusaa won de : "Bugo tuggordu maa ndun weduru". Jaka yoo hindi moЙ—a ko Й“e pepekindotonoo."
  7,118,"Goonga on feeГұi, ko Й“e ngollaynoo kon [fof] boni."
  7,119,"ЖҒe poolaa Й—oon Й“e kooti ko Й“e ja'asuЙ“e."
  7,120,"WileeЙ“e Й“een nduuyi cujji."
  7,121,"ЖҒe mbi'i : "min ngooЕӢЙ—inii JeyЙ—o winndere ndeen,"
  7,122,"Joomum Muusaa e Haaruuna"."
  7,123,"Fir'awna wi'i : "On ngooЕӢЙ—ini mo adii mi mi yamirde= sakkitoore on? Pellet, Й—uum Й—oo ko fewjoore nde pewjuЙ—on ka saare fii no njaltiniron toon yimЙ“e mayre. ma on nganndu."
  7,124,"Ma mi taЖҙa juuЙ—e mon Й—en e koyЙ—e mon Й—een (mi) luutindira, refti ma mi feta on denndaangal"."
  7,125,"ЖҒe mbi'i : "minen, ko faade ka Joomi amen woni ruttorde amen."
  7,126,"A aГұiraani min si wanaa fii min ngooЕӢЙ—inii maandeeji Joomi amen, tuma nde Й—i ngarunoo amen. Joomi amen! Yuppu muГұal e amen, Жҙettitaa min ko min jebbilii Й“e.(juulЙ“e)"
  7,127,"Mbatu yimЙ“e Fir'awna ngun mbi'i : "A accat Muusaa e yimЙ“e mum Й“een no bonnira ka leydi, o acce an e deweteeЙ—i maa Й—in?!" o wi'i : "ma min mbar Й“iЙ—Й“e maЙ“Й“e worЙ“e Й“een men ngaccita Й“iЙ—Й“e maЙ“Й“e rewЙ“e Й“een (nguura). Pellet, minen, e dow maЙ“Й“e ko min foolooЙ“e"."
  7,128,"Muusaa maakani yimЙ“e makko Й“een : "mballinoree Alla muГұГұoЙ—on. Pellet, leydi ndin ka Alla woodani, Himo ronina ndi on mo o muuyi e jeyaaЙ“e makko Й“een. battane moЖҙЖҙe Й—een ko gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“een woodani"."
  7,129,"ЖҒe mbi'i : "min lorranooma adii a arde amen e Й“aawo nde ngarЙ—aa e amen". O maaki : "Hino jortaa nde Joomi mon halkata gaГұo mon O lomtina on ka leydi, O ndaara ko holno ngollirton"."
  7,130,"GooЕӢЙ—ii min nanngirii yimЙ“e Fir'awna Й“e kokke e usytagol Й“esnooje ; mbelejo'o, Й“e mbaajitoto."
  7,131,"Si moЖҙЖҙere nden arii Й“e, Й“e mbi'a : "miЙ—en kaan di e ndee Й—oo" ; si bone on heЙ“ii Й“e, Й“e kiitinora Muusaa e won duЙ“e e makko Й“een. nganndee pellet, kiiti maЙ“Й“e Й—in ko ka Alla iwri, kono ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e yimЙ“e Й“en nganndaa."
  7,132,"ЖҒe mbi'i : "Kala ko ngaaddan Й—aa min e kaawis fii no mbilЙ—oraa min Й—uum ; min wonaani gooЕӢЙ—inooЙ“e ma"."
  7,133,"Min ngurti e maЙ“Й“e waame, e kanu, e karan=tendi, e totiiji=paabi, e ЖҙiiЖҙam, ko kaawisaaji pensitaaЙ—i, Й“e mawnintinii, Й“e laatii yimЙ“e bon Й“e."
  7,134,"Tuma nde lepte Й—een njannoo e maЙ“Й“e, Й“e mbi'i : "ko an Muusaa, torano amen Joomi maa sabu kon ko O ahodi e maaЙ—a. Si a huncanii amen Й—ee lepte, ma men ngooЕӢЙ—ine, ma min accide kadi e Й“iЙ—Й“e Israa'iila Й“een"."
  7,135,"Nde min kuЕӢcannoo Й“e lepte Й—een haa e lajal ngal Й“e njottotoo, jaka yoo kamЙ“e ko Й“e firtooЙ“e (ahadi maЙ“Й“e ndin)."
  7,136,"Min njottii e maЙ“Й“e ; minn njooliri Й“e ka maayo sabu ko Й“e njeddiri kon kaawisaaji amen Й—iin, Й“e laatii welsindiiЙ“e e majje."
  7,137,"minn ndonnni yimЙ“e wonnooЙ“e e lo'ineede Й“een fuЙ—naange leydi ndin e hiirnaange mayri ndi min mbarkini e mu'um. Konngol Joomi maa moЖҙЖҙongol ngol timmii e Й“iЙ—Й“e Israa'iila Й“een sabu ko Й“e muГұГұinoo kon. min kalki ko Fir'awna e yimЙ“e mum Й“een moЖҙЖҙinanynoo, e kon ko Й“e Й“amtaynoo (e kuЙ“eeje)."
  7,138,"Min lummbini Й“iЙ—Й“e Israa'iila Й“en maayo ngon, Й“e ndewi e yimЙ“e ГұiiЙ“uЙ“e (e dewugol) sanamuuji mu'un, Й“e mbi : "ehey Muusaa, waЙ—an amen deweteeЙ—o wano deweteeЙ—i woodirani Й“e non". O maaki : "Pellet, onon ko on yimЙ“e majjooЙ“e"."
  7,139,"Pellet, Й“ee Й—oo, ko Й“e ngoni e mum kon ko kalkaaЙ—um, kadi ko mehre woni ko Й“e ngollatnoo."
  7,140,"E ko ko woori Alla mi Й—aЙ“Й“anta on deweteeЙ—o, KaЕӢko O Й“urnii on e winndere ndeen?!"."
  7,141,"(ciftoree) tuma nde minn ndaЙ—ndunoo on e yimЙ“e Fir'awna Й“een, heЙ“e meeЙ—na on lepte bon Й—e : Й“e mbara Й“iЙ—Й“e mon worЙ“e Й“e kedda rewЙ“e mon Й“een. No e Й—uum mooЙ—on jarrabuyee mawЙ—o immorde ka Joomi mon."
  7,142,"Min haldidi e Muusaa jemmaaji cappanЙ—i tati, Min timminiri Й—i sappo, happu Joomi makko on timmiri jemmaaji cappanЙ—e nayi. Muusaa maakani musiЙ—Й—o makko Haaruuna : "Lomtom ka yimЙ“e am, moЖҙЖҙinaa (fiyaake maЙ“Й“e), wata a jokku laawol bonnooЙ“e Й“een"."
  7,143,"Nde Muusaa arunoo fii happu amen on Joomi makko yeewti mo, o maaki : "Joomi, hollam mi ndaare!" O Daali : "A yi'ataa kam ; kono ndaar fello ngon : si ngo ГұiiЙ“ii e nokku maggo, aray ka yi'at kam". Nde Joomi makko feeГұannoo fello ngon, O waЙ—ti ngo Й—iggu ngo, Muusaa yani faЙ—Й—aa. Nde o Й—igtunoo, o maaki : "Senaare woodani Ma! mi tuubanii ma, min ko mi arano e gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“een"."
  7,144,"O Daali : "Eehey ma Muusaa, min mi suЙ“ii ma e yimЙ“e Й“een Nule mm Й—een e konngol am ngol. Jogito ko mi jonnu maa kon njeyeeЙ—aa e yettooЙ“e Й“een"."
  7,145,"Min mbnndani mo ka alluuje kala huunde, waaju e fensitannde kala huunde. Jogitor nde doole, njamiraa yimЙ“e maa Й“e jogitagol ko Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude e mayre. Arma mi holla on galle yaltuЙ“e Й—oftaare Й“e"
  7,146,"Mi firto ga e Aayeeje Am Й—e Й“een mawnintinorayЙ“e ka leydi ko aldaa e goonga. hay si Й“e nji'i kala kaawis Й“e ngooЕӢЙ—intaa mo, si Й“e nji'ii laawol peewal ngol Й“e njogitotaako ngol laawol, si Й“e nji'ii laawol bewre ngol Й“e njogitoo ngol laawol. ЖҠuum noon, ko tawde Й“e njeddii kaawniinde amen Й—e, Й“e ngoni welsindiiЙ“e e majje."
  7,147,"ЖҒeen yedduЙ“e kaawniiЙ—e amen Й—en e kawraangal e laakara, golle maЙ“Й“e Й—e mbonii. Hara Й“een njoЙ“oyte si wanaa kon ko Й“e ngollaynoo?"
  7,148,"YimЙ“e Muusa Й“een njogitii Й“aawo makko cuЙ—aari maЙ“Й“e ndin ngaari Й“anndinnke, hindi mari nuunaango=kuunaali. E Й“e nji'aani won de ndi yewtidataa e maЙ“Й“e ndi fewntanaa Й“e kadi e laawol? ЖҒe njogitike ndii [ngaari reweteendi], Й“e laatii tooГұooЙ“e."
  7,149,"Nde yantunoo e juuЙ—e maЙ“Й“e, Й“e nji'i won de gooЕӢЙ—ii Й“e majjii, Й“e mb'i : "Si Joomi amen yurmaaka amen, o yaafi men, pellet, min laatoday e hayruЙ“e Й“en".(pertuЙ“e)"
  7,150,"Nde Muusaa ruttinoo e yimЙ“e makko Й“en ko o tikkuЙ—o, cuniiЙ—o, o maaki : "Bonii kon ko lomtiЙ—on kam Й“aawo am. E on keГұor yamiroore Joomi mon nde?!" O weddii alluuje Й—een o nanngi hoore (musiЙ—Й—o) neene-gooto makko on himo fooЙ—a mo e makko. [Haaruuna] Maaki : "Ko an yo Й“iЙ—Й—o neene am, Й“ee yimЙ“e lo'inii kam, Й“e Й—eЙ“i'i warde kam. Wota a weltin aГұЙ“e am, wata a waЙ—tidam kadi e yimЙ“e toonoЙ“e Й“e"."
  7,151,"O maaki : "Joomi am, yaafom min e (musiЙ—Й—o)neene-gooto am on, naataa min ka yurmeende aa. Ko an woni Й“urЙ—o yurmeede e yurmeteeЙ“e Й“en"."
  7,152,"Pellet, Й“een jogitii Й“e ngaari ndi (reweteendi), arma tikkere heЙ“a Й“e immorde e Joomi maЙ“Й“e, e koyeera ka nguurndam aduna. Ko wano non min njoЙ“irta fekintooЙ“e Й“een."
  7,153,"ЖҒeen golluЙ“e boneeji, refti Й“e tuubi Й“aawo Й—uum Й“e ngooЕӢЙ—ini, pellet, Joomi maa, Й“aawo Й—um, ko jafotooЙ—o, jurmotooЙ—o."
  7,154,"Nde tikkere nden deeЖҙunoo e Muusaa, o Жҙetti alluuje Й—en. Tawi no e binndoodi majje, peewal e yurmeende wonan de Й“een hulooЙ“e Joomi muen."
  7,155,"Muusaa suЙ“ii e yimЙ“e makko Й“en worЙ“e cappanЙ—e njeeЙ—iЙ—o fii happu amen. Nde dillaango ngon nanngunoo Й“e, o maaki : "Joomi, si a muuyuno, A halkayno Й“e adii hannde, e min kadi. E A halkiray men ko Й—aayЙ“e amen Й“en ngollii? ЖҠum wonaani si wanaa jarrabuyee maaЙ—a, HaЙ—a majjinira Й—um on mo muuyu-Й—aa, HaЙ—a feewna on mo muuyu-Й—aa. Ko aan woni keeto amen, hafran amen njurme-Й—aa amen. Ko aan woni Й“urЙ—o moЖҙЖҙude e yaafooЙ“e Й“e"."
  7,156,"Winndan amen ka aduna Й—oo moЖҙЖҙere, e ka laakara. minen min tuubanii ma. O Daali : "Lepte am Й—e, mi meminay Й—e on mo mi muuyi. Yurmeende am nden yaajanii kala huunde. arma mi winndana nde Й“en hulooЙ“e (Alla), Й“e totta zakka, e Й“en ngooЕӢЙ—inooЙ“e Aayeeje amen Й—e"."
  7,157,"ЖҒeen jokkatЙ“e nulaaЙ—o on, annabaajo humammbinneejo, on mo Й“e tawta fii mum no winndaa ka maЙ“Й“e ka Tawreeta e ka Linnjiila. Homo yamira Й“e moЖҙЖҙere, o haЙ—a Й“e ЕӢiГұere, homo daginana Й“e dagiiЙ—i Й—i, o harminana Й“e coЙ“Й—i Й—in, o ittana Й“e teddeelo e kolommbooje=tonngi wonunooЙ—e e hoore-maЙ“Й“e. ЖҒen gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e mo, Й“e teddini mo, Й“e walli mo, Й“e njokki annoore JippinaaЙ—o won dude e makko ; Й“en, ko kamЙ“e woni malaaЙ“e Й“een."
  7,158,"Maaku : "Eey mon yimЙ“e, min ko mi NulaaЙ—o Alla e mooЙ—on on denndaangal, on mo woodani Й—um laamu kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin. deweteeЙ—o alaa si wanaa kaЕӢko. Homo wuurna wara. ngooЕӢЙ—inee Alla e nulaaЙ—o makko annabaajo humammbinneejo on, on ngooЕӢЙ—inЙ—o Alla e KonnguЙ—i makko Й—in. njokkee mo, mbelejo'o, on peeway"."
  7,159,"Hino e yimЙ“e Muusaa Й“een, mofte (leГұol)fewnirayЙ—e (yimЙ“e Й“en) e goonga, ko Й—uum ngoni ko Й“e nuunЙ—iraa."
  7,160,"Min ceerndi Й“e gori sappo e Й—iЙ—i (lenol). min wahyini e Muusaa tuma nde yimЙ“e makko Й“een Й—aЙ“Й“irnoo mo yarnineede won de : "fiyir tuggordu maa ndun haaЖҙre nden". Й“ulli sappo e Й—iЙ—i yallti e mayre. GooЕӢЙ—ii gorol kala andii yarirde mu'm. min Й—owdinirani Й“e duule, min Jippini e maЙ“Й“e demmbe-njuuri, e teewu colli. "Г‘aamee e laaЙ“uЙ—i Й—i min arsiki on". ЖҒe tooГұaani min, kono ko woЕӢkiiji maЙ“Й“e Й“e tooГұatnoo."
  7,161,"Tuma nde Й“e mbi'anaa : "koЙ—ee e ndee saare, Гұaamon e mayre nokku kala ka njiЙ—uЙ—on, mbion : Й“oran amen [goopi amen], naatiron ka damal ko on sujjuЙ“e, minn njaafoto on goopi mon. Arma min Й“eydana moЖҙЖҙimЙ“e Й“een"."
  7,162,"TooГұuЙ“e Й“en e maЙ“Й“e mbayliri konngol ngol ko wanaa ngol ngol Й“e mbiananoo. min njippini e maЙ“Й“e lepte immorde ka kammu, sabu ko Й“e laatinoo heЙ“e tooГұa."
  7,163,"Naamno Й“e fii saare wonunoonde nden ka sera maayo, tuma nde Й“e jaggitaynoo e Aseweere nden, tuma nde liЖҙЖҙi maЙ“Й“e Й—in ngraynooЙ“e Гұalnde Aseweere maЙ“Й“e nden ko Й—i kuywuЙ—i, Гұalnde woni wanaa aseweere maЙ“Й“e Й—i ngrataa Й“e. Ko wano nii min jarriborta Й“e kon ko Й“e njaltatnooko Й—oftaare"
  7,164,"Tuma nde dentaal jeyaaЙ—o e maЙ“Й“e wi'noo : "Ko holЙ—um mbaajoantoЙ—on yimЙ“e, Allaahu ko kalkoowo Й“e maa O lepta Й“e lepte sattuЙ—e?" Й“e mbi'i : "Ko [ittugol] ngantu faade ka Joomi mo'on ; e belejo'o, kamЙ“e Й“e ndentoto"."
  7,165,"Nde Й“e njejjitunoo ko Й“e mbaajanoo fii mum kon, minn ndaЙ—ndi Й“een haЙ—aynooЙ“e e bone on, minn nanngiri Й“een tooГұuЙ“e lepte sattuЙ—e sabu ko Й“e njalatnooko.e Й—oftaare."
  7,166,"Nde Й“e townitaninoo e ko Й“e kaЙ—aa e mum kon, min mbi'ani Й“e : "Laatee baaЙ—i jaasuЙ—i"."
  7,167,"siftor tuma nde Joomi maa anndinnoo (won de) ma o nulu e maЙ“Й“e haa Г‘alnde Darngal on meeЙ—inoowo Й“e lepte bon Й—e. Pellet, Joomi maa ko jaawuЙ—e lepte, pellet kadi, ko O jaafotooЙ—oo, jurmotooЙ—o."
  7,168,"Men senndiri Й“e ka leydi dente : hino e maЙ“Й“e moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e, hino e maЙ“Й“e ko jaasi Й—um. min njarribori Й“e moЖҙЖҙuЙ—i e boЙ—Й—i, mbelejo'o, kamЙ“e Й“e nduttoto."
  7,169,"Lomtii Й“aawo maЙ“Й“e lomtii Й“e (bonЙ“e), Й“e roni deftere nden, hiЙ“e Жҙetta weeЙ“itanЙ—e oo aduna Й“e mbi'a : "Aray min njaaffee". Si weeЙ“itannde sugu mum arii e maЙ“Й“e, Й“e Жҙetta Й—um.hara ahadi deftere nden Жҙettidaaka e maЙ“Й“e, won de wata Й“e wowlu e Alla si wanaa goonga?! Й“e janngi ko woni e mayre. Ko galle laakara Й—en Й“uri moЖҙЖҙannde Й“en rentiiЙ“e. E on kakkiltaa?!"
  7,170,"ЖҒeen jogitotooЙ“e deftere nden Й“e ГұiiЙ“na juulde, pellet, mien min yeebataa njoЙ“di moЖҙЖҙinooЙ“e Й“een."
  7,171,"Siftor tuma nde min Й“orunoo fello ngon senngo dow maЙ“Й“e, a sikkat ko ngo Й—owdi.Й“e pelliti ngo yanat e maЙ“Й“e. "njogitoree ko min ngokki on kon doole, jaЕӢtee ko woni e mayre, mbelejo'o, on kulon Alla"."
  7,172,"siftoro kadi nde Joomi maa Жҙettunoo e Й“iЙ—Й“e Aadama Й“en ka keeci maЙ“Й“e jurriiyaaji maЙ“Й“e Й—in, O seendintini Й“e e woЕӢkiiji maЙ“Й“e Й—in : "Wanaa kon min woni Joomi mon?" Й“e mb'i : "Ko non woniri, min seedike". Ko fii (wata) on mb'oy Г‘ande Darngal : "minn min ngoniino welsindiiЙ“e e Й—uum Й—oo"."
  7,173,"Maa mbi'oyon : "woni ko baabiraaЙ“e amen Й“e cirkunoo ko adii, min wonti (tun) jurriiya Й“aawo maЙ“Й“e. E A halkiray men ko bonnooЙ“e Й“en mbaЙ—i?"
  7,174,"Ko wano nii min fensitirta Aayeeje Й—een, e mbeleo'o kamЙ“e Й“e nduttoto."
  7,175,"Janngan Й“e kumpite on mo min ngokkuno Aayeeje amen Й—en, o Й“oorii Й—e, seytaane jokki mo, e laatodii e majjuЙ“e Й“en(.bewЙ“eЙ“e)"
  7,176,"Sinno min muuyuno, min Й“amtirayno mo Й—e, ko woni tun o heddike ka leydi o jokki belaaЙ—e makko. yeru makko ko sifa rawaandu, si a ronndii ndu ndu lahay, maa si a terti ndu du lahay. Ko Й—uum woni misal yimЙ“e yedduЙ“e Aayeeje amen Й—een. Fillo qissaaji Й—in ; mbelejo'o, Й“e miijitoto."
  7,177,"[Alaa ko Й“uri] bon de misal Й“een yimЙ“e yedduЙ“e Aayeeje amen Й—en, ko woЕӢkiiji maЙ“Й“e woni ko Й“e tooГұaynoo."
  7,178,"Kala mo Alla feewni, ko on feewata ; kala kadi mo O majjini, ko Й“een hayruЙ“e Й“een."
  7,179,"GooЕӢЙ—ii min taganii Jahannama ko Й—uuЙ—i e jinna e yimЙ“e. HeЙ“e mari Й“erЙ—e, Й“e faamirtaa Й—e. HiЙ“e mari gite, Й“e njiirtaa Й—e. HiЙ“e mari noppi, Й“e nanirtaa Й—i. Й“een no mb'i wa neemoraaЙ—i, toode ko kamЙ“e Й“uri majjude. Ko Й“een ngoni welsindiiЙ“e Й“en."
  7,180,"Ko Alla woodani inЙ—e Й“urЙ—e moЖҙЖҙude Й—en. Noddiree Mo Й—e, tertoЙ—on Й“en ooГұotooЙ“e ka inЙ—e makko : arma Й“e njoЙ“oyee ko Й“e ngollaynoo."
  7,181,"Hino e Й“en Й“e Men tagi, mofte (leЖҙЖҙi)feewirayЙ—e goonga, ko Й—um kadi Й“e nuunЙ—irta."
  7,182,"ЖҒeen yedduЙ“e Aayeeje amen Й—en, min suyniray Й“e e nokku ka Й“e anganndaa."
  7,183,"MiЙ—o neeЙ“nana Й“e, pellet, pewje Am Й—en ko tiiЙ—uЙ—e."
  7,184,"E Й“ee miijitaaki? gonndiijo maЙ“Й“e on aldaa e jinna : on wonaani si wanaa jeertinoowo Й“annguЙ—o.(peeГұЙ—o)"
  7,185,"E Й“e ndaaraani laamuuji kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin, e ko Alla tagi e piiji, e haawnaaki hara lajal maЙ“Й“e ngal Й“adike? E ko yewtere honnde Й“aawo ndee Й—oo Й“e ngooЕӢЙ—inta?!"
  7,186,"Kala mo Alla majjini, peewnoowo mo alaa. Himo acca Й“e e bewre maЙ“Й“e hiЙ“e bumam-bumannoo .(mbumo)"
  7,187,"HiЙ“e naamno maa fii darngal : "ko honnde woni daragol maggal?" Maaku : " ganndal mum ko ka Joomi am woni. Alaa feГұГұioowo waqtu maggal on si wanaa KaЕӢko. Ngal teddii ka kammuuli e ka leydi. Ngal arataa e mon si wanaa e juhal". HiЙ“e laЙ“ndo maa a sikkay ko a kuЙ“indiiЙ—o e Й—um. Maaku : "ganndal mum ko ka Alla woni". kono ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e yimЙ“e Й“en ngnndaa [Й—um]."
  7,188,"Maaku : "Mi waawanaa hoore-am nafa wanaa lorra, si wanaa ko Alla muuyi. Sinno miЙ—o anndunoo ko wirnii, mi hebbinorayno moЖҙЖҙere, bone kadi memataano kam. mi wonaani si wanaa jeertinoowo e bewlinoowo, wonan de yimЙ“e gooЕӢЙ—inooЙ“e"."
  7,189,"Ko KaЕӢko woni takЙ—o on immorde e woЕӢkii gooti, o waЙ—i e makki genndo makko, fii yo o deeЖҙu e makko. tuma nde o renndunoo e makko, o sowii sowannde hoyfunde, o duumodi e mun. Nde o teddidunoo [e reedu ndun], Й“e torodi Alla Joomi maЙ“Й“e : "Pellet, si a weeЙ—ii amen (Й“iЙ—Й—o) yottiiЙ—o, ma min njeye e yettooЙ“e Ma Й“een"."
  7,190,"Nde O weeЙ—noo Й“e (Й“iЙ—Й—o) yottiiЙ—o, Й“e waЙ—idani Mo kafidiiЙ“e e kon ko o yeЙ—i Й“e. Alla toowii e kon ko Й“e corkata."
  7,191,"E Й“e kafiday (mo) e kon ko tagataa hay e huunde, kamЙ“e tigi ko Й“e tagaaЙ“e?!"
  7,192,"ЖҠi waawanaa Й“e ballal, wanaa (hay) ko'e majji Й—i mballata."
  7,193,"Si on noddii Й—i e peewal, Й—i njokkataa on. Hino fotanion , si on noddii Й—i maa hara ko on deyЖҙuЙ“e."
  7,194,"Pellet, Й—iin Й—i noddoton gah Alla, ko jeyaaЙ—i yeruuji mon. Noddee Й—i, yo Й—i njaabinanii on, si on laatike gooЕӢЙ—uЙ“e."
  7,195,"Hara hiЙ—i mari koyЙ—e ko Й—i yahra? kaa hiЙ—i mari juuЙ—e ko Й—i duГұira? Kaa hiЙ—i mari gite ko Й—i nji'ira? Kaa hiЙ—i mari noppi ko Й—i nanira? maaku : "Noddee kafidiiЙ—i mon Й—iin, refti pewjanon kam, wata on neeЙ“tiitanam"."
  7,196,"Pellet, ko Alla woni keetam on, On JippinЙ—o deftetere nden, ko KaЕӢko woni keet moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e Й“en."
  7,197,"ЖҠin Й—i noddoton gah mo, Й—i kattanaa e wallude on, wanaa kadi ko'e majji Й—i mballata."
  7,198,"Si on noddii Й—i e peewal, Й—i nanataa. haЙ—a yi'a hiЙ—i hiЙ—ima ndaara, (kono) kaЕӢji Й—i yi'ataa."
  7,199,"Jogito yaafuyee, njamiraa moЖҙЖҙere nden Й—uurno-Й—aa e majjuЙ“e Й“een."
  7,200,"Si sowinsinoore arii heЙ“ude ma immorde e seytaane, moolor Alla. KaЕӢko ko O nanoowo, gannduЙ—o."
  7,201,"Pellet, Й“een hulЙ“Й“e(Alla), si sowonsinoore heЙ“ii Й“e immorde e sytaane, Й“e ngannditay [Alla] : jaka yoo kamЙ“e ko Й“e yi'ooЙ“e."
  7,202,"MusiЙ“Й“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en [ka yimЙ“e] hino fooЙ—a Й“e e bewre, refti Й“e raЙ“Й“intaako."
  7,203,"Si a addanaani Й“e Aaya, Й“e mbi'a : "Ko haЙ—noo sincaa Й—um?"(pekindoЙ—a) Maaku : "Anndee ko jokku-mi, ko kon wahyina e am immorde ka Joomi am. Ndee Й—oo [Alqur'aanaare] ko hujjaaji (Й“annguЙ—i) immorde ka Joomi mon, e peewal e yurmeende wonnande yimЙ“e gomЙ—inooЙ“e"."
  7,204,"Si Alqur'aana no janngeede, keЙ—tee nde deЖҙЖҙiton ; mbelejo'o, on njurminte."
  7,205,"Siftor Joomi maaЙ—a ka woЕӢkii maa, ka yankinaare e ka kulol, ko aldaa e feГұГұingol konngol, bimmbi e kiikiiЙ—e, wata a laatodo e welsindiiЙ“e Й“en."
  7,206,"Pellet, Й“een [maleykaaji] won Й“e ka Joomi maa, Й“e townitantaako dewgol Mo, hiЙ“e subbunhinanoo Mo, ko KaЕӢko woni ko Й“e cujjanta."
  8,1,"HeЙ“e laЙ“ndo maa fii konhoyri. Maaku : "Konhoyri ndin ko Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on njeyi". Kulee Alla, moЖҙЖҙinon hakkunde mon Й—oftoЙ—on kadi Alla e NulaaЙ—o makko on si on laatike gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e."
  8,2,"Pellet, gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“en, ko Й“een Й“e (tawata) si Alla jaЕӢtaama, Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en kulay. Si Aayeeje makko Й—en janngaama e maЙ“Й“e, Й—e Й“eyda Й“e gooЕӢЙ—inal. Ko e Joomi maЙ“Й“e (tan) Й“e pawotoo."
  8,3,"ЖҒeen ГұiiЙ“nooЙ“e juulde nde e komin ngarsiki Й“e heЙ“e wintoo=nafqa.(tottira)"
  8,4,"ЖҒeen Й—oon, ko kamЙ“e ngoni gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“e ka goonga : hino woodani Й“e darjaaji ka Joomi maЙ“Й“e, e yaafuye e arsike tedduЙ—o."
  8,5,"Ko wano Joomi maa yaltinirno maa non ka suudu maa sabu goonga, (tawi non) pellet, fedde e gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“een ko aГұuЙ“e (Й—um)."
  8,6,"HeЙ“e mbeeГұd maa fii goonga kan Й“aawo nde ka feeГұi ; elle ko Й“e soggeteeЙ“e fa'ade maayde hara kamЙ“e heЙ“e ndaara (nde)."
  8,7,"(Siftor) tuma nde Alla fodanoo on gootel e peЙ—le Й—iЙ—i, won de "gootel e majji ko onon woodani, hoЙ—on njiЙ—a sinno ko fedde nde alaa doole nde laatantoo on, (tawi) Alla no yiЙ—i nde O jojjin de goonga o ekonngii makko he taЖҙa Й“abbe heeferaaЙ“e Й“een."
  8,8,"Fii yo o jojjoniri goonga kan o bonne fii meere nden, hay si bonЙ“e Й“een njiЙ—aa."
  8,9,"(Siftor) tuma nde paabinoranoЙ—on Joomi mon o jaabinani on : "min ko mi Й“eydiroowo on ujunere e maleykaaji jokkondirooЙ“e"."
  8,10,"Alla waЙ—iraali Й—uum si wonaa weltaare-e fii no Й“erЙ—e mon deeЖҙira Й—uum. Balla wonaani si wonaa immorde ka Alla. Pellet, Alla ko pooluЙ—o Г‘eeГұЙ—o."
  8,11,"E Tuma nde ЕӢoЕӢre nden hippaynoo on hoolaare immorde ka makko, Homo Jippinana on ndiyam immorde ka kammu fii yo o laЙ“Й“inir on Й—am, O ittana on soЙ“e seytaane, e fii yo O tiiЙ—inir (Й—um) e Й“erЙ—e mon O tabintinira Й—am teppe [mon] Й—en.(teppe)"
  8,12,"Tuma nde Joomi maa wahyinaynoo e maleykaajiЙ—i : "Min miЙ—o won di e mo'on : tabintinee gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“en. Arma Mi bugoo Й—enЖҙere(kulol ) e Й“erЙ—e heeferЙ“e Й“en. Tappee dow daaЙ—e Й—een tappon e maЙ“Й“e kala wunnjere.(jokkule)"
  8,13,"ЖҠuum, ko fii kamЙ“e Й“e luutndike Alla e NulaaЙ—o makko on. "Kala non luutndiiЙ—o Alla e NulaaЙ—o makko on, pellet, Alla ko caЙ—tuЙ—o lepte"."
  8,14,"ЖҠuum mooЙ—on ; meeЙ—ee Й—um ! E won de pellet, no waadani heeferЙ“e Й“een lepte Yiite."
  8,15,"Eeheymon yo gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e, si on kawrii e Й“een heeferЙ“e ko Й“e mooЙ“iiЙ“e, wata on nduЕӢton Й“e Й“abbe Й—een(.ndogon)"
  8,16,"Kala duЕӢtiiЙ—o Й“e nden Гұande (Й“abbal mu'un), -si wonaa hara ko on keЙ“Й“itantooЙ—o hare nden, maa hara ko ukkitotooЙ—o e fedde, -gooЕӢЙ—ii haray o ruttodii e tikkere immorde ka Alla, jaaЖҙorde maЙ“Й“e nden ko Jahannama nge bonii ruttorde!"
  8,17,"On mbaraano Й“e : Ko Allaahu On wari Й“e. A werninooki tuma mberniЙ—aa : Ko Allaahu On wernii, e fii yo O jarribor gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“een immorde ka makko jarrabuyee moЖҙЖҙuЙ—o. Pellet, Alla ko Nanoowo gannduЙ—o."
  8,18,"ЖҠuum mooЙ—on, ko tawde pellet, Alla ko lo'inoowo pewje heeferЙ“e Й“een."
  8,19,"Si on Й—aЙ“Й“ii uddital, gooЕӢЙ—ii uddital arii on. Si on haЙ—itike, ko Й—uum Й“uri moЖҙЖҙannde on. Si on nduttiima, men nduttoo. Fedde mon nden nafataa on hay e huunde, hay si nde Й—uuЙ—ii. tawde pellet, Alla no won di e gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“een."
  8,20,"Eehey mon gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e, Й—oftee Alla e NulaaЙ—o makko on wata on Й—uurnu mo hara hoЙ—on nannde (Aayeeje Й—een)."
  8,21,"Wata on mbano Й“een wi'inooЙ“e : "minn nanii", tawi kamЙ“e Й“e alaa e nan de."
  8,22,"Pellet, ko Й“uri bon de e ko ruugata (kulle)Й—ee ka Alla, ko fa'aЙ—uЙ“e muumЙ—uЙ“e Й“e kakkiltaa."
  8,23,"Sinno Alla annduno e maЙ“Й“e moЖҙЖҙere, O naninayno Й“e. Hay si O naninno Й“e, Й“e nduЕӢtotoo hara ko Й“e Й—uurnii Й“e."
  8,24,"Eeheymon yo gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e, Nootee Alla e NulaaЙ—o on si Й“e noddii on fi ko wuurnata on (e goonga), nganndee pellet, Alla no heeda hakkunde neЙ—Й—o e Й“ernde mum, e won de pellet, ko ka Makko mooЙ“oyteЙ—on."
  8,25,"Ndentee e bone tawЙ—o o memataa tooГұuЙ“e Й“een e mooЙ—on tan. Nganndee pellet, Alla ko caЙ—tuЙ—o lepte."
  8,26,"Ciftoree tuma ngonndoЙ—on famЙ—uЙ“e, lo'inaaЙ“e ka leydi, hoЙ—on kula nde yimЙ“e Й“en jilotoo on. O weerni (tappion), O semmbiniri on ballal makko ngal, O arsiki on immorde e laaЙ“uЙ—i mbelejo'o, on njettatmo e( dokke makko Й—e)."
  8,27,"Eehey mon gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e, wata on jamfo Alla e NulaaЙ—o on, jamfoЙ—on koolaaje mon Й—en hara hiЙ—on nganndi."
  8,28,"Nganndee pellet, jawЙ—e mon Й—en e Й“iЙ—Й“e mon Й“en ko fitina e won de no ka Alla njoЙ“di mawndi."
  8,29,"Eehey mon gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e, si on kulii Alla, O waЙ—anay on ceerndirЙ—um (goonga e meere), O heefana on bakkatuuji mon O haforana on. Alla ko Jom-Й“ural mawnungal."
  8,30,"(siftor) tuma nde heeferЙ“e Й“een fewjanayno maa fii yoЙ“e nannguma maa, Й“e mbar maa, Й“e njaltinmaa. HeЙ“e pewja, Alla no fewja. Ko Alla Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude fewjooЙ“e Й“een."
  8,31,"Si Aayeeje amen Й—een janngaama e maЙ“Й“e, Й“e mbi'a : "GooЕӢЙ—ii men nanii, sinno men ynjiЙ—noЙ—uno min kaalatno yeru Й—um, ndee wonaani si wonaa tinndi adinooЙ“e"."
  8,32,"E tuma Й“e mbiunoo : "Yaa Alla, si tawii ko Й—um woni goonga immorde ka MaaЙ—a, haray saaЖҙin kaaЖҙe e amen immorde ka kammu, maa addanaa men lepte mu'usuЙ—e"."
  8,33,"Alla wonaani leptoowo Й“e, hara an haЙ—a hakkunde maЙ“Й“e. Alla siforaalni leptoowo Й“e, hara kamЙ“e heЙ“e imsinaade."
  8,34,"Ko haЙ—ata Й“e nde Alla leptataa Й“e, hara kamЙ“e heЙ“e faddade Juulirde hormante nden? ЖҒe ngonaani weldiiЙ“e nde. KeeteeЙ“e mum wonaani si wonaa Й“een gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e, kono Й“urЙ“e Й—uuЙ—ude e maЙ“Й“e nganndaa."
  8,35,"Juulde maЙ“Й“e nden ka Suudu wonaani, si wonaa guuЙ—gol e kellugol : "MeeЙ—iree lepte Й—en sabu ko njeddiratoЙ—on kon"."
  8,36,"Pellet, Й“een yedduЙ“e, heЙ“e nafqira jawЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—een no Й“e paddora(yimЙ“e Й“en) e laawol Alla ngol. Maa Й“e nafqu Й—e, refti wontana Й“e nimsa, refti Й“e poolee. ЖҒeen yedduЙ“e noon, ko ka Jahannama Й“e mooЙ“oytee,"
  8,37,"Fii yo Alla senndindir soЙ“e Й—en e ko laaЙ“i kon, O waЙ—a soЙ“e Й—en yoga mum e dow yoga, O fawindira Й—um fof O waЙ—ta Й—um ka ndeer Jahamma. ko Й“een Й—oon ngoni hayruЙ“e(pertuЙ“e.)Й“e"
  8,38,"Maakan Й“een yedduЙ“e: si Й“e haЙ—itike; Й“e njaafete ko yawti. Si Й“e ndutti, haray gooЕӢЙ—ii laawol (halkaare)adinooЙ“e Й“een yawtii."
  8,39,"KaЙ“ee Й“e haa ka tawata fitina laatotaako, diine kan fof laatanoo Alla. Si Й“e haЙ—itike, haray pellet, Alla ko deenЙ—o ko Й“e ngollata kon."
  8,40,"Si Й“e Й—uurniima, nganndee pellet, ko Alla woni GiЙ—o mon. o moЖҙЖҙiii keedo mo moЖҙЖҙii Balloowo."
  8,41,"ngandee won de kala ko hoЙ—on e huunde, pellet, hino woodani Alla e NulaaЙ—o makko on jowaЙ“al mum., e jom-Й“adondiral, e won Й—uЙ“e (Alyatimeebe) Й“een, e waasuЙ“e Й“een, (Й—atniyaЕӢkooЙ“e)tumaraЕӢkuЙ“e si on laatike gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Alla e kon ko minn njippini e jeyaaЙ—o amen oon, Г‘ande ceertugol (goonga e fenaande): Гұande dente Й—een Й—iЙ—i pottunoo. Alla ko kattanЙ—o kala hu'unde."
  8,42,"Nde tawnoo onon hoЙ—on ka baЕӢЕӢe Й“aЙ—tiiЙ—e, kamЙ“e (aГұЙ“e Й“en) hiЙ“e ka baЕӢЕӢe woЙ—Й—itiiЙ—e, tawi waЙ—Й—iiЙ“e Й“en no senngo ley mon. Sinno on saatondirno(,podondirno) on luutondiratno ka caate(.nokkuhe) Ko no ko fii yo Alla Гұaaw fiyaaku laatinooЙ—o golleteeЙ—o, fii yo maayowo maayu e ko Й“anngi, (laaЙ“ti)guuroowo wuura e Й“anngi.(laaЙ“ti) E pellet, Alla ko Nanoowo gannduЙ—o."
  8,43,"Tuma nde Alla hollayno maa Й“e ka Й—oyngol maaЙ—a ko Й“e seeЙ—aaЙ“e. Sinno O holluno Й“e ko Й“e Й—uuЙ—uЙ“e, on lo'ayno, on pooЙ—indiryno kadi e fiyaaku on. Kono Alla hisini. Pellet, KaЕӢko ko o gannduЙ—o ko woni e Й“erЙ—e Й—een."
  8,44,"E tuma nde Alla hollatnoo on Й“e, nde pottunoЙ—on, ko Й“e seeЙ—aaЙ“e e gite mon, Homo famЙ—ina on kadi e gite maЙ“Й“e fii yo Alla Гұaawo fiyaaku laatinooЙ—o golleteeЙ—o. Ko faade ka Alla woni ruttorde fiyakuuji Й—iin."
  8,45,"Eeymono gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e, si on pottii e fedde (aГұЙ“e Й“e), tabitee, jaЕӢtoЙ—on Alla ko Й—uuЙ—i=heewi; mbelejo'o, on malete."
  8,46,"ЖҠoftee Alla e NulaaЙ—o makko on, wata on pooЙ—ondir sakko lo'on doole mon njaha. muГұГұee, pellet, Alla no won di e muГұГұiiЙ“e Й“e."
  8,47,"Wata on mbano'u wa Й“een yaltirnooЙ“e ka galleeji maЙ“Й“e townitaare e yiinagol yimЙ“e, heЙ“e paddo e laawol Alla ngol. Alla noon ko piiltiiЙ—o ko Й“e ngollata."
  8,48,"E tuma nde seytaane cuЙ—aynnoo Й“e golle maЙ“Й“e Й—en o wi'i: "pooloowo on alaa hannde e yimЙ“e Й“e, min non ko mi kawtal mo'on". Nde peЙ—le Й—iЙ—i njiadirnoo, o yiltorii gaЙ—a teppe makko o wi'i: "min ko mi daЙ—ndiiЙ—o(kisЙ—o) e mon. min miЙ—o yi'a ko on nji'ataa, miin mi hulii Alla. Alla ko caЙ—tuЙ—e lepte"."
  8,49,"Tuma nde naafigeeЙ“e Й“en e Й“en Й“e Гұawu [lo'ere iimaanu] wonu e Й“erЙ—e mun mbi'atnoo : "diine Й“ee Й—oo kan hodii Й“e". Kala non pawiiЙ—o e Alla, pellet, Alla ko pooluЙ—o Г‘eeГұuЙ—o."
  8,50,"Sinno a yi'atno tuma maleykaaji Й—i mbarata heeferЙ“e Й“een, Й“e piya jeece maЙ“Й“e e Й“abbe maЙ“Й“e (Й“e mbi'ora Й“e) : "MeeЙ—ee lepte cumu"."
  8,51,"ЖҠuum (heЙ“irii on) sabu ko juuЙ—e mon Й—en ngardini ko. wonnde pellet, Alla wonaani TooГұoowo jeyaaЙ“e Й“een."
  8,52,"Wano mboowdi yimЙ“e Fir'awna e Й“en adinooЙ“e Й“e. ЖҒe njeddii kaawisaaji Alla Й—in. Alla Nanngitiri Й“e bakkatuuji maЙ“Й“e Й—in. Pellet, Alla ko TiiЙ—uЙ—o caЙ—tuЙ—o lepte."
  8,53,"(Ko waЙ—i) Й—um, ko tawde Alla wonaani bayloowo dokke mo rokki e yimЙ“e haa Й“e mbayla ko woni e woЕӢkiiji maЙ“Й“e. E wonnde pellet, Alla ko Nanoowo gannduЙ—o."
  8,54,"Wano mboowdi yimЙ“e Fir'awna e Й“en adinooЙ“e Й“e. ЖҒe njeddi Aayeeje Joomi maЙ“Й“e Й—een. min kalkiri Й“e bakkatuuji maЙ“Й“e Й—i, Men njooli yimЙ“e Fir'awna Й“een. Kala (maЙ“Й“e) laatino tooГұooЙ“e."
  8,55,"Pellet, ko Й“uri bonnde e ko ruugata kon ka Alla, ko Й“een yedduЙ“e, kamЙ“e Й“e ngooЕӢЙ—intaa."
  8,56,"ЖҒeen Й“e ahodiЙ—aa e mu'm refti Й“e firta ahadi maЙ“Й“e ndiin e kala laawol, kamЙ“e Й“e kulataa [Alla]."
  8,57,"Si waawii Й“e ka hare, yagginir (sar) Й“e arooЙ“e Й“aawo maЙ“Й“e. mbejo'o, Й“e mbaajitora Й“e"
  8,58,"Ammaa si a hulii e yimЙ“e jamfa, bugita(werla) e maЙ“Й“e (firtugol ahadi ndin) dow potondiral, tawde pellet, Alla yiЙ—aa jamfotooЙ“e Й“een."
  8,59,"Wota Й“een yedduЙ“e cikku Й“e laawki. Pellet, kamЙ“e Й“e ronknitaa (kam)."
  8,60,"Keplanee(heblanee) Й“e kala ko kattanЙ—on e doole e pucci kebilaaЙ—i, kulЙ“iniron Й—uum aГұЙ“e Alla Й“een e aГұЙ“e mon Й“een, e woЙ—Й“e goo gaanin maЙ“Й“e Й“e onon on nganndaabe Alla kaГұum no anndi Й“e. Kala ko nafkudon e laawol Alla ngol timminate on, onon on tooГұoytaake.(hay huude)"
  8,61,"Si Й“e naayanike kisal nagl, naayano ngal (an kadi) pawoЙ—aa e Alla, pellet, KaЕӢko ko O nanoowo gannduЙ—o."
  8,62,"Si Й“e paalaamo nde Й“e jamfoto maa, pellet, ko Alla yonay maa. Ko KaЕӢko woni cemmbinirЙ—o ma e ballal makko ngal, e (wallitagol) gooЕӢinЙ“e Й“een."
  8,63,"O woowindiri hakkunde Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—een. Sinno a wintino(nafkuna) ko woni kon ka leydi fof, a woowindirtaano hakkunde Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—een; ko woni tan ko Alla woowindiri hakkunde maЙ“Й“e. Pellet, KaЕӢko ko o pooluЙ—o Г‘eeГұuЙ—o."
  8,64,"Ko an yo Annabiijo, Alla yonii ma [O yoniii] kadi jokkuЙ“e ma e gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“een."
  8,65,"Eehey ma Annabiijo, hirjin gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“een e hare. Si no e mooЙ—on noogayo muГұГұiiЙ“e, Й“e poolay teemeЙ—Й—e Й—iЙ—o; si no e mooЙ—on kadi teemedere, Й“e poolay ujunere e heeferЙ“e Й“een; tawde Й“een ko yimЙ“e Й“e paamataa."
  8,66,"Jooni Alla hoynanii on,O anndii no e mooЙ—on lo'ere. Si no e mooЙ—on teemedere muГұГұiiЙ“e, Й“e poolay teemeЙ—Й—e Й—iЙ—o; si no e mooЙ—on kadi ujunere, Й“e poolay ujune Й—iЙ—o duЕӢaye (yamiroore) Alla. Alla no won di e muГұГұiiЙ“e Й“een."
  8,67,"Haananaa Annabiijo nde laatantoo mo dahaaЙ“e haa o Й—uЙ—Й—ina waraaЙ“e ka leydi. HiЙ—on paala jawkoy aduna, Alla kam no faalanaa (on) laakara. Alla ko pooluЙ—o Г‘eeГұuЙ—o."
  8,68,"Si wanaano binndol adingol immorde e Alla, lepte mawЙ—e memirayno on kon ko nannguЙ—on. [e konhoyri ndiin]"
  8,69,"Г‘aamee e kon ko konЙ—on, ko dagiiЙ—um laaЙ“uЙ—um. kulon Alla, pellet, Alla ko kaforoowo hinnotooЙ—o=jurmotoodo."
  8,70,"Eehey ma Annabiijo, maakan dahaaЙ“e wonuЙ“e e juuЙ—e mon Й“en : "Si Alla no anndi moЖҙЖҙere ka Й“erЙ—e mon, O okkay on ko Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude ko jaЙ“anoЙ—on kon, O haforana on. Alla ko kaforoowo jurmotooЙ—o."
  8,71,"Si Й“e paalaamo jamfagol ma, gooЕӢЙ—ii Й“e jamfinooma Alla ko adii; O newinan (maa) e mabЙ“e. Alla ko gannduЙ—o Г‘eeГұuЙ—o."
  8,72,"Pellet, Й“een gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e, Й“e peri Й“e tiiЙ—norii jawЙ—e maЙ“Й“e e woЕӢkiiji maЙ“Й“e fii laawol Alla, e Й“een weernu Й“e walli (Й“e); Й“en Й—on yoga maЙ“Й“e ko wallooЙ“e yoga. ЖҒeen non ngooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e kono Й“e peraani, alanaa on wallugol Й“e hay e huunde haa Й“e pera. Si Й“e mballinorii on ka diine, no fawii on wallitagol (Й“e), si wanaa hara ko e yimЙ“e Й“e ahadi woni hakkunde mon e maЙ“Й“e. Alla ko reenuЙ—o ko ngolloton kon."
  8,73,"ЖҒeen yedduЙ“e, yoga maЙ“Й“e ko wallooЙ“e yoga. Si on mbaЙ—aali Й—uum [ko Mi Й—aЙ“Й“iri on wallugol gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“een aГұra e heeferЙ“e Й“en], wonay fitina ka leydi e bone mawЙ—o."
  8,74,"ЖҒeen gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e, Й“e peri Й“e tiiЙ—nii e laawol Alla ngol, e Й“een weernu Й“e walli (Й“e); ko Й“en woni gooЕӢЙ—imЙ“e goonga Й“een: no woodani Й“e kaforanal e arsike tedduЙ—o."
  8,75,"ЖҒeen gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“aawo (Й—uum), Й“e peri Й“e tiiЙ—nodii e mon, Й“en Й—on ko jeyaaЙ“e e mon. JoomiraaЙ“e enЙ—ammaaji Й“een (ko) yoga maЙ“Й“e Й“uri hanndude e yoga ka Deftere Alla. Pellet, Alla ko gannduЙ—o kala huunde."
  9,1,"Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on kisii e Й“een sirkooЙ“e Й“e ahoduЙ—on(:ngaadondirЙ—on)"
  9,2,"Njahee ka leydi lebbi nayi; nganndon pellet, onon o ngonaa ronkinooЙ“e Alla e won de pellet, Alla ko koynoowo heeferЙ“e Й“een."
  9,3,"E ewnaango immorde ka Alla e NulaaЙ—o makko oon, haa e yimЙ“e Й“een, Гұalaande hajju mawnde nden, won de : Alla e NulaaЙ—o makko on ko daЙ—ndiiЙ“e =hisЙ“e e sirkooЙ“e Й“een. Si on tuubii, ko Й—um Й“uri moЖҙЖҙannde on. Si on Й—uurni, nganndee pellet, on ngonaa roЕӢkinooЙ“e Alla. weltinir Й“een yedduЙ“e lepte mu'usuЙ—e."
  9,4,"Si wonaa Й“een sirkooЙ“e Й“e ngaadondirnoЙ—ono Й—on, refti Й“e ngustaani [e aadi he] hay e huunde, Й“e mballindiraan kadi e gooto hoore-mon : timminanee Й“een Й—oon ahadi maЙ“Й“e ndin haa ka dumunna maЙ“Й“e. nganndon pellet, Alla no yiЙ—i gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“een."
  9,5,"Si lebbi hormante Й—in timmii, mbaree sirkooЙ“e Й“een kala ka tawuЙ—on Й“e : nanngee Й“e, huuЙ“iton Й“e jooЙ—anoЙ—on Й“e e kala tommborde. Si Й“e tuubii, Й“e ГұiiЙ“inii juulde Й“e tottii zakka, (haray) ngaccitee laawol maЙ“Й“e ngol. Pellet, Alla ko kaforoowo jurmotooЙ—o."
  9,6,"Si goЙ—Й—o e sirkooЙ“e Й“een fatike(hoddiniimo) ma, fattin(hottu) mbo haa o nana konngol Alla ngol, refti yottinoy mo nokku hisirde makko. Tawde kamЙ“e ko Й“e yimЙ“e Й“e nganndaa."
  9,7,"Ko holno ahdi woniranta sirkooЙ“e Й“een ka Alla e ka NulaaЙ—o Makko on? Si wanaa Й“een Й“e ngaadondirnoЙ—on ka Juulirde hormanteere. Fodde heЙ“e po'occanii on, po'occanee Й“e. Pellet, Alla no yiЙ—i gooЕӢЙ—uЙ“e Й“een."
  9,8,"Ko holno si Й“e poolii on, Й“e ndeenataa e mooЙ—on enЙ—am wanaa ahdi?! HiЙ“e mbeltinira on kunnduЙ—e maЙ“Й“e, Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en caloo; ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e maЙ“Й“e kadi ko yaltuЙ“e Й—oftaare"
  9,9,"ЖҒe ngostotirii Aayeeje Alla Й—en coggu pamЙ—ungu Й“e sakkii(paddii) e laawol makko ngol. Pellet, kamЙ“e ko Й“e ngollatnoo kon na bonii."
  9,10,"ЖҒe ndeenataa e gooЕӢЙ—inЙ—o enЙ—am wanaa ahadi. Ko Й“een woni yawtooЙ“e keeri Й“een."
  9,11,"Si Й“e tuubii, Й“e ГұiЙ“nnii juulde Й“e tottii zakka, haray ko Й“e siЙ—Й“e mo'on ka diina. miЙ—en fensitana Aayeeje Й—en yimЙ“e annduЙ“e."
  9,12,"Si Й“e pirtii gooЙ—ndooje maЙ“Й“e Й—een Й“aawo ahdi maЙ“Й“e ndin Й“e njuwi e diine mon kan, haray kaЙ“ee hooreeЙ“e keeferaagu Й“een -tawde kamЙ“e ahadi alanaa Й“e - mbelejo'o, Й“e kaЙ—itoto."
  9,13,"E on kaЙ“ataa yimЙ“e firtuЙ“e gooЙ—ndooje maЙ“Й“e, Й“e hkmmiri yaltinngol NulaaЙ—o on, ko kamЙ“e kadi adii on Й—aЙ“Й“itude? E on kulay Й“e?! Ko Alla Й“uri haan du de kuloton si on laatike gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e."
  9,14,"kaЙ“ee e mabЙ“e. Alla leptira Й“e juuЙ—e mon Й—en, O hoyna Й“e, O walla on e dow maЙ“Й“e, O sellina Й“erЙ—e yimЙ“e gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e."
  9,15,"O itta tikkere Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e. Alla no jaЙ“ana tuubuubuyee on Mo O muuyi. Alla ko gannduЙ—o Г‘eeГұuЙ—o."
  9,16,"Kaa on cikku on ngaccete, hara Alla anndaani Й“een tiiЙ—niiЙ“e e mon, hara Й“e jogitaaki gah Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on e gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“en weldiiЙ“e? Alla ko kumpitiiЙ—o ko ngolloton."
  9,17,"Haananaa sirkooЙ“e Й“een nde Й“e nguurnitata JuulirЙ—e Alla Й—een, hara ko Й“e seeditaniiЙ“e woЕӢkiiji maЙ“Й“e Й—in keeferaaku. ЖҒeen Й—on golle maЙ“Й“e Й—een njirbii yani; ko ka Yiite woni ko Й“e luttoyta.=saasooЙ“e"
  9,18,"Nganndee ko wuurnitata JuulirЙ—e Alla Й—en : ko on gooЕӢЙ—inЙ—o Alla e Гұalaande Sakkitiinde nden, o ГұiiЙ“ni juulde nde, o totti zakka on hara kadi o kulaani ko wanaa Alla. Hino tijjaa ka Й“en Й—on ngodata e feewuЙ“e Й“een."
  9,19,"E on mbaЙ—at yarnooЙ“e hajjooЙ“Й“e Й“en e wuurnitooЙ“e Juulirde hormanteere nden wano on gooЕӢЙ—inЙ—o Alla e Г‘alaande Sakkitiinde O tiiЙ—nii e laawol Alla?! ЖҒeen Й“e potataa ka Alla. Alla non fewnataa yimЙ“e tooГұooЙ“e Й“een."
  9,20,"ЖҒeen gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e, Й“e peri fii laawol Alla ngol jawЙ—e maЙ“Й“e e woЕӢkiiji maЙ“Й“e, Й“uri mawnude darja ka Alla. Ko Й“een ngoni malaaЙ“e Й“een."
  9,21,"Joomi maЙ“Й“e no wewlinira Й“e yurmeende immorde ka makko, e yarluyee, e Aljannaaji, no woodani Й“e nder majji dokke Alla ГұiiЙ“atЙ—e"
  9,22,"Ko Й“e saasooЙ“e nder majji poomaa. Pellet, njoЙ“di mawndi no ka Alla."
  9,23,"Ko onon yo gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e, wota on jogitor baabi- raaЙ“e mon Й“en e musiЙ—Й“e mon Й“en weldiiЙ“e; si Й“e Й“urni keeferaaku e dow lgooЕӢЙ—inere. Kala e mo'on belduЙ—o e maЙ“Й“e, ko Й“een Й—oon ngoni tooГұuЙ“e Й“en."
  9,24,"Maaku : "Si tawii ko baabiraaЙ“e mon Й“een, e Й“iЙ—Й“e mon Й“en, e musiЙ—Й“e mon Й“een, e resondiraa- Й“e mon Й“een, e bolondaa mon oon, e jawЙ—eele (mon) Й—e paggitiЙ—on, e njulaagugu ngu kulaon faЙ“Й“ugol, ngu koЙ—orle Й—e mbelaЙ—on- (Й“urani on)yiЙ—eede e mon diine Alla, e NulaaЙ—o makko on e tiiЙ—norgol fii makko, haray patndee haa Alla adda yamiroore makko nden. Alla noon feewnataa yimЙ“e yaltuЙ“e Й—oftaare Й“een"."
  9,25,"Wollahi Alla wallii on e nokkuuji Й—uuЙ—uЙ—i. [Ciftoree] kadi Гұande Hunayni, tuma nde Й—uuЙ—al mon haawnoo on, ngal nafaani on hay e huunde, leydi ndi faaЙ—ani on e hoore ko ndi yaaji kon fow, refti nduЕӢtiЙ—on ko on dogooЙ“e."
  9,26,"Refti Alla Jippini deeЖҙere makko ndeen e dow nulaaЙ—o makko on e gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“een. o jiippini kadi konu ngu on yi'aani, o lepti Й“een yedduЙ“e. Ko Й—uum woni njoЙ“di yedduЙ“e Й“een."
  9,27,"Refti Й“aawo Й—uum, Alla jaЙ“ana tuubuubuyee on mo o muuyi, Alla ko kaforoowo jurmotooЙ—o."
  9,28,"Eehey mon gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e, ngnndee sirkooЙ“e Й“een ko soЙ“Й“e : wata Й“e Й“aЙ—to Juulirde hormanteere nden Й“aawo hitaande maЙ“Й“e ndee Й—oo. Si on kulii baasal, arma Alla alЙ—inira on Й“ural makko ngal, si on muuyii. Pellet, Alla ko gannduЙ—o Г‘eeГұuЙ—o."
  9,29,"KaЙ“ee Й“een Й“e ngooЕӢЙ—inaani Alla e Г‘alaande sakkitiinde nden, Й“e karmintaa ko Alla e NulaaЙ—o akko on karmini koon, Й“e diininortaako diine goonga, Й“een jeyaaЙ“e e okkaaЙ“e defte, haa Й“e njonnira sagalle=lempo on juuЙ—e [maЙ“Й“e], ko Й“e jaasuЙ“e."
  9,30,"Alyahuuda'en mbi'i : "Uzayru ko Й“iЙ—Й—o Alla", Annasara'en kadi mbi'i : "Almasiihu ko Й“iЙ—Й—o Alla". ЖҠuum ko konngol maЙ“Й“e iwrungol e kunndule maЙ“Й“e. heЙ“e nanndinoo konngol Й“een yeddunooЙ“e ko adii. Alla huЙ—ii Й“e. Ko honno Й“e wonaa fefindoreede (pirlitirtee) (e meere)?!"
  9,31,"ЖҒe njogitorii annduЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“een, e ruuЙ—iiЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en, e Almasiihu Й“iЙ—Й—o Maryama rewetee gah Alla, Й“e njmiranooka si wanaa nde Й“e ndewa deweteeЙ—o gooto, deweteeЙ—o alaa ko wanaa KaЕӢko. Senaaree woodanii mo e kon ko Й“e cirkata."
  9,32,"HeЙ“e njiЙ—irii Гұifgol Annoore Alla nde e kunndule maЙ“Й“e Й—een, Alla no saloo si wanaa de O timmiЕӢta Annoore makko on, hay si heeferЙ“e Й“en ngaГұii [Й—um]."
  9,33,"Ko KaЕӢko woni NulirЙ—o NulaaЙ—o makko on peewal e diina goonga, fii yo o Й“amtu ka e hoore kala diine, hay si sirkooЙ“e Й“een ngaГұii [Й—uum]."
  9,34,"Ehey mon goooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e, tabitii ko Й—uuЙ—uЙ“e e annduЙ“e (Alyahuuda) Й“e, e ruuЙ—iiЙ“e (Annasaara) Й“e, hino Гұaamira jawЙ—eele yimЙ“e Й“en meere, heЙ“e paddoo e laawol Alla ngol. ЖҒeen Й“e no mooЙ“indira kaЕӢЕӢe e kaalise hara Й“e wintortaako(nafqataaЙ—e) fii laawol Alla, weltinirЙ“e lepte muusuЙ—e."
  9,35,"Г‘alnde Й—een (jawЙ—eele) ngulnoytee ka Yiite Jahannama, Й—e cumiree jeece maЙ“Й“e, e becce maЙ“Й“e e Й“abbe maЙ“Й“e : ko Й—um Й—oo mooЙ“annoЙ—on woЕӢkiiji mon, meeЙ—ee non kon ko mooЙ“anaynoЙ—on."
  9,36,"Tabitii limoore lebbi Й—in ka Alla, ko lebbi sappo e Й—iЙ—i, ka Alluwal Alla (deenaangal), Г‘alnde O taknoo kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin. No e majji nayi hormanteeji : Ko Й—uum woni diine ГұiiЙ“Й—a=poociiЙ—o. Wata on tooГұu e majji woЕӢkiiji mon. KaЙ“ee sirkooЙ“e fof maЙ“Й“e wano Й“e kaЙ“irta on Й“e fof maЙ“Й“e. gandon pellet, Alla na wondi e gooЕӢЙ—unЙ“e Й“en."
  9,37,"Anndee neeЙ“nugol ngol ko Й“eydaari e keeferaaku. ЖҠum no majjiniree Й“en yedduЙ“e : hiЙ“e dagintinira Й—um hitaande, Й“e harmintina Й—um hitaande, fii yo Й“e hawritoy e limoore nden nde Alla harmini, Й“e dagintina ko Alla harmini. ЖҒe cuЙ—anaama golle maЙ“Й“e bonЙ—e Й—en. Alla non fewnataa yimЙ“e heeferЙ“e Й“en."
  9,38,"Eeymon gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e, ko heЙ“i on, si on mbianaama : "njaltee fii laawol Alla"; teddintinoЙ—o ka leydi? E on wela nguurndam aduna e diini laakara? dakamme aduna Й—am wonaani ka laakara si wanaa seeЙ—a!"
  9,39,"Si on njaltaani, O leptiray on lepte mu'usuЙ—e, o waЙ—titira on yimЙ“e woЙ—Й“e, on lorrirtaa mo huunde. Alla ko kaЙ—tanЙ—o kala huunde."
  9,40,"Si on mballaani mo, gooЕӢЙ—ii Alla walliino mo; tuma nde Й“en yedduЙ“e njaltinnoo mo, Й—iЙ—aЙ“o e Й—iЙ—ooЙ“e, tuma nde Й“e ngnoo ka fammeere=wimmba, tuma nde o maakanaynoo gon diiЙ—o makko on : "Wata a suno, pellet, Alla no won di e meeЙ—en". Alla Jippini deeЖҙre makko nden e makko, O semmbini- niri mo konuuji ko on nji'aani, O waЙ—i konngol Й“een yedduЙ“e lesЙ—ungol, Konngol Alla ngol woni toowungol. Alla ko pooluЙ—o Г‘eeГұuЙ—o."
  9,41,"NduГұГұe [ka jihaadi] ko on hoyfiraaЙ“e, maa teddiraaЙ“e, tiiЙ—noron jawЙ—eele mon e woЕӢkiiji mon fii laawol Alla. Ko Й—uum mooЙ—on Й“uri moЖҙЖҙannde on, si on laatike annduЙ“e."
  9,42,"Sinno Й—uum laatino weeЙ“itannde (konhoyri) Й“adiindi e setewu =Й—atngal daЙ“Й“iЙ—ngal= juutaani, Й“e njokketeno; kono saЙ—teende (yahdu ndun) woЙ—Й—anii Й“e. Aray ka Й“e ngЙ—oondira Alla: "Sinno min kattanno, min jaltidayno e mo'on".HeЙ“e kalka woЕӢkiiji maЙ“Й“e. Alla no anndi pellet, ko Й“e fenooЙ“e."
  9,43,"Alla yaafanike ma! ko haЙ—Й—no ngaccaa duЕӢagol (cakkitgol) Й“e haa Й“anngane gooЕӢЙ—uЙ“e Й“een, nganndaa fenooЙ“e Й“e?"
  9,44,"ЖҒeen gooЙ—inЙ“e Alla e Г‘alaande sakkitiinde nden duЕӢinortaako ma nde Й“e mbaЙ—ata jihaadi jawЙ—eele maЙ“Й“e Й—en e woЕӢkiiji maЙ“Й“e Й—in. Alla ko gannduЙ—o gooЕӢЙ—uЙ“e Й“een."
  9,45,"Anndu ko duЕӢinoto maa, ko Й“een Й“e ngooЕӢЙ—inaani Alla e Г‘alaande sakkitiinde nden, Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—een cikkitii. KamЙ“e e sikkitaare maЙ“Й“e nden hiЙ“e rutti-ruttinnoo."
  9,46,"Sinno Й“e paalano yaltugol, Й“e kebilanayno ngol hebilaare. Kono Alla aГұii jaltugol Й“e ngol; O aamini Й“e. ЖҒe mb'anaa : "njooЙ—odee e jooЙ—iiЙ“e Й“en"."
  9,47,"Sinno Й“e njaltiduno e mooЙ—on, Й“e Й“eydataano on si wanaa bone, Й“e liЙ“ayno kadi konnaagu hakkunde mon; heЙ“e Й—aЙ“Й“ana on fitina. Hino e mo'on heЙ—itantooЙ—o Й“e. Alla non ko gannduЙ—o tooГұooЙ“e Й“een."
  9,48,"Wollahii Й“e Й—aЙ“Й“iino fitina on ko adii, Й“e mbaylitan-maa fiyaaku on haa goonga kan ari, fiyaaku Alla on feeГұi tawi ko Й“e aГұuЙ“e (Й—uum)."
  9,49,"Hino e maЙ“Й“e bi'oowo : "DuЕӢano(sakkitan) kamm (heddagol), wata a fitinam." Anndee ko e fitina on (tigiri) Й“e njani; pellet, Jahannama ko huuЙ“itaynge(fiiltii) heeferЙ“e Й“en."
  9,50,"Si moЖҙЖҙere heЙ“ii ma, metta Й“e. Si musiiba heЙ“ii ma, Й“e mbi'a : "Banni min nanngunoo fiyaaku amen ko adii." HiЙ“e Й—uurnoo ko Й“e weltiiЙ“e."
  9,51,"Maaku : "HeЙ“ataa men si wanaa kon ko Alla winndani amen. Ko KaЕӢko woni GiЙ—o amen. Ko e Alla woni ko gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“e pawotoo"."
  9,52,"Maaku : "Hara hoЙ—on kabbitori amen si wanaa gootel e moЖҙЖҙereeji Й—in Й—iЙ—i? minen kadi miЙ—en paditii e mon, nde Alla meminirta on lepte immorde ka makko, maa e juuЙ—e amen. Padee! minnen miЙ—en padi e mooЙ—on."
  9,53,"Maaku : "Wintee(nafqe) hoЙ—on njiЙ—i maa hoЙ—on ngaГұi : on njaЙ“antaake, onon on laatinoke yimЙ“e yaltuЙ“e". Й—oftaare."
  9,54,"HaЙ—aani Й“e jaЙ“eneede wintaaje maЙ“Й“e Й—en, si wanaa ko Й“e njediri kon Alla e nulaaЙ—o makko on, Й“e ngarataa e juulde si wanaa hara ko Й“e aamuЙ“e, Й“e wintotaako si wanaa hara ko Й“e aГұuЙ“e."
  9,55,"Wata jawЙ—eele maЙ“Й“e e Й“iЙ—Й“e maЙ“Й“e haawne! Anndu ko Alla fa'andii ko nde O leptirta Й—e Й“e ka nguurndam aduna, woЕӢkiiji maЙ“Й“e Й—in Й—oofee hara ko Й“e yedduЙ“e."
  9,56,"HiЙ“e ngooЙ—ndira Alla [kamЙ“e naafigeeЙ“e'en] won de ko Й“e jeyaaЙ“e e mo'on; Й“e ngonaani jeyaaЙ“e e mo'on. Ko woni kamЙ“e ko Й“e yimЙ“e hulooЙ“e."
  9,57,"Sinno Й“e keЙ“atno ooГұorgal, maa pammeeje maa pulfa(naatirde), Й“e huccayno e Й—um hara hiЙ“e yaccoo."
  9,58,"No e maЙ“Й“e Й“en aybinooЙ“e ma ka senndugol sadakaaji : si Й“e njonnaama e majji, Й“e mbeltoo; si Й“e njonnaaka noon e majji, jaka yoo kamЙ“e hiЙ“e tikka."
  9,59,"Sinno kamЙ“e Й“e mbeltorno kon ko Alla okki Й“e e nulaaЙ—o makko on, Й“e mb'i : "Alla yonii amen. Arma Alla okkora amen e Й“ural makko ngal e nulaaЙ—o makko on. minen ko men reerЙ—uЙ“e faade e Alla"."
  9,60,"nganndee sadakaaji Й—iin ko fii waasЙ“e Й“en, e miskiineeЙ“e Й“en, e gollooЙ“e e majji Й“een, e woowinirteeЙ“e Й“erЙ—e mun (Lislaamu) Й“een, e daaЙ—e rimЙ—inteeЙ“e, e Й“een ГұaliiЙ“e, e fii laawol Alla e Й—atniiЙ“e. tumraЕӢkuЙ“e koЙ—um fairilla immorde ka Alla. Alla ko gannduЙ—o Г‘eeГұuЙ—o."
  9,61,"No e maЙ“Й“e Й“en lorrayЙ“e annabiijo on heЙ“e mbi'a : "Ko o nofel".-Maaku : "Ko nofel moЖҙЖҙere mon. homo gooЕӢЙ—ini Alla o gooЕӢЙ—iini gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“een, e yurmeende Й“een gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e e mooЙ—on. Й“een lorrayЙ“e NulaaЙ—o Alla on, hino woodani Й“e lepte mu'usuЙ—e."
  9,62,"HeЙ“e ngooЙ—ndirana on Alla fii yo Й“e mbeltin on. Ko Alla -e NulaaЙ—o makko on- Й“uri haan dude e weltineede, si Й“e laatike gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e."
  9,63,"E Й“e nganndaa won de mo lunnduki Alla e NulaaЙ—o makko on, haray no woodani mo Yiite Jahannama, ko o luttoowo e magge? Ko Й—um woni koyeera mawЙ—o."
  9,64,"NaafigeeЙ“e Й“een no kuli nde cortewol(simoore) Jippintee e maЙ“Й“e ngol no humpita Й“e ko woni e Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e. Maaku : "njalkitee, pellet, Alla ko yaltinoowo kon ko kuluЙ—on (wata jippo)".(suhritde on)"
  9,65,"Si a laЙ“ndike Й“e, Й“e mbi'ay: "nganndee men laatinoke miЙ—en jumpa miЙ—en fija." maaku : "E ko Alla, e Aayeeje makko Й—een e nulaaЙ—o makko on laatinoЙ—on hoЙ—on njalkita?"
  9,66,"Wota on ngantino: gooЙ—ii on njddii Й“aawo gooЙ—inal mon. Si minn njaafike fedde goo e mooЙ—on, minn leptat fedde woЙ—nde tawde kamЙ“e Й“e laatinoke bonnooЙ“e."
  9,67,"Naafigi'en worЙ“e, e naafigi'en rewЙ“e, yoga maЙ“Й“e no jeyaa e yaga. HeЙ“e njamira ЕӢiГұere, Й“e kaЙ—a moЖҙЖҙere, heЙ“e tama juuЙ—e maЙ“Й“e. Й“e yejjitii Alla, KaЕӢko kadi o yejjiti Й“e. Pellet, naafigiiЙ“e Й“en ko kamЙ“e ngoni yaltuЙ“e. Й—oftaare."
  9,68,"Alla fodanii naafigeeЙ“e'en worЙ“e, e naafigeeЙ“e rewЙ“e, e heeferЙ“e Й“een, Yiite Jahannama, ko Й“e luttinteeЙ“e toon.Nge yonii Й“e. Alla huЙ—ii Й“e, hino woodani Й“e lepte duumiiЙ—e."
  9,69,"[HiЙ“e mba'i] wano Й“een adinooЙ“e on : Й“e laatinoke Й“urЙ“e on saЙ—tude doole, Й“urЙ“e on Й—uuЙ—ude jawЙ—eele e Й“iЙ—Й“e. ЖҒe dakmitori [ontuma] e geЙ—al maЙ“Й“e ngal dakmitorЙ—on geЙ—al mon ngal wano adinooЙ“e on Й“en dakmitornoo geЙ—al maЙ“Й“e ngal, jnumpirЙ—on wano Й“e njumpirnoo. Й“een Й—oon, golle maЙ“Й“e Й—en poЙ“ii(njirbii) aduna e laakara. Ko Й“een Й—oon ngoni hayruЙ“e(perduЙ“e) Й“en."
  9,70,"E kabaaru Й“en adinooЙ“e Й“e araali Й“e : yimЙ“e Nuuhu Й“en, e Aadi'en, e Thamuuda'en, e yimЙ“e Ibraahiima Й“en, e wonndiЙ“e Madyana Й“en e waylitanooЙ“e Й“en? NulaaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en addani Й“e hujjaaji Й“annguЙ—i.=peeГұЙ—i Alla wonaani tooГұoowo Й“e, ko woni tan ko woЕӢkiiji maЙ“Й“e Й—in Й“e wonunoo tooГұude."
  9,71,"GooЕӢЙ—imЙ“e worЙ“e Й“en e gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e rewЙ“e Й“en yoga maЙ“Й“e ko wallooЙ“e yoga. HiЙ“e yamira moЖҙЖҙere, Й“e haЙ—a ЕӢiГұere=bone, Й“e ГұiiЙ“na juulde, Й“e totta zakka, Й“e Й—oftoo Alla e NualaaЙ—o makko on. Й“en Й—oon, arma Alla yurmee Й“e. Pellet, Alla ko pooluЙ—o, Г‘eeГұuЙ—o."
  9,72,"Alla fodanii gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e worЙ“e Й“en e gooЙ—inЙ“e rewЙ“e Й“en Aljannaaji, Й—i caatli ilata e ley majji, ko Й“e duumotooЙ“e nder majji, e koЙ—ooli laaЙ“uЙ—i e nder Aljanna duumal. E yarluyee=weluye Alla Й“urЙ—o mawnude. Ko Й—um woni malal mawnungal."
  9,73,"Eehey ma annabiijo, haЙ“a heeferЙ“e Й“en e naafigeeЙ“e Й“e, caЙ—tinanaa Й“e; jaaЖҙnde maЙ“Й“e nden ko Jahannama, nge bonii ruttorde."
  9,74,"HiЙ“e ngooЙ—ndira Alla Й“e wowlaali, gooЕӢЙ—ii le Й“e wowlii konngol keeferaaku ngol, Й“e njeddi Й“aawo silmugol maЙ“Й“e, Й“e himmiri ko Й“e heЙ“aani. Й“e mettiniraani (Й“e aybiniri) si wanaa fii Alla - e nulaaЙ—o makko on - alЙ—inirii Й“e e Й“ural makko ngal. Si Й“e tuubii, wonanay Й“e moЖҙЖҙere. Si Й“e nduЕӢtiima noon, Alla leptiray Й“e lepte muusuЙ—e aduna e laakara; giЙ—o alanaa Й“e ka leydi wanaa balloow"
  9,75,"Hino e maЙ“Й“e ЖҙettanЙ“e Alla ahadi : "Si O okkorii men e Й“ural makko ngal, ko ma min cakkor min laatoo jeyaaЙ“e e moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e Й“en"."
  9,76,"Nde O okkunoo Й“e e Й“ural makko nagl, Й“e wuddiri Й—uum Й“e hucciti to Й“e Й—uurnii Й“e."
  9,77,"O waЙ—tintinirani Й“e naafigaaku ka Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e haa Г‘alnde Й“e kawroyta e makko, sabu ko Й“e lunndii Alla kon ko Й“e fodunoo mo e ko Й“e laatinoo hiЙ“e pena."
  9,78,"E Й“ee nganndaa won de Alla no anndi koЙ“e cuuЙ—i eko Й“e peГұГұini (gunndo) maЙ“Й“e e won de pellet, Alla ko gaannduЙ—o mbirniiЙ—i Й—in?"
  9,79,"ЖҒeen aybinooЙ“e gattooЙ“e jeyaaЙ“e e gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“een ka sadakaaji e Й“en Й“e keЙ“ataa si wanaa tiiЙ—naare maЙ“Й“e nden, heЙ“e njalkita Й“een. Alla jalkitii Й“e. hino woodani Й“e lepte muusuЙ—e."
  9,80,"Imsinano Й“e, maa hara a imsinanaaki Й“e -hay si a imsinanike Й“e laaЙ“i cappanЙ—e jeeЙ—iЙ—i - Alla yaafataako Й“e. Ko waЙ—i Й—uum, Й“een Й“e njeddii Alla e nulaaЙ—o makko on. Alla feewnataa yimЙ“e yaltuЙ“e Й—oftaare Й“een."
  9,81,"LuutndinooЙ“e Й“en mbeltorii jooЙ—agol maЙ“Й“e ngol lunndoo nulaaЙ—o Alla on, Й“e aГұiniri kaЙ“irgol jawЙ—eele maЙ“Й“e Й—en e woЕӢkiiji maЙ“Й“e Й—in fii laawol Alla ngol, Й“e mbi'i : "Wata on njltu e nguleendi ndin". Maaku : "Ko Yiite Jahannama Й“uri tiiЙ—ude nguleendi." - Sinno Й“e faamaynoo ! -"
  9,82,"Yo Й“e njaal seeЙ—a Й“e ngulla buy njoЙ“di ko Й“e laatinoo hiЙ“e paggitoo."
  9,83,"Si Alla ruttitii ma faade e fedde jeyaande e maЙ“Й“e Й“e duЕӢinani maa yaltugol, maaku : "On njaltidataa e am poomaa, on kaЙ“idataa e am gaГұo. Onon on mbelaama jooЙ—agol ka laawol aranol, njooЙ—odee e lunndii Й“e Й“en"."
  9,84,"Wata a juulu e gooto maЙ“Й“e maayЙ—o poomaa, wata a daro e aГұГұeere makko. KamЙ“e Й“e njeddii Alla e nulaaЙ—o makko on Й“e maayi ko Й“e yaltuЙ“e Й—oftaare"
  9,85,"Wata jawЙ—eele maЙ“Й“e e Й“iЙ—Й“e maЙ“Й“e haawne! anndu ko Alla fa'andii ko nde O leptirta Й—e Й“e ka aduna, woЕӢkiiji maЙ“Й“e Й—in Й—o'ofee hara ko Й“e yedduЙ“e."
  9,86,"Si Cortewol=simoore jippinaama : "Si ko woni, gooЕӢЙ—inee Alla tiiЙ—nodon jihaadi e nulaaЙ—o makko on", jom-yaajeende'en e maЙ“Й“e duЕӢinoto ma Й“e mbia : "Accu min wontida e jooЙ—iiЙ“e Й“een"."
  9,87,"ЖҒe mbelaama heddodugol e lunndiiЙ“e Й“en. notaama =tappaama e Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en, kamЙ“e Й“e paamataa."
  9,88,"Kono NulaaЙ—o on kaГұum e gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e won duЙ“e e makko Й“en Й“e tiiЙ—norii jawЙ—eele maЙ“Й“e Й—en e woЕӢkiiji maЙ“Й“e Й—in. ЖҒen Й—on, hino woodani Й“e moЖҙЖҙereeji, ko Й“een kadi ngoni malaaЙ“e Й“een."
  9,89,"Alla heblanii Й“e Aljannaaji Й—i caatli ilata senngo ley majji, ko Й“e duumotooЙ“e ton. Ko Й—um woni maloore mawnde ndeen."
  9,90,"NgantinotooЙ“e jeyaaЙ“e e yimЙ“e buruure Й“en nari fii yo Й“e duЕӢinane. een fenanЙ“e Alla e nulaaЙ—o makko on luttiti (jooЙ—ii). Arma lepte muusuЙ—e mema Й“en yedduЙ“e e maЙ“Й“e."
  9,91,"Bakkaatu fawaaki e lo'uЙ“e Й“en, wanaa ГұawЙ“e Й“en, wanaa Й“en Й“e keЙ“aani ko wintoo( nafqa) si Й“e laaЙ“anii Alla e NulaaЙ—o makko on. Laawol feloore alanaa moЖҙЖҙimЙ“e Й“en. Alla ko jaafotooЙ—oo, jurmotooЙ—o."
  9,92,"Wanaa kadi e Й“een arooЙ“e ka maaЙ—a fii yo a waЙ—Й—imЙ“e, mbi'aa : "mi heЙ“aali ko mi waЙ—Й—ina on." ЖҒe kuccita hara gite maЙ“Й“e no njuppa gonЙ—i suno fii Й“e heЙ“aali ko Й“e wintoo nafki."
  9,93,"Anndu ko laawol (bakkaatu) fawii, ko Й“een duЕӢinotooЙ“e(sakkinkinotoobe) ma hara ko Й“e alЙ—uЙ“e. Й“e mbelaama nde Й“e laatoda e luutndiiЙ“e Й“en. Alla tapi Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e tawi kamЙ“e Й“e nganndaa."
  9,94,"HeЙ“e ngantinoo e mooЙ—on si on nduttitike e maЙ“Й“e. Maaku : "Wata on ngantino : min ngooЕӢЙ—intaa on. GooЕӢЙ—ii Alla habriino amen kabaruuji moooЙ—on. Arma Alla yi'a golle mon Й—en, e nulaaЙ—o makko on. Refti ruttiteЙ—on e on gannduЙ—o ko wirnii eko feeГұi, ko kumpita on kon ko laatinoЙ—on hoЙ—on ngolla."
  9,95,"Aray ka Й“e ngooЙ—ndirana on Alla, si on nduttitike e maЙ“Й“e, fii yo on Й—uurno Й“e (on pelaani Й“e). ЖҠuurnee Й“e. Pellet, Й“e koЙ“e soЙ“e. JaaЖҙorde maЙ“Й“e nden ko Jahannama, njoЙ“di kon kobe laatinoo hiЙ“e paggitoo."
  9,96,"heЙ“e ngooЙ—ndirana on fii yo on mbele Й“e. Si on mblaama Й“e, pellet, Alla weletaake yimЙ“e yaltuЙ“e Й“e."
  9,97,"YimЙ“e ladde en hino Й“uri tiiЙ—ude keeferaaku e naafiaagu, Й“e Й“uri haandude kadi nde Й“e ngandataa keeri Й—i Alla jippini e NulaaЙ—o makko on. Alla ko AganduЙ—o, Г‘eeГұuЙ—o."
  9,98,"Hino e yimЙ“e ladde Й“en, on mo no jogitoo ko wintotoo kon sooyo, himo habbitanoo on jiilotooЙ—i bonЙ—i. Ko e dow maЙ“Й“e jiiotooЙ—i bonЙ—i (njanata). Alla ko Nanoowo, gannduЙ—o."
  9,99,"Hino e yimЙ“e ladde Й“en (fahin), on gooЕӢЙ—inoowo Alla e Г‘alaande sakkitiinde nden, o jogitora kon ko o nafqata Й“aЙ—torЙ—um ka Alla e [heЙ“ugol] du'aaji nulaaЙ—o on. Nnganndee Й—um ko Й“adorЙ—um (Alla) wonan de Й“e. Aray Alla naada Й“e ka Yurmeende makko. Pellet, Alla jaafotooЙ—o, jurmotooЙ—o."
  9,100,"ЖҒeen adinooЙ“e [gooЕӢЙ—inal] adiiЙ“e e ferЙ“e Й“een e weernuЙ“e wallitiiЙ“e Й“een, e Й“en jokkuЙ“e e Й“een no moЖҙЖҙiri, Alla welaama Й“e, kamЙ“e kadi Й“e mbelaama mo. o maranii Й“e Aljannaaji Й—i caatli ilata ley majji, ko Й“e duumotooЙ“e ton poomaa. Ko Й—uum woni malal mawnungal."
  9,101,"Hino e Й“een won Й“e banЕӢe mon jeyaaЙ“e e yimЙ“e ladde Й“en,naafigeeЙ“e,e yimЙ“e Madiina Й“een kadi.Й“e candolЙ—inii e naafigaagu.A anndaa Й“e, minen miЙ—en nganndi Й“e.Aray min lepta Й“e laabi Й—iЙ—i,refti Й“e nduttitee e lepte mawnuЙ—e."
  9,102,"E woЙ—Й“e goo, kirliiЙ“e bakkatuuji maЙ“Й“e Й—in, Й“e njilli gollal moЖҙЖҙal e goЙ—ngal bon gal. Hino tijja nde Alla jaЙ“anta Й“e tuubuubuyee.Pellet, Alla ko jaafoooЙ—o, jurmotooЙ—o."
  9,103,"Жіettu e jawЙ—eele maЙ“Й“e Й—en sadaka, laЙ“Й“iniraaЙ“e lootiraaЙ“e mo, ndu'anoЙ—aa Й“e. Pellet, du'aa maa ko deeЖҙere wonan de Й“e. Alla ko Nanoowo, gannduЙ—o."
  9,104,"E Й“e ngannda won de ko Alla no jaЙ“ana jeyaaЙ“e makko Й“en tuubuubuyee, himo jaЙ“a sadakaaji Й—in, e won de ko Alla woni JaЙ“oowo tuubuubuyee, ko jurmotooЙ—o."
  9,105,"Maaku : "ngollee, arma Alla yi'a golle mon Й—een, e nulaaЙ—o makko on e gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“een. Aray ruttita-Й—on ka gannduЙ—o ko wirni eko feeГұi Й—in, O humpita on ko ngollaynoЙ—on"."
  9,106,"E woЙ—Й“e goo ko nennanaaЙ“e e yamiroore Alla : immaa O lepta Й“e, maa O jaЙ“ana Й“e tuubuubuyee. Alla ko gannduЙ—o, Г‘eeГұuЙ—o."
  9,107,"ЖҒeen jogitorЙ“e juulirde fii lorra, e keefereegu, e senndude hakkunde gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“een, e tommbaade on kabuЙ—o Alla e nulaaЙ—o makko on ko adii. Pellet, heЙ“e ngooЙ—ndira : "min paandaaki si wanaa moЖҙЖҙere" Alla no seedii won de pellet, ko Й“e fenooЙ“e."
  9,108,"Wata a daro (juulugol) e mayre poomaa. Ko juulirde diidiraande kulol Alla gila ka arannde Гұalaande, Й“uri jojjude nde darotoЙ—aa e mun [juulaa]. Hino e mayre worЙ“e yiЙ—Й“e nde Й“e laЙ“Й“inotoo. Alla no yiЙ—i laЙ“Й“inotooЙ“e Й“en."
  9,109,"E ko on didirЙ—o maadi mu'un kulol Alla e welayee makko, Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude, kaa ko on didirЙ—o maadi mu'un e sera ngasko yirbuka, o yirbida e mayri ka Yiite Jahannama?! Alla feewnataa yimЙ“e tooГұooЙ“e Й“en."
  9,110,"Ndin maadi maЙ“Й“e ndi Й“e mahi seerataa ko ndi sikke ka Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e, si wanaa Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en taЖҙay tun. Alla ko gannduЙ—o, Г‘eeГұuЙ—o."
  9,111,"Pellet, Alla sooditirii e gooЙ—inЙ“e Й“en woЕӢkiiji maЙ“Й“e Й—in, e jawЙ—eele maЙ“Й“e Й—en won de no woodani Й“e Aljanna. HeЙ“e kaЙ“a fii laawol Alla ngol : heЙ“e mbara, heЙ“e mbaree. Ko fodoore goonga nde O fodi ka tawreeta, e ka Linjiila e Alqur'aana. Ko hommbo Й“uri Alla huuЙ“ngol ahdi mun? mbeltoree njeeygu mon ngu njeeeyondirЙ—on e mum : ko Й—uum woni malala mawnungal ngal."
  9,112,"Ko tuubooЙ“e Й“een, rewooЙ“e (Alla) Й“een, yettooЙ“e (Mo) Й“een, hoorooЙ“e Й“een, ruЖҙЖҙooЙ“e Й“een, sujjooЙ“e Й“een, yamirooЙ“e ko moЖҙЖҙi Й“een kaЙ—a ko boni, e reenotooЙ“e e keeri Alla Й—iin.weltin gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“een."
  9,113,"Haananaa Annabiijo on e Й“een gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e nde Й“e imsinantoo sirkooЙ“e Й“en, hay si Й“en laatike joomiraaЙ“e Й“adondiral, Й“aawo nde feeГұani Й“e won de koЙ“e yimЙ“e Jahiimi."
  9,114,"Imsinanagol Ibraahiima ngol baaaba makko wonaano si wanaa fodoore nde o fodannnoo mo. Tuma nde Й“anngannoo mo won de on ko gaГұo Alla, o daЙ—ndino(hisnii) mo. Pellet, Ibraahiima ko heewuЙ—o yankinaare, muГұГұiiЙ—o."
  9,115,"Alla siforaali majjinoowo yimЙ“e Й“aawo nde o feewni Й“e, haa O Й“annginana Й“e ko Й“e kaani reentaade e mu'um. Pellet, Alla ko gannduЙ—o kala huunde."
  9,116,"Pellet, Ko Alla woodani laamu kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin. Himo wuurna, himo wara. Alanaa on gah Alla giЙ—o, wanaa balloowo"
  9,117,"Wollahi Alla jaЙ“anii Annabiijo on tuubuubuyee, e ferЙ“e Й“een e walluЙ“e weerni Й“en jokkuЙ“e e saa'a saЙ—tuЙ—o, Й“aawo nde Й“erЙ—e woЙ—Й“e e maЙ“Й“e eЙ“Й“unoo ooГұaade. refti Alla jaЙ“ani Й“e tuubgol. Pellet, KaЕӢko ko O jaafotoooЙ—o, jumotooЙ—o Й“e."
  9,118,"[O jaЙ“anii tuubuubuyee on] kadi Й“een tato luutndiooЙ“e, haa leydi ndin faaЙ—ani Й“e e hoore ko ndi yaaji kon; woЕӢkiiji maЙ“Й“e Й—in Й“ittaniiЙ“e, Й“e fellitii won de moolorde e Alla aalaa si wanaa ka makko. refti o hawrindini Й“e e tuubuubuyee fii yo Й“e tuubu. Pellet, ko Alla woni jaЙ“oowotuubabuya, jurmotooЙ—o."
  9,119,"Eeymon gooЕӢЙ—iiЙ“e, kulee Alla laatodon e gooЕӢЙ—uЙ“e Й“een."
  9,120,"Haananaa yimЙ“e Madiina Й“een, e Й“een wonЙ“e sera maЙ“Й“e immorde e yimЙ“e ladde Й“en, nde Й“e luttitata Й“aawo NulaaЙ—o Alla on, wanaa nde Й“e yiЙ—atanta ko'e maЙ“Й“e Й“ura mo.Ko waЙ—i, noon ko heЙ“ataa Й“e, wanaa tampere, wanaa heege fii laawol Alla ngol, Й“e tippataa(yabbatah) e nokkuure tikkinaynde heeferЙ“e Й“een, Й“e kawrataa e gaГұo hawrannde, si wanaa Й“e mbinndante e Й—uum gollal moЖҙЖҙal. Pellet, Alla yeebataako njoЙ“di moЖҙЖҙinooЙ“e Й“een."
  9,121,"ЖҒe wintotaako(nafqatah) wintaari, famЙ—undi maa mawnundi, Й“e taЖҙataa aynde(joolol)=caatngol, si wanaa Й“e mbinndante Й—uum, fii yo Alla yoЙ“ Й“e ko Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude e ko Й“e ngollaynoo."
  9,122,"Haananaa gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“en nde Й“e njahata (jihaadi) Й“e fof maЙ“Й“e. Ko haЙ—no fedde kala e maЙ“Й“e yalta fii yo Й“e faamino ka diina, e fii yo Й“e jeertin yimЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“e si Й“e nduttitike e maЙ“Й“e, mbelejo'o, kamЙ“e Й“e ndeentoto."
  9,123,"Eehey mon yo gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e, kaЙ“ee Й“een Й“aЙ—iiЙ“e on immorde e heeferЙ“e Й“een; yo Й“e taw e mooЙ—on ГұaaЙ—re. ngnndon pellet Alla no won di e gooЕӢЙ—uЙ“e Й“een."
  9,124,"Si cortewol(simoore) jippinaama, hino e maЙ“Й“e on wi'oowo : "ko hommbo e mo'on woni ko ngol Й“eydi gooЕӢЙ—inal?" Ammaa Й“een gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e, ngol Й“eydu Й“e gooЕӢЙ—inal, kamЙ“e heЙ“e mbeltoo."
  9,125,"Ammma Й“een Й“een Гұawu woni ka Й“erЙ—e muen, ngol Й“eydu Й“e soЙ“e e hoore soЙ“e maЙ“Й“e, Й“e maayi ko Й“e heeferЙ“e."
  9,126,"E Й“ee njiaani won de kamЙ“e heЙ“e njarribee hitaande kala laawol maa laaЙ“i Й—iЙ—i? refti Й“e tuubataa, Й“e ngonnah waactotooЙ“e."
  9,127,"Si tawii cortewol jippinaama, yoga maЙ“Й“e ndaara yoga [Й“e mbi'a] : "Hara goЙ—Й—o no yi*a on?" refti Й“e haЙ“ana=pirlito. Alla firlitii Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e tawde ko Й“e yimЙ“e Й“e paamataa."
  9,128,"Mi wooЙ—ndi nulaaЙ—o arii e mooЙ—on, jeyaaЙ—o emon hino saЙ—ta e makko ko tampoton, deerЙ—uЙ—o e mooЙ—on, newaniiЙ—o hinnotooЙ—o(yurmotoodo) gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“een."
  9,129,"Si Й“e huccitii(nduЕӢtiima), maaku : "Alla yonii kam. Alaa deweteeЙ—o si wanaa KaЕӢko. Ko e makko mi fawii; ko KaЕӢko woni JeyЙ—o daЕӢkii mawnuЙ—o on"."
  10,1,"Alif, laam, Raa, Й—een ko aayeeje deftere ГұeГұaande ndeen."
  10,2,"Kere wonan yimЙ“e Й“een kaawasee, fii min wahyii- ma e gorko jeyaaЙ—o e maЙ“Й“e, wonВҙde : "jeertin yimЙ“e Й“e? mbeltiniraa gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“e wonВҙde no woodani Й“e nokku goongaajo ka Joomi maЙ“Й“e? heeeferЙ“e Й“e mbi : "oo ko mbileejo peeГұЙ—o"."
  10,3,"Pellet Joomi mon ko Alla on takЙ—o kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin ndeer balЙ—e jeegoo, refti o fotondiri ka dow Arsi, hombo toppitoo fiyakkuuji Й—in. Alaa woo e tefoowo si wanaa Й“aawo duЕӢayee makko. Ko on mo'on woni Joomi mooЙ—on, ndewee mbo. E on ciftorta?"
  10,4,"Ko ka makko woni ruttorde mon on denndaangal, ko fodoore Alla gooЕӢuЙ—nde! Ko kaЕӢko woni fuЙ—Й—ude tagoore nde, refti o ruttita nde fii yo o yoЙ“a Й“een gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“e ngolli golle moЖҙЖҙe e nunЙ—al. Й“een heeferЙ“e kan, hino woodani Й“e njaram immorde e fatayЙ—am, e lepte muusuЙ—e sabu ko Й“e laatinoo hiЙ“e njedda."
  10,5,"Ko kaЕӢko woni baЙ—Й—o naange ngen jalbunge e lewru ndun nurЙ—undu, o eЙ“Й“ani ndu jipporЙ—e fii yo on anndu emmbere duuЙ“i Й—in e limoore ndeen Alla tagiraani Й—iin si wanaa e goonga. hombo fensitana aayeeje Й—en yimЙ“e anndooЙ“e."
  10,6,"Hino e luutindirgol jemma e Гұalama ngol, e kon ko Alla tagi ka kammuuli e ka leydi, maandeeji wonanВҙde yimЙ“e gooЕӢЙ—uЙ“e."
  10,7,"ЖҒen Й“e njoortaaki hawrugol e amen, Й“e mbeltori nguurndam aduna Й—am, Й“e deeЖҙiri Й—am, e Й“een welsindiiЙ“e e aayeeje amen Й—een,"
  10,8,"ЖҒeen, jaaЖҙorde maЙ“Й“e nden ko Yiite ngen, sabu Й—uum ko Й“e paggittonoo."
  10,9,"Pellet, Й“een gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“e ngolli golle moЖҙЖҙe, joomi maЙ“Й“e feewnayЙ“e e gooЕӢЙ—inal maЙ“Й“e ngal. Caatli no ila ley maЙ“Й“e ka aljannaaji dokke."
  10,10,"Noddaandu maЙ“Й“e nder ton, ko "Ya Alla senaade woodaniima", salminaandu maЙ“Й“e ndu toon, ko : "Salaam", [kisal]. Ko woni wattannde noddaandu maЙ“Й“e, ko : "jettoore ngoodanii Alla, JeyЙ—o Winndere ndeen"."
  10,11,"Sinno Alla yaccinanayno yimЙ“e Й“en bone wano o yacciniranta Й“e moЖҙЖҙere, lajal maЙ“Й“e ngal timminanteno Й“e. min, ngacca Й“e Й“e tamЖҙinaaki kawrugol e amen e bewre maЙ“Й“e nde heЙ“e bumam-bumannoo."
  10,12,"Si lor memii neЙ—Й—aЕӢke o, o nodda min Й“aЕӢЕӢe makko, maa ko jooЙ—iiЙ—o, maa ko o dariiЙ—o. tuma nde min kuГұcini mo lor makko o, o feЖҙЖҙira wa si o noddaano min e lor memЙ—o mo. Ko wano noon Й“urtinooЙ“e Й“een cuЙ—iranaa ko ko Й“e ngollaynoo."
  10,13,"GooЕӢЙ—ii min kallkiino gire adinooЙ“e on nde Й“e tooГұnoo, nulaaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“een ngaddani Й“e Й“anngannduyeeji. Й“e wonaano gooЕӢЙ—inooЙ“e. Ko wana nii min njoЙ“irta yimЙ“e bonЙ“e Й“een."
  10,14,"Refti min mbaЙ—i on lomtotooЙ“e ka leydi Й“aawo maЙ“Й“e, ha min ndaara no ngollirton."
  10,15,"Si aayeeje amen Й“annguЙ—e Й—een njanngaama e dow maЙ“Й“e, Й“een Й“e tamЖҙinaaki kawrugol e amen mbi'a: "Addu Alqur'aanaare goo hara wanaa ndee Й—oo" maa "wostonde". maaku : haananaa kam nde mi waЙ—titira nde immorde e Й“aЕӢЕӢe wonkii am. mi jokkataa si wanaa kon ko wahayinaa e am. min miЙ—o huli si mi yeddii joomi am, lepte Гұalaande mawnde"."
  10,16,"Maaku : "Sinno Alla muuyuno, mi janngataano nde e dow mooЙ—on, mi aanndintaande mon kadi. GooЕӢЙ—ii mi ГұiiЙ“iino e mooЙ—on nguurndamado may- re. e on haqqiltaa?"."
  10,17,"Alaa Й“urЙ—o tooГұude haa hewta on pekifindiiЙ—o fenaande e hoore Alla, maa o yenni aayeeje makko Й—een. Si ko woni, o malnatah bonЙ“e Й“en."
  10,18,"HeЙ“e ndeewa ga Alla Й—uum ko lorrataa Й“e nafataa Й“e, heЙ“e mbi'a : "Ko Й—ii Й—oo ngoni tefanooj amen Й—i ka Alla". Maaku : "E on njweetoto Alla ko o anndaa ka kammuuli wanaa ka leydi?" Senayee woodanii mo, O toowii gaay e ko Й“e sirkata."
  10,19,"YimЙ“e Й“e laatanooki si wanaa mofte goote. ЖҒe lurri. Sinno wanaa konngol adinoo ngol immorde ka Joomi maa, Гұaaweteno hakkunde maЙ“Й“e e Й—uum ko Й“e lurraynoo."
  10,20,"HeЙ“e mbia : "Ko haЙ—noo aaya njiippinee e makko immorde ka Joomi makko?" Maaku : "ngannde ko wirnii kon ko Alla woodanii.padee; min komi patЙ—o wonndude e mo'on"."
  10,21,"Si minn meeЙ—inirii yimЙ“e Й“e yurmeende Й“aawo lorra memnooka Й“e, jaka yoo heЙ“e mari pewje e aayeeje amen Й—een. Maaku : "Ko Alla Й“uri yaawude pewjugol". Pellet, NulaaЙ“e amen Й“en heЙ“e mbinnda kon ko pewjoton."
  10,22,"Ko kaЕӢko woni doginoowo on ka njorndi e ka maayo, haa si on wonii ka laaЙ—e, Й—e ndoknira Й“e henndu laaЙ“ndu, Й“e weltora ndu. Ara e majje henndu bippooru, mollooЙ—e (bempejje) Й—en ara e maЙ“Й“e immorde e kala baЕӢЕӢe, Й“e pellita wonВҙde kamЙ“e Й“e huЙ“indaama, Й“e toroo Alla ko Й“e laЙ“Й“inana mo diina kan, [Й“e mbi'a]: "Si a daЙ—ndii amen e Й—um Й—oo, pellet, men laatoday e yettooЙ“e [ma] Й“een."
  10,23,"ЖҒaawo nde o daЙ—ndi Й“e, e jaka yoo kamЙ“e heЙ“e bewira ko leydi ko adaa e goonga. eehey mon yimЙ“e, ngandee bewre mon nden yantay e woЕӢkiiji mon. Ko dakamme nguurndam aduna. refti ko ka amen woni rutorde mon, min kaalano on ko laatino hoЙ—on ngolla."
  10,24,"Nganndee misal nguurndam aduna Й—am, ko wano ndiyam Й—am minn njippini immorde ka kammu, puЙ—i leydi ndin jillondira e majjam Й—um ko yimЙ“e e neemoraaЙ—i Гұaamata. Haa si ndi leydi ndi Жҙettii cuЙ—aari mayri ndi cuЙ—ike, yimЙ“e mayri Й“en jikka wonВҙde ko Й“e hattamЙ“e (soГұugol) e mayri, yami- roore amen ardira e mayri jemma maa Гұalorma, minn mbaЙ—a (puЙ—i) Й—in soГұaaЙ—i wa si tawii Й—i moЖҙ- Жҙaano hanki mun. Ko wano nii min fensitirta aayeeje Й—e wonanВҙde yimЙ“e miijitotooЙ“e Й“en."
  10,25,"Alla no nodda on faade e galle kisal, hombo fewna on mo o muyyi faade e laawol pocciingol ngol."
  10,26,"Hino woodani Й“een moЖҙЖҙimЙ“e (golle) moЖҙЖҙere e Й“eydaari. Nduggu hippataa geece maЙ“Й“e Й—en, wanaa kadi koyeera. Ko Й“en woni yimЙ“e Aljanna Й“en, kamЙ“e ko Й“e duumotooЙ“e ton."
  10,27,"ЖҒeen faggitiiЙ“e boneeji Й—in, njoЙ“di bone ko yeru makko. Koyeera hippay Й“e, Alanaa Й“e immorde ka Alla hay daЙ—ndoowo, A sikkay jeece maЙ“Й“e Й—en ko hippiraa ko taЖҙontinnde jemma niЙ“Й“utЙ—o. Ko Й“een ngoni yimЙ“e yiite, kamЙ“e ko luttooЙ“e toon."
  10,28,"Г‘ande min mooЙ“indirta Й“e denndaangal, refti min mbi'ana Й“ene sirkunooЙ“e : "ngonee e nokku mon, onon e kafidiiЙ“e mon." min senndindira hakkunde maЙ“Й“e, kafidiiЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en mbi'a : "wonaa minen ngonoЙ—on e rewde"."
  10,29,"Alla yonii seedee hakkunde amen e mon. Si ko woni, min laatinoke welsindiiЙ“e ga e dewe mon Й—en."
  10,30,"Ko Й—on woЕӢkii kala jarriborte ko ki ardinnoo. Й“e nduttee ka Alla giЙ—o maЙ“Й“e on ka goonga; ko Й“e ngonnoo e fefindaande kon majjira Й“e."
  10,31,"Maaku : "Ko hommbo arsikata on immorde ka kammu e ka leydi? Kaa ko hommbo jeyti nanЙ—e Й—en e giiЙ—e Й—en, ko hommbo kadi yaltinta ko wuuri e ndeer ko maayi, o yaltina ka maayi e nder ko wuuri, ko hommbo kadi yiilata fiyaaku on?" Й“e mbi'ay : "Ko Alla". Maaku : "e on kulatah?"."
  10,32,"Ko oon Й—oon mo'on Alla, woni jeyЙ—o on e goonga. Ko holЙ—um woni Й“aawo goonga si wanaa majjere? Ko honno pirlitirte Й—on?"
  10,33,"Ko wano nii konngol joomi maa ngol jojjiri e hoore yaltuЙ“e Й—oftaare Й“en :wonВҙde pellet, Й“e ngooЕӢЙ—intah."
  10,34,"Maaku : "Hara no e kafidiiЙ“e mon Й“en oon mb no fuЙ—Й—a tagoore refi o ruttita nde [Й“aawo maayde]?" Maaku :"Ko Alla fuЙ—Й—ata tagoore nde refti O ruttita nde Ko honno fefindara Й—on [faade e meere]?""
  10,35,"Maaku : "Hara no e kafidiiЙ“e mon Й“een on feewnoowo e goonga?" Maaku: "Alla no feewna e goonga. E ko on peewnoowo e goonga Й“uri haandude e jokkeede, kaa ko on mo feewanataa (hoore mon) si wanaa o feewna? Ko heЙ“i on sifa no Гұaawirton?"
  10,36,"Ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e maЙ“Й“e jokkah si wanah sikke. Pellet sikke Й—en nafataa e goonga kan hay e huunde. Pellet Alla ko gannduЙ—o ko Й“e ngollata."
  10,37,"Sellatah ka ndee Alqur'aanaa fefindiree gaanin Alla, si ko woni, ko nde gooЕӢginnde ko woni yeeso mayre, e fensitunde deftere, sikke alaa e mayre, ko nde immorde ka JeyЙ—o winndere nden."
  10,38,"Kaa Й“e mbiat : "o fekindi nde?" Maaku : "ngaddee cortewol(simoore) yeru mayre, noddon kala mo kattanЙ—on ga Alla, si on laatike gooЕӢЙ“e"."
  10,39,"Ko woni, Й“e njeddii ko Й“e kuЙ“indaaki ganndal mun, [ko Й“e fenniri nde], ko nde tawnoo firo mayre araani Й“e taho. Ko wano non adinooЙ“e Й“en fennirnoo. Ndaaru ko honno battane tooГұooЙ“e Й“en wa'unoo."
  10,40,"No e maЙ“Й“e gooЕӢЙ—inЙ—o nde, no e maЙ“Й“e kadi mo gooЕӢЙ—inaa nde. Ko Joomi maa Й“uri anndude bonnooЙ“e Й“een."
  10,41,"Si Й“e njeddii ma, maaku : "No woodani kam (njoЙ“di) golle am, no woodani on (njoЙ“di) golle mon. Onon ko on hisЙ“e ko mi gollata, min kadi ko mi kisЙ—o ko ngolloton"."
  10,42,"No e maЙ“Й“e Й“een heЙ—otooЙ“e ma. E ko annannta faaЙ—u Й“e Й“een, hay tawii Й“e haqqiltah?"
  10,43,"ino e maЙ“Й“e on ndaaroowo ma. e ko aan fewnata bumЙ—o oon, hay si wonii Й“e nji'atah?"
  10,44,"Pellet Alla tooГұirta yimЙ“e Й“een huunde, ko woni, ko yimЙ“e Й“e tooГұata ko'e muen."
  10,45,"Г‘ande o mooЙ“oyta Й“e, wa'ata kona si Й“e ГұiiЙ“aano si wanaa sa'a gooto e Гұalawma, heЙ“e nganndandira hakkunde maЙ“Й“e. GooЕӢЙ—ii Й“een yedduЙ“e kawral Alla ngal sooyii, Й“e ngonaano feewЙ“e."
  10,46,"Si min kollii ma yoga e ko ko min podaniЙ“e, maa Й—uum min Жҙettitii ma, (fow e mun), ko faade ka amen woni ruttorde maЙ“Й“e. refti Alla ko ceediiЙ—o e ko Й“e ngollata ko."
  10,47,"Hino woodani mofte kala nulaaЙ—o. Si nulaaЙ—o maЙ“Й“e on arii, Гұaawiree hakkunde maЙ“Й“e nuunЙ—al, kamЙ“e Й“e tooГұetaake."
  10,48,"HeЙ“e mbi'a: "Ko honnde tuma woni ndee fodoore, si on laatike gooЕӢguЙ“e?""
  10,49,"Maaku : "mi waawanaa hoore am lorra wanaa nafa si wanaa ko Alla muuyi. Hino woodani mofte kala lajal. Si lajal maЙ“Й“e ngal arii, Й“e neeЙ“nirantaake saa'a Й“e ngardinantaake kadi"."
  10,50,"Maaku : "kaalaneekam, si lepte makko Й—e ngarii e mon jemma maa Гұalawma, ko holЙ—um bonЙ“e Й“e hawjiranta Й—e?""
  10,51,"E ko tuma Й—e yani ngooЕӢЙ—in ton Й—e? e ko jooni noon, gooЕӢЙ—ii on laatinoke heГұaniiЙ“e Й—um?"
  10,52,"Refti tooГұЙ“e Й“en mbi'anee : "meeЙ—ee lepte luttugol. hara on njoЙ“ete si wanaa kon ngonnoЙ—on e faggitaade?""
  10,53,"HeЙ“e kabrino maa : "Й—uum ko goonga?" maaku : "Ko non, mi wooЙ—ndirii joomi am, pellet ko Й—e goonga. on ngonaani roЕӢkinooЙ“e"."
  10,54,"Sinno tabitanno kala woЕӢkii tooГұki jeyno ko woni leydi, ki sottorayno Й—um. Й“e cuuЙ—i nimse Й—een Й“aawo nde Й“e nji'i lepte Й—e. Гұaawiree hakkunde maЙ“Й“e nuunЙ—al, kamЙ“e Й“e tooГұetaake."
  10,55,"Ngandee ko Alla woodani ko woni ka kammuuli e ka leydi. Ngandee pellet, fodoore Alla nde ko goonga. Kono ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e yimЙ“e he Й“e nganndaa."
  10,56,"KaЕӢko Hombo wuurna hombo wara; ko faade ka makko nduttoteЙ—on."
  10,57,"Eehey mon yimЙ“e, gooЕӢЙ—ii waaju arii e mon immorde e Joomi mon, e lekki fii (Гұabbuuji) ko woni e Й“erЙ—e, e peewal, e yurmeende wonannanВҙde gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“e."
  10,58,"Maaku : "[Ko addan-mi on kon] ko Й“ural Alla e yurmeende makko; yo Й“e mbeltor Й—um Й—on. Ko Й—uum Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude ko Й“e mooЙ“ata"."
  10,59,"Maaku : "kaalaneekam, Й—uum ko Alla jippinani on e arsike, mbaЙ—Й—Й—on e mun ko harmi e ko dagii? -maaku : "Ko Alla duЕӢanii on? kaa ko e Alla pekintoЙ—on (penaale)?""
  10,60,"Ko holЙ—uum woni sikke Й“een fekindotooЙ“e fenaande e Alla, Г‘ande Darngal? Pellet, Alla ko Joom Й“ural e dow yimЙ“e Й“en. Kono ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e maЙ“Й“e njettatah (dokkem Й—e)."
  10,61,"A wonatah e fiyaaku, a janngataa e mayre e janngannde (alqur'aana), on ngollataa e gollal si wanaa minn ngoonat seediiЙ“e e mooЙ—on tuma nde ngonoton e mun. Wirnotaako gaay e joomi maa yeru abbere jarra, wonaa ka leydi wonaa ka kam- mu; wonaa ko Й“uri Й—um famЙ—ude, wonaa ko Й“uri mawnude si wonaa no e ndeer deftere Й“anngunde.(feeГұnde).."
  10,62,"Nganndee yimЙ“e Alla Й“e, kulol alanaa Й“e, Й“e ngonah sunoytooЙ“e."
  10,63,"ЖҒeen gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e, Й“e ngoni hulooЙ“e [Alla]."
  10,64,"Hino woodani Й“e welo-welo ka nguurndam aduna e ka laakara. - Alaa bayloowo konnguЙ—i Alla Й—in -. Ko Й—um woni malal mawngal."
  10,65,"Wota konngol maЙ“Й“e sunine. Pellet, teddungal ngal denndaangal ko Alla woodani. Ko kaЕӢko woni Nanoowo, gannduЙ—o."
  10,66,"Nganndee ko Alla heeranii Й“een wonЙ“e ka kammuuli e Й“een wonЙ“e ka leydi. eko Й“een noddooЙ“e gah Alla njokkaani e kafidiiЙ“e? Й“e jokkaani si wonaa sikke, Й“e ngoonaani si wonaa fenooЙ“e."
  10,67,"Ko KaЕӢko woni baЙ—anЙ—o on jemma on fii yo on ndeeЖҙ e maako, e Гұalawma on jii'rЙ—o. Pellet, wonii e Й—um maandeeji wonannВҙde yimЙ“e nanooЙ“e."
  10,68,"ЖҒe mbi'i : "Alla jogitike Й“iЙ—Й—o". Senaade woodanii mo! Ko KaЕӢko woni galo jon diЙ—iiЙ—o on. Hino woodani mo Й—uum ko woni ka kammuuli e Й—uum ko woni ka leydi; alanah on cemmbe e Й—uum. E on wowlay Alla ko on nganndaa?"
  10,69,"Maaku: "Pellet, Й“een fekindotooЙ“e fenaande e Alla Й“e maletaake"."
  10,70,"Ko dakamme ka aduna, refti ko ka amen woni ruttorde maЙ“Й“e nde refti min meeЙ—ina Й“e lepte cattuЙ—e Й—en sabu ko Й“e njeddiraynoo ko."
  10,71,"Janngan Й“e kabaaru Nuuhu, tuma nde o maakan-no yimЙ“e makko Й“en: "Ko onon yo yimЙ“e, si tawii ГұiiЙ“ugol am (hakkunde mon) mawnii e mon, e baa- jorgol lam Aayeeje Alla Й—e, ko e Alla woni ko mi fawii. Haray pellitee fiyaaku mon on, e kafidiiЙ“e mon Й“een. refti wota fiyaaku mon on wonan on ko mugii. refti pewjanon kam (ko paalaЙ—on), wota on neeЙ“tinanam."
  10,72,"Si on nduЕӢtiima, mi lamndaaki on njoЙ“di, njoЙ“di am ndi wonaani si wonaa ka Alla. mi yamiraama nde mi laatotoo e jebbiliiЙ“e Й“een"."
  10,73,"ЖҒe njeddi mo. minn daЙ—ndi mo kaЕӢko e wondiiЙ“e makko Й“een ka laana. min mbaЙ—i Й“e lomtotooЙ“e (e leydi). min njooli Й“een yeddunooЙ“e Aayeeje amen Й—en. Ndaar ko honno battane jertinaaЙ“e (salii) Й“een waЙ—i."
  10,74,"Refti minn immini Й“aawo makko nulaaЙ“e haa e yimЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en. ЖҒe ngaddani Й“e Й“anngannduyeeji. ЖҒe ngonaano gooЕӢЙ—inooЙ“e sabu ko njeddiri Й—uum ko ko adii. Ko wano nii min notirta e Й“erЙ—e Й“een jaggituЙ“e.(yawtuЙ“e keeri)."
  10,75,"Refti minn immini Й“aawo maЙ“Й“e Muusaa e Haaruuna haa e Fir'awna e mbatu mun, won`dude e Aayeeje amen Й—en. ЖҒe mawnikini, Й“e ngoni yimЙ“e bonЙ“e."
  10,76,"Nde goonga kan ari e maЙ“Й“e immorde e amen, Й“e mb'i : "Й—um Й—oo ko mbilewu peeГұngu"."
  10,77,"Muusaa maaki: "E on mbi'anay goonga kan tuma ka ari e mon : E nee ko mbilewu nii? Hara le wiljuЙ“e Й“en maletaake"."
  10,78,"ЖҒe mbi'i : "E a ar e amen fii yo a yiltu amen e ko min tawri ko baabiraaЙ“e amen Й“e, mawngu ngun laatano on onon Й—iЙ—o ka leydi? Minen min ngonaani gooЕӢЙ—inooЙ“e on"."
  10,79,"Fir'awna wi'i : "ngaddanee kam kala bileejo agannduЙ—o"."
  10,80,"Nde wileeЙ“e Й“een ngarnoo, Muusaa maakani Й“e : "Bugee(mberne) ko bugotoЙ—on kon"."
  10,81,"Tuma nde Й“e buginoo, Muusaa maaki : "Kon ko ngadduЙ—on ko ko mbilewu, pellet, Alla bonnay Й—um. Pellet, Alla moЖҙЖҙintah golle bonnooЙ“e Й“een"."
  10,82,"Alla no tabintinira Goonga kan KonnguЙ—i makko Й—in, hay si bonЙ“e Й“en ngaГұii."
  10,83,"GooЕӢЙ—inaano Muusaa si wanaa geГұngol( Й“esngu)e yimЙ“e makko Й“en, sabu kulol Fir'awna e mbatu maЙ“Й“e ngun, nde Й“e fitinta Й“e. Pellet, Fir'awna ko townintinooЙ—o ka leydi, pellet, ko e fantimЙ“e Й“en o jeyaa."
  10,84,"Muusaa maaki: "Eehey mon yimЙ“e am, si on laatike goosЙ—inЙ“e Alla, haray ko e Makko pawotoЙ—on si on laatike jebbiliiЙ“e"."
  10,85,"ЖҒe mb'i : "Ko e Alla min koolori. Joomi amen, wota waЙ— amen fitina wonanВҙde tooГұooЙ“e Й“een."
  10,86,"DaЙ—ndiraa men yurmeende maa nden e yimЙ“e heeferЙ“e Й“een"."
  10,87,"Min wahayini faade e Muusaa e neene-gooto makko on, wonВҙde: "njippinee yimЙ“e mon Й“en Misra e cuuЙ—i, mbaЙ—on cuuЙ—i mon Й—in fewtuЙ—i (qibla), ГұiiЙ“non julde nden. mbeltinaa gooЕӢЙ—iinЙ“e Й“en"."
  10,88,"Muusaa maaki: "Joomi amen, A okkii Fir'awna e mbatu mum ngu cuЙ—aari e jawЙ—eele ka nguurndam aduna, Joomi amen, fii yo Й“e majjin gaay e laawol Maa ngol. Joomi amen, mehu(momtu) jawЙ—eele maЙ“Й“e Й—en, uddaa Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en, hara Й“e ngooЕӢЙ—intaa haa Й“e nji'a lepte muusЙ—e Й—een"."
  10,89,"O daali: "GooЕӢЙ—ii toraare mon nden jaabinaama. Г‘iiЙ“ee (e diina), wota on njokku laawol Й“een Й“e nganndaa"."
  10,90,"Min lummbini Й“iЙ—Й“e Israa'iila Й“en maayo ngon. Fir'awna konu mun ngun njokkitiri Й“e bewre e jaggitere. Haa nde joolagol ngol hewtitii mo, o wi'i: "mi gooЕӢЙ—inii wonВҙde deweteeЙ—o Alla si wonaa on mo Й“iЙ—Й“e Israa'iila Й“en ngooЕӢЙ—ini. min ko mi jeyaaЙ—o e jebbiliiЙ“e Й“een".(juulЙ“e Й“e)."
  10,91,"E ko jooni non? GooЕӢЙ—ii a yeddiino ko ado, njeyaya-Й—aa e bonnooЙ“e Й“een."
  10,92,"Hannde minn daЙ—dnirte Й“anndu maa ndun, fii yo a wonan Й“een arooЙ“e Й“aawo maaЙ—a tasakuyee. Pellet, ko Й—uuЙ—i e yimЙ“e Й“en gaay e aayeeje amen Й—en ko welsindiiЙ“e."
  10,93,"GooЕӢЙ—ii minn weernii Й“iЙ—Й“e Israa'iila Й“en weerde teddunde, min arsike Й“e immorde e laaЙ“uЙ—i. ЖҒe lurraali haa nde ganndal ngal ari e maЙ“Й“e. Pellet, Joomi maa Гұaawoya hakkunde maЙ“Й“e Г‘ande Darngal, e kon ko Й“e luutondiraynoo e muuЙ—um."
  10,94,"Si a wonii e sikkitaare e Й—uum ko min njippinii e maaЙ—a, lanndii Й“en Й“e no jannga deftere nden ado maaЙ—a. GooЕӢЙ—ii goonga kan arii maa immorde ka Joomi maa, wata a jeye e Й“en sikkitiiЙ“e."
  10,95,"Wata a jeye e Й“een yedduЙ“e aayeeje Alla Й—en, laato-daa e sooyuЙ“e Й“een."
  10,96,"Pellet, Й“een Й“en konngol Joomi maa ngol jojji e mun Й“een Й“e ngooЕӢЙ—intah."
  10,97,"hay si arii e maЙ“Й“e kala aaya, haa Й“e nji'a lepte muusuЙ—e Й—een."
  10,98,"MeeЙ—aani laataade e hoЙ—o gooЕӢЙ—ingo, gooЕӢЙ—inal maЙ“Й“e nafi Й“e si wonaa yimЙ“e yuunusa Й“en. Nde Й“e ngooЕӢЙ—innoo, minn kuncanno Й“e lepte koyeera Й—en ka nguurndam aduna, min dakmiti Й“e haa e saanga."
  10,99,"Sinno Joomi maa muuyuno, wonЙ“e ka leydi Й“en fof ngooЕӢЙ—inayno. E an a doolay yimЙ“e haa Й“e ngoona gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e?"
  10,100,"Laatanaaki wooЕӢkii nde ki gooЕӢЙ—inta si wonaa e duЕӢayee Alla. Homo waЙ—a soЙ“e [lepte] Й—en e hoore Й“een Й“e kaqqiltaa."
  10,101,"Maaku: "Ndaaree ko holЙ—um woni ka kammuuli e ka leydi". aayeeje Й—e e jertinooje Й—e nafatah yimЙ“e Й“e ngooЙ—intaa Й“en."
  10,102,"Hara heЙ“e habbii si wonaa yeru ГұanЙ—e Й“en feЖҙЖҙunooЙ“e ado maЙ“Й“e? Maaku: "cabbitee, min miЙ—o wonndi e mo'on jeyaaЙ—o e sabbitiiЙ“e Й“en"."
  10,103,"Reft mnn ndaЙ—nda nulaaЙ“e amen Й“en e Й“een gooЕӢ-Й—inЙ“e. Ko woni non jojjiri e amen daЙ—ndugol gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“e."
  10,104,"Maaku: "eeheymon yimЙ“e, si on wonii e sikkitaare e diina am, (miin) mi rewataa Й—iin Й—i dewoton gaa nin Alla; ko mi rewata, ko Alla oon baroowo on. mi yamiraama nde mi laatotoo e gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“en"."
  10,105,"E wonВҙde : "Г‘iiЙ“in yeeso maa ngon diina kan ko o ooГұiiЙ—o, wata a wonu jeyaaЙ—o e sirkooЙ“e Й“een"."
  10,106,"Wota a noddu gah Alla, Й—uum ko nafatah ma lorrataa ma. Si a waЙ—ii (Й—uum), an dey haray a jeyaama ontuma e tooГұooЙ“e Й“een"."
  10,107,"Si Alla meminirii ma lorra, alaa kГұuncoowo mo si wonaa KaЕӢko. Si o faandike e maaЙ—a moЖҙЖҙere, alaa duttoowo Й“ural makko ngal. Homo memina nde on mo o muuyi e jeyaaЙ“e makko Й“een. Ko KaЕӢko woni jaafotooЙ—o, jurmotooЙ—o on."
  10,108,"Maaku : "Eehey mon yimЙ“e, gooЕӢЙ—ii goonga ka arii mon immorde ka Joomi mon. Kala peewuЙ—o, e haray ko hoore-makko o feewani; kala kaadi majju- Й—o, haray ko e makko defii. min wonaani pawaaЙ—o e hoore-mon."
  10,109,"Jokku ko wona ko e wahayineede ko e maaЙ—a, muГұГұo-Й—aa haa Alla Гұaawa. Ko KaЕӢko woni Й“urЙ—o moЖҙЖҙude e ГұaawooЙ“e."
  11,1,"Alif, Laam, Raa, ko deftere nde aayeeje mun ГұeГұaa refti Й—e fensitaa immorde e oon Г‘eeГұo kumpitiiЙ—o."
  11,2,"wota on ndw si winaa Alla.min dee komi jeertinoo jeertinoowo ummaade e makko, beltinoowo"
  11,3,"E nde imsintoЙ—on Joomi mon; refti tuubanon mo. O dakmita on dakamme labaaЙ—o haa e lajal innangal o jonna kala jom Й“ural Й“ural makko ngal. Si on nduЕӢtiima, haray min mi hulanii on lepte Гұalaande mawnde."
  11,4,"Ko ka Alla woni ruttorde mon. KaЕӢko ko O kattanЙ—o kala huunde."
  11,5,"Nganndee Й“een Й—oon Й“e cowa Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en fii yo Й“e cuuЙ—o e makko. Nganndee fewndo Й“e cuddotortnoo comci maЙ“Й“e Й—in, Homo anndi ko Й“e cuuЙ—ata e ko Й“e peГұГұinta. Pellet ko O gannduЙ—o ko woni e Й“erЙ—e Й—en."
  11,6,"Alaa e ruugayngel ka leydi si wanah ko Alla fawtii arsike maggel on, Homo anndi ГұiiЙ“irde maggel e daakorde maggel; fof no e deftere Й“anngunde. FeeГұnde"
  11,7,"Ko KaЕӢko tagi kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin nder balЙ—e jeegoo, hari arsi makko kin no ka hoore ndiyam, fii yo o ndaarndo on ko hommbo e mo'on Й“urata moЖҙЖҙinnde gollal. Pellet si a wi'i: "onon ko on ummintinteeЙ“e Й“aawo maayde", maa heeferЙ“e Й“en mbi'u: "Й—um wonaani si wonaa mbilewu peeГұngu"."
  11,8,"Pellet si min neeЙ“aniiЙ“e lepte Й—en haa e dumunna limaaЙ—o, maa Й“e mbi'u: "Ko tonngi Й—e?" nganndee Гұande nde arat e mabЙ“e, Й“e wonataa sureteeЙ“e e majje; jippoo e maЙ“Й“e Й—uum ko laatinoo heЙ“e njalkita."
  11,9,"Si tawii min meeЙ—inii neЙ—Й—aЕӢke on dokke immornde ka amen, refti min Й“oori nde e makko, kaЕӢko ko otaЖҙiido, yeddoowo."
  11,10,"Si tawii kadi minn meeЙ—inirii mo dokke Й“aawo lorra memЙ—o mo, maa o wi'oy : "Satteende nden iwii e am", kaЕӢko (ontuma) ko o beltiiЙ—o, ГұaaЖҙoowo."
  11,11,"Si wonaa Й“een muГұГұii Й“e, Й“e ngolli golle moЖҙЖҙe. Й“een Й—oon, no woodani Й“e haforanal e njoЙ“di mawndi."
  11,12,"Yaamajo'o ko a accoowo yoga ko wahayinaa e maaЙ—a, Й“ernde maa nden Й“iЙ—tora Й—um; fii heЙ“e mb'i: "Ko haЙ—no ngalu jippinee e makko? maa Malaa'ika arda e makko?" Anndu an ko a jertinoowo. Alla ko deenoowa kala huunde."
  11,13,"Kaa Й“e mbi'at : "O fekindi nde?" Maaku : "ngaddee Corteeji( cimooje) sappo yeru mayre, pekindaaЙ—e, noddon kala mo haЙ—tanЙ—on gaanin Alla, si on laatike gooЕӢЙ—uЙ“e"."
  11,14,"Si Й“e njaabitaaki on, ngnndee wonВҙde ko nde jippinira ko ganndal Alla, e wonВҙde deweteeЙ—o alaa si wanaa KaЕӢko. Hara onon ko on jebbiliiЙ“e?"
  11,15,"Kala on tawЙ—o ko nguurndam aduna e cuЙ—aari majjam faandii, min humnanay Й“e golle maЙ“Й“e Й—en ton, hara kamЙ“e Й“e ustantaake ton."
  11,16,"Ko Й“een ngoni Й“e alanah Й—um en ka laakara si wanaa Yiite. Ko Й“e ngolli ton kon firtii, ko meere woni koЙ“e ngollaynoo."
  11,17,"E ko oon laatiiЙ—o e Й“anngannduyee immorde ka Joomi makko, homo janngande mo seediiЙ—o immorde ka makko, e nde aditiinde mo [kaЕӢko Muhammadu], deftere Muusaa nden ardiinde e yurmeende [Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude diini ko alah hujja kon?]: ЖҒen Й—on hino gooЕӢЙ—ini nde; kala on jedduЙ—o nde e feddeeji Й—in, ko Yiite ngen woni fodoore makko. wota a laato e sikke fii mayre. Pellet ko nde goonga immornde ka Joomi maa; ko woni tun, ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e yimЙ“e Й“en gooЕӢЙ—intaa."
  11,18,"Alaambo Й“uri tooГұde Й“uri on pekandiido fenaa- nde e Alla? Й“een Й—oon kolliroyte ka Joomi maЙ“Й“e, (malaleykaaji) seediiЙ“e Й“en mbi'a: "Ko Й“ee Й—oo pennoo e Joomi maЙ“Й“e". Hey, kuddi Alla ndin wonii e tooГұooЙ“e Й“een."
  11,19,"ЖҒeen falotooЙ“e ga e laawol Alla ngol, Й“e Й—aЙ“Й“ana ngol ooГұorde, hara kadi ko Й“e yedduЙ“e laakara."
  11,20,"ЖҒeen Й“e ngonaani laawotooЙ“e ka leydi, laatanaaki Й“e kadi weldiiЙ“e gaanin Alla, heЙ“e cowayanee lepte Й—een. ЖҒe laatanooki hattanЙ“e nangol, Й“e ngonaano kadi yi'ooЙ“e."
  11,21,"Ko Й“e ngoni sooyinЙ“e woЕӢkiiji mun Й—in. Й—uum ko Й“e pekintonoo majji gaay e maЙ“Й“e."
  11,22,"Sikke alah, won`de Й“en Й—on ka laakara, ko kamЙ“e Й“uroyta sooyude."
  11,23,"ЖҒeen gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e, Й“e ngolli golle moЖҙЖҙe, Й“e njankinanii Joomi maЙ“Й“e, ko Й“e ngoni yimЙ“e Aljanna Й“en, kamЙ“e ko Й“e duumotooЙ“e toon."
  11,24,"Misal peЙ—le Й—iЙ—i Й—e: ko wano bumЙ—o e pahЙ—uЙ—o, e ji'oowo e nanoowo. E Й“ee Й—oo Й—iЙ—i fotat e misal? E on mbaajitotaako?"
  11,25,"Wollahi min nuliri Nuuhu e yimЙ“e makko Й“en: "miin wonanВҙde on ko mi jertinoowo Й“annginЙ—o.(peeГұЙ—o.)"
  11,26,"wonВҙde wota on ndew si wanah Alla. min miЙ—o hulani on lepte Гұalaande muВҙusnde"."
  11,27,"Mbatu Й“een yedduЙ“e e yimЙ“e makko Й“en mbi'i: min nji'aani ma si wonah ko a Й“anndiЕӢke sifa amen, men nj'aani kadi Й“en jokkuЙ“e ma si wo- naa jaasЙ“e amen faaЙ—uЙ“e feere, men nji'anaani on e amen Й“ural. Worin miЙ—en cikki ko on fenooЙ“e"."
  11,28,"O maaki: "eehey mon yo yimЙ“e am, kaalnee kam si tawii miЙ—o e Й“anngannduyee immorde ka Joomi am, O weeЙ—ii kam yurmeende (Annabaaku) immorde ka makko, Й—uum wumna e mooЙ—on, e min mbaaw- nay on nde hara ko on aГұЙ“e nde?""
  11,29,"Eeheymon yo yimЙ“e am, mi laЙ“ndaaki on jawdi e Й—uum. NjoЙ“di am wonaani si wonah ka Alla. min mi wonaani raЙ—otooЙ—o Й“en gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e, kamЙ“e ko Й“e hawroyooЙ“e Joomi maЙ“Й“e. Ko woni tun, min mi yi'ii on yimЙ“e majjuЙ“e."
  11,30,"Eehey mon yimЙ“e am, ko hommbo walloytammi ka Alla si mi raЙ—ike Й“e? E on mbaajitotaako?"
  11,31,"Mi wi'antah on miЙ—o mari ngaluujii Alla, mi annah kadi ko wirnii, mi wi'ataa wonВҙde ko mi maleyko, mi wi'antaa Й“een Й“e gite mon Й—en yawi, Alla okkoytaa-Й“e moЖҙЖҙere; ko Alla Й“uri anndude ko woni e woЕӢkiiji maЙ“Й“e. miin ontuma [si mi waЙ—ii Й—um], haray ko mi jeyaaЙ—o e tooГұЙ“e Й“een."
  11,32,"ЖҒe mbi'i: "Ko an yo Nuuhu, gooЕӢЙ—ii a wenjidii e amen, a Й—uЙ—Й—inii yeddondiral ngal e amen. Addan men Й—uum ko pod-Й—aa amen, si a laatike jeyaaЙ—o e goonguЙ“e Й“e"."
  11,33,"o maaki: "nganndee ko Alla addanta on Й—e -si o muuyii- on ngonaani roЕӢkinooЙ“e."
  11,34,"LaaЙ“al-reedu am nafatah on, si mi faandike laaЙ“angol on, si tawii Alla no faandii bewnugol on (majjina). Ko KaЕӢko woni Joomi mon, ko ka makko woni ruttorde mon."
  11,35,"Si ko woni, Й“e mbay : o fekindi-nde. Maaku: "Si mi fekindi nde, haray bonnere am nden no fawii kam. min no ko mi daЙ—ndiiЙ—o ko mbonnoton kon"."
  11,36,"Wahayinaa e Nuuhu wonВҙde : "GooЕӢЙ—intah e yimЙ“e maa Й“en si wanaa Й“en gooЕӢЙ—innooЙ“e. Wota a suno e ko Й“e ngollaynoo"."
  11,37,"MoЖҙЖҙin laana kan e ndeenka amen e yamiroore amen. Wota a yewtidoy e am fii Й“en tooГұЙ“e, kamЙ“e ko Й“e yoolotooЙ“e."
  11,38,"Homo moЖҙЖҙina laana kan. Tuma kala nde dental hoorewal rewi ka o moЖҙЖҙinta ton, Й“e jalkita mo. o maaki: "Si on jalkitii men, minen kadi min njalkitoyay on wano njalkitirton [men non]"."
  11,39,"Arma nde ngannduЙ—on ko hommbo lepte koynatЙ—e aroyat e muuЙ—um, lepte duumiiЙ—e njippoo e makko."
  11,40,"Haa si yamiroore amen nden aroyii, huЙ“Й“inirЙ—e Й—en fati, min daali: "Roondo e makka kala nooneeji Й—iЙ—i resindirayЙ—i e Й“eynguure maa nden -si wanaa Й“en konngol lepte ngol adii e mu'un- e Й“en gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e". GoosЙ—inaano won`dude e makko si wonah seeЙ—aaЙ“e."
  11,41,"O maaki: "mbaЙ—Й—ee e makka e Innde Alla ka dogugol makka e daragol makko. Pellet Joomi am ko kaforoowo jurmotooЙ—o"."
  11,42,"Kan no dogida e maЙ“Й“e e mollooЙ—e waaЙ—e wa pelle. Nuuhu noddi Й“iЙ—Й—o makko on, hari on no serindi: "eehey ma yo Й“inngel am, waЙ—Й—ida e amen, wata a wonВҙdu e yedduЙ“e Й“een"."
  11,43,"O wi'i: "Mi Жҙawoyay e fello daЙ—ndayngo kam ndiyam Й—am". O maaki: "DaЙ—oowo yamiroore Alla nden alaa hannde si wanah oon Mo O yurmini". Molloonde nden heedi hakkunde maЙ“Й“e, o laatodii e yoolaaЙ“e Й“en."
  11,44,"Wi'a: "eeyma leydi, moЙ— ndiyam maa Й—am! eeyma kadi yo kammu, jogito [sorombooji ndiyam Й—in]!". Ndiyam Й—am Й“eeЙ“i, fiyaaku on Гұaawaa, [laana] kan daroyii ka dow fello juudiiy, wi'aa: "Halkaare woodanii Й“en yimЙ“e tooГұЙ“e"."
  11,45,"Nuuhu noddi Joomi makko, o maaki: "Joomi am, pellet Й“iЙ—Й—o am on ko jeyaaЙ—o e Й“eynguure am, pellet fodoore maa nde ko goonga. Ko aan Й“uri nuunЙ—ude Гұaawoore ГұaawooЙ“e"."
  11,46,"O daali: "Ko an yo Nuuhu, pellet on jeyaaka e Й“eynguure maa, nden (toraare) ko gollal ngal moЖҙЖҙaa. Wata a toro kam ko a alanaa Й—um ganndal. min miЙ—o waajo maa fii wata a jeye e majjuЙ“e Й“een"."
  11,47,"O maaki: "Joomi am, mi moolorike ma nde mi lanndoto maa huunde nde mi alanah Й—um ganndal. Si wanaa A hafranam yurmin ЖҠaa mi, mi jeyete e hayruЙ“e Й“en"(.pertuЙ“e)"
  11,48,"Wi'aa: "Ko an yo Nuuhu, jippor kisiyee immorde ka amen, e moЖҙЖҙi dow maaЙ—aa e mofte wonВҙduЙ“e e maaЙ—a. Mofte goo (no ton), aray min dakmita Й“e, refti memoya Й“e immorde e amen, lepte muusЙ—e"."
  11,49,"ЖҠii Й—oo ko jeyaaЙ—i e kabaruuji birniiЙ—i, miЙ—en wahayina Й—e e maaЙ—a. A anndaano Й—e an, wanaa yimЙ“e maa Й“en, ko adii Й—um. MuГұГұo, pellet battane moЖҙЖҙe Й—en woanii gooЕӢЙ—uЙ“e Й“en."
  11,50,"[minn Nulii] kadi faade e AadinkooЙ“e Й“en, musiЙ—Й—o maЙ“Й“e on Huudi. O maaki : "eeheymon yo yimЙ“e am, ndewee Alla, deweteeЙ—o alanah on ko woori mo. On ngonaani si wonaa fekindotooЙ“e"."
  11,51,"Eeheymon yimЙ“e am, mi laЙ“ndaaki on e Й—uum njoЙ“di. NjoЙ“di am wonaani si wonaa ka on takЙ—o lam. En on haqqiltaa?"
  11,52,"Eheymon yimЙ“e am, imsinee ka Joomi mon, refti tuubanon mo o jippina e mooЙ—on toЙ“o jokkondirn-ngo, o Й“eyda on cemmbe e hoore cemmbe mon Й—en. Wota on nduЕӢto ngono ko on bonЙ“e."
  11,53,"ЖҒe mbi'i: "eheymaHuudu, kala ko addan-Й—aa men e Й“anngannduyee, minen men wonaani accooЙ“e deweteeЙ—i amen Й—in fii konngol maa ngol, minen min ngonaani gooЕӢЙ—inooЙ“e ma"."
  11,54,"Min mb'atah si wanaa yoga e deweteeЙ—i amen Й—in meminirii ma bone". O maaki: "Min miЙ—o seedina Alla -seeditee onon kadi- wonВҙde min, ko mi daЙ—ndiiЙ—o e Й—uum ko sirkoton,"
  11,55,"ga makko. Pewjanee kam on denndaangal, refti wata on padiree kam."
  11,56,"Min mi fawike e Alla, Joomi am e Joomi mon. Alaa e ruugayngel si wanaa ko O nannguЙ—o jubuuru maggel. Pellet, Joomi am no e laawol poocciingol."
  11,57,"Si on nduЕӢtii, gooЕӢЙ—ii mi yottinanii kon ko mi nulidaa e mooЙ—on. Joomi am lomtinay yimЙ“e goo Й“e wonaa onon, on lorrirtaa mo hay e huunde. Pellet, Joomi am ko deeno kala huunde."
  11,58,"Nde yamiroore amen nden ari, min daЙ—ndiri Huudi e Й“en goosЙ—inЙ“e wonВҙduЙ“e e makko yurmeende amen. min daЙ—ndi Й“e lepte tiiЙ—Й—e."
  11,59,"ЖҒeen ko AadinkooЙ“e. e njedduno aayeeje Joomi amЙ“Й“e Й—en, Й“e yeddi NulaaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en, Й“e jokki yamiroore kala dunndaranke sanndolЙ—inЙ—o."
  11,60,"ЖҒe jokkindinaa ka aduna Й—oo, kuddi, e Г‘ande Darngal. ngnndee pellet, AadinkooЙ“e Й“en njeddi Joomi maЙ“Й“e. ngndee goЙ—Й—al woodanii Aadi'en, yimЙ“e Huudi."
  11,61,"[Men Nulii] kadi e Samuuda'en, musiЙ—Й—o maЙ“Й“e Saalih, o maaki: "eehey monyimЙ“e am, ndewee Alla. deweteeЙ—o alanaano on ko woori mo. Ko KaЕӢko fuЙ—Й—i on ka leydi, O wuurni on e mayri. Imsinanee mo, refti tuubon ka makko. Pellet Joomi am ko Й“aЙ—iiЙ—o, jaabotooЙ—o"."
  11,62,"ЖҒe mbi'i: "eeheyma Saalihu, gooЕӢЙ—ii a woniino hakkunde amen jaakoraaЙ—o ado Й—um Й—oo. E a haЙ—ay amen rewugol ko baabiraaЙ“e amen rewatno? Minen non, min ngonii e sikke e huunde nde noddataa amen e mun (sikke) jaaliiЙ—e"."
  11,63,"O maaki: "eeheymon yimЙ“e! Kaalanee kam, si mi laatike e Й“anngannduyee immorde ka Joomi am, O okkii kam immorde ka makko yurmeende, ko hommbo faabotoo mi ka Alla si mi yeddii mo? On Й“eydataa kam si wonaa hayrugol.perte"
  11,64,"Eeheymon yimЙ“e am, baa Й—oo ko ngelooba wonanВҙde on maande. Tertee mba, mba Гұaama e leydi Alla. Wata on memir-mba bone, lepte Й“aЙ—tiiЙ—e keЙ“a on"."
  11,65,"ЖҒe mborii-ba. o maaki: "ndakmitee ka galleeji mon balЙ—e tati! ЖҠuum ko fodoore nde fennetaake"."
  11,66,"Nde yamiroore Alla nden arunoo, min daЙ—ndiri Saalihu e Й“en gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e wonВҙduЙ“e e makko, yur-meende immorde ka amen- e koyeera nden Гұande Pellet Joomi maa, ko KaЕӢko woni cemmbinЙ—o, pooluЙ—o."
  11,67,"Haacaango ngoon nanngi tooГұuЙ“e Й“een.ЖҒe waЙ—tini ka galleeji maЙ“Й“e jicciiЙ“e.(jusЙ“e)."
  11,68,"A sikkay Й“e ГұiiЙ“aano Й—oon. Nganndee pellet Samuudu en njedduno Joomi maЙ“Й“e, nganndee goЙ—Й—al yurmee- nde (Alla) woodanii Samuuda'en!"
  11,69,"GooЕӢЙ—ii NulaaЙ“e amen Й“een nggaddanii Ibraahiima welo-welo, Й“e mbi'i: "Kisal (e mon)". O maaki: "Kisal (e mon). NeeЙ“aani o ardi e ngaari juЙ—aandi."
  11,70,"Nde o yi'noo juuЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—een njottaaki ndi, o faytiЙ“e (o sikkitii), o soomi kulol e maЙ“Й“e. ЖҒe mbi'i: "Wota a hul, ko min nulaaЙ“e e yimЙ“e Luuti Й“een"."
  11,71,"Tawi cuddiiЙ—o makko on no darii, o jali, min mbeltiniri mo Ishaaqa, e Й“aawo Ishaaqa, Yaaquube."
  11,72,"[Debbo on] wi'i: "Ee jalla am! emi jibinay e hoore ko mi nayeejo, e hino oo Й—oo gorko am ko nayeejo? Pellet Й—uum Й—oon ko huunde haawniinde!"."
  11,73,"ЖҒe mbi'i: "E a haawete fiyaaku Alla on? Yurmeende Alla e barkiiji makko ngonii e mon, yimЙ“e nduu suudu. Pellet ko O jettiniiЙ—o TedduЙ—o"."
  11,74,"Nde kulol ngol iwnoo e Ibraahiima, welo-welo o ari e makko, homo yeddandira e amen fii yimЙ“e Luuti Й“een."
  11,75,"Pellet, Ibraahiima ko muГұГұiiЙ—o, keewЙ—o jankina-gol, tuuboowo."
  11,76,"Eheyma Ibraahiima, Й—uurno ga e Й—um; gooЕӢЙ—ii yamiroore Joomi maa nden arii, e pellet, lepte aray e maЙ“Й“e lepte Й—e nduuttetaake."
  11,77,"Nde nulaaЙ“e amen Й“en ngarnoo ka Luuti, o sunanii Й“e, o Й“iЙ—tori fonndo makko ngon fii maЙ“Й“e, o maaki: "ndee Й—oo ko Гұalaande saЙ—tunde"."
  11,78,"YimЙ“e makko Й“een ngari e makko e yaccoo. Ado Й—um hari heЙ“e ngollaynoo bonЙ—i. O maaki: "Eeheymon yimЙ“e am, Й“ee Й—oo ko jiwЙ“e am: ko kamЙ“e Й“uri laaЙ“annde on. Kulee Alla, wata on kersinam e hoЙ“- Й“e am. E gorko peewЙ—o alaa e mo'on?"."
  11,79,"ЖҒe mi'i: "Pellet haЙ—a anndi haaju alanah men e jiwЙ“e maa Й“een, pellet haЙ—a anndi kadi ko men faalaako" koy.."
  11,80,"O maaki: "Sinno miЙ—o marunoo doole e mon! maa Й—uum mi fattinoo(moolo) e soЙ“Й“undu sattundu(jookdu)!"."
  11,81,"[HoЙ“Й“e Й“en] mbi'i: "eheymaLuutu, pellet ko men nulaaЙ“e Joomi maa. Й“e njottotaaka ema. Yaltinir Й“eynguure maa nden e taЖҙunnde jemma, wata gooto e mo'on yeЖҙЖҙito si wonaa cuddiiЙ—o maa on, ko fii heЙ“ay mo ko heЙ“ata Й“eya kon. Nganndon fodoore maЙ“Й“e nden ka subaka. E subaka on laataaki Й“aЙ—iido?"."
  11,82,"Nde yamiroore amen nden arnoo, min waЙ—tiri dow [saare] nden ley mayre, min caaЖҙini e mayre kaaЖҙe iwruЙ—e loope juЙ—aaЙ—e dewondirЙ—e."
  11,83,"MaandinaaЙ—e ka Joomi maa. Й—e ngonaani goЙ—Й—uЙ—e e tooГұooЙ“e Й“een."
  11,84,"[Min Nulii] kadi e Madyana'en, musiЙ—Й—o maЙ“Й“e on Shu'aybu, o maaki: "eheymon yo yimЙ“e am, ndewee Alla; deweteeЙ—o alanaa on ko woori mo. Wota on ustu Й“etu ngun e manndake Й—en. min on miЙ—o yi'i on e moЖҙЖҙere. miin non miЙ—o hulani on lepte Гұalaande fiiltiindede."
  11,85,"Eeheymon yo yimЙ“e am, timminee Й“etu ngun e manndake Й—en nuunЙ—al. Wata on ustan yimЙ“e Й“en coggu maЙ“Й“e ngun, wata on njahru ka leydi bonnugol."
  11,86,"Ko keddiiЙ—e Alla Й—en Й“uri moЖҙЖҙannde on si on laatike gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e. Mi wonaani deenoowo on"."
  11,87,"ЖҒe mbi'i: "eeheyma yo Shu'aybu! E ko juulde maa nden yamiru-maa nde men ngaccata rewugol ko baabiraa- Й“e amen Й“een rewaynoo kon, maa nde men nggollata huuwata e jawle amen Й—en ko men njiЙ—i? Pellet an ko a muГұГұiiЙ—o peewЙ—o"."
  11,88,"O maaki: "eeheymon yo yimЙ“e am, kaalaneekam: si miЙ—o e Й“anngannduyee immorde ka Joomi am, O arsikii lam immorde ka makko arsike moЖҙЖҙo?... mi faandaaki lunndaade on e kon haЙ—ay-mi on e muuЙ—um. mi faandaaki si wonaa moЖҙЖҙingol fotde yeru am on. Kawral am wonaani si wonaa ka Alla. Ko e makko mi fawii, ko ka makko mi ruttotoo"."
  11,89,"Eehmon yimЙ“e am, wata ngaГұngu am defu on haa heЙ“a on sifa ko heЙ“noo yimЙ“e Nuuhu maa yimЙ“e Huudi maa yimЙ“e Saalih. YimЙ“e Luuti Й“en kan ngoЙ—Й—aani on."
  11,90,"Imsinanee Joomi mon, refti tuubanon mo. Pelet Joomi am ko jurmotooЙ—o, GiЙ—o"."
  11,91,"ЖҒe mbi'i: "eeheyma Shu'aybu, men alah faamude ko Й—uuЙ—i e Й—uum ko mbi'ataa; minen miЙ—en ma nji'a hakku-nde amen lo'oЙ—o. Si wanaano gorol maa ngol, men piyirteno keeЖҙe. Aan a wonaani tedduЙ—o e amen"."
  11,92,"O maaki: "E ko gorol am ngol Й“uri teddudo e mon diini Alla, on waЙ—tirii mo Й“aawo mon hawkaaЙ—o? Pellet Joomi am ko huЙ“indiiЙ—o(fiiltiido) ko ngollaton kon."
  11,93,"Eeheymon yimЙ“e am, ngollee e nokku mo'on. miin kadi ko mi golloowo. Arma nde nganndoton ko hombo lepte koynooje arat e mu'm e ko hommbo woni penoowo on. (Jooni non) padee! min kadi miЙ—o wonВҙdi e mon patndiiЙ—o."
  11,94,"Nde yamiroore amen nden arnoo, min daЙ—ndiri Shu'aybu e Й“een gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e wonВҙduЙ“e e makko yurmeende amen. Haacaango ngon nanngi Й“en tooГұЙ“e, Й“e waЙ—tini ka cuuЙ—i maЙ“Й“e jicciiЙ“e(.jusЙ“e)"
  11,95,"A wi'ay Й“e ГұiiЙ“aano Й—on. ngandee woЙ—Й—ineede yurmeende wonanii Madayana wano Samuuda'en woЙ—Й—iniranoo."
  11,96,"GooЕӢЙ—ii Men Nulirii Muusaa Aayeeje amen Й—een e hujja Й“annguЙ—o."
  11,97,"Ha e Fir'awna e mbatu mun. Й“e njokkii yamiroore Fir'awna nden, yamiroore Fir'awna non wanaa feewnde."
  11,98,"O ardoyto yimЙ“e makko Й“een Гұande darngal, o jolna Й“e ka Yiite. (Nge)bonii jolirde jolaande."
  11,99,"ЖҒe njokkinaama kuddi e oo (aduna), e Гұande Darngal. Bonii ballal ngal Й“e njokkindiranaa."
  11,100,"ЖҠuum ko jeyaaЙ—um e kumpite ce'e, miЙ—en fillano maa Й—uum: no e majje ГұiiЙ“Й—e e coГұaaЙ—e."
  11,101,"Min tooГұaani Й“e. Ko woni, ko kamЙ“e tooГұi ko'e maЙ“Й“e. deweteeЙ—i maЙ“Й“e Й—iin Й—iЙ“e ndwatnoo gah Й—in duncanaali Й“e hay e huunde, tuma nde yamiroore Joomi maa nden arnoo; Й—i Й“eydaani Й“e si wonaa hayrude."
  11,102,"Ko wano nii nanngal Joomi maa ngal, si tawii o nanngii ce'e Й—en hara ko Й—e tooГұЙ—e. Pellet nanngal makko ngal ko muusngal caЙ—tungal."
  11,103,"Pellet tasakuyee wonii e Й—uum Й—oo wonanВҙde on kulЙ—o lepte laakara. nden ko Гұalaande yimЙ“e en mooЙ“oyte e mun, nde kadi ko Гұalaande seedoyteende."
  11,104,"Min neeЙ“tinataa nde si wanah haa e lajal limangal."
  11,105,"Г‘alnde ngal arata, woЕӢkii (woo) wowlatah si wanaa e duЕӢayee makko. Hino e maЙ“Й“e malkisaaЙ—o e malaaЙ—o."
  11,106,"Si ko malkisaaЙ“e Й“en, ko ka Yiite; hino woodani Й“e ndeer ton ottaango e hiikaango."
  11,107,"Ko Й“e luttinteeЙ“e ndeer magge fotde kammuuli Й—iin e leydi ndin no duumii, si wonah si Joomii maa muuyii; pellet Joomi maa ko baЙ—oowo kala ko O faandii."
  11,108,"Si tawii non ko malaaЙ“e Й“en, ko ka ndeer Aljanna woni ko duumintee e mun fotde kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin no duumii, si wanaa si Joomi maa muuyii. (ЖҠum) ko dokkal ngal taЖҙondirtaa."
  11,109,"Wota a won e sikke e huunde ko Й“ee ndewata. Й“e rewiraani si wanaa no baabiraaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e ndewiray- noo ko adii. minen non, min hunniranay Й“e geЙ—al maЙ“Й“e ngal ko aldah e ustugol."
  11,110,"GooЕӢЙ—ii min ngkkii Muusaa Deftere nden, luutondi- raa e mayre. Si wanaano konngol ardinoongol immorde ka Joomi maa, Гұaaweteno hakkunde maЙ“Й“e. KamЙ“e kan heЙ“e e sikke sikkitiiЙ—o e e mayre."
  11,111,"Wonaani kala maЙ“Й“e si wonaa Joomi maa hunna- nay Й“e (njoЙ“di) kuuЙ—e maЙ“Й“e. Pellet ko O kumpitiiЙ—o ko Й“e ngollata kon."
  11,112,"Г‘iiЙ“ir [e pocciingol ngol] wano njamiraЙ—aa non, e tuubuЙ“e wonВҙduЙ“e e maaЙ—a. wota on mbew. Pellet ko O deenЙ—o ko ngolloton kon."
  11,113,"Wata on ooГұor e tooГұuЙ“e Й“en sakko Yiite ngen mema on. Alanah on gah ni Alla yiЙ—Й“e. refti on mballoytaake."
  11,114,"Г‘iiЙ“nu juulde nde ka seraaji Й—iЙ—i Гұalawma e saa'iiji jemma. Pellet moЖҙЖҙi Й—in hino momta bonЙ—i Й—in. ЖҠuum ko waaju wonanВҙde Й“een waajitotooЙ“e."
  11,115,"MuГұГұo. pellet Alla yeebataa njoЙ“di moЖҙЖҙinooЙ“e Й“een."
  11,116,"Ko haЙ—noo wona e gire adinooЙ“e on Й“en, joomiraa- Й“e kedde, Й“e no haЙ—a e bonnugol ka leydi! si seeЙ—aaЙ“e e Й“en Й“e min ndaЙ—ndunoo e maЙ“Й“e. TooГұuЙ“e Й“en nokki e ko Й“e neeminaa e mun kon, Й“e laatii bonЙ“e."
  11,117,"Joomi maa siforaani kalkiroowo ce'e e hoore tooГұe tawa yimЙ“e maЙ“Й“e ko moЖҙЖҙinooЙ“e."
  11,118,"Sinno Joomi maa muuyiino, O waЙ—atno yimЙ“e Й“en moftal gootal. Й“e ceerataa ko Й“e luutondirooЙ“e."
  11,119,"si wanaa Й“een Й“e Joomi maa yurmaa. Ko sabu Й—uum O tagiri Й“e. Konngol Joomi maa ngol jojjii wonВҙde: "Pellet, Mi hebbiniray Jahannama jinna e yimЙ“e, Й“e denndaangal"."
  11,120,"Kala e mu'un, miЙ—en fillano maa kabaruuji NulaaЙ“e, ko min tabintinra Й—uum Й“ernnde maa ngon. Aranii ma e ngol (cortewol) goonga e waaju e janntoore wonanВҙde gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“en."
  11,121,"Maakan Й“een Й“e gooЕӢЙ—inah: "NGollee e nokku mo'on. minen kadi, ko min gollooЙ“e."
  11,122,"Padee kadi. minen ko men fatndiiЙ“e"."
  11,123,"Ko Alla heeranii birniiЙ—i kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin, ko ka makko fiyaaku no fow ruttetee. Awa rewu Mo, fawo-Й—aa e makko. Joomi maa wonaani belsindiiЙ—o e Й—uum ko ngolloton."
  12,1,"Alif, laam, Raa, ЖҠeen ko Aayeeje deftere Й“anngunde nden. feeГұnde."
  12,2,"Minen min njippiniriinde janngeteende [e Й—emngal] Aarabu, mbelejo'o, on kaqqilay."
  12,3,"Minen MiЙ—en pillano maa ko Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude e fillayee, e Й—uu ko min mbahyi e maaЙ—a ndee Alqur'aanaare, hay si woniino ado mayre, ko a jeyaaЙ—o e welsindiiЙ“e Й“en.b"
  12,4,"Tuma nde Yuusufu maakannoo baabamakko: "eehey may baaba', mi yi'ii [e koyЙ—ol] koode sappo e go'o, naange ngen kadi e lewru ndun; mi yi'ii Й—in no cujjana kam"."
  12,5,"[Baaba makko] maaki: "Eehey ma Й“inngel am, wota a fillano musiЙ—Й“e maa Й“en koyЙ—ol maa ngol sakko Й“e fewjane feere; pellet seytaane ko gaГұo aade Й“annguЙ—o(.peeГұЙ—o.)"
  12,6,"Ko wano nii Joomi maa suЙ“oray maa, O anndinma firo koyЙ—i, o timmina dokke makko on e maaЙ—a e Й“eynguure Yaaquuba nden, wano o timminirnoo mo e baabiraaЙ“e maa Й“en Й—iЙ—o: Ibraahiima e ishaaqa. Pellet Joomi maa ko gannduЙ—o Г‘eeГұЙ—o."
  12,7,"GooЕӢЙ—ii wonii e Yuusufa e musiЙ—Й“e makko Й“een, taskuyeeji wonanВҙde laЙ“ndotooЙ“e Й“en."
  12,8,"tuma nde Й“e mbi'noo: "Pellet ko Yuusufa e neene-gooto(musiЙ—Й—o )mun on Й“uraa yiЙ—eede ka ben-men dii enen, enen le ko en jamaa Й—uuЙ—uЙ“e. Pellet baabamen wonii e majjere Й“anngunde"."
  12,9,"Mbaree Yuusufa maa feroЙ—on mo e leydi; yeeso baaba mon ngon heeranoo on, ngonton Й“aawo Й—um yimЙ“e moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e"."
  12,10,"Gooto e maЙ“Й“e wi'i: "Wota on mbarYuusufa, mbeddee mo ka niЙ“e woyndu yoga e seteeЙ“e hoccay mo, si on laatike gollooЙ“e"."
  12,11,"ЖҒe mbi'i: "eeheyma baaba amen, ko heЙ“u-maa a hoolotaako amen e fii Yuusufa? Minen le ko men laaЙ“amЙ“e mo reedu"."
  12,12,"Accitid-mo e amen o Гұaama, o fija,minen ko men reenooЙ“e mo."
  12,13,"O maaki: "miin no suninat kam nde njahdoton e makko; miЙ—o huli nde boyeeru ndu Гұaamata-mo tawa Ko on mbelsindi-Й—oon e makko"."
  12,14,"ЖҒe mbi'i: "Pellet si saafaandu Гұaamii mo e hoore ko men jamaa Й—uuЙ—uЙ“e, haray ko men hayruЙ“e"(pertuЙ“e.)"
  12,15,"Nde Й“e njahdunoo e makko, Й“e fottani ukkugol mo ka niЙ“e woyndu, min mbahayini e makko: "Ma a haaltayan Й“e Й—ee kuuЙ—e maЙ“Й“e hara Й“e so'aa anndude".Й“e( tinaani).."
  12,16,"ЖҒe ngrti ka baaba maЙ“Й“e kiikiiЙ—e heЙ“e woya ."
  12,17,"ЖҒe mb'i: "Ko an yo baaben amen, minen men njehii miЙ—en adondira, men ngacci Yuusufa ka kaake amen saafaandu ndun Гұaami mo. A hoolotaako min non, hay si min ngonii gooЕӢЙ—uЙ“e"."
  12,18,"ЖҒe ngardi e dolokke makko on hino moddi ЖҙiiЖҙam fenaande. o maaki: "si ko woni, woЕӢkiiji mon Й—in cuЙ—inanii on fiyaaku. Ko muГұal moЖҙЖҙal [heddanii kam]! Ko Alla woni ballitorЙ—o e ko sifotoЙ—on kon"."
  12,19,"SeteeЙ“e ngari, Й“e nuli Жҙoogoowo maЙ“Й“e on, o jippini baagal makko ngal. O wi'i: "Ee welВЁ-welo am! E hino paykum!" ЖҒe cuuЙ—iri mo keyee maЙ“Й“e. Alla non ko gannduЙ—o ko Й“e ngollata kon."
  12,20,"ЖҒe njeeyiri mo coggel pamЙ—ungel: dirhamoГұ limotoo-koГұ. ЖҒe ngoni welsindiiЙ“e e fii makko."
  12,21,"CootЙ—o mo on Misra wi'ani Й“eyngu makko: "Teddin jipporde makko. Hino gasa ka o nafa en maa njogitoЙ—en mo Й“iЙ—Й—o". Ko nii min koЙ—niri Yuusufa ka leydi fii yo minn nganndin mo firo koyЙ—i. Alla ko pooluЙ—o e fiyaaku makko on: kono ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e yimЙ“e Й“en nganndaa."
  12,22,"Nde o yottinoo sagatalaagu makko, min ngokki mo faamu e ganndal. Ko wano nii min njoЙ“irta moЖҙЖҙinooЙ“e Й“een."
  12,23,"OOn [debbo] mo on woni e suudu mun Й—aЙ“Й“iri mo hoore-makko. O soki baafe Й—en o wi'i: "mi heblanii-mo-ma!" o maaki: "Moolaare Alla! JeyЙ—o kam on moЖҙЖҙinii weerde am. Si ko woni, tooГұooЙ“e Й“en maletaake"."
  12,24,"GooЕӢЙ—ii [debbo] on himmanii oon. KaЕӢko kadi o himmanayno mo si wanaa o yi'ii hujja Joomi makko on. Ko nii [min gerdiri] fii yo min njiiltu mo e bone e paЕӢkare. Pellet ko o jeyaaЙ—o e jeyaaЙ“e amen laЙ“Й“inaaЙ“e Й“een."
  12,25,"ЖҒe Й—iЙ—o kala Й“e ngidondiri ka baafal, o seekiri dolokke oya oon Й“aawo. ЖҒe tawi moodi makko ka baafal. [debbo] on wi'i: "Ko holЙ—um woni njoЙ“di on paalanaaЙ—o Й“eynguure maa nden bonki si wanaa yo soke [o leptiree] lepte muusЙ—e?""
  12,26,"[Yuusufu] maaki: "Ko kaЕӢko Й—aЙ“Й“iri kam hoore-am". TawanooЙ—o e yimЙ“e [debbo] on ceeditii: "Si tawii dolokke mum on ko yeeso seekiraa, haray ko [debbo] oon gooЕӢЙ—i, kaЕӢko [gorko] on ko jeyaaЙ—o e fenЙ“e Й“een."
  12,27,"Si tawii noon dolokke makko oon ka Й“aawo seekiraa, haray [debbo] on fenii, kaЕӢko [gorko] on ko o jeyaaЙ—o gooЕӢЙ—uЙ“e Й“een."
  12,28,"Nde [moodi makko] yi'noo dolokke oon ko Й“aawo seekori, o wi'i: "ЖҠum ko jeyaaЙ—um e pewje mon! Pellet pewje mon Й—en ko mawЙ—e!"."
  12,29,"Yuusufa, Й—uurno gah e Й—um. Aan [debbo on], imsinano junuubi(bakkaat) maa Й—in; tawde pellet a jeyaama e woopЙ“e Й“een"."
  12,30,"RewЙ“e Й“en ka saare mbi'i: "Debbo laamЙ—o on Й—aЙ“Й“irii kurka makko o hoore-makko! GooЕӢЙ—ii yiЙ—de Й“urtirii mo. Minen dey miЙ—en nji'a oo [debbo] e majjere Й“anngunde"."
  12,31,"Nde o nannoo pewje maЙ“Й“e Й—en, o nulani Й“e, o hebilani Й“e ngawluuji, o jonni gooto kala e maЙ“Й“e laЙ“i, o wi'i: "Yaltu e maЙ“Й“e!". Nde Й“e nji'unoo mo, Й“e mawnini mo, Й“e taЖҙi juuЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en, Й“e mbi'i: "Kaawee Alla! Oo wanaa Й“anndiЕӢke, oo wonaani si wanaa malayiko tedduЙ—o"."
  12,32,"O wi'i: "Ko oo mo'on felirЙ—on kamm fii mun, gooЕӢЙ—ii mi Й—aЙ“Й“irii mo hoore-makko o haЙ—itii. Si wonii o waЙ—aani ko mi yamirta mo kon, ma o soke ma o laato jeyaaЙ—o e hoyЙ“e Й“en"."
  12,33,"O maaki: "Joomi am, Ko kaso oon Й“urani kam e ko Й“e noddata kam e mun kon. Si a pottinaani kam pewje maЙ“Й“e Й—en, mi ooГұoto e maЙ“Й“e, mi jeyee e majjuЙ“e Й“e"."
  12,34,"Joomi makko jaabinani mo, O firliti e makko pewje maЙ“Й“e Й—en. Pellet, ko KaЕӢko woni Nanoowo, gannduЙ—o O."
  12,35,"Refti feeГұani (rewЙ“e) Й“en Й“aawo nde Й“e nji'i maandeeji Й—in, ma Й“e cok-mbo tigi haa e saaji."
  12,36,"SukaaЙ“e Й—iЙ—o naatidi e makko ka kaso. GoЙ—Й—o e maЙ“Й“e wi'i: "Min mi hoyЙ—ii hoore-am miЙ—o siiwa sanngara". Oya kadi wi': "Min mi hoyЙ—ii hoore-am miЙ—o ronndii ka hoore-am cobbal, colli no Гұaama e maggal". Humpitii min firo Й—in, minen men nji'ii ma jeyaaЙ—o e moЖҙЖҙinooЙ“e Й“een"."
  12,37,"O maaki: "Г‘aametee mo wonaЙ—on okkoreede on aratah on si wanaa mi humpitay on firo mun ado o arde on. ЖҠuum mo'on ko jeyeeЙ—um e ko Joomi am anndini lam. Min mi Й—alii diina yimЙ“e Й“e ngooЕӢЙ—inaa Alla, hara kamЙ“e e fii laakara ko Й“e yedduЙ“e"."
  12,38,"Njookku-mi diina baabiraaЙ“e am Й“en: Ibraahiima e Ishaaqa e Yaaquuba. Haananaa men nde men kafidata e Alla hay e huunde. ЖҠuum ko jeyaaЙ—um e Й“ural Alla e dow amen e hoore yimЙ“e Й“een; kono ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e yimЙ“e Й“en Й“e njettataa."
  12,39,"Eehey mon wonВҙdiiЙ“e am Й—iЙ—o ka kaso! E ko deweteeЙ—i ceertuЙ—i Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude, kaa ko Alla Gooto poolЙ—o o?"
  12,40,"On ndewani gah mum, si wonah inЙ—e Й—e innuЙ—on Й—um, onon e baabiraaЙ“e mon, Alla jippinanaani Й—en hujja. Г‘aawoore ndeen alanah si wanaa Alla. O yamirii wota on ndw si wanaa KaЕӢko. Ko Й—uum woni diina ГұiiЙ“uka kan; kono ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e yimЙ“e Й“en Й“e nganndaa."
  12,41,"Eehey mon wonВҙdiiЙ“e am Й—iЙ—o ka kaso! GoЙ—Й—o e mo'on yarnay koohoo mun on sanngara; oya on, o fetee, colli Й—in Гұaama ka hoore makko. Fiyaaku mo laЙ“ndiЙ—on fii mun on Гұaawaama."
  12,42,"O maakani on mo o sikke daЙ—ay e maЙ“Й“e kamЙ“e Й—iЙ—o: "JaЕӢto lam ka koohoojo maa on". Seytaane yejjintini mo jaЕӢtanagol koohoojo makko on. [Yuusufu] ГұiiЙ“iti ka kaso yoga e duuЙ“i."
  12,43,"LaamЙ—o on wi'i: "Min mi yi'ii (e koyЙ—ol) na'i jeeЙ—iЙ—i payЙ—i, na Гұaama pooЖҙuЙ—i jeeЙ—iЙ—i Й—in, e butaali jeeЙ—iЙ—i kecci, e goЙ—Й—i goo joorЙ—i. Eheymon dental, pirtanee kam ngol koyЙ—ol am, si on laatike firtooЙ“e koyЙ—i"."
  12,44,"ЖҒe mbi'i: "Ko jiiЙ“u-jaaЙ“u koyЙ—i ! min ngonaani annduЙ“e firo koyЙ—i !"."
  12,45,"DaЙ—nooЙ—o on e Й“eya Й—iЙ—o miijitii Й“aawo dumunna o wi'i: "Min mi humpitay on firo maggol. Nulee kam"."
  12,46,"Yuusufu, an yo gooЕӢЙ—uЙ—o! haalani min fii na'i jeeЙ—iЙ—i payЙ—i, na Гұaama pooЖҙuЙ—i jeeЙ—iЙ—i Й—in, e butaali jeeЙ—iЙ—i kecci e goЙ—Й—i jooruЙ—i, mbelejo'o mi ruttoo ka yimЙ“e Й“en, belejo'o, Й“e ngannday"."
  12,47,"O maaki: "On ndemat duuЙ—i jeeЙ—iЙ—i jokkondirЙ—i. Kala ko coГұЙ—on, ngccon Й—um ka dukkal(butaali) mun, si wanaa seeЙ—a e kon ko Гұaamoton"."
  12,48,"Refti aroyat Й“aawo Й—um, duuЙ“i jeeЙ—iЙ—i caЙ—tuЙ—i, Й—in (duuЙ“i) no Гұaama Й—uum ko marnaЙ—on Й—i si wonaa seeЙ—a e ko maroton [fii awdi]."
  12,49,"Refti aroya Й“aawo Й—uum, hitaande, ko e mayre yimЙ“e Й“en toЙ“etee, ko e mayre kadi Й“e kamata."
  12,50,"LaamЙ—o on wi'i: "ngaddanee kam on". Nde imminaaЙ—o on arunoo mo, o maaki: "Rutto ka koohoojo maa on laЙ“ndoЙ—aa mo: Ko woni fiyaaku Й“en rewЙ“e taЖҙnooЙ“e juuЙ—e mun Й—en? Pellet Joomi am ko gannduЙ—o pewje maЙ“Й“e Й—en"."
  12,51,"[LaamЙ—o on] wi'i: "Ko holЙ—um wonnoo fiyaaku mon tuma Й—aЙ“Й“irnoЙ—on Yuusufa hoore-makko?" ЖҒe mbi'i: "Moolaare Alla! min nganndiraa mo ko boni". ЖҒeyngu laamЙ—o on wi'i: "Jooni goonga kan feeГұii. Ko min Й—aЙ“Й“irnoo mo hoore-makko, pellet ko o jeyaaЙ—o e gooЕӢЙ—uЙ“e Й“en"."
  12,52,""ЖҠuum ko fii yo o anndu wonВҙde mi jamfaaki mo ka wirnii, e wonВҙde Alla fewnatah pewje jamfotooЙ“e Й“en."
  12,53,"Mi laЙ“Й“inaa hoore-am, tawde woЕӢkii ko heewkii yamirde bone, si wanah kiin ki Joomi am yurmini. Joomi am ko jaafotooЙ—o jurmotooЙ—o."
  12,54,"LaamЙ—o on wi'i: "ngaddanee kam mo, mi heertinana mo hoore-am". Nde o yewtunoo mo, o wi'i: "Aa on hannde ka amen, ko a jom-nokku koolaaЙ—o"."
  12,55,"O maaki: "WaЙ—am e hoore-ngaluuji leydi ndin: ko mi deenoowo gannduЙ—o"."
  12,56,"Ko wano nii min Гұimnirani Yuusufa ka leydi, homo jippora e mayri nokku ka o yiЙ—i. miЙ—en keЙ“nira yurmeende amen nden on mo min muuyi, min njeebataaka njoЙ“di moЖҙЖҙinooЙ“e Й“en."
  12,57,"Pellet ko njoЙ“di laakara ndiin Й“uri moЖҙЖҙannde Й“en gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“e laatii gooЕӢЙ—uЙ“e."
  12,58,"-MusiЙ—Й“e-baaba-gootooЙ“e Yuusufa Й“een ngari Й“e naati ka makko. O annditi Й“e, kono kamЙ“e Й“e paayti mo."
  12,59,"Tuma nde o hebllannooЙ“e doЕӢlle maЙ“Й“e Й—een, o maaki: "ngaddanee kam musiЙ—Й—o mon baaba-gooto. E on nji'aani miЙ—o timmina Й“etu ngun, e wonВҙde ko mi Й“urdo moЖҙЖҙude e weernooЙ“e Й“en?"(jippinooЙ“r)."
  12,60,"Si on ngaddanaani kam mo, haray Й“etu alanaa on ka am Й—oo; wota on Й“ado kamm kadi"."
  12,61,"ЖҒe mb'i: "min Й—aЙ“Й“iray mo baba makko, minen ko men gollooЙ“e (Й—uum)"."
  12,62,"O maakani gollooЙ“e makko Й“en: "mbaЙ—ee coggeeji(njigguuji) maЙ“Й“e Й—in ka doЕӢle maЙ“Й“e: belejo'o Й“e ngannditat Й—i si Й“e nduttima ka yimЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en, belejo'o Й“e njiiltoto"."
  12,63,"Tuma nde Й“e nduuttinoo ka ben maЙ“Й“e, Й“e mbi'i: "eeheyma ben(baaba) amen, min skaЙ—aama Й“etu. neldu amen musiЙ—Й—o amen on, men Й“etanee. Ko men reenooЙ“e mo"."
  12,64,"O maaki: "Hara mi hooloray on e fii makko, si wonaa no mi hoolornoo on non e musiЙ—Й—o-neene-gooto makko on ko adii? Ko Alla woni moЖҙЖҙo deenoowo, ko KaЕӢko Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude yurmotooЙ“e Й“een"."
  12,65,"Nde Й“e ngudditunoo doЕӢle maЙ“Й“e Й—een, Й“e tawi cogguuji(njigguuji) maЙ“Й“e Й—in ruttaama e maЙ“Й“e. ЖҒe mbi'i: "eeyma yo ben amen, ko men Й—aЙ“Й“ata [kadi]? ЖҠii ko cogguuji amen, Й—i nduttaama e amen. MiЙ—en njiggana yimЙ“e amen, men ndeena musiЙ—Й—o amen on, men Й“eydora Й“etu ngelooba; Й—uum ko Й“etu newiingu"."
  12,66,"O maaki: "Mi immindintaa(neldatah) mo e mooЙ—on haa Жҙettanon mi ahadi ka Alla, wonВҙde on ngrtiranat kam mo si wonaa hara on kuЙ“inda". ЖҒaawo Й“e Жҙettanii mo ahadi maЙ“Й“e ndin, o maaki: "Alla e dow ko wowluЙ—en kon, ko o deenoowo"."
  12,67,"O maaki: "eeheymin Й“iЙ—Й“e am, wota on naatiroy e damal gootal, naatiree e dame ceertuЙ—e. Mi dun-cantaa on e (muyЙ—e) Alla hay e huunde. Г‘aawoore alanaa si wonaa Alla: Ko e makko mi fawii, ko e makko kadi, yo fawo fawotooЙ“e Й“een"."
  12,68,"Nde Й“e naatirnoo nokku ka baaba maЙ“Й“e yamirnoo Й“e Й—on, Й—um wonaano no duncana Й“e [ko iwri] ka Alla si wanaa haaju wonunooЙ—o e fittaandu Yaaquuba mo o gasini. KaЕӢko on, ko o jom-ganndal ngal min anndini mo. Kono ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e yimЙ“e Й“en Й“e nganndaa."
  12,69,"Nde Й“e naatnoo ka Yuusufa, o maЙ“Й“i musiЙ—Й—o-neene-gooto makko on e makko, o maaki: "Ko mi musiЙ—Й—o-neene-gooto maa, wata a sunor ko Й“e ngollatnoo"."
  12,70,"Tuma nde o hebilannoo Й“e doЕӢle maЙ“Й“e Й—en, o waЙ—i Й“etirgal ngal ka doЕӢngal musiЙ—Й—o-neene-gooto makko on, refti ewnotooЙ—o eewnii: "eeymon yo seteeЙ“e, Ko on wuyЙ“e"."
  12,71,"ЖҒe fewtiti e maЙ“Й“e Й“e mbi'i: "Ko holЙ—uum kattiЙ—on?""
  12,72,"ЖҒe mbi'i: "minn kattike Й“etirde laamЙ—o on. Hino woodani kala gadduЙ—o ngal, doЕӢngal ngelooba, ko miin woni pawtiiЙ—o Й—uum"."
  12,73,"ЖҒe mbi'i: "min ngooЙ—ndirii Alla, gooЕӢЙ—ii hoЙ—on nganndi min ngaraani bonnugol ka leydi, min laataaki kadi wuyЙ“e"."
  12,74,"ЖҒe mbi'i: "Ko wonata njoЙ“di makko si tawii ko on fenooЙ“e?""
  12,75,"ЖҒe mbi'i: "NjoЙ“di makko: ko kala mo: [Й—uum] tawaa ka doЕӢngal mun, haray ko kaЕӢko [tigir] woni njoЙ“di mun. Ko wano non min njoЙ“itirta tooГұooЙ“e Й“en"."
  12,76,"[Yuusufu] fuЙ—Й—ori doЕӢle maЙ“Й“e Й—en ado doЕӢngalmusiЙ—Й—o- neene-gooto makko on; refti o yaltiniri nde ka doЕӢngal musiЙ—Й—o-neene-gooto makko on. Ko wano non men fewjirani Yuusufa, [tawde] o hattantaano nanngude musiЙ—Й—o-neene-gooto makko on ka sariya laamЙ—o on, si wonaa hara ko Alla muuyi. MiЙ—en Й“antana darajaaji on mo min muuyi. No e dow kala jom-ganndal ganndo [goo]."
  12,77,"ЖҒe mbi'i: "Si o wujjii, haray musЙ—o- neene-gooto makko wujjiino ko adii". Yuusufu mari Й—um ka woЕӢkii makko, o feГұГұinanaani Й“e Й—uum. o maaki: "Ko onon Й“uri bonВҙde nokku! Ko Alla Й“uri anndude ko cifotoЙ—on"."
  12,78,"ЖҒe mbi'i: "heyma yo laamЙ—o on, oo no mari baabiraawo nawyuЙ—o oggos; Жҙettu gooto e amen lomto makko. Menen men nji'ii ma jeyaaЙ—o e moЖҙЖҙinooЙ“e Й“een"."
  12,79,"O maaki: "Moolaare Alla nde min nanngata si wanaa oon mo men tawi doЕӢle amen Й—een e juuЙ—e mun. Mene haray ontuma ko men tooГұЙ“e"."
  12,80,"Nde Й“e taЖҙinoo fii hettugol mo, Й“e martiti ko Й“e gunndondirЙ“e. MawЙ—o maЙ“Й“e on wi'i: "E on nganndaa wonВҙde baaba mon Жҙettodii e mo'on ahadi ka Alla, e aranun tuma belsindinoЙ—on e Yuusufa? Mi seerataa leydi ndin haa baaba am duЕӢanoo kam maa o Гұaawana kam [hettugol mo], ko KaЕӢko Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude e ГұaawooЙ“e Й“een"."
  12,81,"Nduttee ka baaba mon mbi'on: "eeheyma yo baaba amen, Й“iЙ—Й—o maa on wujjii. min ceedaaki si wonaa ko men nganndi, men wonaani reenЙ“e ko wirnii."
  12,82,"LaЙ“ndo (yimЙ“e) saare nden nde men ngonunoo e mun, e seteeЙ“e Й“en Й“e men kawrondirnoo e mun. Pellet ko men gooЕӢЙ—uЙ“e"."
  12,83,"[Yaaquuba] maaki: "WoЕӢkiiji mon Й—in cuЙ—anii on fiyaake! Ko muГұal labangal. Hino hasii ka Alla artiranta mi Й“e, Й“e denndaangal. Ko KaЕӢko woni gannduЙ—o, Г‘eeГұЙ—o"."
  12,84,"O Й—uurnii Й“e o maaki: "Ee suno am e fii Yuusufa!" Gite makko Й—en ndanwiri suno. Ko o cuuЙ—Й—o suno."
  12,85,"ЖҒe mb'i: "min ngooЙ—dirii Alla! A seerataa haЙ—a jaЕӢtoo fii Yuusufa, haa ngonaa horsuЙ—o maa ngonaa jeyaaЙ—o e halkiiЙ“e Й“en"."
  12,86,"O maaki: "nganndee ko e Alla mi wullitotoo ngannde am e sunaare am. MiЙ—o anndi ka Alla ko on nganndaa"."
  12,87,""Eeheymon Й“iЙ—Й“e am, njehee tefon fii Yuusufa e musiЙ—Й—o neene-gooto makko on. Wota on taЖҙo e yurmeende Alla. Ko fii, taЖҙotaako e yurmeende Alla si wanaa yimЙ“e yedduЙ“e Й“en"."
  12,88,"Nde Й“e naatunoo ka makko [kaЕӢko Yuusufa], Й“e wi'i: "Ko an yo laamЙ—o, lorra heЙ“ii men memen e Й“eynguure amen; men angadii e sil'a jaasuЙ—o. HuЙ“nan men Й“etu ngun, cakko-Й—aa e amen. Pellet, Alla yoЙ“ay sakkotooЙ“e Й“een"."
  12,89,"O maaki: "Enee, on ngannditii ko mbaЙ—unoЙ—on Yuusufa e musiЙ—Й—o neene-gooto makko on kon tuma nde ngonnoЙ—on majjuЙ“e?""
  12,90,"ЖҒe mbii'i: "Kere ko aan woni Yuusufa?" O maaki: "Ko miin woni Yuusufa. Oo Й—oo ko miГұam. GooЕӢЙ—ii Alla moЖҙЖҙike e amen. Ko fii, mo gomЙ—ii o muГұГұike, pellet, Alla yeebataa njoЙ“di moЖҙЖҙinooЙ“e Й“en"."
  12,91,"ЖҒe mbi'i: "min ngooЙ—ndiri Alla, Alla Й“urnii ma e amen, men woniino woopЙ“e"."
  12,92,"O maaki: "Feloore alaa e hoore-mon hannde! Yo Alla yawtan on. Ko Kano woni Й“urЙ—o YurmotooЙ“e"."
  12,93,"Njehhdee e oo dolokke am Й—oo, mberloЙ—on mo ka yeeso baaben am: o wattinat ji'oowo. ngaddanon kam Й“eynguure mon nden Й“e denndaangal"."
  12,94,"Nde seteeЙ“e Й“en ceerti [yalti Misra]ben maЙ“Й“e maaki: "miin miЙ—o heЙ“a balangol Yuusufa, sinno wanaa fii yo on Й—aaytinam"."
  12,95,"ЖҒe mbi'i: "min ngooЙ—ndirii Alla, an haЙ—a e majjere maaЙ—a Й“ooyunde nden"."
  12,96,"Nde beltinoowo on arnoo, o werlii [dolokke] on ka yeeso makko, o wonti yi'oowo. O maaki: "E mi wi'anaano on miЙ—o anndi ka Alla ko on nganndaa?""
  12,97,"ЖҒe mbi'i: "eheyma yo baaba amen, imsinano men junuubi amen. minen men ngoniino woopЙ“e"."
  12,98,"O maaki: "Arma mi imsinano on Joomi am. Ko KaЕӢko woni jaafotooЙ—o, jurmotooЙ—o"."
  12,99,"Nde Й“e naatnoo ka Yuusufa, o tappi ka makko [Й—oun] mawЙ“e makko Й“en Й—iЙ—o, o maaki: "Naatiree Misra, si Alla muuyii, ko on hooliiЙ“e"."
  12,100,"O towniri mawЙ“e makko Й“en Й—iЙ—o ka belorki(daЕӢki), Й“e naayirani mo cujjugol. O maaki:"eymon baaba'en, ko Й—um Й—oo woni firo koyЙ—ol am ngol oya tuma, gooЕӢЙ—ii Joomi am waЙ—ii ngol goonga. GooЕӢЙ—ii O moЖҙЖҙike e am tuma O yaltinnoo kam ka kaso, O itti on ka ladde, Й“aawo nde seytaane bonnii hakkunde am musiЙ—Й“e- baab-gootooЙ“e am Й“en. Pellet, Joomi am ko newaniiЙ—o ko O muuyi kon. Ko KaЕӢko woni gannduЙ—o, Г‘eeГұЙ—o"."
  12,101,"Joomi am, gooЕӢЙ—ii A weeЙ—ii kam laamu, A anndinii kam kadi firo koyЙ—i. [Aan] TakЙ—o kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin, ko Aan woni giЙ—o am aduna e laakara. Жіettitam ko mi juulЙ—o, waЙ—itdaa kam e moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e Й“en."
  12,102,"ЖҠuum ko jeyaaЙ—um e kumpite wirniiЙ—e, miЙ—en wahayini Й—e e maaЙ—a. A tawanooka e maЙ“Й“e tuma nde Й“e eЙ“Й“unoo fiyaaku maЙ“Й“e on heЙ“e pewja."
  12,103,"Ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e yimЙ“e Й“en, hay si a reerЙ—i, (Й“e) ngonaani gooЕӢЙ—inooЙ“e."
  12,104,"A Й—aЙ“Й“iraani Й“e e Й—uum njoЙ“di. Nde wonaani si wanaa waaju wonanВҙde winndere nden."
  12,105,"ЖҠuuЙ—ii e aayeeje ka kammuuli e ka leydi, heЙ“ee ndewa e majje hara ko Й“e Й—uurniiЙ“e Й—e."
  12,106,"Ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e maЙ“Й“e goosЙ—intaa Alla, si wonaa hara ko Й“e sirkuЙ“e."
  12,107,"E Й“e kooli nde hippooje arata Й“e e lepte Alla Й—ee maa darngal ngal ardira Й“e juhal, hara kamЙ“e Й“e tinaani"
  12,108,"Maaku: "Ko ngo'ol woni laawol am, miЙ—o noddira e Alla dow hujja, min e Й“een jokkuЙ“e kam. Senayee woodanii Alla! Mi wonaani jeyaaЙ—o e sirkooЙ“e Й“en."
  12,109,"Men nulaali ado maa si wanaa worЙ“e jeyaaЙ“e e yimЙ“e ca'e Й—en, miЙ—en mbahayina e maЙ“Й“e. E Й“ee [fennooЙ“e ma] yiilotaako ka leydi, Й“e ndaara ko honno battane Й“een adinooЙ“e Й“e w'anoo? Pellet ko saare laakara nden Й“uri moЖҙЖҙannde Й“en hulЙ“e [Alla]. E on haqqiltaa?"
  12,110,"Haa si tawii nulaaЙ“e Й“en taЖҙike, (heeferЙ“e Й“en) fellita wonВҙde kamЙ“e Й“e fennaama, ballal amen ngal ara e maЙ“Й“e; min daЙ—nda on mo min muuyi, lepte amen Й—en ruttetaake gaayi e yimЙ“e bonЙ“e Й“en."
  12,111,"GooЕӢЙ—ii wonii e fillayeeje maЙ“Й“e Й—in tasakuyye wonan`de joomiraaЙ“e haqqillaaji Й“en. Nde wonaani yewtere fekidaande. Ko woni, ko nde gooЕӢЙ—innde Й—en adinooЙ—e nde, e fensitunde kala huunde, e peewal e yurmeende wonanВҙde yimЙ“e gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“en."
  13,1,"Alif, Laam, Miim, Raa. ЖҠee ko aayeeje deftere nden; jippinaande nden e maaЙ—a immorde ka Joomi maa ko goonga; kono ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e yimЙ“e Й“en Й“e ngooЕӢЙ—intaa."
  13,2,"Ko Alla woni Й“amtuЙ—o kammuuli Й—in doose Й—e on nji'ataa. refti O fotondiri ka dow 'Arshi, O elti naange ngeen e lewru ndun: kala majji no doga haa e lajal innaangal. Hino toppitoo fiyaakuuji Й—in, Homo fensita aayeeje Й—een belejo'o on njanante kawwroygol e Joomi mon."
  13,3,"Ko KaЕӢko woni fontuЙ—o leydi ndin, O waЙ—i e majji pelle e caatli. E kala (noone) e dimЙ—e, o waЙ—i e majje noone Й—iЙ—i resindirayЙ—i. Homo suddira jemma on Гұalawma on. Wonii e Й—uum, maandeeji wonan`de yimЙ“e miijitotooЙ“e."
  13,4,"Hino ka leydi tummbe Й“adondirЙ—e, e gese 'inabu, e remuruuji, e tamarooje dukkinЙ—e e Й—e wonaa Й—ukkinЙ—e, heЙ—e yarniree ndiyam ngootam, MiЙ—en Й“urna yoga majji dow yoga ka dakamme. Wonii e Й—uum, maandeeji wonanВҙde yimЙ“e haqqilooЙ“e."
  13,5,"Si a ЕӢalЙ—ay, -haawete-haray ko konngol maЙ“Й“e ngol jojji ЕӢalЙ—ude:-haawniinde- "Eyoo si men wontii mbulmbuldi, mene men wontat e tagoore hesre?" Ko Й“een ngoni yedduЙ“e Joomi mun Й“en, ko Й“een tonngoytee ka daaЙ—e mun, ko Й“en kadi ngoni yimЙ“e Yiite; kamЙ“e ko Й“e luttooЙ“e e magge."
  13,6,"HeЙ“e hawjirane bone on ado moЖҙЖҙere nden. GooЕӢЙ—ii wulike ado maЙ“Й“e [lepte] yeruuje majje. Pellet, Joomi maa ko Jom-haforanal wonan`de yimЙ“e Й“een, e tooГұe maЙ“Й“e Й—een. Pellet kadi Joomi maa, ko cЙ—ttuЙ—o lepte."
  13,7,"ЖҒeen heefereЙ“e no wi'a: "Ko haЙ—no maande jippiniree e makko immorde ka Joomi makko?" Anndu ko an ko a jertinoowo, hino woodani yimЙ“e kala pewnoowo."
  13,8,"Alla no anndi ko roondotoo kala deyel, e ko renngaaji Й—in ustata e ko Й—i Й“eydata. Kala huunde ka makko, ko eЙ“Й“aa-Й—um."
  13,9,"gannduЙ—o k owirniiЙ—i e feeГұuЙ—i, mawЙ—o, toownitiiЙ—o."
  13,10,"Hino fota [ka makko ganndugol] oon cuuЙ—uЙ—o konngol e mooЙ—on, e on peГұГұinЙ—o ngol, on cuuЙ—iratЙ—o jemma, e on jaltiniroowo Гұalawma."
  13,11,"Hino woodani mo lomtondirooЙ“e yeeso makko e Й“aawo makko, heЙ“e ndeenira mo yamiroore Alla. Pellet Alla waylataa ko woni e yimЙ“e, haa Й“e mbayla ko woni kon e maЙ“Й“e. Si Alla faandanike yimЙ“e bone, alaa yiltoowo mo. Alanaa Й“e gaanin makko giЙ—o-heftoowo."
  13,12,"Ko KaЕӢko woni kollirayЙ—o on maЖҙe Й—en kulul [Й—e] e tamЖҙinagol [toЙ“o]; O fuЙ—Й—a Й—een duule tedduЙ—e."
  13,13,"Digge Й—een no senina mo yettugol mo, e maleykaaji Й“en, immorde e kulol makko. o wurta parГұite Й—en, O meminira Й—e on mo o muuyi. KamЙ“e heЙ“e wennja fii Alla, KaЕӢko non ko O saЙ—tuЙ—o nanngal."
  13,14,"Hino woodani oo noddaandu goonga! ЖҠiin Й—i Й“e noddata ko woori Mo, Й—i jaabotaako Й“e e huunde; si wanaa wano fontuЙ—o newe mun e ndiyam fii yo Й—am yotto hunnduko makko, kono Й—am wonaani joottotoo-Й—am kon (hunnduko). Noddaandu heefereЙ“e Й“en wonaani si wonaa e majjere."
  13,15,"Ko Alla woni ko sujjannta, denndaangal ko woni ka kammuuji e la leydi, Й—oftaare e waawneede, e Й—owdiiji maЙ“Й“e, bimmbi e kiikiiЙ—e."
  13,16,"Maaku: "Ko hommbo jeyi kammuuji Й—iin e leydi ndin?" Maaku: "Ko Alla". Maaku: "E on njogiti gaanin makko, keediiЙ—i Й—i mbaawanaa ko'e majji nafa wanaa lorra?" Maaku: "Hara bumЙ—o e ji'iiwo no fota? Kaa hara niЙ“e Й—en fotay e ndaygu ngu? Kaa Й“e waЙ—an Alla kafidiiЙ“e tagirЙ“e wano tagoore makko nde, tagoore nde nanndari Й“e? Maaku: "Ko Alla woni takЙ—o kala huunde, ko KaЕӢko woni bajjo, poolЙ—o"."
  13,17,"O jippinirii ka kammu ndiyam, Й—am ili e jooli=caatli =emmbere majjam. Ilol ngol roondii ngufo hummbu-ngo. No e kon ko Й“e kuЙ“Й“ata yiite e mun fii Й—aЙ“Й“u Й—aЙ“Й“ugol cuЙ—aari maa nafa-hoy, ngufo sugu mun. Ko wano nii Alla waЙ—irta misal goonga e fenannde. Si ko ngufo ngon, ngo yahray Й“eeЙ“ugol, ammaa ko nafata yimЙ“e Й“een kon, Й—um ГұiiЙ“a ka leydi. Ko wano nii Alla waЙ—irta yeruuji Й—iin."
  13,18,"Hino woodani Й“een nootiiЙ“e Joomi mun moЖҙЖҙere. ЖҒeen Й“e nootaaki Mo, sinno woodaniino Й“e denndaangal ko woni kon ka leydi, e yeru mun wonВҙdude e mu'un, Й“e soktorayno(coottorto) Й—um. ЖҒeen Й—on, no woodani Й“e bonЙ—um hasboore, jaaЖҙorde maЙ“Й“e nden ko Jahannama. Nge bonii ndaЙ—Й—undi."
  13,19,"E ko on gannduЙ—o wonВҙde ko jippinaa ko e maaЙ—a immorde ka Joomi maa ko goonga, wa'ata wa on Й“umЙ—o? Anndu ko waajitotoo, ko joomiraaЙ“e-haqqillaaji Й“een,"
  13,20,"ЖҒeen huuЙ“nooЙ“e ahadi Alla ndiin, Й“e pirtataa ahodal(hoolaare)."
  13,21,"e Й“een jokkooЙ“e Й—uum ko Alla yamiri yo jokke, heЙ“e kula Joomi maЙ“Й“e, heЙ“e kula bonВҙde hasboore,"
  13,22,"ЖҒeen muГұГұoriiЙ“e Й—aЙ“Й“ugol yarluyee Joomi maЙ“Й“e, Й“e ГұiiЙ“ni julde, Й“e nafqii e kon ko min arsiki Й“e, gunndoo e kene, heЙ“e duГұira moЖҙЖҙere ndeen bone on. ЖҒeen Й—oon, no woodani Й“e battane galle,"
  13,23,"Aljannaaji ГұiiЙ“al, heЙ“e naata Й—i, e Й“een moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e e baabiraaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“een, e rewЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en, e geyngolji=Й“esnguuji =maЙ“Й“e Й—in. Hara Maleykaaji Й—i hino naatirana Й“e kala damal:"
  13,24,""Kisal wonii e mo'on, sabu muГұal mon ngal. battane galle Й—een moЖҙЖҙii"."
  13,25,"ЖҒeen (non) firtooЙ“e ahadi Alla ndin Й“aawo piЙ“ugol ndi, heЙ“e taЖҙoo e ko Alla yamiri kon yo jokke, heЙ“e mbonna ka leydi, Й“ee Й—oo, hino woodani Й“e kuЙ—di, hino woodani Й“e kadi bonЙ—um galle."
  13,26,"Alla no yaГұГұana arsike on mo o muuyi, Himo Й“ittina. heЙ“e mbeltora nguurndam aduna, nguurndam aduna non wonaani ka laakara, si wanaa dakamme-hoy."
  13,27,"ЖҒeen yedduЙ“e no mbi'a: "Ko haЙ—no aaya jippinee e makko immorde ka Joomi makko?" Maaku: "Alla majjinat tun mo o muuyi, O fewna e makko on tuubuЙ—o-ruttii""
  13,28,"ЖҒeen gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e, Й“e Й“erЙ—e mun deeЖҙirta jantagol Alla. Ngandee ko jaЕӢtagol Alla ngol Й“erЙ—e Й—een ndeeЖҙirta."
  13,29,"ЖҒeen gooЕӢЙ—iiЙ“e Й“e ngolli golle moЖҙЖҙe, welo-welo woodaniiЙ“e e moЖҙЖҙude ruttorde."
  13,30,"Ko wano nii min nulir-maa e mofte - gooЕӢЙ—ii mofte goo yawtiino ado majje - fii yo a janngan Й“e nden nde min wahayini e maaЙ—a, kono heЙ“e yedda YurmeteeЙ—o on. maaku: "Ko KaЕӢko woni Joomi am. deweteeЙ—o alaa si wanaa KaЕӢko. Ko e makko mi fawii, ko ka makko kadi woni ruttorde am"."
  13,31,"Sinno janngeteende naЙ“irano pelle Й—e, maa leydi ndin seekiraa sabu mayre, maa nde wowliniraa maayЙ“e Й“en (harayno ko ndee Й—oo). Ko woni, ko Alla woodani fiyaaku on fow. E gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“en nganndaanii wonВҙde, sinno Alla muuyuno, o fewnatna denndaangal yimЙ“e Й“en? Masiibo seeraani no heЙ“ira yedduЙ“e Й“een ko Й“e paggitii kon, maa [ngon masiibo] yana takko galle maЙ“Й“e nden haa fodoore Alla nden ara. Pellet Alla firtataa fodoore."
  13,32,"GoЕӢЙ—ii nulaaЙ“e njalkitanoo ma ado maaЙ—a. mi muГұГұanii Й“en yedduЙ“e, refti Mi nanngi Й“e. Ko honno lepte am Й—en ngonirnoo!"
  13,33,"E hara ko oon dariiЙ—o e kala woЕӢkii ko ki faggitii kon [Й“uri hanndude e dewal?...] ЖҒe mbaЙ—anii Alla kafidii- Й—i. Maaku: "Innee-Й—i" Kaa on humpitay mo ko o ngnndaa ka leydi? Kaa ko ko [tun] e konngol? Ko woni, heeferЙ“e Й“een cuЙ—inanaa ma pewje maЙ“Й“e Й—een, Й“e sakkaa(pala) e laawol ngol. Kala mo Alla majjini, peewnoowo alanaa mo."
  13,34,"Hino woodani Й“e lepte ka nguurndam aduna. Pellet ko lepte laakara Й—en Й“uri sattude, alanaa Й“e daЙ—ndoowo (Й“e) e Alla."
  13,35,"Sugu Aljanna mo gooЕӢЙ—uЙ“e Й“een fodaa on: Caati no ila ley makko; Гұaamri makko Й—i ko duumiiЙ—um, e Й—owdi makko ndin. ЖҠuum ko battane Й“en gooЕӢЙ—uЙ“e, battane heeferbe non ko Yiite."
  13,36,"ЖҒeen Й“e mnn okki deftere ndeen, heЙ“e mbeltora Й—uum ko jippinaa e maaЙ—a. No e leЖҙЖҙi kon Й“en yeddooЙ“e yoga mayre. Maaku: "nganndee ko yamiraa-mi, ko nde reway-mi Alla hara mi sirkanaali mo. Ko e makko nodday-mi, ko ka makko kadi woni ruttorde am"."
  13,37,"Ko wano nii min njippiniri nde Гұaawoore (e haala) aarabu. Pellet si a jokkii mbeleeЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en Й“aawo nde ganndal ari e maa, alanaa ma gaanin Alla immorde e giЙ—o, wanaa daЙ—ndoowo."
  13,38,"GooЕӢЙ—ii min nulii nulaaЙ“e ado maa, min waЙ—ani Й“e genndiraaЙ“e e geyngol. Haananaa NulaaЙ—o nde o addata Aaya, si wanaa e sakkitoore Alla. Hino woodani kala lajal caati.(happu binndaЙ—o)"
  13,39,"Alla no meha (momta)ko Muuyi o tabatina (ko o wela), ko ka makko yumma defte Й—een woni."
  13,40,"Si minn kolliima yogo e ko min fodi Й“e, maa Mmin hunnu maa (ado mun), anndu ko fawi maa ko yottingol, haasboore nde ko minen fawtii."
  13,41,"E Й“ee nji'aani wonВҙde miЙ—en ngara e leydi ndin, min ustira ndi ka seraaji mayri? Alla no Гұaawa, alaa wurtinoowo Гұaawoore makko nden, ko o yacciiЙ—o (jaawЙ—o)Гұaawoore."
  13,42,"GooЕӢЙ—ii Й“en adinooЙ“e Й“e pewjaniino (AnnabaaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e); ko Alla non pewje Й—een fow keeranii. Homo anndi kala woЕӢkii faggitotoo. Arma heefereЙ“e Й“een ngannda ko hommbo battane galle (moЖҙЖҙe) woodani."
  13,43,"HeeferЙ“e Й“een heЙ“eo mbi'a: "wonaa a nulaaЙ—o". Maaku: "Alla yonii seedee hakkunde am e mon, e Й“en jogitiiЙ“e ganndal deftere ndeen"."
  14,1,"Alif, Laam, Raa. (Ndee ko) deftere nde min njppini e maaЙ—a, fii yo yaltinir yimЙ“e Й“een e niЙ“e faade e annoora, e duЕӢayee Joomi maЙ“Й“e, haa e laawol pooluЙ—o, jettiniiЙ—o."
  14,2,"Alla, oon oo woodani kala ko woni kammuuli e ka leydi. Bone woodani yedduЙ“e Й“een, immorde e lepte cattuЙ—e."
  14,3,"ЖҒeen Й“urdinooЙ“e nguurndam aduna Й—am e dow laakara, Й“e paddoo e laawol Alla ngol, Й“e Й—aЙ“Й“ana ngol ooГұorgal. ЖҒeen Й—oon ngonii e majjere woЙ—Й—unde."
  14,4,"Min nuliraali nulaaЙ—o (woo), si wanaa e Й—emngal yimЙ“e makko Й“een, fii no o Й“annginirana Й“e. Alla no majjina on mo muuyi, o fewna on Mo o muuyi. Ko KaЕӢko woni pooluЙ—o, ГұeeГұuЙ—o."
  14,5,"GooЕӢЙ—ii min nulirii Muusaa aayeeje amen Й—en [wi'ugol Mo]: "Yaltin yimЙ“e maa Й“en e niЙ“e faade e annoora, nganndintinaa Й“e ГұalЙ—i Alla Й—iin". Pellet hino e Й—uum, tasakuyeeji kala munyoowo, jettoowo (dokke)."
  14,6,"(JaЕӢto) tuma nde Muusaa maakannoo yimЙ“e makko Й“en: "ciftoree dokke Alla on e mooЙ—on, tuma o daЙ—ndunoo on e yimЙ“e Fir'awna Й“e no defaynoo on lepte bonВҙЙ—e. HeЙ“e kirsa Й“iЙ—Й“e mon (worЙ“e) Й“e ngacca (Й“iЙ—Й“e) mon rewЙ“e. Wonii e Й—uum mo'on, jarrabuyee mawЙ—o immorde ka Joomi mon","
  14,7,"e tuma nde Joomi maa anndinnoo: "Pellet si on njettii, ma mi Й“eydan on. Si on njeddii non, pellet lepte am Й—een ko caЙ—tuЙ—e"."
  14,8,"Muusaa maaki: "Si on njeddii, onon e wonЙ“e ka leydi Й“en fow, [ngnndon] pellet Alla ko Galo jettiniiЙ—o"."
  14,9,"E kumpite Й“een adinooЙ“e on araani on, yimЙ“e Nuuhu e Aadi, e Samuuda e Й“een wonunooЙ“e Й“aawo maЙ“- Й“e, anndaa Й“e si wanaa Alla? NulaaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en addanii Й“e Й“anngannduyeeji, Й“e ndutti juuЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—een ka kunndule maЙ“Й“e, Й“e mbii: "minen min yed- dii ko nulidaЙ—on e mun kon, minen, miЙ—en e cikkitii e ko noddoton men e mun sikkitiiЙ“e"."
  14,10,"NulaaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“een maaki: "E hara sikke no e fii Alla, puЙ—Й—uЙ—o kammuuli Й—iin e leydi ndin, homo nodda on fii yo O haforan on yoga e bakkatuuji mon, homo neeЙ“nana on haa e lajal innaangal?" ЖҒe mbi'i: "On ngonaani si wanaa Й“anndinke yeru amen. HoЙ—on faandii nde sakkotoЙ—on(falotodon) men e kon ko baabiraaЙ“e amen ndewatnoo. ngaddanee amen hujja Й“annguЙ—o"."
  14,11,"NulaaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en maakani Й“e: "[Ko goonga], min ngonaani si wanaa Й“anndiЕӢkooЙ“e yeru mon, kono Alla no moЖҙЖҙoo e mo o muuyi e jeyaaЙ“e makko Й“een. Laatanaaki min nde min ngaddana on hujja, si wanaa e duЕӢayee Alla. Ko e Alla gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“een pawotoo."
  14,12,"Ko haЙ—ata men nde pawotoo e Alla, gooЕӢЙ—ii o fewnii min (e) laawi amen? Ma min muГұГұo e kon ko lorroton men. Ko e Alla gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“en pawotoo"."
  14,13,"ЖҒeen yedduЙ“e (kadi) mbi'ani nulaaЙ“e mun Й“en: "Ma min njaltin on ka leydi amen, maa nduttoЙ—on e diina amen". Joomi maЙ“Й“e wahayini e maЙ“Й“e: "Ma min kalku tooГұuЙ“e Й“een,"
  14,14,"Ma lin koЙ—nu on e leydi ndin Й“aawo maЙ“Й“e. ЖҠuum ko wonanВҙde on kulЙ—o daroyagol yeeso Am, o huli kammbaa am on".(sapporam.)"
  14,15,"ЖҒe Й—aЙ“Й“i uddita, sooyi kala dunndaranke ЖҙagguЙ—o."
  14,16,"Jahannama no yesso makko, himo yarniree ndiyam mbordi ЖҙiiЖҙiiri,"
  14,17,"homo wooЙ“a Й—am, e Й—eЙ“ataa Й“ennugol Й—am. maayde ndeen ardana mo e kala nokku, kono o wonaani maayoowo. Hara no yeeso makko lepte cattuЙ—e."
  14,18,"Ko woni sifa Й“een yedduЙ“e Joomi mun, kuuЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en, ko wano ndoondi ndi henndu tiiЙ—i e mun, e Гұalaande bippoore. ЖҒe hettoytaa huunde e ko Й“e paggitinoo. Ko Й—uum woni majjere wonЙ—Й—unde."
  14,19,"E a yi'aani Alla tagirii kammuuli Й—iin e leydi ndiin goonga? Si o muuyii, o ittay on o adda tagoore hesre."
  14,20,"Й—uum wonaani caЙ—tuЙ—um ka Alla."
  14,21,"ЖҒe peeГұana Alla Й“e denndaangal. Lo'uЙ“e Й“en mbi'ana townitinooЙ“e Й“en: "Minen min ngonanno on jokkuЙ“e. Taw si on nduncanat amen e lepte Alla Й—en goЙ—Й—um?" ЖҒen mbi'a: "Sinno Alla fewnuno amen, men pewnatno on. Hino fota e amen, si en Й—enЖҙi maa si en muГұГұi; daЙ—irde alanaa en"."
  14,22,"Seytaane wi'a, tuma fiyaaku on Гұaawaa: "Pellet Alla fodiino on fodoore goonga; mi podanli on mi lunndii on. Alanaa kam e mo'on immorde e hujja, si wanaa mi nodii on, on njaabike kam. Wata on felam; pelee ko'e mon. Wanaa mi faabotooЙ—o on; ngoanaa on faabotooЙ“e kam. Mi yeddii ko kafidunoЙ—on mi kon [e Alla] ado (hannde)". Pellet, tooГұooЙ“e Й“een, hino woodani Й“e lepte muusЙ—e."
  14,23,"GooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e ngolli moЖҙЖҙuЙ—i Й“en naatnaa e Aljannaaji, caatli hino ila ley majji, ko Й“e duumorayЙ“e ton e duЕӢayee Joomi maЙ“Й“e. Hiwraandu maЙ“Й“e ndun ton ko: "Salaam" (Kisiyee)."
  14,24,"E a yi'aani ko honno Alla piyiri misal konngol laaЙ“ungol, ko wano leggal welngal, binndeere maggal ko tabituЙ—i, caalЙ—i maggal no ka weeyo?"
  14,25,"Hangal okkira dimЙ—e maggal on tuma kala, e duЕӢayee Joomi maggal. Alla no piyana yimЙ“e Й“en mise, belejo'o Й“e waajitoto."
  14,26,"Ko woni kadi misal konngol coЙ“ungol, ko wano leggal soЙ“ungal, irtaangal ka hoore-leydi, ngal alanaa Й—uum ГұiiЙ“irde."
  14,27,"Alla no tabintinira gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“een konngol tabitungol, ka nguurandam aduna e ka laakara. Alla no majjina tooГұooЙ“e Й“een. Alla no waЙ—a ko o muuyi."
  14,28,"E a tinaali Й“een waЙ—titirЙ“e dokke Alla Й—in keeferaaku, Й“e mbeerni yimЙ“e Й“en galle halkaare."
  14,29,"Jahannama, heЙ“e naata nge, nge bonii ГұiiЙ“irde!"
  14,30,"ЖҒe mbaЙ—ani Alla yerondiraaЙ—i fii yo Й“e majjin (yimЙ“e Й“en) e laawol Alla ngol. Maaku: "ndakmitee, pellet ruttorde mon ndeen ko ka Yiite"."
  14,31,"Maakan jeyaaЙ“e am ngooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“een, yo Й“e Гұinnu juulde Й“e wintoo e kon ko Men arsiki Й“e gunndoo e kene, ado nde arata Й“e Гұalaande nde njeeygu alaa e mun wanaa weldigal."
  14,32,"Ko Alla woni takЙ—o kammuuli Й—in e leydi, O jippiniri ka kammu ndiyam; o yaltiniri Й—am dimЙ—e arsike wonanВҙde on. o eltirani on laaЙ—e Й—en, fii yo Й—e ndogir ka maayo e duЕӢayee makko. O eltani on kadi caatlЙ—i Й—in."
  14,33,"O eltani on naange ngeen e lewru nduun dogooji Й—iЙ—i. O eltani on jemma on e Гұalawma on."
  14,34,"O okki on e kala ko toriЙ—on mo. Si on linmii neemaaji Alla Й—iin, on moftataaЙ—i. Pellet neЙ—Й—aЕӢke oon ko kee wЙ—o tooГұe, keewuЙ—o jeddugol."
  14,35,"(JaЕӢto) kadi tuma nde Ibraahiima maakunoo: "Joomi am, waЙ—u ndee saare hooliinde, ndaЙ—ndaa kam e Й“iЙ—Й“e am Й“en nde men ndewata sanamuuji."
  14,36,"Joomi am, kaГұji (sanamuuji Й—iin), Й—i majjinii ko Й—uuЙ—i e yimЙ“e Й“en. Kala jokkuЙ—o kam, oon Й—oon ko jeyidaaЙ—o e am. Kala noon jedduЙ—o kam, haray Aan ko A jaafotooЙ—o, jurmotooЙ—o."
  14,37,"Joomi amen, min mi hoЙ—inii yoga e Й“iЙ—Й“e am Й“en e aynde nde wonaa remotoonde, ka Suudu Maa Hormanteeru, - Joomi amen - fii yo Й“e ГұiiЙ“nu juulde. WaЙ— Й“erЙ—e yimЙ“e Й“en no yiiloo e maЙ“Й“e, arsikaaЙ“e dimЙ—e, belaje'o Й“e njetta."
  14,38,"Joomi amen, pellet, Aan haЙ—a anndi ko min cuuЙ—i e ko min peГұГұini: hay huunde suuЙ—otaako Alla ka leydi wonaa ka kammu."
  14,39,"Jettooje ngoodanii Alla, oon jedduЙ—uЙ—o kam e hoore mawngu, Ismaa'iila e Ishaaqa. Pellet, Joomi am ko nanoowo du'aa."
  14,40,"Joomi am, waЙ—an ГұiiЙ“noowo juulde e Й“eynugol am ngol. Joomi amen, jaЙ“ toraare am nden."
  14,41,"Joomi amen, haforanam min e jipnaaЙ“e am Й“een e gooЕӢЙ—imЙ“e Й“en, Гұalnde Гұaawoore nden dorotoo"."
  14,42,"Wata sikku Alla ko belsindiiЙ—o e ko tooГұooЙ“e Й“een ngollata. Anndu ko o neeЙ“niranta Й“e, ko haa e Гұalaande nde gite saafotoo e mun."
  14,43,"Ko Й“e heГұiiЙ“e, ЕӢallimЙ“e ko'e maЙ“Й“e, ndaarЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—een yiltotaako e maЙ“Й“e, Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—een ko jeewЙ—e."
  14,44,"Jeertniri yimЙ“e Й“en Гұalaande nde lepte Й—een arata Й“e, tooГұЙ“e Й“een mi'a: "Joomi amen, neeЙ“nan amen haa lajal Й“aЙ—iingal, min nootoo noddaanndu Maa, min njokka NulaaЙ“e Й“een". E on laatanooki on ngoondiino ado (hannde) alanaa on iwugol (tion)?"
  14,45,"KoЙ—Й—Й—on e koЙ—orli Й“een tooГұuЙ“e ko'e mun. ЖҒanngani on ko honno min mbaЙ—noo Й“e, Men piyani on yeruuji"
  14,46,"GooЕӢЙ—ii Й“e pewjii feere maЙ“Й“e nden. Ko ta Alla feere maЙ“Й“e ndeen woni, hay si feere maЙ“Й“e nden ittayno (Й—oofatno) pelle Й—een."
  14,47,"Wata a sikku Alla ko luunndotooЙ—o fodoore makko (nde O fodi) nulaaЙ“e makko Й“een. Pellet, Alla ko poolЙ—o, Jom yottagol,"
  14,48,"Гұalnde leydi ndiin waЙ—titirtee leydi goo, e kammuuli Й—iin, Й“e feeГұana Alla, Bajjo oon, poolЙ—o On."
  14,49,"A yi'ay bonЙ“e Й“een nden Гұalnde, ko jokkindiraaЙ“e e kolombooje."
  14,50,"Dolokkaaji maЙ“Й“e Й—iin ko mbullam feewnira, Yiite ngeen no sudda geece maЙ“Й“e Й—een."
  14,51,"Fii yo Alla yoЙ“itu kala woЕӢkii ko ko faggitii. Pellet, Alla ko jaawuЙ—o hasboore."
  14,52,"Ndee (Alqur'aanaare) ko yottinoore yimЙ“e Й“een fii yo Й“e waajitornde, e yooЙ“e nganndu kadi, wonВҙde KaЕӢko ko o deweteeЙ—o Gooto, e fii yo joomiraaЙ“e haqqillaaji Й“ren waajitor."
  15,1,"Alif, Laam, Raa. Й—een ko aayeeje deftere e janngeteende Й“annginnde."
  15,2,"Na waawi heeferЙ“e Й“en njeloyto sinno Й“e laatino juulЙ“e."
  15,3,"Accu Й“e, Й“e Гұaama Й“e dakmitoo, yela soklina Й“e; arma Й“e nganndoya."
  15,4,"Min kalkaani saare woo, si wanaa hara no woodani nde happu ganndaaЙ—o."
  15,5,"Mofte woo adotaako lajal mun, Й“e neeЙ“nantaake kadi."
  15,6,"ЖҒe mbi'i: "Ko aan yo mo deftere nden jippinaa e mun, an ko a peetuЙ—o."
  15,7,"Ko haЙ—no addanaa men maleyikaaji si a laatike gooЕӢЙ—uЙ—o?""
  15,8,"Min njippinirtaa maleykaaji si wonaa fii goonga; Й“e wonataa ontuma, neeЙ“nanteeЙ“e."
  15,9,"Minen min njippinii deftere nden, minen kadi ko min reenooЙ“e nde."
  15,10,"GooЕӢЙ—ii min nuliino ado maa, e leЖҙЖҙi adinooЙ“e."
  15,11,"NulaaЙ—o (woo) araani e maЙ“Й“e si wonaa Й“e njalkitay mo."
  15,12,"Ko wano nii min naadiri Й—um e Й“erЙ—e bonЙ“e Й“een."
  15,13,"ЖҒe ngooЕӢЙ—intaa nde, gooЕӢЙ—ii sunna aramЙ“e Й“en yawtiino."
  15,14,"Hay si minn udditanno Й“e damal ka kammu, Й“e mbaЙ—tini hiЙ“e Жҙawra heen."
  15,15,"Й“e mbi'ayno: "nganndee gite amen Й—een kippa. Wurin ko min yimЙ“e wilaaЙ“e"."
  15,16,"GooЕӢЙ—ii min mbaЙ—ii ka kammu koode, min cuЙ—irani Й—e ndaarooЙ“e."
  15,17,"Min ndeeni mbo e kala seytaane diiwaaЙ—o."
  15,18,"Si wonaa oon guujjuЙ—o nanЙ—e, o jokkintina hoodere-fiЙ—aynnde jalЙ“unde."
  15,19,"Leydi ndin, min weerti ndi min werlii e mayri pelle, min puuЙ—ini e mayri kala huunde eЙ“Й“aande."
  15,20,"Min mbaЙ—ani on e mayri wuurirЙ—e, e Й“een Й“e on laatanooki arsikooЙ“e Й—um."
  15,21,"Huunde alaa si wanaa marga mun ko ka amen, min njippintaa Й—uum si wanaa e eЙ“Й“oore anndaande."
  15,22,"Min ngurti keneeli Й—iin hawrondirooji e duule; min njippiniri ka kammu ndiyam min njarniri on Й—aam, wonaa onon mari Й—am."
  15,23,"Ko minen kadi ngoni ko wuurnata min mbara, ko minen ngoni ronooЙ“e Й“een."
  15,24,"GooЕӢЙ—ii min nganndii adiiЙ“e e mon Й“en GooЕӢЙ—ii min nganndii sakkitiiЙ“e Й“en."
  15,25,"Pellet, Joomi maa, ko KaЕӢko mooЙ“oyta Й“e. KaЕӢko ko o ГұeeГұo, gannduЙ—o."
  15,26,"GooЕӢЙ—ii min tagii neЙ—Й—aЕӢke on e senЖҙayngal, e (cenlatngal) loopal-Й“alewal Й“owrungal."
  15,27,"E jinnaaji Й—in, min tagiri ndu ko adii, e yiite ooyunge."
  15,28,"JaЕӢto tuma nde Joomi maa daalannoo maleykaji'en: "min ko Mi tagiroowo Й“anndiЕӢke immorde e senЖҙayngal, e loopal-Й“alewal Й“owrungal"
  15,29,"si mi fotndiii mo, mi wuttii e makko ruuhu am on, haray suuyanee mo ko on sujjuЙ“e"."
  15,30,"Maleykajien fof cujji Й“e denndaangal."
  15,31,"si wonaa ibliisa, o salii tawdeede e sujjooЙ“e Й“en."
  15,32,"O daali: "eey ma ibliisa, e ko heЙ“ maa a laatodaaki e sujjuЙ“e Й“een?""
  15,33,"O wi'i: "mi wonatah sujjanoowo Й“anndinke mo taguЙ—aa immorde e senЖҙayngal, e loopal-Й“alewal Й“owrungal"."
  15,34,"O daali: "Yaltu toon, aan o ko a diiwaaЙ—o,"
  15,35,"pellet, kuddi fawike e ma haa Гұande njoЙ“di diina"."
  15,36,"O wi'i : "joomi am, neeЙ“nitanam haa Гұande ndeЙ“e immintintee"."
  15,37,"O daali:"Aa,ko a jeyaaЙ—o e neeЙ“nitanteeЙ“e Й“en."
  15,38,"haa e Гұalaande happu ganndaaЙ—o"."
  15,39,"O wi'i: "Joomi am, sabu ko mbewnuЙ—aa mi kon, ma mi cuЙ—inan Й“e ka leydi, ma mi bewnu Й“e fow maЙ“Й“e,"
  15,40,"si wanaa jeyaaЙ“e maa, laЙ“Й“inaaЙ“e Й“en e maЙ“Й“e"."
  15,41,"O daali: "nogol Й—oo ko laawol ka am poocciingol."
  15,42,"Pellet, jeyaaЙ“e am Й“en, a alanaa Й“e cemmbe, si wonaa Й“een bewЙ“e jokkuЙ“e ma."
  15,43,"Pellet Jahannama on wonii fodoore maЙ“Й“e Й“e fof."
  15,44,"Henge mari dame jeeЙ—iЙ—i; damal kala e majje no mari geЙ—al senndaangal."
  15,45,"Pellet, gooЕӢЙ—uЙ“e Й“een wonii e aljannaaji e Й“ulli."
  15,46,""Naatiree Й—i e kisial, ko on hooliiЙ“e"."
  15,47,"Min Й—oofi kala ko woni e Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e e konnaagu(cokotaagal): Й“e ngonti musiЙ—Й“e fewtondirЙ“e e danЙ—e."
  15,48,"Tampere heЙ“ataa Й“e toon,, Й“e ngonah kadi yaltintee Й“e toon."
  15,49,"Yeetito jeyaaЙ“e am Й“en, ko miin woni jaafotooЙ—o, jurmtooЙ—o On"
  15,50,"e wonnde lepte am Й—een, ko Й—en ngoni lepte muusЙ—e Й—en."
  15,51,"haЙ“ru Й“e kadi fii hoЙ“Й“e Ibraahiima Й“een,"
  15,52,"Tuma Й“e naatunoo ka makko Й“e mbi'i: "Salaam (Kisiyee mon)". O maaki: "minen ko min Й—enЖҙii Й“e on"."
  15,53,"ЖҒe mbi'i: "Wota a faay, minen miЙ—en mbeltinirma [Й“iЙ—Й—o] gorko ganndo"."
  15,54,"O maaki: "E on mbeltiniratkam [Й—uum] e hoore ko mi naywi ko? E ko mbeltinirton mi?""
  15,55,"ЖҒe mbi'i: "min mbeltininirii ma goonga, wota a jeye e taЖҙiiЙ“e Й“een"."
  15,56,"O maaki: "Ko hommbo taЖҙotoo e yurmeende Joomi mun nden, si wonaa majjuЙ“e Й“een?""
  15,57,"O maaki: "Ko woni fii mon, onon Й“ee imminaaЙ“e?"(nuleeЙ“e.)"
  15,58,"ЖҒe mbi'i: "minen min nulaa ko e yimЙ“e bonЙ“e,"
  15,59,"si wonaa Й“eynguure Luuti nde, pellet ko min daЙ—ndooЙ“e Й“e denndaangal,"
  15,60,"si wonaa debbo makko on". min koddirii oon Й—on ko jeyaaЙ—o e halketeeЙ“e Й“en."
  15,61,"Nde imminaaЙ“e Й“en ngaruno ka Й“eynguure Luuti,"
  15,62,"O maaki: "onon ko on yimЙ“e faaytaa Й“e"."
  15,63,"ЖҒe mbi'i: "Wurin min ngaddanii ma ko Й“e ngonnoo e sikkitaade kon."
  15,64,"Min ngaddanii ma goonga kan, pellet ko min goonЕӢЙ—uЙ“e."
  15,65,"Yahdu e Й“eynguure maa ndeen ka taЖҙitannde jem- ma, jokkaa Й“aawo maЙ“Й“e; hara gooto e mo'on yeЖҙЖҙitaaki, ndewon ka njamiraЙ—on"."
  15,66,"Min anndini mo on fiyaaku: wonnВҙde wattannde Й“ee Й—oo, ko taЖҙeteeЙ—um ka subaka."
  15,67,"YimЙ“e saare nden ngri heЙ“e mbeltoro."
  15,68,"O maaki: "Й“ee Й—oo ko hoЙ“Й“e am, wata on wirtam.(cuhritam)."
  15,69,"Kulee Alla, wota on koynam"."
  15,70,"ЖҒe mbi'i: "e min kaЙ—aali ma [weernugol] tagoore nden?""
  15,71,"O maaki: "Й“ee Й—oo ko jiwЙ“e am, si wonii ko on waЙ—ooЙ“e [goЙ—Й—um]!""
  15,72,"Mi woondirii nguurndam maa! Й“e ngonii e siwrugol maЙ“Й“e heЙ“e mbeemi."
  15,73,"Haacaango ngoon nanngiri Й“e ka puЙ—al,"
  15,74,"Min mbЙ—tiniri dow mayre on ley mayre, min saaЖҙini(toЙ“ri) e maЙ“Й“e kaaЖҙe iwruЙ—e e loope juЙ—aaЙ—e."
  15,75,"Wonii e Й—uum, maandeeji wonanВҙde Й“en teskotooЙ“e."
  15,76,"Pellet, Й—een [ca'e] no e jurol(bolol) ГұiiЙ“ngol."
  15,77,"Wonii e Й—uum, maande wonanВҙde Й“een gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e."
  15,78,"GooЕӢЙ—ii yimЙ“e fitaare(sutu) Й“een [kadi] ko tooГұЙ“e."
  15,79,"Min yoЙ“tii e maЙ“Й“e. Pellet Й—een [ca'e] Й—iЙ—i ngonii e laawol Й“anngungol."
  15,80,"GooЕӢЙ—i yimЙ“e (aynde) Hijiri nden njeddii nulaaЙ“e Й“een."
  15,81,"Min ngaddani Й“e aayeeje amen Й—en, Й“e laatii Й—uurniiЙ“e Й—e."
  15,82,"Hari heЙ“e lesoynoo e pelle Й—een cuuЙ—i, ko Й“e hooliiЙ“e."
  15,83,"Haacaango ngoon nanngi Й“e ka subaka."
  15,84,"NafaaniЙ“e Й—uum ko Й“e laatinoo heЙ“e paggitoo."
  15,85,"Min tagiraani kammuuli Й—iin e leydi ndin, e ko woni hakkunde majji kon, si wonaa e goonga. Pellet, darngal ngal ko arayngal! yaafora jaafaggol labaangol."
  15,86,"Tabitii ko Joomi maa woni TakЙ—o, gannduЙ—o."
  15,87,"GooЕӢЙ—ii min okkii ma jeeЙ—iЙ—i ummorde Й—immitaa-ngol, e Alqur'aanaare mawnde nden."
  15,88,"Wata a Й“amtu gite maa Й—en e neemaaji Й—i lin dakmiti Й“e e mum en, wata a sunu e maЙ“Й“e, lesЙ—in becce maa Й—en gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“en."
  15,89,"Maaku: "min ko mi jertinoowo Й“annginoowo"."
  15,90,"Wano min njppinirnoo e senndooЙ“e [defte Alla] Й“en [lepte],"
  15,91,"ЖҒeen waЙ—Й“e Alqur'aanaare nden geЙ—e-geЙ—e."
  15,92,"Mi wooЙ—ndirii Joomi maa! Ma min laЙ“ndoyo Й“e fof maЙ“Й“e."
  15,93,"fii ko Й“e ngonnoo e huuwude.(gollude)."
  15,94,"FeГұГұin ko njamira-Й—aa kon, Й—uurno-Й—aa sirkooЙ“e Й“een."
  15,95,"minen min njonii ma e Й“en jalkitooЙ“e."
  15,96,"ЖҒeen waЙ—dooЙ“e e Alla deweteeЙ—o goo. arma ka Й“e ngannda."
  15,97,"GooЕӢЙ—ii miЙ—en nganndi wonВҙde bernde maa nde na Й“iЙ—tora ko Й“e kaalata kon."
  15,98,"Subbhinor yettugol Joomi maa, laato-daa e sujjooЙ“e Й“ee."
  15,99,"ndewaa Joomi haa yananeede (maayde) ara e maa."
  16,1,"Yamiroore Alla nde ari wota on hawjan nde. senaaree woodanii mo! o toowii e ko Й“e cirkata.ko."
  16,2,"Homo jippinira maleykaaji Й—i e wayhu on e yamiroore makko, dow mo muuyi e jeyaaЙ“e makko Й“een, wonВҙde : "Jertinree wiide deweteeЙ—o alaa si wonaa min. Kulee kam"."
  16,3,"O tagiri kammuuli Й—iin e leydi ndin goonga. o toowii e ko Й“e sirkoobe cirkata ko."
  16,4,"O tagiri neЙ—Й—aЕӢke iwde e toЙ“Й“ere (maniiyu); jaka yoo kaЕӢko ko wennjoowo Й“annguЙ—o.peeГұЙ—o"
  16,5,"NeemoraaЙ—i Й—in, o tagani on Й—i; no e majji nguli nugguki e nafooje. Ko e majji kadi Гұaamoton."
  16,6,"Hino woodani on e majji cuЙ—aari, tuma njofnoton Й—i e tuma oornoton Й—i."
  16,7,"HiЙ—i ndoono doЕӢle mon naЙ“a e leydi ndi on njotto- tanooko si wanaa e tampere pittaali. Pellet, Joomi mon ko O YurmeteeЙ—o HinnotooЙ—o."
  16,8,"E pucci, e mbam-pucci, e mbabbi, fii yo on mbaЙ—Й—o Й—i, e cuЙ—aari. Himo taga kadi ko on nganndaa."
  16,9,"Ko Alla woodani Й“anngingol laawol poocciingol ngol, no e majji ngol feewaani. Si o muuyuno, o fewnat on denndaangal."
  16,10,"Ko KaЕӢko woni jippinirЙ—o ndiyam ka kammu, hino woodani on e majjam njaram, leЙ—Й—e no (yalta) e majjam, ko e majjam kadi oornoton."
  16,11,"Homo fuЙ—nirana on Й—am aawruuji, nebbanteeje, e tamarooje, e inabuuje, e kala dimЙ—e.Й“esnoje wonii e Й—uum, tasakuyee wonanВҙde yimЙ“e miijitotooЙ“e."
  16,12,"O eltani on jemma on e Гұalawma on; naange ngen e lewru nduun. Koode Й—een kadi ko eltiraaЙ—e yamiroore makko. Wonii e Й—uum, tasakuyeeji wonanВҙde yimЙ“e haqqilooЙ“e."
  16,13,"E ko o tagani on kon ka leydi ceertuЙ—um nooneeji. wonii e Й—uum, tasakuyee wonanВҙde yimЙ“e waajitoratЙ“e."
  16,14,"Ko KaЕӢko woni eltanЙ—o on maayo ngon fii yo on Гұaam e maggo teewu keccu, yaltinon e maggo cuЙ—aari ndi Й“ornotoЙ—on. A yi'ay laaЙ—e no feЖҙЖҙa e maggo, e fii yo on Й—aЙ“Й“u e Й“ural makko ngal, belejo'o, on njettat [mo]."
  16,15,"O tuti penle ka leydi fii wata Й—e dillidu e mo'on, e caatli, e Й—ate, belejo'o on peeway."
  16,16,"e maandeeji [laawi]. Koode Й—en heЙ“e Й—owora Й—e."
  16,17,"E hara tagoowo on wa'ay wa on tagataa? E on mbaactotaako?"
  16,18,"Si on limtii doke Alla Й—e, on moftataa Й—i. Pellet, Alla ko jaafotooЙ—o, jurmotooЙ—o."
  16,19,"Alla no anndi ko cuuЙ—oton e ko peГұГұinton."
  16,20,"ЖҠiin Й—i Й“e ndewata ga ni Alla, Й—i tagataa hay huunde, kaЕӢji tigi ko Й—i tageteeЙ—i."
  16,21,"KoЙ—i maayЙ—i Й—i nguuraani, Й“e so'aa-anndude (Й“etinaani)de Й“e mmintintee."
  16,22,"deweteeЙ—o mon on ko deweteeЙ—o gooto. Й“een Й“e ngooЕӢЙ—inaa laakara, Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en ko jedduЙ—e, Й“en ko townitiiЙ“e."
  16,23,"Sikke alaa wonВҙde Alla no anndi ko Й“e cuuЙ—ata e ko Й“e peГұГұinta. KaЕӢko O yiЙ—aa townitiiЙ“e Й“en."
  16,24,"Si Й“e mbianaama : "Ko holЙ—um Joomi mon jippini?" ЖҒe mbi'a: "Ko tinndi adinooЙ“e!"."
  16,25,"Fii yo Й“e ndoondo bakkaatuuji maЙ“Й“e Й—iin fof Гұande Darngal, e bakkaatuuji Й“een Й“e majjinirta ko aldaa e ganndal; nganndee bonii ko Й“e ndonndoytoo."
  16,26,"GooЕӢЙ—ii Й“een adinooЙ“e Й“e pewjiino, Alla jirbiniri mahdeele maЙ“Й“e Й—een ka doose. Kippoodi ndin yanti e maЙ“Й“e, lepte Й—en ardirani Й“e nokku ka Й“e so'aa-aanndude(.tinaani.)"
  16,27,"Refti Гұande darngal, O hoynoyayЙ“e, O wi'anaЙ“e: Ko holto kafidaaЙ—i am Й—iin Й—i haЙ“iraynoЙ—on fii mum?" Й“een okkaaЙ“e ganndal mbi'a: "Koyeera on hannde e bone on wonii e heeferЙ“e Й“en"."
  16,28,"ЖҒeen Й“en maleykaaji Й“en hunnata, tooГұuЙ“e ko'e-mun, Й“e werloo jebbilraare, (Й“e mbia): "min ngoonaa- no gollatnooЙ“e ko boni!" -"wonaa non woniri, pellet Alla ko nganduЙ—o ko huuwaynoЙ—on".(ngollatnЙ—on.)"
  16,29,"Naatiree dame Jahannama Й—en luttugol ton. Nge bonii ГұaaЖҙorde wonanВҙde townitiiЙ“e Й“en."
  16,30,"Wi'anee Й“een gooЕӢЙ—uЙ“e: "Ko holЙ—uum Joomi mon jippini?" ЖҒe mbi'a: "Ko moЖҙЖҙere". Hono woodani Й“en moЖҙЖҙinЙ“e aduna Й—oo moЖҙЖҙere; pellet ko saare laakara nden Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude. nde moЖҙЖҙii saare gooЕӢЙ—uЙ“e Й“en."
  16,31,"Aljannaaji duumal, heЙ“e naati Й—i, caatli no ila ley majji. Hino woodani Й“e toon kala ko Й“e paaletee; ko wano nii Alla yoЙ“irta gooЕӢЙ—uЙ“e Й“en."
  16,32,"ЖҒeen Й“e maleykaaji Й—i mbarata hara ko Й“e laaЙ“Й“e- Й“e mbi'an [Й“en]: "Kisiyee wonii e mon! Naatiree Aljanna on, sabu ko ngollatnoЙ—on kon".e"
  16,33,"Hara [Й“ee sirkooЙ“e fenna] hino habbitii si wonaa nde maleykaaji Й—i ngarata e maЙ“Й“e, maa yami- roore Joomi maa ndeen ara? Ko wano noon Й“en adinooЙ“e Й“e waЙ—irnoo. Alla tooГұaani Й“e; si ko woni, ko ko'e maЙ“Й“e Й“e wonnoo e tooГұuЙ“e."
  16,34,"Boneeji Й—i Й“e huuwi Й—in memi Й“en, kon ko Й“e njalkitatnoo jippii e maЙ“Й“e."
  16,35,"ЖҒeen sirkuЙ“e mbi'i: "Sinno Alla muuyuno, men ndewataano ga ni makko hay huunde, wonaa minen wanaa baabiraaЙ“e amen; min karmintaa- no gaanin makko hay huunde". Ko wano non adi- nooЙ“e Й“een gerdunoo. taw si no fawiiii nulaaЙ“e Й“en si wonaa jottingol Й“anngina?"
  16,36,"GooЕӢЙ—ii min imminii e kala mofte nulaaЙ—o, wonВҙde ndewee Alla, ngoЙ—Й—itoЙ—on bewnayЙ—i Й—in. Hino e maЙ“Й“e on Mo Alla feewni, hino e maЙ“Й“e kadi on mo majjere ndeen jojji e mum. Yiilee ka leydi, ndaaron ko honno battane yeddunooЙ“e Й“een wa'unoo."
  16,37,"Si a reerЙ—ii e peewal maЙ“Й“e, [anndu] pellet, Alla feewnataa on mo o majjini, alanaa Й“e kadi wallooЙ“e."
  16,38,"ЖҒe ngooЙ—ndirii Alla haЙ—tirde gooЙ—ndooje maЙ“Й“e: "Alla immintintaa on maayuЙ—o". Wanaa non! ЖҠuum ko fodoore goonga ka makko, ko woni tan, ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e yimЙ“e Й“e nganndaa."
  16,39,"(O immintiniroyay Й“e) fii yo O Й“annginan Й“e ko Й“e luutondiratnoo e mum. e fii yo Й“een yedduЙ“e anndu wonВҙde hari ko Й“e jeddunooЙ“e."
  16,40,"nganndee daalol amen wonanВҙde huunde, si min faandike nde, min mbianat nde tan: "Laato", nde laatoo."
  16,41,"ЖҒeen fernooЙ“e fii Alla, Й“aawo Й“e tooГұaama, ma min hoЙ—nu Й“e ka aduna (e weerde) moЖҙЖҙere. Pellet, ko njoЙ“di laakara ndin Й“uri mawnude, si tawno heЙ“e nganndi."
  16,42,"ЖҒeen muГұГұiiЙ“e, e tuugii e Joomi maЙ“Й“e."
  16,43,"Min nulaani ado maaЙ—a si wanaa worЙ“e, min wahayina e maЙ“Й“e. Lanndee yimЙ“e defte Й“een si wonii on nganndaa."
  16,44,"(Men nulirii Й“e) Й“anngudi e defte. min njippini e maaЙ—a janngeteende nden, fii yo a Й“annginan yimЙ“e Й“een kon ko jippinaa e maЙ“Й“e, belejo'o kamЙ“e Й“e miijitoto."
  16,45,"E hara Й“een fewjuЙ“e boneeji Й—iin kooli wonВҙde Alla munnirtaa Й“e leydi ndin, maa lepte Й—een ngardirana Й“e nokku mo Й“e so'aa-anndude,(Й“etinaani)."
  16,46,"maa o nanngira Й“e yahdu maЙ“Й“e, Й“e ngonaani laawotooЙ“e."
  16,47,"Maa O nanngira Й“e e hoore kulol. anndu Joomi mon ko YurmeteeЙ—o, jurmotooЙ—o."
  16,48,"E Й“ee njii'aani ko Alla tagi kon e huunde nde Й—owЙ—e mun yiiltondirta Гұaamo e nano, sujjangol Alla, hara ko Й—i jankiniiЙ—i."
  16,49,"Ko Alla woni ko sujjanta kala ko woni ka kammuuli e ka leydi, immorde e ruugayngel, e maleykaaji Й“en, kamЙ“e Й“e townitotaako.(mawnakintaako.)"
  16,50,"HeЙ“e kulira Joomi maЙ“Й“e, senngo dow maЙ“Й“e, heЙ“e mbaЙ—a ko Й“e njamiraa."
  16,51,"Alla daali: "Wota on njogito reweteeЙ“e Й—iЙ—o. ngnndee KaЕӢko ko O deeweteeЙ—o gooto. Ko min ngoni ko kuloton"."
  16,52,"Ko KaЕӢko woodani kala ko woni ka kammuuli e ka leydi; ko KaЕӢko Й—oftagol duumiingol tabitani. E ko ko woori Alla kuloton?"
  16,53,"Kala ko keЙ“Й—on e neema ko immorde ka Alla. refti si lorra memii on, ko Ka makko ngullitotoЙ—on."
  16,54,"Refti si o huncanii on lorra kan, e jaka fedde goo e mo'on, ko sirkanooЙ“e Joomi maЙ“Й“e."
  16,55,"Fii yo Й“e njeddu ko min ngokki Й“e kon. Awa ndakmitee, arma nganndon."
  16,56,"HeЙ“e mbaЙ—ana huunde nde Й“e nganndaa geЙ—al e kon ko min arsiki Й“e. Wallaahi! On lannditete e kon ko pekindotonoЙ—on."
  16,57,"HeЙ“e mbaЙ—ana Alla Й“iЙ—Й“e rewЙ“e. senaare woodanii mo HeЙ“e (waЙ—ana) ko'e maЙ“Й“e ko Й“e wooЙ—itii."
  16,58,"Si gooto e maЙ“Й“e weltiniraama Й“iЙ—Й—o debbo, yeeso makko ngon waЙ—tina wayliingo Й“alewo e, hara ko o suuЙ—-suno."
  16,59,"Homo suuЙ—ora yimЙ“e Й“een, sabu bone mo o weltiniraa oon. E o jogitoray mo e hoore koyeera kaa o uway mo ka leydi? ngannde bonii ko Й“e Гұaawata!"
  16,60,"Hino woodani Й“een Й“e ngooЕӢЙ—inaa laakara sifa bonЙ—o on. Ko Alla woodani sifa toowЙ—o on. Ko KaЕӢko kadi woni poolЙ—o, ГұeeГұЙ—o."
  16,61,"Si tawno Alla nanngitirayno yimЙ“e Й“een sabu tooГұe maЙ“Й“e Й—en, O ccataano e dow mayri ruugayngel. Ko woni tun, Himo neeЙ“tinana Й“e haa e lajal gannda- ngal. Si lajal maЙ“Й“e ngal arii, Й“e neeЙ“nantaake yonta Й“e adintinantaake."
  16,62,"HiЙ“e mbaЙ—ana Alla ko Й“e ngaГұanta [ko'e-maЙ“Й“e]. ЖҠemЙ—e maЙ“Й“e no cifoo fenaande, wonВҙde no woodani Й“e moЖҙЖҙere. Sikke alaa wonВҙde no woodani Й“e Yiite, e wonВҙde ko Й“e Й—aliiЙ“e."
  16,63,"Wallaahi! GooЕӢЙ—ii min nulii e mofte adinooЙ“e ma, seytaane cuЙ—ani Й“e ngolle maЙ“Й“e Й—en. Ko kaЕӢko woni giЙ—o maЙ“Й“e hannde, hino woodani Й“e lepte muusЙ—e."
  16,64,"Min jippiniraali deftere nden e maaЙ—a si wonaa fii yo a Й“annginan Й“e kon ko Й“e luutondiri e mun, kadi ko nde peewal, e yurmeende wonanВҙde yimЙ“e gooЙ—inЙ“e Й“een."
  16,65,"Alla jippinirii ka kammu ndiyam, O wuurnitiri Й—am leydi ndin Й“aawo ndi yoorde. wonii e Й—uum, maande wonanВҙde yimЙ“e nanooЙ“e."
  16,66,"Hino woodani on e neemoraaЙ—i Й—iin tasakuyee: miЙ—en njarna on e ko woni e deedi majji, - hakkunde coowo e ЖҙiiЖҙam - Й“iraaЙ—am laaЙ“uЙ—am, welЙ—am fii yarooЙ“e."
  16,67,"E dimЙ—e tamarooji e inabuuje, hoЙ—on jogitora Й—am siwran e arsike moЖҙЖҙo. wonii e Й—uum, maande wonanВҙde yimЙ“e haqqilooЙ“e."
  16,68,"Joomi maa wahayini e Гұaakii ngii, wonВҙde : "Jaggu ka pelle cuuЙ—i, e leЙ—Й—e Й—en, e kon ko Й“e caГұata."
  16,69,"Refti Гұaamaa e kala dimЙ—e Й—en, naaton e Й—ate Joomi mon newinaaЙ—e. Hino yalta e deedi majji [kannji Гұaaki Й—in], njaram seruЙ—am nooneeji mun, no e majjam cellal wonanВҙde yimЙ“e Й“en. Wonii e Й—uum, maande wonanВҙde yimЙ“e miijitotooЙ“e."
  16,70,"Alla tagii on, refti O hunnay on. Hino e mooЙ—on on rutteteeЙ—o e jaasuЙ—um nguurndam, fii wata o anndu huunde Й“aawo ganndal [makko aranal]. Pellet, Alla ko gannduЙ—o, kattanЙ—o."
  16,71,"Alla Й“urnii yoga mon e dow yoga ka arsike. ЖҒurnaaЙ“e Й“en ngonaani ruttirooЙ“e arsike maЙ“Й“e on e Й“een Й“e jeytiri Гұaame maЙ“Й“e Й—en haa Й“e pota e mayri. E ko dokke Alla on Й“e njeddata?"
  16,72,"Alla waЙ—iranii on e woЕӢkiiji mon Й—iin resondirЙ“e, o waЙ—irani on e resondiraaЙ“e mon Й“en Й“iЙ—Й“e e taaniraaЙ“e, o arsiki on immorde e laaЙ“uЙ—i. E ko meere nden Й“e gooЕӢЙ—inta? E ko neema Alla on kamЙ“e Й“e njeddata?"
  16,73,"HeЙ“e ndewa gaanin makko, huunde nde waawanaa Й“e (addude) arsike ka kammuuli e ka leydi hay huunde, Й—i kattanaaka [Й—um]."
  16,74,"Wata on mbaЙ—an Alla yerodniraaЙ—i. Pellet, Alla ko gannduЙ—o, onon on nganndaa."
  16,75,"Alla piyii misal maccuЙ—o jeyaaЙ—o, mo waawaa hay huunde, e on mo min arsiki immorde e amen arsike moЖҙЖҙo, hara on wintoo e Й—uum gunndoo e kene. Hara Й“een no fota? Yettooree woodanii Alla! Ko woni, ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e maЙ“Й“e anndaa."
  16,76,"Alla piyi kadi misal worЙ“e Й—iЙ—o: goЙ—Й—o e maЙ“Й“e ko mbobo, o waawaa hay huunde, kaЕӢko ko o donngal e hoore jeyЙ—o mo on; nokku kala ka on fewtiniri mo, o addataa moЖҙЖҙere; hara on Й—on fotay e on yamiroowo nuunЙ—al, hara himo e laawol pocciingol?"
  16,77,"Ko Alla woodani wirniiЙ—i kammmuuli Й—in e leydi ndin. Fiyaaku Darngal ngal wonaani si wonaa yeru kinЖҙan yiitere maa hara ko kaГұun Й“uri Й“aЙ—taade. Pellet, Alla ko kattanЙ—o kala huunde."
  16,78,"Alla yaltinii on ka deedi neeniraaЙ“e mon, on anndaa huunde, O waЙ—ani on nanЙ—e, e giiЙ—e e Й“erЙ—e, belejo'o, on yettay [Mo]."
  16,79,"E Й“e nji'aani colli Й—iin ko Й—i eltaaЙ—i ka weeyo kammu (wonВҙde) jogitaaki Й—i si wanaa Alla? Wonii e Й—uum, maandeeji wonanВҙde yimЙ“e gooЕӢЙ—inooЙ“e Й“en."
  16,80,"Alla waЙ—anii on e cuuЙ—i mon Й—in koЙ—orle, O waЙ—ani on e guri neemoraaЙ—i Й—in tillisaaji Й—i taggoton Гұande eggoton e Гұande koЙ—toton. No e leeЙ“i (baali) Й—in, e leeЙ“i (gelooЙ—i) Й—in e leeЙ“i (dammi) Й—iin ndaЙ—Й—udi [suudu] e dakmitorЙ—i haa e saanga."
  16,81,"Alla waЙ—anii on e ko o tagi kon Й—owЙ—e. O waЙ—ani on e pelle Й—een cuuЙ—orЙ—e. O waЙ—ani on comci daЙ—ndayЙ—i on nguleendi, e conci daЙ—ndayЙ—i on e hare mon. Ko wano nii o timminirta dokke makko Й—een e dow mon, mbelejo'o on njebbiloto."
  16,82,"Si Й“e nduЕӢtiima, anndu ko fawi maa, ko yottingol Й“anngina (peeГұngol.)"
  16,83,"HeЙ“e nganndi dokke Alla Й—een; refti Й“e njedda Й—e. Ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e maЙ“Й“e ko heeferЙ“e."
  16,84,"(JaЕӢto) kadi Гұande min immintinoyta e kala mofte seedeejo, refti Й“een yedduЙ“e sakkitoyantaake (ngantinagol), wanaa kamЙ“e ngoni ko Й—aЙ“Й“iroytee ruttitagol [e yarluyee Joomi maЙ“Й“e]."
  16,85,"Si tooГұuЙ“e Й“een ynj'ii lepte Й—een, Й“e hoynantaake, lepte wanaa Й“e neeЙ“nitanteeЙ“e."
  16,86,"Si sirkooЙ“e Й“een nji*i kafidaaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“een, Й“e mbi'a: "Joomi amen, ko Й—ii woni kafidaaЙ—i amen Й—i men ndrewaynoo gah ni ma". [KafidaaЙ—i maЙ“Й“e] Й—iin njilta e maЙ“Й“e konngol ngol: "Onon ko on fenooЙ“e"."
  16,87,"ЖҒe mbernoo e Alla ndeen Гұalnde jebbilaare, kon ko pekindotonoo majjira Й“e."
  16,88,"ЖҒeen yedduЙ“e Й“e paddii e laawol Alla ngol, min Й“eydiranii Й“e lepte e hoore lepte, sabu ko Й“e bonniraynoo kon."
  16,89,"(JaЕӢto kadi) Гұande minn immintinoyta e kala mofte ko seeditoo e maЙ“Й“e, jeyaaЙ—o e maЙ“Й“e, min ngadda maa [an Muhammadu] ko seeditoo e Й“ee Й—oo. min njippini e maaЙ—a deftere nden, ko nde Й“annginoore kala huunde, e peewal, e yurmeende, e welo-welo wonanВҙde juulЙ“e Й“en."
  16,90,"Tabitii Alla yamirii nuunЙ—al, e moЖҙЖҙingol, e moЖҙЖҙagol e joomiraaЙ“e Й“adondiral. homo haЙ—a gaay e pan-kare, e ko aГұinii, e bewre. homo waajoo on, mbeleejo'o, on mbaajitoray."
  16,91,"kuuЙ“nee ahadi Alla ndiin si on ahodaama, wata on pirtu gooЙ—ndooje Й—een Й“aawo Й—e tenntineede, gooЕӢЙ—ii on mbaЙ—ii Alla seedaniiЙ—o [on e hunnugol ngol]. Pellet, ko gannduЙ—o ko ngolloton."
  16,92,"Wota on ngon wano (debbo) pirtunooЙ—o mottawol mun Й“aawo doole firtude, hoЙ—on njogitora gooЙ—ndooje mon Й—een jamfondiro hakkunde mon, nde mofte [mon Й—en] wonata Й“urde tonaade e dii mofte goo. ngandee Alla no jarribora on Й—uum. ma o Й“anngina- na on Гұande darngal, Й—uu ko luutondiratnoЙ—on e mum."
  16,93,"Sinno Alla muuyuno, o waЙ—atno on mofte goote. Kono, Himo majjina on Mo o muuyi, O feewna on mo O muuyi. ma on lannditoye e Й—uu ko ngollatnoЙ—on."
  16,94,"Wota on njogitor gooЙ—ndooje mon jamfondiro hakkunde mon, sakko koyngal [mon] mortotoo (fergito) Й“aawo ngal tabitude, meeЙ—iron bone sabu ko paddiЙ—on ko e laawol Alla ngol. hino woodani on lepte mawЙ—e."
  16,95,"Wota on mbaЙ—titir ahadi Alla ndiin coggu pamЙ—ungu. Гұganndee ko ko woni ka Alla ko Й“uri moЖҙЖҙanВҙde on, si tawno hoЙ—on nganndi!"
  16,96,"Ko marЙ—on kon re'ay (gasat), ko woni ka Alla ko ko keddotooЙ—um. ma min mbarjor Й“een muГұГұiiЙ“e njoЙ“di maЙ“Й“e ndiin ko Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude e ko Й“e ngollatnoo kon."
  16,97,"Kala golluЙ—o moЖҙЖҙere, woni gorko maa debbo, hara ko o gooЕӢЙ—inЙ—o, maa min wuurnu mo nguur- ndam laaЙ“uЙ—am. Ma min mbaajor Й“e njoЙ“di maЙ“Й“e ndin, ko Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude e ko Й“e ngollatnoo kon."
  16,98,"Si a janngay Alqur'aana, moolor Alla seytaane diiwaaЙ—o on."
  16,99,"KaЕӢko on, mbawdi(cemmbe) alanaa mo e Й“en gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e, Й“e fawii e hoore Joomi maЙ“Й“e."
  16,100,"nganndee mbawdi makko ndiin, ko hoore Й“een weldiiЙ“e e makko woni, e Й“een sirkirooЙ“e sabu makko."
  16,101,"Si min lomtinii aaya lomto aaya goo - Ko Alla Й“uri anndude ko O jippinta - ЖҒe mbi'a: "aan on ko a pekindiiЙ—o". Si ko woni, ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e maЙ“Й“e anndaa."
  16,102,"Maaku: "Ko jippini ndee, ko [Jibriilu] Fittaanndu LaaЙ“ndu ndun, immorde ka Joomi maa, fii yo o tabintin Й“een gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e, e [fii yo nde won] peewal, e welo-welo wonanВҙde juulЙ“e Й“een"."
  16,103,"GooЕӢЙ—ii min miЙ—en nganndi wonВҙde heЙ“e mbi'a: "Ko neЙ—Й—aЕӢke woni mo anndinnde (Alqur'aana)". ЖҠemngal ngal Й“e ooГұotoo e mun ngal ko ajami, ndee Й—oo non ka Й—emngal Aarabi Й“anngungal(.laaЙ“tungal.)"
  16,104,"Pellet, Й“en Й“e ngooЕӢЙ—inaani Aayeeje Alla Й—een, Alla feewnataa Й“e. Hino woodani Й“e lepte muusЙ—e."
  16,105,"Nganndee ko fejkindotoo fenaande, ko Й“een Й“e ngoЕӢЙ—inaani- aayee Alla Й—en; ko kamЙ“e ngooni fenooЙ“e Й“een."
  16,106,"Kala jedduЙ—o Alla Й“aawo gooЕӢЙ—inal makko ngal - si wanaa on waawnaaЙ—o hara Й“ernde makko nden ko deeЖҙirnde gooЕӢЙ—inal , kono, Й“een yaГұГұamЙ“e Й“erЙ—e mun keeferaaku, hino fawii Й“e tikkere immorde Alla, hino woodani Й“e kadi lepte mawЙ—e."
  16,107,"Ngol [murtugol maЙ“Й“e], ko tawde Й“e cuЙ“iima nguurndam aduna e dow laakara, e wonВҙde Alla kan, O feewnataa yimЙ“e yedduЙ“e Й“een."
  16,108,"Ko Й“een ngoni Й“e Alla noti e Й“erЙ—e mum, e nanЙ—e mun e gite mum. Ko Й“een ngooni welsindiiЙ“e Й“en."
  16,109,"Sikke alaaa wonВҙde Й“een Й—oon ka laakara, ko kamЙ“e ngoni sooyЙ“e Й“een."
  16,110,"refti pellet Joomi maa, wonannde Й“en ferunooЙ“e Й“aawo nde Й“e tampinaama, hooti Й“e tiiЙ—nii Й“e muГұГұii, pellet Joomi maa, Й“aawo Й—uum, Ko O jaafotooЙ—o, jurmotooЙ—o."
  16,111,"(JanЕӢo) tuma Гұande kala woЕӢkii arata, hara hiki wennja fii hoore-makki, woЕӢkii kala yoЙ“ee ko ki golli kon, kamЙ“e Й“e tooГұetaake."
  16,112,"Alla piyii misal hoЙ—o: hoЙ—o hoolinoongo, deeЖҙungo; arsike maggo no ardirana ngo nokku kala e yaaj- jeende. ЖҒe njeddi dokke Alla Й—e, Alla meeЙ—iniri Й“e kolgu heege e kulol, sabu ko Й“e ngollatnoo kon."
  16,113,"GooЕӢЙ—ii arii e maЙ“Й“e nulaaЙ—o jeyaaЙ—o e maЙ“Й“e, Й“e njeddi mo. Lepte Й—een nanngi Й“e, tawi ko Й“e tooГұЙ“e."
  16,114,"Г‘aamee e kon ko Alla arsike on dagiiЙ—i laaЙ“uЙ—i, njeetton dokke Alla Й—een, si wonii ko KaЕӢko ndewoton."
  16,115,"nganndee ko o Harminani on, ko jiiba, e ЖҙiiЖҙam (rufaaЙ—am), e teewu kose, e [huunde hirsiraande] daginiraande ko woori Allah. Kala on duГұaaЙ—o [e Гұaamugol Й—uum] hara wonaa Й“ewЙ—o wonaa jaggi- tuЙ—o,nganndee pellet, Allah ko jaatooЙ—o jurmotooЙ—o."
  16,116,"Wota on mbi'u ko Й—emЙ—e mon sifotoo e penaale: "ЖҠum Й—oo no dagii, Й—um Й—oo no harmi", fii no pekindoron e hoore Alla fenaande. Pellet, Й“en fekindotooЙ“e fenaande e hoore Alla, Й“e maletaake."
  16,117,"Ko dakamme pamЙ—uЙ—o, hino woodani Й“e lepte muusЙ—e."
  16,118,"E hoore AlyahuudaaЙ“e Й“een (kan), min karminno ko min fillani maa kon ko adii. min tooГұaano Й“e; ko woni, ko ko'e-maЙ“Й“e Й“e ngonnnoo e tooГұude."
  16,119,"Refti pellel, Joomi maa, wonanВҙde Й“een golluЙ“e bone on majjere, refti Й“e tuubi Й“aawo Й—uum Й“e moЖҙЖҙini, pellet Joomi maa, Й“aawo Й—uum, ko jaafotooЙ—o, jurmotooЙ—o."
  16,120,"Pellet, Ibraahiima woniino Й—owro koykinaniiЙ—o Alla, ooГұiiЙ—o [e Й—iya diinaaji], o wonaana jeyaaЙ—o e sirkooЙ“e Й“een."
  16,121,"jettatnooЙ—o dokke makko Й—in. [Alla] suЙ“ike mo, O feewni mo e laawol poocciingol."
  16,122,"Min ngokki mo ka aduna moЖҙЖҙere. KaЕӢko oon ka laakara, ko o jeyaaЙ—o e moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e Й“een."
  16,123,"Refi min mbahayini e maaЙ—a, wonВҙde: " Jokku diina Ibraahiima ka naayaaki e diinaaji mehre o jeyanooka e sirkooЙ“e Й“een"."
  16,124,"ngandee [mawningol fii] aseweere nden ko waЙ—anaa, ko Й“een luutondirЙ“e e mayre. Pellet, Joomi maa, ko Гұaawoyoowo hakkunde maЙ“Й“e Г‘ande Darngal, e Й—uum ko Й“e luutondiratnoo fii mum."
  16,125,"Noddir e diina Joomi maa kan ГұeeГұal e waaju moЖҙЖҙu. Wennjiraa Й“e e noone Й“urЙ—o moЖҙЖҙude. Pellet, Joomi maa, ko KaЕӢko Й“uri anndude on majjuЙ—o e laawol makko ngol, ko KaЕӢko kadi Й“uri anndi feewЙ“e Й“een."
  16,126,"Si on yagginay, haray yagginiree yeru no waЙ—iranoЙ—on non. Ko si on muГұГұike, pellet ko Й—uum Й“uri moЖҙЖҙanВҙde muГұГұiiЙ“e Й“een."
  16,127,"MuГұГұo! MuГұal maa ngal ko sabu Alla tan. wota a suno fii maЙ“Й“e. wota wonu Й“ittorЙ—o e Й—uum ko Й“e pewjata."
  16,128,"Pellet, Alla no wonВҙdi e Й“een hulЙ“e [Mo] e Й“een moЖҙЖҙinooЙ“e."
  17,1,"Senaare wondani oon doЖҙnuЙ—o JeyaaЙ—o makko on jehma, iwde ta juulirde hormante haa ka juulirde woЙ—Й—itiinde, nden nde min mbarkini banЕӢe mun,fii yo min kollu mo immorde e aayeeje amen. Pellet, Ko KaЕӢko woni Nanoowo, jiвҖҷoowo."
  17,2,"Min njnniino Muusaa deftere nden, men mbaЙ—i nde peewal, wonan'de Й“iЙ—Й“e IsraaвҖҷiila Й“en, won'de : "Wata on njogito ga Am kooloraaЙ—o"."
  17,3,"[Ko onon yo] Й“iЙ—Й“e Й“e Й“e min mbaЙ—Й—innoo wonnudude e Nuuhu.Pellet, o laatino jeyaaЙ—o yettoowo."
  17,4,"Min mbahyinino e Й“iЙ—Й“e IsraaвҖҷiila Й“e to deftere [won'de] : "On mbonnayat ta leydi laabi Й—iЙ—i, on townitoyto kadi townitaare mawnnde"."
  17,5,"Si fodoore gootel e Й—in Й—iЙ—i arii, min ngurta e mon jiyaaЙ“e Amen, marЙ“e doole tiiЙ—Й—e, Й“e njiloo hakkunde galleeji Й—i. ЖҠuum wonii fodoore huuwoyteende =golloteende."
  17,6,"Refti min nduttitanani on n on doole Й—en e hoore maЙ“Й“e; min ЖҒeydi on jawЙ—e e Й“iЙ—Й“e,min mbaЙ—a on gorol Й“urngol heewde."
  17,7,"Si on moЖҙЖҙinii, ko ko'e mon moЖҙЖҙinanЙ—on ; si on mbonnii kadi, ko koвҖҷe mon [bonnannЙ—on]. Si fodoore sakkitiinde nden arii, ko fii yo Й“e hoynu j'eece mon Й—en, e fii yo no Й“e naatiraa ka juulirde wano Й“e naatirnoo e mayre ka laawol adanol, e fii yo Й“e muncu yeru woo ko Й“e townani muncudee."
  17,8,"Hino jortaa ka Joomi mon yurmee on.Si on fillitike (non),min fillitoo. min mbaЙ—anii yedduЙ“e Й“e Jahannama on tonngorde."
  17,9,"Pellet, ndee AlqurвҖҷaanaare no fewnat e ko Й“uri e nuunЙ—ude,hende wewlinira=weltanira gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e,Й“en gollooЙ“e moЖҙЖҙuЙ—i Й—in, won'de, no woodani Й“e njoЙ“di mawndi."
  17,10,"E won'de pellet, Й“en Й“e gooЕӢЙ—inaa laakara on, men maranii Й“e lepte muusuЙ—e."
  17,11,"NeЙ—Й—o no toroo bone, wano o tororta non moЖҙЖҙere,neЙ—Й—aЕӢke on wonii ko heГұiiЙ—o."
  17,12,"Min mbaЙ—ii jemma on e Гұalawma on Aayeeje Й—iЙ—i, min momti aaya jemma on, min mbaЙ—i aaya Гұalawma on hentiiЙ—o, fii yo on Й—aЙ“Й“u Й“ural immorde e Joomi mon, e fii yo on ngandu limoore duuЙ“i, e hasboore. Kala huunde, min n fensitirii nde fensitudee."
  17,13,"Kala neЙ—Й—aЕӢke, min mbaЙ—Й—inii mo talkuru makko ndun ka daande makko. Men njaltinanoyat mo Г‘ande Darngal, deftere, o hawra e mayre ko nde fontaande."
  17,14,"Janngu deftere maa nden, hoore-maa yonante hannde kasboowo."
  17,15,"Mo feewii, haray pellet, ko hoore-makko o feewani ; mo majii kadi, haray pellet, ko o majji kon yantate hoore-makko. WoЕӢkii ronndotaako bone wokki goo. Men ngonaani leptooЙ“e, haa min immina NulaaЙ—o."
  17,16,"Si min faandike halkude saare, Men y Njamirat neeminaaЙ“e mayre Й“en, Й“e faasinqinoo e mayre, konngol (lepte) ngol jojja e mayre, Men munca nde muncudee."
  17,17,"Heewii gire Й—e min kalki Й“aawo Nuuhu! Joomi maa Yonii HumpitiiЙ—o, jiвҖҷoowo junuubi=bakkatuuji jeyaaЙ“e makko Й“en."
  17,18,"Kala mo faala yaawnaneede, min n njaawnanat mo ton huunde ko min muuyi, wonan'de on mo min njЙ—i, refti min mbaЙ—ana mo Jahannama, o naatoya nge ko o ГұiЕӢaaЙ—o, goЙ—Й—inaaЙ—o [yurmeende]."
  17,19,"On paalaaЙ—o laakara, o gollani Й—um golle mum, hara kaЕӢko ko o gooЕӢЙ—inЙ—o ;Й“een Й—oon, golle maЙ“Й“e Й—en ngonii jaarnaaЙ—e."
  17,20,"Kala (maЙ“Й“e),miЙ—en Й“eydana ; Й“ee Й—oo e Й“ee Й—oo, immorde e dokkal Joomi maa. Dokkal Joomi maa ngal wonaani kaЙ—aa ngal."
  17,21,"Ndaarii no min Й“urniri yoga maЙ“Й“e e dow yoga, ko laakara on Й“uri mawnude darjaaji,Й“uri mawnude kadi Й“ural."
  17,22,"Wota a waЙ—an Alla deweteeЙ—o goЙ—Й—o; njooЙ—oyoЙ—aa ko a ГұiЕӢaaЙ—o noppaaЙ—o."
  17,23,"Joomi maa yamirii :"wota on ndew ko wonaa KaЕӢko, jipnaaЙ“e Й“,moЖҙЖҙagol [e maЙ“Й“e]:si nayewu goЙ—Й—o e maЙ“Й“e yottike ma,maa Й—um Й“e Й—iЙ—o non;wota a wiвҖҷi Й“e "eh=uf!" wota a wikko Й“e =wota a furo,layan Й“e konngol teddungol."
  17,24,"NjankinanoЙ—aa Й“e njurmeЙ—aa Й“e, mbiвҖҷaa: В« Joomi an, yurme Й“eвҖҷe, wano Й“e neвҖҷirnoo kam non hari ko mi tosokum В»."
  17,25,"Joomi mo'on no andi ko woni ka nder woЕӢkiiji mon, si tawii on ngonnno moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e ; pellet KaЕӢko o wonanii ruttotooЙ“e Й“e cuhroowo."
  17,26,"Jonnu jom Й“adondiral haqqee makko o, e Й“illiiЙ—o, e seteejo haqqee makko on ; wota a bonnu bonnere."
  17,27,"Pellet bonnooЙ“e Й“e, ko siЙ—Й“e seytanuuji Й—i ; seytaane non wonii jedduЙ—o Joomi mum."
  17,28,"Si a Й—uurniima Й“e fii Й—aЙ“Й“ugol yurmeende immorde ka Joomi maa, nde jortiЙ—aa Й—um, wi'i Й“e konngol newingol."
  17,29,"Wota a waЙ— junngo maa ngo ko lmbaango, ka daande maa ; wota a fortu ngo kadi kala portugol, haa njooЙ—oЙ—aa ko a pelniiЙ—o, nimsuЙ—o."
  17,30,"Pellet Joomi maa, no yaacnana arsike, on mo O muuyi. O Й“ittina. Pellet KaЕӢko O wonii kumpitiiЙ—o, jiвҖҷoowo jeyaaЙ“e makko."
  17,31,"Wote on mbare Й“iЙ“Й“e mon Й“en kulol Й“illa=ba'asal, ko minen ngarsikata Й“e, won'dude e mon ; pellet bargol Й“e ngol, wonii goopol manngol."
  17,32,"Wota on Й“atto jina=fijrde nde, pellet Й—uum wonii paЕӢkare e laawol bon'ngol."
  17,33,"Wota on mbar woЕӢkii, ki Allah harmini kin [bargol], si wonaa sabu hakkee. Mo tooГұaama waraama, min waЙ—anii heftuЙ“e e makko Й“e doole wota non o fantin ka bargol. Pellet KaЕӢko o wonii ballaaЙ—o."
  17,34,"Wota on Й“atto jawle Alyatiim, si wonaa Й“attagol Й“urngol moЖҙЖҙude, haa sagatalaaku makko timma ; kuumnee aadi ndin; pellet, aadi ndin wonii laЙ“nditoytee ndi."
  17,35,"KuuЙ“nee Й“etu ngu si petat, manndikiron manndakke=peeson peese peewЙ—e, ko Й—um moЖҙЖҙi, ko kaГұum Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude battane."
  17,36,"Wota a rewindo e ko a anndaa fii mum. Pellet nanЙ—e Й—en, e giiЙ—e Й—en e Й“ernde nden, Й—iiЙ—oo fow ngonii laЙ“nditoyteeЙ—i ka makko."
  17,37,"Wota a yaaru e leydi ГұaaЖҙa bunnga, ko fii pellet an a yulataa leydi ndin, a yottotaako pelle Й—e njuuteendi."
  17,38,"Й—e fof, bone majji on ngonii gaГұaaЙ—i to Joomi maa."
  17,39,"ЖҠuum, ko goЙ—Й—um e ko Joomi maaЙ—a wahayini fa'ade e maa, immorde e Г‘eeГұal wota a waЙ— deweteeЙ—o goo wond'ude e Alla, sakko mberleЙ—aa ka ndeer jahannama ko a pelaaЙ—o daЙ—aaЙ—o."
  17,40,"E mati Joomi mon suЙ“ani on Й“iЙ“Й“e worЙ“e, O jogitoo immorde e malaa'ikaaji Й—i rewЙ“e? Pellet, onon hoЙ—on layde konngol mawnungol!"
  17,41,"GooЕӢЙ—ii min fensitii e nder ndee Alqur'aanaare fii yo Й“e mbaactor, Й—um Й“eydaani Й“e si wonaa woЙ—Й—itagol."
  17,42,"" Maaku : В« Si tawno no won'di e makko, deweteeЙ—i wano Й“e mbiвҖҷiri ni Й—i Й—aЙ“Й“ayno laawol feewde de Jom Arsi o.""
  17,43,"Senaade wonanii mo, o Toowii gaayi e ko Й“e mbi'ata Toowal mawnngal."
  17,44,"No subunhinan'de mo kammuuli Й—in jeeЙ—iЙ—i e leydi ndin e Й“e won'Й“e e majji, alaa e hay e hu'unde si wonaa hende Subunhinaade sabu Yettugol mo, kono on faamataa cubunhinaali maЙ“Й“e Й—in, pellet, KaЕӢko O wonii munГұiiЙ—o cuhroowo."
  17,45,"Si a janngii Alqur'aanaare nden min maЙ—at hakkunde maa e Й“een Й“e mgooЕӢЙ—inaa laalara on heedo suuЙ—iingo."
  17,46,"Min mbaЙ—i aЙ—i e dow Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—een cokooЙ—e fii wata Й“e paamu nde [Alqur'aanaare nden] e ka noppi maЙ“Й“e kadi teddeele, si a jaЕӢtike Joomi maaЙ—a ka ndeer Alqur'aanaare KaЕӢko Tun Й“e huccinay Й“abbe maЙ“Й“e Й—en ko Й“e dogooЙ“e."
  17,47,"Ko Minen ngnndi ko Й“e keЙ—otoo kon, tuma Й“e keЙ—otoo fa'ade e maaЙ—a [yo NulaaЙ—o], e tuma Й“e cowndondirta=ndeeydata, tuma nde tooГұooЙ“e Й“e mbi'ata: В«On jokkaani si wonaa gorko mbilЙ—aaЙ—o=bilaaЙ—oВ»."
  17,48,"Ndaarii [yo NulaaЙ—o] ko honno Й“e piyiranay maa mise=yeruuji, Й“e majjii Й“e kattantaake [heЙ“de] laawol."
  17,49,"ЖҒe mbi'i: В«E hara si mon mgonii Жҙi'e e nguЙ—u, haray ko min immintinoyteeЙ“e tagoore hesre?В»"
  17,50,"Maaku: [yo NulaaЙ—o] В«ngonee kaaЖҙe maa jamЙ—eВ»"
  17,51,"Ma Й—uum tagoore tawa nde mawni e Й“erЙ—e mon, Й“e mbi'a: 'Ko hommbo ruttata amen?" Maaku: "Ko On takЙ—o on ka laawol adanol". ЖҒe tura ko'e maЙ“Й“e Й—e fa'ade e maa, Й“e mbi'a: "ЖҠuum ko honde tuma"?, Maaku: 'No tijjaa nde tawata Й“adike"."
  17,52,"Г‘annde o noddata on nootoЙ—on njetton mo cikkon on ГұiiЙ“aano [ka leydi] si wonaa seeЙ—a."
  17,53,"Maakan jiyaaЙ“e aan Й“e: "Yoo Й“e lay ko Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude, pellet, Seytaane o bonnat hakkunde maЙ“Й“e, pellet, Seytaane wonanii neЙ—Й—aЕӢke gaГұo laaЙ“tuЙ—o"."
  17,54,"Joomi mon ko o ganndo fii mon, si o yiЙ—ii o yurmoo on, maa Й—um si o yiЙ—ii olepta on. Min nulaani ma e dow maЙ“Й“e fawtiiЙ—o."
  17,55,"Ko Joomi maa anndi fii Й“e wonЙ“e ta kammuuli e ta leydi, pellet, Min Й“urnii woЙ“Й“e e AnnabaaЙ“e Й“e e dow woЙ“Й“e, Min Jonni Daawuuda Jabuura."
  17,56,"Maaku: "Noddee Й“e Й“e aaЖҙiЙ—on [ko deweteeЙ“e] gaanin makko, Й“e maraa huncugol lorra kan gaayi mo'on wonaa waylugol kadi"."
  17,57,"ЖҒen, Й“e Й“e ngoni noddude, heЙ“e Й—aЙ“Й“ude Й—oworgal fa'ade e Joomi maЙ“Й“e, ko hommbo e maЙ“Й“e Й“uri Й“adaade, heЙ“e njoortii yurmende makko on heЙ“e kuli lepte makko Й—e, pellet, lepte Joomi maa Й—e Й—e laatike ko deentaaЙ—e."
  17,58,"Alaa e saare si wonaa minen ko min halkatЙ“e nde ko adii Гұande darngal, maa ko min leptatЙ“e nde lepte cattuЙ—e, Й—uum Й—o wonii ko winndaa Й—um to Deftere."
  17,59,"HaЙ—aani min nde min nula aayeeje Й—e, si wona sabu yeddiino Й—e adiiЙ“e Й“en, Min okki Samuuda Ngeelooba ba yi'teemba Й“e tooГұi ba, Min nuliraani Aayeeje Й—e si wonaa hulЙ“inirЙ—e."
  17,60,"[Janto] Tuma nde min wi'anno maa: "Pellet, Joomi maa o huЙ“indima yimЙ“e Й“e, Min mbaЙ—iraani nde yi'annde nde Min kollumaa si wonaa fitina wona'de yimЙ“e Й“e e lekki huЙ—aaki ki ka Alqur'aana, MiЙ—en kulЙ“ina Й“e kono Й“eydataa Й“e si wonaa bewre mawnde."
  17,61,"Nde min n Daalannoo Maleykaaji Й—i cujjanee aadama, Й“e cujji si wonaa Ibliisa o wi'i: " mi sujjanta on mo talЙ—a e loopal?"."
  17,62,"O wi'i: "A yi'ii oo mo teddinЙ—aa e dow am, pellet, si A neeЙ“nanii kan haa Гұande darnga mi bonnat Й“iЙ“Й“e makko Й“e si wonaa seeЙ—aaЙ“e."
  17,63,"[Alla] Daali: "Yahu, kala jokkuЙ—o ma e maЙ“Й“e pellet, ko jahannama woni njoЙ“di mon, njoЙ“di yonoori"."
  17,64,"Dillinir on mo kattanaЙ—aa e maЙ“Й“e hito maa o, pooЙ—a e dow maЙ“Й“e pucci maa e seppooЙ“e maa, rentu e maЙ“Й“e jawle e Й“iЙ“Й“e foduЙ“e, [kono] Seytaane fodaani Й“e si wonaa hodo."
  17,65,"Pellet, JiyaaЙ“e am Й“e a maraa doole e hoore maЙ“Й“e, Joomi maa yonii kooloraaЙ—o."
  17,66,"Ko Joomi mon woni sogganatЙ—o on laaЙ—e Й—e e maayo, fii yo on Й—aЙ“Й“u immorde e Й“ural makko , pellet, KaЕӢko ko O jurmotooЙ—o on."
  17,67,"Si lorra heЙ“ii on to maayo, majja Й“een Й“e noddatno Й—on, si wonaa KaЕӢko [Alla] nde danndi on ka njorndi Й—urnoЙ—on, neЙ—Й—aЕӢke on wonii te o seeraani won'de heewuЙ—o jeddugol."
  17,68,"Enee, on kooli mutintaa on ka baЕӢe njorndi maaЙ—um o nula e mon damagariire [toЙ“o koccu], refti heЙ“antaake on fawtiiЙ—o."
  17,69,"Ma kooli o nduttaraa on e maggo laawol goo o accita e dow mon bippooru immorde e keneeli o yoolira on sabu ko njedduno Й—on ko, refti on keЙ“antaake jokkitiratЙ—o e dow amen cukkoowo."
  17,70,"GooЕӢЙ—ii, min teddinii Й“iЙ—Й“e aadama Й“e, min ronndike Й“e ka njorndi e ka maayo min arsiki Й“e immorde e laaЙ“uЙ—i min n Й“urni Й“e e dow ko heewi e Й“en Й“e min tagi Й“urnudee."
  17,71,"Г‘annde min noddiroyta kala yimЙ“e gardiiЙ—o maЙ“Й“e on,kala on jonnitiroyaaЙ—o deftere makko nde ka Гұaamo makko Й“e Й—on Й“e janngay deftere maЙ“Й“e nde Й“e tooГұirtaake hay yeru gaarayol hun tamaro."
  17,72,"Kala on gon'Й—o e [ngurndan aduna] ko o bunЙ—o, haray kaЕӢko, ko ka laakara o Й“urata wumde e majjude laawol."
  17,73,"Fii kala Й“e eЙ“Й“ii nde Й“e fitinatmaa gaayi nde hu'unde nde min n wahayini e maaЙ—a fii yo a fekindo e amen ko wonaa Й—un [ko min n tellini e maa] on tuma Й“e njogitoto ma sehlaajo."
  17,74,"Si tawiino min tabintinaanoma, gooЕӢЙ—ii a do'ii ooГұa'ade e maЙ“Й“e hu'unde seeЙ—aare."
  17,75,"On tuma min meeЙ—inteno cowale [lepte] ka nguurndam e cowale [lepte] kumayde refti heЙ“antaake ma ballo e hoore Amen."
  17,76,"Fii kala Й“e eЙ“Й“iino dillinngol ma ka leydi fii yo Й“e yaltine e mayri, on tuma Й“e ГұiiЙ“ataano Й“atte maa si wonaa seeЙ—a."
  17,77,"ЖҠum ko Sunna Й“e Й“e min n nuli ko adimaa immorde e NulaaЙ“e amen, a heЙ“antaa Sunna amen on mbattiigu."
  17,78,"Г‘iiЙ“u juulde nde ka mortagol na'ange nge haa ka niЙ“re jemma, Juulde subaha nde, pellet, Juulde subaha nde wonii seedeteende."
  17,79,"Ka jemma tinno e makko ko Й“eydaari maaЙ—a, no jortaa nde Joomi maaЙ—a immintinat ma e darorЙ—e yettiniinde."
  17,80,"Ma'aku: "Jooma, naadira naatirgal goonga yaltiniraa mi jaltirgal goonga, mbaЙ—anaa mi immorde ka maaЙ—a doole ballal"."
  17,81,"Maaku: "goonga o arii mehre nde fuuyii, pellet, mehre nde wonii fuuyoore"."
  17,82,"MiЙ—en tellina ka Alqur'aana hu'unde nde konde cellal e yurmeende wona'nde gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“e, Й“eydataa tooГұooЙ“e Й“en si wonaa hayre."
  17,83,"Si min n neeЙ“nii e neЙ—Й—aЕӢke on o Й—uurnoo o townaa balaaje makko, si bone heЙ“ii mo o wona hattuЙ—o e taЖҙiiЙ—o."
  17,84,"Maaku: "mo kala yo golluЙ—o e laawol mum, ko Joomi mon woni gannduЙ—o on Й“urЙ—o feewde laawol"."
  17,85,"HeЙ“e laЙ“do maa fii fittaandu, maaku: "Fittaandu ndu ko e fiyaake Joomi an, on okkaaka e ganndal si wonaa seeЙ—aГ©."
  17,86,"Mi woondii, si MiЙ—en njiЙ—noo min naЙ“atno nde hu'unde nde min wahyini fa'ade e maaЙ—a, refti heЙ“antaake ma fawtiiЙ—o Й—um e hoore amen."
  17,87,"Ko woni tan, ko Hinnayee immorde ka Joomi maa, pellet, Й“ural makko ngal e dow maa wonii mawngal."
  17,88,"Maaku: "Mi woondii, si yimЙ“e Й“e e jinnaaji Й—i kawtitii fii yo Й“e ngaddu yeru ndee Alqur'aanaare, Й“e mgaddataa yeru mayre, hay si wonii woЙ“Й“e maЙ“Й“e ko wallindratЙ“e e woЙ“Й“e"."
  17,89,"GooЕӢЙ—ii min Й“annginanii yimЙ“e Й“en e ndee Alqur'aanaare immorde e kala misal, Й“urЙ“e Й—uuЙ—ude e yimЙ“e Й“e calii, si wanaa jeddugol."
  17,90,"ЖҒe mbi'i: "min ngoЕӢЙ—intaa ma, haa Й“ullitanaa men e lesdi Й“unndu"."
  17,91,"Mu Й—um laatano maa ngesa immorde e tamorooje e inabuuje Й“ullitaa caatli Й—i hakkunde majje Й“ullitugol."
  17,92,"Ma Й—um liЙ“aa kammu ngu e hoore amen wano aaЖҙorЙ—aa non kunte, maa Й—um ngddaa Alla e Maleykaaji Й—i [men] kuccandira."
  17,93,"Ma Й—um laatano maa suudu immorde e cuЙ—aaje [kanЕӢe], maaЙ—um Жҙawaa ka kammu, men ngooЕӢЙ—intaa Жҙawugol maaЙ—a ngol haa njippinaa e amen deftere men jannga nde. Maaku: "Senaade Jom an, hara mi wonu, ko wonaa Й“anndinke NulaaЙ—o?!"."
  17,94,"HaЙ—aani yimЙ“e Й“e nde Й“e ngooЕӢЙ—inta tuma nde peewalngal arnoo Й“e, si wonaa fii Й“e mbi'i i'ii: "E hara Alla nulay Й“anndiЕӢke NulaaЙ—o?!""
  17,95,"Maaku: "Si tawiino laatinooma lesdi maleykaaji heЙ“e njaha ko Й“e deeЖҙЙ“e, min njippinatno e maЙ“Й“e immorde ka kammu Malayla NulaaЙ—o"."
  17,96,"Maaku: "Alla yonii ceediiЙ—o hakkunde am e mon, pellet KaЕӢko o wonii kumpitiiЙ—o deenЙ—o jeyaaЙ“e makko Й“en"."
  17,97,"Oon mo Alla feewni ko oon woni peewuЙ—o, Й“e o majjini Й“e a heЙ“antaaЙ“e wallooЙ“e ko woori mo. Min mooЙ“ay Й“e Гұande darnga e dow je'ece maЙ“Й“e Й—e ko Й“e wumЙ“e e muumЙ—uЙ“e= fahdube Й“e e faaЙ—uЙ“e, ja'aЖҙndee maЙ“Й“e nden ko jahannama tuma kala nge rocci min Й“eydana Й“e huЙ“Й“unge."
  17,98,"ЖҠuum ko njoЙ“di maЙ“Й“e, sabu kamЙ“e Й“e njeddii aayeeje amen Й—e, Й“e mbi'i i: "E hay si min ngonii Жҙi'e e mbuЙ—u e hara minen ko min immintinteeЙ“e tagoore?!" hesre."
  17,99,"Enee, Й“ee nji'aani, won'de Alla O TakЙ—o kammuuli Й—i e leydi ndi ko kattanЙ—o nde o tagata yeru maЙ“Й“e, o waЙ—ani Й“e lajal [caate] sikke alaa e maggal. TooГұooЙ“e Й“e calii si wonaa jeddugol."
  17,100,"Maaku: "Sinndo onon hoЙ—on marnoo ngaluuji yurmeende e Joomi am on, on tuma, on njogitotono kulol nafkugol, neЙ—Й—aЕӢke on wonii nguddo"."
  17,101,"GooЕӢЙ—ii min n ngkkiino Muusaa aayeeje jeenay Й“annguЙ—e, lanndii Й“iЙ“Й“e Israa'iila Й“en tuma nde o arnoo Й“e Fir'awna wi'ani mo: "min dey miЙ—o sikkumaa ko an yo Muusaa ko a mbilЙ—aaЙ—o"."
  17,102,"Maaku: "GooЕӢЙ—ii haЙ—a anndi jippinaani Й—ee si wonaa JeyЙ—o kammuuji Й—i e leydi ndi aayeeje [yi'eteeЙ—i]. Min dey miЙ—o sikkumaa ko an yo Fir'awna ko a kalkiiЙ—o"."
  17,103,"O faalaa nde o dillinta Й“e ka lesdi min n njoooli mo e Й“e won'du Й“e e makko Й“e denndaangal."
  17,104,"Min Daalani Й“aawo makko Й“iЙ“Й“e Israa'iila Й“e: "HoЙ—ee ka leydi, si fodoore sakkitiinde nden arii, min ngaddana on ko on muuЙ“iiЙ“e=fiiliibe"."
  17,105,"Ko sabu Goonga min telliniri nde, ko sabu Goonga nde tellii, Min nuliraani ma si wanaa [ko a] beltinoowo=beltinoowo e jertinoowo."
  17,106,"E Qur'aanaare min n Й“anngini nde fii yo a janngannde yimЙ“e Й“e e dow deeЖҙere, min njippini nde jippin'de."
  17,107,"Maaku: "ngooЕӢЙ—inee nde, maaЙ—um wota on ngoЕӢЙ—ine, pellet, Й“en okkaaЙ“e ganndal ko adii nde si [nde] janngaama e taweende maЙ“Й“e Й“e suuyiray wokkuЙ—e ko Й“e sujjooЙ“e"."
  17,108,"ЖҒe mbi'a:Senaade woodanii Joomi amen,nde wonnoo Fodoore Joomi amen nden ko waЙ—oore."
  17,109,"HeЙ“e suuyira wokkuЙ—e Й“e ngulla [Alqur'aana on] Й“asda Й“e yankinaare."
  17,110,"Maaku: "Noddiree mo Alla maa noddiro mo jurmotooЙ—o, kala no noddirЙ—on Mo, ko KaЕӢko InЙ—e MoЖҙЖҙe Й—en heeranii, wota a fenГұin juulde maaЙ—a nden wota a suuЙ—nde nde Й—aЙ“Й“u hakkunde Й—uum laawol."
  17,111,"Maaku: jettooje Й—e ngoodanii Alla o mo jogitaaki Й“iЙ—Й—o laatanaaki mo kafidaaЙ—o e Laamu laatanaaki mo tedduЙ—o mo o huykinantoo, Mawnin Mo Mawnin'dee."
  18,1,"Jettooje ngodanii Alla, On jippinЙ—o e dow JeyaaЙ—o makko on deftere nden o waЙ—anaani nde ooГұaare."
  18,2,"Feewnde fii yo o [NulaaЙ—o on] hulЙ“inir lepte cattuЙ—e immorde ka makko o weltinira gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“en, Й“e no golla MoЖҙЖҙuЙ—i Й—in won'de no woodani Й“e njoddi moЖҙЖҙiri."
  18,3,"Ko Й“e ГұiiЙ“ooЙ“e e ndeer makko [dokke] poomaa."
  18,4,"O reentina Й“en wi"iЙ“e: "Alla jogitike Й“iЙ—Й—o"."
  18,5,"Ganndal alanaaЙ“e e mun, wonaa baabiraaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e woodani, mawnii konngol gon'ngol e yaltude e kunnduЙ—e maЙ“Й“e, Й“e kaalaani si wonaa fenaande."
  18,6,"Mbele jo'o aan a tanpinat hoore-maa e dow batteeji maЙ“Й“e, si ngooЕӢЙ—inaani ndee Yewtere ka suno."
  18,7,"Minen min mbaЙ—ii ko woni ko ka hoore leydi cuЙ—aari mayri, fii yo min mjarribo Й“e ko hommbo e maЙ“Й“e Й“urata moЖҙЖҙin'de golle."
  18,8,"Minen ko min waЙ—ooЙ“e ko woni kon e hoore mayri boowol joorungal."
  18,9,"Kaa a sikku no yimЙ“e fammeere=wimmba nden e binndi Й—in, Й—uum wonu immorde e aayeeje amen kaawniiЙ—e?"
  18,10,"Tuma nde sukaaЙ“e Й“en cornoo to wimmbo, Й“e mbi'i: "Joomi amen okku men immorde ka maaЙ—a Hinnayee=yurmeende newinanaa amen kadi e fiyaake amen peewal."
  18,11,"Min piyi e dow noppi maЙ“Й“e Й—i to ndeer wimbo he limoore duuЙ“i."
  18,12,"Refti min n immintini Й“e fii yo min penГұinir gonndal ko honnde e mojobe=pelle Й—en Й—iЙ—i Й“uri moftude [limoore] ko Й“e ГұiiЙ“i kon dummunne."
  18,13,"Minen MiЙ—en pillanaade ma kumpital fii maЙ“Й“e e Goonga, Й“en Й—oon, ko sukaaЙ“e gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Joomi maЙ“Й“e min Й“eydani Й“e Peewal."
  18,14,"Min kaЙ“Й“i e dow Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e tuma nde Й“e darinoo, Й“e mb'i: "Joomi amen ko JeyЙ—o o kammuuji Й—in e leydi ndin, men noddataa ko woori Mo deweteeЙ—i, gooЕӢЙ—ii haray men mb'ii ontuma [konngol] pantungol."
  18,15,"ЖҒee yimЙ“e amen, Й“e jogitike ko woori Mo deweteeЙ—i, ko haaanunoo ko yo Й“e ngddu e dow maЙ“Й“e dalil Й“annguЙ—o. Ko hommbo Й“uri tooГұde ko foti e on pekindiiЙ—o fenaande o fawi e Alla."
  18,16,"Tuma nde mgoЙ—Й—itinoЙ—on Й“e e ko Й“e ndewata ko ko woori Alla, Й“e coroyi to wimbo Joomi mon fontani on e Yurmeende makko nden o newinani on e fiyaake mon neweende."
  18,17,"HaЙ—a yi'a naange nge si nge Жҙellitike henge naayora ka wimbo maЙ“Й“e seЕӢgo Гұaamo, si henge mutude nge mutirana Й“e ka seЕӢgo nano, kamЙ“e heЙ“e e yaajeende e Й—um, ko jeyaaЙ—um e kaawisaji Alla, on mo Alla feewni ko on woni peewЙ—o, kala mo,o majjini a heЙ“antaa mo keeЙ—o perwnoowo."
  18,18,"HaЙ—a sikka Й“e ko Й“e finЙ“e, tawi kamЙ“e ko Й“e Й—aaniiЙ“e, MiЙ—en mbylitira Й“e seЕӢgo Гұaamo e seЕӢgo nano, rawaandu maЙ“Й“e ndu no fori koyЙ—e ndun Й—e ka dammbugal, si a Жҙellitike e maЙ“Й“e a ruЕӢtotono e maЙ“Й“e ndogaa a heewatno kulol immorde e maЙ“Й“e."
  18,19,"Ko nii Min immintiniri Й“e fii yo Й“e laЙ“nondir hakkunde maЙ“Й“e, bi'oowo wi'i e maЙ“Й“e: "No foti heewde ko ГұiiЙ“Й—on?" ЖҒe mbi'i: "Min ГұiiЙ“ii Гұallal maa goЙ—Й—um e Гұallal." ЖҒe mbi'i: "Ko Joomi mon woni ngannduЙ—o emmbere ko ГұiiЙ“uЙ—on, nulee goЙ—Й—o e mon won'dude e Й—ii kaaki=ceede mon Й—oo ka saare, yo o ndaaru ko hommbo e maЙ“Й“e Й“uri laaЙ“de Гұaamitee, yo o addan on Гұaametee immorde e on Й—on, yo o molto wata go'oto tin fii mon."
  18,20,"Pellet, kamЙ“e si Й“e Жҙellitike e mon Й“e piЙ—at on, ma Й“e ndutta on e laawol maЙ“Й“e ngol, on tuma on maletaake poomaa."
  18,21,"Ko nii min n njaltiniri fii maЙ“Й“e, fii yo Й“e nganndu pellet, Fodoore Alla nde ko nde Goonga, Pellet, Darnga sikke alaa e maggal. Tuma nde Й“e pooЙ—ondiratnoo hakkunde maЙ“Й“e fiyaake maЙ“Й“e Й—en, Й“e mbi'i'i: "Mahee e hoore maЙ“Й“e maadi, ko Joomi maЙ“Й“e woni gannduЙ—o fii maЙ“Й“e." ЖҒe foolЙ“e e fiyaake mu'un mbi'i i: "Min njogitoto e dow maЙ“Й“e Juulirde.""
  18,22,"Aray Й“e mbi'a: "Ko Й“e tato nayaЙ“o maЙ“Й“e ko rawaandu maЙ“Й“e ndu." ЖҒe mbi'a kadi: "Ko Й“e njowo njeegaЙ“o maЙ“Й“e ko rawaandu maЙ“Й“e ndu ko fampaangol e niЙ“e." ЖҒe mbi'a kadi: "Ko Й“e njeeЙ—iЙ—o njeetataЙ“o maЙ“Й“e ko rawaandu maЙ“Й“e ndun." Maaku: "Ko Joomi an woni gannduЙ—o limoore maЙ“Й“e, anndaa Й“e si wonaa seeЙ—aaЙ“e." Wata a weeГұju fii maЙ“Й“e si wonaa yewtere feeГұnde, wota a lanndo fii maЙ“Й“e hay e gooto e maЙ“Й“e."
  18,23,"Wota a wi'an huunde: "Min mi mbaЙ—ay Й—um janngo.""
  18,24,"Si wonaa si Alla Muuyii, janto Joomi maaЙ—a si a yejjitii, maaku: "No tijjaa nde Joomi an Feewnan mi ko Й“uri Й“adaade immorde e Й—um Peewal.""
  18,25,"ЖҒe ГұiiЙ“i ka wimbo maЙ“Й“e duuЙ“i teemeЙ—Й—e tati, Й“e Й“eydi jeenay."
  18,26,"Maaku: "Ko Alla woni gannduЙ—o emmbere ko Й“e ГұiiЙ“i, ko KaЕӢko heeranii ko wirnii ko ka kammuuji e ka leydi kaawes ko yi'iri wa makko e ko naniri, alanaa Й“e ga makko giЙ—o, o kafidaa e Гұaawoore makko he hay gooto."
  18,27,"Janngu ko wahayinaa e maaЙ—a ko immorde e deftere Joomi maa nden, alaa wattitoowo Daaluyeeji=konngudi Makko Й—in, a heЙ“ataa ga makko fattorde."
  18,28,"Tabintin woЕӢkii maaЙ—a kin won'dude e Й“en noddooЙ“e Joomi maЙ“Й“e ka bimmbi e ka kiikiiЙ—e heЙ“e faandii Jaati makko Kin, wota gite maa Й—e njawtu ga maЙ“Й“e hara haЙ—a fa'andii cuЙ—aari nguurndam aduna, wota a Й—ofto on mo Min mbelsindini Й“erЙ—e mun ga jaЕӢtagol Min o njokki beleeЙ—e makko fiyaake makko on woni halkaare."
  18,29,"Maaku Goonga ka immorde ka Joomi mon, mono faalaa yo o gooЕӢЙ—in mono faalaa yo o yeddu, minen min n keblanii tooГұooЙ“e Й“e Yiite no hunnditi Й“e Й—enЙ—e magge Й—en si Й“e Й—aЙ“Й“ii faabo, Й“e faaboree Ndiyam mba'uЙ—am no sila taynaaЙ—o Й—am juЙ—a je'ece Й—e, bonii njaram bonii werde."
  18,30,"Pellet, Й“en gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“e ngolli moЖҙЖҙi Й—in, Minen Min njeebataa njoЙ“di kala moЖҙЖҙinЙ—o golle."
  18,31,"ЖҒeen Й—oon no woodani Й“e Aljannaaji ГұiiЙ“al caatli no ila ley maЙ“Й“e, hiЙ“e cuЙ—iree ton immorde e jawЙ—e kanЕӢe Й“e Й“ornoo comci haakЙ—uЙ—i Й—ewluЙ—i e jalbuЙ—i ko Й“e soЙ“Й“indiiЙ“e=tuugiibe ton e hoore julle, moЖҙЖҙii mbarjaari moЖҙЖҙii kadi fooftorde."
  18,32,"fiyan Й“e yeru,worЙ“e Й—iЙ—o min mbaЙ—ani goЙ—Й—o e maЙ“Й“e gese Й—iЙ—i inab Menhunndintini вҖңkurliriЙ—e Й—e tamarooje Min mbaЙ—i hakkunde majje remuru."
  18,33,"ЖҠeen gese Й—iЙ—i kala mgaddi Гұaametee majje, Й—e tooГұaani hay e huunde e Й—uum, Min ce'eki hakkunde majje [gese Й—en Й—iЙ—i] caangol."
  18,34,"Wonani mo dimЙ—e, o wi'ani gon'diijo makko on tawi himo yewtude mo: "Miin miЙ—o Й“urmaa jawdi e teddude gorol"."
  18,35,"O naati ka ngesa makko tawi ko o tooГұЙ—o hoore-makko, o wi'i: "Mi sikkaani ba re'ay poomaa"."
  18,36,"Mi sikkaani kadai Darnga ngal daroto, mi wooЙ—ndii si mi artira le ka Joomi am, maa mi taw sanne, waylitorde Й“urnde ba moЖҙЖҙude."
  18,37,"Gon'diijo o makko on wi'i mo, tawi homo yewtude mo: "Enee, a yeddii On TakЙ—o ma immorde mbullaari=leydi refti e toЙ“Й“ere [maniiyu] refti O fotndumaa gorko"."
  18,38,"Kono min ko KaЕӢko Alla woni Joomi am, mi kafidataa e Joomi am hay gooto."
  18,39,"Ko haanunoo tuma nde naatuЙ—aa ka ngesa maaЙ—a mbi'aa: "Ko Alla muuyi ko doole alaa si wanaa Alla". Si a yi'ii kam min miЙ—o Й“urmaa famЙ—ude jawdi e Й“iЙ—Й“e."
  18,40,"No jortaa nde Joomi am okkoyta kam moЖҙЖҙere Й“urnde ngesa maa ba O nula e mabba lepte immorde ka kammu ba wonta boowal Й“owrungal."
  18,41,"Maa de ndiyam mabba Й—a wonta Й“eeЙ“uЙ—am, hara a hattantaa Й—aЙ“Й“ugol Й—am."
  18,42,"DimЙ—e makko Й—en bonnaa o weeti homo waylita newe makko Й—en e dow ko o nafki kon e mabba, tawi kammba ko fukkiiba e daЖҙЖҙe mabba, homo wi'a: "Ee haaniina,hara mi kafidaano e Joomi an hay e gooto"."
  18,43,"Laatanaaki mo fedde nde no walla mo ga Alla, o wonaani poolЙ—o."
  18,44,"No toon Giggol Alla Goongawol ngol ko KaЕӢko moЖҙЖҙi mbarjaari moЖҙЖҙi battane."
  18,45,"Fiyan Й“e yeru nguurndam aduna Й—am no wa'i wa ndiyam Min njippiniЙ—am immorde ka kammu jillondiri e majjam puЙ—i leydi ndin, Й—i wonti munciiЙ—i keneeli no jarooЙ—i, Alla wonii ko o kattanЙ—o e dow kala hu'unde."
  18,46,"Jawdi ndi e Й“iЙ—Й“e worЙ“e Й“e ko cuЙ—aari nguurndam aduna, moЖҙЖҙi keddotooЙ—i Й—in ko Й—i Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude mbarjaari ka Joomi maaЙ—a e moЖҙЖҙude yela."
  18,47,"Г‘annde min n naЙ“ata pelle Й—en a nji'a leydi ndin ko feeГұndi, min mooЙ“a Й“e Min ngaccataa immorde e maЙ“Й“e hay e gooto."
  18,48,"ЖҒe kolliree ka Joomi maa [ko Й“e] saffewol, [O Daalana Й“e] gooЕӢЙ—ii on arii e amen wano min n tagirnoo on non, ka laawol adanol, ko woni on aaЖҙino won'de min n waЙ—anaani on fodoore."
  18,49,"Deftere nde wallinee, a nj'a bonЙ“e Й“e ko hulЙ“e ko woni kon e mayre, Й“e mbi'a: "Ee bone amen, ko heЙ“i ndee deftere nde Й—alataa tosokum wonaa njanum si wonaa nde moftii Й—um, Й“e tawa ko Й“e ngolli ko no weeЙ“itaa, Joomi maaЙ—a tooГұataa hay e gooto."
  18,50,"Tuma nde Min mb'annoo maleykaaji: "cujjanee Aadama, Й“e cujji si wonaa Ibliisa o laatike jeyaaЙ—o e jinnaaji Й—in o yalti e Yamiroore Joomi makko. E on jogitoto mo e Й“iЙ—Й“e makko Й“en yiЙ—Й“e ga Am, hara kamЙ“e ko Й“e aГұЙ“e mo'on, bonanii tooГұooЙ“e Й“e battudi."
  18,51,"Mi tawnaani Й“e tagugol kammuuji Й—in e leydi ndi wonaa tagugol ko'e maЙ“Й“e kadi, Mi wonaani jogitotooЙ—o majjinooЙ“e Й“e sembinooЙ“e."
  18,52,"E Гұannde O Daalata: "Noddee kafidaaЙ“e Am Й“e, Й“en Й“e ngaaЖҙiЙ—on, Й“e nodda Й“e, Й“e njaabotaako Й“e min n mbaЙ—i hakkunde maЙ“Й“e halkorde"."
  18,53,"BonЙ“e Й“en nji'a Yiite ngen Й“e pellita won'de kamЙ“e ko Й“e ukketeeЙ“e e magge, Й“e keЙ“ataa gaay magge yiiltorde."
  18,54,"GooЕӢЙ—ii Min fensitanii yimЙ“e Й“en e ndeer ndee Alqur'aanaare immorde e kala yeru, neЙ—Й—aЕӢke on wonii homo Й“uri kala huunde wennjugol."
  18,55,"HaЙ—aani yimЙ“e Й“en nde Й“e gooЕӢЙ—inta Й“e insinanoo Joomi maЙ“Й“e tuma nde Peewal ngal arnoo e maЙ“Й“e, si wonaa nde arata e maЙ“Й“e sunna aranЙ“e Й“en maaЙ—un nde arata e maЙ“Й“e lepte Й—en ko Й—e peeГұuЙ—e."
  18,56,"Min Nuliraani NulaaЙ“e Й“e si wonaa ko weltinooЙ“e e jeertinooЙ“e, Й“e heeferЙ“e heЙ“e wennjana meere nden fii yo Й“e fuynir nde Goonga kan, Й“e njogitii aayeeje Am Й—en e ko Й“e mjeertiniraa kon jalnori."
  18,57,"Alaa potatЙ—o tooГұde on waajuraaЙ—o aayeeje Joomi makko o Й—uurii=fali e gaayi majje o yejjiti ko juuЙ—e makko Й—en ardini kon. Minen Min mbaЙ—ii e Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en cokooЙ—e fii wota Й“e faamu nde, ka noppi maЙ“Й“e kadi pahu, hay si a noddii Й“e fa'ade e Peewal Й“e peewataa on tuma haapoomaa."
  18,58,"Ko Joomi mon woni cuhroowo ko O Jom yurmeende e on, sinndo O nangitirno Й“e ko Й“e paggitii kon O yaccinanatno Й“e lepte Й—e, ko woni, no woodani Й“e fodoore Й“e heЙ“ataa ga mayre fattorde."
  18,59,"ЖҠeen ca'e, Min kalkuno Й“e tuma nde Й“e tooГұnoo min mbaЙ—ani halkeede maЙ“Й“e nden Fodoore."
  18,60,"Tuma nde Muusaa maakannoo sagata makko on: "Mi seerataa haa mi yottoo ka fottirde maaje Й—e Й—iЙ—i, ma de mi wuloo jamaanu."
  18,61,"Tuma nde Й“e njottoyinoo hakkonde majje Й“e njejjiti li'ingu maЙ“Й“e, ngu jogitii laawol maggol ka maayo wuddere."
  18,62,"Nde Й“e lummbunoo o [Muusaa] maakani sagataa makko on: "Addan en sojjaari=bottaari men ndi, gooЕӢЙ—ii en kawrii e nduu yahdu men Й—oo tampere."
  18,63,"O wi'i: "A yi'ii, nde cornoЙ—en ka fetere, min mi yejjiti Й—oon li'ingu o yejjintinaani kam fii maggil si wonaa Seytaane nde mi anndita ngu jogitii laawol maggol nder maayo no haawnori"."
  18,64,"[Muusaa] maaki: "Ko Й—oon ko ngonЙ—en Й—aЙ“Й“ude kon [woni], Й“e nduuttii e Й“atteeji maЙ“Й“e fillitagol."
  18,65,"ЖҒe tawoyi jeyaaЙ—o immorde e jeyaaЙ“e Amen min n ngokki mo jurmeende immorde ka amen, min nganndini mo immorde e amen Ganndal."
  18,66,"Muusaa maakani mo: "Enee [a accay] mi jokkete fii yo a anndinam goЙ—Й—um e ko ngandinaЙ—aa kon peewal ewal"?"
  18,67,"[Khadiru] maaki: "Pellet, aan a hattantaa muГұal won'dugol e an"."
  18,68,"Ko honno muГұuirtaa e dow kon ko a huЙ“indoraa Й—um ganndal?"
  18,69,"[Muusaa] maaki: "A tawat kam n si Alla Muuyi ko mi munГұiiЙ—o, mi yeddataa yamiroore maa"."
  18,70,"O maaki: "Si a jokkat kam wota a lanndo kan gaayi hu'unde haa mi yeewte immorde e mayre jaЕӢta"."
  18,71,"ЖҒe njahi haa de Й“e mbaЙ—Й—noo ka laana o yulika, [Muusaa] maaki: "A yulii ka fii yo ka yoolu yimЙ“e makka?! gooЕӢЙ—ii a addii hu'unde mawnde"."
  18,72,"[Khadiru] maaki: "Enee, mi wi'aano ma pellet, an a hattantaa muГұal won'dugol e am"."
  18,73,"[Muusaa] maaki: wota a jogoram ko mi yejjiti kon, wota a hewtinan e fiyaake am on satteende"."
  18,74,"ЖҒe njehi haa nde Й“e pottunoo e suka o wari mo! P maakani [mo]: "E a war woЕӢkii laaЙ“uki tanaa [yoЙ“tanagol] woЕӢkii, gooЕӢЙ—ii a addii hu'unde aГұiinde"."
  18,75,"[Khadiru] wi'i: "Enee, mi wi'aano ma pellet, an a hattantaa muГұal won'dugol e am"."
  18,76,"[Muusaa] maaki: "Si mi lanndike ma gaayi hu'unde Й“aawo Й—ii, wata a won'dino e am, gooЕӢЙ—ii a timminii ngantu e am."
  18,77,"ЖҒe njehi haa Й“e njaltiti e yimЙ“e saare, Й“e Й—aЙ“Й“iri Й“e Гұaametee Й“e calii wernude Й“e, Й“e tawi e ndeer mayre maadi faalaa fukkaade [Khadiru] o darnindi , o [Muusaa] maaki: "Sinno a yiЙ—no a Жҙettatno njoЙ“di e Й—um"."
  18,78,"[Khadiru] maaki: "Ko Й—um woni ceerdigal hakku- nde am e ma'a, mi yeewtu maa firo k ko a hattanaana munГұaade e dow mum"."
  18,79,"Si ko laana ka, ka laatanike miskineeЙ“e ngollo- Й“e ka maayo, mi faalaa aybin'de ka, hari laatike Й“aawo maЙ“Й“e laamЙ—o homo nannga kala laana o jaЙ“ta."
  18,80,"Si ko suka on mawЙ“e makko Й“e ngoni gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e , min kuli wata o fawu Й“e bewre e keeferaaku."
  18,81,"Men paalaa nde Joomi maЙ“Й“e waЙ—titanta Й“e Й“urЙ—o mo moЖҙЖҙude laaЙ“Й—o e Й“urЙ—o Й“attaade yurmeende."
  18,82,"Si ko maadi ndin, ndi laatanino sukaaЙ“e Й—iЙ—o won'Й—uЙ“e ka saare, laatii ley mayri ngalu maЙ“Й“e kamЙ“e Й—iЙ—o, hari baaba maЙ“Й“e laatinoke moЖҙЖҙo, Joomi maaЙ—a Faalaa nde Й“e njottotoo sagatalaagu maЙ“Й“e, O yaltina ngalu maЙ“Й“e ngu [Й—uum] ko Yurmeende immorde ka Joomi maa, mi waЙ—iraani Й—um e yamirooree am, Й—uum ko firo kon ko a hattanaani munГұaade e dow mum."
  18,83,"HeЙ“e fa'umaa laЙ“ndaade fii Julqarnayni, maaku: "Aray mi jannga e taweede mon e Й—um jaЕӢta."
  18,84,"Minen, Min weeЙ“inanno mo ka leydi, Min ngokki mo immorde e kala hu'unde sabu."
  18,85,"O jokki sabu[laawol}"
  18,86,"Haa nde o yottinoo ka mutirde na'ange ngen o tawi henge muta e loope Й“aleeje, o tawi ton yimЙ“e : Min mbi'i'i: "Ko aan yo jom galaaЙ—i Й—iЙ—i, ko si a leptay ma si a jogitoto e maЙ“Й“e ko moЖҙЖҙi."
  18,87,"O wi'i: Si tawii ko on tooГұuЙ—o min lepta mo, refti o ruttee ka Joomi makko o lepta mo lepte aГұiiЙ—e"."
  18,88,"Si tawii ko on gooЕӢЙ—inЙ—o o golli ko moЖҙЖҙi no woodani mo njoЙ“di moЖҙЖҙiri ndin, aray min n mbi'ana mo e fiyaake amen on neweende."
  18,89,"Refti o jokki laawol."
  18,90,"Haa de o yottinoo ka Жҙellitorde na'ange nge, o tawi henge Жҙellitoo e dow yimЙ“e, Min mbaЙ—anaani Й“e ga magge heeЙ—o."
  18,91,"Ko wano nii, gooЙ—ii Min kuЙ“indike ko woni kon ka makko e ganndal."
  18,92,"Refti o jokki laawol."
  18,93,"Haa nde o yottinoo hakkunde heedooji Й—i Й—iЙ—io tawi ga majji yimЙ“e Й“e Й—eЙ“ataa faamde konngol."
  18,94,"ЖҒe mbi'i: eey ma Julqarnayni, pellet, Yaajuuja e Maajuuja ko bonnooЙ“e ka leydi. Enee, min waЙ—ante njeenaari fii yo a waЙ— hakkunde amen e maЙ“Й“e heedo?"
  18,95,"O wi'i: "Ko Joomi am weeЙ“inani kan kon Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude, walliree kan doole mi waЙ—a hakkunde mo'on e maЙ“Й“e heedo"."
  18,96,"Ngaddanee kam kunte njamЙ—e haa nde o feppi- ndirnoo hakkunde naЙ—e Й—en Й—iЙ—i, o wi'i: "pifee haa nde o waЙ—noo Й—um yiite, o wi'i: ngaddanee kam sila mi wancina e dow mum"."
  18,97,"ЖҒe kattantaa Жҙellitagol ndi, Й“e hattantaa kadi julgol ndi."
  18,98,"O wi'i: Й—um Й—oo ko Yurmeende immornde e Joomi am, si Fodoore Joomi am nden arii o waЙ—at [heedo] ngo Й—iggungo, Fodoore Joomi am nde laatike ko nde Goonga"."
  18,99,"Min Й—ala yoga e maЙ“Й“e nden Гұalnde no yolloo e yoga, wuttaa ka allaadu Min mooЙ“a Й“e mooЙ“udee."
  18,100,"Min weeЙ“itanat(holliray) Jahannama nden Гұannde yedduЙ“e Й“en weeЙ“itugol=holllirgol."
  18,101,"ЖҒeen Й“e gite mue'n laatii e wirngallo gaayi jaЕӢta Aan, Й“e laatiЙ“e kattantaa nangol."
  18,102,"Enee, Й“en yedduЙ“e cikku Й“e njogoto jeyaaЙ“e Am Й“en ga Am, Minen Min heblanii Jahannama on fii yedduЙ“eЙ“en wona werde."
  18,103,"Maaku: "Taw si min kumpitay on fii Й“urЙ“e hayrude(pertude) golle?""
  18,104,"Ko Й“een Й“e golle mu'en yeebii ka ngurdam aduna hara kamЙ“e heЙ“e cikka heЙ“e moЖҙЖҙin'de golle."
  18,105,"Ko Й“een ngoni yedduЙ“e aayeeje Joomi maЙ“Й“e Й—en e kawroygol e makko, golle maЙ“Й“e Й—en bone Min ГұiiЙ“inantaaЙ“e Г‘ande Darngal ЖҒetu."
  18,106,"Jahannama ko Й—um woni njoЙ“di maЙ“Й“e, sabu ko Й“e njeddi kon Й“e jogitii aayeeje am Й—en e NulaaЙ“e am Й“en njalkitde."
  18,107,"Pellet, Й“een gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“e ngolli moЖҙЖҙi Й—in laatanto Й“e Aljannaaji Firdawsi Werdi(jipporde)."
  18,108,"Ko Й“e duumotooЙ“e ndeer ton, Й“e Й—aЙ“Й“ataa gani makko waylitorde."
  18,109,"Maaku: "Sinno maayo ngo laatino ndaha fii Daaluyeeji Joomi am Й—i, maayo ngo re'ayno ko adii ndee re'ata Daaluyeeji Joomi am Й—in, sinno Min addii yeru maggo e Й“eydude"."
  18,110,"Maaku: "Pellet min, ko mi Й“anndiЕӢke yeru mon, no wahayineede e am. Pellet, deweteeЙ—o mon o ko deweteeЙ—o Gooto, kala jortiiЙ—o kawroyde e Joomi makko yo o gollu golle moЖҙЖҙe wota o kafidu e dewal Joomi makko hay e gooto"."
  19,1,"Kaaf Haa Yaa ayn saad."
  19,2,"JaЕӢto Yurmeende Joomi maaЙ—a jeyaaЙ—o makko on Jakariyaa."
  19,3,"Tuma nde o noddunoo Joom makko noddaannu suuЙ—iindu."
  19,4,"O maaki: "Jooma, min dey Жҙi'e Й—en lo'ii e am hoore nden ranwi puri, mi laataaki non Й—awaaЙ—o ka toragol ma Jooma."
  19,5,"Min dey mi hulii lomtotooЙ“e Й“en Й“aawo am, cuddiiЙ—o am on laatike dimaro okkam immorde ka maaЙ—a Й“iЙ—Й—o."
  19,6,"O rona kam, o rona kadi e Й“eynguure Yaaquuba nde waЙ—aa mo Joomi weltoraaЙ—o."
  19,7,"Eeyma Jakariyaa Minen Min mbeltinirii ma suka innde makko ko Yahyaa Min mbЙ—anaani mo ko adii tokoraajo."
  19,8,"O maaki: "Jooma ko honno laatoranta kam suka sonnaajo am on laatike dimaro min kadi mi yottike e nayewu yooruЙ—o tere?""
  19,9,"[Maleka on] wi'i: "Ko nii Joomi maaЙ—a Daaliri: ЖҠum no neewii e Am gooЙ—ii Mi Tagiino ma ko adii, hari a laataaki huunde"."
  19,10,"O maaki: "Jooma waЙ—anam ma'ande". O Daali: "ma'ande maaЙ—a nden ko wota a wowlidu e yimЙ“e Й“en jemmaaji tati potondirЙ—i"."
  19,11,"O yalti hakkunde yimЙ“e makko Й“en immorde ka ganngunal o joopii fa'ande e maЙ“Й“e, Й—um woni subunhinee bimmbi e kiikiiЙ—e."
  19,12,"Eeyma Yahyaa nanngir deftere nden doole, min n ngokki mo ГұeeГұal ko o suka."
  19,13,"E Yurmeende immorde ka amen ko o laaЙ“uЙ—o o laatike kuloowo [Alla]."
  19,14,"Ko o Й—igganЙ—o jipnaaЙ“e mo Й“en o wonaani ndunndarankeejo gaaЖҙiiЙ—o."
  19,15,"Kisal e makko Гұande o jibinaa e Гұande o maayata e Г‘ande o immintintee ko o guuruЙ—o."
  19,16,"JaЕӢto ka deftere Mariyama tuma nde o woЙ—Й—itinoo immorde e yimЙ“e makko Й“en [o yaari] e nokkuure funnaangeyaЕӢkoore."
  19,17,"O jogitii ga maЙ“Й“e wirngallo, min Nuli e makko Ruuhu amen o nanndintinanii mo e Й“anndiЕӢke fotondirЙ—o."
  19,18,"O maaki: min mi moolorii jurmoteeЙ—o On immorde e maaЙ—a si tawii a laatike ko a kulЙ—o [Alla]."
  19,19,"O wi'i: "Pellet, min ko mi NulaaЙ—o Joomi maaЙ—a fii yo mi okke suka laaЙ“Й—o."
  19,20,"O wi'i: "Ko hono laatoranta kam suka hara Й“anndiЕӢke memaani kam mi laataaki kadi jeenoowo(pijoowo)"."
  19,21,"O wi'i: "ko nii Joomi maaЙ—a Daaliri: "ЖҠuum no newii e am e fii yo min mbaЙ— mo ma'ande fii yimЙ“e Й“en e Yurmeende immornde e amen Й—um laatike fiyaake Г‘aawaaЙ—o"."
  19,22,"O roondii mo, o pottidodi e makko e nokkuure woЙ—Й—itiinde."
  19,23,"ЕҠata(qatwere) on fiЙ—i mo e jullere tamarohi, o wi'i: "Ee hara noon mi maayno ko adii Й—um mi laatoo hu'unde yejjitaande"."
  19,24,"O noddi mo immorde e ley makki, [o wi'i] wota a suno gooЕӢЙ—ii Joomi maaЙ—a waЙ—ii ley maaЙ—a caatngol."
  19,25,"YeЖҙu(dimmbu) fa'ade e maaЙ—a jullere tamarohi kin nde liЙ“a e ma,aЙ—a Й“ennduЙ—e teЙ“eteeЙ—e."
  19,26,"Г‘aam yaraa Й“uЙ“Й“inaa gite, si a yi'ii goЙ—Й—o immorde e Й“anndiЕӢke wi'u: "Miin dey mi takkanii Hinnorante(jurmotooЙ—o korka mi wowlidata e neЙ—Й—aЕӢke hannde"."
  19,27,"O radi e makko ka yimЙ“e makko, homo tammbii mo Й“e wi'i: "Ko an yo Mariyama gooЕӢЙ—ii a addii hu'unde hawnii nde"."
  19,28,"Eyma banndiraawo Haaruuna baaba maa laatanooki neЙ—Й—o bonЙ—o neene maaЙ—a kadi laataaki jinoowo."
  19,29,"[Mariyama] joopii e makko, Й“e mbi'i:"Ko hono min njewtirta e on sanfaajo gonЙ—o e woofordu(liir) gondo e tiiggu"."
  19,30,"[Iisaa] maaki: "Miin dey ko mi jiyaaЙ—o Alla o okkii kam deftere nden o waЙ—ii kam annabaajo"."
  19,31,"O waЙ—i kam BarkinaaЙ—o nokku kala ka mi woni, o wasiyii kam Juulde nden e Jakka on fodde miЙ—o wuuri."
  19,32,"Ko mi Й—igganЙ—o yumma am, o waЙ—aani kam ndunndarankeejo malkisaaЙ—o."
  19,33,"Kisal on wonii e am Гұande mi jibinaa e Гұande mi maayata e Гұande mi immintintee ko mi guuruЙ—o."
  19,34,"On ko Iisaa geЙ—al Mariyama Daalol Goongawol ngol heЙ“e cikkitoo fii mu'um."
  19,35,"Haananaa Alla nde o jogitotoo Й“iЙ—Й—o senaare e wonanii mo, si O Гұaawii fiyaake o daalanay mo tan: "Won" o wona."
  19,36,"Pellet, ko Alla Woni Joomi am e Joomi mon, mdewee o. Ko Й—um woni Laawol poocciingol"."
  19,37,"Pelle Й—e luutondiri hakkunde majji, bone wonanii Й“en yedduЙ“e ceedagol Гұalaande mawnde."
  19,38,"Kaawee ko nanirta yi'ira wa maЙ“Й“e Г‘ande Й“e aroyta e amen, kono tooГұooЙ“e Й“en hannde heЙ“e e ndeer majjere Й“anngunde."
  19,39,"KulЙ“inir Й“e Гұande Nimse, tuma nde fiyaake on Гұaawaa hara kamЙ“e hiЙ“e e ndeer welsindaare hara Й“e gooЕӢЙ—inaa."
  19,40,"Minen min ndonat lesdi ndi e Й“en wonЙ“e e dow mayri, ko ka amen Й“e nduttetee."
  19,41,"JaЕӢto ka deftere Ibraahiima, pellet, kaЕӢko o laatino GoonguЙ—o annabaajo."
  19,42,"Tuma nde o maakannoo bem makko: "eeyma baaba ko holЙ—um ndewantaa Й—um ko nanataa yi'ataa hara duncantaa ma hay e hu'unde?"
  19,43,"Eeyma baaba min dey gooЙ—ii arii am immorde e Ganndal kon ko araani e maaЙ—a, jokkam mi fewne e Laawol po'occiingol."
  19,44,"Eeyma baaba, wota a rew Seytaane, pellet, Seytaane laatike jedduЙ—o jurmotooЙ—o."
  19,45,"Eeyma baaba, min dey miЙ—o huli wota meeme Lepte immorde ka jurmotooЙ—o laatanoЙ—aa Seytaane giЙ—o."
  19,46,"[Baaba makko] wi'i: "Enee, an a aГұ deweteeЙ—i am Й—in nee Ibraahiima, pellet, si a accaani mi fiЙ—ete selam dummunne [juutuЙ—o]."
  19,47,"[Ibraahiima] maaki: "Kisal e maaЙ—a aray mi inminanomaa ka Joomi am, pellet, KoЕӢko O Laatike NewaniiЙ—o kam."
  19,48,"Mi martoo(deestoo) on e kon ko ndewoton ga Alla, mi toroo Joomi am no gasa mi wonataa tampirЙ—o toragol Joomi am."
  19,49,"Tuma nde o martinoo(deestinoo) Й“e e ko Й“e ndewata kon gaAlla, min n ngokki mo Ishaaqa e Yaaquuba kala [gooto e maЙ“Й“e] Men waЙ—i [mo] Annabaajo."
  19,50,"Min ngokki Й“e immorde e Yurmeende amen, min mbaЙ—ani Й“e mantoore toownde."
  19,51,"JaЕӢto ka deftere Muusaa, pellet, kaЕӢko o laatinoke laЙ“Й“inЙ—o o laatinoke kadi NulaaЙ—o Annabiijo."
  19,52,"Min noddi mo ka senЕӢgo Гұaamo [fello] Tuuri Min Й“attini mo gunndeteeЙ—o."
  19,53,"Min ngokki mo immorde e Yurmeende amen musiЙ—Й—o makko on Haaruuna Annabiijo."
  19,54,"JaЕӢto ka defftere Ismaa'iila, pellet, kaЕӢko o laatinoke gooЕӢЙ—uЙ—o fodoore o laatinoke kadi NulaaЙ—o Annabiijo."
  19,55,"O laatino himo yamira yimЙ“e makko Й“en Juulde e askal on, o laatino kadi beltoraaЙ—o ka Joomi makko."
  19,56,"JaЕӢto ka deftere Idriisa, pellet, kaЕӢko o laatino goonguЙ—o Annabiijo."
  19,57,"Men Й“amti mo e nokkuure Toownde."
  19,58,"Ko Й“een ngoni Й“een, Й“e Alla Neemini e dow mu'en immorde e AnnabaaЙ“e ka geЙ—al Й“ebibbe Aadama e Й“en Й“e Men mbaЙ—Й—innoo wond'ude e Nuuhu e geЙ—alЙ“e Ibraahiima e Israa'iila e Й“en Й“e Min peewni min n cuЙ“ii si janngaama e dow maЙ“Й“e aayeeje Hinnorante Й“e fukko koЙ“e sujjooЙ“e e wullooЙ“e."
  19,59,"Lomtii Й“aawo maЙ“Й“e lomtotooЙ“e, Й“e njeeebi Juulde nden Й“e njokki welamuuji Й—in aray Й“e kawroya e bone."
  19,60,"Si wonaa on tuubuЙ—o o gooЕӢЙ—ini o golli ko moЖҙЖҙi, Й“en Й—on Й“e naatat Aljanna on Й“e tooГұiroy- taake hay e huunde."
  19,61,"Aljannaaji Adan Й—in Й—i jurmotooЙ—o o Fodi jeyaaЙ“e makko Й“en e birnagal, pellet KaЕӢko, Fodoore Makko nden laatike ko aroore."
  19,62,"ЖҒe nanataa ndeer ton rayrayti si wonaa kisal no woodani Й“e arsike maЙ“Й“e on nder ton bimmbi e kiikiiЙ—e."
  19,63,"Oon Aljanna mo Men ndoninta immorde e jeyaaЙ“e amen Й“en, on laatiiЙ—o kulol [Alla]."
  19,64,"Min njippotaako si wonaa e Yamaruyee Joomi maaЙ—a, no woodani mo ko woni kon hedde yeeso amen e ko woni kon Й“aawo amen e ko woni kon hakkunde Й—um, Joomi maaЙ—a laataaki yejjitoowo."
  19,65,"Jooma kammuuli Й—in e lesdi ndin e ko woni kon hakkunde majji, rew mo monГұitor dewal makko. Taw si haЙ—a anndani mo tokoraajo?"
  19,66,"NeЙ—Й—aЕӢke on no wi'a: "Eyoo, e jaka si mi maai aroyay ka mi yaltinee tawa ko mi guurЙ—o?""
  19,67,"Enee, neЙ—Й—aЕӢke on annditaani Menen Men Tagiino mo ko adii, hari o wonaali hay e hu'unde."
  19,68,"Mi woondirii Joomi maaЙ—a min mooЙ“at Й“e sanne e Seytanuuji Й—in, refti min ngadda Й“e sara Jahannama ko Й“e jiccii Й“e."
  19,69,"Refti min n Й—o'ofa immorde e kala fedde ko hommbo e maЙ“Й“e Й“urnoo saЙ—tude dartagol e dow jurmotooЙ—o e o."
  19,70,"Refti ko minen nganndi Й“een Й“urЙ“e haan'dude e sumugol e magge."
  19,71,"Alaa hay e gooto e mo'on si wanaa o joloyat e magge, Й—um laatike e dow Joomi maaЙ—a ko ГұaawaЙ—um TeeЕӢtinaa."
  19,72,"Refti min ndaЙ—na Й“en hulunooЙ“e [Alla] min n Й—ala tooГұooЙ“e Й“en ko Й“e jicciiЙ“e ndeer ton."
  19,73,"Si janngaama e taweede maЙ“Й“e aayeeje amen ЖҒannguЙ—e Й—e yedduЙ“e Й“e mb'a gom- Й—imЙ“e Й“en: "Ko honnde e feddeeji Й—i Й—iЙ—i Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude darnde Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude kadi batu"."
  19,74,"Heewii ko min kalki ado maЙ“Й“e immorde e gire tawi ko kamЙ“e Й“uri fotude mirannji suudu e mba'adi."
  19,75,"Maaku: "On laatiiЙ—o e ndeer majjere nde yo jurmotooЙ—o fortan mo fontudee, haa si Й“e yi'ii ko Й“e fodaa kon, si tawii ko lepte Й—en maa si ko Darngal ngal, aray Й“e annda on m bonuЙ—o nukkuure e Й“urЙ—o lo'ude konu"."
  19,76,"Alla no Й“eydana Й“en feewЙ“e Peewal, MoЖҙЖҙi heddotooЙ—i Й—in Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude mbarjaari ka Joomi maaЙ—a Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude kadi ruttorde."
  19,77,"Enee, a yi'ii on jedduЙ—o aayeeje amen Й—e, o wi'i: "Maatun mi okkee jawdi e Й“iЙ—Й—o"."
  19,78,"Enee o Жҙelliti e ko wirnii kon, kaa jogiti ka jurmotooЙ—o e Aadi?"
  19,79,"Wonaa non, aray Min mbinnda ko o wi'ata kon min Й“eydana mo immorde e Lepte Й—en Й“eydude."
  19,80,"Min ndonna mo e ko o wi'ata ko, o ara e Amen ko o weddiiЙ—o(gooto)."
  19,81,"ЖҒe njogitii ga Alla deweteeЙ—i fii yo Й—i laatano Й“e semmbe."
  19,82,"Wonaa non, maЙ“e njeddu dewugolЙ“e ngol, Й“e laatanoo Й“e aГұЙ“e."
  19,83,"Enee a yiaani minen min Nulii Seytanuuji e dow yedduЙ“e Й“en hiЙ—i Жҙuuna Й“e Жҙuunudee."
  19,84,"Wata a hawjan Й“e, pellat, limonayЙ“ebe kala limugol."
  19,85,"Г‘ande Min mooЙ“oyta hulooЙ“e [Alla] Й“e ka jurmotooЙ—o TeddinaaЙ“e."
  19,86,"Men cogga bonЙ“e Й“e haa ka Jahannama ko Й“e jolooЙ“e."
  19,87,"ЖҒe maraa tefoore nden si wonaa on jogitiiЙ—o ka jurmotooЙ—o Aadi."
  19,88,"ЖҒe mbi'i: "jurmotooЙ—o jogitike Й“iЙ—Й—o"."
  19,89,"GooЕӢЙ—ii on mgaddii hu'unde pankarЙ—ii nde."
  19,90,"Kammuuli Й—in no do'a(Й—esa) se'ekaade immorde e Й—uum leydi ndin feera pelle Й—e nduuya fii unagol."
  19,91,"fii Й“e noddanii jurmotooЙ—o Й“iЙ—Й—o."
  19,92,"Haananaa jurmotooЙ—o de o jogitotoo Й“iЙ—Й—o."
  19,93,"Alaa ko woni e kammuuli e leydi si wanaa o aray e jurmotooЙ—o hombo woni jeyaaЙ—o."
  19,94,"GooЙ—ii o moftii Й“e o limii Й“e kadi e limugol."
  19,95,"[Gooto] Kala e maЙ“Й“e aray Mo Г‘ande Darngako o woddiiЙ—o(teeldЙ—o)."
  19,96,"Pellet, Й“een gooЙ—inЙ“e ngolli ko moЖҙЖҙi ko aray ka jurmotooЙ—o waЙ—anaЙ“e Giggol."
  19,97,"Anndu ko min n newiniri nde ka Й—enngal maaЙ—a; ko fii yo a weltinir nde hulooЙ“e [Alla] Й“en njertiniraa nde yimЙ“e saЙ—tuЙ“e weeГұre."
  19,98,"Heewii ko min kalki ado maЙ“Й“e e gire taw si hiЙ—a so'a e maЙ“Й“e immorde e goЙ—Й—o, maa haЙ—a nana Й“e hito?"
  20,1,"Taa Haa."
  20,2,"Min Telliniraani Alqur'aanaare nde e maaЙ—a fii yo a tampu."
  20,3,"Si wonaa waaju wonan'de on kuloowo [Alla]."
  20,4,"Ko Jippinaande immorde e oon takЙ—o leydi ndi e kammuuji toowuЙ—i Й—in."
  20,5,"JurmotooЙ— o O fotii e dow Arsi he."
  20,6,"No woodani mo o ko woni ko e kammuuji Й—in e ko woni kon e leydi ndi e ko wini kon hakkunde majji kannji Й—iЙ—i e ko woni ko e les leydi."
  20,7,"Si a fenГұinii konngol ngol, pellet, KaЕӢko homo Anndi ko feeГұi e ko o suuЙ—i."
  20,8,"Alla deweteeЙ—o alaa si wonaa KaЕӢko, no woodani mo InЙ—e moЖҙЖҙe Й—e."
  20,9,"taw si arii e maaЙ—a yewtere fii Muusaa."
  20,10,"Tuma nde o yi'inoo yiite, o wi'ani Й“eynguure makko nden: "Г‘iiЙ“ee, min de mi haynike jayngol mbele-jo'o mi addanat on immorde e maggol docotal ma mi tawa ka [moggo] yiite tinndinoowo."
  20,11,"Tuma nde o aunoo e maggol o noddaa; "eyma Muusaa"."
  20,12,"[Alla Daalano mo] Min dey ko miin Woni Joomi maaЙ—a poortu paЙ—e maa Й—en; pellet an, haЙ—a ka aynde(caatngol) Tuwaa LaЙ“Й“inaande(seninangol)."
  20,13,"Miin mi SuЙ“ike ma Jento ko wonaa Wahyineede ko."
  20,14,"Pellet, ko miinn Woni Alla deweteeЙ—o alaa si wonaa miin n rewam; ГұiiЙ“i e Juulde nde fii Annditugol am."
  20,15,"Pellet, Darnga ko aroowa MiЙ—o Й—eЙ“a suuЙ—ude ngo fii yoЙ“e kala woЕӢkii ko ki gollu no."
  20,16,"Wota faddo ma e gaayi maggal on mo gooЕӢ- Й—inaani ngo o jokki mbeleeЙ—e makko o halkii."
  20,17,"Ko holЙ—uum woni ka Гұaamo maaЙ—a an Muusaa?"
  20,18,"O maaki: "Ndu ko tuggordu am miЙ—o tuggoo ndu miЙ—o liwtirana ndu dammi am Й—in, miЙ—o mari kadi haajuuji gЙ—Й—i e mayru"."
  20,19,"O Daali: "weddo ndu, aan Muusaa"."
  20,20,"O weddi ndu, tawi kayru ko ndu mbooЙ—di won'ndi e yahde."
  20,21,"O Daali: "Nanngu ndi wota a hul min ngartira ndu e mba'adi mayru araniri ndi"."
  20,22,"Naatnu junngo maaЙ—a ngo ka ndeer seЕӢgo maa; ngo yalta ko ngo raneewo ko aldaa e rafi Й—um ko Aaya goo."
  20,23,"Fii yo min n kollle immorde e aayeeje amen aawЙ—e Й—e."
  20,24,"Yah to Fir'awna, pellet, kaЕӢko o bewi."
  20,25,"O maaki: "Jooma Yaacnanam Й“ernde am nde."
  20,26,"Newinana am fiyaake am on."
  20,27,"PiЙ“taa fiЙ“nde nde e Й—emngal am."
  20,28,"Fii yoo Й“e pahmu konngol am ngol."
  20,29,"MbaЙ—anaa kam ballo jeyaaЙ—o ka Й“eynguure am."
  20,30,"[Hara ko] Haaruuna musiЙ—Й—o am o."
  20,31,"Semmbinir mo darnde am."
  20,32,"Tawnaa mo e ndeer fiyaake am o."
  20,33,"Fii yo mon cenine ko herwi."
  20,34,"Min jaЕӢtomaa ko heewi."
  20,35,"Pellet, aan a wonii kumpitiiЙ—o min ."
  20,36,"O Daali: "GooЕӢЙ—ii a okkaama toraare maaЙ—a nde aan Muusaa"."
  20,37,"GooЕӢЙ—ii n neeminiino ma e laawol goЙ—ngol."
  20,38,"Tuma de min mbahayinnoo fa'ade e yumma maa ko wahayinaa ko."
  20,39,"[Men Daali] weddo mo to ndeer hontoore weddo Й—um nde kadi ka ndeer diidere, yo diidere nden kadi weddoyo mo ka maayo ; Жҙetta mo gaГұo am e gaГұo makko, mi werni e maaЙ—a Giggol immorde ka am e fii yo a ne'e e dow ndeenka am."
  20,40,"Tuma de banndiraawo maaЙ—a on yahynoo; o wi'a: "Enee, yo mi tinndin on e on mo no ne'a mo?" min ngartirmaa ka yumma maaЙ—a fii yo gite makko Й—en Й“uuЙ“u hara o sunaaki. MbarЙ—aa woЕӢkii min ndaЙ—umaa immorde e saЙ—teende nde, min njarribimaa jarrabuyeeje ГұiiЙ“Й—aa duuЙ“i ka yimЙ“e Madyana refti ngarЙ—aa ka fodoore aan Muusaa."
  20,41,"Miin suЙ“imaa fii hooram"
  20,42,"Yah aan e musiЙ—Й—o maa on won'dude e aayeeje am Й—e wota on derfu e jaЕӢtagol Lam."
  20,43,"Njehee ka Fir'awna, pellet, kaЕӢko o bewi."
  20,44,"Mbianee mo konngol newiingol mbele-jo'o kaЕӢko o waajitoto ma o hula."
  20,45,"ЖҒe maaki: "Joomi amen, minen dey moЙ—en kuli nde murtata e hoore amen maa de o bewata"."
  20,46,"O Daali: "Wota on kule, pellet, miin miЙ—o won'di e mooЙ—on miЙ—o Nana MiЙ—o Yi'a"."
  20,47,"Ngare ee e makko, mbi'on: "minen ko min NulaaЙ“e Joomi maaЙ—a, accit won'dude e amen Й“iЙ—Й“e Israa'iila Й“e wota a leptu Й“e, gooЕӢЙ—ii min ngddanii e ma aaya immorde ka Joomi maaЙ—a, kisal wonii e oon jokkuЙ—o Peewal ngal."
  20,48,"GooЕӢЙ—ii Wahayinaama e amen; won'dema, Lepte Й—e no fawii ka jennuЙ—o Й—uurni."
  20,49,"[Fir'awna] wi'i: "eeyma o Muusaa, ko hommbo woni Joomi mooЙ—on?""
  20,50,"[Muusaa] maaki: "Joomi amen, ko on OkkuЙ—o kala hu'unde tagoore mayre refti o feewni."
  20,51,"[Fir'awna] wi'i: "Ko holno gire arane Й—en pewndori?""
  20,52,"[Muusaa] maaki: "ganndal Й—um no ka Joomi am e ndeer Deftere, Joomi am majjataa o yejjitataa"."
  20,53,"Oon baЙ—anЙ—o on leydi ndi weЖҙЖҙitaandi, o naadani on e ndeer mayri laabi, O jippini immorde e kammu ngu ndiyam Min njaltiniri Й—am nooneeji immorde e puЙ—i ceertuЙ—i."
  20,54,"Г‘aamee ngaynon neemoraaЙ—i mo'on Й—i. Pellet, no e ndeer Й—um [ko jaЕӢtaa Й—oo] Aayeeje fii joomiraa- Й“e kakkillaaji Й—in."
  20,55,"Ko immorde e mayri Min Tagi on, ko e ndeer mayri Min nduttata on, ko immorde e mayri kadi Min njaltinoyta on laawol goЙ—gol"
  20,56,"GooЕӢЙ—ii Min kolli mo aayeeje Amen Й—en kala majje, o jeddi i o salii."
  20,57,"[Fir'awna] wi'i: "enee, a ar ka amen fii yo a njaltinir min ka leydi amen mbilewu maaЙ—a ngun aan Muusaa?""
  20,58,"Maa min ngaddane mbilewu yeru maggu, waЙ— fodoore hakkunde amen e maaЙ—a hara men lunndataako nde wonaa an kadi [lunndotoo nde] e nokkuure fotondirnde."
  20,59,"[Muusaa] maaki: fodoore mooЙ—on nden ko Гұande saЙ—Й—ugol ngol, yo yimЙ“e Й“en mooЙ“indire mbeetaa(fenynyaange)."
  20,60,"Fir'awna ruЕӢiti o mooЙ“i pewje makko Й—en refti o ari."
  20,61,"Muusaa maakani Й“e: "On boniraama, wota on 'pekindo fenaande fawon e Alla sakko O mehira on Lepte, gooЕӢЙ—ii sooyii on pekindiiЙ—o."
  20,62,"ЖҒe pooЙ—ondiri fiyaake maЙ“Й“e on hakkunde maЙ“Й“e, Й“e vuuЙ—i cowndi Й—in."
  20,63,"ЖҒe mbi'i: "Pellet Й“ee Й—iЙ—o ko wileeЙ“e heЙ“e paalaa yaltinirnde on ka leydi mon e mbilaaku maЙ“Й“e ngu Й“e itta laawol mon Й“urngol l ngol."
  20,64,"MooЙ“itee pewje mo'on Й—e refti ngaron ko on lappol, gooЕӢЙ—ii malaama hannde on poolЙ—o."
  20,65,"Muusaa maaki: "Ko si tawii ko onon mbeddotoo ma si ko minen ngonata adotooЙ“e weddaade."."
  20,66,"[Muusaa] maaki: "ko woni, (mbedde), tawi Й“oggi maЙ“Й“e e cawoy maЙ“Й“e koy no wa'itana mo sabu mbilewu maЙ“Й“e ngun woni ko e yahde."
  20,67,"Muusaa so'i kulol ka woЕӢkii makko."
  20,68,"Min Daali: 'Wota a hul, pellet ko an woni pooloowo on."
  20,69,"Weddo ko woni ko ka Гұaamo maaЙ—a Й—um moЙ—ay ko Й“e moЖҙЖҙini ko, pellet, ko Й“e moЖҙЖҙini ko ko pewje mbile bileejo on maletaake nukkuwoo ka o ardi."
  20,70,"WileeЙ“e Й“e mbernaa ko Й“e sujjuЙ“e, Й“e mbi'i: "Min ngooЕӢЙ—inii Joomi Haaruuna e Muusaa"."
  20,71,"[Fir'awna] wi'i: Eyoo, on gooЕӢЙ—inii mo ko adii mi duЕӢanaade(sakkitaade) on? Pelet, ko kaЕӢko woni mawЙ—o mo'on on anndinЙ—o on mbilewu ngu, mi wooЙ—ndii, maa mi taЖҙa juuЙ—e mon Й—en e koyЙ—e mon Й—en taЖҙa luutindira, maa mi feta on e julle tama aray anndon ko hommbo e amen Й“uri lepte caЙ—tuЙ—e e heddotooЙ—e."
  20,72,"[wileeЙ“e Й“e] mbi'i: "Min Й“urnataa ma e dow koo ko ari e amen immorde e Й“annganguyeeji, e On TakЙ—o min, [an Fir'awna] Гұaawu ko Гұaawataa ko, pellet, ko Гұaawataa ko ka ngurndan aduna Й—oo"."
  20,73,"Minen dey, men ngooЕӢЙ—inii Joomi amen fii yo o yawtan men goopi amen e kon ko dooluЙ—aa men e mu'un immorde e mbilewu nguyn, ko Alla woni MoЖҙЖҙo keddotooЙ—o."
  20,74,"Pellet on mo ari ka Joomi mu'un hara ko o bonЙ—o; haray pellet, no woodani mo Jahannama o maayataa e nder magge o wuurataa kadi ."
  20,75,"mo ari ka makko ko o gooЕӢЙ—inЙ—o hara gooЕӢЙ—ii o golliino moЖҙЖҙi Й—i, haray Й“en Й—on no woodani Й“e Darjaaji ToowЙ—i Й—in."
  20,76,"Aljannaaji ГұiiЙ“al no doga e ley majji caatli Й—i, ko Й“e duumotooЙ“e ndeer ton, ko Й—um woni njoЙ“di on laЙ“Й“iniiЙ—o."
  20,77,"GooЙ—ii Min mbahaynii fa'ade e Muusaa roЖҙdu e jeyaaЙ“e Am Й“e waЙ—an Й“e laawol yooru ngol ka maayo joorngol wota a hul hewtiteede wota a hul [yoolagol]."
  20,78,"Fir'awna jokkitiri Й“e konooli makko Й—i, suumi Й“e ka maayo ko suumi Й“e kon."
  20,79,"Fir'awnan majjini yimЙ“e makko Й“e, o fewnaani [Й“e]."
  20,80,"Eey monЙ“iЙ—Й“e Israa'iila gooЕӢЙ—ii Min danndiino on e gaГұo mon on, Min podi on kadi ka baЕӢЕӢe Гұaamo [fello] Tuuri ngon, Min njippini e mooЙ—on Manna= Й—acce njumri e doobe ."
  20,81,"Г‘aamee immorde e laaЙ“Й—i ko Min arsiki on kon, wota on bew e nder mu'un sakko Tikkere Am nden njippo e mo'on, on mo tikkere am jippii e mu'un gooЕӢЙ—ii haray o halkike."
  20,82,"Pellet, Min ko Mi keewuЙ—o Yawtanngol wonan'de on tuubuЙ—o o gooЕӢЙ—ini o golli ko moЖҙЖҙi refti o feewi."
  20,83,"Ko holЙ—um heГұinmaa ga yimЙ“e maa Й“en aan Muusaa?"
  20,84,"[Muusaa] maaki: "ЖҒeeЙ—oo, hieЙ“e iwtiri Й“aawo am, mi heГұike ka MaaЙ—a Joomi fii yo A welto."
  20,85,"[Alla] Daali: "Pellet, Mennen gooЕӢЙ—ii Men njarribike=finninii yimЙ“e maaЙ—a Й“en Й“aawo maaЙ—a, Saamiriiyu majjinii Й“e"."
  20,86,"Muusaa ruttii ka yimЙ“e makko Й“en ko o tikkuЙ—o suniiЙ—o; o maaki: "Ko onon yo yimЙ“e, enee, Joomi mo'on Fodanaani on Fodoore MoЖҙЖҙere, kaa ko aadi ndin juutani on? Kaa on faandi nde jippotoo e mo'on Tikkere immorde ka Joomi mooЙ—on si lunndi Й—on fodoore am nden?""
  20,87,"ЖҒe mbi'i: "Min lunndaaki fodoore maaЙ—a nde e sago amen, kono minen men ndonndinaama teddeendi e cuЙ—aaje yimЙ“e Й“en men wernii Й—e, ko nii Saamiriiyu kadi welirni"."
  20,88,"O yaltinani Й“e Й“anndu ngaari marn hito= huunaango, Й“e mbi'i: "Ko ko'ol woni deweteeЙ—o mon e deweteeЙ—o Muusaa on, o yejjiti [mo Й—oo]"."
  20,89,"Enee, Й“ee yiaani wonan'dema ruttataako e maЙ“Й“e konngol, ndi maranaa Й“e kadi lorra wonaa fii non [pooЙ—ugol] nafa."
  20,90,"GooЙ—ii Haaruuna maakaniino Й“e ko adii: "Ko onon yo yimЙ“e, pellet, on njarribora kol, pellet, Joomi mooЙ—on ko jurmotooЙ—o o jokkee kam Й—oftoЙ—on yamiroore am nden"."
  20,91,"ЖҒe mbi'i i: "Min ceerataa ko min ГұiiЙ“uЙ“e e [dewal] makkol haa Muusaa ruttoo e amen"."
  20,92,"[Muusaa] maaki: "eeyma Haaruuna, nde nji'iЙ—aa Й“e majjii ko haЙ—maa,"
  20,93,"de njokkitataa mi? Kaa a yeddii yamirooe am on?!""
  20,94,"[Haaruuna] maaki: "eeyma Й“iy neene am, wota a nanngu wahre am nde wonaa hoore am nden kadi, miin dey, mi hulu wata a wi'i: Mi seerdii hakkunde Й“iЙ—Й“e Israa'iila Й“e, mi heЙ—aaki konngol maaЙ—a ngol"."
  20,95,"[Muusaa] maaki: "Ko hol Й—uum woni fiyaake maaЙ—a on an Saamiriiyu?""
  20,96,"[Saamiriiyu] wi'i: "Mi yi'ii ko Й“e yiaani Й—um, mi nokki nokkannde e batte nulaaЙ—o on [Jibriila] mi wernii Й—um ko nii suЙ—irani lam woЕӢkii am."
  20,97,"[Muusaa] maaki: "Yahu, pellet, no woodanmaa ka ngurndam nde wowlataa wanaa meemondiral, pellet, no woodanmaa kadi Fodoore a lunndataako nde, ndaarii fa'ade e dewteeЙ—o maa, on mo ГұalluЙ—aa ufinaade e hoore mun, mi woondii mi sumat mo refti mi Жҙaroo mo ka maayo e Жҙaragol"."
  20,98,"Pellet, deweteeЙ—o mon On ko Alla, On Mo DeweteeЙ—o alaa si wanaa KaЕӢko, Ganndal makko Yaajanii kala hu'unde."
  20,99,"Ko wano nii Men polloranay maa immorde e kumpital ko feЖҙЖҙunoo kon, gooЕӢЙ—ii Men ngaddanii ma immorde ka Amen jaЕӢta."
  20,100,"Mo Й—uurike e mayre pellet, o ronndoto Г‘ande Darngal teddeele [bakkaatu]."
  20,101,"Ko o luttinteeЙ—o e ndeer majje, bonanii Й“e donngal Г‘ande Darngal."
  20,102,"Г‘aande wuttoytee ka alaadu Min mooЙ“a bonЙ“e Й“en nden Г‘alnde ko mbuliiЙ“e [gite]."
  20,103,"HeЙ“e sowndondira hakkunde maЙ“Й“e [Й“e mbi'a] on ГұiiЙ“aani si wonaa [balЙ—e] sappo."
  20,104,"Ko Minen ngoni AnnduЙ“e ko Й“e wowlata kon, tuma nde koohooЙ“e maЙ“Й“e e laawol wi'ata: "On ГұiiЙ“aani si wonaa Гұallal"."
  20,105,"HeЙ“e lanndaade ma fii pelle Й—en, maaku: "Joomi am Жҙaroto Й—e e Жҙaragol"."
  20,106,"O acca [leydi] ndi ko ndi boowal Й“owrungal."
  20,107,"A yi'ataa e mayri ooГұannde wonaa tintiire.(naЙ—de)."
  20,108,"Ko nden Г‘ande Й“e njokkata noddoowo on ko aldaa e celugol mo,, hitooji Й—i yankinanoo Hinnorante On hara a nanataa si wnaa Гұu'umbaangol."
  20,109,"Nden Г‘ande tefoore nden nafataa, si wonaa on mo Hinnorante On sakkiti Й—um O weltori konngol makko."
  20,110,"Homo Anndi ko woni ko yeeso maЙ“Й“e e Й“aawo maЙ“Й“e Й“e kuЙ“indortaa Й—um ganndal."
  20,111,"Je'ece Й—en yankinanii guruЙ—o DartiiЙ—o On, gooЕӢЙ—ii sooyii on donndiiЙ—o tooГұe."
  20,112,"On mo ngolli immorde e moЖҙЖҙi Й—in hara ko o gooЕӢЙ—inЙ—o o hulaa tooГұe wonaa uytaneede kadi."
  20,113,"Ko nii Min Telliniri nde Alqur'aanaare Aarabuure Men fensiti kadi e nder mayre immorde e kammbaaji Й—in mbela-jo'o kamЙ“e Й“e kulat maa nde fuЙ—Й—anoo Й“e waaju."
  20,114,"Alla LaamЙ—o GoonguЙ—o On Toowii, wata a heГұor Alqur'aanaare nden ko adii nde timmintee e maaЙ—a wahayu mayre, maaku: "Joomi Й“eydanam Ganndal"."
  20,115,"GooЕӢЙ—ii min ngaadondiri e Aadama ko adii o yejjiti Min keЙ“anaani mo pellital."
  20,116,"Tuma Nde Men Daalannoo maleylaaji Й—i cujjanee Aadama, Й“e cujji si wanaa Ibliisa o salii."
  20,117,"Men Daali: "eeyma Aadama, pellet, ooЙ—oo ko o gaГұo maa aan e sonnaajo maa on, wota o yaltin on dey ka Aljanna sakko tampaa"."
  20,118,"Pellet, no woodanmaa nde a heegetaake nder ton a holataa kadi."
  20,119,"Pellet, an a Й—omЙ—etaake nde ton e wuletaake kadi."
  20,120,"Seytaane sonwonsini faade e makko; o wi'i: eeyma Aadama,hara yo mi tinndine e leggal luttineede ngal e laamu ngu follotaako ngu?""
  20,121,"ЖҒe Гұaami e maggal, feeГұani Й“e mettefooji maЙ“Й“e Й—in, Й“e naati e suddirgol e dow maЙ“Й“e immorde e kaaki Aljanna o, Aadama yeddi Joomi makko o majji."
  20,122,"Refti Joomi makko SuЙ“ii mo, o Tuubini mo o Feewni [mo]."
  20,123,"O Daali: "njippee toon, onon fof yoga e mo'on ko aГұЙ“e yoga. Si tawii tun aroyii e mo'on immorde e am peewnoowo kala jokkuЙ—o Peewal Am ngal o majjataa o malkisataake kadi"."
  20,124,"Kala Й—urniiЙ—o gaayi jaЕӢtagol lam, haray pellet, no woodani mo ngurndam Й“illuЙ—am Men mooЙ“oya mo Г‘alnde Darngal ko o bumЙ—o."
  20,125,"O wi'a: "Joomi, ko fii holЙ—um mooЙ“anЙ—aa lam ko mi bumЙ—o, goЕӢЙ—ii mi laatinoke ji'oowo?""
  20,126,"O Daala: "Ko wano nii arnoo e maaЙ—a Aayeeje Amen Й—en njejjituЙ—aa Й—e, ko wano nii kadi hannde njejjitirteЙ—aa"."
  20,127,"Ko wano nii min njoЙ“irta on Й“urtinЙ—o Й—o o gooЕӢЙ—inaa aayeeje Joomi makko Й—en, pellet, ko Lepte Laakara Й—en Й“uri saЙ—tude ko Й—en kadi heddotoo."
  20,128,"Kaa hara Й“annganaali Й“e no foti hewde ko Men halki ado maЙ“Й“e immorde e gire? HeЙ“e yaha e koЙ—ooli maЙ“Й“e, pellet, no e Й—uum aayeeje wonan'de joomiraaЙ“e kakkillaaji Й“en."
  20,129,"Sinno wonaano Daalol aditii ngol immorde ka Joomi maaЙ—a [Lepte] Й—en laatotono duumiiЙ—e e lajal innaangal."
  20,130,"MunГұo e dow ko Й“e kaalata ko, subuhinor jettugol Joomi maaЙ—a ko adii Жҙellitagol naange ngen e ko adii mutugol magge e ka saa'iiji jemma subuhino e ka seraaji Гұallal belajo'o a weltoto."
  20,131,"Wota a yawtin de gite maa Й—e fa'ade k ko Min ndakmini Й—um nooneeji immorde e maЙ“Й“e, cuЙ—aari ngurndam aduna fii yo Min njarribor Й“e e Й—um, Arsike Joomi maaЙ—a on Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude ko on kadi keddotoo."
  20,132,"Yamir Й“eynguure maaЙ—a nden Juulde nden munГұitoraa e Й—um, Min laЙ“ndaaki ma arsike ko Minen arsikaymaa. Battane [moЖҙЖҙe] Й—en kadi wonanii hulooЙ“e Alla Й“en."
  20,133,"ЖҒe mbi'i'i: "Ko hЙ—nno ara e amen Aaya immorde ka Joomi makko?" Enee, hara araani e maЙ“Й“e Й“anngal ko woni ko e Й—eri adani Й—in?"
  20,134,"Sinndo Minen Min kalkirno Й“e Lepte ko adii Й—um, Й“e mbi'atno: "Joomi amen, ko hannoo Nualaa e amen NulaaЙ—o men njokka Aayeeje Maa Й—en, ko adii nde Men koyata men hesra."
  20,135,"Maaku: "Gooto kala [e amen] no habbitii, [onon kadi] habbitee aray anndon ko hommbo woni jom Laawol Pocciingol ngol ko hommbo kadi feewi"."
  21,1,"ЖҒattiimo yimЙ“e Й“e hasboore maЙ“Й“e nde, te kamЙ“e heЙ“e e ndeer welsindaare ko Й“e Й—uurniiЙ“e."
  21,2,"Arataa e maЙ“Й“e waajo immorde ka Joomi maЙ“Й“e ko fuЙ—Й—aa si wonaa Й“e jentike nde kamЙ“e heЙ“e pija."
  21,3,"ЖҒerЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—e ko belsandiiЙ—e Й“e tooГұЙ“e suuЙ—a cowndi(gunndo) [wi'a] enee, h oo wonu si wanaa Й“anndiЕӢke yeru mo'on, kaa on ngarat ee mbilewu hara onon hoЙ—on nji'a (ndaara)?!"
  21,4,"O maaki: "Joomi am no anndi Konngol ngol ka kammu e ka Leydi KaЕӢko ko o Nanoowo gannduЙ—o on."
  21,5,"Ko woni, Й“e mbi'i i'u: "Ko nde jiiЙ“u-jaaЙ“u koyЙ—i, toode, o fekindi nde, ko woni, kaЕӢko ko o jimoowo, awa yo o addan en aayewal wano aranЙ“e Й“en Nuliranoo non"."
  21,6,"GooЕӢЙ—inaani ado maЙ“Й“e immorde e saare Min kalki nde. Enee, hara ko kamЙ“e gooЕӢЙ—ita?"
  21,7,"Min Nulaani ado maaЙ—a si wonaa worЙ“e Min Wahayina e maЙ“Й“e, lanndee yimЙ“e defte Й“e si tawii wonii on anndaa."
  21,8,"Min mbaЙ—aani Й“e Й“alli Й“e Гұaamataa Гұaametee, Й“e laataaki kadi luttinteeЙ“e."
  21,9,"Refti Min nGoonginani Й“e Fodoore nde Min danndi Й“e won'dude e Й“en Й“e Min Muuyi, Min kalki fantinЙ“e Й“en."
  21,10,"GooЕӢЙ—ii Min njippinii fa'ade e mooЙ—on deftere no e ndeer mayre jaЕӢtawol mooЙ—on. Kaa on kakkiltaa."
  21,11,"Heewii ko Min kalki immorde e saare laatinoonde ko tooГұunde Min puЙ—Й—i Й“aawo mayre yimЙ“e goo."
  21,12,"Tuma nde Й“e so'unoo Lepte amen Й—en, tawi kamЙ“e heЙ“e ndoga Й—e."
  21,13,"Wota on ndogu, nduttee fa'ade e ko neeminaЙ—on kon e mu'un e koЙ—anЙ—e mo'on, mbelejo'o on lannditoyte."
  21,14,"ЖҒe mbi'a: "Eeyoo, bone amen, pellet, minen min laatinoke tooГұЙ“e"."
  21,15,"Seerataa ndun noddaandu maЙ“Й“e, haa Men mbaЙ—a Й“e coГұateeri ko Й“e mayЙ“e."
  21,16,"Min tagaani kammu ngun e leydi ndin e ko woni kon hakkunde majji ko Min fijooЙ“e."
  21,17,"Sinndo Min 'a'andino nde Min njogotoo fijindaaru, Min njogitotono Й—um immorde ka Amen si tawii Min laatike waЙ—ooЙ“e."
  21,18,"Ko woni, MiЙ—en mberloo Goonga ka e dow mehre nden ka munca nde, tawa kayre ko nde fuuyoore, no woodani on bone kon ko cifotoЙ—on."
  21,19,"Ko KaЕӢko woodani ko woni ko ka kammuuji e ka leydi Й“en wonЙ“e ka Makko kadi Й“e mawnittaako ga rewugol Mo, Й“e hasrintaaka kadi."
  21,20,"HeЙ“e cubhinoo jemma e Гұaloma Й“e ngaamataa."
  21,21,"Kaa Й“e njogiti deweteeЙ—i ka leydi kannji hiЙ—i immintina [mayЙ“e Й“en]."
  21,22,"Sinndo laatino e majji [kammuuli Й—i e leydi ndi] deweteeЙ—i ko wonaa Alla Й—i bonayno. Senayee wonanii Alla Jom Arsi kin ga koЙ“e cifotoo."
  21,23,"O laЙ“ndetaake ko o gollata ko, kamЙ“e ko Й“e laЙ“nditoyteeЙ“e."
  21,24,"Kaa Й“e njogiti gaanin makko deweteeЙ—i? Maaki: "ngaddee daliili mon on, ko ndee woni jaЕӢta Й“e won'Й—uЙ“e e am e jaЕӢta Й“en adiiЙ“e kam". Ko woni, Й“urЙ“e Й—uuЙ—ude e maЙ“Й“e Й“e anndaa Goonga kan kamЙ“e ko Й“e Й—urniiЙ“e."
  21,25,"Min Nulaani ado maaЙ—a immorde e NulaaЙ—o si wonaa Min mbahayinii e makko; pellet, deweteeЙ—o alaa si wanaa Min ndewee Kam."
  21,26,"ЖҒe mbi'i wi'i: "jurmotooЙ—o O jogitike Й“iЙ—Й—o". Senaare woodanii mo, ko woni, [Й“en ko Й“e] jiyaaЙ“e teddinaaЙ“e."
  21,27,"ЖҒe adortaa mo konngol ngol, kamЙ“e ko Yamiroore makko nden Й“e ngollata."
  21,28,"Homo Anndi ko woni ko yeeso maЙ“Й“e e ko woni ko Й“aawo maЙ“Й“e, Й“e tefanoytaa si wanaa on mo o Weltanii, kamЙ“e immorde e kulol makko ko Й“e jootuЙ“e."
  21,29,"Kala e maЙ“Й“e kadi bi'iЙ—o: "min ko mi deweteeЙ—o gaanin makko". On Й—o Min njoЙ“at mo Jahanna- ma ko wano nii Min njoЙ“irta tooГұooЙ“e Й“en."
  21,30,"Enee, Й“en yedduЙ“e yiaani won'dema kammuuji Й—i e leydi ndi Й—i laatinoke kippondirЙ—i, Min ngudditi Й—i Min mbaЙ—i immorde e ndiyam Й—am kala hu'unde wuuru nde. Kaa Й“e ngonЙ—intaa?"
  21,31,"Min mbaЙ—i aЙ—i ka leydi pelle fii wata nde ooГұodo e maЙ“Й“e, Min mbaЙ—i aЙ—i e mayri Й—ate jaacuЙ—e, mbelejo'o kamЙ“e Й“e peewat."
  21,32,"Min mbaЙ—i kammu ngun kippuЙ—i reenaandi, kamЙ“e ko Й“e Й—urniiЙ“e ga aayeeje amen Й—e."
  21,33,"Ko KaЕӢko woni On TakЙ—o jemma on e Гұalawma on e na'ange nge e lewru ndun kala majji hiЙ—i fubboo(lummboo) ka fuluku."
  21,34,"Min mbaЙ—anaani Й“anndunke ado maaЙ—a luttineede, enee, si a maayii ko kamЙ“e ngoni luttinteeЙ“e Й“en?"
  21,35,"Kala woЕӢkii meedat maayЙ—e nde, Min njarribora on bone on e moЖҙЖҙere nde njarrabagol, ko ka amen kadi nduttotoЙ—on."
  21,36,"Si Й“en yedduЙ“e nji'ii ma, Й“e njogitortaa ma si wanaa jalkitde [Й“e mbi'a] "Enee, hara ko oo woni on jaЕӢtotooЙ—o deweteeЙ—i mo'on Й—in?" hara kamЙ“e ko Й“e yedduЙ“e jantagol jurmotooЙ—o On."
  21,37,"NeЙ—Й—akTagaama immorde e hawjere, aray Mi holla on Aayeeje Am Й—en wata on kawju."
  21,38,"HeЙ“e mbi'a: "Ko honnde tuma woni ndee Fodoore, si tawii ko on gooЕӢЙ—uЙ“e?""
  21,39,"Sinndo Й“en yedduЙ“e ngandiino tuma tawi Й“e ittataa Yiite nge ka je'ece maЙ“Й“e wanaa kadi ka Й“abbe maЙ“Й“e kadi, kamЙ“e Й“e wonaani walloyteeЙ“e."
  21,40,"Ko woni, nge aray e maЙ“Й“e e juhayee nge muga Й“e, hara Й“e kattantaake mdttugol nge, Й“e wonaani kadi neeЙ“noyateeЙ“e."
  21,41,"GooЕӢЙ—ii NulaaЙ“e goo jalkitanooma ado maaЙ—a, jippii e Й“en jalkituЙ“e ko Й“e laatinoo heЙ“e njalkita."
  21,42,"Maaku: "Ko hommbo reenata on jemma e Гұalawma immorde e jurmotooЙ—o On, ko woni, kamЙ“e gah jaЕӢta Joomi maЙ“Й“e ko Й“e Й—urniiЙ“e."
  21,43,"Kaa no woodani Й“e reweteeЙ“e Й“e no dannda Й“e gaanin Amen? ЖҒe kattantaake wallude hay woЕӢkiiji maЙ“Й“e, wanaa kamЙ“e ngoni wondateeЙ“e immorde e Amen."
  21,44,"Ko woni, Min ndakmitii Й“ee e baabiraaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en haa ngurndam Й—am juutani Й“e. Enee, Й“ee nji'aani won'de Menen MeЙ—en ara e leydi ndin Min ustira ndi immorde e seraaji mayri? Kaa ko kamЙ“e ngoni foolooЙ“e Й“en."
  21,45,"Maaku: "Anndu ko mi woni jeertinirde on ko Wahyu on, [kono] paho on nanataa noddaandu ndu, si Й“e njertinaama"."
  21,46,"Mi woЙ—ndii si meemii Й“e seeЙ—a immorde e Lepte Joomi maa Й—en, maa Й“e mbi'a: "Ee-yoo, bone amen pellet, minen min laatinoke tooГұЙ“e"."
  21,47,"Min mbaЙ—a manndikirЙ—e(peesirЙ—e) NuunЙ—al ngal fii Г‘ande Darngal hara woЕӢkii woo toГұiroytaake hay e hu'unde, hay si laatii ko yeru gabbun pamarun Min ngaddat kum Min njonii HasbooЙ“e."
  21,48,"GooЕӢЙ—ii Min ngokkii Muusaa e Haaruuna Serndoore nden e ndayngu e jaЕӢta wonan'de hulooЙ“e Й“en."
  21,49,"ЖҒe hulayЙ“e Joomi maЙ“Й“e ka wirnii hara kamЙ“e immorde e Darngal ngal ko Й“e kuli."
  21,50,"Ndee [AlqurвҖҷaanaare] ko nde JaЕӢta, ko nde barkinaande Min nJippiniinde. Kaa onon ko on yeddatЙ“e nde?"
  21,51,"GoЕӢЙ—ii Min ngkkii Ibraahiima Peewal makko ngal ko adii, Min laatike kadi AnnduЙ“e mo."
  21,52,"Tuma nde o maakannoo baaba makko e yimЙ“e makko Й“e: "Ko holЙ—um woni Й—ii nanndonlaaji nate mahiiЙ—e, Й—in Й—i ufiniЙ—on e [dewal] mu'un?""
  21,53,"ЖҒe mbi'i: "Min taw baabiraaЙ“e amen Й“e no rewde Й—i"."
  21,54,"O maaki: "GooЕӢЙ—ii on laatike onon e baabiraaЙ“e mon Й“e e ndeer majjere Й“anngunde ngonЙ—on"."
  21,55,"ЖҒe mbi'i: "Enee, ko Goonga kan addanЙ—aa min, kaa an ko e fijooЙ“e Й“e njeyaЙ—aa?""
  21,56,"Maaku: "Ko woni, Joomi mo'on ko Jooma kammuuji Й—in e leydi ndin oon TagkЙ—oЙ—i, min komi jeyaaЙ—o e seediiЙ“e Й“e e dow Й—uum"."
  21,57,"Mi wooЙ—ndirii Alla, maa mi fewja fii Й—ii sanamuuji mo'on Й“aawo duЕӢtagolmo'on ko on ruЕӢii Й“e."
  21,58,"O waЙ—i Й—i kunte, si wanaa mawndu majji ndun, mbelejo'o kamЙ“e Й“e nduttoto e mayru."
  21,59,"ЖҒe mbi'i: "Ko hommbo waЙ—i Й—u'un e deweteeЙ—i amen Й—in? Pellet, on ko o jeyaaЙ—o e tooГұЙ“e Й“en."
  21,60,"ЖҒe mb'i: "Min naniino suka no jaЕӢtoo Й—i ko Ibraahiima o wi'etaa"."
  21,61,"ЖҒe mi'i: "ngaddee mo yeeso gite yimЙ“e Й“e, belejo'o Й“e ceedoto"."
  21,62,"ЖҒe mbi'i: "Enee, Ibraahiima ko an waЙ—i Й—u'um Й—oo e deweteeЙ—i amen Й—in?""
  21,63,"O maaki: "Ko woni, ko mawndu majji ndun golle Й—um, lanndeeЙ—i si tawii Й—i laatike hiЙ—i kaala"."
  21,64,"ЖҒe nduttii fa'ade e woЕӢkiiji maЙ“Й“e, Й“e mb'i: "Pellet, ko onon ngoni tooГұЙ“e Й“en"."
  21,65,"Refti Й“e nguggini ko'e maЙ“Й“e Й—en [Й“e mbi'i:] gooЕӢЙ—ii haЙ—a anndi Й—i'i wonaa layatЙ—i."
  21,66,"O maaki: "Enee, on ndewat gaanin Alla kon ko nafataa on hay e hu'unde lorrataa on kadi?""
  21,67,"Bis mo'on e kon ko ndewoton ga Alla. Kaa on kakkiltaa?"
  21,68,"ЖҒe mbi'i: "Sunnee mo, mballee deweteeЙ—i mo'on Й—in, si tawii ko on gollooЙ“e"."
  21,69,"Min Daali: "eeyma yiite, laato Й“uuЙ“ol e kisal e dow Ibraahiima"."
  21,70,"ЖҒe pa'andii mo pewje Min mbaЙ—i Й“e pertube Й“en."
  21,71,"Min danЙ—di mo [Min ndan Й—i kadi] Luutu fa'ade e ndin leydi ndi Min mbarkini e mu'un wonan'de tageefooji Й—in."
  21,72,"Min ngkki mo Ishaaqa e Yaaquuba ka Й“eydugol, kala maЙ“Й“e Min mbaЙ—i [Й“e] moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e."
  21,73,"Min mbaЙ—i Й“e AlmaamiiЙ“e heЙ“e pewna e Yamiroore Amen Min mbahayini fa'ade e maЙ“Й“e gollugol moЖҙЖҙi Й—in e Гұinnugol Julde nden e okkugol Jakka on, Й“e laatinoke ko Й“e ndewat Й“e Min."
  21,74,"E Luutu Min ngokki mo Г‘eeГұal e Ganndal, Min ndanЙ—ni mo immorde e nden Saare nde [yimЙ“e mu'un] laatinoo no golla soЙ“uЙ—i Й—in, pellet, kamЙ“e Й“e laatinoke yimЙ“e bon'Й“e faasiqiiЙ“e."
  21,75,"Min naatni mo e ndeer Yurmeende Amen, pellet, kaЕӢko ko o jeyaaЙ—o e moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e Й“en."
  21,76,"E Nuuhu tuma nde o noddunoo ko adii, Min njaabinani mo kaЕӢko e Й“eynguure makko nden immorde e saЙ—teende mawnde nden."
  21,77,"Moen mballi mo immorde e Й“en yimЙ“e jedduЙ“e Aayeeje Amen Й—en. Pellet, kamЙ“e Й“e laatino yimЙ“e bon'Й“e, Min njooli Й“e, Й“e fof maЙ“Й“e."
  21,78,"E Daawuuda e Sulaymaana tuma nde Й“e Гұaawatnoo fii ngesa ba tuma nde bonnunoo e ndeer mabba dammi yimЙ“e Й“en Men woni seediiЙ“e Гұaawoore maЙ“Й“e nden."
  21,79,"Min 'aamini nde Sulaymaana [Гұaawoore nden] go'oto-kala e maЙ“Й“e Min ngokki Г‘eeГұel e Ganndal Min eelti wond'ude e Daawuuda pelle Й—en heЙ—e cubhinoo e colli Й—in kadi, Min laatike golluЙ“e."
  21,80,"Min nganndini [Daawuuda] moЖҙЖҙinngol mekeГұaaji fii mo'on, fii yo Й—i ndeen on immorde e hare mo'on. Taw si onon ko on jarnooЙ“e?"
  21,81,"[Min eeltani] Sulaymaana henndu ndu ko ndu bippooru hindu doga e yamiroore makko, fa'ade e ndin leydi ndi Min mbarki e mu'un. Min laatike AnnduЙ“e kala hu'unde."
  21,82,"No e Seytanuuji Й—in, Й—in Й—i no mutana mo, Й—i ngolla golle ga Й—um. Min laatanike Й—i ReenooЙ“e."
  21,83,"[JaЕӢto kadi fii] Ayyuuba tuma nde o noddunoo Joomi makko, [O maaki:] "Min dey memii kam lorra kan, ko aan woni Й“uroowo Yurmeede yurmtooЙ“e Й“en"."
  21,84,"Min njaabinani mo Min kuГұci ko heЙ“i mo kon immorde e lorra, Min ngkkiti mo Й“eynguure makko nden e yeru maЙ“Й“e wond'ude e maЙ“Й“e kadi, Й—um ko Yurmeende immorde ka amen e waaju wona nde rewooЙ“e Й“en."
  21,85,"[JaЕӢto kadi fii] Ismaa'iila e Idriisa e Jalkifli, Й“en fow ko e muГұЙ“e Й“en Й“e njeyaa."
  21,86,"Min naadi Й“e e ndeer Yurmeende Amen nden, pellet, kamЙ“e ko Й“e jeyaaЙ“e e moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e Й“een."
  21,87,"[JaЕӢto kadi fii] Jannuuni tuma nde o yahnoo ko o tikkuЙ—o o sikki won'de Min njarribtaaka e hoore makko, o noddi ka niЙ“e; "Won'de deweteeЙ—o alaa si wanaa An Senaare wonanii Ma, min dey mi laatike jeyaaЙ—o e tooГұuЙ“e Й“en"."
  21,88,"Min njaabinani mo, Min ndaЙ—ndi mo immorde e suno ngo, ko wano nii kadi Min danndirta gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“en."
  21,89,"[JaЕӢto kadi fii] fii Jakariyaa tuma nde o noddunoo Joomo makko, [o maaki:] Jooma, wota A Й—alam bajjo, ko aan woni ЖҒurЙ—o MoЖҙЖҙude ronooЙ“e Й“en."
  21,90,"Min njaabinani mo, Min ngokki mo Yahyaa, Min moЖҙЖҙinani mo sonnaajo makko on, pellet, kamЙ“e Й“e laatinoke hiЙ“e yaccoo e [gollugol] moЖҙЖҙi Й—in hiЙ“e nodda Min ka reerЙ—eende e kulol Й“e laatinoke yannkinaniiЙ“e Min."
  21,91,"[JaЕӢto kadi fii] oya [cuddiiЙ—o] deennooЙ—o farju makko on Min wutti e makko immorde e Fittaandu amen, Min mbaЙ—i mo kaЕӢko e geЙ—aljo makko on Ma'ande wona nde winndere nden."
  21,92,"Pellet, Й—ee mofte mo'on ko mofte go'ote, ko Min ngoni Joomi mo'on Rewee Lam."
  21,93,"ЖҒe taЖҙi fiyaake maЙ“Й“e on hakkunde maЙ“Й“e, Й“e fof ko fa'ade ka am Й“e nduttoytoo."
  21,94,"Kala golluЙ—o immorde e moЖҙЖҙuЙ—i Й—in hara kaЕӢko ko o gooЕӢЙ—inЙ—o, dullugol alaa fii golle makko Й—en, pellet, Minen Min mbinndanay mo."
  21,95,"No harmani saare nde Mon kalki Й—um, won'de kamЙ“e Й“e mduttataako [ton]."
  21,96,"Haa si udditoyaama Ya'ajuuja e Ma'ajuuja, hara kamЙ“e immorde e kala naЙ—el heЙ“e cortoo."
  21,97,"Fodoore Goongaare nde Й“adike, tawi kayre puttini giiЙ—e Й“en yedduЙ“e, [Й“e mbi'a:] "Eeyoo bone amen, gooЕӢЙ—ii min laatinoke e nder welsindaare immorde e Й—u'um, ko woni, men laatike tooГұЙ“e."
  21,98,"Pellet, onon e ko ndewoton kon ga Alla, ko on doccote Jahannama. Onon, ko on joloyayЙ“e e magge."
  21,99,"Sinndo Й“ee laatinoke reweteeЙ“e Й“e njolataano e magge. ЖҒe fof maЙ“Й“e ko Й“e luttinteeЙ“e e ndeer magge."
  21,100,"No woodani Й“e e ndeer magge haraango, kamЙ“e Й“e nanataa ndeer ton."
  21,101,"Pellet, Й“een Й“e moЖҙЖҙi Й—i adanii Й—um immorde ka amen Й“een Й—oon ko Й“e woЙ—Й—intinteeЙ“e ga magge."
  21,102,"ЖҒe nanoytaa wuuЙ—aango magge kamЙ“e heЙ“e e ndeer ko woЕӢkiiji maЙ“Й“e lokaa(wooЙ—a) ko, ko Й“e duumotooЙ“e."
  21,103,"SuninoytaaЙ“e Й—enЖҙere mawnde nde, Maleykaaji Й“en no jaЙ“Й“ooЙ“e [Й“e mbia:] "Ko ndee woni Г‘alaande mo'on, nden nde laatinoЙ—on hoЙ—on podee"."
  21,104,"Г‘ande Min taggoyta kammu ngun wano taggugol Й—erol defte. Ko wano Min puЙ—Й—ori non ka arannde tagoore Min nduttirta nde, [Й—um] ko Fodoore e dow amen, pellet, Minen Min laatike gollooЙ“e."
  21,105,"GooЕӢЙ—ii Min mbinndiino ka Jabuura Й“aawo Alluwal deenangal ngal, pellet, leydi ndin ko jeyaaЙ“e Am moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e Й“en ndonoyta ndi."
  21,106,"Pellet,no e Й—uum [ko jaЕӢtaa Й—oo] jottingol wonan'de yimЙ“e rewooЙ“e Й“en."
  21,107,"Min Nuliraani ma si wonaa Yurmeende wonan'de winndire nde."
  21,108,"Maaku: "Anndu ko Wahayinaa e am, wonan'dema DeweteeЙ—o mon On ko O DeweteeЙ—o Gooto. Enee, hara onon ko on jebbiliiЙ“e?"."
  21,109,"Si tawii Й“e mduЕӢtiima, maaku: "Mi anndinii on e dow potondiral, pellet, mi anndaa si no Й“adii maa Й—um si no woЙ—Й—i ko ko podaЙ—on"."
  21,110,"Pellet, KaЕӢko himo Anndi ko feeГұi ko e konngol ngol, homo Anndi kadi ko cuuЙ—oton."
  21,111,"Mi anndaa non, mbelejo'o Й—uum ko jarrabuyee mo'on, e dakamme haa e dummunne."
  21,112,"Maaku: "Jooma, Г‘aawir Goonga kan ko Joomi amen jurmotooЙ—o o woni ballitorteeЙ—o On e dow ko cifotoЙ—on"."
  22,1,"Eey monyo yimЙ“e, kulee Joomi mo'on, pellet, dillannde Darnga ngo ko hu'unde mawnde."
  22,2,"Г‘ande nji'oton ngal, njejjitoyay kala muyninoowo ko o muyninaynoo ko, fukka kala cowiiЙ—o ko o sowiinoo kon, a yi'at yimЙ“e Й“en no manndili, hara kamЙ“e Й“e manndiaa, kono Lepte Alla Й—en ko saЙ—tuЙ—e."
  22,3,"No e yimЙ“e Й“e on mo no wennja e fii Alla ko aldaa e ganndal, o jokka kala Seytaane canndallo."
  22,4,"Winndaama e hoore-makko won'de pellet, kala belduЙ—o e makko pellet, o majjinat mo, o Й—owa mo haa ka Lepte Sa'iiri."
  22,5,"Ey mon yimЙ“e, si tawii on e cikkatiima immorde e immital ngal, pellet, Minen Min Tagii on immorde e mbullaari refti e toЙ“Й“ere maniiyu, refti e heЙ—Й—ere refti e husre timmunde tagoore e nde wonaa timmunde tagoore fii yo Min Й“annginan on, MiЙ—en Г‘iiЙ“ina ka renngaaji ko Min Muuyi kon haa e happu innaaЙ—o, refti Min njaltini on ko on boobooЙ“e, refti fii yo on njotto sagatalaaku mo'on no e mo'on Й“en Й“e no maaya no e mo'on kadi Й“en Й“e no nduttee fa'ade ka Й“uri ja'asde e nguurndam Й—am fii wota Й“e nganndu Й“aawo ganndal hay e hu'unde. A yi'at leydi ndin ko yo'orundi si Min njippinii e dow mayri ndiyam Й—an ndi dilla ndi Жҙura ndi fuЙ—ina immorde e kala noone wooЙ—uЙ—o."
  22,6,"ЖҠum, ko tawde pellet, Alla ko KaЕӢko woni Goonga kan, pellet, O wurtinat maayЙ“e Й“en, tawde pellet, ko O kattanЙ—o e dow kala hu'unde."
  22,7,"Pellet, Darngal ngal ko aray ngal sikke alaa e maggal, won'de pellet, Alla immintinay Й“en won'Й“e ka genaale."
  22,8,"No e yimЙ“e Й“en on mo no weeГұdaa e fii Alla ko aldaa e ganndal wonaa peewal wonaa deftere nurЙ—unde(jalbunde)."
  22,9,"HkfЙ—o balaaji mu'un [mawnintiniiЙ—o] fii yo o majjin gah Laawol Alla ngol, no woodani mo ka aduna koyeere Min meeЙ—inoyay mo kadi Г‘ande Darngal Lepte cumoowe ngen."
  22,10,"ЖҠum ko sabu ko juuЙ—e maaЙ—a Й—en ngardini kon. E won'de pellet, Alla wonaani TooГұoowo jeyaaЙ“e Й“en."
  22,11,"No e yimЙ“e Й“en on mo no rewa Alla e dow selindaare; si moЖҙЖҙere heЙ“ii mo o tabitira sabu Й—uum si jarrabuyee kadi heЙ“ii mo o waylitoo e ye'eso makko, o hayrii aduna on e La'akara on ko Й—um tigi woni hayrere Й“anngunde nden."
  22,12,"Homo rewa gah Alla ko lorrataa mo e ko nafataa mo kadi. ЖҠuum [ko jaЕӢtaa Й—oo], ko Й—um woni majjere woЙ—Й—unde nden."
  22,13,"Homo rewa on mo lorra mum no Й“uri Й“adaade diini nafa mum kan, bonii welddiЙ—o bonii kadi wuuridaaЙ—o."
  22,14,"Pellet, Alla homoo naatna Й“en gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“e ngolli moЖҙЖҙi Й—in Aljannaaji no ila sengo ley majji caatlii Й—i, pellet, Alla homo waЙ—a ko o faandii ko."
  22,15,"On gonЙ—o no sikka won'de Alla wallataa mo ka aduna e ka La'akara; yo o fortu Й“oggol fa'ade ka kammu refti o taЖҙa ngol yo o ndaaru taw si pewje makko Й—en ittay ko tikkani ko."
  22,16,"Ko wano nii Min nJippiniri Й—e Aayeeje Й“annguЙ—e. Pellet, Alla homo Feewna on Mo o muuyii."
  22,17,"Pellet, Й“en gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e e Й“en YahuudinkooЙ“e e Saabi'iyaЕӢkooЙ“e e AnnasaaraЕӢkooЙ“e e MajuusiЕӢkooЙ“e e Й“en sirkooЙ“e, pellet, Alla O ceerndoowo hakkunde maЙ“Й“e Г‘ande Darngal. Pellet, Alla e dow kala hu'unde ko O SeediiЙ—o."
  22,18,"Enee a yi'aali, won'dema Alla no sujjan'de Mo Й“e won'Й“e ka kammuuji e Й“e won'Й“e ka leydi, na'ange nge kadi e lewru ndun e koode Й—en e pelle Й—en e leЙ—Й—e Й—en e daabeeji Й—in e ko Й—uuЙ—i immorde e yimЙ“e Й“en, ko Й—uuЙ—i kadi wajibike e mu'un Lepte Й—en. Kala mo Alla hoyni alanaa mo teddinoowo, pellet Alla homo golla ko o muuyi kon."
  22,19,"ЖҒee Й—oo Й—iЙ—o ko weeГұdondirЙ“e, Й“e mbeГұdondirii fii Joomi maЙ“Й“e Й“en yedduЙ“e non, taЖҙanoyte Й“e comci immorde e Yiite fatuЙ—am yuppee ka dow ko'e maЙ“Й“e."
  22,20,"HaЙ—am honciniree(tayniree) ko woni kon ka deedi maЙ“Й“e e guri Й—in kadi."
  22,21,"No woodani Й“oonЙ—e e jamЙ—e."
  22,22,"Tuma kala Й“e cokli jaltugol ndeer ton immorde e suno, Й“e nduttee e ndeer magge, [Й“e mbiiвҖҷanee:] meeЙ—ee Lepte cumoowe nge."
  22,23,"Pellet, Alla naatna Й“en gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“e ngolle moЖҙЖҙi Й—in Aljannaaji no ila e ley majji caatЙ—lii Й—in, Й“e cuЙ—iree ndeer ton immorde jawe kanЕӢe e lu'ulu'uuje koltu maЙ“Й“e on nder ton ko hariire."
  22,24,"ЖҒe peewnaama fa'ade e ko laaЙ“i immorde e konngol ngol, Й“e peewnaa kadi fa'ade e Laawol jettiniingol ngol."
  22,25,"Pellet, Й“een yedduЙ“e heЙ“e faddaade gah Laawol Alla ngol e Juulirde Horminnde nden, nden nde Min mbaЙ—ani Й—um yimЙ“e Й“en, no fota ter ГұiiЙ“uЙ—o on e mayre e liigotooЙ—o on. Kala paalaaЙ—o ooГұorde e mayre tooГұe, Min meeЙ—inat mo immorde e Lepte mu'usЙ—e."
  22,26,"E tuma nde Min nJippinnoo Ibraahiima nokku Suudu ndun, [Min Daali:] Wota a kafidu e Am hay e hu'unde, laЙ“Й“in Suudu Am ndun fii wanngotooЙ“e Й“en e darotooЙ“e Й“en [juula] e rukЖҙooЙ“e cujja Й“en."
  22,27,"Noddin e yimЙ“e Й“en fii Hajju ngun, Й“e ngarat e maaЙ—a ko Й“e seppooЙ“e e dow kala Й—ehiimba reedu, Й“e ngarat immorde e kala laawol goЙ—Й—ungol."
  22,28,"Fii yo Й“e seedo nafoore maЙ“Й“e, Й“e njaЕӢtoo Innde Alla e ndeer ГұalЙ—i ganndaaЙ—i e dow ko o arsiki Й“e kon immorde e muumi neemoraaЙ—i, Гұaamee e majji, Гұamminon kadi baaso Й“illiiЙ—o on."
  22,29,"Refti yo Й“e ittu tuundi maЙ“Й“e ndi, yo Й“e kuuЙ“nu takke maЙ“Й“e Й—en, yo Й“e mbanngo Suudu rimЙ—inaa- ndu ndu."
  22,30,"ЖҠuum [ko njamiraЙ—on], kala mawninЙ—o Hurumji Alla Й—i tawat Й—uum ko moЖҙЖҙere makko ka Joomi makko. Daginanaama on neemoraaЙ—i Й—in, si wonaa kon ko janngaa e taweede mo'on, ngoЙ—Й—itee coЙ“Й—ii Й—i immorde e sanamuuji, ngoЙ—Й—itoЙ—on kadi konngol fenaande ngol."
  22,31,"NewaniiЙ“e Alla Й“e ngonaani sirkanooЙ“e Mo, kala sirkanЙ—o Alla no wa'ita wa si o pukkiiЙ—o immorde ka kammu sonndu biftoo mo ma henndu ruuyida e makko [liЙ“oya] e nokkure woЙ—Й—unde."
  22,32,"ЖҠuum [ko jaЕӢtaa Й—oo hollii] kala mawninЙ—o Ma'andeeji Alla Й—in, pellet Й—um, ko e kulol Й“erЙ—e Й—en jeyaa."
  22,33,"No woodani on e majji nafaaji haa e dummunne innaaЙ—o, refti nokku majji on ko ka cuudu Ndimuru."
  22,34,"Min mbaЙ—anii kala mofte laawol fii yo Й“e njaЕӢto Innde Alla e dow ko O arsiki Й“e kon immorde e muumi neemoraaЙ—i. DeweteeЙ—o mon on ko DeweteeЙ—o Gooto ko KaЕӢko njebbilatoЙ—on, weltinir Й—oftiiЙ“e Й“en."
  22,35,"ЖҒeen [tawЙ“e] si Alla jaЕӢtaama Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en kulay, e muГұГұiiЙ“e Й“en e dow kon ko heЙ“i Й“e e ГұinnooЙ“e Julde nden heЙ“e nafka goЙ—Й—um e ko Min arsiki Й“e kon."
  22,36,"E gelooЙ“i [fayЙ—i] Й—in Min mbaЙ—anii on Й—i jeyaaЙ—um e Ma'andeeji Alla no woodani on e majji moЖҙЖҙere, njaЕӢtee Innde Alla e dow majji ko Й—i saffiniiЙ—i si becce majji Й—en yanii Гұaamee immorde e majji Гұamminon kadi yonndiniiЙ—o e weeЙ“itotooЙ—o, ko wano nii, Min eeltirani on Й—i mbelajo'o onon on j Njaarnay."
  22,37,"Hewtoytaa Alla tebbuuli majji wonaa ЖҙiiЖҙe majji kadi, kono heewtoy mo kulol ngol immorde e mo'on. Ko wano nii O eeltani on Й—i fii yo on mawni Alla e dow ko o feewni on ko, weltin moЖҙЖҙinЙ“e Й“en."
  22,38,"Pellet, Alla O solnanay(duГұanat) Й“een gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e, pellet, Alla o yiЙ—aa kala kodoowo keewЙ—o jeddi."
  22,39,"DuЕӢanaama Й“een wonaaЙ“e haЙ“eede [joЙ“tagol] sabu kamЙ“e ko Й“e tooГұaaЙ“e, pellet, Alla ko o kattanЙ—o e dow wallude Й“e."
  22,40,"ЖҒeen yaltinaaЙ“e ka galleeji mu'en ko aldaa e goo- nga si wonaa fii tun Й“e wi'ii: "Joomi amen ko Alla". Sinndo wonaano Alla duГұirde yimЙ“e Й“e yoga e maЙ“Й“e yoga, yirbinteno dewirЙ—i ruhbaaniyankooЙ“e Й“en e dewirЙ—i Annasaara en e dewirЙ—i Alyahuuda en e JuulirЙ—e Й—e Innde Alla jaЕӢtetee e ndeer mu'un ko heewi. ma Alla wallu Й“en wallooЙ“e mo, pellet, Alla ko o cemmbuЙ—o TedduЙ—o."
  22,41,"ЖҒeen tawЙ“e si Min newinanii Й“e ka leydi Й“e ГұiiЙ“nat Juulde nde Й“e totta askaal o Й“e njamira ko moЖҙЖҙi ko Й“e kaЙ—a ko boni ko Ko Alla woodani Й“attane fiyakuuji Й—i."
  22,42,"Si Й“e njennii ma, gooЕӢЙ—ii yeddiino ado maЙ“Й“e yimЙ“e Nuuhu Й“e e AadiЕӢkooЙ“e Й“e e SamuudiЕӢkooЙ“e Й“e."
  22,43,"E yimЙ“e Ibraahiima Й“e e yimЙ“e Luutu Й“e."
  22,44,"E yimЙ“e Madyana Й“e Muusaa kadi fennaama, Mi neeЙ“nani yedduЙ“e Й“en refti Mi nanngi Й“e, ko honno yagginngol Am ngol wonirnoo?"
  22,45,"No foti hewde e ce'e Й—ee Min kalki Й—um tawi ko nde tooГұnde, hara hende ngajjii e kippudiiji majje, e woyndu jirbundu e kuЙ“eeje toowЙ—ee [eggaande]."
  22,46,"Enee, hara Й“ee njhaani ka leydi sakko laatanooЙ“e Й“erЙ—e Й“e haqqilira Й—e, ma noppi Й“e nanira Й—i? Pellet, [ko woni kon] wonaa gite Й—e mbumi, kono ko Й“erЙ—e gonЙ—e Й—e e nder becce Й—en mbumi."
  22,47,"HeЙ“e Й—aЙ“Й“ire yaccinaneede Lepte Й—e, [e Й—uum le] Alla luutndataako fodoore makko nde. Pellet Гұallal ka Joomi maaЙ—a ko wano duuЙ“i wuluure no limorton non."
  22,48,"No foti heewde e saare nde min neeЙ“nani Й—um hara kayre ko nde tooГұude, refti Mi nannginde ko fa'ade ka Am woni ruttorde nden."
  22,49,"Maaku: "eymon yo yimЙ“e, nganndee min ko mi jeertinoowo on Й“annguЙ—o"."
  22,50,"ЖҒeen gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“e ngolli moЖҙЖҙi Й—in no woodani Й“e haforanal e arsike tedduЙ—o."
  22,51,"ЖҒeen yacciiЙ“e [fii bonnugol] e aayeeje amen Й—en, Й“e ndoЕӢkintaa [Min] ko Й“en Й—on woni yimЙ“e Jahiimaawe ngen."
  22,52,"Min Nulaani ado maaЙ—a immorde e NulaaЙ—o wonaa kadi Annabaajo si wonaa si o janngii Seytaane wernoto e ndeer njangin makko kin. Alla itta ko Seytaane wernii kon, refti Alla tabintina aayeeje makko Й—en. Alla ko O ganndo Г‘eeГұЙ—o."
  22,53,"Fii yo o waЙ—uko Seytaane wernotoo ko njarraboye wonan'de Й“een Й“e nawnaare woni ka Й“erЙ—e mu'uen Й“e Й“erЙ—e mu'uen njo'ori Й“en. Pellet, tooГұooЙ“e Й“en Й“e wonii e luural goЙ—Й—ungal."
  22,54,"Fii yo Й“een okkaaЙ“e Ganndal ngal nganndu pellet, ko [Alqur'aanaare nden woni] Goonga kan immorde ka Joomi maaЙ—a Й“e gooЕӢЙ—ina nde, Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en yankinanoo Й—um. Pellet Alla Feewnat Й“en gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e fa'ade e Laawol Pocciingol."
  22,55,"ЖҒeen yedduЙ“e ceerataa heЙ“e e nder sikke [fii Alqur'aana] haa Darngal ngal ara e maЙ“Й“e e juhayee maa Й—um ara e maЙ“Й“e Lepte Г‘alaande saЙ—tunde."
  22,56,"Laamu ngu nden Г‘ande ko Alla heeranii O Г‘aawoyat hakkunde maЙ“Й“e, Й“en gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“e ngolli ko moЖҙЖҙi Й—in heЙ“e e ndeer Aljannaaji NeemiiЙ—i."
  22,57,"ЖҒeen yedduЙ“e, Й“e penni kadi aayeeje amen Й—en, Й“en Й—on no woodani Й“e lepte koynooje."
  22,58,"ЖҒeen ferЙ“e e Laawol Alla refti Й“e waraa maa Й—um Й“e maayi Alla arsikoyay Й“e arsike moЖҙЖҙo. Pellet, Alla ko KaЕӢko woni Й“uri MoЖҙЖҙude ArsikooЙ“e."
  22,59,"Ma O naatnoyЙ“e naatirgal ngal Й“e welaa Й—um. Pellet, Alla ko O gannduЙ—o MuГұГұiiЙ—o."
  22,60,"ЖҠuum [ko jaЕӢtaa Й—oo], kala leptuЙ—o yeru ko o leptaa ko, refti bewaa e hoore-makko ma Alla wallu mo. Pellet, Alla ko O YaafotooЙ—o cuhroowo."
  22,61,"ЖҠuum [ko jaЕӢtaa Й—oo], ko fii pellet, Alla hono naatna jemma on e ndeer Гұalorma on, hiMo naada kadi Гұalawma on e ndeer jemma on. Pellet, Alla ko o Nanoowo ji'oowo."
  22,62,"ЖҠuum [ko jaЕӢtaa Й—oo], ko fii pellet, Alla ko KaЕӢko woni Goonga kan pellet, kon ko Й“e noddata gaanin makko ko Й—uum woni meere nden. Pellet, ko KaЕӢko woni ToowuЙ—o mawnuЙ—o on.u"
  22,63,"Enee, a tinaani won'dema Alla o jippinii ndiyam immorde ka kammuuji, leydi ndin wonti hecciЙ—undi? Pellet, Alla ko oNewiiЙ—o kumpitiiЙ—o."
  22,64,"Ko KaЕӢko woodani ko woni kon ka kammuuji e ka leydi. Pellet, Alla ko KaЕӢko woni Galo jettiniiЙ—o on."
  22,65,"Enee, a tinaani wonan'dema Alla eeltani on ko woni kon ka leydi, laaЙ—e Й—en no ndogira ka maaje Yamaruyee makko on, homo jogitii kammu ngun fii wata ngu yanu e hoore leydi ndin si wonaa e duЕӢayee mkko. Pellet, Alla ko o newaniiЙ—o yimЙ“e Й“en jurmotooЙ—o Й—o [Й“e]."
  22,66,"Ko KaЕӢko woni on guurnuЙ—o on refiti o wara on refti o wurnitoya on. Pellet neЙ—Й—aЕӢke on ko o keewЙ—o jeddi."
  22,67,"Min mbaЙ—anii kala mofte laawol ngol Й“e ndewata e mu'un, wata Й“e pooЙ—ondir e maaЙ—a e fiyaake on, noddu fa'ade ka Joomi maaЙ—a. Pellet, an haЙ—a e hoore Laawol Pocciingol."
  22,68,"Si Й“e mbeГұdi ma, Maaku: "Ko Alla woni gannduЙ—o ko ngolloton kon"."
  22,69,"Alla Г‘aawat hakkunde mo'on Г‘ande Darngal fii kon ko luutondirton fii mu'um."
  22,70,"Enee, a anndaani won'dema Alla homo Anndi ko woni kon ka kammu e ka leydi, pellet, Й—uum no e ndery Deftere. Pellet, Й—um [ko jaЕӢtaa Й—oo] no newanii Alla."
  22,71,"HeЙ“e ndewa ga Alla kon ko Dalil jippinaaka e fii mu'um, e kon ko ganndal alanaa Й“e e mu'um. Alanaa tooГұooЙ“e Й“en balloowo."
  22,72,"Si jannganaama Й“e aayeeje amen Й—een Й“annguЙ—e a ngandat e je'ece Й“en yedduЙ“e mettinaare heЙ“e Й—eЙ“a yanude e Й“en jannganayЙ“e Й“e aayeeje amen Й—en. Maaku: "Yo mi habru on ko Й“uri bon'de e Й—um mooЙ—on [ko jaЕӢtanaЙ—on ko] ko Yiite ngen Alla fodii nge Й“een yedduЙ“e bonii ruttorde."
  22,73,"Eey mon yimЙ“e, yeru fiyaama keЙ—tee mo, pellet Й“een Й“e noddoton gaAlla, Й“e tagata hay mbu'ubu, hay sinndo Й“e mooЙ“ondiriino fii Й—um. Si coongil(mbuubu)ngil jattii Й“e goЙ—Й—um Й“e kattantaake jaЙ“tugol ngil Й—um. ЖҠaЙ“Й“uЙ—o on e Й—aЙ“Й“aaЙ—o on fof no lo'i."
  22,74,"ЖҒe mawniniraani Alla no O haani Mawninirde non. Pellet, Alla ko cemmbuЙ—o TedduЙ—o."
  22,75,"Alla no suЙ“oo immorde e Maleykaaji Й—i NulaaЙ“e e yimЙ“e Й“en kadi. Pellet, Alla ko O Nanoowo ji'oowo."
  22,76,"Homo Anndi ko woni kon yeeso maЙ“Й“e e ko woni ko Й“aawo maЙ“Й“e, ko faade ka Alla fiyakuuji Й—in ruttetee."
  22,77,"Eey mon yo Й“en gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e, ndukЖҙee cujjon ndewon Joomi mo'on, ngollon ko moЖҙЖҙi kon mbelejo'o onon on maloyte."
  22,78,"MbaЙ—ee Jihaadi fii Alla no Jihaadi haaniri non, KaЕӢko OSuЙ“iima on o mbaЙ—anaani on Й“itteende ka nder diina, diina baaba mooЙ—on Ibraahiima ko KaЕӢko inni on juulЙ“e ko adii [ndee Alqur'aanaare] e nder mayre kadi, fii yo NulaaЙ—o on laato seedo e hoore-mo'on onon kadi ngonon seeditoytooЙ“e e hoore yimЙ“e Й“e. Г‘iiЙ“nee e Juulde nden totton askal on njogitee Alla, ko KaЕӢko woni GiЙ—o mooЙ—on moЖҙЖҙii giЙ—o moЖҙЖҙii balloowo on."
  23,1,"GooЕӢЙ—ii malaama gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“en."
  23,2,"ЖҒeen hulooЙ“e ka ndeer Juulde maЙ“Й“e koЙ“e yankiniiЙ“e."
  23,3,"E Й“een Й—urniiЙ“e ga rayrayti( bolle mehre)."
  23,4,"E Й“een ittooЙ“e askal on."
  23,5,"E Й“een reenЙ“e farjuuji maЙ“Й“e Й—i."
  23,6,"Si wonaa e dow suddiiЙ“e maЙ“Й“e ma Й“e Гұaame maЙ“Й“e Й—e njeyi(horbe), haray kamЙ“e Й“e ngonaa feleteeЙ“e."
  23,7,"OOn mo Й—aЙ“Й“i Й“aawo Й—um, haray ko Й“een ngoni jaggitooЙ“e Й“en."
  23,8,"E Й“een aynuЙ“e koolaaje maЙ“Й“e e aadiiji maЙ“Й“e Й—i."
  23,9,"E Й“een Й“e kaГұun koЙ“e reenЙ“e e dow Juulde maЙ“Й“e Й—en."
  23,10,"ЖҒee [siforЙ“e Й—ii sifaaji Й—oo] ko kamЙ“e ngoni ronooЙ“e Й“en."
  23,11,"ЖҒeen ronoyatЙ“e Firdawsi on kamЙ“e ko Й“e duumotooЙ“e e ndeer makko."
  23,12,"GooЕӢЙ—ii Min tagii neЙ—Й—aЕӢke on immorde e lasili loopal."
  23,13,"Refti Min mbaЙ—i mo toЙ“Й“ere [maniiyu] e ndeer ГұiiЙ“irde kuЙ“indiinde."
  23,14,"Refti Min Tagi toЙ“Й“ere nde heЙ—Й—ere, Min Tagi heЙ—Й—ere nden huyre, Min Tagi huyre nde Жҙi'e, Min koltini Жҙi'e Й—eteewu. Refti Min puЙ—Й—anii mo Tagoore woo, barkanii Alla MoЖҙЖҙo TakЙ—o."
  23,15,"Refti onon Й“aawo Й—uum ko on maayooЙ“e."
  23,16,"Refti pellet, onon Г‘ande Darngal on imminoyte."
  23,17,"GooЕӢЙ—ii Min Tagii dow mooЙ—on Й—ati jeeЙ—iЙ—i, Min ngonaani kadi welsindiiЙ“e gaayi tagoore nde."
  23,18,"Min njippini immorde ka kammu ndiyam e emmbere [haaju tagoore nde], Min ndewni Й—am ka leydi, pellet, Minen ko Nden HattanЙ“e e dow naЙ“ugol Й—am."
  23,19,"Min puЙ—Й—ani on sabu majjam gese immorde e tamarooje e inabuuje, no woodani on ndeer ton dimЙ—e Й—uuЙ—uЙ—e ko e majje Гұaamoton."
  23,20,"E leggal ngal no yalta immorde to Tuuri Siinaa hangal fuЙ—ina guЖҙam [nebban wujeteeЙ—am] e li'am [maafirЙ—am] wonan'de ГұaamooЙ“e."
  23,21,"Pellet, no woodani on e neemoraaЙ—i Й—i tasakuyee, MiЙ—en njarna on boЙ—Й—um e ko woni kon ka deedi majji, no woodani on e majji nafooje keewЙ—e, ko immorde e majji kadi Гұaamoton."
  23,22,"Ko e hoore-majji e hoore laaЙ—e Й—e ndoonndeteЙ—on."
  23,23,"GooЕӢЙ—ii Min Nulii Nuuhu e yimЙ“e makko Й“e o maaki : eey mon yo yimЙ“e am, ndewee Alla. DeweteeЙ—o alanaa on ko woori mo. Enee, on kulatah?"."
  23,24,"HooreeЙ“e mbatu ngun mbii'ani Й“en yedduЙ“e immorde e yimЙ“e makko Й“en: "Oo wonaani si ko o Й“anndiЕӢke yeru mo'on homo faalaa nde o Й“urnotoo e dow mooЙ—on. Sinndo Alla muuyino O jippinayno Malaa'ikaaji, min naniraani Й—um baabiraaЙ“e amen aranЙ“e Й“en"."
  23,25,"KaЕӢko o wonaani si wonaa ko o gorko mo jinna woni e mu'um, habbitee mo tun haa seeЙ—a."
  23,26,"O maaki: "Joom am, wallam e ko Й“e njennimi kon"."
  23,27,"Min wahayini fa'ade e makko yo o lesu laana kan e dennka amen e Wahayu Amen, si Yamiroore amen nden arii huЙ“Й“inirde nden pullitike [ndiyam] naatu e ndeer makka immorde e kala nooneeji Й—in Й—iЙ—i-Й—iЙ—i. E koreeji ma, si wonaa Й“een konngol ngol aditii e mu'um, wata a haaldu e am fii Й“en tooГұuЙ“e, pellet, kamЙ“e ko Й“e yooleteeЙ“e."
  23,28,"Si a fotondirii aan e Й“een won'Й—uЙ“e e maaЙ—a e dow laana kan, haray maaku: "Yettoore ndeen ko Alla woodani, On dannduЙ—o Min immorde e yimЙ“e tooГұooЙ“e Й“en"."
  23,29,"Maaku: "Joomam, jippinam e jipporde barkinaande ko Aan woni moЖҙЖҙo Jippinoowo"."
  23,30,"Pellet, no e ndeer Й—um [ko jaЕӢtaa Й—oo] sayeeje, haysi men laatike ko min njarribotooЙ“e."
  23,31,"Refti Min 'uЙ—Й—i Й“aawo maЙ“Й“e yiirde woЙ“Й“e goo."
  23,32,"Min Nulii e maЙ“Й“e NulaaЙ—o jeyaaЙ—o e maЙ“Й“e, Й—um woni ndewee Alla, dewateeЙ—o on ko woori Mo. E on kulatah [Mo]?!"."
  23,33,"Batu e yimЙ“e makko Й“en yedduЙ“e Й“e penni kawroygol e Laakara on, Min neemini Й“e ka ngurdam aduna wi*i: "Oo wonaani si wonaa Й“annduЕӢke yeru mooЙ—on homo Гұaama ko Гұaamoton kon homo yara kadi ko njaroton kon"."
  23,34,"Mi wooЙ—ndii si on Й—oftike Й“annduЕӢke yeru mo'on, pellet, onon on tuma ko on hayruЙ“e(pertube)."
  23,35,"Enee, o 'oton wonan'dema onon si on maayii on laatike mbullaari e Жҙi'e, wonan'dema onon ko on yaltinoyteeЙ“e?!"
  23,36,"WoЙ—ndii woori kon ko podaЙ—on."
  23,37,"[ЖҒe mbi'i:] "ЖҠum wonaani si wonaa nguurdam amen aduna, miЙ—en maaya min nguura kadi, minen min ngnaani immintinoyteeЙ“e"."
  23,38,"KaЕӢko o wonaani si wonaa ko o gorko pekindiiЙ—o fenaande fawi e Alla, minen non, min mgnaami gooЕӢЙ—inatЙ“e mo."
  23,39,"O maaki: "Joom am, wallam e ko Й“e njeddii kam kon"."
  23,40,"O Daali: "SeeЙ—anii tan, Mi wooЙ—ndii Й“e ngontat nimsuЙ“e"."
  23,41,"Haacaango ngon nanngi Й“e e Goonga, Min mbaЙ—i Й“e duuГұo, halkaare wonanii yimЙ“e tooГұooЙ“e Й“en."
  23,42,"Refti Min puЙ—Й—i Й“aawo maЙ“Й“e gire woЙ“Й“e goo."
  23,43,"Mofte woo lajal majje ngal adotaako Й—e, Й“e neeЙ“nantake kadi."
  23,44,"Refti Min Nuli NulaaЙ“e amen Й“en ko Й“e jokkondirЙ“e, tuma kala ari e mofte NulaaЙ—o majje on Й“e njedda mo Min njokkini yoga e maЙ“Й“e yoga, Min mbaЙ—i Й“e yewtereeji, woЙ—Й—ineede wonanii yimЙ“e Й“e gooЕӢЙ—intaa Й“en."
  23,45,"Refti Min Nuli Muusaa e musiЙ—Й—o makko on Haaruuna wond'ude e aayeeje amen Й—en e hujja Й“annguЙ—o."
  23,46,"Fa'ade e Fir'awna e mbatu mu'um ngun, Й“e mawnintinii Й“e laatii yimЙ“e townitiiЙ“e."
  23,47,"ЖҒe mbi'i: "Enee, hara min ngooЕӢЙ—inat yimЙ“e Й—iЙ—o yeru amen, hara yimЙ“e maЙ“Й“e ko maccuЙ“e amen?""
  23,48,"ЖҒe njeddi Й“en Й—iЙ—o, Й“e laatii jiyaaЙ“e e halkaaЙ“e Й“en."
  23,49,"GooЕӢЙ—ii Min ngokkiino Muusaa Deftere nde mbelejo'o kamЙ“e Й“e peewa."
  23,50,"Min mbaЙ—i geЙ—al Mariyama on e neene makko Ma'ande, Min werni Й“e fa'ade e tulde joomiraare ГұiЙ“rude e callungol."
  23,51,"Eey mon yo NulaaЙ“e, Гұaamee immorde e laaЙ“uЙ—i Й—in ngollon ko moЖҙЖҙi, pellet Min, MiЙ—o Anndi ko ngolloton kon."
  23,52,"E pellet, kaa Diina mo'on ko Diina woota, ko Min woni Joomi mo'on lulee Kam."
  23,53,"ЖҒe taЖҙi fiyaake maЙ“Й“e on hakkunde maЙ“Й“e dente, kala fedde no farnora ko woni kon ka mayre."
  23,54,"ЖҠalu Й“e e siwrere nde haa e dummunne."
  23,55,"Enee, hara Й“e cikku wonan'dema ko Min Й“eydiri Й“e kon immorde e jawdi e Й“iЙ—Й“e."
  23,56,"Min njaccinana Й“e e moЖҙЖҙereeji, ko woni Й“e tin'aa."
  23,57,"Pellet, Й“ern Й“e kaГұum immorde e kulol Joomi maЙ“Й“e ko Й“e hulЙ“e."
  23,58,"E Й“en Й“e kaГұum ko Й“e gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e sayeeje Joomi maЙ“Й“e Й—en."
  23,59,"E Й“een Й“e kaГұum Й“e nhonah sirkanooЙ“e Joomi maЙ“Й“e."
  23,60,"E Й“en okkayЙ“e ko Й“e ngokkaa kon, hara Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en ko hulЙ—e [Alla], wonan'dema kamЙ“e ko fa'ade ka Joomi maЙ“Й“e Й“e nduttoytoo."
  23,61,"ЖҒeen [sifaaЙ“e Й—ii sifaaji Й—oo] heЙ“e yaccoo e moЖҙЖҙereeji Й—i, hara kamЙ“e ko Й“e adotooЙ“e e majji."
  23,62,"Min pawaani woЕӢkii si wonaa fodde bawЙ—e makki, no ka amen Deftere wowlaynde Goonga kan, hara kamЙ“e Й“e tooГұoytaake."
  23,63,"Ko woni, Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—e no e welsungo immorde e Й—um, no woodani Й“e kadi golle ga Й—uum ko kamЙ“e ngollate Й—e."
  23,64,"Haa si Min nanngirii neeminaaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en Lepte Й—en njaka yoo kamЙ“e heЙ“e haaca."
  23,65,"Wata on haacu hannde, pellet onon, on wallataake immorde e amen."
  23,66,"GooЕӢЙ—ii Aayeeje Amen Й—en no janngee e taweede mooЙ—on, laatiЙ—on hoЙ—on nduttoo e dow codduli mooЙ—on."
  23,67,"Ko on mawnintiniiЙ“e sabu [jeyeede makka] hoЙ—on kiira haalde bonЙ—i."
  23,68,"Enee, teskaaki konngol ngol, kaa hara ar e maЙ“Й“e ko araani e baabiraaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e adinooЙ“e Й“e?"
  23,69,"Kaa Й“e nganndaani NulaaЙ—o maЙ“Й“e on, hara kamЙ“e ko Й“e faaytuЙ“e mo?"
  23,70,"Kaa hara Й“e mb'ay feetere no e makko? Ko woni, o addanii Й“e Goonga kan Й“urЙ“e heewde e maЙ“Й“e ko aГұЙ“e Goonga kan."
  23,71,"Sinndo Alqur'aana jokkuno beleeЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en, kammuuji Й—in e leydi ndin bonayno e Й“en wonuЙ“e e majji, ko woni, Min addaniiЙ“e waaju maЙ“Й“e ngun, kamЙ“e koЙ“e Й—urniiЙ“e ga waaju maЙ“Й“e ngun."
  23,72,"Kaa a tori Й“e njeenaari? [Awa] ko njeenaari Joomi maaЙ—a ndin Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude, ko KaЕӢko woni MoЖҙЖҙo Arsikoowo."
  23,73,"Pellet, an haЙ—a noddude fa'ade e Laawol Pocciingol."
  23,74,"E pellet, Й“en Й“e mgooЕӢЙ—inaani Laakara on ko Й“e seluЙ“e e Laawol ngol."
  23,75,"Sinndo Min Yurmino Й“e, Min hunci ko heЙ“i Й“e kon immorde e lorra, Й“e duumotono e ndeer bewre maЙ“Й“e heЙ“e wemmboo."
  23,76,"GooЕӢЙ—ii Min nanngirii Й“e Lepte Й—en, Й“e koykinanaaki Joomi maЙ“Й“e Й“e yankinaaki."
  23,77,"Haa si Min ngudditii e dow maЙ“Й“e dammbugal marungal Lepte saЙ—tuЙ—e, e jaka, kamЙ“e e nyder Й—um ko Й“e taЖҙii Й“e."
  23,78,"Ko KaЕӢko woni On uЙ—Й—anЖҠo on nanЙ—e Й—en e giiЙ—e Й—en e Й“erЙ—e Й—en, fanЙ—ii ko njeettoton."
  23,79,"Ko KaЕӢko woni On TakЙ—o on ka leydi ko fa'ade ka makko mooЙ“oyteЙ—on."
  23,80,"Ko KaЕӢko woni on mo no wurna O wara no woodani mo luutindirgol jemma on e Гұalawma on, enee, kaa on hakkiltah?"
  23,81,"Ko woni, Й“e mbii' yeru ko aramЙ“e Й“e mb'inoo ko."
  23,82,"ЖҒe mb'i: "Enee, si min maayii min ngonii mbullaari e Жҙi'e, hara minen ko min immintinoyteeЙ“e?""
  23,83,"GooЕӢЙ—ii min podanooma Й—um minen e baabiraaЙ“e amen ko adii, Й—um wonaani si wonaa tinndi adinooЙ“e."
  23,84,"Maaku: "Ko hommbo leydi ndi woodani e Й“een wonЙ“e e mayri, si tawii hiЙ—on nganndi?"
  23,85,"Aray Й“e mbi'a: "Ko Alla woodani" maaku: "Enee, on mbaajitotaako?""
  23,86,"Maaku: "Ko hommbo woni Jom kammuuji Й—in jeeЙ—iЙ—i e Jom Arsi mawki kin?""
  23,87,"Aray Й“e mbi'a: "Ko Alla" maaku: "Enee, on kulatah [Alla]?""
  23,88,"Maaku hommbo woni e Junngo Mu'um Laamu kala hu'unde hara KaЕӢko homo walla O walletaake, si tawii on laatike hoЙ—on nganndi?"
  23,89,"Aray Й“e mbi'a: "Ko Alla woodani" maaku: "Enee, ko honno mbilirteЙ—on ?""
  23,90,"Ko woni, Min ngaddanii Й“e Goonga kan, pellet kamЙ“e ko Й“e fenЙ“e."
  23,91,"Alla jogitaaki Й“iЙ—Й—o, deweteeЙ—o laataaki wond'ude e Makko, e jaka [si waЙ—um waЙ—uno] kala deweteeЙ—o yaadayno e ko o tagi kon, yoga e maЙ“Й“e townitotono e dow yoga. Senayee wonanii Alla e ga kon ko Й“e cifotoo."
  23,92,"GannduЙ—o ko wirnii kon e ko seedaa ko O Toowii e gai ko Й“e cirkata kon."
  23,93,"Maaku: "Jooma am si A hollii kam ko Й“e podaa kon"."
  23,94,"Jooma am, wota A waЙ—am e yimЙ“e tooГұooЙ“e Й“en."
  23,95,"Pellet, Minen fii yo Min holle ko Min fodi Й“e kon ko Min HattanЙ“e [Й—um]."
  23,96,"DuГұir nden hu'unde Й“urnde moЖҙЖҙude [hu'unde] bonunde nden, ko Minen nganndi ko Й“e scfoto kon."
  23,97,"Maaku: "Jooma, mi moolorii ma immorde e kodooje Seytanuuji Й—i"."
  23,98,"Mi moolorii ma Jooma am nde Й—i tawata kam."
  23,99,"Haa si maayde arii e goЙ—Й—o e maЙ“Й“e nden, o wi'a: "Jooma am nduttee kam"."
  23,100,"Mbelejo'o min, mi ngollay ko moЖҙЖҙi e ndeer kon ko mi accunoo, Й—um waЙ—ataa, ngol ko kanngol ko kaЕӢko wowli ngol, no hedde Й“aawo maЙ“Й“e heedo haa Г‘ande nde Й“e imminoytee."
  23,101,"Si wuttaama ka alaadu, askaaji alah hakkunde maЙ“Й“e nden Г‘ande, Й“e lanndandirtah ."
  23,102,"Kala on mo jisti(teddi) manndake (peesirgal)muuЙ—um, haray ko Й“en Й—on ngoni maloyteeЙ“e Й“en."
  23,103,"Kala mo manndake [moЖҙЖҙi] muЙ—um hoytii, (hoyi)haray ko Й“en Й—on ngoni hayruЙ“e pittaali muuЙ—um, ko ka ndeer Jahannama woni ko Й“e luttintee."
  23,104,"Yiite ngen no sunna je'ece maЙ“Й“e Й—en, hara kamЙ“e e ndeer magge ko Й“e ГұirЙ“iniiЙ“e."
  23,105,"Enee, hara Aayeeje Am Й—en laataaki no janngee e taweede mo'on, laatiЙ—on hoЙ—on njedda Й—e?"
  23,106,"ЖҒe mbi'i: "Joomi amen, ko malkiso amen ngon foolii min, min laatinoke yimЙ“e majjuЙ“e.""
  23,107,"Joomi amen, yaltin min e magge, si min ruttike hara pellet, minen ko min tooГұЙ“e."
  23,108,"O Daala: "Г‘iiЙ“ee e ndeer magge wota on kaalanam"."
  23,109,"Pellet, laatinoke fedde e jiyaaЙ“e Am Й“en hiЙ“e mbi'a: "Joomi amen, min ngooЕӢЙ—inii haforan men njurmeЖҠaa men ko Aan Й“uri MoЖҙЖҙude YurmeteeЙ“e Й“een"."
  23,110,"NJogitiЙ—on Й“e jalnori(jalkigol), haa Й“e njejjintini on jaЕӢta Am, laatiЙ—on hoЙ—on njala Й“e."
  23,111,"Min Mi yoЙ“ii Й“e hannde sabu ko Й“e muГұГұinoo kon, pellet, kamЙ“e ko kamЙ“e ngoni malaaЙ“e Й“een."
  23,112,"O Daali: "No foti heewde ko ГұiiЙ“Й—on ka leydi, limoore duuЙ“i?""
  23,113,"ЖҒe mbi'i: "Min ГұiiЙ“ii Гұallal maaЙ—um yoga e Гұallal, lanndo limooЙ“e Й“een.""
  23,114,"O Daali: "On ГұiiЙ“aani si wonaa seeЙ—a, sinndo onon on laatino hoЙ—on nganndi.""
  23,115,"Enee, on cikku wonan'dema ko Min Tagiri on ko puyndan, hara onon on mduttetaake fa'ade ka Amen?!"
  23,116,"Alla Toowii LaamЙ—o GoonguЙ—o On, dewetee- Й—o alah si wonaa KaЕӢko Jooma Arsi Tedduki kin."
  23,117,"Kala nodduЙ—o wond'ude e Alla deweteeЙ—o goo, daliil alanah mo e Й—um, anndu pellet, hasboo- re makko ko ka Joomi makko, pellet KaЕӢko, O malnatah heeferЙ“e Й“een."
  23,118,"Maaku: "Jooma am, Yaafo Yurmo ko Aan ЖҒuri MoЖҙЖҙude YurmeteeЙ“e Й“en.""
  24,1,"Simoore, Min njippinii nde Min farlii nde, Min njippini e ndeer mayre aayeeje Й“annguЙ—e mbelejo'o onon on mbaajitoto."
  24,2,"Debbo jinoowo on e gorko jinoowo on foccee gooto kala e maЙ“Й“e paatawol(looci) teemedere, wota njurmeende maЙ“Й“e nanngu on e fii Diina Alla ka, si tawii on laatike hoЙ—on ngooЕӢЙ—ini Alla e Г‘alaande Laakara nden. Yo seedo foccugol Й“e ngol jamaa immorde e gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“en."
  24,3,"Gorko jinoowo on o resataa si wonaa debbo jonoowo maaЙ—um cirkoowo, debbo jinoowo on resata mo si wonaa gorko jinoowo ma cirkoowo, Й—um harminaama e dow gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“en."
  24,4,"E Й“en Й“e no tukka rewЙ“e saЕӢiiЙ“e Й“en refti Й“e ngaddaani seedeeЙ“e nayo, piyee Й“e paatawol(lo'oci) cappanЙ—e jeetati. Wota on njaЙ“an Й“e ceedagol poomaa. ЖҒen Й—on, ko kamЙ“e ngoni FaasiqiiЙ“e Й“en."
  24,5,"Si wonaa Й“en tuubuЙ“e Й“aawo Й—uum Й“e moЖҙЖҙini. Pellet, Alla ko O cuhroowo jurmeteeЙ—o."
  24,6,"E Й“een Й“e no tukka sonnaaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en hara laatanaaki Й“e seedeeЙ“e si wonaa wonkiiji maЙ“Й“e Й—in, ko yo goЙ—Й—o e maЙ“Й“e seedo seedeeji nayi [o woondira] Alla pellet, kako ko e googuЙ“e Й“en o jeyaa."
  24,7,"JowaЙ“un Й—um, won'dema yo kuddi Alla wonu e dow makko si o laatike jeyaaЙ—o e fenooЙ“e Й“een."
  24,8,"ЖҒe nduГұira e [sonnaajo on] lepte Й—en, nde o seedotoo seedeeji nayi [o woondira] Alla, pellet [gorko on] ko e fenooЙ“e Й“en o jeyaa."
  24,9,"JowaЙ“um Й—um, ko nde Alla tikkata e dow makko si [gorko on] laatike ko e gooЕӢuЙ“e Й“en o jeyaa."
  24,10,"Sinndo wonaano ЖҒural Alla ngal e dow mooЙ—on e Yurmeende Makko nden, e wonan'dema Alla ko O jaЙ“oowo tuubuubuye Г‘eeГұЙ—o."
  24,11,"Pellet, Й“een adduЙ“e penaale Й—en ko Й“e jamaa jeyaaЙ—o e mooЙ—on, wota on cikku Й—um ko bone mo'on; ko woni Й—um ko moЖҙЖҙere mo'on. No woodani kala neЙ—Й—o immorde e maЙ“Й“e ko o faggitii kon e bakkaat, on fawtiiЙ—o [bakkaat on] immorde e maЙ“Й“e, no woodani mo Lepte mawЙ—e."
  24,12,"Ko haЙ—no oo tuma nde nanЙ—on Й—um, worЙ“e gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“en e rewЙ“e gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“en Й“e njananee ka wonkiiji maЙ“Й“e ko moЖҙЖҙi, Й“e mbi'a: "ЖҠum ko penaale Й“annguЙ—e nii"."
  24,13,"Ko haЙ—no ko nde Й“e ngaddata e Й—um seedeeЙ“e nayo, si Й“e ngaddaani seedeeЙ“e Й“en; haray Й“een Й—on, to Alla ko kamЙ“e ngoni fenooЙ“e Й“en."
  24,14,"Sinndo wonaano Й“ural Alla ngal e yurmeende makko nden e dow mooЙ—on e aduna e yo La'akara Lepte mawЙ—e meematno on fii kon ko ukkiЙ—on e muuЙ—um."
  24,15,"Tuma nde werloraynoЙ—on Й—um Й—enmЙ—e mooЙ—on, wowliron kunnduЙ—e mooЙ—on kon ko ganndal alana on e muuЙ—um sikkon Й—um kadi ko newiiЙ—um, hara non Й—um ko mawnuЙ—om ka Alla."
  24,16,"Ko haanunoo tuma nanЙ—on nde, mbi'on: "Haanaa min nde min wowlata e dum, Senayee woodanii ma, Й—um ko fenaande mawnde nii"."
  24,17,"Alla no waajaade on fii wota on fillo sugu [ndee fenaande] poomaa, si tawii on laatike gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e."
  24,18,"Alla no Й“annginannde on Aayeeje Й—en Alla ko O ganduЙ—o ГұeeГұЙ—o."
  24,19,"Pellet, Й“een yiЙ—Й“e yo bone Й—en sa'ako e [hoore] Й“en gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e; no woodani Й“e Lepte muusЙ—e ka aduna e ka Laakara. Alla no Anndi, onon on nganndah."
  24,20,"Sinndo wonaano ЖҒural Alla ngal e dow mooЙ—on e Yurmeende makko nden e tawde pellet, Alla ko o NewiiЙ—o jurmotooЙ—o o."
  24,21,"Eey mon Й“en gooЕӢ Й—inЙ“e, wota on mjokku Й—ate Seytaane Й—en, kala jokkuЙ—o Й—ate Seytaane Й—en, pellet, o yamirat [mo] ko boni kon e ko aГұaa kon. Sinndo wonaano ЖҒural Alla ngal e dow mooЙ—on e Yurmeende Makko nden; hay e gooto e mooЙ—on laaЙ“ataano poomaa, kono Alla homo laЙ“Й“ina on mo o muuyi. Alla ko O Nanoowo gannduЙ—o."
  24,22,"Wota joomiraaЙ“e Й“ural ngal e yaajeende nde e mooЙ—on wooЙ—ndu wonan'dema Й“e okkortaa Й“adondiraaЙ“e Й“en e Й“illiiЙ“e Й“en e ferЙ“e Й“en ka Laawol Alla, yo Й“e yaafo. Kaa on yiЙ—aa yo Alla yawtan on? Alla ko o jawtoowo YurmeteeЙ—o."
  24,23,"Pellet, Й“een wonЙ“e tukkude [sonnaaЙ“e] saЕӢiiЙ“e welsindiiЙ“e gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e, Й“e huЙ—aama ka aduna e ka Laakara no woodani Й“e Lepte mawЙ—e."
  24,24,"Г‘ande seedoytoo e dow maЙ“Й“e Й—emЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en e juuЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en e koyЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en, ko Й“e laatinoo kon heЙ“e ngolla."
  24,25,"Nden Г‘ande Alla huuЙ“inanay Й“e [njoЙ“di] Diina maЙ“Й“e Goongaha kan, Й“e ngannda pellet, Alla ko KaЕӢko woni Goonga ЖҒannguka kan."
  24,26,"RewЙ“e soЙ“Й“e Й“en ko fii worЙ“e soЙ“Й“e Й“en. WorЙ“e soЙ“Й“e Й“en ko fii rewЙ“e soЙ“uЙ“e Й“en. RewЙ“e laaЙ“Й“e Й“en ko fii worЙ“e laaЙ“Й“e Й“en, worЙ“e laaЙ“uЙ“e Й“en ko fii rewЙ“e laaЙ“uЙ“e Й“en. ЖҒee Й—oo ko hisnaaЙ“e e kon ko Й“e wowlata, no woodani Й“e haforaneede e arsike tedduЙ—o."
  24,27,"Eey mon yo gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e, wota on naat e cuuЙ—i tanaa cuuЙ—i mo'on Й—in haa duЕӢinoЙ—on calminon e dow yimЙ“e majji Й“en, ko Й—um Й“uri moЖҙЖҙannde on. Mbelejo'o jo'o onon on mbaajitoto."
  24,28,"Si on tawaani ndeer ton goЙ—Й—o, wota on naat toon haa duЕӢaneЙ—on, si on mbi'aama: "Yiltee" yiltee, ko Й—uum Й“uri laaЙ“annde on. Alla non homo Anndi ko ngolloton kon."
  24,29,"Bakkaatu fawaaki on nde naatoton e cuuЙ—i Й—i koЙ—iraaka hara no e ndeer majji miranhoy mo'on, Alla non homo Anndi ko ngonЙ—on e feГұГұinde e ko ngonЙ—on e suuЙ—ude."
  24,30,"Maakan worЙ“e gooЙ—inЙ“e Й“en yo Й“e meeru ndaarЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en Й“e ndeena farjuuji maЙ“Й“e Й—in, ko Й—uum Й“urata laЙ“Й“innde Й“e. Pellet, Alla ko o kumpitiiЙ—o ko Й“e ngollata."
  24,31,"Maakan rewЙ“e gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“en yo Й“e meernu ndaarЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en, Й“e ndeena farjuuji maЙ“Й“e Й—in, wota Й“e peГұГұin cuЙ—aari maЙ“Й“e ndin si wonaa ko feeГұi kon e mayri. Yo Й“e fawu tiggaaje maЙ“Й“e Й—en ka becce maЙ“Й“e, wota Й“e feГұГұinan cuЙ—aari maЙ“Й“e ndin si wonaa genndiraaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en ma baabiraaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e ma baabiraaЙ“e genndiraaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e ma Й“iЙ—Й“e maЙ“Й“e, ma Й“iЙ—Й“e genndiraaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e ma musiЙ—Й“e maЙ“Й“e, ma Й“iЙ—Й“e musiЙ—Й“e maЙ“Й“e, ma Й“iЙ—Й“e banndiraaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e, ma sonnaaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e, maaЙ—um Й“en Й“e Й“e jeyiri Гұaame maЙ“Й“e ma Й“en worЙ“e jokkooЙ“e Й“e haaju mun alaa e rewЙ“e, ma boobo mo Жҙellitaaki e awraaji sonnaaЙ“e Й“en. Wata Й“e tappindir koyЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en fii yo Annde ko Й“e suuЙ—i kon immorde e cuЙ—aari maЙ“Й“e. Tuubee ruttoЙ—on ka Alla on fow mo'on, ko onon yo gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e mbelejo'o jo'o on malete."
  24,32,"Ndesinee Й“e ndesaani Й“een e mooЙ—on e moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e Й“en immorde e muccuЙ“e mooЙ—on e horЙ“e mooЙ—on, si Й“e laatike waasЙ“e Alla alЙ—inat Й“e immorde e ЖҒural makko ngal, Alla ko o jaacЙ—o gannduЙ—o."
  24,33,"ЖҒe keЙ“aani fehre desugol Й“een yo Й“e cabbo haa Alla alЙ—inira Й“e ЖҒural makko ngal. ЖҒeen Й—aЙ“Й“atЙ“e soottaade e Й“en Й“e Гұaame mooЙ—on njeyi, coottaadede Й“e si on nganndii e maЙ“Й“e moЖҙЖҙere, njonnee Й“e immorde e jawdi Alla ndin, ndin ndi O jonni on, wota on waawnu horЙ“e mooЙ—on Й“en e fii jeeno, si Й“e faandike saЕӢaade, wota on Й—aЙ“Й“u jawkal ngurndam aduna, kala waawnuuЙ—o Й“e pellet, Alla Й“aawo baawnugol Й“e ko O cuhroowo jurmiteeЙ—o."
  24,34,"GooЕӢЙ—ii min njippinii e mooЙ—on aayeeje Й“annguЙ—e e misal immorde e Й“eya wulinooЙ“e ko adii on e waaju wonan'de hulooЙ“e [Alla] Й“en."
  24,35,"Ko Alla woni annoore kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin, sifa annoore makko nde ko wano tuЙ—Й—ere hara no e mayre pitilol(lampu), pitilol ngol wona e ndeer biiniiri, biiniiri ndin hara hindi wa'i wa hoodere jalbunde hinde huЙ“Й“a immorde e leggal barkinaangal nebbantewal ngal wonaa funnaangeyaЕӢkowal ngal wonaa hirnaangeyaЕӢkowal nebbam maggal Й—am no Й“adoo jalbude, hay si yiite memaani Й—am, annoore e hoore annoore, Alla no feewnira annoore makko nde oon mo o muuyi, Alla no piyana yimЙ“e Й“en mise, Alla ko o gannduЙ—o kala hu'unde."
  24,36,"E nder cuuЙ—i Й—i Alla duЕӢii(sakkiti) yo darne Innde makko jaЕӢtee e ndeer majji Subunhinanee mo ndeer majji ka bimmbi e ka kiikiiЙ—e."
  24,37,"WorЙ“e Й“e njulaaku e njeyngu maapintaa Й—um ga jaЕӢtagol Alla e Гұimnugol Juulde nden e tottu- gol askal on, heЙ“e kuli Г‘alaande nde waylitoytoo e muuЙ—um Й“erЙ—e Й—en e jiiЙ—e Й—en."
  24,38,"Fii yo Alla yoЙ“oyЙ“e ko Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude ko Й“e ngollunoo kon, O Й“eydana Й“e e ЖҒural makko ngal. Alla no arsika on mo O muuyi ko Aldaa hasboore."
  24,39,"ЖҒen yedduЙ“e, golle maЙ“Й“e Й—en no mba'i wa merere won'nde e boowal, Й—omЙ—aaЙ—o on no sikka ko nde ndiyam, haa si o arii e mayre o tawataa hay e hu'unde, o tawa Alla ka makko O huuЙ“inana mo hasboore makko nden, Alla ko O jaawЙ—o Hasboore."
  24,40,"Ma ko wano niЙ“e e maayo luggungo, no suddi ngo bempeЖҙЖҙe no dow maggo bempeЖҙЖҙe no dow majje duule, niЙ“e yoga e majje no e dow yoga, si o yaltinii junngo makko ngon o Й“adotaako ji'igol ngo. oon mo Alla waЙ—anaani annoore hara o alaa annoore."
  24,41,"Enee, a yiaani wonan'dema Alla no subuhinanaade Mo Й“en wonЙ“e ka kammuuli e ka leydi e colli Й—in kadi ko saffiniiЙ—i? Gooto kala e Й—ii gooЕӢЙ—ii anndii juulde mu'um nden e subuhinaali mu'um Й—in, Alla ko O gannduЙ—o ko Й“e ngollata."
  24,42,"Ko Alla heeranii Laamu kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin, ko fa'ade ka Alla woni waЙ—tinirde nden."
  24,43,"Enee, a nji'aani won'dema Alla homo sogga duulere, refti o hawtindira nde, refti o waЙ—a nde fawondirnde haЙ—a yi'a toЙ“o ngon no yalta e ndeer mayre, ngo jippoo immorde ka kammu, immorde e pelle no e ndeer mayre marmalle homo heewtina Й—e on mo o Muuyi, homo pottina Й—e on mo o muuyi? Ndaneeri maЖҙe mayre no do'a naЙ“de giiЙ—e Й—en."
  24,44,"Alla homo waylita jemma on e Гұalawma on, pellet, na wonii e Й—um tasakuyee wonan'de joomiraaЙ“e jiiЙ—e Й“en."
  24,45,"Ko Alla tagii kala kullel immorde e ndiyam, no e majji yaarooji reedu muuЙ—um, no e majji yaarooji koyЙ—e muuЙ—m no e majji kadi yaarooji [koyЙ—e] nayi. Alla homo Taga ko o muuyi, pellet, Alla ko kattanЙ—o kala hu'unde."
  24,46,"GooЕӢЙ—ii Min njippinii Aayeeje Й“annguЙ—e, Alla no feewna on mo O muuyii fa'ade e Laawol Pocciingol ngol."
  24,47,"HeЙ“e mbia: "Min gooЕӢЙ—inii Alla e NulaaЙ—o on, min Й—oftike, refti huccita fedde goo e maЙ“Й“e, Й“aawo Й—uum, Й“en wonaani gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e"."
  24,48,"Si Й“e noddaama fa'ade ka Alla e NulaaЙ—o makko on fii yo o Гұaawu hakkunde maЙ“Й“e, tawa fedde goo e maЙ“Й“e ko Й“e Й—uurniiЙ“e."
  24,49,"Si tawii ko kamЙ“e mari goonga ka, Й“e ngara e makko ko Й“e Й—oftiiЙ“e."
  24,50,"Enee, ko nawnaare woni ka Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e, kaa Й“e sikkiti, kaa Й“e hulu wota Alla e NulaaЙ—o makko on tooГұu Й“e? Ko woni, Й“ee ko kamЙ“e woni tooГұooЙ“e Й“en."
  24,51,"Anndu ko woni konngol gooЙ—inЙ“e Й“en si Й“e noddaama faade ka Alla e NulaaЙ—o makko on fii yo o Гұaawu hakkunde maЙ“Й“e, ko nde Й“e mbi'ata: "Min nanii men Й—oftike." ЖҒen Й—on ko kamЙ“e woni malaaЙ“e Й“en."
  24,52,"Kala Й—oftiiЙ—o Alla e nulaaЙ—o makko on o kuli Alla o rentii [e Lepte makko Й—en] haray Й“en Й—on ko kamЙ“e ngoni malaaЙ“e Й“en."
  24,53,"ЖҒe ngooЙ—ndiri Alla, e hattirde goondooje maЙ“Й“e, si a yamirii Й“e ma Й“e njaltu sanne. Maaku: "wota on ngooЙ—ndu, Й—oftaare no nganndaa, pellet, Alla ko kumpitiiЙ—o ko ngolloton""
  24,54,"Maaku: "ЖҠoftee Alla Й—oftoЙ—on NulaaЙ—o on". Si Й“e nduЕӢtiima anndu ko fawii mo ko, ko o roondaa kon, no fawii on ko ndoonda Й—o kon, si on Й—oftike mo on peewat, fawaaki NulaaЙ—o on si wonaa jottinngol Й“anngungol."
  24,55,"Alla Fodii Й“en gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e e mooЙ—on Й“e ngolli moЖҙЖҙi Й—in o lomtinat Й“e ka leydi wano O lomtinirnoo non Й“en adiiЙ“e Й“e, ma O weeЙ“inan Й“e diina maЙ“Й“e ka O welanaa Й“e, ma O wattitan Й“e Й“aawo kulol maЙ“Й“e ngol hoolaare, Yo Й“e ndewam wota Й“e cirkanam hay e hu'unde. Kala jedduЙ—o Й“aawo Й—um haray Й“en Й—on ko kamЙ“e woni faasiqiiЙ“e Й“en."
  24,56,"Г‘iiЙ“ee e Juulde totton askal on Й—oftoЙ—on kadi nulaaЙ—o on, mbela jo'o on njurmete."
  24,57,"Wota a sikku Й“een yedduЙ“e Й“e laawoto ka leydi, jaaЖҙorde maЙ“Й“e nden ko ka Yiite, pellet, bonii wattnde."
  24,58,"Eey mon yo gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e, yo sakkintino e mooЙ—on Й“en Й“e Гұaame mooЙ—on jeyi, e Й“en Й“e njottaaki koyЙ—ol immorde e mooЙ—on, laabi tati ko adii Juulde Peeral nden, e tuma mballinton conci mooЙ—on ka njollooro e ka Й“aawo Juulde geeЖҙe ko awraaji mooЙ—on tati non. Bakkaatu fawaaki on fawaaki Й“e Й“aawo majji, jinndooЙ“e hakkunde mooЙ—on, yoga e mooЙ—on e dow yoga. Ko wano nii Alla Й“anngini- rani on aayeeje Й—en Alla ko O gannduЙ—o Г‘eeГұuЙ—o."
  24,59,"Si sukaaЙ“e mooЙ—on njottike kellefuyee, yo Й“e cakkitinono wano duЕӢinornoo non Й“en adiiЙ“e Й“e, ko wano nii Alla Й“annginiranta on sayeeje makko Й—en, Alla ko O gannduЙ—o Г‘eeГұЙ—o."
  24,60,"E sonnaaЙ“e jottiiЙ“e Й“en, Й“en Й“e njoortaaki desal bakkaatu fawaaki Й“e nde Й“e wallinta conci maЙ“Й“e Й—in hara Й“e wonaa feГұГұinЙ“e cuЙ—aari, ko nde Й“e nantotoo Й“uri moЖҙЖҙannde Й“e, Alla ko O Nanoowo gannduЙ—o."
  24,61,"Bakkaat fawaaki bumЙ—o on, bakkaatu fawaaki laЖҙoowo on, bakkaat fawaaki ГұawЙ—o on, fawaaki e wonkiiji mooЙ—on nde Гұaamoton ka cuuЙ—i mooЙ—on maaЙ—um ka cuuЙ—i baabiraaЙ“e mooЙ—on, maaЙ—um ka cuuЙ—i neeniraaЙ“e mooЙ—on, maaЙ—um ka cuuЙ—i musiЙ—Й“e mooЙ—on, maaЙ—um ka cuuЙ—i banndiraaЙ“e mooЙ—on, maaЙ—um ka cuuЙ—i bappiraaЙ“e mooЙ—on, maaЙ—um ka cuuЙ—i yaayiraaЙ“e mooЙ—on, maaЙ—om ka cuuЙ—i kaawiraaЙ“e mooЙ—on, maaЙ—um ka cuuЙ—i neeniraaЙ“e mooЙ—on ka dewol, maaЙ—um Й—in Й—i jogiЙ—on cottirЙ—e muuЙ—um, maaЙ—um giЙ—o mooЙ—on. Bakkaat fawaaki on nde kawtoton Гұaamon maaЙ—um Гұaamon ko on sertuЙ“e. Si on naatay e cuuЙ—i salminee e dow woЕӢkiiji mooЙ—on, salminango immorde ka Alla barkinaango laaЙ“ngo, ko wano nii Alla Й“annguniranta on aayeeje Й—en mbelejo'o onon on kaqqilay."
  24,62,"Anndu gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“en ko Й“en gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Alla e NulaaЙ—o makko on, si Й“e laatike hiЙ“e wonndi e makko e dow fiyaake moftuЙ—o, Й“e njahatah haa Й“e duЕӢinoo e makko, pellet, Й“en Й—aЙ“Й“irayЙ“e ma duЕӢayee ko Й“en Й—on woni gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Alla e NulaaЙ—o makko on, si Й“e Й—aЙ“Й“irii ma duЕӢayee fii yoga e fiyaake maЙ“Й“e, duЕӢano on mo yiЙ—Й—aa [duЕӢanaade] e maЙ“Й“e, imsinanoЙ—aa Й“e ka Alla. Pellet, Alla ko cuhroowo jurmeteeЙ—o."
  24,63,"Wota on mbaЙ— noddugol NulaaЙ—o on hakkunde mooЙ—on wano noddugol yoga e mooЙ—on yoga. GooЕӢЙ—ii Alla no Anndi Й“een sortotooЙ“e e mooЙ—on e moltagol, Й“en wonЙ“e lunndaade yamaruyee makko on, yo Й“e rento fii wata fitina hiЙ“u Й“e maaЙ—um Lempte mu'usuЙ—e heЙ“a Й“e."
  24,64,"Ko non woniri, pellet, ko Alla heeranii ko woni kon ka kammuuli e ka leydi gooЕӢЙ—ii homo Anndi ko ngonЙ—on e hoore mu'um kon, Г‘ande Й“e nduttetee fa'ade ka makko p yeetoo Й“e ko Й“e ngollunoo kon. Alla ko O gannduЙ—o kala hu'unde."
  25,1,"Mawnii On JippinЙ—o Seerndoore nden e dow jiyaaЙ—o makko on fii yo wonan winndire nden jeertinoowo."
  25,2,"Oon mo woodanii Й—um Laamu kammuuji Й—in e leydi ndin, o jogitaaki Й“iЙ—Й—o laatanaaki mo kadi kafidaaЙ—o ka Laamu. O tagii kala hu'unde O eЙ“Й“indiinde e eЙ“Й“ugol."
  25,3,"ЖҒe njogitii ga makko deweteeЙ—i Й—i tagaani hu'unde kannji ko Й—i tagaaЙ—i, Й—i maranah ko'e majji lorra wonaa nafa Й—i marah maayde wonaa ngurndam wonaa ummital."
  25,4,"ЖҒeen yedduЙ“e mbi'i: "Ndee [Alqur'aanaare] wonaani si wona pene Й—i o fekindii Й—um, walli mo e hoore majje yimЙ“e goo". GooЕӢЙ—ii Й“e ngaddii tooГұe e bagamma."
  25,5,"ЖҒe mbi'i: "Ko nde tinndi adinooЙ“e o mbinnditi Й—i hiЙ—i fidanee mo bimmbi e kiikiiЙ—e"."
  25,6,"Maaku: "Jippinii nde on gannduЙ—o ngunndoo on ka kammuuli e ka leydi, pellet, KaЕӢko o Laatike cuhroowo jurmeteeЙ—o meteeЙ—o"."
  25,7,"ЖҒe mbi'i: "Ko heЙ“i oo NulaaЙ—o, homo Гұaama Гұaametee homo yaha kadi ka lokooji(jeereeji)В°? Ko haanunoo ko nde jippintee e makko Maleykaaji o laatoo wond'ude e makko jeertinoowo"."
  25,8,"Ma werlee e makko ngal, ma laatanoo mo ngesa o Гұaama e mabba. TooГұooЙ“e Й“en mbi'i: "on njokkaani si wonaa gorko mbilЙ—aaЙ—o.""
  25,9,"Ndaarii [yo NulaaЙ—o] ko honno Й“e piyiranat maa mise, Й“e majjii Й“e hattantaake [heЙ“ude] laawol."
  25,10,"Mawnii on tawЙ—o si O muuyii O waЙ—ane moЖҙЖҙere, no e Й—um gese no ila ley majje canЙ—e Й—en, o waЙ—ane kadi kuЙ“eeje."
  25,11,"Ko woni, Й“e njeddu Darngo ngo, Min heblorani Й“en jedduЙ“e Darngal ngal Yiite ooynge."
  25,12,"Si nge yi'ii Й“e immorde e nokkuure woЙ—Й—unde nananee nge tikkere e faraango."
  25,13,"Si Й“e mbernaama e ndeer magge e nokkuure Й“ittunde ko Й“e sinndindiraaЙ“e, Й“e nodda ton halakuyee."
  25,14,"Wota on noddu hannde halkaare wootere, noddee halkaaje buy."
  25,15,"Maaku: "Enee, ko Й—uum Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude, kaa ko Aljanna luttoowo on, on mo hulooЙ“e Alla Й“en podaa? O laatanike Й“e njoЙ“di e wattinirde."
  25,16,"No woodani Й“e ndeer ton ko Й“e mbelaa, ko Й“e ГұiiЙ“ooЙ“e, Й—uum laatike e dow Joomi maaЙ—a Fodoore lannditeteende."
  25,17,"Г‘ande O mooЙ“idoyta Й“e e ko Й“e ndewatnoo kon gaanin Alla, O Daala: "Enee, ko onon majjini Й“ee JiyaaЙ“e Am, kaa ko kamЙ“e majji Laawol ngol?""
  25,18,"ЖҒe mbi'a: "Senaarre wonanii ma, haananah min nde min njogitotoo gaanin MaaЙ—a immorde e deweteeЙ—i, kono, A dakmintinii Й“e e baabiraaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en haa Й“e njejjiti waajo nguo Й“e laatii yimЙ“e halkiiЙ“e.""
  25,19,"GooЕӢЙ—ii Й“e njeddi on, sabu ko mbi'oton kon, Й“e kattanta yiltugol [Lepte Й—en] wonaa wallude, kala tooГұЙ—o e mooЙ—on Meon meeЙ—inat mo Lepte mawЙ—e."
  25,20,"Min Nulaali ado maaЙ—a immorde e NulaaЙ“e si wonaa kamЙ“e heЙ“e nafoo Гұaametee heЙ“e seenoo kadi ka luumaaji, Min mbaЙ—i yoga e mooЙ—on fitina yoga, fii yo on muГұГұo. Joomi maaЙ—a laatike ko o ji'oowo."
  25,21,"ЖҒen Й“e njortaaki hawroyde e amen mbi'i: "Ko hannoo jippinee e makko Maleykaaji Й“en, ma min nji'a Joomi amen?" GooЕӢЙ—ii Й“ee mawnintinike ka wonkiiji maЙ“Й“e, Й“e townitii townitaare mawnunde."
  25,22,"Г‘ande Й“e nji'oyta Maleykaaji Й“en weltaare alanaa bonЙ“e Й“en nden Г‘ande, Й“e mbi'a: "Heedo heedaango"."
  25,23,"Min ardini faade e ko Й“e ngollunoo kon immorde e gollal, Min mbaЙ—i ngal punndi saraandi."
  25,24,"YimЙ“e aljanna Й“e nden Г‘ande Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude ГұiiЙ“irde Й“uri labeede kadi Гұallirde."
  25,25,"E Г‘ande nde kummu ngun seekorta duule Й—en Malaa'ikaaji Й“en njippinee jippineede."
  25,26,"Laamu goongaawu ngun nden Гұalnde ko Hinnorante On ngu woodani, laatoo Гұalnde saЙ—tunde e dow yedduЙ“e Й“en."
  25,27,"E Г‘ande tooГұЙ—o on ЕӢatoyta junngo makko ngon, o wi'a: "Eeh jalla min, mi jogitino wond'ude e NulaaЙ—o on Laawol."
  25,28,"Eeh bone am haaniino min, mi njogitanooki kaariijo sehilaajo."
  25,29,"GooЕӢЙ—ii o majjinii lam gaayi deftere nden Й“aawo nde arii a am, Seytaane laatike ko o jaasinoowo neЙ—Й—aЕӢke on."
  25,30,"NulaaЙ—o on maaka: "eeyma Jooma pellet, yimЙ“e am Й“en Й“e njogitike ndee Alqur'aanaare wikkaande(accaande)"."
  25,31,"Ko wano nii, Min mbaЙ—irani kala Annabaajo gaГұo immorde e bonЙ“e Й“en, Joomi maaЙ—a yonii peewnoowo e ballo."
  25,32,"ЖҒeen yedduЙ“e mbi'i: "Ko hanno Alqur'aanaare nden jippinee e makko e jumla gooto?" ЖҠuum ko wano nii, fii yo Min tabintinir nde Й“ernde maaЙ—a nden Min rewnindira nde rewnindirgol."
  25,33,"ЖҒe ngaddantaa ma yeru, si wonaa Min ngaddanii ma Goonga kan e ko Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude firo."
  25,34,"ЖҒeen mooЙ“oyteeЙ“e e dow je'ece muuЙ—um fa'ade ka Jahannama, ko Й“en Й—on woni Й“urЙ“e bon'de nokkuure e Й“uruЙ“e majjude kade laawol."
  25,35,"GooЕӢЙ—ii Min ngokkii Muusaa deftere nden, Min mbaЙ—i wond'ude e makko MusiЙ—Й—o makko on Haaruuna ballo."
  25,36,"Men Daali: "njahee ka Й“en yimЙ“e fennuЙ“e Aayeeje Amen Й—en, Min njirbini Й“e jirbinndee"."
  25,37,"E yimЙ“e Nuuhu tuma nde Й“e njeddunoo NulaaЙ“e Й“en, Min njooli Й“e Min mbaЙ—i Й“e Ma'ande fii yimЙ“e Й“e, Min keblani tooГұooЙ“e Й“en Lepte mu'usЙ—e."
  25,38,"E AadiЕӢkooЙ“e Й“en e SamuudiЕӢkooЙ“e Й“en e yimЙ“e Й“unndu ndun e gire Й—uuЙ—uЙ—e hakkunde Й—uum."
  25,39,"Gooto kala e maЙ“e Min piyani Й—um mise, gooto kala e maЙ“Й“e min kalki Й—um kalkugol."
  25,40,"GooЕӢЙ—ii Й“e ngarii e nden saare toЙ“aande toЙ“o bonngo. Kaa Й“e laataaki heЙ“e nji'a Й—e? Ko woni, Й“e laatinoke Й“e njoortaaki Immotal."
  25,41,"Si Й“e nji'ii ma, Й“e njogitotaako ma si wonaa jalnori. Enee, ko oo Alla Immini NulaaЙ—o?"
  25,42,"Fii kala hari o Й“adike(Й—esi) majjinnde en gaayi deweteeЙ—i me'en Й—in si tawiino wonaa ko muГұГұi Й—en kon e dow majji. Aray Й“e nganndoyat tuma Й“e nji'ata Lepte Й—en ko hommbo Й“urЙ—o majjude laawol."
  25,43,"Enee, a tinii on jogitiiЙ—o deweteeЙ—o makko on beleeЙ—e makko Й—en. E hara ko an laatotoo e dow makko pawtiiЙ—o."
  25,44,"Kaa a sikku won'de ko Й“uri heewde e maЙ“Й“e heЙ“e nana ma heЙ“e kakkila? Anndu kamЙ“e Й“e ngonaani si wanaa wano neemoraaЙ—i, toode, ko kamЙ“e Й“uri majjude laawol."
  25,45,"Kaa a tinaani fa'ade e Joomi maaЙ—a honno O fortiri Й—owdi ndin? Sinndo O Muuyuno O waЙ—atno ndi deeЖҙundi, refti Min mbaЙ—i na'ange ngen tinndinatnge e mayri."
  25,46,"refti Min tami ndi ka amen tamannde newiinde."
  25,47,"Ko Kako woni oon baЙ—anЙ—o on jemma on koltu e Й—oyngol ngol fooftere, O waЙ—i Гұalama on ngal saakorЙ—o."
  25,48,"Ko KaЕӢko woni On gaccituЙ—o keni Й—in ko Й—i weltinooji hakkunde Yurmeende makko nden, Min njippini immorde ka kammu ndiyam laaЙ“Й—am."
  25,49,"Fii yo Min nguurnitir Й—am leydi maayndi, Min njarrnaЙ—am kadi kon ko Min tagi neemoraaЙ—i e yimЙ“e Й—uuЙ—uЙ“e."
  25,50,"GooЕӢЙ—ii Min pennsitii nde hakkunde maЙ“Й“e fii yo Й“e mbaajito, salii Й“urЙ“e Й—uuЙ—ude e yimЙ“e Й“en si wonaa jeddugol."
  25,51,"Sinndo min muuyuno min Nulatno e kala saare jeertinoowo."
  25,52,"Wota a Й—ofto yedduЙ“e Й“e haЙ“ e maЙ“Й“e hare jihaadi mawnde."
  25,53,"Ko KaЕӢko woni oon jillindirЙ—o maaje Й—en Й—iЙ—i, ngooЙ—oo ko welngo Жҙem ngooЙ—oo kadi ko haaЙ—ngo tak, O waЙ—i wirngallo hakkunde majje, e heedo heedaango."
  25,54,"Ko KaЕӢko woni on TakЙ—o Й“anndunke immorde e ndiyam Й—am, O waЙ—i mo dammbe e esiraawo, Joomi maaЙ—a laatike ko o kattanЙ—o."
  25,55,"HeЙ“e ndewa gah Alla kon ko nafataa Й“e lorrataa Й“e, jedduЙ—o on laatike ko o teeЙ—iiЙ—o Joomi makko."
  25,56,"Min Nuliraali ma si wonaa ko a beltinoowo e jeertinoowo."
  25,57,"Maaku: "Mi naamaaki on e dow Й—um njoЙ“di si wonaa on njiЙ—uЙ—o jogitaade fa'ade ka Joomi makko Laawol"."
  25,58,"Wakkilo e On guuruЙ—o mo maayataa subuhinoЙ—aa won'dude e jettugol mo, O yonii e Й—um kumpitiiЙ—o bakkatuuji jeyaaЙ“e makko."
  25,59,"On TakЙ—o kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin e ko woni kon hakkunde majji, e ndeer balЙ—e jeego'o refti O fotondiri ka dow Arsi, jurmotooЙ—o On lanndo Mo ko O kumpitiiЙ—o."
  25,60,"Si wi'anaama Й“e: "cujjanee jurmotooЙ—o On" ЖҒe mbi"a: "Ko hommbo woni jurmotooЙ—o On? Enee, hara men sujjanay kon ko yamirЙ—aa min?" ЖҠuum Й“eydi Й“e foЙ—Й—itaare."
  25,61,"Mawnii oon baЙ—uЙ—o ka kammu burjuuji(buurti) o waЙ—i e ndeer majji pitilol e leelewal jalbungal."
  25,62,"Ko KaЕӢko woni On baЙ—uЙ—o jemma on e Гұalawma on lontondirayЙ—i fii on faandiiЙ—o annditugol maaЙ—um o faandii jaarnugol."
  25,63,"E jiyaaЙ“e jurmotooЙ—o e On, Й“en yahooЙ“e ka leydi ko no newiri, si majjuЙ“e Й“een ewnike Й“e, Й“e mbi'a: "kisal "."
  25,64,"E Й“een waalooЙ“e sujjannde Joomi maЙ“Й“e e daragol [juula]."
  25,65,"E Й“een wi'ooЙ“e: "Joomi amen woЙ—Й—intinan men Lepte Jahannama Й—en, pellet, Lepte magge Й—en ko duumiiЙ—e"."
  25,66,"Pellet, Й—een bonii ГұiiЙ“irde e darorde."
  25,67,"E Й“een tawЙ“e si Й“e nafkii Й“e fantintaa Й“e Й“ittintaa kadi, [Й“e] ngoni ГұiiЙ“Й“e hakkunde Й—uum."
  25,68,"E Й“een Й“e ndewaani wond'ude e Alla deweteeЙ—o goo, Й“e waraani fittaandu ki Alla harmini kin si wonaa sabu goonga, hara Й“e njinataa. Mo waЙ—ii Й—uum o hawray e bakkaat."
  25,69,"Sowanoyte mo Lepte Й—en Г‘ande Darngal, o luttinoyee e ndeer majje ko o koynaaЙ—o."
  25,70,"Si wonaa Й“en tuubuЙ“e Й“e gooЕӢЙ—ini Й“e golli golle moЖҙЖҙe, haray Й“en Й—on Allalomtinay bonЙ—i maЙ“Й“e Й—in moЖҙЖҙi. Alla wonii ko O cuhroowo JurmeteeЙ—o."
  25,71,"Kala tuubuЙ—o o golli ko moЖҙЖҙi haray pellet, kaЕӢko o ruttoto ka Alla ko o jaЙ“anaaЙ—o tuubuubuyee."
  25,72,"E Й“een Й“e seeditotaako penaale Й—en si Й“e rewii ka rayrayti Й—in [wowletee] Й“e feЖҙЖҙay ko tedduЙ“e"
  25,73,"E Й“een tawЙ“e si Й“e waajoraama aayeeje Joomi maЙ“Й“e Й—en Й“e hippotaako e dow majje ko Й“e faaЙ—uЙ“e e wumuЙ“e."
  25,74,"E Й“een wi'ooЙ“e: "Joomi amen, okku men immorde e sonnaaЙ“e amen e geЙ—alЙ“e amen Й“uuЙ“endan gite, waЙ—aa min wonan'de hulooЙ“e Alla Й“en ГұentinteeЙ“e"."
  25,75,"ЖҒenЙ—on Й“e njoЙ“oyte huЙ“eere nden sabu ko Й“e muГұГұii kon, Й“e hawroya ndeer ton e hiwraango e salminaango."
  25,76,"Ko Й“e ГұiiЙ“ooЙ“e ndeer ton moЖҙЖҙii ГұiiЙ“irde e darorde."
  25,77,"Maaku: "JeyЙ—o lam On haajaaka e mooЙ—on sinndo wonaano du'aaji mo'on Й—in, gooЙ—ii on fenniino aray Й—e laatoo duumiiЙ—e [Lepte laakara]."
  26,1,"Taa, Siin, miim."
  26,2,"ЖҠeen ko aayeeje Deftere Й“anngunde nde."
  26,3,"Mbelejo'o an a tampiniray hoore maaЙ—a kin fii Й“e laataaki gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e."
  26,4,"Si Min muuyii Min njippinat e maЙ“Й“e immorde ka kammu aaya daaЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en Гұalla ko Й—e yankinaniiЙ—e mo."
  26,5,"Arataa e maЙ“Й“e waaju immorde ka jurmotooЙ—o on fuЙ—Й—aangu si wonaa Й“e laatike Й—uuriiЙ“e ngu."
  26,6,"GooЕӢЙ—ii Й“e njeddii aroyay e maЙ“Й“e kabaruuji ko Й“e laatinoo koЙ“e njalkitano."
  26,7,"Enee, Й“e nji'aani fa'ade e leydi ndin, no foti heewde ko Min puЙ—ini e mayri immorde e kala noone tedduЙ—o?"
  26,8,"Pellet, wonii e Й—uum [ko jaЕӢtaa Й—oo] aaya, Й“urЙ“e heewЙ“e e maЙ“Й“e laataaki gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e."
  26,9,"Pellet, Joomi maaЙ—a ko KaЕӢko woni tedduЙ—o JurmeteeЙ—o On."
  26,10,"JaЕӢto tuma nde Joomi maaЙ—a noddunoo Muusaa, Й—um woni ar e yimЙ“e tooГұooЙ“e Й“e."
  26,11,"YimЙ“e Fir'awna, kaa on kulataa"
  26,12,"O maaki: "Joom am , min miЙ—o huli wota Й“e njeddam."
  26,13,"ЖҒernde am nden Й“ittoo hara Й—emngal am ngal wellitaaki, awa Nul to Haaruuna."
  26,14,"No woodani Й“e e dow am bakkaat miЙ—o huli fii wota Й“e mbaram."
  26,15,"O Daali: "Wonaa non, njahee onon Й—iЙ—o, MiЙ—en ngon'di e mooЙ—on ko Min heЙ—iiЙ“e"."
  26,16,"Aree ka Fir'awna wi'on: "Minen dey ko min NulaaЙ“e Jooma winndere nden.""
  26,17,"ЖҠuum woni accitu Й“iЙ—Й“e Isra'iila Й“en wond'ude e amen."
  26,18,"O wi'i: "Enee, min ne'aano ma ka amin Й—oo hari ko a boobo, ГұiiЙ“uЙ—aa ka amin Й—oo duuЙ“i e ngurndam maaЙ—am?""
  26,19,"NGolluЙ—aa gollal maaЙ—a ngal ngollunoЙ—aa ngal, an ko e yedduЙ“e Й“en njeyaЙ—aa."
  26,20,"O maaki: "Mi waЙ—ii Й—um, ontuma min ko mi jiyaaЙ—o e majjuЙ“e Й“een"."
  26,21,"Mi dogi on, tuma nde mi kulunoo on, Joomi am okkin mi Ganndal o waЙ—in mi jiyaaЙ—o e NulaaЙ“e Й“en."
  26,22,"ЖҠum ko neema mo mbajitirtaa mi Й—um, fii a maccinЙ—inii Й“iЙ—Й“e Israa'iila Й“en."
  26,23,"Fir'awna wi'i: " Ko hommbo jeyi winndere nde?""
  26,24,"O maaki: "Ko Jooma kammuuji Й—in e leydi ndi e ko woni kon hakkunde majji, si on laatike yananaaЙ“e.""
  26,25,"O wi'ani Й“een wonЙ“e banЕӢe makko: "Enee; on leЙ—ataako?""
  26,26,"O maaki: "Joomi mooЙ—on e Jooma baabiraaЙ“e adiiЙ“e Й“en.""
  26,27,"[Fir'awna] wi'i: "Pellet, NulaaЙ—o mooЙ—on on NulaaЙ—o fa'ade e mooЙ—on ko o kaangaaЙ—o.""
  26,28,"O maaki: "Ko Jooma funna'ange e hirna'ange e ko woni kon hakkunde majji, si on laatike kakkilooЙ“e.""
  26,29,"[Fir'awna] wi'i: "Mi wooЙ—ndii si jogitike deweteeЙ—o tan am, mi waЙ—ete jiyaaЙ—o dummbaaЙ“e Й“een"."
  26,30,"O maaki: "enee, hay si mi addanii ma hu'unde Й“anngunde?""
  26,31,"[Fir'awna] wi'i: "Awa addu Й—um, si tawii ko e gooЕӢЙ—u Й“e Й“e njiyaaЙ—aa.""
  26,32,"O wernii tuggordu makko ndu, jaka ko ndu mbooЙ—di (ngoolwa) Й“annguba."
  26,33,"O yaltini junngo makko ngo, jaka yoo ko ngo ranwungo wonan'de ndaarooЙ“e Й“e."
  26,34,"[Fir'awna] wi'ani mbatu ngu fee makko: "Pellet, ooЙ—oo ko bileejo keewЙ—o ganndal"."
  26,35,"Homo fa'andii jaltinirgol on ka leydi mooЙ—on mbilewu makko ngu. Ko hulЙ—un njamirЙ—on?"
  26,36,"ЖҒe mbi'i : "NeeЙ“nu mo e musiЙ—Й—o makko on, nulaa e ca'e Й—en mooЙ“ooЙ“e (wileeЙ“e)"."
  26,37,"ЖҒe ngddane kala bileejo gannduЙ—o."
  26,38,"WileeЙ“e Й“en mooЙ“aa fii fodoore Гұalaande anndaande."
  26,39,"YimЙ“e Й“en mbii'anaa: "Taw si onon ko on mooЙ“ike(ndenndi)""
  26,40,"Mbelejo'o lajo'o minen min njokkay wileeЙ“e Й“en, si Й“e laatike ko kamЙ“e ngoni foolЙ“e Й“en."
  26,41,"Tuma nde wileeЙ“e Й“en ngrnoo; Й“e mbi'ani Fir'awna: "Enee, no woodani min njoЙ“di si tawii ko min ngoni foolЙ“e Й“e?""
  26,42,"O wi'i : "Eyyo, on tuma on njeyaama e Й“aЙ—tinaaЙ“e Й“en"."
  26,43,"Muusaa maakani Й“e: "mbeddee, ko mbernoton kon"."
  26,44,"ЖҒe liЙ“i Й“oggi maЙ“Й“e e cawoy maЙ“Й“e kon, Й“e mbi'i: "Sabu teddungal Fir'awna, ko minen ngoni foolooЙ“e Й“e"."
  26,45,"Muusaa wernii tuggordu makko ndu, tawi kayru hundu moЙ—a ko Й“e fekindii ko."
  26,46,"WileeЙ“e Й“e nduuyi Й“e cujji."
  26,47,"ЖҒe mbi'i : "Min ngoЕӢЙ—inii JeyЙ—o Winndere nde,"
  26,48,"Joomum Muusaa e Haaruuna"."
  26,49,"[Fir'awna] wi'i: "Enee, on ngooЕӢЙ—inat mo, ko adii mi duЕӢanaade on? Pellet, ko kaЕӢko woni mawЙ—o mooЙ—on anndinЙ—o on on mbilewu ngu, kono a nganndon, mami taЖҙ juuЙ—e mooЙ—on e koyЙ—e mooЙ—on [taЖҙa] luutindira. Mami fetu on, on fof mooЙ—on"."
  26,50,"ЖҒe mbi'i: "Tanaa alaa, minen ko fa'ade ka Joomi amin min nduttotoo"."
  26,51,"Minen miЙ—en tamЖҙinii nde Joomi amin yawtani min ngoopi amin Й—in,tawde min laatike adiiЙ“e gooЕӢЙ—innde Й“en."
  26,52,"Min mbahayini fa'ade e Muusaa: "ЖҠuum woni roЖҙidu e JiyaaЙ“e Am Й“een. Pellet, onon ko on jokkiteteeЙ“e"."
  26,53,"Fir'awna nuli to ca'e mooЙ“ooЙ“e."
  26,54,"[O wi'i:] Pellet, Й“ee ko Й“e mojobum pamarum."
  26,55,"Pellet, kamЙ“e heЙ“e tikkinnde min."
  26,56,"Enen non en fof ko en reentiiЙ“e."
  26,57,"Min njaltini Й“e immorde e gese e caatli."
  26,58,"E ngaluuji e ГұiiЙ“irde teddunde."
  26,59,"Ko wano nii, Min ndonini Й—um Й“iЙ—Й“e Israa'iila Й“en."
  26,60,"ЖҒe njokkiЙ“e de puЙ—al."
  26,61,"Tuma nde jamaaji Й—in Й—in yi'ndirnoo, yimЙ“e Muusaa Й“e mbi'i: "Enen en hewtoyte"."
  26,62,"O maaki: "ЖҠuum waЙ—ataa, pellet, Joomi am no won'di e am o feewnat kam"."
  26,63,"Min mbahayini e Muusaa, Й—um woni piyir tuggordu maaЙ—a ndu maayo ngon, ngo seekii ceekol kala seekol na foti e tulde mawnde."
  26,64,"Min Й“anni ton heddiiЙ“e Й“e."
  26,65,"Min ndaЙ—ni di Muusaa e won'Й—uЙ“e e makko Й“e fof maЙ“Й“e."
  26,66,"Refti Min njooli heddii Й“e Й“e."
  26,67,"Pellet, wonii e Й—uum [ko jaЕӢtaa Й—oo] aaya, Й“urЙ“e heewude e maЙ“Й“e laataaki gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e."
  26,68,"Pellet, Joomi maaЙ—a, ko KaЕӢko woni TedduЙ—o jurmeteeЙ—o."
  26,69,"Janngan Й“e kumpital fii Ibraahiima."
  26,70,"Tuma nde o wi'annoo baaba makko e yimЙ“e makko Й“e; ko holЙ—um ndewoton?"
  26,71,"ЖҒe mbi'i: "MiЙ—en rewde sanamuuji, min Гұallat ufnanaade Й—i"."
  26,72,"O maaki: "mati i hiЙ—i nanana on, nde noddoton"."
  26,73,"Maa hiЙ—i nafa on ma Й—i lorra on?"
  26,74,"ЖҒe mb'i: "Ko woni, men tawii baabiraaЙ“e amen Й“e konii Й“e ngolliratnoo"."
  26,75,"O maaki: "Enee, on nji'ii kon ko ngonЙ—on e rewde?""
  26,76,"Onon e baabiraaЙ“e mon adinooЙ“e Й“e."
  26,77,"Pellet, kamЙ“e ko Й“e aГұЙ“e am, si wonaa Jooma winndire nden."
  26,78,"On TalЙ—o kam, ko KaЕӢko feewnata kam."
  26,79,"On ko KaЕӢko Гұamminta kam O yarnan-mi."
  26,80,"Si mi nawnii, ko KaЕӢko sellinta kam."
  26,81,"E oon barayЙ—o kam refti o wurnitan mi."
  26,82,"Oon mo mi tamЖҙinii kadi nde O yaafatoomi goopi am Й—in Г‘ande [njoЙ“di] Diina ka."
  26,83,"Joomam, okkam Ganndal wattidaa mi e moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e Й“e."
  26,84,"MbaЙ—anaa kam jaЕӢto moЖҙЖҙo ka sakkitiiЙ“e Й“en."
  26,85,"MbaЙ—aa mi jiyaaЙ—o e ronooЙ“e Aljanna Neemaaji Й—in."
  26,86,"NjaafЙ—aa baaba am, pellet, kaЕӢko o laatinoke jiyaaЙ—o e majjuЙ“e Й“een."
  26,87,"Wota A hersinoyam Г‘ande Й“e Immital."
  26,88,"Г‘ande nde jawdi e Й“iЙ—Й“e nafataa."
  26,89,"Si wonaa on arduЙ—o ka Alla e Й“ernde hisnde."
  26,90,"Aljanna oon Й“atinanee hulooЙ“e Alla Й“een."
  26,91,"Jahiim ngeen feГұГұinanee bewЙ“e Й“ern."
  26,92,"ЖҒe wi'nee: "Honto woni ko laatinoЙ—on kon hoЙ—on ndewa"."
  26,93,"Ga Alla? Taw si Й—i walla on ma Й—i wallat hoore majji?"
  26,94,"ЖҒe kippee e ndeer magge kamЙ“e e bewЙ“e Й“en."
  26,95,"E konnuuji ibliisa Й—iin Й—i fof majji."
  26,96,"ЖҒe mbi'i tawi kamЙ“e heЙ“e wennjondira ndeer ton:"
  26,97,""Min woondirii Alla, min woniino e ndeer majjere Й“anngunde."
  26,98,"Tuma nde min njeddunoo on e Jooma winndere nde""
  26,99,"Majjinaani min si ngonaa bonЙ“e Й“en."
  26,100,"Alanaa min tefooЙ“e."
  26,101,"Wonaa kadi giЙ—o ГұallamЙ“ereejo(tigi tigi)."
  26,102,"Sinndo no woodannoo min ndutteede, min laatoo jiyaaЙ“e e gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“en."
  26,103,"Pellet, wonii e Й—uum [ko jaЕӢtaa Й—oo] aaya, Й“urЙ“e heewЙ“e e maЙ“Й“e laataaki gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e."
  26,104,"Pellet, Joomi maaЙ—a, ko Kako woni TedduЙ—o jurmeteeЙ—o."
  26,105,"YimЙ“e Nuuhu Й“en njeddii NulaaЙ“e Й“en."
  26,106,"Tuma nde Nuuhu musiЙ—Й—o maЙ“Й“e on mbiannoo Й“e: "Enee, on kulataa [Alla]?""
  26,107,"Min dey, ko mi nulaaЙ—o e mooЙ—on koolaaЙ—o."
  26,108,"Kulee Alla Й—oftoЙ—on mi."
  26,109,"Mi toraaki on e dow Й—um njoЙ“di, njoЙ“di am ndin fawaaki si wonaa Jooma winndere nde."
  26,110,"Kulee Alla Й—oftoЙ—on mi."
  26,111,"ЖҒe mbi'i: "Enee, hara men ngooЕӢЙ—inte, ja'asЙ“e Й“en no njokkumaa?""
  26,112,"O maaki: "Ko holЙ—um woni ganndal am e ko Й“e ngonoo e gollude?"."
  26,113,"Hasboore maЙ“Й“e nde fawaaki si wonaa e Joomi am, sinndo hoЙ—on so'aynoo."
  26,114,"Min mi ngonaani raЙ—otooЙ—o gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“en."
  26,115,"Min mi ngonaani si wonaa jerrtinoowo Й“annguЙ—o."
  26,116,"ЖҒe mbi'i: "Min woondii si a accaani aan Nuuhu, ma a laato sanne jiyaaЙ—o e rajmeteeЙ“e Й“en"."
  26,117,"O maaki: "Joom am, pellet, yimЙ“e am Й“en Й“e fenni kam"."
  26,118,"Г‘aawu hakkunde am e maЙ“Й“e Гұaawoore, ndanndaa mi e Й“een wonnduЙ“e e am joyaaЙ“e e gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“en."
  26,119,"Min danndi mo e Й“een won'Й—uЙ“e e makko ka ndeer laana Жҙoltiika(loowaaka)."
  26,120,"Refti Min yooli Й“aawo [maЙ“Й“e] heddiiЙ“e Й“en."
  26,121,"Pellet, wonii e Й—uum [ko jaЕӢtaa Й—oo] Aaya, Й“urЙ“e heewde e maЙ“Й“e laataaki gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e."
  26,122,"Pellet, Joomi maaЙ—a, ko KaЕӢko woni TedduЙ—o jurmeteeЙ—o."
  26,123,"AadiЕӢkooЙ“e Й“en njeddiino NulaaЙ“e Й“en."
  26,124,"Tuma nde Huudu musiЙ—Й—o maЙ“Й“e on wi'annoo Й“e: "Enee, on kulataa [Alla]?""
  26,125,"Min dey, ko mi NulaaЙ—o e mooЙ—on koolaaЙ—o."
  26,126,"Kulee Alla Й—oftoЙ—on mi."
  26,127,"Mi toraaki on e dow Й—uum njoЙ“di, njoЙ“di am ndin fawaaki si wonaa Jooma winndere nde."
  26,128,"Enee, on mahat Ma'ande e kala tulde hoЙ—on pija?"
  26,129,"NjogitoЙ—on kuЙ“eeje a wi'ayma onon ko on luttinteeЙ“e [ka aduna]."
  26,130,"Si on njaggitii, njanggiton ko ndunndarankooЙ“e."
  26,131,"Lulee Alla Й—oftoЙ—on mi."
  26,132,"Kulee oon Й“eydirЙ—o on ko ngannduЙ—on."
  26,133,"O Й“eydiri on neemoraaЙ—i e Й“iЙ“Й“e worЙ“e."
  26,134,"E gese e canЙ—i.(gite)."
  26,135,"[O maaki] min dey, miЙ—o hulani on Lepte Г‘alaande mawnde."
  26,136,"ЖҒe mbi'i: "No fotana min ter, si a waajike ma si a laataaki jiyaaЙ—o e waajotooЙ“e Й“een"."
  26,137,"Pellet, Й—uum wonaani si wonaa jikku adinooЙ“e Й“een."
  26,138,"Minen Min ngonaani leptoyteeЙ“e."
  26,139,"ЖҒe njeddi mo, Min kalki Й“e. Pellet, wonii e Й—uum [ko jaЕӢtaa Й—oo] Aaya, Й“urЙ“e heewude e maЙ“Й“e laataaki gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e."
  26,140,"Pellet, Joomi maaЙ—a, ko KaЕӢko woni TedduЙ—o jurmeteeЙ—o."
  26,141,"SamuudiЕӢkooЙ“e Й“een njeddiino NulaaЙ“e Й“en."
  26,142,"Tuma nde Saalihu musiЙ—Й—o maЙ“Й“e on wi'annoo Й“e: "Enee, on kulataa [Alla]?""
  26,143,"Min dey, ko mi NulaaЙ—o e mooЙ—on koolaaЙ—o."
  26,144,"Kulee Alla Й—oftoЙ—on mi."
  26,145,"Mi toraaki on e dow Й—uum njoЙ“di, njoЙ“di am ndi fawaaki si wonaa Jooma winndere nde."
  26,146,"Enee, hara on ngaccete e koo ko woni Й—oo ko on hooliiЙ“e?!"
  26,147,"E ndeer gese e canЙ—i.(gote.)"
  26,148,"E remuruuji e tamarooje hara dukke majje ko Й“ennduЙ—e."
  26,149,"HoЙ—on lesa pelle Й—een [mbaЙ—on] cuuЙ—i ko on haawitiiЙ“e."
  26,150,"Kulee Alla Й—oftoЙ—on mi."
  26,151,"Wota on Й—ofto jamaruyee fantinooЙ“e Й“een."
  26,152,"ЖҒeen bonnooЙ“e ka leydi hara Й“e moЖҙЖҙintaa."
  26,153,"ЖҒe mbi'i: "Pellet, an ko a jiyaaЙ—o wilaaЙ“e Й“een"."
  26,154,"An a wonaani si wonaa Й“annduЕӢke yeru amen, awa addu aaya, si tawii a laatike jiyaaЙ—o e gooЕӢЙ—uuЙ“e Й“en."
  26,155,"O maaki: "baaЙ—oo ko naaqawa, no woodani mba yarannde, no woodani on onon kadi yarannde Гұalaande anndaande"."
  26,156,"Wota on memir mba ko boni, sakko nannga on Lepte Г‘ande Mawnde."
  26,157,"ЖҒe mborii mba, Й“e ngonti nimsuЙ“e."
  26,158,"Lepte Й—en nanngi Й“e. Pellet, ngonii e Й—uum [ko jaЕӢtaa Й—oo] Aaya, Й“urЙ“e heewde e maЙ“Й“e laataaki gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e."
  26,159,"Pellet, Joomi maaЙ—a, ko Kako woni TedduЙ—o JurmeteeЙ—o."
  26,160,"YimЙ“e Luutu Й“een njeddi NulaaЙ“e Й“en."
  26,161,"Tuma nde Luutu musiЙ—Й—o maЙ“Й“e on wi'annoo Й“e: "Enee, on kulataa [Alla]?""
  26,162,"Min dey, ko mi NulaaЙ—o e mooЙ—on koolaaЙ—o."
  26,163,"Kulee Alla Й—oftoЙ—on mi."
  26,164,"Mi toraaki on e dow Й—um njoЙ“di, njoЙ“di am ndin fawaaki si wonaa Jooma winndere nde."
  26,165,"Enee, on ngarat e worЙ“e Й“e immorde e winndere nde?!"
  26,166,"ЖҠalon ko Joomi mooЙ—on tagani on kon immorde e sonnaaЙ“e mooЙ—on? Ko woni, onon ko on yimЙ“e yawtuЙ“e Keerol."
  26,167,"ЖҒe mbi'i: "Min ngooЙ—ndiri si a accaani aan Luutu, ma a laato sanne jiyaaЙ—o e yaltiteeЙ“e Й“en"."
  26,168,"O maaki: "Min dey, miЙ—o jiyaa e aГұЙ“e Й“en golle mooЙ—on Й—en"."
  26,169,"Jooma, danndam min e Й“eynguure am ndeen kon ko Й“e ngollata."
  26,170,"Min danndi mo e Й“eynguure makko nden, Й“e fof maЙ“Й“e."
  26,171,"Si wonaa jiidiraare(nayeejo debbo) nden ka halkaaЙ“e Й“en."
  26,172,"Refti Min oЖҙЖҙi heddii Й“e Й“en."
  26,173,"Min toЙ“ini e dow maЙ“Й“e toЙ“o, bonii toЙ“o jeertinaaЙ“e Й“en."
  26,174,"Pellet, wonii e Й—uum [ko jaЕӢtaa Й—oo] aaya, Й“urЙ“e heewuЙ“e e maЙ“Й“e laataaki mgooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e."
  26,175,"Pellet, Joomi maaЙ—a, ko Kako woni TedduЙ—o JurmeteeЙ—o."
  26,176,"YimЙ“e fitaare(sutu) nden njeddiino NulaaЙ“e Й“een."
  26,177,"Tuma nde Su'aybu wi'annoo Й“e: "Enee, on kulataa [Alla]?""
  26,178,"Min dey, ko mi NulaaЙ—o e mooЙ—on koolaaЙ—o."
  26,179,"Lulee Alla Й—oftoЙ—on mi."
  26,180,"Mi toraaki on e dow Й—uum njoЙ“di, njoЙ“di am ndin fawaaki si wonaa Jooma winndere nde."
  26,181,"Kumnee Й“etu ngu, wata on laato jiyaaЙ“e e ustooЙ“e Й“een."
  26,182,"Manndikiree(pe'esirЙ—e) manndikirЙ—e peewЙ—e Й—een."
  26,183,"Wata on ustan yimЙ“e Й“en piiji maЙ“Й“e Й—in, wota on lancito ka leydi hara ko on bonnooЙ“e."
  26,184,"Kulee oon TakЙ—o on, o tagoore adinoongu ngun."
  26,185,"ЖҒe mbi'i: "Pellet, an ko a jiyaaЙ—o wilaaЙ“e Й“en."
  26,186,"Aan a wonaani si wonaa Й“annduЕӢke yeru amen, tawde miЙ—en cikkumaa ko a jiyaaЙ—o e fenooЙ“e Й“een."
  26,187,"Awa fukku e dow amen kunte kammu ngun, si tawii a laatike jiyaaЙ—o e gooЕӢЙ—uЙ“e Й“een."
  26,188,"O maaki: "Ko Joomi am woni gannduЙ—o ko ngolloton kon"."
  26,189,"ЖҒe njeddi mo, nanngi Й“e Lepte Гұalaande Й—owdiinde nden. Pellet, Й—en laatino Lepte Гұalaande mawnde."
  26,190,"Pellet, wonii e Й—uum [ko jaЕӢtaa Й—oo] aaya, Й“urЙ“e heewЙ“e e maЙ“Й“e laataaki gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e."
  26,191,"Pellet, Joomi maaЙ—a, ko KaЕӢko woni TedduЙ—o JurmeteeЙ—o."
  26,192,"E pellet, kayre ko nde jippinaande Joom winndere nde."
  26,193,"Jippinii nde ruuhu koolaaЙ—o oon."
  26,194,"E Й“ernde maaЙ—a fii yo a laato jiyaaЙ—o e jeertinooЙ“e Й“en."
  26,195,"E Й—emngal Aarabi Й“anngungal."
  26,196,"Pellet, kayre hende ka Й—eri aranЙ“e Й“een."
  26,197,"Enee, hara laatanaaki Й“e Ma'ande, nde tawata anndiino nde Й“iЙ“Й“e Israa'iila annduЙ“e Й“en?"
  26,198,"Sinndo Min njippinno nde e dow yoga e ajamiyaЕӢkooЙ“e Й“en."
  26,199,"o janngi nde e dow maЙ“Й“e, Й“e laatotaako gooЙ—inЙ“e nde."
  26,200,"Ko wano nii Min naatniri Й—um e Й“erЙ—e bonЙ“e Й“en."
  26,201,"ЖҒe ngooЕӢЙ—intaa nde, haa Й“e nji'a Lepte mu'usuЙ—e Й—en."
  26,202,"ЖҠe ngara e maЙ“Й“e e juhayee, hara Й“e so'aa."
  26,203,"Sakko Й“e mbi'a: "Taw si ko min neeЙ“nanteeЙ“e?""
  26,204,"Enee, ko Lepte amen Й—en Й“e keГұorta?"
  26,205,"A tinii si Min ndakmitii Й“e duuЙ“i."
  26,206,"Refti ari e maЙ“Й“e ko Й“e laatinoo heЙ“e podee."
  26,207,"Nafaali Й“e ko Й“e laatinoo kon heЙ“e ndakmitoo."
  26,208,"Min kalkatanii saare woo, si wonaa hara no woodani nde jeertinooЙ“e."
  26,209,"[ЖҠuum] ko waaju, Min laataaki tooГұooЙ“e."
  26,210,"Wonaa seytanuuji Й—in njippini nde."
  26,211,"[ЖҠuum] haananaaЙ—i, Й—i kattantaa Й—um kadi."
  26,212,"Pellet, kannji ko Й—i follateeЙ—i ga keЙ—agol ngol."
  26,213,"Wota a noddu deweteeЙ—o goo wond'ude e Alla, sakko laatoЙ—aa jiyaaЙ—o e LepteteeЙ“e Й“en."
  26,214,"Jeertin gorol maaЙ—a Й“urЙ“e Й“adaade Й“en."
  26,215,"LesЙ—inan balbe maaЙ—en, wona nde Й“en jokkuЙ“e ma immorde e gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“en."
  26,216,"Si Й“e njeddii ma, haray maaku: "Min dey, ko mi danndiiЙ—o ko ngolloton"."
  26,217,"Hoolor On TedduЙ—o JurmeteeЙ—o."
  26,218,"On jioowo ma saha de darotoЙ—aa."
  26,219,"E baylitogol maaЙ—a e hakkunde sujjooЙ“e Й“een."
  26,220,"Pellet, ko KaЕӢko woni Nanoowo gannduЙ—o On."
  26,221,"Taw si mi humpitay on ko e hommbo Seytanuuji Й—in njippotoo?"
  26,222,"HiЙ—i njippoo e dow kala fekindotooЙ—o bakkodinЙ—o."
  26,223,"HiЙ—i mbernoo nanЙ—e Й—en, ko Й“urЙ“e heewude e majji ko penooji."
  26,224,"YimooЙ“e Й“een ko jokkata Й“e, ko bewЙ“e Й“een."
  26,225,"Enee, a tinaani won'dema kamЙ“e heЙ“e yinoo e kala aynde?"
  26,226,"E tawde kamЙ“e heЙ“e wowla ko Й“e ngollataa."
  26,227,"Si wonaa Й“een gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“e ngolli golle moЖҙЖҙe Й“e njaЕӢtii Alla ko Й—uuЙ—i Й“e yoЙ“tii Й“aawo Й“e tooГұaama. Aray ka Й“een tooГұuЙ“e annday ko honde e waylitorde Й“e mbaylitotoo."
  27,1,"Taa Siin, Й—een ko aayeeje Alqur'aanaare nden e deftere Й“anngunde."
  27,2,"Ko nde Peewal e welo-welo wonan'de gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“en."
  27,3,"ЖҒeen Й“e no ГұiiЙ“a e Juulde nden Й“e totta askal on, kamЙ“e heЙ“e njananaa fii Laakara on."
  27,4,"Pellet, Й“een Й“e ngooЕӢЙ—inaani Laakara on, Min cuЙ—anii Й“e golle maЙ“Й“e Й—en, kamЙ“e heЙ“e mbumo."
  27,5,"Ko Й“een ngoni Й“en, Й“e woodani Й—um Lepte bonЙ—e Й—en, kamЙ“e ka Laakara ko kamЙ“e ngoni hayruЙ“e Й“een."
  27,6,"E pellet, an haЙ—a lonnginee Alqur'aanaare nden immorde ka Г‘eeГұo gannduЙ—o."
  27,7,"Tuma nde Muusaa maakannoo Й“eynguure makko nden: "Min dey, mi haynike yiite, mi addana on ka nge woni Й—on kumpital ma mi addana on docotal kuЙ“Й“ungal, bela jo'o onon on itwoto."
  27,8,"Tuma nde o arnoo e magge, o noddaa: ЖҠuum woni barkinaama on wonЙ—o ka yiite e Й“en wonЙ“e banЕӢe magge, e Senaare wonanii Alla Jooma winndere nden."
  27,9,"Eey ma Muusaa, ko woni, ko Min woni Alla TedduЙ—o Г‘eeГұЙ—o On."
  27,10,"LiЙ“u tuggordu maaЙ—a ndun, Tuma nde o yi'unoo ndu hundu dilla, a wi'ayma kayru ko ndu mbooЙ—di, o hucciti ko o doguЙ—o o yiltitaake. Ko an yo Muusaa: "Wata a hul, Min dey NulaaЙ“e Й“en kulataa to Am"."
  27,11,"Si wonaa oon tooГұЙ—o, refti o lomtini ko moЖҙЖҙi Й“aawo bone Й—en. Pellet, Min ko Mi cuhroowo JurmeteeЙ—o."
  27,12,"Naatnu junngo ma ngon ka jiiba maaЙ—a, ngo yaltay ko ngo ranewo ko aldaa e bone, [Й—um no jeyaa] e ndeer aayeeje jeenay nulaaЙ—e e Fir'awna e yimЙ“e makko Й“en, pellet, kamЙ“e Й“e laatike yimЙ“e faasiqiiЙ“e."
  27,13,"Tuma nde arnoo e maЙ“Й“e Aayeeje amen Й—en ko yi'eteeЙ—e, Й“e mbi'i: "ЖҠu'um, ko mbilewu Й“anngungu"."
  27,14,"ЖҒe njeddi [aayeeje Й—en], tawi wonkiiji maЙ“Й“e Й—in no yananaa fii majje, tooГұe e mawnintinaare. Ndaaru ko honno laatornoo battane yedduЙ“e Й“en."
  27,15,"GooЕӢЙ—ii Min ngokkii Daawuuda e Sulaymaana Ganndal Й“e maaki: "Yettoore nden woodanii Alla On Й“urnuЙ—o min e dow Й—uuЙ—uЙ“e immorde e jeyaaЙ“e makko gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“en"."
  27,16,"Sulaymaana roni Daawuuda, O maaki: "eey mon yimЙ“e, min nganndinaama haala colli Й—in, men okkaama immorde e kala hu'unde, Pellet, Й—umЙ—oo ko Й—um woni Й“ural Й“anngungal"."
  27,17,"Sulaymaana mooЙ“anaa koneeli makko Й—i immorde ka jinnaaji e ka yimЙ“e e ka colli, kamЙ“e ko Й“e yuЙ“Й“inaaЙ“e."
  27,18,"Haa nde Й“e ngrnoo e aynde korndolli Й—in, korndolil mbi'i i'i: "eey mon korndolli, naatee ka koЙ—anЙ—i mooЙ—on, fii wata Sulaymaana e koneeli mu'um Й—in muncu on, tawa kamЙ“e Й“e tinaa"."
  27,19,"[Sulaymaana] moosi ko o jaluЙ—o immorde e konngol maggi ngol, o maaki: "Jooma, lonnginam no mi yettira neema maaЙ—a mo neeminЙ—aa e dow am on, e jibibinЙ“e lam Й“en, e nde mi gollata ko moЖҙЖҙi mbeltoraa Й—um, naatnaami ka Yurmeende MaaЙ—a wond'ude e jiyaaЙ“e Ma moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e Й“e"."
  27,20,"O Жҙewtii colli Й—in, o maaki: "Ko heЙ“i kam, mi yiaani Hud-huda. Kaa ndu laati jiyaandu e wirniiЙ—i Й—in?""
  27,21,"Maa mi lepta ndu sanne lepte caЙ—tuЙ—e ma maa mi hirsandu sanne, ma ndu addana kam hujja Й“annguЙ—o."
  27,22,"Ndu ГұiiЙ“e ko woЙ—Й—aani, ndu wi'i: "mi huЙ“indike ko a huЙ“indaaki Й—um, mi addanii ma immorde to Saba'i kumpital yananaangal"."
  27,23,"Min dey, mi tawii sonnaajo no laamii Й“e homo okkaa immorde e kala hu'unde, no woodami mo kadi jullere [laamu] mawnde."
  27,24,"Mi tawii mo kaЕӢko e yimЙ“e makko Й“en heЙ“e cujjana na'ange nge ga Alla; Seytaane no cuЙ—aniЙ“e golle maЙ“Й“e Й—en o faddii Й“e ga Laawol ngol, kamЙ“e Й“e peewataa."
  27,25,"Ko haЙ—ata Й“e cujjana Alla oon jaltinoowo ko suuЙ—ii kon ka kammuuli e ka leydi homo Anndi ko cuuЙ—oton e ko peГұinton."
  27,26,"Alla, DeweteeЙ—o alaa si wonaa KaЕӢko Jooma Arsi Tedduki kin."
  27,27,"O maaki: "Aray min ndaara si a gooЕӢЙ—u, maaЙ—um si laati jiyaaЙ—o e fenЙ“e Й“en"."
  27,28,"Yahdu e nduu talkuru am mbernoЙ—aa ndu ka maЙ“Й“e, refti kuccaa Й“e ndaaraa ko holЙ—um Й“e nduttata."
  27,29,"[Sonnaajo on] wi'i: "eey mon mbatu, min dey wernaama ka am talkuru teddundu"."
  27,30,"Pellet, nduu ko immorde e Sulaymaana, pellet, ko woni e mayru ko: "Innde Alla kuuЙ“uЙ—o Yurmeende keeriiЙ—o Yurmeende Oon"."
  27,31,"Wota on townitano kam, ngaree e am ko jebbiliiЙ“e."
  27,32,"O wi'i: "eey mon mbatu, mbaЙ—tee kam e feere e Й—ee fiyaake am, mi laataaki taЖҙoowo fiyaake haa tawteЙ—on e am"."
  27,33,"ЖҒe mbi'i: "Enen ko en jooma doole e jooma hare caЙ—tuЙ—e, fiyaake Й—en ko ka maaЙ—a woni, ndaaru ko holЙ—um njamirtaa"."
  27,34,"[Debbo on] wi'i: "Pellet, laamЙ“e Й“en si Й“e naatii e saare Й“e mbonnat nde, Й“e mbaЙ—a tedduЙ“e mayre Й“en hoyЙ“e, ko wanonii Й“e ngollirta."
  27,35,"Awa miin, mi nulay e maЙ“Й“e neldaari, mi ndaara ko holЙ—um nulaaЙ“e Й“en nduttodata."
  27,36,"Tuma nde Й“e arnoo ka Sulaymaana, o maaki: "Enee, on Й“eydiray kam jawdi, kon ko Alla okkimmi, no Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude diini kon ko O okki on, ko woni, onon hoЙ—on farnora neldaari mooЙ—on ndin"."
  27,37,"Rutto ka maЙ“Й“e, mamen ngaddana Й“e koneeli Й—i Й“e maraa feere muuЙ—um, mamen njaltin Й“e ton ko Й“e ja'asЙ“e hara kamЙ“e ko hoyЙ“e."
  27,38,"O maaki: "eey mon mbatu, ko hommbo e mooЙ—on addanta kam jullere laamu makko nden, ko adii Й“e arude ka am ko Й“e jebbiliiЙ“e?""
  27,39,"Ngaari jinna ndin wi'i: "Min, mi addante nde ko adii a immaade e darnde maaЙ—a nden, e pellet, min e dow Й—um ko mi cemmbuЙ—o koolaaЙ—o"."
  27,40,"Oon mo woni ka mu ganndal immorde ka deftere wi'i: "Min mi anndante nde ko adii a nde ndarЙ—e maaЙ—a Й—en ruttotoo e maaЙ—a". Tuma nde o yi'unoo nde ko nde ГұiiЙ“unde ka makko, o maaki: "ЖҠum Й—oo, ko immorde e ЖҒural Joomi am, fii yo o ndarndo lam si mi jarnay [mo] maaЙ—um si mi yeddat [mo], kala jarnuЙ—o anndu ko o jarni kon wonanay wonkii makko kin, kala yedduЙ—o kadi pellet, Joomi am ko o Galo TedduЙ—o"."
  27,41,"O maaki: "Faytinanee mo jullere laamu makko nden, ndaaren si on annditat, kaa o laatoto jiyaaЙ—o e Й“en Й“e anndittaa"."
  27,42,"Tuma nde o arnoo, [o] wi'aa: "Enee, ko nii jullere maaЙ—a nden wa'i?" O wi'i: "Awi'ayma ko kayre tigi nii". Min ndokkaama ganndal ko adii mo, min laatii jebbiliiЙ“e."
  27,43,"Faddii mo, Й—um ko o laatinoo homo rewa ga Alla, pellet, kaЕӢko o laatinoke jiyaaЙ—o e yimЙ“e yedduЙ“e."
  27,44,"Wi'anaa mo: "Naatu ka huЙ“eere". Tuma nde o yi'unoo nde o sikki ko nde duneere(tewru), o Гұori dense (korle)makko Й—en. [Sulaymaana] maaki: "Pellet, ndee ko huЙ“eere newЙ—iniraande ndaarorЙ—e". [Debbo on] wi'i: "Jooma, min dey mi tooГұii woЕӢkii am, mi jebbilanike Alla Jooma winndire nden, wond'ude e Sulaymaana"."
  27,45,"GooЕӢЙ—ii Min Nulii fa'ade e SamuudinkooЙ“e Й“en musiЙ—Й—o maЙ“Й“e on Saalihu, Й—um woni rewee Alla. Tawi kamЙ“e ko Й“e feddeeji Й—iЙ—i hiЙ“e beeГұondira."
  27,46,"O maaki: "Ko onon yo yimЙ“e am, ko fii holЙ—um heГұornton bone Й—en ko adii moЖҙЖҙere nden?" "Ko haЙ—i imsinanao Alla mbelejo'o onon on njurminoyte"."
  27,47,"ЖҒe mbi'i: "Min kiitinorii ma e Й“en won'Й—uЙ“e e maaЙ—a". O maaki: "kiite mooЙ—on on ko ka Alla woni, ko woni, onon ko on yimЙ“e fitneteeЙ“e""
  27,48,"Laatinoke ka saare ton worЙ“e njeenayo heЙ“e mbonna ka leydi Й“e moЖҙЖҙintaa."
  27,49,"ЖҒe mb'i: ЖҒe ngooЙ—ndirii Alla, ma min waalanan mo ka suudu kaЕӢko e Й“eynguure makko nden refti ma min wi'an jeyЙ“e mo Й“en; men tawaaka bargol yimЙ“e makko Й“en, e pellet, menen ko men gooЕӢЙ—uЙ“e"."
  27,50,"ЖҒe kodi hodoore Minen kadi Min pewji fewjoore, tawi kamЙ“e Й“e so'ataa."
  27,51,"Ndaaru, ko honno laatorno battane hodo maЙ“Й“e ngon, Minen Min njirbinno Й“e kamЙ“e e yimЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en Й“e fof maЙ“Й“e."
  27,52,"ЖҠin cuuЙ—i maЙ“Й“e ko jeewuЙ—i sabu ko Й“e tooГұunoo kon. Pellet, wonii e Й—um Ma'ande wonan'de yimЙ“e haqqilooЙ“e Й“en."
  27,53,"Min danndi Й“en gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e, Й“e ngoni hulooЙ“e [Alla]."
  27,54,"E Luutu, tuma nde o wi'anno yimЙ“e makko Й“en: 'Enee, on aray paЕӢkare Й—en hara hoЙ—on cutii?""
  27,55,"Eyoo, onon on ngarat e worЙ“e Й“en ka tuuyo ngccon rewЙ“e Й“en?! Si ko woni, onon ko on yimЙ“e majjaaЙ“e."
  27,56,"Jaabawol yimЙ“e makko Й“en ngonaano si wonaa ko Й“e mbi'i : "Yaltinee yimЙ“e Luutu Й“en ka hoЙ—o (wura) mooЙ—on ; kamЙ“e ko Й“e yimЙ“e laЙ“Й“intintooЙ“e"."
  27,57,"Min daЙ—ndi mo kaЕӢko e yimЙ“e makko Й“en, si wonaa debbo makko on; [on Й—on] Min hoddiranii mo ko o jiyaaЙ—o e halketaaЙ“e Й“en."
  27,58,"Min toЙ“ini e dow maЙ“Й“e toЙ“o, bonii toЙ“o jeertinaaЙ“e Й“en."
  27,59,"Maaku: Yettoore nden ko Alla woodani, kisiyee wonii e jiyaaЙ“e makko Й“en Й“e O suЙ“ii. Enee, ko Alla Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude, kaa ko Й—in Й—iЙ“e sirkanta?"
  27,60,"Kaa ko hommbo tagi kammuuji Й—in e leydi ndin O jippinani on immorde ka kammu ndiyam? Min puЙ—iniri Й—am gese joomiraaje ЕӢari. Wonantaa on nde puЙ—inon leЙ—Й—e majje. Enee, hara deweteeЙ—o no woodi wond'ude e Alla? Ko woni, kamЙ“e ko Й“e yimЙ“e ooГұotooЙ“e."
  27,61,"Kaa ko hommbo waЙ—i leydi ndin ГұiiЙ“ndi, O waЙ—i hakkunde mayri calluЙ—i O waЙ—ani ndi pelle o waЙ—i hakkunde maaje Й—en Й—iЙ—i heedo?, hara na woodi deweteeЙ—o [goo] wond'ude e Alla? ko woni, Й“urЙ“e Й—uuЙ—ude Й“en e maЙ“Й“e Й“e nganndaa."
  27,62,"Kaa ko hommbo jaabato Й“ittiiЙ—o on si o noddi mo o hunca bone Й—en o waЙ—a on lontiiЙ“e ka leydi? Na woodi KoreweteeЙ—o goo wond'ude e Alla? FamЙ—ii ko mbaajitoЙ—on."
  27,63,"Kaa ko hommbo feewnata on ka niЙ“e njoorndi e ka maayo, e ko hommbo accitata keni Й—in wewlinirayЙ—i fii Yurmeende Makko nden? Enee, ko deweteeЙ—o goo wond'ude e Alla? Alla Toowii ga ko Й“e cirkata kon."
  27,64,"Kaa ko hommbo woni puЙ—Й—uЙ—o tagoore nde refti O rutta ngu, e ko hommbo arsikata on immorde ka kammu e ka leydi? Enee, ko deweteeЙ—o goo wond'ude e Alla? Maaku: "Addee daliili mooЙ—on on si tawii ko on gooЕӢЙ—uЙ“e"."
  27,65,"Maaku: "Anndaa ko wirnii kon Й“en wonЙ“e ka kammuuli e ka leydi si wonaa Alla. ЖҒe so'ataa kadi ko honnde tuma Й“e immintinoytee"."
  27,66,"Ko woni, ganndal maЙ“Й“e ngal hattii fii Laakara on, ko woni, kamЙ“e heЙ“e e sikke fii [Laakara], ko woni, kamЙ“e ko Й“e wumuЙ“e fii Й—um."
  27,67,"ЖҒeen yedduЙ“e mbi'i: " Enee, hay si min laatike mbullaari e baabiraaЙ“e amen Й“en kadi, e hara minen ko min yaltinoyteeЙ“e?""
  27,68,"GooЕӢЙ—ii min podanooma Й—um minen e baabiraaЙ“e amen ko adii, Й—um wonaani si wonaa tinndi adinooЙ“e."
  27,69,"Maaku : "njehee ka leydi ndaaron ko honno battane bonЙ“e Й“en laatornoo"."
  27,70,"Wota a suno fii maЙ“Й“e, wota a laato e Й“itteende immorde e ko Й“e peewjata kon."
  27,71,"HeЙ“e mb'a: "Ko honnde tuma woni ndee Fodoore, si on laatike gooЕӢuЙ—Й“e?""
  27,72,"Maaku: "No tijjaa de tawata Й“adanike on yoga e kon ko Й—aЙ“Й“uЙ—on yaccinaneede"."
  27,73,"Pellet, Joomi maaЙ—a ko O Jom ЖҒural e dow yimЙ“e Й“een, kono Й“urЙ“e Й—uuЙ—ude Й“en e maЙ“Й“e Й“e njaarnataa [Alla]."
  27,74,"Pellet, Joomi maaЙ—a hiMo Anndi ko Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en coomi e ko Й—e 'eГұГұinta ko."
  27,75,"Alaa e birniikum ka kammu e ka leydi si wonaa [fii makkun] no e ndeer deftere Й“anngunde."
  27,76,"Pellet ndee Alqur'aanaare, hende filloo e dow Й“iЙ—Й“e Israa'iila Й“en fii hu'unde nde Й“e Й“uri luutondirde nden e fii muuЙ—um."
  27,77,"Pellet, kayre ko nde peewal e Yurmeende wonan'de gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“en."
  27,78,"Pellet, Joomi maaЙ—a O Гұaawirat hakkunde maЙ“Й“e Г‘aawoore makko ngal, ko KaЕӢko woni TedduЙ—o gannduЙ—o."
  27,79,"Wakkilo e Alla, pellet, an haЙ—a e hoore Goonga Й“annguka ka."
  27,80,"Pellet, an a nanintaa maayЙ“e Й“en, a nanintaa fa'aЙ—uЙ“e Й“en noddaandu ndun si Й“e Й—uurnike Й“e nduЕӢitii."
  27,81,"An a wonaani peewnoowo wumЙ“e Й“en e ga majjere maЙ“Й“e nde. A nanintaa si wonaa Й“en gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Aayeeje Amen Й—en hara kamЙ“e ko Й“e jebbiliiЙ“e."
  27,82,"Si konngol ngol yanii e dow maЙ“Й“e, Min yaltinana Й“e daabewa immorde ka leydi himba kaalana Й“e won'nde yimЙ“e Й“en laatike Й“e yananaaka aayeeje Amen Й—en."
  27,83,"E Гұande Min mooЙ“oyta immorde e kala mofte dental jeyaaЙ“e e Й“en yennooЙ“e Aayeeje Amen Й—en hara kamЙ“e heЙ“e coggee."
  27,84,"Haa si Й“e ngarii, O Daala: "Eyoo, on yenniino Aayeeje Am Й—en, hara on huЙ“indoraali Й—i ganndal. Kaa ko holЙ—um wonЙ—on e gollude?""
  27,85,"Konngol [Lepte] ngol yani e maЙ“Й“e sabu ko Й“e tooГұi ko, kamЙ“e Й“e kaalataa."
  27,86,"Enee, hara Й“e yiaani, Minen Min mbaЙ—ii jemma on fii yo Й“e deeЖҙu e maako, e Гұalawma on nji'irЙ—o? Pellet, wonii e Й—um Aayeeje wonan'de yimЙ“e gooЕӢЙ—inooЙ“e Й“en."
  27,87,"E Г‘ande wuttoytee ka alaadu, Й—enЖҙoo Й“en wonЙ“e ka kammuuli e Й“en wonЙ“e ka leydi, si wonaa Й“en Й“e Alla muuyi, gooto kala e maЙ“Й“e aray e makko hara ko Й“e hoykiniiЙ“e."
  27,88,"HaЙ—a tina pelle Й—en, cikka ko Й—e fenndiiЙ—e, hara le kannje heЙ—e wuloo wulagol duule Й—en, Й—uum ko kuugal Alla, On ЕӢarЙ—inЙ—o kala hu'unde, pellet, KaЕӢko ko O kumpitiiЙ—o ko ngolloton kon."
  27,89,"Mo ardii e moЖҙЖҙere nden haray no woodani mo ko Й“uri nde moЖҙЖҙude, hara kamЙ“e ko Й“e hooliiЙ“e immorde e Й—enЖҙere nden Г‘ande."
  27,90,"Mo ardii kadi e bone Й—en, j'eece maЙ“Й“e Й—en kippete ka Yiite. Yalli on yoЙ“ete si wonaa kon ko laatinoЙ—on hoЙ—on ngolla?"
  27,91,"Anndu ko mi yamiraa ko yo mi rewJooma ndii leydi ndi Alla harmini Й—um, no woodani mo kala hu'unde. Mi yamiraama kadi yo mi laato jiyaaЙ—o e jebbiliiЙ“e Й“een."
  27,92,"E yo mi janngu Alqur'aanaare ndeen, mo feewii ko hoore-makko o feewani, mo majjii kadi maaku: "Min dey, ko mi jiyaaЙ—o e jeertinooЙ“e Й“een."
  27,93,"Maaku kadi: "jettooje nden ngoodanii Alla, aray O holla on Aayeeje makko Й—een ngaanndon Й—e". Joomi maaЙ—a wonaani belsindiiЙ—o ga e kon ko ngolloton."
  28,1,"Taa, Siin, Miim."
  28,2,"ЖҠee ko aayeeje deftere Й“anngunde nden."
  28,3,"MoЙ—en janngira e maaЙ—a hoore goonga, kumpital Muusaa e Fir'awna, wonan'de yimЙ“e gooЕӢЙ—inooЙ“e Й“en."
  28,4,"Pellet, Fir'awna townitino ka leydi; o waЙ—i yimЙ“e mayri ndin pecce-pecce: homo lo'ina fedde goo e maЙ“Й“e, o hirsa Й“iЙ“Й“e maЙ“Й“e worЙ“e Й“en o acca rewЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en. Pellet, ko e bonnooЙ“e Й“en o jiyanoo."
  28,5,"MiЙ—en faandinoo moЖҙЖҙagol e lo'inanooЙ“e Й“en ka leydi; Min mbaЙ—a Й“e koohooЙ“e, Min mbaЙ—a Й“e kadi ronooЙ“e Й“en."
  28,6,"Min kuЙ“indina Й“e e leydi ndin, Min kolla Fir'awna e Haamaana e koneeli maЙ“Й“e Й—in, kon ko Й“e kulaynoo."
  28,7,"Min mbhayini e yumma Muusaa, wonn'de: "Muynin mo". Si a hulanoyii mo, ko yo a bugoyo mo ka maayo. Wata a hulu, wata a suno; pellet, Men ruttay mo ka maaЙ—a, Min mbЙ—oya mo gooto e NulaaЙ“e Й“en"."
  28,8,"YimЙ“e Fir'awna Й“en kocci mo, fii yo laatano Й“e gaГұo e suno. Pellet, Fir'awna e Haamaana e koneeli maЙ“Й“e Й—in, Й“e laatino woopЙ“e."
  28,9,"Debbo Fir'awna on wi'i: "(Kun entum ko) Й“uuЙ“eendi gite am e an kadi! Wota on war mo, hino gasa ka o nafata en, maa jogitoren mo Й“iЙ—Й—o". Hari Й“e so'aani."
  28,10,"ЖҒernde yumma Muusaa nden wonti yeewnde. Haa o eЙ“Й“i feГұГұin'de fii makko, si wonaano Min tabintinnde Й“ernde makko nden, fii yo o laato e gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“en."
  28,11,"[Yumma Muusaa] wi'ani banndiraawo makko on: "Jokkitu mo"; o haynii mo ka de'estii, Й“e so'aa-anndude."
  28,12,"Min karminani mo ko adii, (enЙ—i) muynirЙ—i Й—in, (banndiraawo makko on) mbi'i: "On ngaccat mi tinndina on fii yimЙ“e suudu, Й“e ne'ana on mo, hara kadi ko laaЙ“anat Й“e mo?""
  28,13,"Min ndtti mo ka yumma makko, fii yo Й“ernde makko Й“uuЙ“u, hara o sunaaki, e fii yo o anndu pellet, fodoore Alla nden, ko goonga. Kono Й“urЙ“e Й—uuЙ—ude e maЙ“Й“e ngaanndaa."
  28,14,"Nde o yottinoo sagatalaaku makko ngun, o fotondi- ri, Min ngokki mo faamu e ganndal. Ko wano non Min njoЙ“irta moЖҙЖҙinooЙ“e Й“en."
  28,15,"O naatiri e saare nden, feewndo welsindaare yimЙ“e mayre; o tawi worЙ“e Й—iЙ—o no haЙ“a ton: goЙ—Й—o on ko jiyaaЙ—o e leГұol makko, oya on ko jiyaaЙ—o e ayЙ“e makko Й“en. JeyaaЙ—o e leГұol makko ngol Й—aЙ“Й“iri faabo e hoore jiyaaЙ—o e gaГұo makko on. Muusaa uttii mo, nde gayni fii makko. [Muusaa] maaki: "ЖҠum Й—oo, ko jiyaaЙ—um e kuuЙ—e seytaane. Pellet, ko o gaГұo, majjinoowo Й“annguЙ—o"."
  28,16,"O maaki: "Joomi am, mi tooГұii hoore-am; haforanam." O haforani mo. Pellet, ko KaЕӢko woni Haforoowo, jurmotooЙ—o On."
  28,17,"O maaki: "Joomi am, sabu ko neeminЙ—aa ko e am, mi wonataa ballo bomЙ“e Й“e"."
  28,18,"O wonti kulЙ—o ka saare, homo habbii [nanngeede]. Tawi faabinornooЙ—o mo on hanki, homo faabinora mo [hannde kadi]. Muusaa maakani mo: "Pellet, ko a bewЙ—o Й“annguЙ—o"."
  28,19,"Nde Muusaa faandinoo nanngugol tawЙ—o on ko gaГұo maЙ“Й“e kamЙ“e Й—iЙ—o, o wi'i: "ey ma yo Muusaa, a faala bargol lam, wano ittirnoЙ—aa woЕӢkii non haЕӢki? A faandaaki, si wonaa wonugol dunndarankeejo ka leydi, a faandaaki jeyeede e moЖҙЖҙinooЙ“e Й“een"."
  28,20,"Gorko iwri ka Й“uri woЙ—Й—ude e saare nden, homo yaccoo, o wi'i: "eey ma Muusaa, mbatu ngun no fewjana fii bargol maa. Yaltu (e leydi ndin). Ko mi jiyaaЙ—o e laaЙ“anooЙ“e ma"."
  28,21,"O yalti ton, ko o kulЙ—o, himo tijjii [nanngeede]. O maaki: "Joomi am, danЙ—ndam e yimЙ“e tooГұooЙ“e Й“een"."
  28,22,"Nde o feewtunoo hella Madyana, o maaki: "Hino hasii ka Joomi am fewnirta lam, e laawol pocciingol ngol"."
  28,23,"Nde o hewtunoo ka Й“unndu Madyana, o tawi Й—on dental yimЙ“e, heЙ“e njarna [daabeeji maЙ“Й“e], o tawi gaanin maЙ“Й“e, rewЙ“e Й—iЙ—o, no sogga [dammi maЙ“Й“e], o maaki: "Ko holЙ—um habbi-Й—on?" ЖҒe mb'i: "Min njarnataa haa aynooЙ“e Й“en nde'estoo, baaba amen, ko mawЙ—o nayeejo"."
  28,24,"O yarnani Й“e [dammi Й—in], refti o huccitiri ka Й—owdi, o maaki: "Joomi am, min ko njippinЙ—aa e am woo e moЖҙЖҙere, ko mi katonjiЙ—o"."
  28,25,"Gooto e [jiwЙ“e] Й“en ari e makko, homo yahra hersa, o wi'i: "Baaba am no nodde, fii yo o yoЙ“e njoЙ“di kon ko njarnan-Й—aa men". Tuma o hewtunoo ka [mawЙ—o] on, o sifanii mo fii [makko], o maaki: "Wota a hul, a daЙ—ii yimЙ“e tooГұooЙ“e Й“en"."
  28,26,"Gooto e [jiwЙ“e] Й“en wi'i: "Жіettu mo golle, yo baaba. Pellet, ko Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude e mo Жҙettataa golle, ko doolnuЙ—o koolniiЙ—o"."
  28,27,"[MawЙ—o] on maaki: "MiЙ—o yiЙ—i desingol ma gooto e jiwЙ“e am Й“en Й—oo Й—iЙ—o, e hoore yo a golla-nam duuЙ“i jeetati. Si a timminii sappo, haray ko e sago maa; mi faalaaka saЙ—tinannde ma. A tawat kam, si Alla jaЙ“ii, ko e moЖҙЖҙinooЙ“e Й“en mi jeyaa"."
  28,28,"[Muusaa] maaki: "ЖҠum wonii hakkunde am e mon. Happu woo e majji Й—iЙ—i, Й—i mi huuЙ“ni, haray Й“iЙ—teede alanaa e kam. En waЙ—ii Alla pawtiiЙ—o e ko wowluЙ—en kon"."
  28,29,"Nde Muusaa timminnoo happu ngun, o yahdi e Й“eydnuure makko, o haynii yiite ka senngo (fello) Tuuri, o maaki Й“eunguure makko nden: "ngonee Й—oo, min mi haynike yiite. Mbelejo'o mi addana on e magge kumpital maa te'annde(docotal) yiite ngen, mbelejo'o itworon"."
  28,30,"Nde o heewtunoo nge, o noddiraa ka fonngo Гұaamo aynde, ka tummbere barkinaande, ka (takko) lekki, won'nde: "eey ma Muusaa! Ko Miin woni Alla, JeyЙ—o winndere nden"."
  28,31,"Kadi: "Bugo tuggordu maa ndun"; nde o tinunoo hundu dillira wa mboddi,o huccitiri dogudu, o yeЖҙЖҙitaaki. [O noddaa]: "Ko an yo Muusaa! Artu, wota a hul; ko a jiyaaЙ—o e hooliiЙ“e Й“een."
  28,32,"Naatnu juungo maa ngon ka jayba maa, ngo yaltat ranewo, ko aldaa e Гұawu. Bakaa e maaЙ—a, juuЙ—e maa Й—en, fii kulol ngol. ЖҠiin ko hujjaaji Й—iЙ—i, immorde ka Joomi maa, haa e Fir'awna e dental mum, pellet, Й“een laatike yimЙ“e faasiqiiЙ“e"."
  28,33,"O maaki: "Joomi am, mi ittiino wonkii e maЙ“Й“e, miЙ—o huli nde Й“e mbarata kam."
  28,34,"Ko musiЙ—Й—o am on Haaruuna, Й“uri kam laaЙ“ude Й—emngal. Immindin-mo e am, ko ballitoo kam, gooЕӢЙ—iam-mi; miЙ—o huli nde Й“e fennata kam"."
  28,35,"[Alla] daali: "Min cemmbinirat tere maa Й—en, musiЙ—Й—o maa on, Min mbaЙ—ana on hujja (e cemmbe); Й“e hewtirtaa on Й—iЙ—o, sabu aayeeje Amen Й—e [Min nuli e] mo'on, e Й“en jokkuЙ“e on foolЙ“e"."
  28,36,"Nde Muusaa addunoo e maЙ“Й“e aayeeje Amen Й—en Й“annguЙ—e, Й“e mbi'i: "ЖҠum wonaani, si wonaa mbilewu fekindaangu. Min naniraani Й—um baabiraaЙ“e amen adinooЙ“e Й“en"."
  28,37,"Muusaa maaki: "Ko Joomi am Й“uri anndude on arduЙ—o e peewal, immorde to makko, e on mo battane moЖҙЖҙe woodani ka La'akara. Pellet, O malnataa tooГұooЙ“e Й“en"."
  28,38,"Fir'awna wi'i: "eey mon dental, mi anndanaa on deweteeЙ—o, si wonaa min. Eey ma yo Haamaana, huЙ“Й“inanam [yiite] e loopal ngal, mahiranaa kam huЙ“eere toownde, no gasa ka mi Жҙellitoo e DeweteeЙ—o Muusaa On; tawde miЙ—o sikki mo e fenooЙ“e Й“en"."
  28,39,"O townitii ka leydi, kaЕӢko e koneeli makko Й—in, ko aldaa e goonga. ЖҒe cikki won'de Й“e ruttitetaako ka Amen."
  28,40,"Men nanngi mo, kaЕӢko e koneeli makko Й—in, Min mbugii Й“e ka maayo. Tasko, ko honno battane tooГұЙ“e Й“en mba'unoo."
  28,41,"Min mbaЙ—i Й“e ardiiЙ“e, noddoo Й“e e Yiite. Г‘ande Darngal, Й“e walletaake."
  28,42,"Min njokkintiniri Й“e ka aduna Й—oo, kuddi. Г‘alnde Darngal, ko Й“e jiyaaЙ“e e woЙ—Й—intinoyteeЙ“e [e yurmeende Alla]."
  28,43,"GooЕӢЙ—ii Min ngokkii Muusaa Deftere nden, Й“aawo nde Min kalkunoo gire arane Й—en, ko nde ndayginorde yimЙ“e Й“en, e peewal e yurmeende. Mbelejo'o, Й“e mbaajitorat."
  28,44,"A tawanooka ka senngo hiirnaange, fewndo Min mbahyinnoo e Muusaa yamiroore nden, a jeyanooka kadi e seediiЙ“e Й“en."
  28,45,"Kono Minen ngoni ni tagkЙ“e gire, duuЙ“i maЙ“Й“e juuti. A hoЙ—aano kadi e yimЙ“e Madyana Й“en, haЙ—a janngana Й“e Aayeeje Amen; ko Minen ngoni nulЙ“e."
  28,46,"A tawanooka ka senngo Fello Tuuri, fewndo Min noddunoo; ko yurmeende immorde ka Joomi maa [woni ko Min nulir-maa], fii no njeertiniraa yimЙ“e, Й“e reentinoowo araali e maЙ“Й“e, ado maaЙ—a, mbelejo'o, Й“e mbaajitoto."
  28,47,"Si wonaano fii yo lepte yanir e maЙ“Й“e, sabu ko juuЙ—e maЙ“Й“e ardini, Й“e wi'ayno: "Joomi amen, ko haЙ—no imminaa NulaaЙ—o e amen? Min njokka nun aayeeje Maa Й—en, men njeyee e gooЕӢЙ—imЙ“e Й“en"."
  28,48,"Nde o addirannooЙ“e goonga kan, immorde ka amen, Й“e mb'i: "Ko haЙ—no o okkee yeru ko Muusaa okkanoo kon?" Kere Й“e njeddaano ko Muusaa okkanoo kon ko adii? ЖҒe mbi'i'i: "Ko bileeji Й—iЙ—i, Й—i no wallindira!" ЖҒe mbi'i kadi: "Ko min yedduЙ“e fof e mun"."
  28,49,"Maaku: "ngadee deftere immorde ka Alla, hara hende Й“uri Й—ee Й—iЙ—i feewde, mi jokkaynde, si on laatike goongunЙ“e"."
  28,50,"Si Й“e njaabaaki ma, anndu ko mbeleeЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й“e njokkata. Ko hommbo Й“uri majjude Й“uri oon jokkirЙ—o mbeleeЙ—e mun, ko aldaa e peewal immorde ka Alla? Pellet, Alla feewnata yimЙ“e tooГұooЙ“e Й“en."
  28,51,"GooЙ—ii Min hewtinii Й“e Konngol ngol, mbelejo'o, Й“e mbaajitora."
  28,52,"ЖҒen Й“e Min ndokki Deftere [Tawreeta] nden, ko adii [Alqur'aana] ndee, ko Й“e gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e nde."
  28,53,"Si nde janngaama e dow maЙ“Й“e, Й“e mbi'a: "Min ngooЕӢЙ—inii nde. Ko nde goonga immorde ka Joomi amen. Pellet min woniino jebbiliiЙ“e, ado mayre"."
  28,54,"ЖҒeen Й—on, Й“e jonniroyte njoЙ“di maЙ“Й“e ndin, laabi Й—iЙ—i, sabu ko Й“e muГұinoo kon, heЙ“e nduГұiraynoo moЖҙЖҙere nden, bone on, e hu'unde nde Min ngarsiki Й“e nden, heЙ“e nafqa."
  28,55,"Si Й“e nanii meerente, Й“e Й—uurnoo e Й—um, Й“e mbi'a: "Ko minen golle amen ngoodani, ko onon kadi golle mon nhoodani. Kisal wonii e mo'on. Min Й—aЙ“Й“ataa wonndugol e majjuЙ“e Й“en"."
  28,56,"Pellet, an (NulaaЙ—o), a feewnata mo njiЙ—Й—aa; kono Alla no feewna on Mo O muuyi. Ko KaЕӢko Й“uri anndude feewЙ“e Й“en."
  28,57,"ЖҒe mbi'i: "Si min njokkidii peewal ngal e maa, men biftete ka leydi amen". E Min hoЙ—iniraali Й“e e nokku horminaaЙ—o, koolniiЙ—o, mo dimЙ—e noone kaka addetee e mun, arsike immorde ka Amen? Si ko woni, ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e maЙ“Й“e, Й“e nganndaa."
  28,58,"ЖҠuuЙ—ii ko Min kakli, e yimЙ“e ca'e, bewrunooЙ“e nguuree mum, e homo non galleeji maЙ“Й“e Й—in, koЙ—iraaka Й“aawo maЙ“Й“e, si wonaa seeЙ—a. Min laatii wonn'de ronooЙ“e Й“een."
  28,59,"Joomi maa siforaali won'de kalkoowo yimЙ“e ca'e, haa O immina e leГұol maЙ“Й“eЙ—en, NulaaЙ—o, ko janngana Й“e aayeeje Amen Й—en. Min siforaali kadi kalkugol yimЙ“e ca'e, si wonaa hara yimЙ“e majje ko tooГұuЙ“e."
  28,60,"Kala ko ngokkaЙ—on e hu'unde, ko dakamme nguurndam aduna e cuЙ—aari mun; ko ko woni ka Alla kon, Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude, woni kadi ko luttata. E on haqqiltaa?"
  28,61,"Eey mon Min podi fodaari moЖҙЖҙuri, ndi o hawrata e mu'un, wa'ata wa on mo Min ndakmitiri dakamme nguurndam aduna, refti hara kaЕӢko on, Г‘alnde Darngal, ko e tawneteeЙ“e (ka Yiite) Й“en o jeyaa?"
  28,62,"Г‘ande O noddoyta Й“e, O wi'a: "Ko hoЙ—o kafidaaЙ—i am, Й—in Й—i ngaaЖҙoratnoЙ—on woni?""
  28,63,"ЖҒen Й“e Konngol jojji e Mu'um wi'a: "Joomi amen, ko Й“ee ngoni ko min bewinnoo. Min bewinirno Й“e, wano men bewirnoo. Min daЙ—ndinike e MaaЙ—a. Wonaa minen Й“e ndewatnoo"."
  28,64,"[ЖҒe] mb'anee: "Noddee non kafidaaЙ—i mon Й—in". ЖҒe nodda Й—i, kono Й—i njaabotaako Й“e. ЖҒe nji'a lepte Й—en, (Й“e njeloo) sinno hara Й“e peewuno."
  28,65,"Г‘ande O noddoyta Й“e, o wi'a: "Ko holЙ—um njaabinoЙ—on NulaaЙ“e Й“en?""
  28,66,"LamitorЙ—i Й—in mbumiЙ—ana Й“e nden Гұande, Й“e lamndondirtaa."
  28,67,"Si ko tuubuЙ—o, o gooЕӢЙ—ini, o golli moЖҙЖҙuЙ—i, hino hasii ka o jeyee e malaaЙ“e Й“een."
  28,68,"Joomi maa no taga ko o muuyi, O suЙ“oo; suЙ“agol alanaa Й“e. Senaade woodanii Alla! O toowii e kon ko Й“e cirkata!"
  28,69,"Joomi maa no anndi ko Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en cuuЙ—ata, e kon ko Й“e peГұГұinta."
  28,70,"Ko KaЕӢko Alla woni, Mo deweteeЙ—o alaa, si wanaa KaЕӢko. Ko KaЕӢko jettooje nhoodani aduna e La'akara. Hino woodani Mo Гұaawoore nden. Ko ka Makko rutteteЙ—on."
  28,71,"Maaku: "njeewtee kam, Si Alla waЙ—iranii on jemma on, duumiiЙ—o haa Г‘ande Darngal, ko deweteeЙ—o hommbo, tanaa Alla, addanta on ndayngu? E on nanataa?""
  28,72,"Maaku: "njeewtee kam, Si Alla waЙ—iranii on Гұalorma on, duumiiЙ—o haa Г‘ande Darngal, ko deweteeЙ—o hommbo, tanaa Alla, addanta on jemma, mo deeЖҙoton e mun? E on nji'ataa?""
  28,73,"Hino jeyaa e yurmeende Makko, O waЙ—iranii on jemma e Гұalawma; fii no deeЖҙiron e (jemma) on, e no Й—aЙ“Й“iron ( e Гұalawma on), Й“ural makko, e no mbelajo'o njettiron [Mo] ."
  28,74,"Г‘ande O noddoyta Й“e, O wi'a: "Ko holto kadidaaЙ—i(renndidiiЙ—i) am, Й—in Й—in ngaaЖҙoratnoЙ—on ngoni?""
  28,75,"Min Й—oofi e kala mofte, seedotooЙ—o, Min mbi'a: "ngddee hujjaajji mon Й—in". ЖҒe ngnndi wonn'de goonga kan, ko Alla woodani; ko Й“e fekindotonoo kon majjitora Й“e."
  28,76,"Pellet,Qaaruuna ko e yimЙ“e Muusaa Й“en jeyanoo,kono o bewi e maЙ“Й“e.Min ngokki mo ngaluuji tawat-Й—i coktirЙ—e mum,no teddana jamaa doolnuЙ—o.Nde yimЙ“e makko Й“een,mbiatno mo:Wata a weltor townitaare.Pellet Alla yiЙ—aa weltortooЙ“e toownitaare."
  28,77,"ЖҠaЙ“Й“ir ko Alla okku-maa kon, galle laakare Й—en. Wota a yejjit geЙ—al maa ngal aduna. MoЖҙЖҙir no Alla moЖҙЖҙorii non e maaЙ—a. Wata a Й—aЙ“Й“u bonnugol ka leydi. Anndu pellet, Alla yiЙ—aa bonnooЙ“e Й“en"."
  28,78,"O wi'i: "Ko mi okkiraa Й—um, ko e hoore ganndal ngal mi jogii". E o anndaa wonn'de gooЕӢЙ—ii Alla kalkiino gire, adiiЙ“e mo, Й“urЙ“e doole, Й“uri mo Й—uuЙ—ude jawle? ЖҒe lamndoytaake fii bakkaat maЙ“Й“e, kamЙ“e bomЙ“e Й“en!"
  28,79,"O yaltitiri e yimЙ“e makko Й“en, cuЙ—aari makko ndin. YiЙ—uЙ“e nguurndam aduna Й“en mbi'i: "Hara nun min keЙ“ayno sugu koo ko Qaaruuna okkaa. KaЕӢko on, pellet, ko o jom-geЙ“al mawnungal"."
  28,80,"OkkaaЙ“e ganndal Й“en kan mbi'i: "Ee bone mon! Ko mbarjaari Alla ndin Й“uri moЖҙЖҙannde on gooЕӢЙ—inЙ—o o golli ko moЖҙЖҙi". Kono hawrataa e Й—uum, si wonaa muГұГұiiЙ“e Й“en."
  28,81,"Min mutindini mo e galle makko Й—en, ka leydi. Fedde woo alanaa mo, ko paaboo mo gaanin Alla, o wonaano paabotooЙ—o hoore-mum."
  28,82,"ЖҒen yelinooЙ“e nokku makko on haЕӢki mum, Й“e mbaЙ—ti wiide: "Ee bone! Alla no wertana arsike on, Mo O muuyani e jiyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en, O Й“iЙ—tinana [Mo O muuyani]. Si wonaa Alla moЖҙЖҙinoo e amen, O mutinayno men. Ee bone! Jaka O malnataa yedduЙ“e Й“en"."
  28,83,"ЖҠen galle laakara, Min mbaЙ—anii Й—e Й“en Й“e yiЙ—aa townitaare ka leydi, wonaa kadi bonnugol. Battane moЖҙЖҙe Й—en, ko fii gooЕӢЙ—uЙ“e Й“en."
  28,84,"Kala garduЙ—o e moЖҙЖҙere, hino woodani mo ko Й“uri nde moЖҙЖҙude; kala kadi garduЙ—o e bonannde, (yo o anndu) huuwuЙ“e bonЙ—i Й—in yoЙ“etaake, si wanaa ko Й“e huuwaynoo kon."
  28,85,"Pellet, jippinЙ—o Alqur'aana on e maaЙ—a, ko duttoo-wo ma ka woowaandi maa. Maaku: "Ko Joomi am Й“uri anndude arduЙ—o e peewal, e gonЙ—o e majjere Й“anngunde"."
  28,86,"A wonaano tamЖҙininooЙ—o jippineede deftere nden e maaЙ—a. Si wonaa tun, ko yurmeende immorde ka Joomi maa. Wota won muk, balloowo heeferЙ“e Й“en."
  28,87,"wota Й“e palo ma kadi e aayeeje Alla Й—en, Й“aawo Й—e jippineede e maaЙ—a. Noddu (yimЙ“e Й“en) fa'ade e Joomi maa, wota a won muk, jiyaaЙ—o e sirkooЙ“e Й“en."
  28,88,"Wota a rewudu e Alla, deweteeЙ—o goo. DeweteeЙ—o goo alaa, si wonaa KaЕӢko. Hu'unde fof re'ay, si wonaa Jaati Maako Kin. Ko KaЕӢko woodani Гұaawugol; ko ka Makko kadi ndtteteЙ—on."
  29,1,"Alif, laam, miim."
  29,2,"E yimЙ“e Й“en cikku Й“e ngaccirte nii, fii Й“e wi'ii: "Min ngooЕӢЙ—inii!" Hara Й“e pitninaaka?"
  29,3,"GooЕӢЙ—ii, Min pitninii Й“en adinooЙ“e Й“e. Maa Alla feГұГұin, fii gooЕӢЙ—uЙ“e Й“en, maa O feГұГұin kadi, fii fenooЙ“e Й“en."
  29,4,"Kaa golluЙ“e bonЙ—i Й“en cikku, won'nde Й“e laawoto Min? ko Й“e Гұaawata kon bonii!"
  29,5,"Kala tawЙ—o homo njortii kawroygol e Alla, ko pellet, lajal Alla ngal, ko hewtaygal. Ko KaЕӢko woni Nanoowo, nganduЙ—o on."
  29,6,"Kala kadi tiiЙ—niiЙ—o, ko hoore-makko o tiiЙ—nanii, tawde pellet, Alla ko jon'diniiЙ—o e tageefo ngon."
  29,7,"ЖҒeen non gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e, Й“e ngolli golle moЖҙЖҙe, ma Min momtan Й“e bonЙ—i maЙ“Й“e Й—in, Min njoЙ“itra Й“e, ko Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude e ko Й“e ngollatnoo kon."
  29,8,"Min njamirii neЙ—Й—aЕӢke on, moЖҙЖҙugol e mawЙ“e makko Й“en. Si Й“e ndoolii maa fii cirkangol Kam, ko a alanaa Й—um ganndal, wota a Й—ofto Й“e ! Ko ka Am, woni ruttorde mon, Mi habra on, ko ngollatno Й—on."
  29,9,"ЖҒeen gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Alla, Й“e ngolli golle moЖҙЖҙe, ma Min mbaЙ—tiduЙ“e e moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e Й“en."
  29,10,"Hino e jimЙ“e Й“en, wi'oowo: "Min ngooЕӢЙ—inii Alla"; hara non si o tampiniraama fii Alla, o waЙ—at lorra yimЙ“e Й“en, wano lepte Alla Й—en. Si ballal kadi immorii ka Joomi maa, pellet, Й“e mbi'ay: "MiЙ—en ngo'dunoo e mo'on!" Kere wonaa Alla Й“uri anndu'de ko woni e Й“erЙ—e tageefo ngon?"
  29,11,"Ma Alla anndin fii gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“en, ma O feГұГұina kadi fii naafiqiiЙ“e Й“een."
  29,12,"HeeferЙ“e Й“en wi'ani gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“en: "Jokkee laawol amen ngol, men fawtoto fii goopi mon Й—in". Kono Й“e ngonaani fawtotooЙ“e hay hu'unde e goopi maЙ“Й“e. Pellet, ko Й“e fenooЙ“e."
  29,13,"Kono maa Й“e paawtoo fii teddeendi bakkaat maЙ“Й“e Й—in, e teddeendi goo, wond'ude e teddeendi maЙ“Й“e ndin. Ko maa Й“e lamndoyee, Г‘ande Darngal, ga e kon ko Й“e fekindotonoo."
  29,14,"GooЕӢЙ—ii Min nulii Nuuhu e yimЙ“e makko Й“en, o ГұiiЙ“i hakkunde maЙ“Й“e, duuЙ“i ujunere, ЕӢakkuЙ—um duuЙ“i cappanЙ—e jowi. Waame on nanngi Й“e, hari ko Й“e tooГұЙ“e."
  29,15,"Min ndaЙ—ndi mo, kaЕӢko e yimЙ“e laana kan; Min mbaЙ—i ka kaawisa tageefo ngo."
  29,16,"(JaЕӢto) kadi Ibraahiima, nde o wi'annoo yimЙ“e makko Й“en: "ndeewee Alla, kulon Mo; ko Й—um Й“uri moЖҙЖҙann'de on, si woni hoЙ—on nganndi"."
  29,17,"Anndee ko ndewoton kon ga Alla, ko sanamuuji, hoЙ—on taЖҙa fenaande. Pellet, Й—in Й—i ndewoton ga Alla, Й—i waawaa on arsikude; Й—aЙ“Й“iree arsike on ka Alla, rewon mo, Жҙetton Mo. Ko ka makko woni rutteteЙ—on."
  29,18,"Si on njeddi i, haray mofte adinooЙ“e kadi njeddiino (NulaaЙ“e mum). Alaa ko fawii e NulaaЙ—o on, si wonaa yottingol Й“annginngol."
  29,19,"E Й“ee yiaani no Alla fuЙ—Й—orta tagoore ngum, refti o ndttat ngu? Pellet, Й—um wonii ko newanii Alla."
  29,20,"Maaku: "Yiilee ka leydi, ndaaron no O puЙ—Й—ori tagoore. refti Alla tagoore sakkitoru ngum. Pellet, Alla ko kattanЙ—o kala hu'unde"."
  29,21,"Homo lepte mo o muuyani, o yurmo mo O muuyani; ko ka makko rutteteЙ—on."
  29,22,"On wonaani laawotooЙ“e ka leydi, wonaa ka kammu; alanaa on ga Alla, woni giЙ—o, wanaa ballo."
  29,23,"ЖҒeen yedduЙ“e aayeeje Alla Й—en, e hawroygol e makko ngol, Й“en taЖҙike e yurmeende Am, Й“en Й—on, hono woodani Й“e lepte mu'usuЙ—e."
  29,24,"Jaabawol yimЙ“e makko Й“en wonaano, si wonaa wiide Й“e: "Waree mo, maa sunnon mo". Kono Alla daЙ—ndi mo e yiite ngen. Pellet, wonii e Й—um, Ma'andeeji, wonan'de yimЙ“e gooЕӢЙ—imЙ“e."
  29,25,"O maaki: "nganndee ko ndewoton kon ga Alla, ko sanamuuji, fii yiЙ—indiro hakkunde mon, ka nguurndam aduna, hooti non, Г‘ande Darndal, yoga mon yeddoyay yoga, yoga mon kadi huЙ—o yoga, hara non, jaaЖҙorde mon nden, ko ka Yiite, hara wallooЙ“e alanaa on"."
  29,26,"Luutu gooЕӢЙ—ini mo. O maaki: "Min on, ko mi feroowo ka Joomi am, ko KaЕӢko woni FooluЙ—o, Г‘eeГұo On"."
  29,27,"Min njeЙ—i mo Ismaa'iila e Yaaquuba, Min mbaЙ—i e geГұngol makko ngol, Annabaaku e Daftere. Min ngokki mo mbarjaari makko ndin aduna, pellet, kaЕӢo on ka La'akara, ko o jeyaaЙ—o e moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e Й“en."
  29,28,"(JaЕӢto) kadi luutu, nde o maakannoo yimЙ“e makko Й“en : " E on aray e paЕӢkare, Й—e gooto e winndere nden adaaki on e mun?"
  29,29,"E on aray jottagol e worЙ“e Й“en? paloЙ—on kadi e laawol? Ngollaton ko mbatirdu mon ko aГұinii?" Kono jaabawol yimЙ“e makko Й“een wonaano, si wonaa wiide Й“e: "Addan men lepte Alla Й—en, si tawii ko a jeyaaЙ—o e gooЕӢЙ—uЙ“e Й“een"."
  29,30,"O maaki: "Joomi am, wallam e hoore yimЙ“e bonnooЙ“e Й“een"."
  29,31,"Tuma nde ImminaaЙ“e Amen Й“en addannoo Ibraahiima welo-welo ngon, Й“e mb"i: "Minen, ko men halkooЙ“ee yimЙ“e ndee saare. Tawde pellet, yimЙ“e mayre laatike tooГұooЙ“e"."
  29,32,"O maaki: "Kono Luutu no ton!" ЖҒe mbi'i: "Ko minen Й“uri anndude fii won'Й“e ton. Ko ma men daЙ—ndu mo, kaЕӢko e yimЙ“e makko Й“en, si wonaa debbo makko on, o jeyaama e helketeeЙ“e Й“een"."
  29,33,"Tum nde imminaaЙ“e Amen Й“en keewtunoo ka Luutu, o saЙ—tiraa fii maЙ“Й“e, Й“ernde makko Й“iЙ—torii fii maЙ“Й“e. ЖҒe mbi'i: "Wota a hul, wota a suno. Ko men daЙ—ndooЙ“e ma an e Й“eynguure maa nde, si wonaa debbo maa on, o jeyaama e halkaaЙ“e Й“en."
  29,34,"Ko moen njippinooЙ“e lepte e yimЙ“e ndee saare, immorde ka kammu, sabu ko Й“e yaltunoo e Й—oftaare kon"."
  29,35,"GooЕӢЙ—ii Min ngaccii e nden (saare), Ma'ande Й“anngunde, wonan'de yimЙ“e haqqilooЙ“e Й“een."
  29,36,"(Min nuli) kadi e Madyana, musiЙ—Й—o maЙ“Й“e on, Shu'aybu. O maaki: "Ko onon yo yimЙ“e am, ndewee Alla, jortoron Г‘alannde sakkitiinde nden, wota woniri e leydi ndin, bonnooЙ“e"."
  29,37,"Kono Й“e njeddi i mo. Dillannde nden nanngi Й“e, Й“e waЙ—tini ka koЙ—ooli maЙ“Й“e, ko Й“e jicciiЙ“e-maayi."
  29,38,"(Meon kalki) kadi Aadi'en, e Saamuda'en. GooЕӢЙ—ii caambbeje maЙ“Й“e Й—in Й“annganii on. Seytaane cuЙ—inani Й“e, golle maЙ“Й“e Й—en, ndu sakkii Й“e e laawol ngol; tawi le, ko Й“e reentunooЙ“e."
  29,39,"(Min kalki) kadi Qaaruuna, e Fir'awna e Haamaana. GooЕӢЙ—ii le, Muusaa addanii Й“e Й“anngannduyeeji, kono Й“e toownitii ka leydi, Й“e wonaano laawotooЙ“e."
  29,40,"Kala maЙ“Й“e, Min leptirno bakkaatuuji mum Й—in: no e maЙ“Й“e, Й“e Min ngurti henndu e mum; no e maЙ“Й“e, Й“e haacaango kalki; no e maЙ“Й“e, mo Min mutini Й—um ka leydi, no e maЙ“Й“e kadi, Й“e Min yoolunoo. Kono non, Alla siforaali tooГұoowo Й“e; si ko woni, ko kamЙ“e tooГұuoo ko'e maЙ“Й“e."
  29,41,"Misal Й“en jogitiiЙ“e ga Alla deweteeЙ—i, ko wano marijaawowal(njomblo) saccungal suudu. Ko Й“uri lo'ode non e cuuЙ—i Й—in, ko suudu marijaawo. Sinno Й“e annduno!"
  29,42,"Pellet, Alla no anndi kala hu'unde nde Й“e noddata ga makko. Ko KaЕӢko woni FoolЙ—o, Г‘eeГұo On."
  29,43,"ЖҠii ko yeruuji Й—e Min piyanta yimЙ“e Й“en; ko woni tun, paamataa Й—en, si wonaa annduЙ“e Й“en."
  29,44,"Alla tagirii kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin, e hoore goonga. Pellet, wonii Й—um, Ma'ande, wonan'de gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“en."
  29,45,"Janngu Й—um ko waayinaa e maaЙ—a ka deftere, ГұiiЙ“aa e juulde nden. Pellet, juulde nden no haЙ—a paЕӢkare e ko aГұinii. Ko jantagol Alla ngol Й“uri (hu'unde kala) mawnude. Alla no anndi ko ngolloton kon."
  29,46,"Wota on weeГұir yimЙ“e defte Й“en si wonaa e no Й“uri e moЖҙЖҙirde, si wonaa hara ko Й“en tooГұЙ“e e maЙ“Й“e. Mbi'on: "Min ngooЕӢЙ—inii nden njippinaande e amen e Й—en njippinaaЙ—e e mon. DeweteeЙ—o amen On e deweteeЙ—o mon On ko gooto, menen non, ko Min jebbilanii Й“e Mo"."
  29,47,"Ko wano non Min njippiniri e maaЙ—a Deftere nden. ЖҒeen Й“e Min ngokki Deftere nden, heЙ“e mgooЕӢЙ—ini nde. Hino e maЙ“Й“e on gooЕӢЙ—inЙ—o nde. Yeddataa Aayeeje Amen Й—en, si wonaa heeferЙ“e Й“en."
  29,48,"A wonaano haЙ—a janngatnoo deftere ado mayre, a winndirtaano Гұaamo maa ngon. Harayno, bonnooЙ“e Й“en cikkittono."
  29,49,"Si ko woni, ko nde Aayeeje Й“annguЙ—e e Й“erЙ—e Й“en okkaaЙ“e ganndal. Yeddataa aayeeje Amen Й—en, si wonaa tooГұЙ“e Й“een."
  29,50,"ЖҒe mb'i: "Hanno jippinee e makko Ma'andeeji immorde ka Joomi makko?" Maaku: "aayaaji ko joomam addata, anndee min, ko mi jeertinoowo Й“annguЙ—o"."
  29,51,"Kere yonaani Й“e won'de Min njippinii e maaЙ—a deftere nden hende janngee e maЙ“Й“e? Wonii e Й—uum, yurmeende e waaju wonan'de yimЙ“e gooЕӢЙ—inooЙ“e."
  29,52,"Maaku: "Alla yonii hakkunde am e mooЙ—on seedee Hino anndi ko woni kon ka kammuuli e ka leydi. ЖҒen non gooЕӢЙ—imЙ“e meere nden Й“e yeddi Alla, ko Й“en ngoni oni sooyЙ“e Й“en."
  29,53,"HeЙ“e kawjirane lepte Й—en. Si wonaano fii lajal innaangal, lepte Й—en ngardiratno e maЙ“Й“e juhal, hara kamЙ“e Й“e so'aa-anndude."
  29,54,"HeЙ“e lawjirane lepte Й—en, hara non pellet, Jahannama ko fiiltiinge heefereЙ“e Й“een."
  29,55,"Г‘ande lepte Й—en suddiroyta Й“e senngo dow maЙ“Й“e e ka ley koyЙ—e maЙ“Й“e, O daala[na Й“e]: "MeeЙ—ee ko ngollatnoЙ—on kon!""
  29,56,"Eey mon jiyaaЙ“e Am gooЙ—inЙ“e! Nganndee leydi Am ndin ko yaajundi. Ko Min ngoni ko ndewoton!"
  29,57,"Kala woЕӢkii meeЙ—ay maayde. refti ko ka Amen ndutteteЙ—on."
  29,58,"ЖҒeen gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“e ngolli golle moЖҙЖҙe, ma Min koЙ—nu Й“e ka Aljanna e cuuЙ—i Й—i canЙ—i ilata senngo ley majji, koЙ“e duumotooЙ“e ton. Iskin(heskey)В° moЖҙЖҙere njoЙ“di gollunooЙ“e,"
  29,59,"Й“een muГұГұiiЙ“e, Й“e tuugii e Joomi maЙ“Й“e."
  29,60,"Heewii e ruugatЙ—i Й—i yooЙ“otaako arsike majji! Ko Alla arsikata Й—i wond'ude e onon. Ko KaЕӢko woni Nanoowo, gannduЙ—o."
  29,61,"Pellet, si a laЙ“ndiima Й“e: "Ko hommbo tagi kammuu- li Й—iin e leydi ndin, O elti na'ange nge e lewru ndu?" Ma Й“e mbi'u: "Ko Alla". Ko holno Й“e ferlitoraa (e gooЕӢЙ—ingol ngol)?"
  29,62,"Alla no yaacnana arsike on mo o muuyi e jiyaaЙ“e makko Й“en, Homo Й“ittana mo. Pellet, Alla ko gannduЙ—o kala hu'unde."
  29,63,"Pellet, si a lanndike Й“e: "Ko hommbo jippiniri ndiyam ka kammu Й—am O wuurnitiri leydi ndin Й“aawo ndi yoorde?", ma Й“e mbi': "Ko Alla". Maaku: "Yettoore woodanii Alla!". Si ko woni, ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e maЙ“Й“e kaqqiltaa."
  29,64,"ЖҠam nguurndam aduna wonaani, si wonaa mbeleeЙ—e e fijindaaru. Pellet, ko hoЙ—o La'akara ngon woni nguurandam. Sinno Й“e annduno."
  29,65,"Si Й“e waЙ—Й—ike ka laana, Й“e nodda Alla Й“e laЙ“Й“inano mo noddaandu ndun. Tuma nde o daЙ—ndi Й“e ka njoorndi, on tuma Й“e cirka."
  29,66,"No Й“e yeddira ko Min ngokki Й“e kon, awa yo Й“e dakmito! Aray kaЙ“e ngannda."
  29,67,"E Й“ee nji'aani won'de Min mbaЙ—ii hormorde hoolniinde, yimЙ“e Й“en no ci'ifee(mbifte) bannge maЙ“Й“e? E ko meere nden Й“e ngooЕӢЙ—inta Й“e njedda neemaaji Alla Й—in?"
  29,68,"E ko hommbo Й“uri tooГұide wa on pekondiiЙ—o fenaande e hoore Alla, maa o fenni goonga kan nde ka arnoo e makko? E wonaa ka Jahannama woni jaaЖҙorde yedduЙ“e Й“en?"
  29,69,"ЖҒeen tiiЙ—norЙ“e e (weltingol) Min, ma Min peewnirЙ“e e laawi Amen, ko pellet, Alla no won'di e moЖҙЖҙinooЙ“e Й“een."
  30,1,"Alif, laam, miim."
  30,2,"RuumiyaЕӢkooЙ“e Й“een poolaama,"
  30,3,"ka Й“uri Й“adaade e lesdi ndin, kamЙ“e kadi Й“aawo Й“e poola, Й“e fooloyooЙ“e,"
  30,4,"e ndeer duuЙ“i seeЙ—aaji. Ko Alla woodani fiyaaku (poolal ngal) ado e Й“aawo (maggal). Nden Гұalaande, gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“en mbeltota."
  30,5,"ballal Alla ngal. Homo walla mo O muuyi. Ko KaЕӢko woni pooloowo, jurmotooЙ—o."
  30,6,"[ЖҠuum] ko fodoore Alla. Alla luutndotaako fodoore makko nden. Kono ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e yimЙ“e Й“en Й“e nganndaa."
  30,7,"HeЙ“e nganndi ko feeГұi e nguurndam aduna, kono kamЙ“e e fii La'akara on, ko Й“e welsindiiЙ“e."
  30,8,"E Й“ee miijitaaki fii ko'e-maЙ“Й“e? Alla tagiraali kammuuji Й—in e lesdi ndin e ko woni hakkunde Й—in Й—iЙ—i, si wonaa goonga e lajal innaangal. Nganndee ko Й—uuЙ—i e yimЙ“e Й“een, ko yedduЙ“e kawroygol e Joomi maЙ“Й“e."
  30,9,"E Й“ee njillaani ka leydi Й“e taskoo ko honno battane Й“een adinooЙ“e Й“e mbi'noo? ЖҒeen ngonno Й“urЙ“e Й“e doole Й“e remi e leydi ndin Й“e nguuri e mayri Й“uri ko Й“ee nguuri e mayri kon. NulaaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en addani Й“e Й“anngannduyeeji. Alla wonaani tooГұoowo Й“e, kono non ko ko'e maЙ“Й“e Й“e ngonno e tooГұude."
  30,10,"Refti ko wonunoo battane bonnuЙ“e Й“en, ko bonan'nde fii Й“e njeddii Aayeeje Alla Й—en, Й“e laatii e jalkitgol Й—e."
  30,11,"Ko Alla fuЙ—Й—i tagoore nde; refti o rutta nde; refti ko ka makko rutteteЙ—on."
  30,12,"Г‘ande Darnga ngal darii, bonЙ“e Й“en taЖҙoto."
  30,13,"WoodantaaЙ“e e kafidiiЙ—i maЙ“Й“e Й—in tefooji, Й“e ngoniino yedduЙ“e kafiduЙ“e Й“e."
  30,14,"Г‘ande Darnga ngal darii,nden Гұande Й“e ceertoyat."
  30,15,"Si ko Й“en gooЕӢЙ—imЙ“e Й“e ngolli golle moЖҙЖҙe, Й“en Й—on ngonoyat e beeli (Aljanna) heЙ“e caЙ—nee(mbeltine)."
  30,16,"Si tawii non ko Й“en yedduЙ“e Й“e njeddi aayeeje amen Й—en e kawrugol ngol e La'akara, Й“en Й—on ko tawnoyteeЙ“e e lepte Й—en."
  30,17,"Cubbunhinanee Alla, tuma kiiroton e tuma mbeetoton."
  30,18,"Ko KaЕӢko jettooje ngoodani ka kammuuji e ka leydi, e kiikiiЙ—e e saaga Гұalloton."
  30,19,"Homo yaltina ko wuuri e nder ko maayi, o yaltina kadi ko maayi e ndeer ko wuuri. Homo wuurnita leydi ndin Й“aawo ndi yoorde. Ko wano non yatainirte- Й—on (e genaale mon)."
  30,20,"Hino jeyaa e Ma'andeeji makko Й—in: won'de O tagii on immorde e mbum-mbuldi, refti jaka ko on Й“anndiЕӢke sa'akotooЙ“e [e leydi ndin]."
  30,21,"Hino jeyaa e Ma'andeeji makko Й—in : won'de O tagiranii on e woЕӢkiiji mon Й—in, resondirЙ“e, fii yo on ndeeЖҙ e maЙ“Й“e, O waЙ—i hakkunde mon giggol e yumeende. Wonii e Й—uum, Ma'andeeji wonan'de yimЙ“e miijitotooЙ“e."
  30,22,"Hino jeyaa e Ma'andeeji makko Й—in: tagugol kammuuji Й—in e leydi ndin, e luutondirgol Й—emЙ—e mon e mbaadiiji mon. Wonii e Й—uum, Ma'andeeji anduЙ“e Й“een."
  30,23,"Hino jeyaa e Ma'andeeji makko Й—in: Й—oyngol mon ngol jemma e Гұalawma, e Й—aЙ“Й“ugol mon Й“ural makko. Wonii e Й—um, Ma'andeeji wonan'de yimЙ“e nanooЙ“e."
  30,24,"Hino jeyaa e Ma'andeeji makko Й—in: Homo hollira on maje Й—een kulol e tama'u (toЙ“o), Homo jippinira ka kammu ndiyam, O wuurnitira Й—am leydi ndin Й“aawo ndi yo'orude. Wonii e Й—um, Ma'andeeji, wonan'de yimЙ“e haqqilooЙ“e."
  30,25,"Hino jeyaa e Ma'andeeji makko Й—in: nde kammu ngun e leydi ndin daroto e yamiroore makko. Refti si O noddii on noddaandu ka leydi, e jaka onon hoЙ—on yalta (e genaale mon)."
  30,26,"Hino Й—um woodani (Laamu, e takgoll e toppitagol) Й“een wonЙ“e ka kammuuji e ka lesdi: kala maЙ“Й“e ko Й—oftiiЙ“e mo."
  30,27,"Ko KaЕӢko woni puЙ—Й—uЙ—o tagoore, refti O ruttita nde; ko Й—uum Й“uri newanaande mo. Homo woodani sifa Й“urЙ—o toowude ka kammuuji e ka leydi. Ko KaЕӢko woni on poolЙ—o, Г‘eeГұЙ—o on."
  30,28,"O piyanii on yeru immorde e ko'e-mon: hara no woodani on e Й“en Й“e njeyruЙ—on Гұaame mon, immorde e kafidal e kon ko min arsiki on, hara hoЙ—on pota e Й—uum, hoЙ—on kulira Й“e wano kulirton ko'e-mon? Ko woni nii Min pensitirta Aayeeje Й—en, wonan'de yimЙ“e haqqilooЙ“e."
  30,29,"Si ko woni, tooГұЙ“e Й“en njokkirii beleeЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en ko aldaa e ganndal. Ko hommbo feewnata mo Alla majjini? Alanaa Й“e wallooЙ“e."
  30,30,"Feewtinir yeeso maa ngon e diina kan ГұiiЙ“ugol [e mun]. [ЖҠuum] ko tagoore Alla ngu O tagiri yimЙ“e Й“en e mum - waЙ—titugol alaa e tagoore Alla nde -. Ko Й—uum woni diina focciika kan; kono Й“urЙ“e Й—uuЙ—ude e yimЙ“e Й“en nganndaa."
  30,31,"Hara ko on ruttotooЙ“e e makko; kulon Mo, Гұinnon juulde nden, wota on njeye e sirkooЙ“e Й“en."
  30,32,"(wano) Й“eya senndunooЙ“e diina mum kan, Й“e woni pecce-pecce, kala fedde no weltora ko woni ka mum kon."
  30,33,"Si saЙ—teende memii yimЙ“e Й“een, Й“e noddira Joomi maЙ“Й“e ko Й“e ruttitiiЙ“e e makko; refti si o meeЙ—inii Й“e yumeende immorde e makko, e jaka fedde goo e maЙ“Й“e no kafida e Joomi mun,"
  30,34,"YoЙ“e yeddu ko min ngokki Й“e kon. "Awa dakmitee, arma nganndon"."
  30,35,"Kaa Min njippin e maЙ“Й“e hujja (Deftere), hara honde yeewta fii ko Й“e cirkatnoo kon?"
  30,36,"Si Min meeЙ—inirii yimЙ“e Й“en neema, Й“e weltoroo mo. Si bone memirii Й“e sabu ko juuЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en ardiniri kon, e jaka heЙ“e taЖҙoo."
  30,37,"E Й“e nkiaani won'de Alla no yaacnana arsike on mo o muuyani, O Й“illina? Wonii e Й—uum, Ma'andeeji wonan'de yimЙ“e gooЕӢЙ—inooЙ“e."
  30,38,"Jonnu jom-Й“adiido o hakke makko on, e Й“illiiЙ“e e Й“ii-laawol. ЖҠuum Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude wonan'de Й“een faalaaЙ“e yarluyee Alla on; ko Й“een ngoni maloyteeЙ“e Й“en."
  30,39,"Kala ko njonnuЙ—on e riba, fii on Й“eydor e jawЙ—e yimЙ“e Й“en, Й—uum Й“eydotaako ka Alla, kala non ko ngokkuЙ—on e Jakka, mo faandoriЙ—on welayee Alla, Й“en Й—on, ko sowanoyteeЙ“e [njoЙ“di] Й“een."
  30,40,"Ko Alla woni takЙ—o on, refti o arsiki on, refti o wara on, refti o wuurnita on. Hara no e kafidaaЙ—i mon Й—in waЙ—ayЙ—i goЙ—Й—um e Й—um? Senayeewoo-dani Mo! O toowii e kon ko Й“e cirkata."
  30,41,"Bone on feeГұiri ka njoorndi e ka maaje, sabu ko juuЙ—e yimЙ“e Й“en faggitii kon; fii yo O meeЙ—in Й“e yoga e ko Й“e ngolli; mbelajo'o, Й“e nduttoto."
  30,42,"Maaku: "Yiilee ka leydi, ndaaron ko honno battane adinooЙ“e Й“en wa'anoo. Tawno ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e maЙ“Й“e ko sirkooЙ“e"."
  30,43,"Feewtinir ye'eso maa ngon e diina po'occiiЙ—a kan, ado Гұalaande arde immorde ka Alla nde ruttetaake. Nde Гұalnde, Й“e seeday:"
  30,44,"Kala jedduЙ—o, haray geddi makko Й—in no fawii mo. Kala non golluЙ—o moЖҙЖҙere, haray ko ko'e-maЙ“Й“e Й“e kebilani (Aljanna),"
  30,45,"fii yo O yoЙ“ Й“een gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“e ngolli moЖҙЖҙuЙ—i, e Й“ural makko ngal. KaЕӢko On, O yiЙ—aa he'eferЙ“e Й“en."
  30,46,"Hino jeyaa e Ma'andeeji makko Й—in: Wurtugol Mo keneeli Й—in wewlinooji, e fii yo O meeЙ—in on e yurmeende makko nden, e no laaЙ—e Й—en dogira e yamiroore makko, e fii yo o Й—aЙ“Й“u e Й“ural makko. Mbelajo'o, on njettat[Mo]."
  30,47,"GooЕӢЙ—ii Min nulii ado maaЙ—a NulaaЙ“e haa e yimЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en, Й“e addani Й“e Й“anngannduyeeji. Min njottii e Й“en bonnuЙ“e; tawi no jojji e Amen paabagol gooЕӢЙ—iiЙ“e Й“en."
  30,48,"Ko Alla woni nuloowo keneeЙ—i Й—in, Й—i cogga duule Й—en; O saakitira Й—uum ka weeyo no o yiЙ—iri; O waЙ—ta Й—uum taЖҙe-taЖҙe. A yi'ay toЙ“o ngon no yalta hakkude mun. Si O heewtinii ngo e on mo o muuyi e jeyaaЙ“e makko Й“en, e jaka kamЙ“e heЙ“e weltoo."
  30,49,"GooЕӢЙ—ii Й“e laatinoke ado (toЙ“o) ngon jippineede e maЙ“Й“e, ko taЖҙinooЙ“e."
  30,50,"Ndaarii e battane yurmeende Alla nden, no o wuurnitorta leydi Й“aawo ndi yoorude. Pellet, waЙ—oowo Й—uum On, ko guurnitoowo maayЙ“e Й“en, KaЕӢko Ko O kattanЙ—o kala hu'unde."
  30,51,"[Hay] si Min nulii henndu, Й“e yi'i [gese maЙ“Й“e] Й—en no soyЙ—i, Й“e njokkay Й“aawo Й—uum, heЙ“e njedda."
  30,52,"Pellet, an a nanintaa maayЙ“e Й“en, a nanintaa fa'aЙ—uЙ“e Й“een kadi noddaandu ndun, si Й“e nduЕӢtiima Й“e huccinii Й“abbe (maЙ“Й“e)."
  30,53,"A wonaani pewnoowo wumЙ“e Й“en e majjere maЙ“Й“e. A nanintaa si wonaa Й“een gooЕӢЙ—imЙ“e Aayeeje Amen Й—en, hara ko Й“e jebbiliiЙ“e."
  30,54,"Ko Alla woni takЙ—o on e lo'ere, refti O waЙ—i Й“aawo lo'ere nde semmbe, refti o waЙ—i Й“aawo cemmbe Й—en lo'ere e puri(dandanndi). Homo taga ko O muuyi, Ko KaЕӢko woni gannduЙ—o, kattanЙ—o."
  30,55,"Г‘ande Darngal nal darotoo, bonЙ“e Й“en ngooЙ—ndat Й“e ГұiiЙ“aani si wonaa saanga. Ko wano nii Й“e wonanoo ferliseede (e goonga)."
  30,56,"OkkaaЙ“e ganndal e gooЕӢЙ—inal Й“een mbi'a: "GooЕӢЙ—ii on ГұiiЙ“ii e ko Alla winndi kon, haa Гұande ummital. Ko ndee woni Гұalaande ummital, kono onon on nganndaano"."
  30,57,"Nden Гұande, ngantooji Й—in nafoytaa tooГұuЙ“e Й“een, wonaa kamЙ“e woni ko Й—aЙ“Й“iretee welayee [Alla]."
  30,58,"GooЕӢЙ—ii Min piyanii yimЙ“e Й“en e nde Alquraanaa- re, kala misal. Pellet, si a addanii Й“e Aaya, Й“en yedduЙ“e mbi'at: "On ngonaani, si wonaa meerenteeЙ“e"."
  30,59,"Ko wano nii Alla notira e Й“erЙ—e Й“e Й“e nganndaa."
  30,60,"MuГұГұo, pellet, fodoore Alla nden, ko goonga. Wota Й“e njananaaka Й“e koyfine."
  31,1,"Alif, laam, miim."
  31,2,"ЖҠee, ko aayeeje deftere ГұeГұaande nde."
  31,3,"Ko nde peewal e yurmeende wonan'de moЖҙЖҙinooЙ“e Й“e,"
  31,4,"Й“een ГұiiЙ“nooЙ“e juulde nden, Й“e totta askal on, hara kamЙ“e ko Й“e yananaaЙ“e (fii La'akara)."
  31,5,"Ko Й“een ngoni e peewal immorde e Joomi maЙ“Й“e Й“e, ko kamЙ“e ngoni malaaЙ“e Й“en."
  31,6,"Hino woodi e yimЙ“e Й“en, soodiroowo mbeleeЙ—e konnguЙ—i haa o majjira e laawol Alla ngol ko aldaa e ganndal, o jogitora (aayeeje) Й—en jalnitgol. Й“een Й—on, hino woodani Й“e lepte koynooje."
  31,7,"Si aayeeje Amen Й—en njanngaama e makko, o huccitira(runtora) townitaare, wa si tawii o nanaani Й—e, wa si tawii ko pahu woni e noppi makko. weltanir-mo lepte mu'usЙ—e."
  31,8,"Pellet, Й“en gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“e golli moЖҙЖҙi Й—in, hino woodani Й“e Aljannaaji neema."
  31,9,"Ko Й“e duumotooЙ“e ton, Й—uum ko fodoore Alla goongunde. Ko KaЕӢko woni On poolЙ—o, Г‘eeГұЙ—o."
  31,10,"O tagirii kammuuji Й—in ko aldaa e tugaale, Й—e nji'oton; o wernii ka leydi pelle fii wota ndi dillidu e mon; o saaki e mayri kala ruugayngel. Min njippiniri ndiyam ka kammu, Min puЙ—ini e mayri kala nooneeji tedduЙ—i."
  31,11,""ЖҠuum Й—oo ko tagoore Alla. Kollee Kam ko Й—i (ndewoton Й—in) ga Makko tagi?" Si ko woni, tooГұЙ“e Й“een no e majjere Й“anngunde."
  31,12,"GooЕӢЙ—ii Min ngokkii Luqmaan ГұenЖҙal: "Won'de yettu Alla. Kala jettuЙ—o, haray ko hoore-makko o yettani; kala noon jedduЙ—o, anndu pellet, Alla ko Galo, jettiniiЙ—o"."
  31,13,"JaЕӢto tuma Luqmaana wi'annoo geЙ—al makko on, hari homo waajoo mo: "Ko an Й“inngel am, wota a sirkan Alla. Pellet, sirku on ko tooГұe mawЙ—e"."
  31,14,"Min njamirii neЙ—Й—aЕӢke on [Й—oftagol] jibinЙ“e mo Й“en; yumma makko saawirii mo lo'ere e hoore lo'ere: entugol mo ngol, ko e ndeer duuЙ“i Й—iЙ—i. "Won'de yettam e jipnaaЙ“e maa Й“en. Ko ka am woni waЙ—tinirde nden"."
  31,15,"Si Й“e tiiЙ—norii ma fii cirkangol Kam e ko a alanaa Й—um ganndal, wota a Й—ofto Й“e; won'ndir e maЙ“Й“e ka aduna Й—oo moЖҙЖҙere. Jokku laawol on duttiiЙ—o e am. Refti ko ka Am woni ruttorde mon, mi yeetitoo on, ko ngollatnoЙ—on."
  31,16,""eeyma Й“inngel am, anndu Й—e [golle bonЙ—e maa moЖҙЖҙe], si fotii wa abbere, immorde e nenndi foГұГұe, Й—um wona e fetere, maa ka kammuuji maa ka leydi, Alla artirat nde. Pellet, Alla ko NewiiЙ—o, kumpitiiЙ—o."
  31,17,"Eey ma Й“inngel am, ГұiiЙ“nu juulde nden, yamiraa moЖҙЖҙere, haЙ—aa ЕӢiГұere(pankare), muГұГұo-Й—aa e ko heЙ“u-maa. Pellet, Й—um ko jeyaaЙ—um e fiyakkuji mawЙ—i."
  31,18,"Wota fal yimЙ“e Й“en ye'eso maa ngon, wota a yahru ka leydi ГұaaЖҙagol. Pellet, Alla yiЙ—aa kala ГұaaЖҙotooЙ—o mantoo."
  31,19,"Hakindo e yahdu-maa ndun, joltinaa(ustu) hito maa ngon; ko Й“uri aГұeede e hitooji Й—in, pellet, ko lu'ukaadu bamЙ—i."
  31,20,"E on nji'aani won'de Alla eeltanii on ko woni kon ka kammuuji e ka leydi? O huuЙ“itiri on neemaaji makko peeГұuЙ—i e suuЙ—iiЙ—i. Hino woodi e yimЙ“e Й“en, on wennjiroowo e fii Alla, ko aldaa e gannndal, wonaa peewal, wonaa Deftere jalbunde."
  31,21,"Si Й“e mbianaa:"njokkee kon ko Allah Jippini", Й“e mbi'a: "Si ko woni, min njokkay ko men tawri kon baabiraaЙ“e amen Й“en"; e hay si tawii seytaane wonii hino nodda Й“e e lepte dulboowe ngen!"
  31,22,"Kala jebbilЙ—o ye'eso mun ngon fa'ade e Alla, hara ko o moЖҙЖҙinЙ—o, gooЕӢЙ—ii o jaggiima e Й“oggol tiiЙ—ungol. Ko ka Alla woni battane fiyakuuji Й—in."
  31,23,"Kala kedduЙ—o, wota ke'eferaaku makko sunine. Ko ka amen woni ruttorde maЙ“Й“e, Min kumpita Й“e ko Й“e ngollatnoo noo. Pellet, Alla ko gannduЙ—o jaati Й“erЙ—e."
  31,24,"Min ndakmitat Й“e seeЙ—a, refti Min forsaЙ“e e lepte tekkuЙ—e."
  31,25,"Pellet, si a lamndike Й“e : "Ko hommbo tagi kammuuji Й—in e leydi ndin?" Ma Й“e mbi'i'u: "Ko Alla!" Maaku: "Jettooje ngoodanii Alla!". Kono ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e maЙ“Й“e nganndaa."
  31,26,"Ko Alla woodani kala ko woni kammuuji e ka leydi. Pellet, Alla, ko KaЕӢko woni Galo, jettiniiЙ—o."
  31,27,"Hay si tawii ko woni ka hoore leydi kon e leЙ—Й—e, [settiraama] karambi, maayo ngo Й“eydora (wontugol ndaha) Й“aawo Й—uum, yeru maaje jeeЙ—iЙ—i, konnguЙ—i Alla Й—in lannataa. Pellet, Alla ko poolЙ—o, Г‘eeГұЙ—o."
  31,28,"Tagugol on e immintingol wonaani, si wonaa wa (takgol) woЕӢkii gooti. Pellet, Alla ko Nanoowo, ji'oowo."
  31,29,"E a yiaani won'de Alla no naatna jemma on e ndeer Гұalawra on, O naatna Гұalawma kadi e ndeer jemma on, O eltii kadi na'ange ngen e lewru ndun, kala majji no doga haa e lajal innaangal? E won'de Alla ko kumpitiiЙ—o ko ngolloton kon."
  31,30,"ЖҠuum [ko jaЕӢtaa Й—oo], ko tawde pellet, Alla ko KaЕӢko woni Goonga, e won'de kon ko Й“e noddata ga makko, ko Й—uum woni mehre nden, e won'de ko Alla woni ToowЙ—o, MawnЙ—o On."
  31,31,"E a yiaani won'de laaЙ—e Й—en heЙ—e ndogira ka maayo e neema Alla, fii yo O hollu on maandeeji makko Й—in? Wonii e Й—uum, maandeeji, wonan'de kala keewuЙ—o-muГұal, jettoowo (neema)."
  31,32,"Si tawii morlooЙ—e(bempejje) kippiriiЙ“e wa duule [maa pelle], Й“e noddat Alla, hara heЙ“e laЙ“Й“inani mo dewal; tuma nde o daЙ—ndunooЙ“e ka njoorndi, tawi no e maЙ“Й“e kakindiiЙ—o. Jeddataa Aayeeje Amen Й—en, si wonaa kala keewЙ—o janfa, ke'efeera."
  31,33,"Eey mon yo yimЙ“e! Kulee Joomi mon, kulon Гұaaande, nde baaba duncanoytaa Й“iЙ—Й—o mun, wonaa Й“iЙ—Й—o on kadi duncanoyta ben mun hay hu'unde. Pellet, fodoore Alla nden ko goonga. Wota nguurndam aduna hodu on, wata hodu on e Alla, (seytaane) kodoowo!"
  31,34,"Pellet, ko ka Alla woni anndal Darngal, Homo jippina toЙ“o; Homo anndi ko woni ka ndeer renngaaji. Wo'kii (woo) anndaa ko ki faggitoto janngo, woЕӢkii (woo) kadi anndaa ko e leydi honndi maayata. Pellet, Alla ko gannduЙ—o, kumpitiiЙ—o."
  32,1,"Alif, laam, miim."
  32,2,"Jippineede deftere nden, sikke woo alaa e Mu'um, ko immorde ka JeyЙ—o winndere nden."
  32,3,"Walla Й“e mb'ay kaЕӢko (Muhammadu) o fekindi nde? Si ko woni, ko nde goongaare, immorde ka Joomi maa, fii yo a jerrtin yimЙ“e, Й“e jeertinoowo araano e mum ado maaЙ—a, mbelajo'o, Й“e peeway."
  32,4,"Ko Alla woni takЙ—o kammuuji Й—in e leydi ndin, e kon ko woni hakkunde majji, e nder balЙ—e je'egoo. refti O fotondiri ka dow "Arski". Alanaa on gaanin makko, giЙ—o wonaa tefoowo. E on mbaajitotaako?"
  32,5,"Homo fewja fiyaakuuji Й—in ka kammu haa ka leydi, refti Й—i Жҙeenga ka makko, e Гұalaande nde emmbere mum woni, duuЙ“i ujunere e ko limoton."
  32,6,"On [fewjoowo fii Й—um on], ko gannduЙ—o wirniiЙ—i e feeГұuЙ—i, pooluЙ—o, jurmotooЙ—o."
  32,7,"Oon labinЙ—o kala hu'unde nde o tagi. o fuЙ—Й—i tagkde neЙ—Й—aЕӢke e loopal,"
  32,8,"refti o waЙ—i geГұngol makko ngol, e sortondiral, immorde ndihal [maniiyu] lo'oЙ—am;"
  32,9,"refi o fotndindiri mo, o wutti e makko ruuhu makko on. O waЙ—ani on nanЙ—e, e j'iiЙ—e e Й“erЙ—e. [Kono] famЙ—i ko njettonton!"
  32,10,"ЖҒe mbii': "E nee, si min majjii ka leydi, eyoo min ngontat e tagoore hesre?" Ko woni kamЙ“e e kawrugol e Joomi maЙ“Й“e, ko Й“e yedduЙ“e [Й—um]."
  32,11,"Maaku: "warata ta on, ko malaa'ikaajo maayde on wakkilaaЙ—o on. Refti ko to Joomi mon ndutteteЙ—on"."
  32,12,"Sinno a yi'atno, tuma nde bonЙ“e Й“en ugginta ko'e-maЙ“Й“e ka Joomi maЙ“Й“e! [lЖҒe mbi'a]: "Joomi amen, min nji'ii min nanii, rutton min, min ngolla ko moЖҙЖҙi; minen men njananaama"."
  32,13,"Sinno Min muuyuno, Min ngokkayno kala woЕӢkii peewal makki. Ko woni tun, konngol jojjii immorde e An : "Ma Mi hebbiniray Jahannama on jinna e yimЙ“e, Й“e denndaangal"."
  32,14,""MeeЙ—iree (lepte Й—en) sabu mbelsindagol mon kawrugol e ndee Гұalaande mon Й—oo. Menen (kadi) Men yejjitii on. MeeЙ—iree lepte luttal, sabu ko ngollatnoЙ—on kon"."
  32,15,"Nganndee ko gooЕӢЙ—inta Aayeeje Amen Й—en, ko Й“en tawЙ“e si Й“e mbaajoraama Й—e, Й“e cuuyiray sujjugol, Й“e subbuhinora jettugol Joomi maЙ“Й“e, kamЙ“e Й“e townitotaako."
  32,16,"Becce maЙ“Й“e Й—en heЙ—e ngoЙ—Й—itoo e lelorЙ—e Й—en, hiЙ“e noddira Joomi maЙ“Й“e kulol e Й—amaa'mu; e kon ko Min ngarsiki Й“e, hiЙ“e mbintoo."
  32,17,"WoЕӢkii (woo) anndaa ko maranaa Й“e e ko Й“uЙ“Й“inta Й“ernde, Й—um ko njoЙ“di ko Й“e gollatnoo kon !"
  32,18,"E on laatiiЙ—o gooЕӢЙ—inЙ—o wa'ay wa on faasiqe? (aa'aa), Й“e potataa."
  32,19,"Si ko Й“en gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“e ngolli golle moЖҙЖҙe, hino woodani Й“e Aljannaaji weerde jipporde, sabu koЙ“e ngollaynoo kon."
  32,20,"Si tawii non ko Й“e faasiqiiЙ“e, haray femporde Й“en Й—on nden, ko ka Yiite: Tuma kala Й“e faalaa jaltugol e magge, Й“e ruttitee e magge, Й“e wi'anee: "MeeЙ—ee lepte Yiite nge pennatoЙ—on ngen"."
  32,21,"Ma Min meeЙ—inir Й“e lepte aduna, ado lepte mawЙ—e Й—en (La'akara),mbelajo'o, Й“e nduttitoto."
  32,22,"Alaa Й“urЙ—o tooГұde wano baajoraaЙ—o Aayeeje Joomi mun Й—en, refti o Й—uurnii Й—e ! Pellet, Meonen, ko Men yoftotooЙ“e e bonЙ“e Й“en."
  32,23,"GooЕӢЙ—ii Min ngokkii Muusaa deftere nden, - wota a wonu e sikke e fii hawroygol e makko -, Min mbaЙ—i nde Й—oworde Й“iЙ—Й“e Israa'iila Й“een."
  32,24,"Min mbaЙ—i e maЙ“Й“e ardiiЙ“e, Й—owirooЙ“e (yimЙ“e Й“en) yamiroore Amen, nde Й“e muГұГұinoo, Й“e woni yananaaЙ“e e aayeeje amen Й—en."
  32,25,"Pellet, Joomi maa, ko KaЕӢko senndoyta hakkunde maЙ“Й“e, Г‘ande Darngal, e kon ko Й“e luutrnoo e fii mum."
  32,26,"E feeГұanaani Й“e, no foti Й—uuЙ—ude e ko Min kalki ado maЙ“Й“e e gire, hiЙ“e yaha e koЙ—ooli maЙ“Й“e? Pellet, no e Й—um, tasakuyeeji ! E Й“ee haqqiltaa?"
  32,27,"E Й“e njiaani, won'de MiЙ—en coggira ndiyam Й—am ka leydi hokkundi, Min njaltinira Й—am remuru, ndu neemoraaЙ—i maЙ“Й“e e kamЙ“e Гұaamata e mum? E Й“e nji'ataa?"
  32,28,"HiЙ“e mbi'a: "Ko holnde tuma woni ngal uddital, si on laatike gooЕӢЙ—Й“e?""
  32,29,"Maaku: "Г‘ande uddial ngal, ko heeferЙ“e Й“en gooЕӢЙ—inoyta nafoytaaЙ“e, wonaa kamЙ“e ngoni neeЙ“nanteeЙ“e !"."
  32,30,"ЖҠuurno Й“e, kaЙ“Й“ito-Й—aa. KamЙ“e , ko Й“e haЙ“Й“itiiЙ“e (lepte)."
  33,1,"Eey ma yo Annabiijo! Hulu Alla, wota a Й—ofto he'eferЙ“e Й“en e naafiqiiЙ“e Й“en. Pellet, Alla laatike gannduЙ—o, Г‘eeГұuЙ—o."
  33,2,"Jokku ko wahayinaa kon e maaЙ—a, immorde ka Joomi maa. Pellet, Alla laatike kumpitiiЙ—o ko nholloton kon."
  33,3,"Fawo e Alla. Alla yonii paweteeЙ—o e mum."
  33,4,"Alla waЙ—anani neЙ—Й—aЕӢke Й“erЙ—e Й—iЙ—i e ndeer fulkuru makko. O waЙ—aali kadi resondiraaЙ“e mon Й“en Й“e nanndinirton, neeniraaЙ“e mon. O waЙ—aani kadi nodditirayЙ“e on (baaba Й“en), Й“iЙ—Й“e mooЙ—on. ЖҠuum mooЙ—on, ko kongol mon [yaltungol e] kunndule mon. Alla non, no daala goonga, ko KaЕӢko woni fewnoowo e pocciingol ngol."
  33,5,"Noddiree Й“e baabiraaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en: ko Й—uum Й“uri nuunЙ—ude ka Alla. Si tawii non on nganndaa baabiraaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“een, haray ko musiЙ—Й“e mon ka diina e heftodiiЙ“e mon. Bakkaat fawaaki on e ko mboopoton (faayon) e mum, kono (on bakkondinay e) ko faandoriЙ—on Й“erЙ—e mon Й—en. Alla laatike kaforoowo, jurmotooЙ—o otooЙ—o."
  33,6,"Ko Annabiijo on Й“uri hanndude e gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“en diini ko'e maЙ“Й“e; suddiiЙ“e makko Й“en, ko neeniraaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e. JoomiraaЙ“e enЙ—amaaji Й“en, ko yoga maЙ“Й“e Й“uri hanndude yoga [e ndonndi ndin] ka deftere Alla, diini gooЙ—inЙ“e Й“en e ferЙ“e Й“en, si wonaa hara on waЙ—an weldiiЙ“e mon [Й“e ronataa] Й“en moЖҙЖҙere. ЖҠum wonii ko winndaa ka deftere."
  33,7,"JaЕӢto tuma nde Min Жҙettidunoo e AnnabaaЙ“e Й“en ahadi maЙ“Й“e, e ma'a an kadi, e Nuuhu, e Ibraahiima, e Muusaa e Iisaa Й“iЙ—Й—o Maryama on: Min Жҙettidi e maЙ“Й“e ahadi tiiЙ—ndi,"
  33,8,"fii no [Alla] laЙ“ndora gooЕӢguЙ“e Й“en e goonga maЙ“Й“e kan. O hebilanii yedduЙ“e Й“en, lepte mu'usuuЙ—e."
  33,9,"Eey mon yo gooЕӢЙ—imЙ“e ! Ngannditee neema Alla on e dow mooЙ—on, tuma nde koneeli arunoo on, Min ngurti e maЙ“Й“e henndu e konuuli, ngu on nji'aani. Alla siforii deentuЙ—o ko ngolloton."
  33,10,"Tuma nde Й“e ngardirannoo on, ka seЕӢgo dow mon e ka ley [saare] mon, e tuma nde gite ooГұinoo, Й“erЙ—e Й—en lewwtiri ka lookoЖҙe, hoЙ—on cikka Alla (on tuma) sikke luutondirЙ—e."
  33,11,"Ko Й—on gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“en njariba, Й“e dilliniraa dillere saЙ—tunde."
  33,12,"JaЕӢto kadi, tuma nde naafiqiiЙ“e Й“en, e Й“en Й“e Гұawu woni e Й“erЙ—e mum mbi'aynoo: "Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on fodaali men, si wonaa hodo"."
  33,13,"E tuma nde fedde goo e maЙ“Й“e wi'inoo: "Ko eey mon yo yimЙ“e Yathrib ! Г‘iiЙ“irde alanaa on (Й—oo), yiltitee [ka mon]". Fedde goo e maЙ“Й“e no waynitoo Annabiijo on, hiЙ“e mbi'a : "CuuЙ—i amen Й—in ko na huncii", hara non wonaa Й—i hunciiЙ—i: Й“e faa:ndaaki, si wonaa dogugol."
  33,14,"Hay si tawno (aГұЙ“e) Й“en naatiranno Й“e Й“annge mayre, refti Й“e lanndaa fitina (jeddugol), pellet, Й“e ngonatno e mun, Й“e leelnataano e Й—uum, si wonaa seeЙ—a,"
  33,15,"hara le gooЕӢЙ—ii Й“e ahodiino e Alla ko adii, won'de Й“e ndutotaako Й“abbe. Ahadi Alla ndin non, ndi laatike lannditorteendi."
  33,16,"Maaku: "Dokgol nafataa on, si on ngogi maayde maa hare; haray Й—uim, on ndakmitetaake, si wanaa seeЙ—a"."
  33,17,"Maaku: "Ko hommbo woni daЙ—ndoowo on e Alla, si o fa'andanike on bone, maa si o fa'andanike on yurmeende?" ЖҒe keЙ“antaa ko'e maЙ“Й“e ga Alla, giЙ—o wonaa ballo."
  33,18,"GooЕӢЙ—ii Alla no anndi falaotooЙ“e Й“en e mon, e Й“een wi'anooЙ“e musiЙ—Й“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en :"ngaree e amen", hara non Й“e arataa e hare nden, si wonaa seeЙ—a."
  33,19,"ko wuddan Й“e on. Si kulol ngol arii, a yi'at hiЙ“e ndaare, hara gite maЙ“Й“e no yiilora wa mo maayde suddaa e mum. Si kulo ngol non yehii, Й“e laggora Й—emЙ—e muusuЙ—e, wuddangol moЖҙЖҙere nden. ЖҒeen Й—on, Й“e ngooЕӢЙ—inaani, Alla bonnii golle maЙ“Й“e Й—en. ЖҠum wonii ko newanii Alla."
  33,20,"HiЙ“e vikka koneeli Й—in njahataa. Hay si koneeli Й—in ngartii, Й“ee [naafiqiiЙ“e] yelotono sinno hara nun heЙ“e ka ladde hakkunde yimЙ“e ladde Й“en, hara heЙ“e laЙ“ndo fii mon. Hay si Й“e tawtodano e mon, Й“e haЙ“ataano si wonaa seeЙ—a nii."
  33,21,"GooЕӢЙ—ii laatanike on e nulaaЙ—o Alla on, Гұemtinal moЖҙЖҙal, wonan'de on joortiiЙ—o Alla, e Г‘alaande sakkitiinde nden, o jaЕӢtii Alla ko Й—uuЙ—i."
  33,22,"Nde gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“en nji'unoo koneeli Й—in, Й“e mbi'i: "Ko Й—uum woni ko Alla e NulaaЙ—o makko on fodi men; haray Alla e NulaaЙ—o makko on goongii". ЖҠuum Й“eydaani Й“e, si wonaa gooЕӢЙ—inal e jebbilaare."
  33,23,"Hino e gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“en, worЙ“e hunnuЙ“e ko Й“e ahodi e Alla kon : hino e maЙ“Й“e timminЙ—o takke mun Й—en (haa o sahodinaa), hino e maЙ“Й“e kadi kaЙ“Й“itiiЙ—o; Й“e waЙ—titaali (ahadi ndin) mbattiigu."
  33,24,"Fii yo Alla yoЙ“ir hunnuЙ“e Й“en sabu gooЕӢЙ—ue maЙ“Й“e, O lepta naafiqiiЙ“e Й“en, si mo yiЙ—i, maa o jaЙ“ana Й“e tuubuubuyee. Tawde pellet, Alla laatike kaforoowo, jurmotooЙ—o ."
  33,25,"Alla ruttidii yedduЙ“e Й“en e tikkere maЙ“Й“e nden, Й“e keЙ“aani moЖҙЖҙere. Alla yonii gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“en e hare. Alla siforii Cemmbe e Poolal."
  33,26,"O jipiini Й“en wallindirnooЙ“e jeyaaЙ“e e yimЙ“e defte Й“en, ka tataaji maЙ“Й“e Й—in, O weddii Й—enЖҙere e Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e; fedde goo (e maЙ“Й“e) hoЙ—on mbara, hoЙ—on daha kadi fede goo."
  33,27,"O ronini on leydi maЙ“Й“e, e galleeji maЙ“Й“e, e jawЙ—e maЙ“Й“e, e leydi ndi on tippaano e mum. Alla siforiikhattanЙ—o kala hu'unde."
  33,28,"Eey ma yo Annabiijo ! Maakan suddiiЙ“e maa Й“en: "Si wonii ko nguurndam aduna paalaЙ—on e cuЙ—aari majjam, haray ngaree mi dakmita on, mi seera on [on tuma] ceergal moЖҙЖҙal."
  33,29,"Si tawii non ko Alla paalaЙ—on, e NulaaЙ—o makko on, e galle La'akara Й—en, haray pellet, Alla maranii moЖҙЖҙimЙ“e Й“en e mooЙ—on, njoЙ“di mawndi"."
  33,30,"Eey mon yo suddiiЙ“e Annabiijo on ! Kala gadduЙ—o e mooЙ—on bone Й“annguЙ—o, lepte Й—en cowirante mo cowalle Й—iЙ—i! ЖҠuum wonii ko newanii Alla."
  33,31,"Kala e mooЙ—on Й—oftiiЙ—o Alla e NulaaЙ—o makko on, o golli ko moЖҙЖҙi, Min njoЙ“iray mo njoЙ“di makko ndin laaЙ“i Й—iЙ—i, MiЙ—en marani mo kadi, arsike tedduЙ—o."
  33,32,"Eey mon suddiiЙ“e Annabiijo! On mba'aa wano gooto e suddiiЙ“e Й“een. Si on ngooЕӢЙ—ii, haray wota on yergin konngol, sakko on mo Гұawu [tuuyo] woni e Й“ernde mun tamЖҙinoo. Wowlon konngol moЖҙЖҙol."
  33,33,"Г‘iiЙ“ee ka cuuЙ—i mon; wota on 'eГұГұinir cuЙ—aari mon, wano wirtaare majjere adinooЙ“e. Г‘iiЙ“nee Juulde nden, totton askal on, Й—oftoЙ—on Alla e NulaaЙ—o makko on. Nganndee ko Alla faandii, ko ittanta on e tuuЙ—e, onon yimЙ“e suudu [Annabiijo], O laЙ“Й“inira on laЙ“Й“ingol."
  33,34,"NjaЕӢtee ko wonaa e janngeede ka cuuЙ—i mon, immorde e aayeeje Alla, e Sunna. Pellet, Alla laatike NewiiЙ—o, kumpitiiЙ—o."
  33,35,"Pellet, juulЙ“e worЙ“e Й“en e juulЙ“e rewЙ“e Й“en, e gomЙ—imЙ“e worЙ“e Й“en e gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e rewЙ“e Й“en, e Й—oftiiЙ“e worЙ“e Й“en e Й—oftiiЙ“e rewЙ“e Й“en, e gooЕӢЙ—uЙ“e worЙ“e Й“en e gooЕӢЙ—Й“e rewЙ“e Й“en, e muГұГұiiЙ“e worЙ“e Й“en e muГұГұiiЙ“e rewЙ“e Й“en, e yankiniiЙ“e worЙ“e Й“en e yankiniiЙ“e rewЙ“e Й“en, e sakkotooЙ“e worЙ“e Й“en e sakkotooЙ“e rewЙ“e Й“en, e hoorooЙ“e worЙ“e Й“en e hoorooЙ“e rewЙ“e Й“en, e worЙ“e reenooЙ“e farjuuji mum e rewЙ“e reenooЙ“e farjuuji mum, e worЙ“e jaЕӢtotooЙ“e Alla ko Й—uuЙ—i Й“en e rewЙ“e jaЕӢtotooЙ“e Й“en: Alla maranii Й“en, haforanal e njoЙ“di mawndi."
  33,36,"Alanaa gooЕӢЙ—iЙ—o gorko, wanaa gooЕӢЙ—inЙ—o debbo, si Alla e NulaaЙ—o makko on Гұaawii fiyaaku, nde suЙ“agol e fiyaaku maЙ“Й“e on. Kala non kedduЙ—o Alla e NulaaЙ—o makko on, haray o majjii majjere Й“anngunde."
  33,37,"JaЕӢto tuma maakanayno-Й—aa on mo Alla neemini e mun, moЖҙЖҙu-Й—aa e makko: "Jogitano suddiiЙ—o maa on, hoore-maa, kulaa Alla", haЙ—a suuЙ—a e fonndo maa, ko Alla feГұГұinta. HaЙ—a hula yimЙ“e Й“en, kono ko Alla fotu-Й—aa hulude. Tuma Zaydu huntunoo e (suddiiЙ—o) on haaju, Min ndesin-maa mo, fii wata Й“ittere wonu e gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“en, e (resugol) suddiiЙ“e nodditiraaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en, si Й“en huntii e maЙ“Й“e haaju. Yamiroore Alla nden laatike golleteende."
  33,38,"Feloore alanaa annabiijo o, e ko Alla daginani mo, Й—um ko Гұaawoore Alla e Й“een feЖҙЖҙuЙ“e ado makko. Г‘aawoore Alla nde wonii eЙ“Й“aande hoddiraande."
  33,39,"ЖҒeen yottiinooЙ“e nule Alla Й—en, Й“e no kula mo, Й“e kula goЙ—Й—o goo si wanaa Alla. Alla yonii kasboowo."
  33,40,"Muhammadu wonaani baaba hay goot e worЙ“e mon, ko [o] woni, ko NulaaЙ—o Alla e timmoode AnnabaaЙ“e. Alla laatike gannduЙ—o kala hu'unde."
  33,41,"Eey mon yo Й“en gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e, jaЕӢtoree Alla jaЕӢtoore Й—uuЙ—unde,"
  33,42,"Cubhinee mo bimmbi e kiikiiЙ—e."
  33,43,"Ko KaЕӢko woni yurmeteeЙ—o on, -e Malaa'ikaaЙ“e makko Й“en (du'orana on), - fii no o yaltinira on e niЙ“e fa'ade e annoora. O siforii hinnotooЙ—o gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“en."
  33,44,"Hiwrondiral maЙ“Й“e ngal Гұande Й“e kawrata e makko, ko "Salaam" [kisiyee], O maranii Й“e mbarjaari teddundi."
  33,45,"Eey ma Annabiijo ! Min nulirii ma [fii yo won] seediiЙ—o, e wewlinoowo e jeertinoowo,"
  33,46,"e noddoowo fa'ade e Alla, duЕӢayee makko; e pitilol jalЙ“ungol."
  33,47,"Wewlinir gooЕӢЙ—iinЙ“e Й“en, won'de no woodani Й“e ka Alla, Й“ural mawnungal."
  33,48,"Wata a Й—ofto heeferЙ“e Й“en e naafiqiiЙ“e Й“e, Й—uurno (e) lorra maЙ“Й“e kan, pawo-Й—aa e Alla. Sabu Alla yonii ka fawee."
  33,49,"Eey mon yo Й“en gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e ! Si resii rewЙ“e gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“en, refti on seerii Й“e ado on meemondirde e maЙ“Й“e, haray alanaa on e maЙ“Й“e, edda mo Й“e eddinotoo. NDakmitiree Й“e [njooЙ“a], ceeriron Й“e ceergal labangal."
  33,50,"Eey ma yo Annabiijo ! Min ndaginanii ma suddiiЙ“e maa Й“en Й“e njonnu-Й—aa teЕӢe mum Й“en, e Й“een [horЙ“e] Й“e njeyru-Й—aa Гұaamo maa, e Й“een [dahaaЙ“e] Й“e Alla neldu-maa, e jiwЙ“e bappa maa, e jiwЙ“e yaayiraaЙ“e maa, e jiwЙ“e kaawu-maa, e jiwЙ“e neeniraaЙ“e maa, - Й“een feridunooЙ“e e maa, - e suddiiЙ—o gooЕӢЙ—inЙ—o, si o yeЙ—ii hoore-makko Annabiijo on, si Annabiijo on kadi fa'andike desgol mo : Й—um ko ko heerani maa, ga gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“en. GooЕӢЙ—ii MiЙ—en nganndi ko min parli e maЙ“Й“e kon, e fii suddiiЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en, e ko Й“e njeytiri Гұaame maЙ“Й“e Й—en, fii wota Й“iЙ—teende wonu e maaЙ—a. Alla laatike kaforoowo, jurmotooЙ—o ."
  33,51,"HiЙ—a nennintina on mo nijЙ—Й—u-Й—aa (nennintinnde) e maЙ“Й“e, Й“aЙ—tinaa e maaЙ—a on mo yiЙ—u-Й—aa. E on mo Й—aЙ“Й“u-Й—aa (belagol ka mum) e Й“en Й“e nennitu-Й—aa, bakkaaku woo fawaaki ma. Ko Й—um Й“uri Й“adaade e ko Й“uЙ“Й“inta Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e, hara Й“e sunotaako, Й“e weltora kadi ko okku-Й—aa Й“e kon, Й“e fow maЙ“Й“e. Alla no Anndi ko woni e Й“erЙ—e mon. Alla laatike gannduЙ—o, muГұГұiiЙ—o."
  33,52,"RewЙ“e Й“en ndagitantaako ma Й“aawo [Й“ee Й—oo], wonaa nde waЙ—titirtaa Й“e genndiraaЙ“e goo, hay si ЕӢari Й“en Й—oon kaawnii ma; si wonaa Й“e njeyru-Й—aa Гұaamo maa Й“en. Alla laatike tommbiiЙ—o kala hu'unde."
  33,53,"Eey mon yo Й“en gooЕӢЙ—imЙ“e ! Wota on naatu ka cuuЙ—i Annabiijo on, si wonaa hara on nodda e Гұaametee, hara wonaa yo on habbito ko Й“enndi ka makko. Kono si on noddaa ma, naatee. Si on Гұaamii, sentee, hara on Й—aЙ“Й“aali haala. Anndon Й—um mooЙ—on, hino lorraynoo Annabiijo on, kono o hersa (haalannde) on, Alla non Й—alataa [yamirde] goonga. Si on lanndoto (suddiiЙ“e makko) Й“en haaju, lanndoree Й“e Й“aawo wirngallo: ko Й—um mooЙ—on, Й“uri laaЙ“annde Й“erЙ—e mon e Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e. Haananaa on nde lorroton NulaaЙ—o Alla on, wanaa nde resoton suddiiЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en Й“aawo makko, poomaa; pellet, waЙ—ugol mon Й—um, wonii ko mawni ka Alla."
  33,54,"Si on peГұГұinii hu'unde, maa on cuuЙ—ii nde, pellet, Alla laatike gannduЙ—o kala hu'unde."
  33,55,"Bakkaat fawaaki Й“e e baabiraaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en, wonaa kadi Й“iЙ—Й“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en, wonaa banndiraaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en, wonaa e Й“iЙ—Й“e banndiraaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en, wonaa e Й“iЙ—Й“e miГұГұiraaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e rewЙ“e Й“en, wanaa e rewЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en, wonaa e Й“en Й“e Й“e jeyiri Гұaame maЙ“Й“e. Kulee Alla (yo suddiiЙ“e). Pellet, Alla siforii ceediiЙ—o kala hu'unde."
  33,56,"Pellet, Alla e Malaa'ikaaЙ“e makko Й“en, heЙ“e du'anaade annabiijo on; ko onon yo Й“en gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e, njuulee e makko, toranoЙ—on [mo] kisal."
  33,57,"Pellet, Й“een lorrooЙ“e Alla e NulaaЙ—o makko on, Alla huЙ—ii Й“en aduna e La'akara, O hebilanii Й“e kadi lepte koynooje."
  33,58,"ЖҒeen kadi lorrooЙ“e gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e worЙ“e Й“en e gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e rewЙ“e Й“en, e hoore ko Й“e faggitaaki, gooЕӢЙ—ii Й“e ronndike fenaande e bakkaatuuji Й“annguЙ—i."
  33,59,"Ko Annabiijo! Maakan suddiiЙ“e maa Й“een, e jiwЙ“e maa Й“en, e genndiraaЙ“e gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“en, nde Й“e joltinta e maЙ“Й“e, wutteeji maЙ“Й“e Й—in: ko Й—uum Й“urata Й“aЙ—taade, nde Й“e annditetee, hara Й“e lorraaka. Alla laatike kaforoowo, jurmotooЙ—o ."
  33,60,"Pellet, si naafiqiiЙ“e Й“en kaЙ—itaaki, e Й“een Й“e Гұawu (sikkitaare) woni e Й“erЙ—e mum, e fena-fenta'en ka saare Madiina, ma Min ngurtite e maЙ“Й“e, refi Й“e kawtirtaa e maaЙ—a ton, si wonaa seeЙ—a."
  33,61,"Ko huЙ—aa Й“e. Kala ka Й“e tawaa, ko Й“e nanngetee Й“e, Й“e mbaree bargol:"
  33,62,"ЖҠum ko sunna Alla e Й“een wulinooЙ“e ko adii. A keЙ“antaa laawol (sunna) Alla ngol, battiigu."
  33,63,"YimЙ“e Й“en o laЙ“ndo maa fii Darngal. Maaku : "ngandee ganndal daragol maggal, ko ka Alla woni". E ko anndin maa, won'de no hasii hara Darngal ngal Й“adike?"
  33,64,"Pellet, Alla huЙ—ii he'eferЙ“e Й“en, O kammbiranii Й“e kadi dulboowe,"
  33,65,"ko Й“e luttooЙ“e ton poomaa. ЖҒe keЙ“ataa giЙ—o, wonaa ballo."
  33,66,"Г‘alnde je'ece maЙ“Й“e Й—en mbaylitetee ka Yiite, Й“e mbiay: "Ee jalla amen! Hara min Й—oftino Alla, min Й—oftii NulaaЙ—o on!"."
  33,67,"ЖҒe mbi'a: "Joomi amen, Minen Min Й—ofti hooreeЙ“e amen e mawЙ“e amen, Й“e majjini min e laawol ngol."
  33,68,"Joomi amen, tottu Й“e cowanЙ—e Й—iЙ—i e lepte Й—en, kuЙ—aa Й“e kuddi mawndi"."
  33,69,"Ko onon yo Й“en gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e! Wota on wa'u wa Й“en lorrunooЙ“e Muusaa, Alla woЙ—Й—ini mo e ko Й“e mbi'i kon, tawde o wonii tedduЙ—o ka Alla."
  33,70,"Eey mon yo Й“en gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e! Kulee Alla, wowlon konngol peewungol."
  33,71,"[Si on waЙ—ii Й—um], O moЖҙЖҙinanay on golle mon, O haforana on bakkaat mon. Kala Й—oftiiЙ—o Alla e NulaaЙ—o makko on, haray o maliraama maloore mawnde."
  33,72,"Min mbeeЙ“itii hoolaare nden e dow kammuuji Й—in, e leydi ndin e pelle Й—en, Й—i kaЙ—itii ronndagol nde, Й—i kuli (battane) majji, neЙ—Й—o on kan ronndii nde; tawde pellet, o wonii Й—uuЙ—uЙ—o-tooГұde [hoore-mun], majjaaЙ—o [battane Й—um]."
  33,73,"[NeЙ—Й—o on ronndiraama Й—um], no Alla leptira naafiqiiЙ“e worЙ“e Й“en e naafiqiiЙ“e rewЙ“e Й“en, e sirkooЙ“e worЙ“e Й“en e sirkooЙ“e rewЙ“e Й“en, e (no) Alla jaЙ“irana gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e worЙ“e Й“en e gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e rewЙ“e Й“en tuububuyee. Alla laatike kafroowo, jurmotooЙ—o."
  34,1,"Jettooje ngoodanii Alla, On jeyЙ—o kala ko woni ka kammuuji e ka leydi. Hino woodani mo kadi jettooje ka La'akara. Ko KaЕӢko woni Г‘eeГұo, kumpitiiЙ—o."
  34,2,"Homo anndi ko naatata ka leydi, e ko yaltata e mayri, ko jippotoo iwra ka kammu e ko Жҙawata e maggu. Ko KaЕӢko woni jurmotooЙ—o otoo, jaafoto."
  34,3,"YedduЙ“e Й“en mbi'i: "Darngal ngal arataa min". Maaku: "aa'a! Mi wooЙ—ndirii Joomi am! pellet, ko aray e mon. [Joomi ma] ko ganduЙ—o wirniiЙ—i. Hu'unde wirnanaaki Mo, ko fotata e abbere jarra, woni ka kammuuji maa ka leydi. Wanaa ko Й“uri Й—um famЙ—ude, wonaa ko Й“uri Й—uum mawnude, si wonaa no e deftere feГұГұinnde."
  34,4,"Fii yo O yoЙ“oy Й“en gooЙ—inЙ“e, Й“e ngolli moЖҙЖҙuЙ—i. ЖҒeen Й—oon, hino woodani Й“e haforaneede, e arsike tedduЙ—o."
  34,5,"ЖҒeen non yaccii Й“e e bonnitugol aayeeje amen Й—en, Й“en Й—on, hino woodani Й“e lepte, immorde e Й“urЙ—e mu'usuuЙ—e."
  34,6,"ЖҒeen okkaaЙ“e ganndal hino yi'ira jippiniraande nden e maaЙ—a, immorde ka Joomi maa, ko kaГұre woni goonga, hinde fewnira e laawol poolЙ—o, jettiniiЙ—o On."
  34,7,"YedduЙ“e Й“en kadi mbi'i: "On ngaccay min tinndina on fii gorko, mo no kumpita on, won'de si on muncitaama kala muncitannde, on ngontoyay e tagoore hesre?"
  34,8,"O fekindi fenaande e hoore Alla? Kaa hara ko jinna nanngi mo? Si ko woni, Й“en Й“e ngooЕӢЙ—inaa La'akara on, Й“e wonii e lepte e majjere woЙ—Й—iinde (goonga)."
  34,9,"E Й“ee nji'aani ko woni yeeso maaЙ“e e ko woni Й“aawo maЙ“Й“e immorde ka kammu e ka leydi? Si Min muuyiino, Min munnirayno Й“e leydi ndin, maa Min pukkina e maЙ“Й“e taЖҙontine (lepte), immorde ka kammu. Wonii e Й—uum, Ma'ande, wonan'de kala jeyaaЙ—o duttotooЙ—o (e Joomi mum)."
  34,10,"GooЕӢЙ—ii Min ngokkii Daawuuda Й“ural, immorde e Amen. [Min mbi'i]: "eey mon pelle e colli, cubbunhinodee e makko. Min newinani mo (tafugol) njamndi ndin."
  34,11,"(Min mbii'ani mo won'de): "Gollu wutteeji njamndi, eЙ“Й“aa ka tafoodi. NGollon golle moЖҙЖҙe, pellet, ko Mi deenuЙ—o ko ngolloton kon"."
  34,12,"(Min eeltani kadi) Sulaymaana henndu ndun: dawol mayru ko yeru (yaadu) lewru, kirndol mayru kadi ko yeru (yaadu) lewu. Min koncinani mo Й“unndu sila (kire). Hino jinnaaji Й—in, golliraynooЙ—i ye'eso makko, e duЕӢayee Joomi makko. Kala ooГұiingii e majji, ga e yamiroore Amen nden, Min meeЙ—ina ngii lepte dulЙ“oowe nge."
  34,13,"HiЙ—i ngollana mo ko o faalaa: gila e tataaji, e nanndollaaji, e looЙ—e wa'iЙ—e wa beeli, e payanЙ—e feЕӢiiЙ—e. "Gollee, onon Й“eynguure Daawuuda, njetton (Alla)", fanЙ—ii e jiyaaЙ“e Am Й“en, jettoowo (Kam)."
  34,14,"Nde Min Гұaawnoo e makko maayde nden, annditaani Й—i fii maayde makko nden, si wonaa gannguuji leydi(mooЖҙu) Й—in, hino Гұaama tuggordu makko ndun. Nde o fukkinoo, feeГұani jinnaaji Й—in, won'de si Й—i nganndunoo ko wirnii, Й—i ГұiiЙ“ataano e lepte [jeyaagu] koynooje."
  34,15,"GooЕӢЙ—ii wonaniino yimЙ“e Saba'i Й“en e koЙ—ooli maЙ“Й“e Й—in, Ma'ande; gese Й—iЙ—i ka bannge Гұaamo e ka nano. (Min wmbiani Й“e): "Г‘aamee e arsike Joomi mon, njetton mo Mo. Leydi ndin ko laaЙ“undi, e Joomiraawo jafotooЙ—o"."
  34,16,"(Kono) Й“e Й—uunii. Min ngurti e maЙ“Й“e ndiyam waame, Min mbaЙ—titani Й“e gese maЙ“Й“e Й—en Й—iЙ—i, gese (goo) Й—iЙ—i, marЙ—e Гұaametee kaaЙ—Й—o, e (leЙ—Й—e) duЙ“Й“eeje, e hu'unde e jaaЙ“e seeЙ—aaje."
  34,17,"Ngool (yaggingol), Min njoЙ“irЙ“e ko Й“e njeddi kon. E hara Min njoЙ“ay si wonaa yedduЙ“e Й“en?"
  34,18,"Min mbaЙ—i hakkune maЙ“Й“e e koЙ—ooli Й—i Min mbaЙ—i barki e mum Й—in, koЙ—ooli feeГұondirЙ—i, Min eЙ“Й“i e majji yaadu. (Min mbi'ani Й“e): "njehee ton jemmaaji e Гұalawmaaji, ko on hooliiЙ“e"."
  34,19,"ЖҒe mbi'i'i: "Joomi amen, woЙ—Й—indir hakkunde yaaduuji amen", Й“e tooГұi ko'e maЙ“Й“e, Min mbaЙ—ti fillitee Й“e fii mum, Min cenndindiri Й“e hattirde e senndirgol. Pellet, wonii e Й—uum, Ma'andeeji wonan'de kala keewuЙ—o muГұal, jettoowo (neema)."
  34,20,"GooЕӢЙ—ii Ibuliisa goonginii jikke mum Й—en e maЙ“Й“e. ЖҒe njokki mo, si wonaa fedde e gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“een."
  34,21,"E doole alanaa mo e dow maЙ“Й“e, cemmbe (wurtugol), si wonaa tan, ko fii no Moen nganndira on gooЕӢЙ—inЙ—o La'akara e on gonЙ—o e sikke fii mum. Joomi maa non, e dow kala hu'unde, ko O deenЙ—o."
  34,22,"Maaku: "Noddee Й—in Й—i Й—aynitorЙ—on [ deweteeЙ—i] ga Alla. ЖҠi njeyaa hay yeru abbere jarra, ka kammuuji wonaa ka leydi. Alanaa Й—i e Й—in (kammuuli e leydi ndin) kafidaaЙ—o (geЙ—al), alanaa mo e Й—iin, hay ballondirteeЙ—o"."
  34,23,"Tefoore nafataa ka makko, si wonaa on Mo O duЕӢanii. Haa si Й—enЖҙere nden yaltinaama e Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en, Й“e mbi'a: "Ko holЙ—um Joomi mon daali?" ЖҒe mb'a: "Ko goonga kan; ko KaЕӢko woni ToowЙ—o, MawЙ—o On"."
  34,24,"Maaku: "Kon hombo woni arsikiroowo on ka kammuuji e ka leydi?" Maaku: "Ko Alla. Ko si ko minen maa si ko onon, ngoni e peewal maa e nder majjere Й“anngunde"."
  34,25,"Maaku: "On laЙ“nditoytaake fii ko min mbonni, minen kadi men laЙ“nditoytaake fii ko ngolloton ton"."
  34,26,"Maaku: "Joomi men renndinoyay en, refti o Гұaawira hakkunde min goonga; Ko KaЕӢko woni Гұawoowo, gannduЙ—o On"."
  34,27,"Maaku: "kollee Kam Й—in Й—i baЙ—tidu-Й—on e makko kafidiiЙ—i. Wonaa non woniri! Si ko woni, ko KaЕӢko woni AllapFooluЙ—o, Г‘eeГұЙ—o On"."
  34,28,"Min nuliraali ma, si wonaa e yimЙ“e Й“en fof: wewlinoowo e jeertinoowo. Kono ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e yimЙ“e Й“en, Й“e nganndaa."
  34,29,"HeЙ“e mbi'a: "Ko holnde tuma woni ndee Fodoore, si on laatike gooЕӢЙ—Й“e?""
  34,30,"Maaku: "Hino woodani on fodoore, nde o neeЙ“nitantaake e mayre fotde saa'i, on ardintinantaake nde kadi!"."
  34,31,"YedduЙ“e Й“en mbi'i: "Min ngooЕӢЙ—intaa ndee Alqur'aanaare muk, wonaa nden adiinde nde". Sinno a tinayno tuma nde tooГұЙ“e Й“en ndarnetee ka Joomi maЙ“Й“e, hara yoga maЙ“Й“e no rutta yoga konngol, lo'inanooЙ“e Й“en mbi'ana townitinooЙ“e Й“en: "Si wonaano onon nun, min ngonayno gooЙ—inЙ“e"."
  34,32,"TownitinooЙ“e Й“enmbi'ani lo'inanooЙ“e Й“en: "E ko minen palinoo on e peewal Й“aawo ngal arde e mon? Si ko woni, on ngoniino bonЙ“e"."
  34,33,"Lo'inanooЙ“e Й“en kadi mbi'ani townitinooЙ“e Й“en: "Si ko woni, ko pewje (mon) jemma e Гұalawma, tuma njamiraynoЙ—on meon yo men njeddu Alla, min mbaЙ—ana Mo potondirЙ—i". ЖҒe cuuЙ—i nimse Й—en, nde Й“e njinoo lepte Й—en. Min mbaЙ—i kolombooje e daaЙ—e Й“en yedduЙ“e. Hara Й“e yoЙ“itete si wanaa ko Й“e ngollatnoo oo kon?"
  34,34,"Min Nulaani jeertinoowo e yimЙ“e saare, si wanaa neeminaaЙ“e mayre Й“en mbiay: "Minen ko men yedduЙ“e ko nulidaЙ—on kon"."
  34,35,"ЖҒe mbi'i kadi: "Ko menen Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude jawЙ—e e Й“iЙ“Й“e, men wonaani kadi lepteteeЙ“e"."
  34,36,"Maaku: "pellet, Joomi am homo weertana arsike on, mo O muuyi, O Й“illini (mo O muuyi). Kono Й“urЙ“e Й—uuЙ—ude e yimЙ“e Й“en, Й“e nganndaa"."
  34,37,"Wonaa jawЙ—e mon, wonaa jiidi mon woni ko Й“aЙ—tinirta on ka Amen Й“adal. Si wonaa Й“en gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“e ngolli golle moЖҙЖҙe; Й“en Й—on, hino woodani Й“e njoЙ“di sowaande, sabu ko Й“e ngolli kon, kamЙ“e ka soorooji, ko Й“e hooliiЙ“e."
  34,38,"ЖҒeen yaccotooЙ“e e doЕӢkingol (yimЙ“e Й“een) e Aayeeje Amen Й—en, Й“en Й—on, ka ka ndeer lepte woni ko Й“e tawnoytee."
  34,39,"Maaku: "pellet, Joomi am homo weertana arsike on, mo o muuyani e jeyaaЙ“e makko Й“en, O Й“illini mo (O muuyi e maЙ“Й“e). Kala non ko wintiЙ—on e hu'unde, KaЕӢko O lomtinay nde. Ko KaЕӢko woni moЖҙЖҙo Arsikoowo"."
  34,40,"Г‘ande o mooЙ“tindiroyta Й“e dendaangal, refti o daalana Maleykaaji Й“in: "E ko Й“ee Й—oo (yimЙ“e) ndewatnoo on?""
  34,41,"ЖҒe mbi'a: "Senayee woodanii ma! Ko Aan woni giЙ—o amen ga maЙ“Й“e. Toode ko jinnaaji Й—in Й“e ndewaynoo, ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e maЙ“Й“e, ko Й—in (jinnaaji) gooЕӢЙ—ini"."
  34,42,"Hannde non, yoga mon waawanaa yoga nafa wanaa lorra. Min mbi'anoya Й“en tooГұЙ“e: "MeeЙ—ee lepte Yiite nge pennatnoЙ—on fii mum"."
  34,43,"Si aayeeje amen Й“annguЙ—e Й—en janngaamma e maЙ“Й“e, Й“e mbi'a: "oo wonaani, si wonaa gorko paalaaЙ—o palagol on e ko baabiraaЙ“e mon ndewayno rewaynoo". ЖҒe mbi'i: "Ndee (AlqurвҖҷaanaare) wonaani, si wonaa fenaande fekindaande". YedduЙ“e Й“en mb'ani goonga kan nde ka arnoo e maЙ“Й“e: "Ndee wonaani, si wanaa mbilewu Й“anngu ngu"."
  34,44,"Min ngaddanaani Й“ee, defte Й—e Й“e janngata. Min meeЙ—aani nulude e maЙ“Й“e, jeertinoowo ado maa."
  34,45,"AdinooЙ“e Й“e Й“en [kadi] njenniino (nulaaЙ“e mum). [YimЙ“e maa Й“en] njottaaki sappaЙ“al ko Min ngkkunoo Й“en kon. ЖҒen njeddi NulaaЙ“e Amen Й“en, taskii no lepte am Й—en mba'unoo!"
  34,46,"Maaku: "nganndee ko mi waajorta on, ko (hu'unde) wootere: "Ko nde daroranton Alla Й—iЙ—o Й—iЙ—o e gooto gooto, refti miijitoЙ—on. (Nganndon) wondiiЙ—o mon on aldaa e jinna: O wonaani, si wonaa jerrtinoowo on, e ko woni yeeso (mon), e lepte caЙ—tuЙ—e"."
  34,47,"Maaku: "Mi laЙ“ndaaki on njoЙ“di, Й—uum ko fii mon. NjoЙ“di am ndin wonaani, si wonaa ka Alla. KaЕӢko Ko o SeediiЙ—o e kala hu'unde"."
  34,48,"Maaku: "pellet, Joomi am ko nerlortooЙ—o [meere nden, hujjaaji] goonga ka, timminЙ—o anndugol wirniiЙ—i"."
  34,49,"Maaku: "Goonga ka arii [Iislaamu on], mehre [ke'eferaagu] ngu alaa ka feeГұa, kadi, nde ruttotaako"."
  34,50,"Maaku: "Si mi majjii, haray ko hoore-am mi majjani; si mi feewii kadi, ko sabu ko sabu ko Joomi am wahayini e am kon, tawde pellet, ko o nanoowo, ЖҒadiiЙ—o"."
  34,51,"Sinno a tinatno, tuma nde Й“e Й—eЕӢЖҙii, - laaworde alanaa (Й“e), - Й“e nanngiree e nokkuure Й“adiinde!"
  34,52,"ЖҒe mbi'a: "Min ngooЕӢЙ—inii [Darngal] ngal", e ko holno gooЕӢЙ—inal woonirani Й“e e nokku goЙ—Й—uЙ—o?"
  34,53,"Hara non Й“e jeddiino nde ko adii, heЙ“e mbernora ko wirnii e nokku goЙ—Й—uЙ—o!"
  34,54,"Heedee hakkunde e ko Й“e tuuyetee, wano golliranoo e nanndo maЙ“Й“e ko adii, tawde Й“e ngoniino e sikke cikkiniiЙ—a."
  35,1,"Jettooje ngoodanii Alla, TakЙ—o kammuuji Й—in e leydi ndin, baЙ—Й—o Malaa'ikaaji nulaaЙ“e, marЙ“e gabitanji(bibje) Й—i Й—iЙ—i, Й—i tati e nayi. Homo Й“esda ko o muuyi e tagu makko ngun, tawde pellet, Alla ko kattanЙ—o kala hu'unde."
  35,2,"Kala yurmeende nde Alla udditani yimЙ“e Й“en, jogitotooЙ—o nde alaa; kala kadi ko o jogitii, gaccitoowo Й—um alaa Й“aawo (jogitagol) makko. Ko KaЕӢko woni pooluЙ—o, ГұeeГұЙ—o."
  35,3,"Eey mon yo yimЙ“e! NjaЕӢtee neema Alla on e mon. Hara tagoowo ko woori Alla no woodi, mo no arsikira on ka kammu e ka leydi? DeweteeЙ—o alaa si wonaa KaЕӢko! E ko honno njilirteЙ—on [e kaa goonga]?"
  35,4,"Si Й“e njeddii i ma, pellet NulaaЙ“e (goo) yeddanooma ado maa. Ko fa'ade e Alla, woni ruttorde fiyakuuji Й—in."
  35,5,"Eey mon yo yimЙ“e! Ngandee pellet fodoore Alla nden ko goonga. Wota nguurndam aduna hodu on, wota (seytaane) kodoowo on hod on e fii Alla."
  35,6,"Pellet, seytaane ko gaГұo wonani on. Haray njogitoree mo gaГұo. Nganndee ko o noddirta fedde makko nden, ko no Й“e jeydiree e yimЙ“e dulЙ“oowe ngen."
  35,7,"Hino woodani yedduЙ“e Й“en, lepte caЙ—tuЙ—e. ЖҒeya gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“e ngolli golle moЖҙЖҙe, hino woodani Й“e haforaneede e njoЙ“di mawndi."
  35,8,"E ko on cuЙ—inanaaЙ—o golle mum bonЙ—e, hara himo yi'a Й—e moЖҙЖҙuЙ—e? - Tawde pellet, Alla no majjina on mo o muuyi, O feewna mo o muuyi. Wota a tampinir hoore-maa, sunagol fii maЙ“Й“e. Pellet, Alla ko gannduЙ—o ko Й“e ngoni gollude."
  35,9,"Ko Alla woni gurtuЙ—o keneeli Й—in, Й—i cogga duule, Min njarnira Й—um leydi yo'orundi; Min nguurnitira Й—um leydi ndin, Й“aawo ndi yo'orude. Ko wano non ummital ngal."
  35,10,"Kala tawЙ—o ko teddungal faalaa (yo o Й—aЙ“Й“ir Alla), tawde ko Alla jeyi teddungal ngal fof: ko ka makko woni ko konngol laaЙ“ungol Жҙawata, golle moЖҙЖҙe Й—en Й“amta ngol. ЖҒeen fewjooЙ“e boneeji, hino woodani Й“e lepte caЙ—tuЙ—e. Pewje Й“en Й—en, ko bonat Й—e."
  35,11,"Ko Alla tagiri on e mbulbuldi, refti e toЙ“Й“ere (maniiyu), refti o waЙ—i on nooneeji. Deyel caawataa, ngel leelnataa kadi, si wonaa e anndal makko. GuurnaaЙ—o wuurnetaake, Й—uytetaake kadi e nguurndam makko, si wonaa no e deftere. Pellet, Й—uum ko newanii Й—um Alla."
  35,12,"Maaje Й—en Й—iЙ—i potataa: [Ndiyam] goo Й—oo Й—am, ko mbelЙ—am, laaЙ“ungo, newiingo njaram mum, ngoo Й—aa, ko lamЙ—am kaaЙ—uЙ—am. HiЙ—on Гұaama e kala majjam, teewu keccu, hoЙ—on njaltina kadi hern, cuЙ—aari ndi Й“oornotoЙ—on. HiЙ—a yi'a laaЙ—e Й—en no awja e maggo, fii yo on Й—aЙ“Й“iron e Й“ural Makko. Mbelejo'o on njettay [Mo]."
  35,13,"Himo naanta jemma on e deer Гұalawma on, O naatna Гұalawma on e ndeer jemma on. O eleti kadi na'ange ngen e lewru ndun. Kala mun no doga haa e lajal innaangal. Ko On mooЙ—on woni Alla, Joomi mon: Ko KaЕӢko Laamu woodani. ЖҠiya Й—i noddoton ga makko, Й—i jeytaa yeru gorol tamara."
  35,14,"Si on noddu Й—i, Й—i nanataa noddaandu mon; hay si Й—i nanoy, Й—i njaabitotaako on. Г‘ande Darngal, Й—i njeddoyat sirku mon on. Alaa kabroowo ma, wano kumpitiiЙ—o On."
  35,15,"Eey mon yo yimЙ“e, ko onon ngoni hatonjimЙ“e e Alla Й“en, Alla kan, ko KaЕӢko woni Galo jettiniiЙ—o On."
  35,16,"Si O yiЙ—ii, o naЙ“a on, o adda tagu hesu."
  35,17,"ЖҠuum wonaani cattuЙ—um to Alla."
  35,18,"WoЕӢki ronndotaako doЕӢgal woЕӢkii goo. Hay si teddiraaki [junuubi] kin noddii e ronndaneede, ki ronndantaake hay hu'unde, hay si ko Й“adondiraaЙ—o Anndu ko jeertintaa [nana waaju], ko Й“en hulirooЙ“e Joomi mum ka wirnii, Й“e ГұiiЙ“i e Juulde. Kala on laЙ“Й“iniiЙ—o, haray ko hoore makko o woni laЙ“Й“inanaade. Ko ka Alla woni ruttorde nden."
  35,19,"BumЙ—o e ji'oowo potataa,"
  35,20,"wonaa niЙ“e Й—en e ndaygu ngun,"
  35,21,"wonaa Й—owdi ndi e henndu wulndu ndu."
  35,22,"Wonaa kadi wuurЙ“e Й“en potata e maayЙ“e Й“en. Pellet, Alla no nanina on mo o muuyani. Wanaa an [NulaaЙ—o], woni naninoowo, wonЙ“e ka genaale Й“een."
  35,23,"Aan a wonaani, si wonaa jerrtinoowo."
  35,24,"Pellet, Min nulirii ma goonga, ko a beltinoowo e jeertinoowo. Alaa e mofte, si wonaa jerrtinoowo feЖҙЖҙii e maЙ“Й“e."
  35,25,"Si Й“e njeddii ma, hari adinooЙ“e Й“e Й“en njedduno (NulaaЙ“e mum), feewndo Й“en NulaaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e ngaddannoo Й“anngannduyeeji, e ЖҠeri e feftere ndayginoore."
  35,26,"Refti nanngitir mi yedduЙ“e Й“en (halakuyee). Tesko no lepte am Й—en mbaЙ—tinirnoo."
  35,27,"E a yiaani won'de Alla jippinirii ndiyam ka kammu? Min puЙ—iniri Й—am dimЙ—e ceertuЙ—e noone. Hino ka pelle, Й—ate daneeje e boЙ—eeje ceertyuЙ—e noone, e pete Й“aleeje."
  35,28,"Hino e yimЙ“e Й“en, e daabeeji Й—in, e neemoraaЙ—i Й—in, Й—i nooneeji mum kadi luutondiri. Anndu ko kulata Alla e jiyaaЙ“e makko Й“een, ko annduЙ“e Й“en. Pellet, Alla ko pooluЙ—o, kaforoowo."
  35,29,"ЖҒeen janngooЙ“e deftere Alla nden, Й“e ГұiiЙ“i e Juulde, Й“e nafqii ko Min arsiki Й“e kon gunndoo e kene, heЙ“e njoortii njulaaku ngu sontataa."
  35,30,"Fii no [Alla] hunnirana Й“e njoЙ“diiji maЙ“Й“e Й—in, o Й“eyda Й“e e Й“ural makko ngal. KaЕӢko, ko o kaforoowo, gannditanoowo [on] ."
  35,31,"Kon ko Min wahayini e maaЙ—a e deftere nden, ko Й—uum woni goonga, gooЕӢЙ—inde e Й—en won'Й—e ye'eso mayre. Pellet, Alla ko kumpitiiЙ—o deentuЙ—o jiyaaЙ“e makko Й“en."
  35,32,"Refti Min ndonini deftere nden, Й“en Й“e Min cuЙ“ii e jiyaaЙ“e Amen. Hino e maЙ“Й“e tooГұЙ“e hoore-mun, mum hino e maЙ“Й“e hakindinЙ—o, hino e maЙ“Й“e foolondirooЙ“e e moЖҙЖҙereeji, duЕӢayee Alla; ko Й—um woni Й“ural mawnungal ngal."
  35,33,"Aljannaaji ГұiiЙ“al, Й—i naatata e mum, hara heЙ“e cuЙ—iree ton, jawe kaЕӢЕӢe e kaalise e luвҖҷu-luвҖҷu; comci maЙ“Й“e Й—in ton, ko cooyi."
  35,34,"ЖҒe mbi'a: "jettooje Ngoodanii Alla, On ittanЙ—o en suno. Pellet, Joomi men, ko kaforoowo, barjotooЙ—o."
  35,35,"On jippinirЙ—o en Й“ural makko ngal, e galle ГұiiЙ“al, tampere (woo) heЙ“ataa en ton, wonaa roЕӢkere keЙ“ata en ton."
  35,36,"YedduЙ“e Й“en kan, ko Yiite Jahannama woodani Й“en; maayde Гұaawetaake e maЙ“Й“e, sakko Й“e maaya, Й“e koynantaake kadi lepte magge Й—en. Ko wano nii Min njoЙ“itirta kala jedduЙ—o."
  35,37,"Hara heЙ“e ooloo nder ton [Й“e mbi'a]: "Joomi amen, yaltin min; min ngolla moЖҙЖҙere, hara wonah ko min ngollatnoo kon". [O jaaboo Й“e]: "E min wuurnaano on yeru ko waajitotooЙ—o waajitoranoo e mum? Jeertinoowo kadi ari e mon? Awa meeЙ—ee, sabu faabo alanaa tooГұooЙ“e Й“en"."
  35,38,"Pellet, Alla ko gannduЙ—o wirniiЙ—i kammuuji Й—in e leydi ndin. Ko O gannduЙ—o ko suuЙ—ii e Й“erЙ—e."
  35,39,"Ko KaЕӢko woni baЙ—uЙ—o on lomtiiЙ“e ka leydi. Kala jedduЙ—o, ko e makko lorra jeddi makko yantata. Jeddugol he'eferЙ“e Й“en, Й“eydataa Й“e ka Joomi maЙ“Й“e, si wanaa tikkere. Jeddugol Й“eydataa heeferЙ“e Й“en, si wanaa hayrere."
  35,40,"Maaku: "E on nji'ii rendiiЙ—i mon ndewoton ga Alla Й—in? Kollee Kam ko Й—i tagi ka leydi. Kaa hiЙ—i mari geЙ—al e [tagugol] kammuuji Й—in? Kaa Min addan Й“e deftere, nde Й“e woni e Й“anndannduyee mum? Si ko woni, tooГұooЙ“e Й“en alaa e fodude yoga maЙ“Й“e, si wanaa hodo"."
  35,41,"Pellet, ko Alla jogitii kammuuji Й—in e leydi ndin, fii wata Й—i dirtu. Hay si Й—i ndirtayno, hay gooto jogitotaako Й—i e Й“aawo makko. O laatike muГұГұiiЙ—o, kaforoowo."
  35,42,"ЖҒe ngoodndiri Alla, hattirde e goondooje maЙ“Й“e, won'de si jeertinoowo arii e maЙ“Й“e, pellet, Й“e ngonay Й“urЙ“e feewude wootere e mofte Й—en. Nde jeertinoowo non arunoo e maЙ“Й“e, Й—um Й“eydaali Й“e, si wonaa woЙ—Й—itagol."
  35,43,"[ЖҒe mbaЙ—iri Й—um] mawnintinaare ka keydi, e pewje Й“enЙ—e. Pewje bonЙ—e Й—en non kuuЙ“itataa, si wonaa jom-munm en. Hara hiЙ“e cabbitii, si wonaa sunna (Alla) on e adinooЙ“e Й“en? A heЙ“antaa sunna Alla on battiigu, a heЙ“antaa sunna Alla mbaylirЙ—um."
  35,44,"E Й“ee njiilaaki ka leydi, Й“e taskoo ko holno battane adinooЙ“e Й“en wonirnoo? Hari no Й“uri Й“e tiiЙ—ude doole. Alla siforaali won'de goЙ—Й—um no roЕӢkina Mo ka kammuuji maa ka leydi. Tawde pellet, ko O gannduЙ—o, kattanЙ—o."
  35,45,"Si tawno Alla nanngitirayno yimЙ“e Й“en ko Й“e paggitorii kon, o accataano ruugayngel e dow mayri. Ko woni tan, Homo neeЙ“nitana Й“e haa e lajal anndaa ngal. Si lajal maЙ“Й“e ngal heewtii, [O nanngay Й“e], tawde pellet, Alla ko deenuЙ—o jiyaaЙ“e makko Й“en."
  36,1,"yaa-siin."
  36,2,"Mi wooЙ—ndirii Al*ur'aana ГұeГұaande nde."
  36,3,"Pellet, an (NulaaЙ—o), ko a jiyaaЙ—o e nulaaЙ“e Й“en."
  36,4,"E dow laawol pocciingol."
  36,5,"Jippinannde On poolЙ—o, jurmotooЙ—o o."
  36,6,"Fii yo a jeertinirde nde yimЙ“e, Й“e baabiraaЙ“e mum jerrtinanooka: Й“een ko welsindiiЙ“e."
  36,7,"GooЕӢЙ—ii konngol [lepte] jojjii e ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e maЙ“Й“e; Й“en Й—oon gooЕӢЙ—intaa."
  36,8,"Minen Min mbaЙ—ii ka daaЙ—e maЙ“Й“e kolommbooje, Й—en ko jottiiЙ—e ka bokkuЙ—e; hara ko Й“e ЕӢalliniiЙ“e."
  36,9,"Min mbaЙ—i ye'eso maЙ“Й“e heedo, Й“aawo maЙ“Й“e kadi heedo, Min kippi Й“e (gite Й—en); mbaЙ—ti Й“e nj'ataa [goonga]."
  36,10,"Hino fota e maЙ“Й“e, foti a jeertini Й“e, maa a jeertinaali Й“e; Й“e ngooЕӢЙ—intaa."
  36,11,"Anndu ko njeertintaa (jaЙ“a), ko on jokkuЙ—o JaЕӢtoore (Alqur'aana) nden, o kuli Jom-Yurmeende On ka wirnii. Wewlinir mo kaforaneede e mbarjaari teddundi."
  36,12,"Ko Minen ngoni wuurnitooЙ“e maayЙ“e Й“en, Min mbinnda ko Й“e ngardini e batteeji maЙ“Й“e. Kala hu'unde, MiЙ—en mofti nde e deftere Й“anngunde."
  36,13,"Piyan-Й“e yeru, fii yimЙ“e saare, tuma nde NulaaЙ“e ngarunoo Й“e,"
  36,14,"Nde Min nulunoo e maЙ“Й“e, [NulaaЙ“e] Й—iЙ—o, Й“e njeddii i Й“en, Min cammbiniri Й“en, tataЙ“o, Й“e mbi'i: "Minen, ko men NulaaЙ“e e mo'on"."
  36,15,"[YimЙ“e saare nden] wi'i: "On ngonaani, si wanaa ko on Й“anndiЕӢke wano menen. Jom-hinaranke On jippinaani hay hu'unde, on wonaani, si wanaa ko on fenooЙ“e"."
  36,16,"[NulaaЙ“e Й“en] mbi'i: "Joomi amen no anndi pellet, ko min NulaaЙ“e e mo'on."
  36,17,"Fawaaki men non, si wonaa jottingol Й“anngina"."
  36,18,"[YimЙ“e saare nden] mbi'iti: "Min kiitori on kataa. Si tawii non on kaЙ—itaaki, ma min piЙ—u on, lepte mu'usuuЙ—e kadi memira on immorde e amen"."
  36,19,"[NulaaЙ“e Й“en kadi] mb'iti: "Kiite mon Й—in, hiЙ—on ngon'di e mum. Ko si on mbaajaama (kiitinoЙ—on)? Tigi on, ko on yimЙ“e fantinooЙ“e!"."
  36,20,"Gorko iwri ka Й“uri woЙ—Й—ude e saare nden, o ari homo yaccoo, o wi'i: "eey mon yo yimЙ“e am, kori njokkee NulaaЙ“e Й“en,"
  36,21,"Njokkee Й“en Й“e laЙ“ndotaako on njoЙ“di, Й“en ko feewnaaЙ“e."
  36,22,"E ko haЙ—ata kam rewugol On takЙ—o Kam? Ko ka makko woni ruttorde mon."
  36,23,"E mi jogtoto deweteeЙ—i ga makko? Si Jom-yurmeende On muuyanii kam lorra, tefoore majji duncantaali kam hay hu'unde, Й—i ndaЙ—andataa kam kadi."
  36,24,"Haray miin on tuma, mi wonii e majjere Й“anngunde."
  36,25,"Min on, mi gooЕӢЙ—inii Joomi mon, nananee kam"."
  36,26,"[O] wi'anaa: "Naatu Aljanna". O wi'i: "Haaniino yimЙ“e am Й“en ngannda,"
  36,27,"ko Joomi am haforani kam, O waЙ—i kam e teddinaaЙ“e Й“een"."
  36,28,"Min njippiniraano koneeli ka kammu, e yimЙ“e makko Й“en, Й“aawo maako. Min ngonaanii jippinooЙ“e [Й—in koneeli]."
  36,29,"(Halkeede maЙ“Й“e) wonaani, si wonaa haacaango wooto, tawi Й“e laatii maayЙ“e-Й“utti."
  36,30,"Ee hayreede jiyaaЙ“e [fenunooЙ“e]! NulaaЙ—o araali e Й“Й“e, si wonaa Й“e waЙ—tayno mo jalnori."
  36,31,"E Й“ee njiaani Й—uuЙ—ii e gire Й—e Min kalki ado maЙ“Й“e? Won'de Й“en ndttitotaako e maЙ“Й“e."
  36,32,"ЖҒe fof wonaani, si wanaa ko mooЙ“oyteeЙ“e ka amen."
  36,33,"Hino wonani Й“e Ma'ande: leydi yoorundi ndin, Min nuurniti ndi, Min njaltini gabbe e mayri, tawi ko e Й—en Й“e Гұaamata."
  36,34,"Min mbaЙ—i e mayri gese tamarooje e inabuuje, Min Й“ulni e mayri Й“ulli(ceewle)"
  36,35,"fii no Й“e Гұaamira dimЙ—e mun Й—en e kon ko Й“e golliri juuЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en. E Й“e njettataa (Alla)?"
  36,36,"Senaade woodanii takЙ—o nooneeji Й—in On fof: gila e ko leydi ndin fuЙ—inta kon, haa e woЕӢkiiji maЙ“Й“e Й—in, e kon ko Й“e nganndaa!"
  36,37,"Ma'ande goo kadi wonanii Й“e: e jemma on, MiЙ—en corta e makko Гұalawma on, tawa Й“e ngontii e niwre."
  36,38,"E na'ange ngen, hinge doga haa e ГұiiЙ“irde magge; Й—um ko eЙ“Й“oore pooluЙ—o, gannduЙ—o On."
  36,39,"E lewru ndun, Min eЙ“Й“ani ndu jipporde, haa ndu waЙ—tinira wa baaЕӢal tamaro kiiЙ—ngal."
  36,40,"Wonaa na'ange ngen woni ko haanini hewtitagol lewru ndun, wonaa jemma on woni ko aditotoo Гұalaema on; kala majji non, ko e laawol mum woni dokde."
  36,41,"Ma'ande goo wonanii Й“e, won'de Min roondike geyngol maЙ“Й“e ngol, ka laana hebbinaaka;"
  36,42,"Min tagani Й“e sugu makko, ko Й“e mbaЙ—Й—oo."
  36,43,"Si MiЙ—en njiЙ—uno, Min njoolayno Й“e; hara faabo alanaa Й“e, wanaa kadi Й“e daЙ—ndeteeЙ“e,"
  36,44,"si wonaa yurmeende immornde e amen, e dakmitagol haa e saanga."
  36,45,"Si Й“e mbi'anaama: "ndentee e kon ko woni yeeso mon e Й“aawo mon, mbelajo'o, on njurminte"...!"
  36,46,"Aaya woo e aayeeje Joomi maЙ“Й“e Й—en araali e maЙ“Й“e, si wanaa Й“e Й—uurnooЙ—e."
  36,47,"Si Й“e mbianaama kadi: "Wintee(nafqe) e kon Alla arsiki on", yedduЙ“e Й“en mbi'ana gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“en: "E men Гұamminay on tawЙ—o si Alla muuyuno, O Гұamminayno mo? On ngonaani, si wanaa e ndeer majjere Й“anngunde"."
  36,48,"HiЙ“e mbi'a: "Ko holnde tuma woni ndee Fodoore, si on laatike gooЕӢЙ—uЙ“e?""
  36,49,"ЖҒe habbaaki, si wonaa ha'acaango wooto, nanngayngo Й“e, hara hiЙ“e njeddondira."
  36,50,"ЖҒe mbaawoytaa wasiyagol on tuma, wonaa Й“e ruttoytooЙ“e e yimЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en."
  36,51,"Wutte e alaandu, Й“e njaltira e genaale Й—en, Й“e keГұora ka Joomi maЙ“Й“e,"
  36,52,"hiЙ“e mbi'a: "Ee bone amen! Ko hommbo immini men e genaale amen?" Ko Й—um woni ko Hinaranke On fodnoo; NulaaЙ“e Й“e o gooЕӢЙ—ini"
  36,53,"(Ummital) ngal wonaano, si wanaa haacaango wo'oto, tawi Й“e fof Й“e ngaaddaama ka Amen."
  36,54,"Hannde non, woЕӢkii tooГұirtaake hay hu'unde. On yoЙ“itirtaake, si wonaa kon ko ngollaynoЙ—on."
  36,55,"YimЙ“e Aljanna Й“e hannde, pellet, heЙ“e e ndeer soklio, hiЙ“e neeminoo;"
  36,56,"kamЙ“e e genndiraaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en,e ley Й—owЙ—e, heЙ“e coЙ“Й“indii e hoore danЙ—e."
  36,57,"Hino woodani Й“e toon, Й“iЙ—Й“e leЙ—Й—e, hino woodani kadi, ko ko Й“e noddata."
  36,58,""Salaamun", konngol [kisal], immorde e JoomiraaЙ—o, jurmotooЙ—o."
  36,59,""ceertee non hande, onon Й“ee bonЙ“e!"
  36,60,"Mi ahodaano e mon, onon Й“iЙ—Й“e Aadama, won'de wota on ndewu seytaane? Tawde pellet, ko o gaГұo mon Й“annguЙ—o,"
  36,61,"[Mi yamiri on] kadi dewugol Kam. Ko ngol woni laawol pocciingol ngol."
  36,62,"GooЕӢЙ—ii o majjinii tagu Й—uuЙ—ungu e mon. E on wonaano haqqilooЙ“e?"
  36,63,"Ko ngee woni Jahannama, nge ngonnoЙ—on fodaneede ngen."
  36,64,"Naatiree nge hannde, sabu ko njeddiratnoЙ—on."
  36,65,"Hannde, Min notay e kunndule maЙ“Й“e Й—en, juuЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en yewta Min, koyЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en kadi seeditoo e kon ko Й“e ngonnoo e paggitagol"."
  36,66,"Si Min njiЙ—uno, Min mehayno gite maЙ“Й“e Й—en, Й“e adondira e laawol ngol. Kono ko honno Й“e njiirata?"
  36,67,"Si Min njЙ—uno kadi, Min montatno Й“e e nokku maЙ“Й“e on; hara Й“e hattantaa feЖҙЖҙugol Й“e yiltotaako."
  36,68,"Kala mo Min njuutni nguurndam mum, Men njiltitay mo e tagoore. E Й“ee haqqiltaa?"
  36,69,"Min ngaanndinaali mo (kaЕӢko Muhammadu) gimЙ—i; Й—uum haananaa mo. [Deftere] nden wonaani, si wanaa jaЕӢtoore e janngeteende Й“anngunde,"
  36,70,"fii yo o jeertin nde, on gonЙ—o guurЙ—o (Й“ernde), Konngol lepte ngol jojja e he'eferЙ“e Й“en."
  36,71,"E Й“e yiaani, won'de Min tagiranii Й“e neemoraaЙ—i, e ko juuЙ—e Amen ngolli, hara heЙ“e njeyinooЙ—i;"
  36,72,"Min eeltani Й“e Й—i: no e majji Й—i Й“e waЙ—Й—otoo, no e majji Й—i Й“e Гұaamata;"
  36,73,"hino woodani Й“e toon, nafooje e njaram. E Й“ee kan njettataa (Mo)?"
  36,74,"ЖҒe jogitorii ga Alla deweteeЙ—i, joortagol Й“e faabeedee."
  36,75,"ЖҠi kattanaa paabagol Й“e; ko Й“e konu tawneteengu e majji."
  36,76,"Wota konngol maЙ“Й“e sunine. Pellet, MiЙ—en nganndi ko Й“e cuuЙ—ata e ko Й“e peГұГұinta."
  36,77,"E neЙ—Й—aЕӢke on yiaani, won'de Min tagirii mo e toЙ“Й“ere maniiyu? Kono tawaa mo ko o wennjoowo Й“annguЙ—o!"
  36,78,"O fiyani Min yeru, kono o yejjiti tageede makko; o wi'i: "Ko hommbo wuurnitata Жҙi'e Й—en, si Й—e ndappii?""
  36,79,"Maaku: "Ko guurnitoowo Й—e, ko takЙ—o Й—e on ka laawol aranol. Ko KaЕӢko woni gannduЙ—o fii kala tagoore;"
  36,80,"On mbЙ—anЙ—o on yiite, iwde e leЙ—Й—e kecce, tawa ko e majje kuЙ“Й“irton nge."
  36,81,"Kere takЙ—o kammuuji Й—in e leydi ndin wonaani kaЙ—tanЙ—o tagugol yeru maЙ“Й“e? ЖҠuum ko pellet! Ko KaЕӢko woni ЖҠuuЙ—uЙ—o tageefo, gannduЙ—o."
  36,82,"Ganndon fiyaaku makko on, si o faandanike hu'unde, ko o wi'anat nde tan: "Laato", nde laatoo."
  36,83,"Senaare woodanii oon mo laamateeri kala hu'unde ngoni e juuЙ—e Mum! Ko ka makko rutteteЙ—on."
  37,1,"Mi wooЙ—ndirii cappniraaЙ—i Й—in saffaaji."
  37,2,"Mi wooЙ—ndirii coggirayЙ—i (duule) Й—in coggugol."
  37,3,"Mi wooЙ—ndirii janngiratЙ—i Й—in, ganndintinorgol:"
  37,4,""Pellet, deweteeЙ—o mon on, ko bajjo,"
  37,5,"JeyЙ—o kammuuji Й—in e leydi ndin, e kon ko woni hakkunde Й—in Й—iЙ—i, JeyЙ—o kadi puЙ—irЙ—e Й—en."
  37,6,"Min cuЙ—irii kammu (hikkii ngu) aduna ngun: cuЙ—aari koode Й—een,"
  37,7,"e deenirgol (ngu) kala seytaane daЙ—aandu."
  37,8,"ЖҠi kaЙ—tanaaka keЙ—itagol mbatu [Maleykaaji toowu ngu ngun; tawde hiЙ—i peroree e kala baЕӢЕӢe,"
  37,9,"ka faЙ—agol (Й—i). Hino woodani Й—i kadi, lepte duumiiЙ—e."
  37,10,"Si wonaa ndun bifti ndu e majji, jilannde [haala], ndu rewnree hoodere tufatnde."
  37,11,"LaЙ“ndo Й“e: si ko kamЙ“e Й“uri saЙ—tude takde kaa ko Й“en Й“e Min tagi? Min tagirii Й“e kamЙ“e, loopal narnungal."
  37,12,"Si ko woni, a haawi, heЙ“e njalnora!"
  37,13,"Si Й“e mbaajaama, Й“e mbajitortaa;"
  37,14,"si Й“e nji'ii ma'ande, Й“e njalkita,"
  37,15,"Й“e mbii'a: "ЖҠuum wonaani, si wonaa mbilewu Й“anngu ngu."
  37,16,"Eyoo si min maayii, min ngontii mbullaari e Жҙi'e, haray ko min immintinoyteeЙ“e?""
  37,17,"BaabiraaЙ“e amin adinooЙ“e Й“een kadi e minen?""
  37,18,"Maaku: "pellet! Hara le ko on hoynaaЙ“e"."
  37,19,"Nganndon Й—um, ko wuttaandu wo'oturu pet, tawee jaka yoo, heЙ“e ndaara,"
  37,20,"ЖҒe mbi'a: Ee bone amen ! Ko ndee woni Г‘aaande njoЙ“di kuuЙ—e"."
  37,21,""Ko ndee woni Г‘alaande Гұaawoore, ko njeddatnoЙ—on fii mum"."
  37,22,"MooЙ“ee tooГұЙ“e Й“en, e nandadiiЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en, e kon ko Й“e ngonnoo e rewde,"
  37,23,"ko woori Alla. CoggireeЙ“e ka laawol Jahiimi."
  37,24,"Ndarnon Й“e, tawde ko Й“e laЙ“nditeteeЙ“e"."
  37,25,""Ko heЙ“i on, on mballindirtaa?""
  37,26,"Ko woni kamЙ“e Й“e hannde, ko Й“e jebbilii Й“e,"
  37,27,"woЙ—Й“e e maЙ“Й“e peewtita Й“eya, Й“e laЙ“ndondira;"
  37,28,"Й“e mbi'a: "Ko onon ngoni ko ardiranaynoo men, ka Й“aЕӢЕӢe Гұaamo"."
  37,29,"(KoohooЙ“e) Й“en mbi'a: "Ko woni kon, on meeЙ—aano won'de gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e."
  37,30,"Doole woo min ngalanaano on. Si ko woni, on ngonno yimЙ“e bewЙ“e."
  37,31,"Konngol Joomi men ngol, jojjii e min; pellet, ko en meeЙ—ooЙ“e [lepte Й—en]."
  37,32,"Min mbewinno on, tawde hay minen, ko min bewnooЙ“e"."
  37,33,"KamЙ“e on nden Гұande, ko Й“e haawtoyteeЙ“e ka lepte."
  37,34,"Ko nii Minen Min ngollirtata bomЙ“e Й“en."
  37,35,"KamЙ“e si Й“e mbi'anooma: "deweteeЙ—o alaa si wonaa Alla", Й“e mawnintinoo."
  37,36,"Й“e mbi'a: "Kere men ngaccitiray deweteeЙ—i amen Й—in, fii yimoowo kaangaaЙ—o?""
  37,37,"Si ko woni, (NulaaЙ—o) on ko goonga ardi, o goongini nulaaЙ“e Й“en."
  37,38,"Pellet, ko on meeЙ—ay Й“e lepte mu'usuuЙ—e Й—en."
  37,39,"On njoЙ“etetaake, si wonaa yeru kon ko ngollatnoЙ—on."
  37,40,"si wonaa jiyaaЙ“e Alla laЙ“Й“inaaЙ“e Й“en,"
  37,41,"hino woodani Й“en Й—oon, fanndaare ganndaandi:"
  37,42,"muuyanteeЙ—i, kadi ko Й“e teddinteeЙ“e,"
  37,43,"ka aljannaaji neeminiiЙ—i,"
  37,44,"e hoore danЙ—e, ko Й“e feewtondirЙ“e."
  37,45,"Hara kore heЙ—e mbannginii e maЙ“Й“e, immorde e Й“ulirde"
  37,46,"daneeje, lewГұunde, fii yarooЙ“e,"
  37,47,"mu'usuuЙ—e hoore alaa e majjam, wonaa Й—am ciwrinirteeЙ“e Й—am."
  37,48,"Hino woodani Й“e (toon): raЙ“Й“uЙ“e ndaarЙ—e, yaaja giteeЙ“e,"
  37,49,"wa'aЙ“e wa Й“occooЙ—e maraaЙ—e."
  37,50,"WoЙ—Й“e e maЙ“Й“e peewtita Й“eya, Й“e laЙ“ndondira."
  37,51,"GoЙ—Й—o e maЙ“Й“e wi'a: "Min miЙ—o marunoo gonndiijo,"
  37,52,"wi'atnooЙ—o: "Kere ko a jiyaaЙ—o e gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“en?"
  37,53,"Eyoo si en maayii, en wontii mbullaari e Жҙi'e, tawa ko en yoЙ“itoyteeЙ“e?""
  37,54,"O wi'a: "Taw si Й—on njiЙ—i Жҙeewde?""
  37,55,"O Жҙeewa, o haynoo oya ka leri dulbunge,"
  37,56,"o wi'a: "Mi wooЙ—ndirii Alla ! A Й—eЙ“Й“i fii no mi halkorde!"
  37,57,"Si wonaano moЖҙЖҙere Joomi am nden, mi tawdeteno e [lepteteeЙ“e Й“een]."
  37,58,"Wonaa noon en maayataa,"
  37,59,"si wonaa maayde men aranere nden, en wngonaani kadi lepteteeЙ“e?""
  37,60,"Pellet, ko Й—uum Й—oo woni maloore mawnude ndeen."
  37,61,"Ko fii sugu Й—uum Й—oo, woni yo gollooЙ“e ngollan."
  37,62,"Hara ko Й—uum Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude jipporde, kaa ko leggal "Zaqquumi" [ngal kaaЙ—ugal]?"
  37,63,"Min mbaЙ—ii ngal jarrabuyee tooГұЙ“e Й“en."
  37,64,"Ngal, ko leggal jaltatngal ka tummbere Dulbunge."
  37,65,"DimЙ—e maggal, hono wa'i no ko'e seytanooji."
  37,66,"KamЙ“e Й“e, pellet, ko e maggal Й“e Гұaamirta, Й“e kebbinira ngal deedi maЙ“Й“e."
  37,67,"Refti hino woodani Й“e e dow maggal, njaram patinaaЙ—am."
  37,68,"Refti ruttorde maЙ“Й“e ndeen, ko ka DulЙ“oowe."
  37,69,"ЖҒe tawu baabiraaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“een, ko majjunooЙ“e,"
  37,70,"Й“e ngoni e yaccagol njokka baЙ—teeji maЙ“Й“e."
  37,71,"GooЕӢЙ—ii, ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e adamЙ“e Й“en, majjiino, ado maЙ“Й“e."
  37,72,"GooЕӢЙ—ii le, Min nuluno e maЙ“Й“e, jeertinooЙ“e."
  37,73,"Kono ndaaru baЙ—tane Й“ren jeertinanooЙ“e, no wa'anoo!"
  37,74,"Si wonaa jiyaaЙ“e Alla, laЙ“Й“inaaЙ“e Й“en."
  37,75,"GooЕӢЙ—ii Nuuhu nodduno Min, Min moЖҙЖҙii jaabotooЙ“e."
  37,76,"Min ndaЙ—ni mo, kaЕӢko e yimЙ“e makko Й“een, e suno mawnngo ngon,"
  37,77,"Min mbЙ—i gelngol makko ngol, heddotooЙ“e Й“en."
  37,78,"Min ngaccani mo mantoore, e sakkitiiЙ“e Й“een."
  37,79,"Kisal wonii e Nuuhu, e ndeer winndere nden."
  37,80,"Ko non woni ko Min mbarjorta moЖҙЖҙimЙ“e Й“en."
  37,81,"KaЕӢko, ko o jeyanooЙ—o e jiyaaЙ“e Amen gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“en."
  37,82,"Refti Min njooli heddii Й“e Й“een."
  37,83,"Hino jeyanoo e jokkunooЙ“e mo Й“e Ibraahiima."
  37,84,"Tuma nde ardunoo e Joomi makko, e Й“ernde hisnde."
  37,85,"Nde o maakannoo ben makko e yimЙ“e mum Й“een: "Ko holЙ—um ndewoton?"
  37,86,"E ko deweteeЙ—i pefindaaЙ—i, ko wanaa Alla, paalaЙ—on?"
  37,87,"Ko cikkuЙ—on e Joomiraawo tagoore ngon?""
  37,88,"O ndaariri ndaarande to koode,"
  37,89,"o maaki: "Ko mi ГұawnЙ—o"."
  37,90,"ЖҒe ngacci mo, Й“e nduЕӢti."
  37,91,"O mooltii e deweteeЙ—i maЙ“Й“e Й—in, o maaki: "E on Гұaamataa?"
  37,92,"Ko heЙ“i on, on kaalataa?""
  37,93,"O naatnani, fiyirde Й—i Гұaamo ngon."
  37,94,"ЖҒe peewti e makko, hiЙ“e njaawno."
  37,95,"O maaki: "E on ndeway ko lesuЙ—on!,cehЙ—on)."
  37,96,"hara le ko Alla tagi on, e ko ngolloton?""
  37,97,"ЖҒe mbi'i: "Mahanee mo mahdi, mbugoЙ—on mo ka dulЙ“ayange"."
  37,98,"ЖҒe pa'andanii mo feere; kono Min mbЙ—i Й“e sooybe Й“en."
  37,99,"O maaki: "Min on, ko mi peroowo ka Joomi am, aray nde O feewnata kam."
  37,100,"Joomi am, weeЙ—am geЙ—al moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e"."
  37,101,"Min mbeltiniri mo, geЙ—al muГұГұiiЙ—o."
  37,102,"Nde on yottinoo e makko jahal, [Ibraahiima] maaki: "Ko an Й“iЙ—Й—o am, min mi yi'ii e Й—oyngol, won'de miЙ—o hirse. Ndaaru ko yi'iЙ—aa". [Ismaa'iila] maaki: "eey ma baaba'en, mbaЙ—ee ko njamiraЙ—on kon, on tawoyay kam, si Alla jaЙ“ii, jiyaaЙ—o e muГұiiЙ“e Й“en"."
  37,103,"Nde Й“e jebbilaninoo (yamiroore Alla nden), o hippiri mo tiinde nde,"
  37,104,"Men noddiri mo wi'ide: "eey ma yo Ibraahiima !"
  37,105,"Pellet, a gooЕӢЙ—iinii koyЙ—ol ngol. Ko Minen Min njoЙ“irte moЖҙЖҙinooЙ“e Й“een"."
  37,106,"Pellet, ko Й—uum Й—oo woni jarrabuyee Й“annguЙ—o oon."
  37,107,"Min cootiri mo kirse mawЙ—e."
  37,108,"Min ngaccani mo mantoore, e sakkitiiЙ“e Й“en."
  37,109,""Kisal wonii e Ibraahiima"."
  37,110,"Ko wano nii Min njoЙ“irta moЖҙЖҙinooЙ“e Й“een."
  37,111,"KaЕӢko, ko o jiyaaЙ—o e jiyaaЙ“e Amen gooЙ—inЙ“e Й“en."
  37,112,"Min mbeltiniri Ishaaqa, Annabaajo jiyaaЙ—o e moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e Й“en."
  37,113,"Min kebbini barki e makko e Ishaaqa. Hino e geГұngol maЙ“Й“e ngol: moЖҙЖҙinЙ—o, e tooГұuЙ—o hoore-mun Й“anngini."
  37,114,"GooЕӢЙ—ii Min moЖҙЖҙike e dow Muusaa e Haaruuna,"
  37,115,"Min ndaЙ—ni Й“e, kamЙ“e e yimЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“een, e ngoЖҙo mawnungo,"
  37,116,"Min mballi Й“e, Й“e ngoni foolЙ“e Й“en."
  37,117,"Min ngokki Й“e deftere Й“annginnde ndeen."
  37,118,"Min peewniri Й“e, e laawol pocciingol ngol."
  37,119,"Min ngaccani Й“e mantoore, e sakkitiiЙ“e Й“een."
  37,120,""Kisal woni e dow Muusaa yo Haaruuna"."
  37,121,"Ko wano nii Min noЙ“itirta moЖҙЖҙimЙ“e Й“en."
  37,122,"KamЙ“e Й—iЙ—o, ko Й“e jiyanooЙ“e e jiyaaЙ“e Amen gooЙ—iinЙ“e Й“en."
  37,123,"Pellet, Ilyaasa kadi, ko jeyanooЙ—o e NulaaЙ“e Й“een."
  37,124,"JaЕӢto nde o maakannoo yimЙ“e makko Й“en: "E on kulataa [Alla]?"
  37,125,"E ko "Ba'ala" ndewoton, ngaccon Й“urЙ—o moЖҙЖҙude tagoore nde?"
  37,126,"Woni Alla, JeyЙ—o on, Jeyi baabiraaЙ“e mon adinooЙ“e Й“een?""
  37,127,"ЖҒe njeddii mo, awa non, ko Й“e tawnoyteeЙ“e (ka lepte)."
  37,128,"Si wonaa jiyaaЙ“e Alla laЙ“Й“inaaЙ“e Й“een."
  37,129,"Min ngaccani mo mantoore, e sakkitiiЙ“e Й“en."
  37,130,""Kisal woni e dow Ilyaasiina'en"."
  37,131,"Ko wano nii Min njoЙ“irta moЖҙЖҙimЙ“e Й“een."
  37,132,"KaЕӢko, ko o jeyanooЙ—o e jiyaaЙ“e Amen gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“en."
  37,133,"Pellet, Luutu kadi, ko jiyanooЙ—o e NulaaЙ“e Й“een."
  37,134,"JaЕӢto nde Min ndaЙ—ndunoo mo, kaЕӢko e Й“eynguure makko nden fof,"
  37,135,"si wonaa nayeeja debba, tawaaЙ—o e luttunooЙ“e Й“een,"
  37,136,"refti Min oЖҙЖҙi heddii Й“e Й“een."
  37,137,"Onon non, hoЙ—on ndewa e hoore-maЙ“Й“e, dawol mon."
  37,138,"e jemma. E on kaqqiltaa?"
  37,139,"Pellet, Yuunusa kadi, ko jiyanooЙ—o e NulaaЙ“e Й“een."
  37,140,"JaЕӢto nde o dogirnoo ka laana hebbinaaka,"
  37,141,"o urbinii, o jiyaa e foolaaЙ“e Й“een."
  37,142,"Liinngii ngii moЙ—i mo, ko o pelniiЙ—o."
  37,143,"Si wonaano tawde homo jeyanoo e subbunhinotooЙ“e Й“en,"
  37,144,"o ГұiiЙ“ayno e reedu maggii, ha Гұalnde ummintinoytee."
  37,145,"Min mberlii mo ka ladde, ko o ГұawnЙ—o."
  37,146,"Min puЙ—ini e mayre, leggal buudi."
  37,147,"Min nuli mo e ujune teemeder yimЙ“e, maa ko Й“uri."
  37,148,"ЖҒe ngooЕӢЙ—ini, Min ndakmiti Й“e haa e dumunna."
  37,149,"LaЙ“ndii Й“e:" E ko Joomi maa woodanta Й“iЙ“Й“e rewЙ“e, kamЙ“e kan worЙ“e?"
  37,150,"Kaa Min tagir Maley'ikaaaji dewwЙ—inaaЙ—i, hara ko Й“e seediiЙ“e?""
  37,151,"Paamee, kamЙ“e e pepindaale maЙ“Й“e Й—en, hiЙ“e mbi'a:"
  37,152,""Allah jibinii"; pellet, Й“e penat"
  37,153,"Hara O cuЙ“ay Й“iЙ“Й“e rewЙ“e Й“en e dow worЙ“e Й“en?"
  37,154,"Ko heЙ“i on, si Й—on Гұaawira noon?"
  37,155,"E on miijtottaako?"
  37,156,"Kaa hoЙ—on njogii hujja Й“annguЙ—o?"
  37,157,"Haray ngaddee deftere mon nden, si wonii ko on gooЕӢЙ—uЙ“e!"."
  37,158,"ЖҒe mbaЙ—i hakkunde makko e Maleykaaji, asko; hara non, Maleykaaji no nganndi, Й“en ko tawnoyteeЙ“e (ka lepte)."
  37,159,"Senaare woodani Allah, e ko Й“e cifotoo!"
  37,160,"Si wonaa jiyaaЙ“e Allah laЙ“Й“inaaЙ“e Й“en."
  37,161,"Nganndon onon e ko ndewoton kon,"
  37,162,"on ngonaani majjinooЙ“e Й—uum [goЙ—Й—o goo],"
  37,163,"si wonaa tawЙ—o on ko naatoowo ka DulЙ“aynge."
  37,164,"[Maleykaaji mbi'i'i]: "Alaa e amen, mo alanaa Й—um, darorЙ—e ganndaande;"
  37,165,"Ko minen ngoni oni saffinaaЙ“e Й“een;"
  37,166,"Ko minen kadi ngoni subbunhinotooЙ“e Й“en."
  37,167,"ЖҒe ngoniino e bii'gol:"
  37,168,""Hara deftere iwnde e adinooЙ“e Й“een, no woodannoo min,"
  37,169,"min ngonayno jiyaaЙ“e Allah laЙ“Й“inaaЙ“e."
  37,170,"ЖҒe njeddi nde, kono aray Й“e nganndoya !"
  37,171,"GooЕӢЙ—ii Konngol Amen ardinoke, fii jiyaaЙ“e Amen, NulaaЙ“e Й“en,"
  37,172,"won'de pellet, ko kamЙ“e ngoni walleteeЙ“e Й“en,"
  37,173,"e won'de ko konu Amen ngun, woni foolooЙ“e Й“en."
  37,174,"ЖҠuurno Й“ee, ha e saanga;"
  37,175,"ndaaraa Й“e, Й“e aray nji'a!"
  37,176,"E hara ko lepte amen men Й—en Й“e keГұorta?"
  37,177,"Si Й—e njippike ka tannde (dingiral)maЙ“Й“e, haray bimmbi waajonooЙ“e Й“een bonii !"
  37,178,"ЖҠuurno Й“ee, ha e saanga;"
  37,179,"ndaaraa, Й“e aray nji'a!"
  37,180,"Senaare woodanii Joomi maa, JeyЙ—o teddungal, e ko Й“e cifotoo !"
  37,181,"Kisal wonii e NulaaЙ“e Й“en,"
  37,182,"Jettooje ngoodani Allah, JeyЙ—o winndere nden!"
  38,1,"Saad. Mi wooЙ—ndirii Alqur'aana, jom waa."
  38,2,"Si ko woni, yedduЙ“e Й“e ngonii e townitaare e lurral !"
  38,3,"ЖҠuuЙ—ii e gire Й—en Min kalki, ado maЙ“Й“e, Й“e noddi faabo, kono tawi ko bonatno bonii."
  38,4,"ЖҒe ЕӢalЙ—i, nde jeertinoowo jiyaaЙ—o e maЙ“Й“e, arata Й“e. YedduЙ“e Й“en mbi'i: "Oo, ko bileejo keewuЙ—o fenaande,"
  38,5,"Kere o waЙ—ay deweteeЙ—i Й—in, deweteeЙ—o gooto? Pellet, Й—um ko hu'unde haawniinde non"."
  38,6,"Mbatu maЙ“Й“e ngun huccitiri wiide: "Yehee, tabiton e deweteeЙ—i mon Й—in. ЖҠuum Й—oo, ko hu'unde eЙ“Й“anaande."
  38,7,"Min nanaali fii Й—um, e diina sakkitiika kan. ЖҠum wonaani, si wonaa ko fefkindaa."
  38,8,"Kere ko e makko JaЕӢtoore nden jippotoo hakkunde amen?" Si ko woni, Й“e ngonii e cikkitagol Jantoore am nden. Wurin, ko fii Й“e meeЙ—aali taho, lepte am Й—en!"
  38,9,"Kaa Й“e njogiti ngaluuji yurmeende Joomi maa, pooluЙ—o, Dokko O?"
  38,10,"Kaa ko kamЙ“e woodani laamagol kammuuji Й—in e leydi ndin e ko woni hakkunde majji? Haray yo Й“e ЖҙeenЕӢu Й“e Жҙawa!"
  38,11,"Ko Й“e konu hoyngu no, foolet e 'peЙ—le Й—en!"
  38,12,"Ado maЙ“Й“e, yimЙ“e Nuuhu Й“en njedduno, e Aadi'en e Fir'awna jom-peme,"
  38,13,"e Samuuda'en, e yimЙ“e Luutu Й“e, e yimЙ“e pitaaji Й“en; ko Й“een ngoni fedde (fennuЙ“e) Й“een."
  38,14,"Kala Й“ee wonaani, si wonaa o njeddi ii NulaaЙ“e Й“en. Lepte Am Й—en jojji e maЙ“Й“e!"
  38,15,"ЖҒee cabbaaki, si wonaa ha'acaango gooto, ngo alaa ruttorde."
  38,16,"ЖҒe mbii': "Joomi amen, yaccinan min geЙ—al lepte amen, ado Г‘alaande hasboore nden"."
  38,17,"MuГұГұo e kon ko Й“e mbi'ata; annditaa jiyaaЙ—o Amen on, Daawuuda, joom doole. Ko o Й—uuЙ—unooЙ—o tuubugol."
  38,18,"Min eeltii pelle Й—en, hiЙ—e cubbunhinoda e makko, ka kiikiiЙ—e e ka bimmbi."
  38,19,"e colli Й—in, hiЙ—i mooЙ“indiraa, kala e majji no tuubana mo."
  38,20,"Min cemmbini laamu makko ngun, Min yeЙ—i mo Annabaaku e fasinteegal."
  38,21,"Hara kumpital wenooЙ“e Й“en arii maa, nde Й“e Жҙawunoo ka ganngunal !"
  38,22,"Nde Й“e naatunoo ka Daawuuda, o Й—enЖҙii Й“e. ЖҒe mbi'i: "Wota a hul ! Ko wennjuЙ“e Й—iЙ—o; goЙ—Й—o e amen tooГұii oya. Г‘aawir goonga hakkunde amen, wota a tooГұ, tinndinaa min e laawol Pocciingol ngol."
  38,23,"Oo ko musiЙ—Й—o am: homo jogii baali cappanЙ—e jeenay e jeenay, miin miЙ—o jogii baalii gootii. O wi'i: "Henndinam ngii"; o foolimi e yeewtere."
  38,24,"O maaki: "Pellet, o tooГұirii ma laЙ“ndagol baalii maa ngii, waЙ—tugol e baali makko Й—in". ЖҠuuЙ—ii ko hawtuЙ“e tooГұindirta hakkunde maЙ“Й“e, si wonaa Й“en gooЕӢЙ—iinЙ“e, Й“e ngolli moЖҙЖҙuЙ—i - Й“en non no fanЙ—i. - Daawuuda felliti, won'de Min njarribike mo. O imsinanii Joomi makko, o suuyiri sujjugol, o tuubi."
  38,25,"Min njaafanii mo Й—um. Pellet non, hino woodani mo ko amen, Й“adal e moЖҙЖҙude ruttorde."
  38,26,"Eey ma Daawuuda, Min mbaЙ—ii ma lomto ka leydi. Г‘aawir goonga hakkunde yimЙ“e Й“en, wota a jokku mbeleeЙ—e, sakko Й—e majjine e laawol Allah ngol". Pellet, Й“en majjooЙ“e e laawol Allah ngol, hino woodani Й“e lepte tiiЙ—uЙ—e, sabu ko Й“e yejjitiri kon, Г‘alaande hasboore nden."
  38,27,"Min tagiraali kammu ngun e leydi ndin e ko woni hakkunde majji kon, meere. ЖҠum ko sikke yedduЙ“e Й“en. Bone woodanii Й“en yedduЙ“e, e Yiite ngeen!"
  38,28,"Ka Min mbЙ—ay Й“en gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“e ngolli moЖҙЖҙi, wano bonnooЙ“e Й“en ka hoore leydi? Kaa Min mbaЙ—ay gooЕӢЙ—uЙ“e Й“en, wano faajireeЙ“e Й“een?"
  38,29,"Ko deftere barkinaande, woni ko Min njippini e maaЙ—a, fii no Й“e taskora aayeeje mayre, e ko joomiraaЙ“e haqqille Й“en mbaajitora."
  38,30,"Min njeЙ—i Daawuuda Sulaymaana, - jiyaaЙ—o moЖҙЖҙo - Ko o Й—uuЙ—uЙ—o tuubugol-ruttoo."
  38,31,"JaЕӢto nde o hollanoo kiikiiЙ—e, pucci yooЙ—uЙ—i yaawuЙ—i,"
  38,32,"o maaki: "Min Й“urnorii joЙ—gol jawdi, dii ko mi jaЕӢtotoo Joomi am kon, haa [na'ange] ngen mutoyii."
  38,33,"Nduttee kam Й—i". O woni e sodugol Й—i ka taape e ka daaЙ—e."
  38,34,"GooЙ—ii Min njarribike Sulaymaana, Min mbernii e jullere makko nden Й“anndu. refti o tuubi."
  38,35,"O maaki: "Joomi am, haforanam, yeЙ—aa kam laamu, ngu heertantaako goЙ—Й—o goo, Й“aawo am. Pellet, ko an woni jeЙ—oowo On"."
  38,36,"Min eeltani mo henndu ndun, tawi hindu wifira e sago makko, neweende, nokku kala to o yiЙ—i."
  38,37,"E seytanuuji Й—iin, mahaynooЙ—i e mutaynooЙ—i."
  38,38,"GoЙ—Й—i Й—i, ko dummbaaЙ—i e peЕӢЙ—e."
  38,39,""ЖҠuum ko dokkal Amen. Okkitir, maa njogitoraa ko aldaa e laЙ“nditoreede"."
  38,40,"Ko pellet, hino woodani mo ka amen, Й“adal e moЖҙЖҙude ruttorde."
  38,41,"JaЕӢto kadi jiyaaЙ—o Amen on Ayyuuba, nde o noddunoo Joomi makko, won'de : "Seytaane memirii lam tampere e muuseendi"."
  38,42,"[Allah wi'ani mo]: "Latir tunndawal maa ngal [ka leydi]: ЖҠam Й—oo, ko lootorЙ—am, Й“uuЙ“Й—am e njaram"."
  38,43,"Min njeЙ—i mo Й“eynguure makko nden, e yeru maЙ“Й“e tawti Й“e, yurmeende immorde e amen, e waaju wonan'de marЙ“e haqqille Й“en."
  38,44,""Nanngir sookewo maa ngon, tamere huЙ—o, piyiraa Й—um [cuddiiЙ—o maa on], fii wata a firtu (woondoore nden)". Min tawu mo, muГұГұiiЙ—o. O moЖҙЖҙii jiyaaЙ—o. Pellet, ko o Й—uuЙ—uЙ—o tuubugol-ruttoo."
  38,45,"JaЕӢto kadi, jiyaaЙ“e Amen Й“en, Ibraahiima e Ishaaqa e Yaaquuba, joomiraaЙ“e semmbe e yi'anЙ—e."
  38,46,"Min keertinanii Й“e heertinannde, annditugol galle (laakara) Й—en."
  38,47,"E kadi Й“ee ka amen, ko jiyaaЙ“e e suЙ“aaЙ“e moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e suЙ“aaЙ“e."
  38,48,"JaЕӢto kadi Ismaa'iila, e Yuusa'u, e Zal-Kifli, kala maЙ“Й“e, ko jiyaaЙ“e e suЙ“aaЙ“e."
  38,49,"ЖҠum ko waaju. Ko pellet, hino woodani gooЕӢЙ—uЙ“e Й“en, ruttorde moЖҙЖҙunde."
  38,50,"ЖҠuum ko Aljannaaji ГұiiЙ“al, Й—i Й“e udditanaa dame mum,"
  38,51,"hara ko Й“e soЙ“Й“indii Й“e ton, heЙ“e nodda ton muuyanteeЙ—i Й—uuЙ—uЙ—i e njaram."
  38,52,"Hino woodani Й“e (ton): raЙ“Й“uЙ“e ndaarЙ—e, goreeЙ“e."
  38,53,"Ko Й—um woni ko podaЙ—on, fii Г‘alaande hasboore ndeen."
  38,54,"Pellet, Й—um ko arsike amen, gasugol alanaa mo."
  38,55,"ЖҠuum, [ko njoЙ“di maЙ“Й“e]. Pellet, hino woodani kadi bewЙ“e Й“een, ko Й“uri bonnde e ruttorde,"
  38,56,"woni Jahannama, nge Й“e naatoyta. Nge bonii ndaЙ—Й—udi!"
  38,57,"ЖҠuum, ko yo Й“e meeЙ—: ko fatata, e ЖҙiЖҙЖҙiri,"
  38,58,"WoЙ“Й“e Й“en, nannduЙ—e e majje, ko nooneeji."
  38,59,"E hino dental naatiroyat ngal doole e mon, toolii alanaa Й“e; tawde ko Й“e naatooЙ“e Yiite !"
  38,60,"ЖҒeen mbia: bismilla alanaa mon, ko onon ndefi min Й—um". Nge bonii ГұiiЙ“irde."
  38,61,"ЖҒe mbi'a: "Joomi amen, defuЙ—o min Й—uim on, Й“eydan mo leptte cowalle ka Yiite"."
  38,62,"ЖҒeya mbi'i: "Ko haЙ—i men jiugol worЙ“e, Й“e min limtaynoo e boonЙ“e Й“en?"
  38,63,"Hara min njogitorno Й“e toon jalnori, kaa ko gite (amen) yawti Й“e?""
  38,64,"Pellet, ka goonga, ko Й—uum woni yeddondiral yimЙ“e Yiite Й“een."
  38,65,"Maaku: "Anndee ko mi jeertinoowo. DeweteeЙ—o woo alaa, si wonaa Allah Gooto, pooluЙ—o On,"
  38,66,"JeyЙ—o kammuuji Й—in e leydi ndin, e kon ko woni hakkunde Й—in Й—iЙ—i, pooluЙ—o, kaforoowo On"."
  38,67,"Maaku: "(ndee Alqur'aanaare), ko nde kabaaru mawЙ—o,"
  38,68,"kono hoЙ—on Й—uurnii Й—um."
  38,69,"Ganndal alanaano kam, e fii mbatu ngun dowrowu, tuma nde Й“e weeГұidaynoo."
  38,70,"Wahayinaaka e am, si wanaa won'de min on, ko mi jeertinoowo Й“anngina"."
  38,71,"JaЕӢto nde Joomi maa daalannoo Malaa'ika'en: "Min mi tagiroowo Й“anndiЕӢke, immorde loopal."
  38,72,"si mi fotindirii mo, Mi wuttii e makko ruuhu am on, haray suuyanee mo cujjon"."
  38,73,"Malaa'ika'en fof cujji Й“e denndaangal."
  38,74,"si wonaa Ibuliisa, o mawnintinii, o woni jiyaaЙ—o e yedduЙ“e Й“en."
  38,75,"(Allah) daali: "eey ma yo Ibuliisa, ko haЙ—u maa sujjangol ko Mi tagiri juuЙ—e am? A mawnintini kaa a jeya e townitiiЙ“e Й“een?""
  38,76,"O wi'i: "Ko min Й“uri mo moЖҙЖҙude. A tagirii lam e yiite, A tagirii mo kaЕӢko e loopal"."
  38,77,"O daali: "Yaltu ton, aan, ko a diiwaaЙ—o;"
  38,78,"pellet, kuddi sm ndin fawike ma haa Г‘ande njoЙ“di diina"."
  38,79,"(Ibuliisa) wi'i : "Joomi am, neeЙ“nitanam, haa Гұande nde Й“e immintintee"."
  38,80,"O daali: "A jeyaama e neeЙ“nitanteeЙ“e Й“en,"
  38,81,"haa e Гұalaande happu ganndaaЙ—o"."
  38,82,"O wi'i: "Mi wooЙ—ndirii mawngu maa ngun ! Ma mi bewnuЙ“e fof maЙ“Й“e,"
  38,83,"si wonaa jiyaaЙ“e Maa, laЙ“Й“inaaЙ“e Й“en e maЙ“Й“e"."
  38,84,"(Allah) daali: "Mi wooЙ—ndirii goonga, ko goonga mi wowlata,"
  38,85,"ma Mi hebbinire Jahannama, e Й“en jokkuЙ“e ma fof e maЙ“Й“e"."
  38,86,"Maaku: "Mi laЙ“ndaaki on njoЙ“di e fii Й—um; mi wonaali jeyaaЙ—o e sincooЙ“e(deftatoobe)."
  38,87,"Ndee [AlqurвҖҷaanaare] wonaani, si wonaa waaju tageefo ngon."
  38,88,"Ma on nganndu (fii) kabaaru mayre, ko neeЙ“aa !"."
  39,1,"Jippagol deftere nden, ko immorde ka Allah, pooluЙ—o, ГұeeГұo oon."
  39,2,"Min njippiniirii deftere nden e maaЙ—a, e hoore goonga. rewu allah, laЙ“Й“inanaa mo diina ka."
  39,3,"Ngaanndee, ko Allah woodani diina laaЙ“uka kan. ЖҒeen non Й“e Й“eya nogitori yiЙ—Й“e ga makko (hara hiЙ“e wi'a): "Min ngaalaa rewirde Й—i, si wonaa tun no Й—i Й“annira min ka Allah, Й“adal". Pellet, Allah Г‘aawoyat hakkunde maЙ“Й“e, e kon ko Й“e woni lurrude e mun. Pellet, Allah feewnata on gonЙ—o fewnoowo, Й—uuЙ—uЙ—o jeddugol."
  39,4,"Sinno Allah yiЙ—no, nde o siforta Й“iЙ—Й—o, O suЙ“ayno ko o yiЙ—i woo, e ko o tagi kon. Senaare woodanii mo ! Ko KaЕӢko woni Allah, Bajjo, pooluЙ—o on."
  39,5,"O tagirii kammuuji Й—iin e leydi ndin, goonga.Homo suddira jemma on Гұalaema oon, O suddira Гұalawma on jemma on. O eelti na'ange ngen e lewru ndun, kala majji no doga haa e lajal taЖҙaangal. Nganndee, ko KaЕӢko woni pooluЙ—o, kaforoowo On."
  39,6,"O tagii on e fittaandu wooturu, refi OwaЙ—i e ndun, genndo mayru. O jippinani on e neemoraaЙ—i Й—in, nooneeji jeetati. Homo taga on ka teege yumma mon en, tagu Й“aawo tagu, e ndeer niЙ“e tati. Ko On mooЙ—on Allah, woni Joomi mon ! Ko KaЕӢko laamu woodani. DeweteeЙ—o alaa, si wonaa Allah. Ko honno perlitoraЙ—on [e dewugol Mo]?"
  39,7,"Si on njeddii, anndon Allah, ko jondiniiЙ—o e mon. O jaЙ“antaa jiyaaЙ“e makko Й“een, ke'eferaaku. Si on njettii Mo noon, O weltanoo on Й—uum.Hay gooto roondantaako goЙ—Й—o woo donngal mum. Refti ko ka Joomi mon, woni ruttorde mon; O yeetitoo on, fii kon ko gollatnoЙ—on. Pellet, ko O gannduЙ—o, ko woni e Й“erЙ—e."
  39,8,"Si loraa memii neЙ—Й—o on, o noddira Joomi makko, ruttagol e makko. Refti si O okkii mo moЖҙЖҙere, immorde ka makko, o yejjita ko o noddatno kon ado Й—uum, o waЙ—ana Allah kafidiiЙ—i, fii no o majjinira (yimЙ“e Й“een) e laawol makko ngol. MaAku: "Dakmitor keeferaaku maa ngun, seeЙ—a. Pellet, ko a jiyaaЙ—o e yimЙ“e Yiite Й“een"."
  39,9,"Kaa ko on yankinotooЙ—o tummbo jemma, ko o cujjoowo, darotooЙ—o (naafe), hara homo La'akara, homo joortii yurmeende Joomi makko nden... Maaku: "Hara annduЙ“e Й“en fotay e Й“e nganndaa Й“en?" Anndu ko waajitotoo, ko joomiraaЙ“e haqqille Й“een."
  39,10,"Maaku: "eey mon yo jiyaaЙ“e Am gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e, kulee Joomi mon". Hino woodani moЖҙЖҙimЙ“e (golle) Й“en e oo aduna, mbarjaari. Leydi Allah ndin ko yaajundi. Nganndee muГұГұiiЙ“e Й“een timminirante njoЙ“di maЙ“Й“e ndin, ko aldaa e limoore."
  39,11,"Maaku: "Miin mi yamiraama dewugol Allah, laЙ“Й“inana mo diina kan,"
  39,12,"Mi yamiraa kadi, gongol arano e jebbiliiЙ“e Й“een"."
  39,13,"Maaku : "Miin miЙ—o huli, si mi yeddii Joomi am, lepte Г‘alaande Mawnde"."
  39,14,"Maaku: "Ko Allah mi rewata, mi laЙ“Й“inan mo diina am."
  39,15,"ndewee ko njiЙ—uЙ—on onon, hara wonaa KaЕӢko. Maaku: "Ko woni hayruЙ“e Й“en, ko Й“een Й“e tawata Г‘ande Darngal, Й“e hayrinii ko'e maЙ“Й“e, e Й“eynguureeji maЙ“Й“e". Nganndee ko nden woni hayrere Й“anngunde ndeen."
  39,16,"Hino woodirani Й“e seЕӢgo dow maЙ“Й“e, kippoodi Yiite, e kippoodi senngo ley maЙ“Й“e. Ko Й—um woni ko Allah hulЙ“inirta jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en. Ko onon yo jiyaaЙ“e Am, kori kulee Kam!"
  39,17,"ЖҒeen woЙ—Й—itorЙ“e rewugol bewnooji Й—i, Й“e nduttii e Allah, welo-welo no woodani Й“e. Wewlinir jiyaaЙ“e am Й“een,"
  39,18,"nanooЙ“e Konngol Й“een, Й“e njokka ko Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude e maggol. Ko Й“een woni Й“e Allah feewni Й“en, ko Й“en ngoni joomiraaЙ“e haqqille Й“een."
  39,19,"E ko on mo konngol lepte jojji e mum... E ko aan daЙ—ndata gonЙ—o ka Yiite?"
  39,20,"Si ko Й“en hulЙ“e Joomi mun, hino woodani Й“e kuЙ“eeje [ka Aljanna] e kuЙ“eeje mahaaЙ—e dow majje, hara canЙ—i no ila ley majje. Ko fodoore Allah ! Allah non firtataa fodoore."
  39,21,"E a yiaani, won'de Allah saaЖҙinirii ndiyam ka kammu, o naadi Й—am e ndeer Й“ulli ka leydi; refti o yaltinira Й—am remuru seedundu noone, refti ndu Й—ayЙ—a, yi'aa hindu soyЙ—i; refti O waЙ—a Й—um ko muncaa. Pellet, wonii e Й—uum, waaju, wonan'de joomiraaЙ“e haqqille Й“een."
  39,22,"E ko on mo Allah yaГұГұani Й“endre mum nden, fii lislaamu, hara homo e ndaygu immorde ka Joomi makko... Bone woodanii Й“en yooruЙ“e Й“erЙ—e mum, e jantagol Allah. ЖҒeen ngonii e majjere Й“anngunde."
  39,23,"Allah jippinii ko Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude e yeewtere, deftere nanndunde [Гұaawooje], Й—immitunde. Nde guri Й“en hulooЙ“e Joomi muyn riЙ“irta (nanugol nde), refti guri e Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e deeЖҙira jaЕӢtoore Allah nden. Ko Й—uum woni peewal Allah ngal O feewnira on mo muuyani. Kala non mo Allah majjini, haray peewnoowo mo alaa."
  39,24,"E ko on reentariiЙ—o yeeso mun ngon, e lepte bonЙ—e Й—en Г‘ande Darngal... TooГұuЙ“e Й“en mbi'anee on tuma: "MeeЙ—ee kon ko ngonnoЙ—on faggitanaade"."
  39,25,"AdinooЙ“e Й“en njeddiino, lepte Й—een ardirani Й“e, ka Й“e tinaani."
  39,26,"Allah meeЙ—iniri Й“e koyeera, ka nguurndam aduna. Pellet non, ko lepte La'akara Й—en noon, Й“uri mawnude, si tawno heЙ“e nganndunoo!"
  39,27,"GooЙ—ii Min piyanii yimЙ“e Й“een, e ndee Alqur'aanaare, kala misal, mbelejo'o, Й“e mbaajitora."
  39,28,"Alqur'aanaare (janngeteende) e haala aarabi, nde aldaa e ooГұaare, fii no Й“e ngooЕӢЙ—ira."
  39,29,"Allah waЙ—ii yeru, gorko mo lurruЙ“e hawti Й—um, heЙ“e pooЙ—ondira mo, e gorko laaЙ“anЙ—o gorko [goo]: Hara Й“en Й—iЙ—o fotay e misal? Yettoore woodanii Allah! Kono Й“urЙ“e Й—uuЙ—ude e maЙ“Й“e, Й“e nganndaa."
  39,30,"Pellet, aan ko a maayoowo, kamЙ“e kadi ko Й“e maayooЙ“e;"
  39,31,"refti onon, Г‘ande Darngal, ko to Joomi mon, njeddondiroyton."
  39,32,"E ko hommbo Й“uri tooГұde wa on jedduЙ—o Й—o e hoore Allah, maa o yeddi goonga kan nde ko arunoo e makko? E wonaa Jahannama woni jaaЖҙorde yedduЙ“e Й“een?"
  39,33,"Oon noon garduЙ—o e goonga, o goongini Й—uum, ko Й“en ngoni gooЕӢЙ—uЙ“e Й“een."
  39,34,"Hino woodani kala ko Й“e paaletee, ka Joomi maЙ“Й“e; ko Й—uum njoЙ“di moЖҙЖҙinooЙ“e Й“een."
  39,35,"fii no Allah yaawtirana Й“e, ko Й“uri bon'de e ko Й“e golli kon, O yoЙ“itira Й“e njoЙ“di maЙ“Й“e ndiin, ko Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude e ko Й“e ngollaynoo kon."
  39,36,"Allah siforaali yonugol jiyaaЙ—o makko on? HeЙ“e kulЙ“inire Й—in Й—i wonaa mo. Kala mo Allah majjini, haray Feewnoowo alanaa mo."
  39,37,"Kala non mo Allah feewni, majjinoowo mo alaa. Allah siforaali won'de pooluЙ—o, Jom lepte?"
  39,38,"Pellet, si a laЙ“ndike Й“e: "Ko hommbo tagi kammuuji Й—in e leydi ndin?", ma Й“e mbi'u: "Ko Allah". Maaku: "Yeewtee kam fii Й—in Й—i ndewoton ga Allah, si Allah faandanike lam lorra, hara Й—i huncanay kam lorra makko kan? Maa si o faandanike lam yurmeende, taw si Й—i haЙ—ay kam yurmeende makko nden? Maaku: "Allah yonii kam, ko e makko hoolnotooЙ“e Й“en tuuginotoo"."
  39,39,"Maaku: "eey mon yimЙ“e am, ngollee e laawol mon, min ko e [laawol am] mi ngollirta. Aray ka nganndon."
  39,40,"ko hommbo lepte koynayЙ—e ngaroyat e muuЙ—um, lepte duumiiЙ—e njippoo e makko."
  39,41,"Min njippinirii deftere nden e maaЙ—a, fii yimЙ“e Й“een, e hoore goonga. Kala peewuЙ—o, ko hoore makko [o feewani]; kala kadi majjuЙ—o, ko hoore makko o majjani. A wonaani wakiil e dow maЙ“Й“e."
  39,42,"Allah homo Жҙettita pittaali Й—in, saanga maayde majji, e Й—in Й—i maayaani, ka Й—oyngol majji. O jogitoo Й—iin Й—i Гұaawani maayde, O accita Й—iya, haa e lajal taЖҙaangal. Pellet, Ma'andeeji ngoni e Й—uum, wona nde yimЙ“e miijitotooЙ“e."
  39,43,"Kaa Й“e njogiti tefooji, ga Allah? Maaku: "Hay si tawii Й—i jiyaa hu'unde, Й—i haqqiltaa kadi?""
  39,44,"Maaku: "Tefoore nden fow, ko Allah heeranii. Ko KaЕӢko woodani laamagol kammuuji Й—iin e leydi ndin. refti ko ka makko ndutteteЙ—on"."
  39,45,"Si fii Allah tun jaЕӢtaama, Й“erЙ“e Й“en Й“e ngooЕӢЙ—inaa La'akara Й“en, tamoo. Si fii Й—iya, Й—i wonaa Mo [KaЕӢko Allah] jaЕӢtaama, e jaka yoo, heЙ“e wewla."
  39,46,"Maaku: "Yaa Allah, puЙ—Й—uЙ—o kammuuji Й—iin e leydi ndin, gannduЙ—o birniiЙ—i e peeГұЙ—i, ko Aan Гұaawata hakkunde jiyaaЙ“e Maa Й“een, ko Й“e luutondiraynoo e mum"."
  39,47,"Si tawno no woodanno tooГұЙ“e Й“een, ko woni kon ka leydi fow, e yeru mum, wond'ude e mum, Й“e sottorayno Й—um, bone lepte Й—en, Г‘ande Darngal; feeГұirana Й“e ka Allah, kon ko Й“e tijjanooki."
  39,48,"boneeji Й—i Й“e paggitinoo Й—in peГұana Й“e, ko Й“e njalkitaynoo kon huuЙ“ita Й“e."
  39,49,"Si lorra heЙ“ii neЙ—Й—o on, o nodda Min. Refti si Min ngokkii mo neema, immorde ka amen, o wi'a: "nganndee ko e ganndal [am] mi okkiira Й—um". ЖҠuum ko jarrabuyee kan; kono ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e maЙ“Й“e, Й“e anndaa."
  39,50,"GooЕӢЙ—ii Й“een adinooЙ“e Й“e mbi'iino Й—um. Kono kon ko Й“e paggitotonoo, nafaani Й“e."
  39,51,"boneeji Й—i Й“e paggitotonoo Й—iin memi Й“e. TooГұЙ“e Й“een e maЙ“Й“e, kon ko Й“e wonnoo e paggitagol, memoyat Й“e, Й“e wonaani laawotooЙ“e."
  39,52,"E Й“e nganndaa won'de Allah no yaГұГұana arsike on mo o muuyani, O Й“illina [mo o muuyani]? Pellet, Ma'andeeji ngonii e Й—um, wona nde yimЙ“e gooЕӢЙ—inooЙ“e."
  39,53,"Maaku: eey mon yo jiyaaЙ“e Am fantimЙ“e e hoore mum, wota on taЖҙo yurmeende Allah nden. Pellet, Allah ko kaforoowo junubaajo Й—in fof. Ko KaЕӢko woni kaforoowo, jurmotooЙ—o On"."
  39,54,"Tuubee nduttoЙ—on ka Joomi mon, jebbilanoЙ—on mo, ado lepte Й—en arde e mon, hara on paabetaake."
  39,55,"Njokkee ko Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude e ko jippinaa e mon, immorde ka Joomi, ado lepte Й—en ado de on, juhal, hara on so'aa anndude."
  39,56,"fii wota woЕӢkii wi'oy: "Ee nimse am, e ko mi welsindii e fii Allah. Pellet, mi jeyano e Й“een jalkitooЙ“e"."
  39,57,"maa ki wi'a: "Si Alah feewnuno kam, mi wonanyno jiyaaЙ—o e gooЕӢЙ—uЙ“e Й“en"."
  39,58,"Maa ki wi'a, tuma ki yi'ata lepte Й—en: "Si fehre ruttagol no woodannoo kam, mi jeyee e moЖҙЖҙinooЙ“e Й“een"."
  39,59,""Gasataa ! Tawde aayeeje Am Й—en aruno e maaЙ—a, njedduЙ—aa Й—e, mawnintiniЙ—aa, laatiЙ—aa jiyaaЙ—o e yedduЙ“e Й“een"."
  39,60,"Г‘ande Darngal, a yi'oya fennonooЙ“e e hoore Allah Й“en, hino Й“awli je'ece. Wonaa ka Jahannama woni jaaЖҙorde mawnintiniiЙ“e Й“een?"
  39,61,"Allah na daЙ—ndira gooЕӢЙ—uЙ“e Й“een, sabu maloore maЙ“Й“e nden. Bone memataa Й“een, wonaa kamЙ“e ngoni sunoytooЙ“e."
  39,62,"Ko Allah woni TakЙ—o kala hu'unde, ko KaЕӢko kadi woni pawtiiЙ—o kala hu'unde."
  39,63,"Ko KaЕӢko sottirЙ—e kammuuji Й—in e leydi ndin woodani. YedduЙ“e aayeeje Allah Й“een non, ko Й“en ngoni hayruЙ“e(pertuЙ“e) Й“en."
  39,64,"Maaku: "E ko woori Allah, njamirton mi, yo mi rew, onon Й“ee majjuЙ“e?""
  39,65,"GooЕӢЙ—ii wahayinaama e maaЙ—a, e Й“en adinooЙ“e ma: "Si a sirkii, pellet, golle maa Й—een bonay njeyiЙ—aa e hayruЙ“e Й“een."
  39,66,"Alah rew Allah, njeyeЙ—aa e yettooЙ“e (Mo) Й“en."
  39,67,"ЖҒe mawniniraani Allah, no O foti maninireede, hara le, leydi ndin fof, ko tamannde makko, Г‘ande Darngal, kammuuji Й—in kadi taggiree Гұaamo makko. Senayee woodanii Mo ! O toowii e kon ko Й“e cirkanta mo."
  39,68,"Wuttee ka Allaandu, kala ko woni ka kammuuji e ka leydi kon faЙ—Й—ee, si wonaa Й“en Й“e Allah muuyani [daЙ—ugol]. refti wuttee e mayru Й—iЙ—aЙ“ol, tawa ko Й“e dariiЙ“e cabbitii."
  39,69,"Leydi ndin jalbira ndaygo Jeydo ndi On; taalkuru nduun wallinee, AnnabaaЙ“e e seedeeЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en addee; goonga Гұaawiree hakkunde maЙ“Й“e, wonaa Й“e tooГұeteeЙ“e;"
  39,70,"woЕӢki kala yoЙ“ee ko golli kon. Ko KaЕӢko [Allah] Й“uri anndude ko Й“e ngollata."
  39,71,"YedduЙ“e Й“en coggiroyee ka Jahannama dente-dente. Haa si Й“e heewtii nge, dame magge udditee, reenuЙ“e nge Й“en mbi'ana Й“e: "E NulaaЙ“e jiyaaЙ“e e mo'on heewtaano on, janngaynooЙ“e aayeeje Joomi mon, e mooЙ—on, Й“e rentina on hawrugol e ndee Гұalaande mon?" ЖҒe mbi'a: "Ko non tigiri, kono Konngol lepte ngol, jojjiino e yedduЙ“e Й“een"."
  39,72,"[ЖҒe] mbi'anee: "Naatiree dame Jahannama Й—en lutton ton. Nge bonii jaaЖҙorde mawnintiniiЙ“e Й“een !"."
  39,73,"HulooЙ“e Joomi mun Й“en kadi Й—owitiree ka Aljanna, dente-dente. Haa si Й“e heewtii mo, dame makko udditee, reenuЙ“e mo Й“en mbi'ana Й“e: "Kisal wonii e mon, on laaЙ“ii, naatiree mo, duumagol"."
  39,74,"ЖҒe mbi'a ontuma: "Jettooje ngoodanii Allah, laatinanЙ—o men fodoore Mum, O ronini min leydi [Aljanna] ndin, meЙ—en weerira e Aljanna on, kala ka min njiЙ—i". Mbarjaari gollunooЙ“e moЖҙЖҙere Й“een moЖҙЖҙii."
  39,75,"Yi'oyaa Malaa'ikaen, heЙ“e taarii Arsi kin, heЙ“e cubbunhinora yettugol Joomi maЙ“Й“e. Goonga Гұaawiree hakkunde maЙ“Й“e. Wi'ee on tuma: "Yettoore woodanii Allah, JeyЙ—o tagoore"."
  40,1,"Haa, miim."
  40,2,"Jippagol deftere nde, ko immorde e Allah, poolЙ—o, ganndo oon."
  40,3,"Kaforoowo bakkatuuji Й—in, JaЙ“oowo tuubuubuyee, caЙ—tuЙ—o lepte, Joom yaajeende. DeweteeЙ—o alaa, si wonaa kaЕӢko. Ko ka makko woni ruttorde nden."
  40,4,"Alaa ko weeГұdata e aayeeje Allah Й—en, si wonaa yedduЙ“e Й“en. Wota a hoditor ko Й“e dillirta kon ka leydi."
  40,5,"Ado maЙ“Й“e, yimЙ“e Nuuhu Й“een e peЙ—le Й“aawo maЙ“Й“e, yedduno (NulaaЙ“e mum Й“een), mofte kala himmiri nanngugol NulaaЙ—o mun oon. ЖҒe njeddiri meere, fii no bonnitira (goonga) kan. Kono Min nanngi Й“e. Taskii no nanngal am ngal waЙ—tinirnoo !"
  40,6,"Ko wano nii Konngol Joomi maa ngol, jojjiri e yedduЙ“e Й“een : "Won'de pellet, ko Й“e yimЙ“e Yiite"."
  40,7,"ЖҒeen (Malaa'ikaaЙ“e) roondiiЙ“e Arsiki kin, e wonЙ“e bannge makki Й“en, hiЙ“e cubbunhinora yettugol Joomi maЙ“Й“e, Й“e ngooЕӢЙ—ina mo, Й“e insinorana gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“en (wiide): "Joomi amen, A yaГұГұirii kala hu'unde, yurmeende e ganndal. Yawtan Й“en tuubuЙ“e, Й“e njokki laawol Maa ngol, daЙ—ndaa Й“e kadi lepte DulЙ“oowe ngeen."
  40,8,"Joomi amen, naaduЙ“e ka Aljannaaji ГұiiЙ“al, Й—in Й—i poduЙ—aa Й“e, e kala moЖҙЖҙuЙ—o e baabiraaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e, e genndiraaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e, e geГұngol maЙ“Й“e. Pellet, ko Aan woni pooluЙ—o, Г‘eeГұЙ—o Oon."
  40,9,"DaЙ—ndaaЙ“e [kuuЙ—e] e bonЙ—e Й—en. Kala mo daЙ—nduЙ—aa [kuuЙ—e] mum bonЙ—e Й—en nden Г‘ande, haray pellet, A yurmiii mo". Ko Й—um woni maloore mawnunde ndeen."
  40,10,"YedduЙ“e Й“een noddiroyte: "Ko tikkere Allah nden Й“uri mawnude, e dii ko tikkanЙ—on ko'e mon Й—um, tuma noddetenoЙ—on e gooЕӢЙ—inal, njeddon."
  40,11,"ЖҒe mbi'a: "Joomi amen, A warii min laawi Й—iЙ—i, nguurnuЙ—aa min laawi Й—iЙ—i: min qirrike bakkaat amen Й—in. Taw si laawol jaltirngol hino woodi?"."
  40,12,""ЖҠuum mooЙ—on, ko tawde si Allah tan noddanooma, on njeddon; si O kafidaama, ngooЕӢЙ—inon. Г‘aawoore nden ko Allah heeranii, ToowЙ—o, MawЙ—o On"."
  40,13,"Ko KaЕӢko woni kolloowo on Ma'andeeji makko Й—in, o jippinirana on toЙ“o ka kammu. Kono taskotaako, si wonaa nduttotooЙ—o [e Allah]."
  40,14,"Rewiree Allah, laЙ“Й“inirangol mo diina kan, hay si he'eferЙ“e Й“een njЙ—aa."
  40,15,"Ko o toowuЙ—o darjaaji, JeyЙ—o Arsi kin. Homo jippiniria wahayu oon, yamiroore makko, e on mo o muuyani e jiyaaЙ“e makko Й“een, no o jeertinirde Гұalnde Kawral ngal,"
  40,16,"Гұande Й“e feeГұoyta. Hu'unde suuЙ—otaako Allah, e fee maЙ“Й“e. Ko hommbo laamu woodani hannde? Ko Allah Bajjo, pooluЙ—o On."
  40,17,"Hannde, woЕӢkii kala yoЙ“ete ko faggitii. TooГұe woo alaa hannde, pellet, Allah ko ГұaawЙ—o Гұaawoore."
  40,18,"JeertnirtЙ“e, Гұalaande dillere nden, tuma Й“erЙ—e Й—en Жҙawtirta ka konondi, hara heЙ“e (heewuЙ“e) ngoЖҙo. GiЙ—o woo alanaa tooГұooЙ“e Й“een, wonaa tefoowo jaЙ“anteeЙ—o."
  40,19,"Homo anndi njamfa gite, e ko Й“erЙ—e Й—een cuuЙ—i."
  40,20,"Allah ko goonga Гұaawirta. ЖҠi Й“e ndeewata Й—iin non, gaanin makko, hay hu'unde Й—i Гұaawirtaa. Pellet, ko kaЕӢko woni Nanoowo, ji'oowo On."
  40,21,"Hara Й“ee njiilaaki ka leydi, Й“e ndaara no battane ado mabbe Й“en wa'unoo? ЖҒeen le no Й“urunoo tiiЙ—ude doole e batteeji, ka leydi. Allah nanngitiri Й“e bakkaauuji maЙ“Й“e Й—iin, Й“e heЙ“aano daЙ—ndoowo Й“e e (lepte) Allah Й—een."
  40,22,"Ko waЙ—i Й—uum, ko tawde NulaaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en ngaddatno Й“e Й“anngannduyeeji, Й“e njedda. Allah halki Й“e. Pellet, ko O DoolnuЙ—o, caЙ—tuЙ—o lepte."
  40,23,"GooЕӢЙ—ii Min nulirii Muusaa aayeeje Amen Й—en, e hujja Й“annguЙ—o."
  40,24,"haa e Fir'awna, e Haamaana, e Qaaruuna. Kono Й“e mbi'i: "Ko bileejo, Й—uuЙ—uЙ—o penaande!"."
  40,25,"Nde o addannoo Й“e goonga ka, immorde e amen, Й“e mb'iti: "mbaree Й“iЙ—Й“e worЙ“e gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“en e makko, accon rewЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en". Pewje he'eferЙ“e Й“en wonaani, si wonaa e majjere."
  40,26,"Fir'awna wi'i: "ngccee mi wara Muusaa. Yo o noddu Joomi makko ! MiЙ—o huli nde o waylata diina mon kan, maa o feГұГұina bonnere e leydi"."
  40,27,"Muusa maaki: "Mi moolorii JeyЙ—o kam on, jeyi on, e bone kala mawnintiniiЙ—o, mo gooЕӢЙ—inaa Гұalaande hasboore"."
  40,28,"Gorko gooЕӢЙ—inЙ—o goo, jiyaaЙ—o e yimЙ“e Fir'awna Й“en - cuuЙ—unooЙ—o gooЕӢЙ—inal mum - :"E on waray gorko, fii o wi'i: "Joomi am ko Allah?" Hara le o addanii on Й“anngannduyeeji, immorde ka Joomi mon. Si tawii o fenu, haray fenaande makko ko kaЕӢko fawii; si tawii kadi o goongu, haray yoga e kon ko kammbirani on, heЙ“ay on". Pellet, Allah feewnata on fantinoowo yeddoowo!"
  40,29,"Eey yo yimЙ“e am, laamu no woodani on hanndi, ko on foolЙ“e ka leydi. Kono ko hommbo wallata en, e lepte Allah Й—en, si Й—e ngarii e men?" Fir'awna wi'i: "Mi hollataa on, si wanaa ko mi yi'i kon. Mi tindintaa on kadi, si wonaa e laawol peewal ngol"."
  40,30,"GooЕӢЙ—inЙ—o on wi'iti: "eey mon yo yimЙ“e am, min on miЙ—o hulani on, sugu Гұalaande heЙ“unoonde peЙ—le Й—in."
  40,31,"Sugu mbowka yimЙ“e Nuuhu Й“een, e Aadi'en, e Samuuda'en, e arnooЙ“e Й“aawo maЙ“Й“e Й“en". Allah faandanaaki tooГұde jiyaaЙ“e Й“en."
  40,32,"Eey mon yimЙ“e am, miin miЙ—o hulani on, Г‘alaande noddindirton"
  40,33,"Г‘alnde nduЕӢtindroyton, hoЙ—on ndoga, hara daЙ—ndoowo on alanaa on e Allah". Kala mo Allah majjini, haray peewnoowo alanaa mo."
  40,34,"GooЕӢЙ—ii Yuusufu ardanii on e Й“annganduyeeji, ko adii, on seeraani e sikkitagol kon ko o addani on. Haa nde o faatinoo, mbiuЙ—on: "Allah nultataa NulaaЙ—o goo, Й“aawo makko". Ko non majjinirta kala gonЙ—o fantinoowo cikkitiiЙ—o."
  40,35,"ЖҒeen weeГұirooЙ“e e aayeeje Allah Й—en ko aldaa e hujja arЙ—o Й“e, [kuuЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en] mawnii tikkere ka Allah, e ka gooЕӢЙ—iiЙ“e Й“en. Ko wano non Allah notirta e Й“ernde kala mawnintiniiЙ—o dundarankeejo."
  40,36,"Fir'awna wi'i: " eey ma yo Haamaana, mahanam sooro, no gasa mi yottoo Й—ate Й—en."
  40,37,"Й—ate kammuuji Й—in, mi Жҙeewoya DeweteeЙ—o Muusaa On; sabu mi sikki mo penoowo". Ko wano non Fir'awna duЙ—iranaa, golle makko bonЙ—e Й—en; o sakkaa e laawol (peewal) ngol. Feere Fir'awna nden wonaano, si wonaa e hayrere."
  40,38,"[Gorko] gooЕӢЙ—inЙ—o on wi'i: "eey mon yo yimЙ“e am, njokkee kam, mi fewna on e laawol peewal ngol."
  40,39,"Eey mon yo yimЙ“e am, nganndee Й—am nguurndam aduna, ko ndakamme-hun tun, ko La'akara on woni, galle ГұiiЙ“al Й—en."
  40,40,"Mo gollii bone, o yoЙ“itetaake, si wonaa yeru makko; mo gollii kadi moЖҙЖҙere, foti ko gorko maa debbo, hara ko o gooЕӢЙ—inЙ—o, Й“een Й—oon naatay Aljanna, Й“e arsikoyee ton, ko aldaa e limoore."
  40,41,"Eey mon yo yimЙ“e am, ko waЙ—i si miЙ—o nodda on e daЙ—al, hoЙ—on nodda kam e Yiite?"
  40,42,"HiЙ—on nodda kam e jeddugol Allah, sirkana mo e ko mi alanaa Й—um ganndal, hara non, min miЙ—o nodda on e poolЙ—o, cuhuroowo bakkaat Oon."
  40,43,"Sikke alaa, won'de ko noddoton kam e mum kon, dewal alanaa Й—um aduna, wonaa La'akara. E won'de ruttorde men nden, ko ka Allah, e won'de ko fantimЙ“e Й“een, ngoni Yiite ngen."
  40,44,"Aray nde nganndoton, ko mi yewtata on kon; mi fawa fiyaaku am on e Allah. Pellet, Allah ko deenЙ—o jiyaaЙ“e Й“en"."
  40,45,"Allah daЙ—ndi mo, boneeji Й—i Й“e pewjunoo, o fiiltii yimЙ“e Fir'awna Й“een, ko Й“uri bon'de e lepte."
  40,46,"Yiite ngen, Й“e mbeeЙ“itoyte e magge, bimmbi e kiikiiЙ—e. Г‘ande darnga daroytoo (wi'oyte): "Naatee yimЙ“e Fir'awna Й“een, ka Й“uri saЙ—tude e lepte"."
  40,47,"JaЕӢto tuma Й“e yeddondiroyta ka Yiite, lo'unooЙ“e Й“en wi'ana townitinooЙ“e Й“een: "Minen, ko onon men jokkuunoo, taw si on duГұanay men geЙ—al e Yiite ngeen?""
  40,48,"TownitinooЙ“e Й“een mbi'a: "En fof, hiЙ—en e magge. GooЕӢЙ—ii Allah Гұaawii hakkunde jiyaaЙ“e Й“en"."
  40,49,"WonЙ“e ka Yiite Й“en kadi mbi'ana ayninaaЙ“e Jahannama Й“en: "Toranee min Joomi mon, O hoynana men, Гұalaande (wootere) e lepte Й—en"."
  40,50,"ЖҒe mbi'a: "NulaaЙ“e mon Й“en ardanaano on e Й“anngannduyeeji?" ЖҒe mbi'a: "oo'owoye !" [AyninaaЙ“e] Й“en wi'a: "Awa toree, onon tigiri !" Kono toraare he'eferЙ“e Й“en ngonaani, si wanaa e majjere."
  40,51,"Pellet, Min mballay NulaaЙ“e Amen Й“en, e gooЕӢЙ—iinЙ“e Й“en, ka nguurndam aduna, e Г‘alnde seedeeЙ“e Й“een daroytoo,"
  40,52,"Гұalnde de ngantinagol nafoytaa tooГұnooЙ“e Й“een, hara kuddi hino woodani Й“e, e galle bonЙ—e."
  40,53,"GooЕӢЙ—ii Min ngokkii Muusaa ganndal [Tawreeta] ngal, Min ndonini Й“iЙ—Й“e Israa'iila Й“en, deftere nden."
  40,54,"ko nde peewal e waaju, wona nde joomiraaЙ“e haqqille Й“een."
  40,55,"MuГұГұo tan, pellet, fodoore Allah nden ko goonga, imsinano bakkaatuuji maa Й—iin, subbunhinanoЙ—aa Joomi maa, kiikiiЙ—e e bimmbi."
  40,56,"Pellet, weeГұinirooЙ“e e aayeeje Allah Й—een, ko aldaa e dalil arЙ—o e maЙ“Й“e, alaa e Й“erЙ—e Й—en, si wonaa mawnintinagol. ЖҒe yottotaako noon, e Й—uum. Moolor Allah, Ko KaЕӢko woni Nanoowo, ji'oowo On."
  40,57,"Pellet, ko takde kammuuji Й—in e leydi ndin, Й“uri mawnude e dii tageendi yimЙ“e Й“een. Kono ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e yimЙ“e Й“en, Й“e nganndaa."
  40,58,"BumЙ—o e ji'oowo potataa, gooЕӢЙ—iinЙ“e Й“een kadi ngolli moЖҙЖҙuЙ—i, potataa e bonЙ—o. FamЙ—ii ko mbajitorton !"
  40,59,"Pellet, Darnga, ko ko arata, sikke alaa e mu'um. Kono ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e yimЙ“e Й“een, Й“e ngoЕӢЙ—inaa."
  40,60,"Joomi mon daali: "Toree Kam, Mi jaabinana on. MawtinantooЙ“e dewugol Lam Й“een, ko pellet, Й“e naatoyay Jahannama, ko Й“e hoyЙ“e"."
  40,61,"Ko Allah waЙ—irani on jemma on, ka fowtoЙ—on e mum, e Гұalawma on, yi'inoowo. Pellet, Allah ko Jom Й“ural e yimЙ“e Й“en, kono ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e yimЙ“e Й“en, Й“e njettataa (neema)."
  40,62,"Ko oon mooЙ—on Allah Joomi mon, woni TakЙ—o kala huunde. ReweteeЙ—o alaa, si wanaa KaЕӢko. Ko honno pirlitortaЙ—on (e Й—uum?)"
  40,63,"Ko noon Й“eya yeddatnooЙ“e aayeeje Allah Й—een, perlisortenoo."
  40,64,"Ko Allah woni baЙ—iranЙ—o on leydi ndin, ГұiiЙ“irde, kammu ngun, kippoodi, O mbaadini on - O moЖҙЖҙini mbaadiiji mon -, O arsiki on e laaЙ“uЙ—i. Ko oon mooЙ—on woni Allah Joomi mon; senaare woodanii Allah, JeyЙ—o winndere nden !"
  40,65,"Ko KaЕӢko woni guurЙ—o Oon. DeweteeЙ—o alaa, si wonaa KaЕӢko. Ndewee Mo kisan; laЙ“Й“inano mo diina kan. Jettooje ngoodanii Allah, JeyЙ—o winndere ndeen !"
  40,66,"Maaku: "Miin mi haЙ—aama dewugol Й—iin Й—i noddoton ga Allah, tuma nde Й“annganduyeeji Й—in ari e am, immorde e Joomi am, mi yamiraama kadi, nde mi jebbilantoo, JeyЙ—o winndere ndeen"."
  40,67,"Ko KaЕӢko woni takЙ—o on e mbumbuldi, refti e toЙ“Й“ere (maniiyu), refti e heЙ—Й—ere, refti o yaltiniri on penuuЙ“e fii no njottoron cemmbe mon, e no laatoron nayeeЙ“e, - no e mo'on, ЖҙettiteteeЙ“e ado Й—uum, - haa no njottoron lajal kappaangal, mbelajo'o, on kaqqilay."
  40,68,"Ko KaЕӢko woni guurnoowo e waroowo. Si O haajii e fiyaaku, ko O wi'anat mo tan: "Laato", o laatoo."
  40,69,"E a tinaani, Й“een yeddondirteeЙ“e e aayeeje Allah Й—een, ko honno Й“e pirlitoraa?"
  40,70,"ЖҒeen yedduЙ“e deftere ndeen, e kon ko Min nuliri nulaaЙ“e Amen Й“een; Й“e ngaray anndude,"
  40,71,"tuma kolombooje Й—en mbaЙ—oyaa e daaЙ—e maЙ“Й“e, e jolokooje(callalle) Й—een, hara heЙ“e ndaasiree"
  40,72,"ka ndeer ngulЙ—am; refti Й“e huЙ“Й“oyee ka ndeer Yiite."
  40,73,"refti Й“e mbi'anee: "Ko holto woni Й—in Й—i kafidatnoЙ—on?"
  40,74,"Ko aldah e Allah?" ЖҒe mbi'a: "ЖҠi majjitike min. Wurin, min ngonaano ko adii, e dewugol hay hu'unde". Ko hona nih Allah majjinirta he'eferЙ“e Й“en."
  40,75,"Ko waЙ—i on Й—uum, ko ko mbeltoratnoЙ—on kon ka hoore leydi, ko aldaa e goonga, e ko mbliratnoЙ—on kon."
  40,76,"Naatiree dame Jahannama Й—een, luttugol ton. nge bonii jaaЖҙorde wona'de mawnintiniiЙ“e Й“een!."
  40,77,"MuГұГұo. Pellet, fodoore Allah nden, ko goonga. Ko si Min hollete yoga e ko Min podi Й“e kon, maa hara Min Жҙettite (ado mum) ko ka Amen Й“e ruttirtee."
  40,78,"GooЕӢЙ—ii Min imminii NulaaЙ“e ado maa. Hino e maЙ“Й“e, Й“e Min cifani maa fii mum; hino maЙ“Й“e, Й“e Min cifanaaki ma fii mum. Haananaa NulaaЙ—o, addugol aaya, si wonaa e duЕӢayee Allah. Si yamiroore Allah nden arii, goonga Гұaawirte meerente'en sooya nden Гұalnde."
  40,79,"Ko Allah woni waЙ—iranЙ—o On neemoraaЙ—i Й—in ko mbaЙ—Й—oron, Гұaamon kadi e majji."
  40,80,"nafooje kadi hino ngoodani on e majji, e no njottoron e majji, haaju hittuЙ—o e berde mon. Ko e hoore majji e hoore laaЙ—e Й—een, woni ko ndonndeteЙ—on."
  40,81,"Himo holla on maandeeji makko Й—in. Ko holЙ—um e Ma'andeeji Allah Й—in, woni ko njeddoton?"
  40,82,"E Й“ee yiilaaki ka leydi, Й“e ndaara ko holno battane Й“eya ado maЙ“Й“e mbattinirnoo? ЖҒen no Й“urunoo Й“e Й—uude e saЙ—tude doole e batteeji [waЙ—aaЙ—i] ka leydi. Kono kon ko Й“e paggotonoo, duncanaano Й“e."
  40,83,"Nde NulaaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en addannooЙ“e Й“anngannduyeeji Й—in, Й“e wewliri ganndal ko woni ka maЙ“Й“e kon. ЖҒe kuuЙ“itiraa kon ko Й“e njalkitaynoo."
  40,84,"Nde Й“e nii'unoo lepte Amen Й—en, Й“e mbi'i: "Min ngooЕӢЙ—inii Allah tan, min yeddii kon ko men wonunoo e cirkannde"."
  40,85,"Kono ngooЕӢЙ—inal maЙ“Й“e wonaano ko nafata Й“e, feewndo Й“e nji'unoo lepte Amen Й—een; Й—um ko laawol Allah non, gooЕӢЙ—ii Й—un yawtiino e jiyaaЙ“e makko Й“een. YedduЙ“e Й“en sooyi Й—on nden Гұalnde."
  41,1,"Haa, miim."
  41,2,"Ko jipporiinde immorde ka JurmeteeЙ—o, HinnotooЙ—o on."
  41,3,"Deftere fensitaande aayeeje mum, janngeteende e Й—emngal aarabu, wonan,de yimЙ“e anndooЙ“e."
  41,4,"wewlinaynde jeertinaaЙ“e. Kono Й“urЙ“e Й—uuЙ—ude Й“en e maЙ“Й“e, Й—uurnii, Й“een Й“e nanataa."
  41,5,"ЖҒe mb'i: "ЖҒerЙ—e amen no ommbanii ko noddataa men e mum kon, noto hino e noppi amen, heedo kadi hino hakkunde amen e maa. Haray wonu e golle maa ; menen kadi miЙ—en e golle amen"."
  41,6,"Maaku: "nganndee ko neЙ—Й—anke yeruujo mon. Wahayinaama e am, won'de DeweteeЙ—o mon on, ko DeweteeЙ—o gooto. Г‘iiЙ“ee e Й—um, insinanoЙ—on mo". Bone woodanii sirkooЙ“e Й“en."
  41,7,"Й“e njonnataa Й“een askal, hara kadi hiЙ“e njeddi fii La'akara."
  41,8,"Pellet, Й“een gooЕӢЙ—iinЙ“e Й“e ngolli moЖҙЖҙi Й—in, hino woodani Й“e njoЙ“di ndi taЖҙondirtaa."
  41,9,"Maaku: "Eey mon on njedda oon takЙ—o leydi ndin ndeer balЙ—e Й—iЙ—i, mbaЙ—anon mo goreeЙ“e? Awa ko oon woni JeyЙ—o winndere ndeen."
  41,10,"O waЙ—i pelle e dow mayri, O hebbini barki e mayri, O eЙ“Й“i nguureeji mayri Й—in e ndeer balЙ—e nayi timmuЙ—e, wonan'de lamndotooЙ“e Й“een."
  41,11,"Refti o fotondiri ka kammu, fewndo ka ngu curkinnoo, O daalidani ngun kanngu e leydi ndin: "ngrdiree Й—oftaare, maa karheede". ЖҠi wi'idi: "Min ngarii ko min Й—oftii Й“e"."
  41,12,"O timminiri Й—i kammuuji jeeЙ—iЙ—i ndeer balЙ—e Й—iЙ—i, O yamiri kala kammu, fiyaaku maggu. Min cuЙ—iniri kammu aduna ngun, koode e reenirЙ—um. ЖҠum ko eЙ“Й“oore pooluЙ—o, gannduЙ—o On."
  41,13,"Si Й“e Й—uurnike, haray wi'u Й“e: "Min nejertinirii on haacaangu, sugu ha'acaango Aadi'en e Samuuda'en."
  41,14,"nde NulaaЙ“e Й“ren ardirannooЙ“e, ye'eso maЙ“Й“e e Й“aawo maЙ“Й“e, won'de: "Wata on ndewu dey, si wonaa Allah", Й“e mb'i: "Si Joomi amen haajuno, ko Malaa'ika O jippinaynoo. Awa minen, ko min yedduЙ“e ko nulaЙ—on mum kon"."
  41,15,"Aadii'en kan, Й“e mawnintini ka hoore leydi, ko aldaa e goonga, Й“e mbi'i: "Hara ko hommbo Й“uri min doole?" E Й“ee yiaani, won'de Allah takЙ—o Й“e On no Й“uri Й“e tiiЙ—ude doole? ЖҒe ngoni e yeddugol Aayeeje amen Й—en."
  41,16,"Min ngurti henndu Й“uuЙ“undu e maЙ“Й“e e ГұalaaЙ—e hiitaaЙ—e, fii no Min meeЙ—inira Й“e lepte koyeera Й—en ka nguurndam aduna. Pellet, ko lepte La'akara Й—en Й“uri won'de koyeera, kadi Й“e faaboytaake."
  41,17,"Samuuda'en kan, Min Й“annginanno Й“e; kono Й“e suЙ“ii bumЙ—am Й—am e dow peewal ngal. Dillere lepte hoynooje Й—en nanngiri Й“e, sabu ko Й“e paggitotonoo kon."
  41,18,"Min ndaЙ—ndi gooЕӢЙ—imЙ“e Й“e woniina hulnooЙ“e Й“en."
  41,19,"Г‘alnde noon ayГұЙ“e Allah Й“een mooЙ“iroytee faade ka Yiite... Hara heЙ“e ГұoЖҙЖҙindiree."
  41,20,"Haa si Й“e hewtii nge, nannЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—een, e giiЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en, e guri Й“alli maЙ“Й“e Й—in seeditoo e dow maЙ“Й“e, kon ko Й“e gollatnoo."
  41,21,"ЖҒe wi'ana guri maЙ“Й“e Й—en: "Ko fii honlЙ—um seeditaniЙ—on e amin?" ЖҠe wi'a: "Ko Allah wowlinЙ—o kala hu'unde On, wowlini men. Ko KaЕӢko tagunoo on gila ka laawol aranol, ko ka makko kadi rutteteЙ—on"."
  41,22,"On ngonaani hiЙ—on cuuЙ—ora, fii wata nanЙ—e mon, e giiЙ—e mon, e guri mon seedito e mon. Kono on cikkuno, won'de Allah anndaa ko Й—uuЙ—i e ko ngolloton."
  41,23,"Ko Й—uum mooЙ—on, cikkunoЙ—on Joomi mon, Й—uum halki on. WaЙ—tinЙ—on jeyyaaЙ“e e pertuЙ“e Й“een."
  41,24,"Hay si Й“e muГұГұike, ko Yiite ngen wonata jaaЖҙorde maЙ“Й“e; si Й“e Й—aЙ“Й“ii feleede ngaccitee, Й“e wonaani feleteeЙ“e accitee."
  41,25,"Min ngurtani Й“e wondiiЙ“e, Й“een cuЙ—inani Й“e ko woni ye'eso maЙ“Й“e, e ko woni Й“aawo maЙ“Й“e. Konngol [lepte] ngol jojji e maЙ“Й“e, won'dude e mofte yawtunooЙ—e ado maЙ“Й“e, immorde e jinna e yimЙ“e. Pellet, Й“e laatino hayruЙ“e."
  41,26,"YedduЙ“e Й“een mb'i: "Wota on jentito ndee Alqur'aanaare, sonkee e mayre (tuma nde janngetee) mbelajo'o, on foolay"."
  41,27,"Ma Min meeЙ—iniroy yedduЙ“e Й“een, lepte saЙ—tuЙ—e, Min njoЙ“ira ko Й“uri bon'de e ko Й“e ngollatnoo noo kon."
  41,28,"Ko Й—um woni njoЙ“di aГұЙ“e Allah Й“een: Ko Yiite ngen. Ko galle luttugol woodani Й“e ton, njoЙ“di kon ko Й“e yeddiraynoo aayeeje amen Й—en."
  41,29,"YedduЙ“e Й“en mbi'a: "Joomi amen, hollii min majjinnooЙ“e min Й“een ka jinna e ka yimЙ“e, min yaaЙ“a Й“e min fuga, haa Й“e wona e Й“urЙ“e joltude Й“en"."
  41,30,"Pellet, wi'uЙ“e Й“een : "Joomi amen ko Allah", refti Й“e tabiti; Malaa'ika'en hino jippoo e maЙ“Й“e (wiide): "Wota on hulu, wota on suno; wewliree Aljanna, on mo wonanoЙ—on fodeede."
  41,31,"Ko minen ngoni ni wallooЙ“e on Й“een ka nguurndam aduna e ka La'akara. Hino woodani on ton, kala ko woЕӢkiiji mon wooЙ—etee, hino woodani ton, kala ko noddoton,"
  41,32,"ko maraari, immorde e kaforoore, HinnotooЙ—o"."
  41,33,"Hara ko hommbo Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude konngol, wano on nodduЙ—o e fii Allah, o golli moЖҙЖҙere, o wi'i: "miin, ko e juulЙ“e Й“en mi njiyaa?"."
  41,34,"MoЖҙЖҙere ndeen fotataa e bone on. DuГұir (golle bonЙ—e Й—en) kon ko Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude; e jaka yoo, on mo ngayngu woni hakkunde maa e mum, himo wa'ita wa giЙ—o saЙ—tuЙ—o giggol."
  41,35,"Kono hawrataa e Й—uum, si wonaa muГұГұiiЙ“e Й“en; hawrataa e Й—uum, si wonaa jom geЙ—al mawnungal."
  41,36,"Si sowinsinoore arii heЙ“ude ma immorde e seytaane, moolor Allah. KaЕӢko ko O Nanoowo, gannduЙ—o."
  41,37,"Hino jiyaa e Ma'andeeji makko Й—in, jemma on e Гұalawma on, e na'ange ngen e lewru ndun. Wota on cujjan na'ange ngen wonaa kadi lewru ndun. Cujjanee Allah, takЙ—o Й—i On, si wonii ko KaЕӢko ndewoton."
  41,38,"Si Й“e townitike, Й“een wonЙ“e ka Joomi maa kan, hiЙ“e cubbunhinorana mo jemma e Гұalawma, hara Й“e haaЙ“ataa."
  41,39,"Hino jeyaa e Ma'andeeji makko Й—in, tawde a nji'ay leydi ndin no yoori. Si wonii Min njippinii ndiyam toЙ“o e mayri, ndi dilla ndi fontoo. Awa nguurnituЙ—o ndi on, pellet, ko wuurnitoowo maayЙ“e Й“en, tawde pellet, ko O kattanЙ—o haka hu'unde."
  41,40,"Pellet, ooГұotooЙ“e Й“een e aayeeje Amen Й—een, Й“e vuuЙ—otaako Min. E ko feroyteeЙ—o on ka Yiite Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude kaa ko aroyoowo on Г‘alnde Darngal hino hoolii? NGollee ko paalaЙ—on, ko pellet, Homo reeni ko ngolloton kon."
  41,41,"YedduЙ“e Й“een Alqur'aana tuma nde arnoo e maЙ“Й“e, pellet noon, ko nde deftere teddunde [foolnde];"
  41,42,"mehre iwrantaa nde ye'eso mayre, wonaa Й“aawo mayre. Ko jipporiinde immorde ka Г‘eeГұo, jettiniiЙ—o On."
  41,43,"A wi'aaka si wonaa ko NulaaЙ“e adinooЙ“e ma Й“en mbi'anoo. Pellet, Joomi maa, ko O Jom yaafuyee, e Jom lepte mu'usuuЙ—e."
  41,44,"Si Min mbaЙ—uno nde janngeteende e haala ajami, Й“e wi'atno: "Ko haЙ—no aayeeje mayre Й—en fensitee? E nde wonat e haala ajami, [NulaaЙ—o] on wona aarabuujo?" Maaku: "Kayre wonan'de gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“en, ko nde peewal e cellal". ЖҒe ngooЕӢЙ—inaa Й“en kan, noto hino e noppi maЙ“Й“e Й—in, kayre ko nde niЙ“e e dow maЙ“Й“e; Й“en hino noddiree e nokku woЙ—Й—uЙ—o."
  41,45,"GooЕӢЙ—ii Min ngokkii Muusaa Deftere ndeen, nde luutondira e mayre. Si wonaano Konngol ardinoongol immorde ka Joomi maa, hakkunde maЙ“Й“e Гұaaweteno. KamЙ“e kan, pellet, hiЙ“e e sikke sikkitiiЙ—o nde."
  41,46,"Kala golluЙ—o ko moЖҙЖҙi, ko fii hoore-makko; kala kadi bonnuЙ—o, yantat e makko. Joomi maa ciforaani won'de, tooГұoowo jiyaaЙ“e Й“en."
  41,47,"Ko ka makko woni ko ganndal Darngal nduttetee. DimЙ—e yaltataa e coomЙ—i mum, deyel (woo) saawataa,ngel jibintaa si wanaa e ganndal makko.Г‘ande O noddiroyta Й“e:"Ko honto woni kafidaaЙ—i am Й—in?", Й“e mbi'a:"Min nganndinii Ma, alah e amen seedotooЙ—o [Й—um]""
  41,48,"ЖҒe majjira e ko ko Й“e ndewatnoo ko adii; Й“e yananee won'de daЙ—irgal alanaa Й“e."
  41,49,"NeЙ—Й—aЕӢke on kaaЙ“ataa toragol moЖҙЖҙere. Si bone memii mo, ko o taЖҙotooЙ—o, jonndiniiЙ—o."
  41,50,"Si Min meeЙ—inir mo moЖҙЖҙere immorde ka Amen, Й“aawo nde lorra memi mo, ko pellet o wi'ay: "ЖҠuum Й—oo ko min ! Mi pellitaani si Darnga daroto. Si mi nduttaama ka Joomi am, ko pellet, moЖҙЖҙere hino woodani lam ka makko". Ma Min kumpitu yedduЙ“e Й“een, fii ko Й“e huuwi kon, ko ma Min meeЙ—inoy Й“e lepte saЙ—tuЙ—e."
  41,51,"Si Min neeminii e neЙ—Й—aЕӢke on, o Й—uurnoo o toowna balaaje makko; si bone non heЙ“ii mo, o wona jom toraare jaaynde."
  41,52,"Maaku: "Yeetee kam, si wonii le ko ka Allah nde iwri, refti njedduЙ—on nde; haray ko hommbo Й“uri majjude on gonЙ—o e lurral woЙ—Й—ungal?""
  41,53,"Aray Min kolla Й“e Ma'andeeji Amen Й—in ka tatteeji e maЙ“Й“e tigi, haa Й“anngana Й“e won'de ko nde goonga. E yonaani won'de Joomi maa, ko O ceediiЙ—o kala hu'unde?"
  41,54,"Ganndee heЙ“e e cikke fii hawroygol e Joomi maЙ“Й“e. Ganndee non, ko O huЙ“indiiЙ—o kala hu'unde."
  42,1,"Haa, miim."
  42,2,"Ain, siin, qaaf."
  42,3,"Ko wano nii woni ko Allah TeЙ—Й—uЙ—o, Г‘eeГұo oon wahayiniri e maa, e Й“een adinooЙ“e maa."
  42,4,"Ko KaЕӢko woodani kala ko woni ka kammuuji e ka leydi. Ko KaЕӢko kadi woni ToowuЙ—o, mawЙ—o oon."
  42,5,"Kammuuji Й—iin no eЙ“Й“a seekorgol dow majji, hara Malaa'ika'en no subbunhinanora yettugol Joomi maЙ“Й“e, Й“e imsinanoo wonЙ“e ka leydi Й“een. Ngandee pellet, ko Allah woni kaforoowo, jurmotooЙ—o otooЙ—o On."
  42,6,"ЖҒeen non jogitiiЙ“e yiЙ—Й“e goo ga Makko, Allah ko deenuЙ—o Й“e. A wonaani deenoowo Й“e."
  42,7,"Ko wano noon Min wahayniri e maaЙ—a, janngeteende e aarabu, fii yo a jeertin yimЙ“e neene ca'e Й—en e wonЙ“e takko mayre Й“een, jerrtinaa fii Гұalnde dental nden, - nde sikke alaa e mu'um - Fedde goo ka Aljnna, fedde goo kadi ka Yiite."
  42,8,"Si Allah haajuno, O waЙ—ayno Й“e mofte goote. Kono himo oon mo O muuyi ka Yurmeende makko. TooГұooЙ“e Й“een non, giЙ—o alanaa Й“e, wonaa ballo."
  42,9,"Kaa Й“e njogiti yiЙ—Й“e goo ga makko? Awa ko Allah woni GiЙ—o on, ko KaЕӢko wuurnitata maayЙ“e Й“een; ko KaЕӢko kadi woni kaЙ—tanЙ—o kala hu'unde."
  42,10,"Kala ko luutondirЙ—on e fii mun, haray Гұaawoore mum nden ko ka Allah woni. Ko on mooЙ—on Allah, woni Joomi am; ko e makko mi fawii, ko ka makko kadi mi ruttorta [tuubugol]."
  42,11,"PuЙ—Й—uЙ—o kammuuji Й—in e leydi ndin. O waЙ—iranii on e pittaali mon Й—in genndooЙ“e, ka neemoraaЙ—i kadi nooneeji; Homo Й—uЙ—Й—inira on Й—um. Hay hu'unde yerondiraa e makko; ko Kanko woni Nanoowo, ji'oowo On."
  42,12,"Ko KaЕӢko heerori soktirЙ—e kammuuji Й—iin e leydi ndin. Homo weertana arsike on mo o muuyani, O Й“iЙ—tinana (mo O muuyani). Pellet, ko O gannduЙ—o kala hu'unde."
  42,13,"O sar'inanii on e diina kan, koЕӢko ko o yamirnoo nuuhu, e kon ko Min wahayini e maaЙ—a, e kon ko Min njamirnoo Ibraahiima, e Muusaa e Iisaa, won'de: "Г‘iЙ“nee diina kan; hara on ceertaani e makka". Kono Ko noddotaa sirkooЙ“e Й“en e mum kon, mawnii e dow maЙ“Й“e. Allah non hino suЙ“anoo Й—um, mo O muuyani, O fewna e makko, kala tuuboowo."
  42,14,"ЖҒe seertaano, si wonaa Й“aawo nde ganndal ngal arde e maЙ“Й“e, sabu bewre hakkunde maЙ“Й“e. Si wonaano fii Konngol ardinoongol, immorde ka Joomi maa, haa e lajal taЖҙaangal, Гұaaweteno hakkunde maЙ“Й“e. Ko pellet, roninaaaЙ“e deftere nden Й“aawo maЙ“Й“e, hino e sikke fii mayre sikkitiiЙ“e."
  42,15,"Noddu (yimЙ“e Й“en) kisan; ГұiiЙ“iraa no yamiraЙ—aa non, wota a jokku mbeleeЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—een, maakaa: "Mi gooЕӢЙ—inii ko Allah jippini kon (fof) e defte, mi njamiraama kadi, nunЙ—ugol hakkunde mon. Allah woni Joomi amen e Joomi mon. Ko minen golle amen woodani, ko onon kadi golle mon woodani. Yeddondiral woo alaa hakkunde amen e mon. Allah mooЙ“oyay e denndaandal. Ko ka makko woni ruttorde nden"."
  42,16,"ЖҒeen weeГұirooЙ“e e diina Allah kan, Й“aawo ka jaЙ“aneede, hujja maЙ“Й“e on ko mehre, tikkere no fawii e maЙ“Й“e, hino woodani Й“e kadi lepte caЙ—tuЙ—e."
  42,17,"Ko Allah woni jippiniri deftere nden goonga, e manndakke Й—en. E ko anndin maa? Hino gasa hara darnga ngal ko ko Й“adii?"
  42,18,"ЖҒeya Й“e gooЕӢЙ—inaani ngal Й“een, hiЙ“e heГұoringal; gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“en kan, ko Й“e hulu fii maggal, e hoore hiЙ“e felliti won'de ko ngal goonga. Awa anndee wonЙ“e yeddondireede Й“en fii Darngal, ko pellet, Й“e ngonii e ndeer majjere woЙ—Й—unde."
  42,19,"Allah ko newaniiЙ—o jiyaaЙ“e makko Й“en. Homo arsike on mo o muuyani. Ko KaЕӢko woni DoolnuЙ—o, poolЙ—o On."
  42,20,"Kala tawЙ—o ko baraaje ndun laakara o faalaa, Men Й“eydanay mo mbarjaari makko ndin; kala kadi tawЙ—o ko jayru ndun aduna o yiЙ—i, Min ngokkay mo Й—um, hara non o alaa ka kaalara (ton) geЙ—al."
  42,21,"Kaa hara denndaaaaЙ—i hino woodani Й“e, sar'inanЙ—i Й“e e diina kan, ko ko Allah duЕӢaaki fii mum? Si wonaano fii Konngol [happunoongol] ngol fii senndugol [hakkunde maЙ“Й“e], Гұaaweteno hakkunde maЙ“Й“e. Ko pellet, hino woodani tooГұuЙ“e Й“en, lepte muusЙ—e."
  42,22,"A yi'at tooГұЙ“e Й“en hino huli e ko Й“e fggitii kon, Й—um le ko yantayЙ—um e maЙ“Й“e. GooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“en, Й“e ngolli golle moЖҙЖҙe, hiЙ“e e dinngire naakooji, hara hino woodani Й“e ka Joomi maЙ“Й“e, kala ko Й“e faaletee. Ko Й—uum tigiri, woni Й“ural mawnungal ngal."
  42,23,"Ko Й—uum woni ko Allah wewlinirta jiyaaЙ“e makko gooЕӢЙ—iiЙ“e Й“en, Й“e ngolli golle moЖҙЖҙe. Maaku: "Mi lamndaaki on njoЙ“di e Й—um, si wonaa tun giggol enЙ—am Й—am". Kala paggitiiЙ—o moЖҙЖҙere, Min Й“eydanay mo moЖҙЖҙere e hoore mayre. Pellet, Allah ko kaforoowo, mantoowo."
  42,24,"Kaa Й“e mbi'ay o fefindor nde e hoore Allah fenaande. Si Allah haajuno, O notatno e Й“ernda maa nden. Alla no meha meere nden, O tabintinira goonga kan Daalol makko ngol. Pellet, ko O gannduЙ—o gunndooji Й“erЙ—e Й—een."
  42,25,"Ko KaЕӢko woni jaЙ“anoowo jiyaaЙ“e makko Й“een tuubuubuyee, O yaafoo bonЙ—i Й—in, e hoore Himo anndi ko ngolloton kon."
  42,26,"Himo jaabinana gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“een, Й“e ngolli moЖҙЖҙuЙ—i, O Й“eydana Й“e e Й“ural makko ngal. HeeferЙ“e Й“en non, hino woodani Й“e lepte caЙ—tuЙ—e."
  42,27,"Si tawno Allah yaГұГұanno jiyaaЙ“e Makko Й“een [fof] arsike, pellet, Й“e bewayno ka leydi; kono Homo jippinira emmbere ko O muuyi. Pellet, ko O kummpitiiЙ—o, yioowo jeyyaaЙ“e makko Й“een."
  42,28,"Ko Kano woni jippinoowo toЙ“o ngoon Й“aawo Й“e taЖҙaade, O saaka yurmeende makko nden. Ko KaЕӢko kadi woni GiЙ—o, jettiniiЙ—o On."
  42,29,"Hino jeyaa e Ma'andeeji makko Й—iin: tagugol kammuuji Й—iin e leydi ndin, e ruugayЙ—i Й—i O saaki Й—in hakkunde majji. KaЕӢko e fii mooЙ“indiroygol Й“e ngool, si O haajii, ko O kattanЙ—o."
  42,30,"Kala ko heЙ“i on e masiibo, ko sabu ko juuЙ—e mon Й—een faggitii kon. Himo ya'afoo noon, ko Й—uuЙ—i."
  42,31,"OOn wonaani laawotooЙ“e ka leydi ; alanaa on ga Allah, giЙ—o, wanaa ballo."
  42,32,"Hino jiyaa e Ma'andeeji makko Й—iin: dogayЙ—e Й—en ka maayo, wa'aЙ—e wa pelle."
  42,33,"Si O haajii, O deeЖҙinay henndu ndun, ndu waЙ—tinira tabitndu e hoore maggo. Wonii e Й—uum, Ma'andeeji, wona 'de kala muГұГұotooЙ—o, jettoowo."
  42,34,"Maa yooliraЙ—e sabu ko Й“e paggitii kon. Himo ya'afoo noon ko Й—uuЙ—i."
  42,35,"WennjooЙ“e Й“eeen e aayeeje Amen Й—en, hino anndi Й“e alaa laaworde."
  42,36,"Kala ko ngokkaЙ—on e hu'unde, ko dakamme nguurndam aduna; ko ko woni ka Allah koon, Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude woni kadi ko heddotoo wonan'de gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“een fawotooЙ“e e Joomi maЙ“Й“e."
  42,37,"woЙ—Й—itotooЙ“e bakkaatuuji mawЙ—i Й—iin e paЕӢkare Й—een, si wonii Й“e tikkii, hara Й“e yaafoto,"
  42,38,"Й“een nootiiЙ“e Joomi maЙ“Й“e, Й“e ГұiЙ“ni juulde nden, Й“e tawata fiyaaku maЙ“Й“e on ko diisondiral hakkunde maЙ“Й“e, nafqooЙ“e e ko ko Min ngarsiki Й“e,"
  42,39,"e Й“een tawЙ“e si bewre heЙ“ii Й“e, Й“e njottoto."
  42,40,"NjoЙ“di bonnere, ko bone yeru mum. Kala non yaafiiЙ—o o moЖҙЖҙintini, haray njoЙ“di makko ndin ko ka Allah woni. Pellet non, O yiЙ—aa tooГұooЙ“e Й“een."
  42,41,"Kala noon yottiiЙ“e Й“aawo Й“e tooГұeede, ko Й“en woni Й“e laawol [nanngitireede] fawaaki e mum."
  42,42,"Ko laawol [nanngitireede] fawii e mum, ko tooГұooЙ“e yimЙ“e Й“een, hara hiЙ“e bewira e leydi ndin ko aldaa e goonga: Й“e Й—oon, hino woodani lepte mu'usuuЙ—e."
  42,43,"MuГұГұiiЙ—o on kadi o yaafii, ko pellet, Й—uum no jiyaa e pellital fiyakuujI."
  42,44,"Kala mo Allah majjini, haray giЙ—o (goo) alanaa mo Й“aawo Й—um. A tinay tooГұЙ“e Й“een, tuma Й“e nji'i lepte Й—een, hiЙ“e mbi'a: "Hara laawol ruttorde no woodi?"."
  42,45,"A tinay Й“e kadi, heЙ“e mbeeЙ“itee e magge, hara heЙ“e njankinii koyeera on, heЙ“e ndaarira ndaarЙ—e leppagol. GooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“en mbi'aya: "Ko woni hayru Й“e Й“een, ko Й“en hayrimЙ“e ko'e mun e Й“eynguureeji maЙ“Й“e Й—in Г‘alnde Darngal". Nganndee pellet, tooГұuЙ“e Й“een no e lepte duumiiЙ—e."
  42,46,"YiЙ—Й“e alanaa Й“e, ko wallitoo Й“e, hara wonaa Allah. Kala noon mo Allah majjini, haray laawol alanaa mo."
  42,47,"Nootee Joomi mon, ado Гұalaande arde, nde ruttoowo alaa Й—uum ka Allah. Nden Гұalnde, faaborde alanaa on, jeddugol kadi alanaa oon."
  42,48,"Si Й“e Й—uurnike non, haray min nuliraali ma, aynoowo Й“e: fawaaki ma, si wonaa joottingol. Si wonii Min meeЙ—iniri neЙ—Й—anke on neema immorde e Amen, o wewlira mo; si ko bone non heЙ“i Й“e, sabu kon ko juuЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en ardiniri, a taway pellet, neЙ—Й—o on ko jedduЙ—o sanne !"
  42,49,"Ko Allah woodani laamagol kammuuji Й—in e leydi ndin. Himo taga ko o muuyi. Homo yeЙ—a mo o muuyani Й“iЙ“Й“e rewЙ“e, O yeЙ—a kadi mo O muuyani Й“iЙ—Й“e worЙ“e."
  42,50,"maa O jillira Й“e worЙ“e e rewЙ“e; Homo waЙ—a dimaro, on mo o muuyani. Pellet, ko O ganduЙ—o, kattanЙ—o."
  42,51,"Sellantaa neЙ—Й—aЕӢke, nde Allah yeewtata mo, si wonaa wahayu, maa e Й“aawo heedo, maa o immina NulaaЙ—o (Malaa'ikaajo), on wayahina e duЕӢayee(sakkitoore) makko, ko ko O haaji. Pellet, ko O toowuЙ—o, Г‘eeГұЙ—o."
  42,52,"Ko wano non Min mbayayinir e maaЙ—a, ruuhu on [Alqur'aana] e yamiroore Amen. A anndaano ko woni deftere, maa gooЕӢЙ—inal; si ko woni, Min mbaЙ—unde ndaygu, ngu Min peewwnirta on mo Min muuyani e jiyaaЙ“e Amen Й“en. Pellet, ko a feewnoowo e laawol Pocciingol,"
  42,53,"laawol Allah, On jeyЙ—o ko woni kammuuji e ka leydi. ganndee, ko ka Allah, fiyakuuji Й—in nduttotoo."
  43,1,"Haa, miim."
  43,2,"Mi wooЙ—ndirii defere Й“anngunde ndeen !"
  43,3,"Min maЙ—ii nde janngeteende [e Й—emngal] aarabu, mbelajo'o, on kaqqilay."
  43,4,"Pellet, hende woni ka Amen gaa, ka yumma defte, toownde, ГұeГұaande."
  43,5,"E Min ngacciray njippinangol on jantoore ndeen, Й—uurngal on, fii on ngonii yimЙ“e fantinЙ“e?"
  43,6,"ЖҠuuЙ—ii e AnnabaaЙ“e Й“e Min nuli e adinooЙ“e Й“een."
  43,7,"Annabaajo araali e maЙ“Й“e, si wonaa Й“e njalkitay mo."
  43,8,"Min kalki ko Й“uri Й“e saЙ—tude doole ! Toode mise adinooЙ“e Й“een jawtiino."
  43,9,"Ko pellet, si a lamndike Й“e: "Ko hommbo tagi kammuuji Й—in e leydi ndin?" ЖҒe mbi'ay: "Ko pooluЙ—o, gannduЙ—o on tagi Й—ii"."
  43,10,"Oon mbaЙ—iranЙ—o on leydi ndin weertaandi, O waЙ—ani on Й—ate e mayri, fii no Й—oworon."
  43,11,"Oon jippinrЙ—o toЙ“o ka kammuu, yeru haaju, Min nguurnitiri ngo leydi maayndi. Ko noon yaltinirteЙ—on."
  43,12,"On takЙ—o nooneeji Й—in fow, O waЙ—irani on e laaЙ—e Й—en e neemoraaЙ—i Й—iin, ko mbaЙ—Й—oron,"
  43,13,"fii yo on potondir e hoore majji, refti ngannditon neema Joomi mon on, tuma potondirЙ—on e majji, mb'on on tuma: "Senaare woodanii eeltanЙ—o min Й—uum On, min ngonaano taaqanaaЙ“e Й—um."
  43,14,"minen noon, ko ka Joomi amen woni ko min nduttotoo"."
  43,15,"ЖҒe mbaЙ—ani mo geЙ—al e jiyaaЙ“e Makko Й“een ! Pellet, on neЙ—Й—aЕӢke ko jedduЙ—o Й“annguЙ—o."
  43,16,"Kaa woo O jogiti Й“iЙ—Й“e rewЙ“e e ko O tagi kon, O heertinani on Й“iЙ—Й“e worЙ“e Й“een?"
  43,17,"Si goЙ—Й—o e maЙ“Й“e wewliniraama ko o waЙ—irani kon Hinaranke On misal, ye'eso makko ngon niЙ“Й“ita metteendi hombo suuЙ—i."
  43,18,"E ko on ne'eteeЙ—o e cuЙ—aari, hara kaЕӢko on ka yeddondiral, wonaa o Й“annginoowo haala?"
  43,19,"ЖҒe mbaЙ—i Malaa'ikaaЙ“e tawЙ“e Й“een ko jiyaaЙ“e Joom yurmeende oon, rewЙ“e ! Kere Й“e seedino tageede Й“een? Awa fii seedagol maЙ“Й“e ngol winndete, Й“e lamnditoyee."
  43,20,"ЖҒe mbi'iti: "Si Joom yurmeende On haajuno, min ndewataano Й“e". ЖҒe alanaa Й—uum hay e ganndal; Й“e ngonaani, si wonaa hiЙ“e pena."
  43,21,"Kaa ko defftere Min ngaddani Й“e ado ndee Й—oo, hara ko nden woni ko Й“e njogitii?"
  43,22,"Si ko woni, Й“e mbi'iu: "Minen Min tawu baabiraaЙ“e amen Й“een e diina, haray ko e batteeji maЙ“Й“e min peewirta"."
  43,23,"Ko wano non, Min nulaali jeertinoowo aditaade ma e saare woo, si wonaa hooreeЙ“e maЙ“Й“e neemiiЙ“e mbi'ay: "Minen Min tawu baabiraaЙ“e amen Й“en e diina, Й—um non ko batteeji maЙ“Й“e Й—in men Гұermtinta"."
  43,24,"O maaki: "Hay si mi addan on ko Й“uri feewude kon ko tawruЙ—on baabiraaЙ“e mon Й“en?" ЖҒe mbi'i: "Minen dey, ko min jedduЙ“e ko nulidaЙ—on e mum koon"."
  43,25,"Min njottii e maЙ“Й“e. ndaare no battande fennuЙ“e Й“een mba'unoo."
  43,26,"JaЕӢto tuma Ibraahiima maakannoo been makko e yimЙ“e makko Й“een: "Min on ko mi daЙ—ndiiЙ—o e kon ko ndewoton,"
  43,27,"si wanaa On takЙ—o lam, KaЕӢko oon, O feewnay kam"."
  43,28,"O waЙ—i ngool konngol heddotoongol Й“aawo makko, mbelajo'o, Й“e nduttoto."
  43,29,"Si ko woni, Mi dakmitii Й“ee Й—oo e baabiraaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“een, haa nde goonga kan ngarnoo e maЙ“Й“e, e NulaaЙ—o Й“annguЙ—o."
  43,30,"Nde goonga kan arnoo e maЙ“Й“e, Й“e mbi'i: "ЖҠuum ko mbilewu, minen ko min njedduЙ“e Й—uum"."
  43,31,"ЖҒe mb'iti: "Ko haЙ—no ndee Alqur'aanaare jippinee e gorko mawЙ—o ca'e Й—en Й—iЙ—i?""
  43,32,"E ko kamЙ“e senndata yurmeende Joomi maa ndeen? Awa ko Minen ngoni ko senndi nguureeji maЙ“Й“e Й—iin hakkunde maЙ“Й“e, ka nguurndam aduna. Min Й“amti yoga maЙ“Й“e e hoore Й“eya, darjaaji, fii no yoga maЙ“Й“e jogitora yoga eeltane. Haray ko yurmeende Joomi maa ndeen, Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude e ko ko Й“e mooЙ“ata."
  43,33,"Si wonaano fii wata yimЙ“e Й“een ngon mofte goote, Min mbaЙ—ayno e cuuЙ—i kala jedduЙ—o Hinnaranke Oon: kiЙ“Й“e kaalisi e ЕӢabbirЙ—e ka Й“e Жҙawra;"
  43,34,"(Min mbaЙ—ayno kadi) e cuuЙ—i maЙ“Й“e Й—iin, dame e ndaЙ—Й—ude ka Й“e soЙ“Й“indoo,"
  43,35,"e cuЙ—aari. Kono Й—uum fow wonaani, si wonaa dakamme nguurndam aduna. Ko La'akara on ka Joomi maa, woni fii gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“een."
  43,36,"Kala Й—uurniiЙ—o e jaЕӢtoore Hinaranko On, Min nguurta mo e seytanuuru, hara ko ndun woni ko o coowodata."
  43,37,"ЖҠiin (awaseeji) noon, ko sakkorayЙ—i Й“e e peewal ngal, haa ka Й“e cikkata hiЙ“e peewi."
  43,38,"Haa si o aroyii e Amin, o wi'a: "Ee bone ! hara hakkunde am e maa woЙ—Й—irayno goЙ—Й—al puЙ—Й—irЙ—e Й—en Й—iЙ—i woЙ—Й—iri ! A bonii cinndadiiЙ—o !"."
  43,39,"[ЖҠuum] nafataa on hannde - nde tawnoo on tooГұii - won'de ko ka lepte kaawtuЙ—on."
  43,40,"E ko an naninta paaЙ—uЙ—o maa feewnaa bunЙ—o e on wonЙ—o e ndeer majjere Й“anngunde?"
  43,41,"Si Min ngar Жҙettitude ma, ko Min yoЙ“ottotooЙ“e e maЙ“Й“e."
  43,42,"maa hara Men holle ko Min kammbirani Й“een kon, haray noon ko Min gaynooЙ“e fii maЙ“Й“e."
  43,43,"Jogito kon ko wahayinaa e maaЙ—a. Pellet, hiЙ—a jokki laawol pocciingol."
  43,44,"Ndee non [Alqur'aanaare], ko nde teddungal maa an e yimЙ“e maa Й“een. Aray nde laЙ“nditeeЙ—on."
  43,45,"Lamndii e Й“een NulaaЙ“e Amen Й“e Min nulunoo ado maa, si Min mbaЙ—uno ko wanaa Hinnaranke On, deweteeЙ—i goo?"
  43,46,"GooЕӢЙ—ii Min immindinii Muusaa e aayeeje Amen Й—een, haa e Fir'awna e mbatu mun ngun, o maaki: "Ko mi NulaaЙ—o JeyЙ—o tagoore"."
  43,47,"Nde o addannooЙ“e aayeeje Amen Й—ren, e jaka yoo hiЙ“e njalaЙ—i."
  43,48,"Min hollaali Й“e aaya, si wonaa haray on Й“uri adiiЙ—o mo on mawnude. Min nanngiri Й“e lepte Й—een, mbelajo'o, Й“e nduttoto."
  43,49,"ЖҒe mbi'i: "Ko an yo mbileejo! Torano min Joomi maa, ko O ahodi kon e maaЙ—a. Pellet, ko min feewooЙ“e"."
  43,50,"Nde Min huncannooЙ“e lepte Й—een, e jaka yoo, hiЙ“e pirta [ahadi]."
  43,51,"Fir'awna noddi e yimЙ“e Й“een, o wi'i: "Ko onon yo yimЙ“e am, wanaa miin jey laamu Misra? E hino Й—ii canЙ—i no ila e ley kuЙ“eeji am? E on nji'ataa?"
  43,52,"Kaa mi Й“uraa teddude oo koyЙ—o mo eЙ“Й“ataa laЙ“Й“innde haala?"
  43,53,"Awa ko hanno jawe kaЕӢЕӢe mbrnee e makko? Ma Malaa'ika'en arda e makko, na jokkondiri?""
  43,54,"O Й—aytini yimЙ“e makko Й“en, Й“e Й—owtii mo. Pellet, Й“een Й—on laatino yimЙ“e faasiqiiЙ“e."
  43,55,"Nde Й“e tikkinnoo Min, Min yottii e maЙ“Й“e; Min njooli Й“e fof."
  43,56,"Min mbaЙ—i Й“e ardiiЙ“e e yeru, wonan'de sakkiitiiЙ“e Й“een."
  43,57,"Tuma nde geЙ—al neene Maryama on piyiranoo misal, tawaa yoo, yimЙ“e maa Й“een no sooЖҙira Й—uum."
  43,58,"Й“e mbi'i: "Ko deweteeЙ—i amen Й—in Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude, kaa ko KaЕӢko?" ЖҒe piyiranaali ma ngal (misal), si wonaa fii wennjugol. Wurin, ko Й“e yimЙ“e saЙ—tuЙ“e mbeГұe."
  43,59,"Awa (Iisaa) wonaani, si wanaa jiyaaЙ—o mo Min neemini e mum, Min mbaЙ—i mo yeru wonan'de Й“iЙ—Й“e Israa'iila Й“een."
  43,60,"Si Moen kaajuno, Min waЙ—titirayno on Malaa'ika, ko lomtoo ka leydi."
  43,61,"Pellet non, ko o anndinorde Darngal. Wota on cikkito fii maggal. Jokkee kam, ko Й—uum woni laawol Pocciingol ngol."
  43,62,"Wota seytaane falo on ! tawde pellet, ko o gaГұo mon Й“annguЙ—o."
  43,63,"Nde Iisaa ardunoo e Й“annguЙ—i Й—in, o maaki: "GooЕӢЙ—ii mi ardanii on e ГұeeГұal, e no mi Й“annginirana on yoga e ko luutondirЙ—on e muuЙ—um. Haray kulee Allah, Й—oftoЙ—on mi."
  43,64,"Pellet, ko Alla Woni Joomi am e Joomi mon. Ndewee Mo. Ko Й—uum woni laawol pocciingol ngol"."
  43,65,"Feddeeji Й—iin luutondiri hakkunde majji. Bone woodanii Й“en yedduЙ“e, immorde e lepte Гұalaande mu'usuuЙ—e !"
  43,66,"Hara Й“e habbi si wpnaa nde Darngal ngal ardata Й“e e juhal, hara Й“e so'aa anndude?"
  43,67,"WelduЙ“e Й“een, nden Гұalnde, yoga maЙ“Й“e ko ayrooЙ“e yoga; si wonaa gooЕӢЙ—uiЙ“e Й“een."
  43,68,"Ko onon yo jiyaaЙ“e Am ! Kulol alanaa on hannde; wonaa on sunotooЙ“e kadi."
  43,69,"Й“een gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Aayeeje Amen Й—een, Й“e ngoni jebbiliiЙ“e,"
  43,70,"naatee ka Aljanna, onon e nannduЙ“e e mon, hoЙ—on saЙ—nee"."
  43,71,"[GollooЙ“e] hino wannginee e maЙ“Й“e, mirannji kaЕӢЕӢe e yedduЙ—e; hino ton kadi: kala ko wonkii muuyetee, gite dakmitoo. Hara le, ko on duumotooЙ“e toon."
  43,72,"Ko on ngoni Aljanna mo roniniraЙ—on, sabu ko ko ngollaynoЙ—on."
  43,73,"Hino woodani on toon, muuyanteeЙ—i Й—uuЙ—uЙ—i, Й—i Гұaamoton e mum."
  43,74,"Pellet, bonЙ“e Й“en, ko ka lepte Jahannama Й“e luttoyta,"
  43,75,"Й“e koynantaake, tee hara ko Й“e taЖҙiiЙ“e toon."
  43,76,"Min tooГұaani Й“e few, si ko woni, ko kamЙ“e woni tooГұuЙ“e Й“een."
  43,77,"ЖҒe nodda: "Ko an yo Maaliku ! Yo Joomi maa gaynu fii amen !" O wi'i: "Pellet, ko on luttooЙ“e [toon] !""
  43,78,""GooЕӢЙ—ii Min ngaddanii on goonga kan ; kono Й—uuЙ—uЙ“e e mon, ko aГұЙ“e goonga"."
  43,79,"Kaa Й“e eЙ“Й“u fehre ? Doo ko Min fewjooЙ“e !"
  43,80,"Maa hara Й“e cikku Min nanataa gunndooji maЙ“Й“e e sirru maЙ“Й“e? OoвҖҷowoye! NulaaЙ“e Amen Й“een hino maandina takko maЙ“Й“e."
  43,81,"Maaku: "Si Hinaranko on no njogitii Й“iЙ—Й—o, ko miin adotonoo rewude oon"."
  43,82,"Senaare woodanii JeyЙ—o kammuuji Й—in e leydi ndin, JeyЙ—o Arsi kin; laaЙ“uЙ—o e kon ko Й“e cifrotta mo."
  43,83,"AccuЙ“e Й“e jumpa, Й“e pija haa Й“e hawroya e Гұalaande maЙ“Й“e ndeЙ“e fodaa."
  43,84,"Ko KaЕӢko woni On deweteeЙ—o ka kammu e deweteeЙ—o ka leydi, ko KaЕӢko kadi woni Г‘eeГұo, gannduЙ—o On."
  43,85,"Barke heewanii on mo woodani Й—um, laamu kammuuji Й—in e leydi ndin e ko woni hakkunde majji. Ko ka makko anndal fii Darngal woni. Ko ka makko kadi ndutteteЙ—on."
  43,86,"ЖҠi Й“e ndewata Й—in ga makko jeyah tefoore, si wonaa seediiЙ“e goonga Й“een, hara heЙ“e nganndi."
  43,87,"Ko pellet, si a lamndike Й“e, ko hommbo woni ko tagi Й“e? ЖҒe mbi'ay: "Ko Allah". Ko holno non Й“e njiiliraa?"
  43,88,"[Himo anndi kadi] fii ko (NulaaЙ—o) oon maakunoo kon: "Ko an yo Joomi, pellet, Й“ee ko yimЙ“e Й“e ngooЕӢЙ—intaa"."
  43,89,"Yaafo Й“e, maakaa: "Kisal !" Aray ndebe ngannda."
  44,1,"Haa, miim."
  44,2,"Mi wooЙ—ndirii defere Й“anngunde nde !"
  44,3,"Min njippinirii nde e jemma barkinaaЙ—o, Min siforii won'de jeertinooЙ“e."
  44,4,"Ko e on (jehma) woni ko seerndetee kala fiyaaku ГұeГұaaЙ—o."
  44,5,"ЖҠuum ko yamiroore immorde ka amen. Min siforii won'de NulooЙ“e."
  44,6,"yurmeende immornde ka Joomi maa. Pellet, ko KaЕӢko woni Nanoowo, gannduЙ—o oon."
  44,7,"JeyЙ—o kammuuji Й—iin e leydi ndiin e ko woni kon hakkunde majji, si wonii ko on yananaaЙ“e."
  44,8,"DeweteeЙ—o goo alaa, si wanaa KaЕӢko. Homo wuurna, Himo wara. JeyЙ—o on Jeyi baabiraaЙ“e mon aramЙ“e Й“een."
  44,9,"Ko woni tan, Й“e wonii e sikke, heЙ“e pija."
  44,10,"Habbito Гұande kammu ngun ardata e curki feeГұuuki,"
  44,11,"suddayki yimЙ“e Й“en. [ЖҒe mbi'anee]: "ЖҠuum ko lepte mu'usuuЙ—e" !"
  44,12,""Joomi amen, huncan min lepte Й—een. Minen ko men gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e"."
  44,13,"Ko honno Й“e mbaajitorta, ko goongo NulaaЙ—o Й“annginЙ—o ariino Й“e?"
  44,14,"Refti Й“e nduЕӢti, Й“e mb'i: "Ko tinndinaaЙ—o, kaangaaЙ—o"."
  44,15,"Awa ko Min ittooЙ“e lepte Й—en seeЙ—a; kono pellet, ko on ruttitotooЙ“e."
  44,16,"Г‘ande Min nanngiroyta bippannde mawnde nden, pellet, ko Min yoЙ“toytooЙ“e."
  44,17,"GooЕӢЙ—ii Min njarribinoke ado maЙ“Й“e, yimЙ“e Fir'awna Й“en, NulaaЙ—o tedduЙ—o ari e maЙ“Й“e,"
  44,18,"won'de: "mbaЙ—ee e juuЙ—e am, jiyaaЙ“e Allah Й“een. Min ko mi NulaaЙ—o e mon, koolniiЙ—o."
  44,19,"E won'de wota on townitano Allah, tawde mi addanay on hujja Й“annguЙ—o."
  44,20,"Min kadi noon, mi moolorii JeyЙ—o kam oon Jeyi on, nde piЙ—otonmi kaaЖҙe."
  44,21,"Si on ngooЕӢЙ—inaa kam, haray celee kam"."
  44,22,"O noddi Joomi makko, won'de: "ЖҒee Й—oo, ko yimЙ“e bonЙ“e"."
  44,23,""Yaadir e jiyaaЙ“e Am Й“en jehma; nganndon ko on sukketeeЙ“e."
  44,24,"Ngaccaa maayo ngoon deeЖҙa [si on lummbii] Й“eya kan, ko konu yooleteengu"."
  44,25,"ЖҠuuЙ—ii ko Й“e ngacci e gese e Й“ulli,"
  44,26,"e remuruuji e koЙ—an'de tedduЙ—e,"
  44,27,"e dokke Й“e ngonnoo e neeminireede."
  44,28,"Ko wano noon. Hooti Min ndonini Й—i yimЙ“e woЙ“Й“e."
  44,29,"Kammu nguun toЙ“aali Й“e, wonaa leydi ndin, Й“e ngonaani kadi muГұanteeЙ“e."
  44,30,"GooЕӢЙ—ii Min ndaЙ—ndii Й“iЙ—Й“e Israa'iila Й“een e lepte koyneeje;"
  44,31,"immorde e Fir'awna, tawde o laatino townitiiЙ—o, jiyaaЙ—o e fantimЙ“e Й“een."
  44,32,"GooЕӢЙ—ii Min cuЙ“orike Й“e e dow ganndal e hoore winndere ndeen,"
  44,33,"Min ngokki Й“e Ma'andeeji, Й—i jarrabuyee Й“annguЙ—o woni e mum."
  44,34,"ЖҒee kan no mbi'a:"
  44,35,""Ndee wonaani, si wonaa maayde amen aranere nden tan. Min wonatah immintinoyteeЙ“e."
  44,36,"Awa artiree baabiraaЙ“e amen Й“een, si wonii ko on gooЕӢЙ—uЙ“e"."
  44,37,"Kere ko kamЙ“e Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude kaa ko yimЙ“e "Tubba'in" Й“een e Й“eya adinooЙ“e Й“e? Min kalkuno Й“een, tawde hari ko Й“e bonЙ“e."
  44,38,"Min tagiraali kammuuji Й—in e leydi ndin e ko woni hakkunde majji kon, fijooЙ“e."
  44,39,"Min tagiraali Й—in Й—iЙ—i, si wonaa e goonga. Kono ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e maЙ“Й“e, Й“e nganndaa."
  44,40,"Pellet, ko Г‘alaande Seerndindiro ngon, woni ko Й“e saatinanaa, kamЙ“e fof."
  44,41,"Г‘alnde nde giЙ—o duncanoytaa giЙ—o [mum] hay hu'unde; Й“e wonaani kadi walloyteeЙ“e,"
  44,42,"si wonaa mo Allah yurmaa woo. Pellet, ko KaЕӢko woni pooluЙ—o, jurmotooЙ—o On."
  44,43,"Pellet, lekki Zaqquumi Kini."
  44,44,"ko Гұaametee bakkodinЙ“e Й“een."
  44,45,"A sikkay ko taayinaa ; hino fata ka ndeer deedi."
  44,46,"Wano ngulЙ—am fatirta."
  44,47,"Nanngee mo pooЙ—iron ka hakkunde dulЙ“atnge."
  44,48,"refti njuppon ka hoore makko, lepte patinaaЙ—e Й—een."
  44,49,"MeeЙ—u noon ! Asn [sikkunooЙ—o] ko a poolЙ—o, tedduЙ—o."
  44,50,"Awa ko Й—uum woni kon ko cikkitiЙ—on e mum."
  44,51,"Pellet, gooЕӢЙ—uЙ“e Й“ren ngonii e weerde koolniinde,"
  44,52,"e ndeer gese e Й“ulli,"
  44,53,"heЙ“e Й“oornoo ko Й—aati e ko tekki, hara hiЙ“e peewtondiri."
  44,54,"Ko wano noon. Min ndesini Й“e kadi yaacЙ“e gite."
  44,55,"HiЙ“e nodda toon, kala muuyanteeЙ—i, hara ko Й“e hooliiЙ“e."
  44,56,"ЖҒe meeЙ—ataa toon maayde, si wonaa maayde aranere nden. O daЙ—nda Й“e lepte Jahiimi Й—een."
  44,57,"ko dokkal noon, immorde ka Joomi maa. Awa ko Й—uum woni maloore mawnde ndeen."
  44,58,"Ko Min newiniri nde e Й—amngal maaЙ—a, ko no Й“e mbaajitora."
  44,59,"Habito. KamЙ“e ne ko Й“e habbitiiЙ“e."
  45,1,"Haa, miim."
  45,2,"Jippagol deftere nde, ko immorde ka Allah, pooluЙ—o, Г‘eeГұo O."
  45,3,"Pellet, hino e tagugol kammuuji Й—iin e leydi ndin, Ma'andeeji wonan'de gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“een."
  45,4,"Hino e takgol oon ngol kadi, e kon ko O saaki e ruugayЙ—i, ko Ma'andeeji wonan'de yimЙ“e yananaaЙ“e Й“een."
  45,5,"E luutondirgol jehma e Гұalawma ngol, e kon ko Allah jippiniri ka kammu, immorde e toЙ“o, O wuurnitiri ngo leydi ndin Й“aawo ndi yo'orude, e firlitagol keneeli Й—in, ko Ma'andeeji wonan'de yimЙ“e haqqilooЙ“e Й“en."
  45,6,"ЖҠiin ko Ma'andeeji Allah Й—i Min njanngirante hoore goonga. E ko holЙ—um e yewtere Й“e gooЕӢЙ—inta, Й“aawo [yewtere] Allah nden e Aayeeje makko Й—een?"
  45,7,"Bone woodanii kala penoowo bakkodin'Й—o !"
  45,8,"Mo no nana Aayeeje Allah Й—en hino janngee e dow makko, refti o hedditora e toownitaare, wa si tawii o nanaani Й—e. Awa weltinir mo lepte mu'usuuЙ—e."
  45,9,"Si o anndii goЙ—Й—um e aayeeje Amen Й—een, o jogitora Й—um jalnori. ЖҒeen Й—oon, hino woodani lepte koynooje:"
  45,10,"Jahannama hino caggal maЙ“Й“e. Ko Й“e paggitinoo duncanoytaaЙ“e hay hu'unde, wonaa kon ko Й“e jogitinoo yiЙ—Й“e ko wonaa Allah. Hino woodani Й“e lepte mawЙ—e."
  45,11,"Ndee [deftere]ko peewal. ЖҒeen yedduЙ“e noon aayeeje Joomi maЙ“Й“e Й—en, hino woodani lepte coЙ“Й—e mu'usuuЙ—e."
  45,12,"Ko Alla oon woni ko eeltanta mon maaya ngam laaЙ—e ndoga e hengo e dow yamiroore makko, ngam Й—aЙ“Й“on e Й“ural makko e yaama joo njetton."
  45,13,"O eeltani on ko woni e kammuuji e ka leydi fof, wonii e Й—uum kaawisaaji wonan'de yimЙ“e miijatooЙ“e."
  45,14,"Maakan Й“een goonЙ—inЙ“e yooЙ“e njaafa Й“een Й“e tijjaaki nyalЙ—i Alla ngam O yoЙ“a Й“e yimЙ“e koЙ“e paggittono ko."
  45,15,"Kalo golluЙ—o ko moЖҙЖҙi,ko fii hoore-makko; kala kadi bonnuЙ—o, yantat e makko refti ko ka Joomi maa woni ruttorde mon."
  45,16,"Min tottii banii Israa*iil deftere e ГұeeГұal e annabaagal Min njeЙ—iЙ“e e dagiiЙ—i Min Й“urniЙ“e ko heewi e binnde he."
  45,17,"Min totti dallillaaji Й“annginooji Й“e luuraani si wonah caggal nde ganndal ari e mum en sabu bewre hakkunde maЙ“Й“e pellet Jooma na Гұaawa hakkunde maЙ“Й“e Гұande darnga koЙ“e njeddandiratnoo ko."
  45,18,"Refti min mbaЙ—ma e laawol e yamiroore amen, woto rew belaaЙ—e Й“een Й“e ngannda."
  45,19,"Pellet Й“een Й“e nafataama gaa e Alla hay hu'unde pellet tooГұooЙ“e yogo e mum en ko weldiiЙ“e, Alla woni keeda hulЙ“e Й“e."
  45,20,"O quraana kombo gite e peewal e yurmeende wonan'de yananaaЙ“e Й“e."
  45,21,"Mbele Й“een waЙ—Й“e boneeji na nanndi e gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“e ngolli golle lobbe hoЙ“e fota e nguurndam mum en e maayde maЙ“Й“e bonii koЙ“e Гұaawata."
  45,22,"Alla tagrii kammuuji e leydi goonga ngam kala fittaandu yoЙ“ee kondu fagginoo ko kamЙ“e Й“e tooГұetaake."
  45,23,"Mbele a yiaani oon jaggirЙ—o belaaЙ—e makko deweteeЙ—o Alla majjini mbo e dow ganndal O uddi nanЙ—e makko e Й“ernde makko, o waЙ—i e gite makko hee cuddi ko hombo feewnata oon caggal Alla mate on miictaaka."
  45,24,"He'eferЙ“e mbii Й—um wona si wona nguurndam aduna min maaya min nguura, halkataa min si wona jamaanu, Й“e ngalana Й—uum ganndal Й“e cikkita tan."
  45,25,"Si aayeeje amen Й“annguЙ—e njanngaama e mum en hujja maЙ“Й“e wonata si wona ngaddee baabiraaЙ“e amen si on ngonii gooЕӢЙ—uЙ“e."
  45,26,"Maaku ko alla wuurnata on refti o wara on refti renndina on fa'ade Гұalawma darnga mbo sikke alah e mum, kono ko Й“uri heewde e yimЙ“e ngannda."
  45,27,"Woodanii Alla laamu kammuuji e leydi, Гұande darnga darii Гұande heen meerenteeЙ“e Й“e perta."
  45,28,"HaЙ—a yiya -aan nulaaЙ—a- kala leГұol na gurfanii e koppi mum,kala leГұol na noddiree deftere mum hannde woni ko njoЙ“eteЙ—on ko ngollatnaЙ—on e ndeer aduna."
  45,29,"Ndee ko deftere amen honde wowla goonga, min ngoniina min ceeraani won'de emin njamira nde winndate ko ngollatna Й—on."
  45,30,"Tawi ko Й“een gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“e ngolli golle lobbe O naatnatЙ“e e yurmeende makko, ko Й—uum woni mala Й“anngungal."
  45,31,"Tawi ko Й“een he'efareeЙ“e mbele aayeeje am Й—e njanngetanooke e dow mon mawnikiniЙ—on laatiЙ—on yimЙ“e bonЙ“e."
  45,32,"Si Й“e mbiaama pellet fodoore Alla ko goonga sikke alah heen mbi'on min ngannda ko woni darnga, min cikkiti cikkitagol min ngonaani yananaaЙ“e."
  45,33,"boneeji Й—i Й“e paggitinoo Й—iin feГұana Й“e, ko Й“e njalkitatnoo kon fiiltoo Й“e."
  45,34,"Й“e mbi'ana hannde min njejjita mon hono no njejjitirЙ—on pottal Гұangu mon hannde ngu, ko yiite woni hoЙ—orde mon on ndaГұata walladiiЙ“e."
  45,35,"Й—uum noon ko sabu on njaggarii aayeeje Alla Й—e njalkito nguurndam aduna hoomti on,hannde Й“e njaltata e yiite Й“e nduttataaka aduna Й“e ngolla golle lobbe haa Alla weleeЙ“e."
  45,36,"Woodanii Alla jettooje nder kammuuji e leydi Jom binnde."
  45,37,"Na woodani mbo manngu ndeer kammuuji e leydi ko KaЕӢko woni mbo gooto foolata ГұeeГұЙ—o."
  46,1,"Haa, miim."
  46,2,"Jippagol deftere nden, ko immorde ka Allah, pooluЙ—o, ГұeeГұo on."
  46,3,"Min tagiraali kammuuji Й—in e leydi ndin e ko woni hakkunde majji, si wonaa e goonga e lajala happaangal [fii mum]. YedduЙ“e Й“en ko Й—uurniiЙ“e e ko Й“e ndentiniraa kon."
  46,4,"Maaku: "On nji'ii ko ndewoton kon hara wonaa Allah, kollee Kam ko Й—i tagi e leydi ndiin? Kaa hara hiЙ—i mari geЙ—al e [tagoore] kammuuji Й—iin? Awa ngaddanee lam deftere jippinaande ado ndee Й—oo ma batte ganndal, si wonii ko on gooЕӢЙ—uЙ“e !"."
  46,5,"Ko hommbo Й“uri majjude, wa on dewoowo ko wanaa Allah, ko jaabotaako mo haa Г‘ande Darngal? Hara Й—in [deweteeЙ—i] ko welsindiiЙ—i e dewal majji."
  46,6,"Si yimЙ“e Й“en mooЙ“oyaama [ka Darngal], Й—i ngontanoyat Й“e aГұЙ“e, Й“e ngona e jeddugol ko Й“e ndewaynooЙ—i kon."
  46,7,"Si aayeeje Amen Й“annguЙ—e Й—en janngaama e maЙ“Й“e, yedunooЙ“e goonga Й“en tuma nde arnoo e maЙ“Й“e Й“en mbi'a: "ЖҠuum ko mbilewu Й“anngu ngu"."
  46,8,"Kaa Й“e wi'at woni :"O pekindi nde?" Awa maaku: "Si taw mi pefkndi nde, awa doo on duncantaa lam hu'unde e [lepte] Allah Й—en. Ko KaЕӢko Й“uri anndude oon, tuma nde jumpoton e mayre. O yonii seedee hakkunde am e mon. Ko KaЕӢko woni kaforowo, jurmotooЙ—o On."
  46,9,"Maaku: "Mi wonaa adano e NulaaЙ“e Й“een; mi anndaa kadi ko waЙ—etee mi, maa ko waЙ—eteЙ—on. Mi jokkaa si wonaa ko wahayinaa kon e am; mi laataaki si wonaa jeertinoowo Й“anngina"."
  46,10,"Maaku: "Yeetee kam, si tawii le konde iwrunde ka Allah, njedduЙ—on Й—um, seedotooЙ—o e Й“iЙ—Й“e Israa'ila Й“en ceedii e [sellugol] Й—um, o gooЕӢЙ—ini, onon kan townitiЙ—on...Pellet, Allah feewnata yimЙ“e tooГұooЙ“e Й“een."
  46,11,"YedduЙ“e Й“en wi'ani gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“en: "Si tawno Й—uum ko moЖҙЖҙere, Й“een (waasuЙ“e) adototaako men e mum". Nde wonunoo Й“e fewnoraani nde, ma Й“e mbi'u: "Ndee ko fenaande neeЙ“unde!"."
  46,12,"Hino aditiinde, deftere Muusaa nden, Й—owornde e yurmeende. Ndee Й—oo kadi, ko deftere gooЕӢЙ—inir- nde [Й—eya defte] e Й—emngal aarabu, fii yo jeertinir (nde) tooГұooЙ“e Й“en e weltinirnde moЖҙЖҙinooЙ“e Й“een."
  46,13,"Pellet, wi'uЙ“e Й“een: "Ko Allah woni Joomi amen", refti Й“e tabiti (e gooЕӢЙ—inal), kulol alanaa Й“een, wonaa kamЙ“e cunoytoo."
  46,14,"Ko Й“een ngoni yimЙ“e Aljanna Й“een duumotooЙ“e ton, njoЙ“di ko Й“e ngollatnoo kon."
  46,15,"Min njamirii neЙ—Й—aЕӢke on moЖҙЖҙagol e jibimЙ“e mo Й“en: Jiido makko soworike mo saЙ—teende, o njibiniri mo kadi saЙ—teende; soweede mo e enteede mo ko lebbi cappanЙ—e tati, haa ka o si o yottike cagatalaaku makku nguun o timminii duuЙ“i cappanЙ—e nayi, o wi'a: "Joomi, longinam jettugol neema Ma mo neeminirЙ—aa mi miin e jibimЙ“e kam, e nde mi ngollata moЖҙЖҙuЙ—i weltinayЙ—e Ma, moЖҙЖҙinanaa kam geГұngol am ngol. Mi tuubanii Ma, ko mi jiyaaЙ—o e jebbiliiЙ“e Й“een"."
  46,16,"Ko Й“een ngoni Й“e Min njaЙ“anta ko Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude e ko Й“e ngolli, Min njawtana Й“e bonЙ—i maЙ“Й“e, (Й“e jeyaama) e yimЙ“e Aljanna Й“en. ЖҠuum ko fodoore goonga nde Й“e podanoo."
  46,17,"Kala noon bi'anЙ—o jipnaaЙ“e mum Й“een: "Uf mo'on ! Kere on poday kam immintineede hara le gooЕӢЙ—ii mofte yawtiino ado kam?" Hara Й“en Й—iЙ—o no faabtinora Allah [wiide mo]: "Ee bone maa, GooЕӢЙ—in ! Pellet, fodooree Allah nde ko goonga". O wi'a: "ЖҠuum wonaani, si wonaa tinndi adinooЙ“e Й“en"."
  46,18,"Ko Й“een woni Й“e Konngol ngol jojji e mum, (Й“e jiyaama) e mofte yawtunooЙ—e ado maЙ“Й“e, immorde e jinna e yimЙ“e. Pellet, Й“e laatino sooyЙ“e."
  46,19,"Hino woodani kala [fedde e maЙ“Й“e]: darjaaji e ko Й“e ngolli ko, fii no O hunnirana Й“e njoЙ“di golle maЙ“Й“e Й—een; e hoore Й“e tooГұetaake."
  46,20,"Г‘ande he'eferЙ“e Й“een weeЙ“itoytee e Yiite ngeen (Й“e mbi'anee): "On naЙ“ii moЖҙЖҙi mon Й—in ka nguurndam mon aduna, ndakmitorЙ—on Й—i. Hannde noon, on njoЙ“itirte lepte koynooje, sabu ko townitoraynoЙ—on ko ka hoore leydi, ko aldaa e goonga, e ko ngollatnoЙ—on noЙ—on kon faasiqaaku"."
  46,21,"JaЕӢto fii musiЙ—Й“e Aadi (Huudi) Й“een, nde o jertinirnoo yimЙ“e makko Й“en aynde nden - gooЕӢЙ—ii hari jeertinooji yawtiino ye'eso makko e Й“aawo makko - won'de: "Wota on rew si wonaa Allah. Miin miЙ—o hulani on lepte Гұalaande mawnde"."
  46,22,"ЖҒe mbi'i: "E a aru min fii yo a firliaa min e dewetee- Й—i amen Й—iin? Awa addan min ko kammbiranЙ—aa min kon, si wonii ko a jiyaaЙ—o e gooЙ“e Й“een"."
  46,23,"O maaki: "Ganndal ngal ko ka Allah woni. Miin mi yottinanat on tun woni, ko mi nulaa kon. Ko woni tun mi yi'ii ko on yimЙ“e majjaaЙ“e"."
  46,24,"Nde Й“e nji'unoo ruulde honde weeЙ“itii fewtiri ayЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en, Й“e mbi'i: "Ndee ko duulere toЙ“atnde e men". Ko nden kan woni ! ko kawjirnoЙ—on kon : ko henndu, ndu lepte mu'usuuЙ—e woni e mum."
  46,25,"hindu muncira kala hu'unde, yamiroore Joomi mayru". ЖҒe mbaЙ—tini, tawi yi'etaake si wonaa koЙ—ooli maЙ“Й“e Й—in. Ko wano nii Min njoЙ“itirta yimЙ“e bonnooЙ“e Й“en."
  46,26,"GooЕӢЙ—ii Min njeЙ—iino Й“e, e ko ko Min njeЙ—aali on e mum. Min mbaЙ—ani Й“e nanЙ—e, e ji'iЙ—e e Й“erЙ—e. Kono Й—een nanЙ—e maЙ“Й“e, e j'iiЙ—e maЙ“Й“e e Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e (fof) duncanaani Й“e goЙ—Й—um, tawde Й“e laatino yeddooЙ“e aayeeje Allah Й—en. Ko Й“e njalkitatnoo ko jippii e maЙ“Й“e."
  46,27,"GooЕӢЙ—ii Min kalkiino ca'e wonnooЙ“e sera mon; Min pirlitiri aayeeje Й—een, mbelajo'o Й“e nduttoto."
  46,28,"Ko haЙ—no Й—in Й—i Й“e njogitornoo deweteeЙ—i Й“aЙ—tinorЙ—i ga Allah, faaboo Й“e? Tigi on, Й—iin majjirii Й“e; ko Й—um wonnoo fenaande maЙ“Й“e e ko Й“e pekindotonoo. Mo"
  46,29,"JaЕӢto tuma nde Min imminnoo fedde jinna e maaЙ—a, hiЙ—i heЙ—oo Alqur'aana. Nde Й—i tawanoo Й—um, Й—i mbi'i: "HeЙ—ee"...Nde [janngin kin] timmunoo, Й—i huccitiri ka yimЙ“e majji, jeertinooji."
  46,30,"ЖҠi mbi'i: "eey mon yo mbatu amen, min nanii deftere jippinaande Й“aawo Muusaa, goonginnde Й—en adiiЙ—e nde. Hinde feewna e goonga e laawol Pocciingol."
  46,31,"Eey mon yo mbatu amen, nootee noddoowo e Allah on, ngooЕӢЙ—inon mo. [On tuma] O haforanat on bakkatuuji Й—iin, O daЙ—nda on lepte mu'usuuЙ—e."
  46,32,"Kala mo nootaake noddoowo e Allah on, o wonaa laawotooЙ—o ka leydi, o alaa kadi giЙ—o ga makko. Ko Й“en ngoni e ndeer majjere Й“anngunde"."
  46,33,"E Й“ee nji'aani won'de ko Allah tagi kammuuji Й—iin e leydi ndin, O ronkiraani tagugol Й—i, won'de ko O kattanЙ—o wuurnitugol maayЙ“e Й“en? Ko non woniri. Pellet, ko O kaЙ—tanЙ—o kala hu'unde."
  46,34,"Г‘ande he'eferЙ“e Й“een weeЙ“itoytee e Yiite ngen, [Й“e mbi'anee]: "Wonaa goonga nii?" ЖҒe mbi'a : "Ko non woniri! Min ngoЙ—ondirii Joomi amen!". O Daala : "Awa meeЙ—iree non lepte Й—een, sabu ko njeddiratnoЙ—on"."
  46,35,"MuГұГұor muГұal joomiraaЙ“e pellital Й“een ka NulaaЙ“e; wota a hawjan Й“e. Г‘ande Й“e nji'oyta ko Й“e kammbiranaa kon, Й“e mba'oyat wa si Й“e ГұiiЙ“aano [ka leydi] si wonaa dumunna-hun Гұalawma. ЖҠun ko yottinal. Ko homЙ“e halketee si wonaa yimЙ“e faasiqiiЙ“e Й“een?"
  47,1,"ЖҒeen yedduЙ“e Й“e falii laawol Allah ngol, O bonnii golle maЙ“Й“e Й—een."
  47,2,"GooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“en Й“e ngolli golle moЖҙЖҙe, Й“e ngooЕӢЙ—ini ko jippinaa kon e Muhammad - on goonga immorЙ—o e Joomi maЙ“Й“e - O yawtanii Й“e bonЙ—i maЙ“Й“e Й—in, O moЖҙЖҙinii fiyaaku maЙ“Й“e oon."
  47,3,"Ko waЙ—i Й—uum, ko tawde yedduЙ“e Й“en njokkii mehre nden, gooЕӢЙ—iinЙ“e Й“en kan njokki goonga kan immorde e Joomi maЙ“Й“e on. Ko wano nii Allah fiyiranta yimЙ“e Й“en yeru maЙ“Й“e Й—en."
  47,4,"Si on kawri e yedduЙ“e Й“een (ka hare), ko soppugol daaЙ—e Й—een. Haa si on Й—uЙ—Й—inii bargol Й“e, kaЙ“Й“on koyЙ—e Й—en. Ko si on moЖҙЖҙora e maЙ“Й“e ngaccitugol Й“e Й“aawo Й—uum, maa si ko soktiigu, haa hare ndeen wallina jogaaji mayre. Ko non Гұaawiraa, si Allah no muuyunoo, O wallitotono on e maЙ“Й“e, ko woni tan, ko no O jarribora yoga mon e dow yoga. WaraaЙ“e fii Allah Й“een, pellet, O yeebataa golle maЙ“Й“e Й—een."
  47,5,"Arma O feewna Й“e, O moЖҙЖҙina fiyaaku maЙ“Й“e,"
  47,6,"O naatnya Й“e Aljanna, mo O anndini Й“e fii mum."
  47,7,"Eey mon yo gooЕӢЙ—iinЙ“e, si on ngonii wallooЙ“e fii Allah, O wallat on, O tabintina teppe mon Й—en."
  47,8,"YedduЙ“e Й“ee kan, halkaare woodanii Й“e, O majjinii kadi golle maЙ“Й“e Й—een."
  47,9,"ЖҠuum le ko tawde Й“e aГұii ko Allah jippini kon, O bonni golle maЙ“Й“e Й—een."
  47,10,"E Й“ee njiilaaki e leydi ndin, Й“e teskoo ko honno battane adinooЙ“e Й“een wa'unoo? Allah halkuno fii maЙ“Й“e. sugu mum kadi hino woodani yedduЙ“e Й“een."
  47,11,"Ko waЙ—i Й—um, ko tawde ko Allah woni giЙ—o gooЕӢЙ—iinЙ“e Й“een; hara non yedduЙ“e Й“en, giЙ—o (woo) alanaa Й“e."
  47,12,"Pellet, Allah naatnoyat gooЕӢЙ—iinЙ“e ngolli moЖҙЖҙuЙ—i Й“en, Aljannaaji Й—i canЙ—i ilata ley (kuЙ“eeje) majje. YedduЙ“e Й“een kan, heЙ“e ndakmitoo, Й“e Гұaamira wano neemoraaЙ—i Й—iin Гұaamirta; hara noon ko Yiite nge woni jaaЖҙorde maЙ“Й“e."
  47,13,"ЖҠuuЙ—ii e ca'e, Й“urnooЙ“e tiiЙ—ude semmbe, e dii ndeen saare maa raЙ—iinde ma, Й“e Moen kalki, ballo alanaa Й“e."
  47,14,"Kere ko on gonЙ—o e Й“anngannduyee immorde ka Joomi mum, wa'i wa Й“een cuЙ—inanaaЙ“e kuuЙ—e mun bonЙ—e Й—en, Й“e jokki beleeЙ—e maЙ“Й“e?"
  47,15,"Ko woni sifa Aljanna podaaЙ—o on gooЕӢЙ—uЙ“e Й“een: ina toon canЙ—i ndiyam Й—i dakamme mum waylaaki, e caatli Й“ira Й—i waylataa dakamme mum, e caatli konnjam mbelayЙ—am yarooЙ“e, e caatlii njuuri laЙ“Й“inaandi. Hino woodani Й“e kadi ton: kala dimЙ“e, e haforaneede immorde e Joomi maЙ“Й“e. [ЖҒeen wa'oyay] wa luttinoyteeeЙ“e Й“en ka Yiite, Й“e njarnee ndiyam fatayЙ—am, Й—am taЖҙa tekteki maЙ“Й“e Й—in?"
  47,16,"Hino e maЙ“Й“e heЙ—itotooЙ“e ma. Kono ko haa si Й“e yaltii ka maaЙ—a, Й“e wi'ana okkaaЙ“e ganndal Й“een: "Ko holЙ—um dee, o wi'unoo naanen?" Ko Й“en woni Й“e Allah noti e Й“erЙ—e mum Й—een, Й“e njokki mbeleeЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—een."
  47,17,"FeewuЙ“e Й“een kan, O Й“eydu Й“e peewal O okkiЙ“e gooЕӢniЙ—al maЙ“Й“e."
  47,18,"Hara Й“ee no kabbbii si wonaa Darngal ngal nde ardata Й“e e juhal? GooЕӢЙ—ii le Ma'andeeji maggal arii. Ko holno Й“e mbaajitoroyta, si ngal ardanii Й“e (juhal)?"
  47,19,"Awa anndu pellet, deweteeЙ—o alaa si wonaa Allah, imsinanoЙ—aa bakkati maa Й—in, e gooЕӢЙ—iinЙ“e worЙ“e Й“een e gooЕӢЙ—iinЙ“e rewЙ“e Й“en. Allah no anndi Гұallirde mon e hiirirde mon."
  47,20,"GooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“en hino mbi'a: "Hara non cortewol (simoore) jippotono!" Si tawii le cortewol ГұeГұaangol jippinaama, fii hare jaЕӢtaama e maggol, a tinay Й“en Й“e Гұawu woni e Й“erЙ—e mum hino ndaare, ndaarЙ—e mo maayde faЙ—Й—ini. Ko haanannoo Й“e,"
  47,21,"ko Й—oftagol e konngol moЖҙЖҙol. Si fiyaaku o fellitii, Й“e ngooЕӢЙ—inno Allah, ko Й—uum Й“uratnoo moЖҙЖҙannde Й“e."
  47,22,"E on tamЖҙinaaki, si wonii on Й—uurnima nde mbonnoton e leydi ndin, taЖҙon enЙ—amaaji mon?"
  47,23,"Ko Й“een ngoni Й“e Allah huЙ—i Й“een, O fa'aЙ—ini Й“e, O wumini giiЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—een."
  47,24,"E Й“ee tasktaako Alqur'aana, ka ko cokirЙ—e woni woni e Й“erЙ—e mum en?"
  47,25,"Pellet, Й“een ruttorЙ“e Й“abbe mum Й“aawo nde peewal ngal Й“anngannoo Й“e, ko seytaane cuЙ—inani Й“e, o hodi Й“e."
  47,26,"Ko tawde Й“e mbi'anii Й“een aГұuЙ“e ko Allah jippini kon: "Min Й—oftoto on e yoga e piiji". Allah non no anndi gunndooji maЙ“Й“e Й—iin."
  47,27,"Ko honno (Й“ee mba'oyta) tuma nde Malaa'ika'en timmini fii maЙ“Й“e, hara hiЙ“e bantoo j'eece maЙ“Й“e e dote maЙ“Й“e?"
  47,28,"Ko tawde ko Й“e njokkii ko tikkinta Allah, Й“e aГұii welayЙ—i Mo Й—iin, O bonni fii golle maЙ“Й“e Й—een."
  47,29,"Kaa Й“een Й“e Гұawu woni e Й“erЙ—e mum sikuu won'de Allah yaltintaa ngaynguuji maЙ“Й“e?"
  47,30,"Sinno Min kaajuno, Min kolleteno Й“e. Ganndiraa Й“e Ma'andeeji maЙ“Й“e Й—iin; ko pellet, a nganndiratno Й“e ka konngol belngol. Allah non hino anndi golle mon Й—een."
  47,31,"Ma Min njarribo on, haa Min ngannda tiiЙ—niiЙ“e Й“en e mon, e muГұГұiiЙ“e Й“een. Min njarriboo kadi kabaruuji mon."
  47,32,"Pellet, yedduЙ“e Й“een Й“e paddi laawol Allah ngol, Й“e lunndii NulaaЙ—o on Й“aawo nde peewal ngal Й“anngannde Й“e, Й“een lorrataa Allah hay hu'unde. Ma O bonnu fii golle maЙ“Й“e Й—een."
  47,33,"Eey mon yo gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e! Й—oftee Allah, Й—oftoЙ—on NulaaЙ—o on, wata on mbonnu golle mon Й—een."
  47,34,"Pellet, Й“een yedduЙ“e Й“e sakkii e laawol Allah ngol, hooti Й“e maayi ko Й“e he'eferЙ“e, Allah haforanoytaa Й“e."
  47,35,"Wota on lo'inkino, noddon e beldal, ko onon woni fooluЙ“e Й“een, Allah no wonndi e mon, O ustantaa on njoЙ“di golle mon Й—een."
  47,36,"Ganndee nguurndam aduna ko fijindaaru e mbeleeЙ—e tan; hara le si on ngooЕӢЙ—iii, on kulii [Allah], O yeЙ—ay on njoЙ“di mon ndiin, o lamndotaako on jawle mon Й—een."
  47,37,"Si O aru laЙ“ndaade on fii majje, haa O duГұii on (e mum), nguddon, O feГұГұina noon konnaagu mon ngun."
  47,38,"Hey mon onon Й—oo, hoЙ—on noddee e nafqugol fii laawol Allah ngol. Hino e mo'on wuddatЙ“e. Kala non gudduЙ—o, haray ko hoore-makko o wuddani. Ko Allah woni Galo On, onon ngoni wa'asuЙ“e Й“een. Si on nduЕӢtii, O waЙ—titira on woЙ“Й“e goo, hara non Й“een mba'ataa wano mon."
  48,1,"Min ngudditanii ma uddital Й“anngungal,"
  48,2,"fii no Allah yaafoma ko ngardinЙ—aa e bakkaat, e ko sakkitii, e fii no O timminira neema makko on e maaЙ—a, O feewne e laawol po'occiingol."
  48,3,"e no Allah wallirma ballal tiiЙ—ngal."
  48,4,"Ko KaЕӢko woni jippinЙ—o deeЖҙere nden e Й“erЙ—e gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“en, fii no Й“e Й“eydora gooЕӢЙ—inal e dow gooЕӢЙ—inal maЙ“Й“e ngal. Ko Allah woodani koneeji kammuuji Й—iin e leydi ndin; Allah siforii won'de gannduЙ—o, Г‘eeГұЙ—o,"
  48,5,"e fii no O naadira gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e worЙ“e Й“en e gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e rewЙ“e Й“en, Aljannaaji Й—i canЙ—i ilata ley mum, ko Й“Й—e duumotooЙ“e e majji, e no O montira-naЙ“e banЙ—i maЙ“Й“e Й—in. ЖҠuum wonii ka Allah, malal mawnungal."
  48,6,"E no O leptira naafiqiiЙ“e worЙ“e Й“een e naafiqiiЙ“e rewЙ“e Й“een, e sirkooЙ“e worЙ“e Й“en e sirkooЙ“e rewЙ“e Й“en, sikkooЙ“e Allah sikke bonЙ—e. Yiiloonde bonЙ—i ngonii e dow maЙ“Й“e. Allah tikkaniiЙ“e kadi, O huЙ—ii Й“e, O hebilanii Й“e Jahannama. Nge bonii ruttorde !"
  48,7,"Ko Allah woodani konuuji kammuuli Й—iin e leydi ndin. Allah siforii won'de 'oolЙ—o, Г‘eeГұЙ—o."
  48,8,"Min nulirii ma seedotooЙ—o, wewlinoowo, e jeertinoowo,"
  48,9,"fii no gooЕӢЙ—iniron Allah e NulaaЙ—o makko on, mawninon mo, teddinon mo, subbunhinanoЙ—on mo bimmbi e kiikiiЙ—e."
  48,10,"Pellet, Й“een wonЙ“e ahodude e maaЙ—a, anndu ko Allah Й“e woni e ahodude. Junngo Allah ngon no dow juuЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en. Kala non pirtuЙ—o, haray ko hoore makko o firtani; kala kadi hunnuЙ—o ko o ahodi kon e Allah, nde o okkata mo njoЙ“di mawnundi."
  48,11,"Aray nde tultuЙ“e jiyaaЙ“e e yimЙ“e ladde Й“en mbi'ane: "Jawle amen Й—een e Й“eynguureeji amen Й—in sokolinii min. Insinano min". HiЙ“e wowlira Й—emЙ—e maЙ“Й“e, ko alaa e Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e. Maaku: "Ko hommbo waawani on ka Allah, si O faandanike on lorra maa hara O faandani on nafa? Wurin Allah siforiino won'de kumpitiiЙ—o ko mgollaynoЙ—on kon."
  48,12,"Wurin on cikkuno NulaaЙ—o on e gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“en ngartataano fes ka Й“eynguureeji maЙ“Й“e. ЖҠuum siЙ—inaa e Й“erЙ—e mon; cikkuЙ—on sikke bonЙ—e, laatiЙ—on yimЙ“e halkaaЙ“e."
  48,13,"Kala dee mo gooЕӢЙ—inaani Allah e NulaaЙ—o makko on, haray MoЙ—en keblani yedduЙ“e Й“een (Yiite) dulbaynge."
  48,14,"Ko Allah heeranii laamagol kammuuji Й—iin e leydi ndiin. Himo haforana mo o muuyani, o lepta mo o muuyani. Allah siforii won'de kaforoowo, jurmotooЙ—o."
  48,15,"Aray nde luttuЙ“e Й“en mbi'a, tuma fokkitanoyton henndagol konu-hoyri ndin: "ngaccee min njokka on". HiЙ“e faalaa waЙ—titugol daalol Allah ngol. Maaku: "On njokkataa min fes. Ko wano mon nii Allah daalirnoo oya tuma". Ma Й“e mbi'u: "On aГұanat min tun woni". Tigi on, Й“e faamataano si wonaa seeЙ—a."
  48,16,"Maakan tultuЙ“e Й“en e yimЙ“e ladde Й“een: "Arma nde noddeteЙ—on e yimЙ“e joomiraaЙ“e doole tiiЙ—uЙ“e. HoЙ“on Й“e maaЙ—um Й“e silma. Si on Й—oftike, Allah okkat on mbarjaari moЖҙЖҙundi; si on nduЕӢtii ii no huccitirnoЙ—on oya tuma, O leptira lepte mu'usuuЙ—e"."
  48,17,"Bakkaatu fawaaki e hoore Й“umЙ—o on, wonaa e laЖҙoowo on wonaa kadi e nawnuЙ—on bakkaatu fawii. Kala Й—oftiiЙ—o Allah e NulaaЙ—o makko on, O naadoyay mo Aljannaaji Й—i canЙ—i ilata senngo ley mum. Kala kadi Й—uurniiЙ—o, O leptiray mo lepte mu'usuuЙ—e."
  48,18,"GooЕӢЙ—ii Allah welano gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“en, tuma Й“e ahondiraynoo e maaЙ—a ka ley lekki kin. O anndi ko woni kon ka Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e, O jippini deeЖҙere nden e maЙ“Й“e, O warjoriiЙ“e uddital Й“adiingal,"
  48,19,"e konu-heyri Й—uuЙ—undi ndi Й“e keЙ“Й“itotoo. Allah siforii won'de poolЙ—o, Г‘eeГұЙ—o."
  48,20,"Allah fodii on konu-heyri Й—uuЙ—undi ndi keЙ“Й“itoЙ—on, O yaccinani on ndii Й—oo, o suri juuЙ—e yimЙ“e Й“een e mo'on, fii yo wonu Ma'ande wonan'de gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“en, O fewnira on laawol Pocciingol."
  48,21,"E woЙ—ndi goo ndi on haЙ—tanaali taho, Allah kan no huЙ“indii ndi. Allah siforii won'de kaЙ—tanЙ—o kala hu'unde."
  48,22,"Hay si yedduЙ“e Й“een haЙ“iino on, Й“e huccintinayno Й“abbe maЙ“Й“e Й—en, refti Й“e keЙ“ataano giЙ—o wonaa ballao."
  48,23,"ЖҠuum ko sunna Alla peЖҙЖҙunooЙ—o ko adii. A heЙ“antaa laawol Alla ngol, mbattiigu."
  48,24,"Ko KaЕӢko woni curanЙ—o on juuЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en e mo'on, e curЙ—o juuЙ—e mon Й—en e maЙ“Й“e, ka aynde Makka, Й“aawo O foolni on e maЙ“Й“e. Allah siforii won'de deenЙ—o ko ngolloton kon."
  48,25,"Ko Й“een ngoni ko jeddi, Й“e paddii on e Juurlirde Hormorde ndeen, [Й“e haЙ—i] neldaari ndin nde ndi yottotoo nokku mayri. Si wonaano sabu worЙ“e gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e e rewЙ“e gooЕӢЙ—innЙ“e Й“e on nganndataano haa kaЙ“on Й“e, bakkaatu heЙ“a on e fee maЙ“Й“e, ko aldaa e ganndugol... fii yo Allah naatnu e yurmeende makko nden, on mo O muuyani. Si Й“e seetndondir-no [e gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“en], ko pellet, Min leptirayno yedduЙ“e Й“en e maЙ“Й“e, lepte mu'usuuЙ—e."
  48,26,"Tuma nde Й“eya yedduЙ“e mbaЙ—noo ka Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e jinngo, jinngo majjiyaЕӢkooЙ“e...Allah jippini deeЖҙere makko nden e dow NulaaЙ—o makko on e gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“en, O fawi Й“e konngol gooЕӢЙ—al, Й“e woni Й“urЙ“e jojjude e hanndude e maggol. Allah siforii ganndugol kala hu'unde."
  48,27,"GooЕӢЙ—ii Allah goonginiranii NulaaЙ—o makko on, koyЙ—ol ngol e hoore goonga : Ko maa naaton e juulirde Hormorde ndeen si Allah muuyii, hara ko on hooliiЙ“e, femmbuЙ“e ko*e mon maa Й—uytuЙ“e (cukuli), on hulataa. Himo anndi ko on nganndaa. O waЙ—i ko wonaa ngol (naatugol makko) Й—on, uddital Й“adiingal."
  48,28,"Ko KaЕӢko woni NulirЙ—o NulaaЙ—o makko on peewal e diina goonga, fii yo o fawaka ka e hoore kala diina. Allah yonii seedee."
  48,29,"Muhammdu ko NulaaЙ—o Allah. Won'Й—uЙ“e e makko Й“een ko ГұaaЙ—uЙ“e e yedduЙ“e Й“een, yurmondirЙ“e hakkunde maЙ“Й“e. A yi'at Й“e hiЙ“e ruЖҙЖҙa, hiЙ“e cujja, hiЙ“e Й—aЙ“Й“ira Allah Й“ural e welayee. Ma'andeeji maЙ“Й“e Й—in no ka j'eece maЙ“Й“e batte cujjugol ngol. Ko Й—uum woni ko Й“e ciforaa ka Tawreeta. No Й“e ciforaa ka Linjiila kan, ko wano remuru yaltingu puЙ—i mayru, ngu Й“anngini Й—i, Й—i tekki, Й—i fotondiri e binndeeje majji, hara Й—uum no haawna remooЙ“e, fii no [Allah] tikkinira Й“e yedduЙ“e Й“en. Allah fodii e maЙ“Й“e Й“en gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“e ngolli moЖҙЖҙuЙ—i Й—in, haforanal e njoЙ“di mawnundi."
  49,1,"Eey mon yo Й“en gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e ! wota on adito ye'eso Allah e NulaaЙ—o makko on. Hulee Allah. Pellet, Allah ko Nanoowo, Ji'oowo."
  49,2,"Eey mon yo Й“en gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e ! wota on toownu hitooji mon e dow hito Annabaajo on, wota on ewnor mo kadi konngol, wano no yoga mon ewnorta yoga, sakko golle mon Й—en mbonata, hara on so'aa-anndude."
  49,3,"Pellet, Й“een joltinooЙ“e hotooji maЙ“Й“e Й—in ka NulaaЙ—o Allah on, ko Й“en ngoni Й“e Alla jarabii Й“erЙ—e mum Й—en gooЕӢЙ—al. Hino woodani Й“e haforanal e njoЙ“di mawndi."
  49,4,"Pellet, Й“een Й“e no noddire ka Й“aawo cuuЙ—i, ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e maЙ“Й“e, wonaa haqqilooЙ“e."
  49,5,"Sinno Й“e muГұГұino haa njaltaa e maЙ“Й“e, ko Й—uum Й“uraynoo moЖҙЖҙannde Й“e. Allah ko kaforoowo, jurmotooЙ—o."
  49,6,"Eey mon yo Й“en gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e ! Si faasiqiijo ardanii on e kumpital, tefee fii wota on keЙ“or e yimЙ“e sabu majjeede, ngonton nimsuЙ“e e kon ko mbaЙ—Й—Й—on."
  49,7,"Nganndee won'de NulaaЙ—o Allah on hino hakkunde mon. Si o tewtino on e ko Й—uuЙ—i e fiyakuuji, on tampayno. Kono Allah yiЙ—ini on gooЕӢЙ—inal, O suЙ—ini ngal e Й“erЙ—e mon; O aГұini on ke'eferaaku, e faasiqaaku e jeddi. Ko Й“een ngoni feewЙ“e Й“en,"
  49,8,"Й—uum ko Й“ural immorde ka Allah e neema. Allah ko gannduЙ—o, Г‘eeГұЙ—o."
  49,9,"Si peЙ—le Й—iЙ—i e gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“en haЙ“ii, moЖҙЖҙintinee hakkunde maЙ“Й“e. Si fedde goo bewii e hoore ndeya, ko kaЙ“ugol won'de e bewude nden, haa nde ruttoo e yamiroore Allah nden. Si nde ruttike, moЖҙЖҙintiniree hakkunde maЙ“Й“e nunЙ—al. NunЙ—ee, tawde pellet, Allah no yiЙ—i nuunЙ—ooЙ“e Й“een."
  49,10,"Nganndee gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“en ko jeyduЙ“e. Haray moЖҙЖҙinee hakkunde jeydal mon ngal, kulon Allah, mbelajo'o on njurminte."
  49,11,"Eey mon yo Й“en gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e ! Wota yimЙ“e jalnor yimЙ“e : hino gasa hara Й“en (jalaaЙ“e) hino Й“uri Й“e moЖҙЖҙude. Wanaa rewЙ“e ngoni ko jalnorta rewЙ“e : hino gasa hara Й“een no Й“uri Й“e moЖҙЖҙude. Wata on aybidnir ko'e-mon, wota on bugondir jammooje (bonЙ—e). Innde faasiqaaku nden bonii Й“aawo nde gooЕӢЙ—inal nden. Kala mo tuubaali, ko Й“een ngoni tooГұuЙ“e Й“en."
  49,12,"Eey mon yo Й“en gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e ! WoЙ—Й—itee e ko Й—uuЙ—i e sikke. Pellet, yoga e sikke ko bakkaatu. Wota on wiЙ—ondir, wata yoga mon Гұo'u yoga. Hara gooto e mo'on njiЙ—ay Гұaamugol teewu musiЙ—Й—o mum maayЙ—o? HiЙ—on aГұi Й—um. Kulee Allah. Pellet, Allah ko JaЙ“oowo tuubuubuyee, jurmotooЙ—o."
  49,13,"Eey mon yo yimЙ“e ! Min tagiriii on immorde e gorel e deyel, Min mbaЙ—iri on leЖҙЖҙi e gori, fii yo on anndindir. Pellet, Й“urЙ“e teddude e mon Й“en ka Allah, ko Й“urЙ“e gooЕӢЙ—ude Й“en e mon. Pellet, Allah ko gannduЙ—o, kumpitiiЙ—o."
  49,14,"YimЙ“e ladde Й“en mbi'i: "Min ngooЕӢЙ—inii". Maaku: "On ngooЕӢЙ—inaani taho. Mbii'ee kan : Min silmii. GooЕӢЙ—inal ngal naataali taho ka Й“erЙ—e mon. Si on Й—oftike Allah e NulaaЙ—o makko on, O Й—uytantaa on hu'unde e golle mon Й—een". Pellet, Allah ko kaforoowo, jurmotooЙ—o."
  49,15,"GooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e (tigi) Й“een, ko Й“en gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Allah e NulaaЙ—o makko on, refti Й“e cikkitaaki, Й“e tiiЙ—nori kadi jawle e pittaali maЙ“Й“e Й—in fii laawol Allah ngol. Ko Й“en ngoni gooЕӢЙ—Й“e Й“en."
  49,16,"Maaku: "Kere on nganndinay Allah diina mon kan, hara non Allah no anndi kala ko woni kammuuji e ka leydi?" Allah ko ganduЙ—o kala hu'unde."
  49,17,"HiЙ“e mbaj Ma fii Й“e silmii. Maaku: "Wata on mbajitam silmugol mon. Si ko woni, ko Allah wajitata on fii O feewnirii on e gooЕӢЙ—inal, si wonii ko on gooЕӢЙ—uЙ“e"."
  49,18,"Pellet, Allah no anndi wirniiЙ—i kammuuji Й—iin e leydi ndin. Allah ko deenЙ—o ko ngolloton kon."
  50,1,"Qaaf. Mi wooЙ—ndirii Alqur'aanaare teddunde ndeen!"
  50,2,"Si ko woni, Й“e ЕӢalЙ—u ko tawi kon jeertinoowo arii Й“e iwЙ—o e maЙ“Й“e ; he'eferЙ“e Й“en mbi'i: "ЖҠuum Й—oo ko hu'unde haawniinde."
  50,3,"Kere si min maayii, min ngoontii mbulmbuldi...? ЖҠuum Й—on ko duttitagol goЙ—Й—ungol noon !""
  50,4,"GooЕӢЙ—ii miЙ—en nganndi ko leydi ndin Гұaamata kon e maЙ“Й“e ; hino ka Amen gaa deftere reennde."
  50,5,"Si ko woni, Й“e njeddu goonga kan tuma nde ka arnoo e maЙ“Й“e, hiЙ“e e ndeer fiyaaku jilЙ“uЙ—o."
  50,6,"E Й“ee ndaaraani kammu ngun dow maЙ“Й“e, ko honno Min mahiri ngun Min cuЙ—ini ngu ; hara perЙ—i alanaa ngu?"
  50,7,"Leydi ndin kadi, Min mbeerti ndi Min mberlii e mayri pelle, Min puЙ—ini e mayri kala nooneeji [puЙ—i] gooЙ—uЙ—i."
  50,8,"fii tasakuyee e waaju wonan'de kala jiyaaЙ—o duttotooЙ—o."
  50,9,"Min njippini kadi ndiyam mbarkinaaЙ—am ummaade ka kammu, Min puЙ—iniri Й—am gese e gabbe coГұeteeЙ—e."
  50,10,"e leЙ—Й—e tamaro juutЙ—e gon'dude e piindi fawondirndi,"
  50,11,"ko arsike jeyaaЙ“e Й“en. Min nguurnitiri Й—am kadi leydi yoorundi. Awa ko noon woni fii ummital ngal."
  50,12,"Ado maЙ“Й“e, yimЙ“e nuuhu Й“en, e yimЙ“e ЖҒunndu Й“een e Samuuda'en [fof] f Njedduno,"
  50,13,"e 'Aadi'en, e Fir'awna e musiЙ—Й“e Luutu Й“een."
  50,14,"e yimЙ“e fitaare nden, e yimЙ“e Tubba' Й“een. Kala maЙ“Й“e jedЙ—uno NulaaЙ“e Й“een, kammbaa am on jojji."
  50,15,"Kere Min ndoЕӢkuno fii tagoore ado nde? Ko woni kamЙ“e, hiЙ“e e jiЙ“aare fii tagiteede laawol kesol."
  50,16,"GooЕӢЙ—ii Min tagii neЙ—Й—aЕӢke on, MeЙ—en nganndi ko woЕӢkii makko kin sowinsinirta mo. Ko Minen Й“uri Й“adaade mo e dii Й—aЙ—ol (makko) daande ngol."
  50,17,"tuma nde jaЙ“Й“oytooЙ“e Й“een Й—iЙ—o jaЙ“Й“oroytoo [golle makko Й—een] Гұaamo e nano, hara hiЙ“e njooЙ—ii."
  50,18,"O wowlataa konngol, si wonaa hino takko makko binndoowo tawaaЙ—o."
  50,19,"ЖҠeЙ—Й—ere maayde nden ardi e goonga : "Ko Й—uum wonnnoo ko ndogaynoЙ—aa"."
  50,20,"Wuttee ka alaandu ; ko nden woni Г‘alaande kammbaa ndeen."
  50,21,"WoЕӢkii kala ara, hara hiki won'di e coggoowo e ceedotooЙ—o."
  50,22,""GooЕӢЙ—ii a laatinoke belsindiiЙ—o e ndee. Min kunci wirngallo maa ngon kisan; gite maa Й—een hannde ko ceeЙ“Й—e"."
  50,23,"Gonndiijo makko on wi'a: "Ko Й—uum Й—oo woni ka am Й—oo, maandinaa-Й—um"."
  50,24,"Bugee ka Jahannama onon Й—iЙ—o, kala jedduЙ—o canndallo."
  50,25,"KaЙ—oowo moЖҙЖҙere, jaggitoowo, cikkitiiЙ—o,"
  50,26,"on baЙ—iduЙ—o e Allah deweteeЙ—o goo. Bugee mo ka ndeer lepte caЙ—tuЙ—e"."
  50,27,"Cinndadiijo makko (seytaane) on wi'i: "Joomi amen, mi bewinaali oo; si ko woni, ko e majjere woЙ—Й—unde o wonnoo e mum"."
  50,28,"[Allah] daala : "Wota on njeddondir ka Am Й—oo ! Nde tawnoo Mi ardiniino e mon kammbaa."
  50,29,"Konngol waЙ—titetaake ka am Й—oo ; Mi siforaa kadi tooГұoowo jiyaaЙ“e Й“en"."
  50,30,"Г‘ande Min mbi'anoyta Jahannama o : "E a heewii?" Nge wi'a: "Ko Й“eydee hino woodi?""
  50,31,"Aljanna on Й“aЙ—tinanee gooЕӢЙ—uЙ“e Й“en, hara wonaa ka woЙ—Й—i."
  50,32,""Ko Й—um Й—oo woni ko podaЙ—on, wonan'de kala duttiiЙ—o [e Joomi mun] deeniiЙ—o."
  50,33,"oon kuluЙ—o Joom Hinaranke oon ka wirnii, o ardi e Й“ernde laaЙ“unde."
  50,34,"Naatiree mo e jam". Ko nden woni Гұalaande luttaynde ndeen."
  50,35,"Hino woodani Й“e toon kala ko Й“e faaletee, hara kadi Й“eydaari hino ka Amen."
  50,36,"ЖҠuuЙ—ii e gire Й—en Min kalki ado maЙ“Й“e, ko Й“een Й“urnooЙ“e doole, Й“een mbanngorii e leydi ndiin, ndaarugol taw si Й“e keЙ“ay laaworde."
  50,37,"Pellet, woni e Й—uum, waajo wonan'de kala jom Й“ernde, maa tuЙ—uЙ—o noppi hara ko tawaaЙ—o."
  50,38,"GooЕӢЙ—ii Min tagii kammuuji Й—iin e leydi ndin e kon ko woni hakkunde majji, ndeer balЙ—e jeegoo, tampere woo heЙ“aani Min."
  50,39,"MuГұГұo e ko Й“e kaalata kon, subbunhinanoЙ—aa Joomi maa ado puЙ—al na'ange ngen e ado mutal ngal."
  50,40,"Jemma on kadi, subbunhinanoЙ—aa mo e ka battane [juluЙ—e] farlaaЙ—e."
  50,41,"HeЙ—o, Гұande noddoowo o noddoyta e nokkuure Й“attiinde,"
  50,42,"Гұande Й“e naniroyta ha'acaango ngon e hoore goonga. Ko ndeen woni Г‘ande yaltugol ngol [ka genaale]."
  50,43,"Pellet, ko Monen nguurnata Min mbara, ko ka amen kadi woni ruttorde nde."
  50,44,"Г‘alnde leydi ndiin seekotoo [Й“e njaltira] keГұagol; ko nde woni mooЙ“irde newaniinde Min."
  50,45,"Ko Minen Й“uri anndude ko Й“e kaalata kon. A wonaa dooloowoЙ“e. Haray waajor Alqur'aanaare nden, kala kuloowo kammbaa an on."
  51,1,"Mi wooЙ—ndirii keneeli jarorayЙ—i (leydi) jaragol !"
  51,2,"Mi wooЙ—ndirii duule donndotooЙ—e toЙ“o tiiЙ—ngo !"
  51,3,"Mi wooЙ—ndirii laaЙ—e dogirayЙ—e newaare !"
  51,4,"E peccooji e yamiraande."
  51,5,"ko podete Й—on ko, ko Й—um goongo."
  51,6,"Haasbeede ko ko wonata.(e goonga)."
  51,7,"Mi wooЙ—ndirii kammu jom Й—ate nguun !"
  51,8,"Pellet, hoЙ—on e konngol luurrangol."
  51,9,"Hino yiltee e makko kala firlitaaЙ—o e gooЕӢЙ—inal."
  51,10,"FenooЙ“e Й“een kuЙ—aama."
  51,11,"Й“een yolliiЙ“e e majjere welsindiiЙ“e."
  51,12,"HeЙ“e laЙ“ndoo : "Ko honnde woni Г‘alaande njoЙ“di kuuЙ—e?""
  51,13,"Г‘alaande nde Й“e leptoyteeЙ“e ta Yiite :"
  51,14,""MeeЙ—ee lepte mon Й—een; ko Й—um woni ko keppatnoЙ—on ko"."
  51,15,"Pellet, gooЕӢЙ—uЙ“e Й“en wonii e aljannaaji e Й“ulli."
  51,16,"JaggitooЙ“e ko Joom maЙ“Й“e okkiЙ“e Й“e ko adii Й—uum koЙ“e moЖҙЖҙinatnooЙ“e."
  51,17,"HeЙ“e pamЙ—uno koЙ“e Й—aanatoo jehma."
  51,18,"E saanga ndoogu heЙ“e toro yaafeede."
  51,19,"Ina e jawЙ—e mu'en hakke wonan'de ГұaagatooЙ“e e Й“e Гұaagataako."
  51,20,"Ina e ndeer leydi he Ma'andeeji wonan'de yananaaЙ“e."
  51,21,"E ndeer pittaali mon mate on teskataaka."
  51,22,"Ina e kammu arsuka mon e ko podante Й—on ko."
  51,23,"E Joom kammu e leydi ko Й—um goongo hono no kaalirton nih."
  51,24,"Mbele arii e maa yeewtere hoЙ—Й“e Ibraahiima teddinaaЙ“e Й“e."
  51,25,"Tuma Й“e naatnoo ka makko Й“e mbi'i: "Salaam (Kisal mon)". O maaki: "Minen ko men Й—enЖҙii Й“e on"."
  51,26,"O naayii fa'ade e koreeji makko o addori ngaari payndi."
  51,27,"O Й“adaniЙ“e ndi o wii on Гұaamata?"
  51,28,"O so*i e mu,'en kulol, Й“e mii woto hul, Й“e mbeltiniriЙ“e cuklel."
  51,29,"Jom suudu makko ari hombo wulla o hellii ye'esa makko, o wii nayeejo dimara.?."
  51,30,"Maleykaaji Й—i mbii ko hono nih Joom ma daali ko KaЕӢko woni ГұeeГұo Ganndo."
  51,31,"[Annabai Ibraahiima] maaki: "Ko ho Й—um woni fii mon, onon Й“ee nelaaЙ“e?""
  51,32,"ЖҒe mbi'i: "Minen Min nela e yimЙ“e bonЙ“e Й“en,"
  51,33,"fii yo min ngaccitu e maЙ“Й“e, kaaЖҙe iwЙ—e e loope (juЙ—aaЙ—e),"
  51,34,"maandiniraaЙ—e ka Joomi maa, fii fantinooЙ“e Й“een"."
  51,35,"Min njaltini toon kala gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e wonunooЙ“e toon."
  51,36,"Min tawaano ton, si wonaa suudu juulЙ“e wo'oturu."
  51,37,"Min ngacci ton Ma'ande, wonan'de Й“en hulooЙ“e lepte mu'usuuЙ—e Й—en."
  51,38,"[Min ngacci kadi ma'ande] e Muusaa, tuma nde Min nulunoo mo e Fir'awna, wond'ude e hujja Й“annguЙ—o."
  51,39,"Kono o Й—uurnodii e semmbe makko, o wi'i [Muusaa]: "Ko bileejo maa feetuЙ—o"."
  51,40,"Min nanngi mo kaЕӢko e koneeli makko Й—in, Min bugodii Й“e ka maayo, tawde ko o pelniiЙ—o."
  51,41,"E 'Adi'en, tuma Min ngurtunoo henndu bonndu ndun e maЙ“Й“e."
  51,42,"ndu accataa hay hu'unde nde ndu arani, si wonaa ndu waЙ—tay nde wa ndoondi."
  51,43,"E Samuuda'en kadi, tuma nde Й“e mbi'ananoo : "ndakmitee haa seeЙ—a !""
  51,44,"ЖҒe townitanii yamiroore Joomi maЙ“Й“e nden, ha'acaango ngon nanngi Й“e, tawi heЙ“e Жҙeewa."
  51,45,"ЖҒe mbaawaano daragol (laawoo), Й“e wonaano kadi faabaaЙ“e."
  51,46,"Ko noon kadi yimЙ“e Nuuhu Й“een ko adii[Й“e]. ЖҒen ko yimЙ“e faasiqiiЙ“e ngonnoo."
  51,47,"Kammu ngun, Min mahir ngu doole Amen. Pellet, ko Min yaГұГұuЙ“e."
  51,48,"Leydi ndin kan, Min mbeertundi. Min moЖҙЖҙii weertuЙ“e."
  51,49,"E kala hu'unde, Min tagii noone Й—iЙ—i; mbelajo'o on mbaajitoray."
  51,50,""Awa ndogee kisan fa'ade e Allah. Min, wonan'de on immorde ka makko, ko mi jeertinoowo Й“annguЙ—o."
  51,51,"Wota on mbaЙ—idane Allah deweteeЙ—o goo. Min, wonan'de on immorde ka makko, ko mi jeertinoowo Й“annguЙ—o"."
  51,52,"Ko wano non. NulaaЙ—o araani e Й“een adinooЙ“e Й“e, si wonaa Й“e mbi'ay : "Ko bileejo maa feetuЙ—o!"."
  51,53,"Hara Й“e mbasondir e Й—uum? Ko woni kon, Й“ee ko yimЙ“e bewЙ“e."
  51,54,"RuЕӢto Й“e, a felnaaki [e fiiaЙ“Й“e."
  51,55,"Waajo tan; sabu baajagol ngol, hino nafa gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“en."
  51,56,"Mi tagiraali jinna e yimЙ“e, si wonaa fii yo Й“e ndewam"
  51,57,"Mi Й—aЙ“Й“iraa Й“e arsike; mi Й—aЙ“Й“aa yo Й“e Гұamminam."
  51,58,"Pellet, ko Allah woni garsikoowo on, Jom semmbe tiiЙ—uЙ—e."
  51,59,"Haray hino woodani Й“en tooГұЙ“e, bakkaat yeru bakkaat nanndo maЙ“Й“e'en, wota Й“e hawju."
  51,60,"Bone woodanii Й“een yedduЙ“e, e nde Г‘alaande maЙ“Й“e nde Й“e kammbanaa!"
  52,1,"Mi wooЙ—ndirii [Fello] Tuuri ngo!"
  52,2,"E deftere winndaande nde,"
  52,3,"e Й—eer portaaЙ—i!"
  52,4,"E Suudu wuurnraandu ndu!"
  52,5,"E Kippoodi (mboodi)toowundi ndi"
  52,6,"E maayo heewno ngo!"
  52,7,"Pellet, lepte Jooma Й—e ko janooje."
  52,8,"Ala duГұoowo Й—e."
  52,9,"Г‘ande kammu ngu dillirta dillere,"
  52,10,"pelle Й—een njaha e jahgol,"
  52,11,"haray nden Гұande, bone woodanii yedduЙ“e Й“e."
  52,12,"Й“een wonЙ“e e jumpugol, heЙ“e pija."
  52,13,"Г‘ande Й“e duГұiroytee doole e Yiite Jahannama duГұannde,"
  52,14,"[ЖҒe mbi'anee] : "Ko ngee Yiite woni ko njeddtnoЙ—on."
  52,15,"E ko mbilewu nii? Kaa hara on ngla yi'ide?"
  52,16,"Cumee e magge! MuГұГұiЙ—on ma on muГұГұaaki, fof no fota e mon. Nganndee ko njoЙ“eteЙ—on, ko ko ngollaynoЙ—on"."
  52,17,"Pellet, gooЕӢЙ—uЙ“e Й“een hino e Aljannaaji e neemaaji,"
  52,18,"ko Й“e dakimitotooЙ“e ko Joomi maЙ“Й“e okki Й“e, Joomi maЙ“Й“e daЙ—ndi Й“e lepte Jahiimi Й—een."
  52,19,"[ЖҒe mbi'anee] : "Г‘aamee njaron, ko newi moЙ—deum, sabu koko ngollaynoЙ—on."
  52,20,"hara ko on soЙ“Й“indiiЙ“e e hoore danЙ—e weertindiraaЙ—e", Min ndesina Й“e kadi yooЙ—a e yaaJa gite en"
  52,21,"ЖҒeen gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e, geГұngol maЙ“Й“e ngol kadi jokki Й“e e gooЕӢЙ—inal, Min tawtindinay Й“e e geГұngol maЙ“Й“e ngol. Min istantaa Й“e hu'unde e golle maЙ“Й“e Й—een; neЙ—Й—o kala ko faggitii kon no tiginaa."
  52,22,"Min Й“eydani Й“e muuyanteeЙ—i e tebbeeli kala ko Й“e tuuyetee."
  52,23,"HeЙ“e njaЙ“ondira toon, ГұedduЙ—e Й—e jillaa mehre wonaa ko bakkondinta."
  52,24,"SukaaЙ“e no eeltanaaЙ“e hino wanngoo hakkunde maЙ“Й“e, wa'aЙ“e wa kaЕӢЕӢe maraaЙ—e."
  52,25,"Yoga maЙ“Й“e feewtita yoga, Й“e laЙ“ndondira;"
  52,26,"Й“e mbi'a: "Pellet, min laatino ado [hannde], hulnooЙ“e [lepte Й—een] hakkunde yimЙ“e amen";"
  52,27,"Allah moЖҙЖҙii e amen, O daЙ—ni meon lepte Norngal."
  52,28,"Min laatino ado [hannde], torotonooЙ“e Mo. Pellet, ko KaЕӢko woni moЖҙЖҙo, jurmotooЙ—o tooЙ—o on"."
  52,29,"Anndintin tan, sabu neema Joomi maa oon, a wonaa ndureejo wonaa a kaangaaЙ—o."
  52,30,"Kaa Й“e mb'ay won'de : "Ko jimoowo ! Min habbitani mo tan jikke maayde"."
  52,31,"Maaku : "kabbitee ! Miin kadi miЙ—o habbitodi e mon"."
  52,32,"Kaa ko haqqille maЙ“Й“e Й—een yamirЙ“e Й—uum? Kaa hara ko Й“e yimЙ“e bewЙ“e tan?"
  52,33,"Kaa Й“e mbi'ay won'de : "O sincu nde?" Si ko woni, wonaa Й“e gooЕӢЙ—inooЙ“e."
  52,34,"Yoo Й“e ngaddu yeewtere sugu mayre, si wonii ko Й“e gooЕӢЙ—uЙ“e."
  52,35,"Kaa Й“e tagira Й“aawo takЙ—o? Kaa ko kamЙ“e ngoni tagooЙ“e Й“en?"
  52,36,"Kaa (ko) kamЙ“e tagi kammuuji Й—in e leydi ndin? Ko woni kon, Й“e njananaaka."
  52,37,"Kaa Й“e njogiti ngaluuji Joomi maa Й—iin? Kaa ko kamЙ“e ngoni huЙ“indiiЙ“e Й“een?"
  52,38,"Kaa Й“e njogiti Й“argal ngal Й“e njentorta? yoo keЙ—itiiЙ—o e maЙ“Й“e oon addu hujja Й“annguЙ—o !"
  52,39,"Maa ko Й“iЙ—Й“e rewЙ“e ngoodanta mo, onon kam worЙ“e Й“een?"
  52,40,"Kaa a laЙ“ndi Й“e njoЙ“di, hara joЙ“ugol ndi no teddani Й“e?"
  52,41,"Kaa Й“e nganndu fii wirniiЙ—i Й—iin, hara heЙ“e mbinnda?"
  52,42,"Maa Й“e paala fewjoore? ko yedduЙ“e Й“een, woni fooleteeЙ“e pewje Й“en."
  52,43,"Kaa heЙ“e mari deweteeЙ—o ko woori Allah? Senaare woodanii Allah, e kon ko Й“e cirkata !"
  52,44,"Si Й“e nji'ii taЖҙatine immornde ka kammu no yani, Й“e mbi'a: "Ko duule pawondirЙ—e"."
  52,45,"Terto Й“e, haa Й“e kawroya e Гұalaande maЙ“Й“e nde Й“e leptoytee e mum;"
  52,46,"Г‘ande nde pewje maЙ“Й“e duncanoytaa Й“e hay hu'unde, Й“e ngonaa kadi walloyteeЙ“e."
  52,47,"Ko pellet, hino woodani tooГұЙ“e Й“een, lepte goo ko wonaa Й—en Й—on. Ko ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude kon e maЙ“Й“e, Й“e nganndaa."
  52,48,"MuГұГұo Гұaawoore Joomi maa ndeen. Tawde pellet, haЙ—a e ndenka amen. Seniniraa yettugol Joomi maa, tuma Й“aЕӢotoЙ—aa."
  52,49,"Jehma on kadi, subbunhinanoЙ—aa mo e ka mutugol koode."
  53,1,"Mi wooЙ—ndirii hoodere si konde fukkiima"
  53,2,"Gondiijo mon majjaani o bewaani."
  53,3,"O haalata kadi belaaЙ—e."
  53,4,"Ndee [AlqurвҖҷaanaare] wonaani, si wonaa waajo bahyateeЙ—o."
  53,5,"Ko joom semmbe janngini Й—um mbo."
  53,6,"Joom mbaadi yooЙ—ndi o fotondiri."
  53,7,"Hombo woni e jookli toowЙ—i."
  53,8,"refti o Й“adi o Й“attii."
  53,9,"O woni Й“adiiЙ—o fotde lahГұe Й—iЙ—e wolla ko Й“uri Й“adaade."
  53,10,"O wahyii e maccuЙ—o makko ko o wahyii ko."
  53,11,"Й“ernde mum fennaani e ko o yi'i ko."
  53,12,"mbele hoЙ—on njeddandira e mum ko yi'i."
  53,13,"Ko noon tigi o yi'i Jibriir laawol goЙ—ngol."
  53,14,"ka lekki jaaЙ“i njani sanne(haaЙ—tirdi)."
  53,15,"ko kiin lekki woni aljanna koЙ—irЙ—o."
  53,16,"Nde muurata e lekki jaaЙ“i-he ko naatata."
  53,17,"Gite Й—e oonГұaaki nde njawtaani keerol."
  53,18,"Ko goonga o yi'i e kaawsaaji Alla Й“urЙ—i he mawnide."
  53,19,"Onon he'eferЙ“e mbelr on nji'i laata e ujjaa."
  53,20,"E manaata tataЙ“iija goЙ—Й—o oon ne."
  53,21,"Mbele hina woodani on gorko na woodani Mbo debbo."
  53,22,"Й—uum de wadde ko peccugol ngol nuunЙ—aani."
  53,23,"Й—i ngonah si wonah inЙ—e Й—e innuЙ—on onon e baabiraaЙ“e mon Alla jippinaani heen daliil Й“e ndewaani si wona sikke e mbelamme pittaali ko goongo peewal arii e maЙ“Й“e ummaade to Joom mu'en."
  53,24,"wolla mbele na woodani neЙ—Й—o ko o wooЙ—a ko."
  53,25,"Ko Alla woodani ko sakkati e ko adii ko."
  53,26,"Heewii e maleykaaji e ndeer kammuuji Й—i tefoore majji nafatah hu'unde tawi wonah caggal de Alla sakkitani wonan'de mbo O wela O."
  53,27,"Pellet Й“een Й“e ngoonЙ—inaani La'akara hoЙ“e innira maleykaaji inЙ—e rewЙ“e."
  53,28,"Woodanaani Й“e ganndal, alah koЙ“r ndewata si wona sikke, pellet sikke nafatae goonga hay hu'unde."
  53,29,"Й—uurno oon nduntiiЙ—a jikru amen mbo yiЙ—ah si wona nguurndam aduna."
  53,30,"Ko Й—oon ganndal mum en haaЙ—i, pellet ko Alla Й“uri anndude oon majjuЙ—o laawol makko, ko KaЕӢko kadi Й“uri anndude oon peewЙ—o."
  53,31,"Ko Alla woodani kala ko woni e kammuuji e leydi ngam o yoЙ“a Й“een bonnuЙ“e koЙ“e mbonni ko, o yoЙ“a kadi moЖҙЖҙinЙ“e moЖҙЖҙoore."
  53,32,"Й“een woЙ—Й—itotooЙ“e bakkatuuji mawЙ—i Й—in e paЕӢkare [Й“e paggitotaako] si wonaa tokoosi Й—in. Pellet, Joomi maa ko jaacЙ—o yaafuyee. Ko KaЕӢko Й“uri anndude on gila O puЙ—Й—unoo on ummaade e leydi, e nde ngonnoЙ—on fuЖҙЖҙannde ka deedi neeniraaЙ“e mon. Wota on mantu ko'e mon; ko KaЕӢko Й“uri anndude gooЕӢЙ—uЙ“e Й“ren."
  53,33,"E a tinaali Й—uurniiЙ—o oon,"
  53,34,"hino okkira seeЙ—aa, hooti o Й—awa?"
  53,35,"Kere o jogi ganndal mbirniiЙ—i ngal o yi'irta?"
  53,36,"Kaa o humpitaaka ko woni kon e Й—eri Muusa Й—iin"
  53,37,"e [ka Й—eri] Ibraahiima kuuЙ“nuЙ—o [ahadi yottini]"
  53,38,"won'de woЕӢkii [woo] ronndotaako doЕӢgal (bakkaat) woЙ—kii goo,"
  53,39,"e won'de alanaa neЙ—Й—anke, si wonaa ko o golli kon;"
  53,40,"e won'de golle makko Й—een, aray ka yi'ee,"
  53,41,"Refti o yoЙ“ire Й—e njoЙ“di timmundi,"
  53,42,"e wonan'de ko ka Joomi ma woni haattirde ndeen."
  53,43,"e won'de ko KaЕӢko woni beltinoowo gullinoowo"
  53,44,"ko KaЕӢko kadi woni barooro Wuurnita,"
  53,45,"e won'de O tagii resindirayЙ—i Й—in Й—iЙ—i : gorel e deyel,"
  53,46,"immorde e toЙ“Й“ere maniiyu si yuppaama,(e raЕӢЕӢa)."
  53,47,"e wonnode ko KaЕӢko woodani tagitugol Й—immum."
  53,48,"e won'de ko KaЕӢko woni galЙ—inЙ—o e gokkuЙ—o,"
  53,49,"e won'de ko KaЕӢko woni JeyЙ—o hoodere Si'ira ndeen,"
  53,50,"e won'de ko KaЕӢko halki Aadi'en adinooЙ“e,"
  53,51,"e Samuuda'en, o heddaano hay e gooto,"
  53,52,"Ko non kadi yimЙ“e Nuuhu Й“een ko adii[Й“e], pellet, Й“een laatino Й“urЙ“e tooГұude e bewde."
  53,53,"e yimЙ“e fitaare Й“een (Й“e) o waylitunoo:"
  53,54,"O hippiri Й—e ko ko o hippiri."
  53,55,"Ko holЙ—um e neemaaji Joomi ma Й—iin cikkitotoЙ—aa?"
  53,56,"Oo ko jeertinoowo jiyaaЙ—o e jeertinooЙ“e adinooЙ“e."
  53,57,"Darngal ngal noon Й“adiima."
  53,58,"DuГұoowo ngal ko woori Allah, ala."
  53,59,"E ko ndee yeewtere [Alqur'aana] kaawetoЙ—on?"
  53,60,"HoЙ—on njala, on ngullataa?"
  53,61,"Te ko on welsindiiЙ“e?"
  53,62,"Kooni cujjanee Allah, ndewon [mo]."
  54,1,"Darngal ngal Й“attiima, lewru ndun kadi se'ekiima"
  54,2,"Si Й“e nji''ii Ma'ande, Й“e Й—uurnoo Й“e mbi'a: "Ko mbilewu jokkondirngu"."
  54,3,"ЖҒe njeddi, Й“e njokki mbeleeЙ—e maЙ“Й“e. Hara le hu'unde kala no mari ГұiiЙ“irde."
  54,4,"GooЕӢЙ—ii kumpite arii e maЙ“Й“e, Й—e kaЙ—itorЙ—um woni e mum;"
  54,5,"[ЖҠuum] ko ГұeГұЖҙal jottiingal. Kono jeertingol ngol nafaani."
  54,6,"Sel Й“e. Г‘ande noddoowo on noddoyta e hu'unde aГұiniinde."
  54,7,"ja'asЙ“e ndaarЙ—e, hiЙ“e njaltira e genaale Й—een wano kanuuji caratooЙ—i."
  54,8,"heГұaniiЙ“e noddoowo on. He'eferЙ“e Й“een mbi'a: "Ndee ko Гұalaande saЙ—tunde"."
  54,9,"Ado maЙ“Й“e, yimЙ“e nuuhu Й“een yedduno. ЖҒe njedfi jiyaaЙ—o Amen on, Й“e wi'i : "Ko jinnaaЙ—o!", o kammbanaa."
  54,10,"O torii Joomi makko, won'de : "Miin on ko mi poolaaЙ—o, faabo [kam]"."
  54,11,"Min ngudditiri dammbuЙ—e kammu ngun, ndiyam wanncoojam,"
  54,12,"Min puccitiri leydi ndin Й“ulli. Ndiye Й—ern fottiri e yamiroore hoddiranoonde."
  54,13,"Min ndoondori mo e [laana] lesaaka marka alluwe e peЕӢe,"
  54,14,"hika dogira e ndenka amen. ЖҠuum ko njoЙ“di [Nuuhu] jeddanooЙ—o oon."
  54,15,"GooЕӢЙ—ii Min ngaccirii [kon ko Min mbaЙ—i Й“e] tasakuyee. Taw si woodi baajitorayЙ—o?"
  54,16,"Tesko ko hono lepte Am e jeertingol (am) wa'anoo?"
  54,17,"GooЕӢЙ—ii Min newinirii Alqur'aanare nden baajitorgol. Hara wooday baajitorЙ—o?"
  54,18,"Aadi'en njedduno. Taskee ko hono lepte am e jeertingol (sm) wa'anoo?"
  54,19,"Min ngurtu e maЙ“Й“e henndu saЙ—tundu, e Гұalaande hiitaande, duumiinde;"
  54,20,"hindu bippitira yimЙ“e Й“een, wa si tawii ko Й“e daЖҙЖҙe tamaro irtaaЙ—e."
  54,21,"Taskee ko hono lepte am Й—en e jertingol (am) ngol wa'anoo?"
  54,22,"GooЕӢЙ—ii Min newinirii Alqur'aanare nden sabu baajitorgol. Hara wooday baajitorЙ—o?"
  54,23,"Samuuda'en njedduno waajo ngo,"
  54,24,"Й“e mb'i: "Kere ko neЙ—Й—o gooto e amen woni ko min njokkata? Haray min ngonii on tumba e nderr majjere e tamperere."
  54,25,"Hara ko e makko jaЕӢtoore nden wernaa hakkunde amen? Si ko woni, ko penoowo nii, townitiiЙ—o"."
  54,26,"Aray Й“e ngaannda (Г‘alnde) Janngo, ko hommbo woni penoowo toownitiiЙ—o on."
  54,27,"Ko Min wurtirooЙ“e ngelooba ndewa ba ngam, jarribagol Й“e. Aynitu Й“e, muГұГұoЙ—aa."
  54,28,"Humpitu Й“e won'de ndiyam Й—am ko sennndaaЙ—am hakkunde maЙ“Й“e [e ngelooba ba]; kala yaray geЙ—al mum."
  54,29,"ЖҒe noddi gon'diijo maЙ“Й“e, o jonni [kaafa kan], o sodi [ba]."
  54,30,"Teskii ko hono lepte am Й—een e jeertingol (am) ngol wa'anoo?"
  54,31,"Ko ha'acaango wooturu tun Min ngurti e maЙ“Й“e, Й“e mba'i wa ledde yo'orude muncaaЙ—e."
  54,32,"GooЕӢЙ—ii Min newinirii Alqur'aanare nden baajitorgol. Hara wooday baajitorЙ—o?"
  54,33,"YimЙ“e Luutu Й“en njedduno jeertine Й—een."
  54,34,"Min ngurtuno henndu kaaЖҙe e maЙ“Й“e, si wonaa e Й“eynguure Luutu nden, Min daЙ—ndirno Й“een ka wenndo,"
  54,35,"moЖҙЖҙere immorde e Amen. Ko non Min nkoЙ“itirta kala kettuЙ—o [neema Allah on]."
  54,36,"GooЕӢЙ—ii le o jeretinirno Й“e nanngal amen cattungal ngal. Kono Й“e cikkitii jeertinol ngol."
  54,37,"GooЕӢЙ—ii Й“e Й—aЙ“Й“irno mo [bonidugol e hoЙ—Й“e makko Й“een]. Min mehi gite maЙ“Й“e Й—een. "MeeЙ—ee lepte Й—een e jeertingol am ngol"."
  54,38,"GooЕӢЙ—ii ko bimmbi law, woni ko lepte duumiiЙ—e ndawirani Й“e."
  54,39,""MeeЙ—ee lepte e jeertingol am"."
  54,40,"GooЕӢЙ—ii Min newinirii Alqur'aanare nden baajitorgol. Hara wooday baajitorЙ—o?"
  54,41,"GooЕӢЙ—ii jeertinaango ngon arii e yimЙ“e Fir'awna Й“een."
  54,42,"ЖҒe njeddi aayeeje amen Й—en fof. Min nanngiri Й“e, nanngal pooluЙ—o kattanЙ—o."
  54,43,"Ko he'eferЙ“e mon Й“en Й“uri Й“eya moЖҙЖҙude? Kaa ko daЙ—gol woodani on ka ЖҠeri?"
  54,44,"Kaa hara Й“e mbi'ay : "Minen ko min dental wallindirooЙ“e"?"
  54,45,"Aray nde dental [maЙ“Й“e] ngal foolee, Й“e ndunntina Й“abbe maЙ“Й“e."
  54,46,"Wurin ko Darnga ngo woni kammbaa maЙ“Й“e on, Ko Darnga noon Й“uri mawnude e haaЙ—ude."
  54,47,"Pellet, bonЙ“e Й“en ngonii e majjere e ooyunge."
  54,48,"Г‘ande Й“e daasiroytee je'ece maЙ“Й“e Й—een ka nder Yiite, (Й“e mbi'anee): "MeeЙ—ee meemugol Saqara"."
  54,49,"Minen Min tagir hu'unde kala e eЙ“Й“oore,"
  54,50,"Yamiroore amen wonaani, si wonaa [konngol] gootol pet, [yaawira] wa hinЖҙaango yiitere."
  54,51,"GooЕӢЙ—ii Min kalkiino yeradiiЙ“e mon. Hara wooday baajitorayЙ—o?"
  54,52,"Kala hu'unde nde Й“e ngolli no ka ndeer Й—eri,"
  54,53,"kala kadi toksum e mawnukum, ko binndaa Й—um."
  54,54,"Pellet, gooЕӢЙ—uЙ“e Й“ren ngonii e Aljannaaji e caatli,"
  54,55,"e toolorde goonga, ka LaamЙ—o kattanЙ—o."
  55,1,"Joom yurmeende e on."
  55,2,"O anndinii alqur'aana."
  55,3,"O tagi neЙ—Й—aЕӢke o."
  55,4,"O anndini mo Й“anngingol.(laЙ“Й“in'gol)"
  55,5,"Nayange ngen e lewru ndun [hiЙ—i ndogira] limoore,"
  55,6,"koode Й—een kadi e leЙ—Й—e Й—een, hino cujjude."
  55,7,"Kammu ngun, o toowni ngu. O waЙ—i nunЙ—al ngal,"
  55,8,"fii wota on mbewu ka pe'esirЙ—e."
  55,9,"Г‘inniron petgol ngol no nunЙ—iri. Wata on ustu pe'esirЙ—e Й—een."
  55,10,"Leydi ndiin, O waЙ—anndi tagoore ndeen:"
  55,11,"MuuyanteeЙ—i hino e mayri, e leЙ—Й—e tamaro marЙ—e poЖҙЖҙi."
  55,12,"e gabbe marЙ—e Гұa'ande, e uurngol."
  55,13,"E ko holЙ—i e ne'emaaji Joomi mon Й—in woni ko njeddoton?"
  55,14,"O tagiri neЙ—Й—o on immorde e loopal, ba'ngal e ko juЙ—aa."
  55,15,"O tagiri jinnaaji Й—iin, immorde e lew lewndu yiite laaЙ“uki."
  55,16,"E ko holЙ—i e ne'emaaji Joomi mon Й—iin njeddoton?"
  55,17,"JeyЙ—o fuЙ—irЙ—e Й—een Й—iЙ—i Jeyi kadi mutirЙ—e Й—een Й—iЙ—i."
  55,18,"E ko holЙ—i e ne'emaaji Joomi mon Й—in njeddoton?"
  55,19,"O Tuppindiri maaje Й—een Й—iЙ—i, hiЙ—e potta."
  55,20,"heedo hino hakkunde majje, Й—e njillondirtaa."
  55,21,"E ko holЙ—i e ne'emaaji Joomi mon Й—in njeddoton?"
  55,22,"Hino yalta e Й—een [maaje] Й—iЙ—i: kaЕӢЕӢe "Lu'lu'u" e "marjaan"."
  55,23,"E ko holЙ—i e neemaaji Joomi mon Й—in njeddoton?"
  55,24,"Ko KaЕӢko woodani dogooje lesaaЙ—e ka ndeer maayo, ba'aЙ—e na pelle."
  55,25,"E ko holЙ—i e ne'emaaji Joomi mon Й—in njeddoton?"
  55,26,"Kala ko woni e hoore mayri ko ko re'oyta,"
  55,27,"heddoo Jaati Joomaa Kiin, Jom mawngu e teddungal."
  55,28,"E ko holЙ—i e ne'emaaji Joomi mon Й—in njeddoton?"
  55,29,"ЖҒeen ngonЙ“e ka kammuuji e ka leydi hino naamnoo mo. Г‘ande woo, Himo e fiyaaku."
  55,30,"E ko holЙ—i e ne'emaaji Joomi mon Й—iin njeddoton?"
  55,31,"Aray nde Min fa'andii hasbude on, onon yo tedda ko'e en Й—iЙ—o en.."
  55,32,"E ko holЙ—i e ne'emaaji Joomi mon Й—in njeddoton?"
  55,33,"Eey mon yo dental jinna e yimЙ“e ! Si on kattanii wuЙ—Й—irgol ka seraaji kammuuji e ka leydi, haray nguЙ—Й—ee. On wuЙ—Й—irtaa si wonaa e doole."
  55,34,"E ko holЙ—i e ne'emaaji Joomi mon Й—iin njeddoton?"
  55,35,"Hino wurtee e mon - [onon jinna e yimЙ“e] - Й—emngal yiite e curki [maa sila taayuЙ—o], on paabondirtaa."
  55,36,"E ko holЙ—i e ne'emaaji Joomi mon Й—in njeddoton?"
  55,37,"Si wonii kammu nguun seekiima, ngu wojjirii wa piindi hono pentiir boЙ—e."
  55,38,"E ko holЙ—i e ne'emaaji Joomi mon Й—in njeddoton?"
  55,39,"Nden Гұande, wonaa neЙ—Й—o maa jinne woni ko laЙ“nditetee fii bakkaat mum."
  55,40,"E ko holЙ—i e ne'emaaji Joomi mon Й—in njeddoton?"
  55,41,"BonЙ“e Й“een hino ngaannditiree Ma'andeeji maЙ“Й“e Й—iin. ЖҒe nanngiroyee ka njubuuji-tin tinЙ—i- e ka koyЙ—e."
  55,42,"E ko holЙ—i e ne'emaaji Joomi mon Й—in woni ko njeddoton?"
  55,43,"Ko ngee woni Jahannama nge bonЙ“e Й“en njeddynoo fii mum."
  55,44,"HiЙ“e mbanngoo hakkunde magge e fatayЙ—am kattuЙ—am wulde."
  55,45,"E ko holЙ—i e ne'emaaji Joomi mon Й—in njeddoton?"
  55,46,"Hino woodani kala kulЙ—o daragol ye'eso Joomi mum, aljannaaji Й—iЙ—i;"
  55,47,"E ko holЙ—i e ne'emaaji Joomi mon Й—in njeddoton?"
  55,48,"(joomiraji)marЙ—e calЙ—i Й—iЙ—i dukke."
  55,49,"E ko holЙ—i e ne'emaaji Joomi mon Й—in njeddoton?"
  55,50,"ЖҒulli Й—iЙ—i hino e ndeer majji, ilayЙ—i."
  55,51,"E ko holЙ—i e neemaaji Joomi mon Й—in njeddoton?"
  55,52,"Hino e ndeer majji kala muuyanteeЙ—i Й—iin, noone Й—iЙ—i."
  55,53,"E ko holЙ—i e neemaaji Joomi mon Й—in njeddoton?"
  55,54,"Hara ko Й“e soЙ“Й“indiiЙ“e e ndaЙ—Й—ule tekkirЙ—e ndeer, dimЙ—e majje Й—een Й—iЙ—i ko Й“adiiЙ—e."
  55,55,"E ko holЙ—i e ne'emaaji Joomi mon Й—in njeddoton?"
  55,56,"(RewЙ“e) Й—aЙ“Й“iЙ—a ndaarЙ—eЙ“e hino toon, Й“e neЙ—Й—o memaani ado maЙ“Й“e wonaa kadi jinna."
  55,57,"E ko holЙ—i e ne'emaaji Joomi mon Й—in njeddoton?"
  55,58,"[LabiraaЙ“e] hono kaЕӢЕӢe yaaquutu e marjaan."
  55,59,"E ko holЙ—i e neemaaji Joomi mon Й—in njeddoton?"
  55,60,"Hara njoЙ“di moЖҙЖҙere no woodi, si wonaa moЖҙЖҙere?"
  55,61,"E ko holЙ—i e ne'emaaji Joomi mon Й—iin njeddoton?"
  55,62,"Hino ga Й—iin Й—iЙ—i, aljannaaji Й—iЙ—i kadi."
  55,63,"E ko holЙ—i e neemaaji Joomi mon Й—in njeddoton?"
  55,64,"KecciЙ—Й—i Й—iЙ—i."
  55,65,"E ko holЙ—i e ne'emaaji Joomi mon Й—iin njeddoton?"
  55,66,"ЖҒulli Й—iЙ—i hino e ndeer majji, Й“ulayЙ—i."
  55,67,"E ko holЙ—i e ne'emaaji Joomi mon Й—in njeddoton?"
  55,68,"Hino e majji : muuyanteeЙ—i, e leЙ—Й—e tamarooje e rummaana."
  55,69,"E ko holЙ—i e ne'emaaji Joomi mon Й—in njeddoton?"
  55,70,"Hino e Й—iin Й—iЙ—i : rewЙ“e suЙ“aaЙ“e (labaaЙ“e)."
  55,71,"E ko holЙ—i e ne'emaaji Joomi mon Й—in njeddoton?"
  55,72,"huurul'ayniiЙ“e(yaaja gite), soomaaЙ“e e tillisooji,"
  55,73,"E ko holЙ—i e ne'emaaji Joomi mon Й—in njeddoton?"
  55,74,"neЙ—Й—o memaani Й“en ado maЙ“Й“e, wonaa kadi jinna."
  55,75,"E ko holЙ—i e neemaaji Joomi mon Й—in njeddoton?"
  55,76,"Ko Й“e soЙ“Й“indotooЙ“e e dow ngawluuji haakooji, e ndaЙ—Й—ule abqari labaaЙ—e."
  55,77,"E ko holЙ—i e ne'emaaji Joomi mon Й—in njeddoton?"
  55,78,"Barkinii innde Jooma nden, Jom mawngu e teddungal !"
  56,1,"Si ko darotoongal ngal dariima,"
  56,2,"alanaa daragol maggal ngol pennoowo."
  56,3,"KoyfinЙ—inatngal (yedduЙ“e), Й“amtatngal (gooЙ—iiЙ“e)."
  56,4,"Si lesdi ndiin dilliniraama dillannde,"
  56,5,"pelle Й—een munciroyee muncannde,"
  56,6,"Й—e ngonta collaari ruuynatndi,"
  56,7,"Mbattinon nooneeji tati :"
  56,8,"Ko wontirooЙ“e Гұaamo Й“een - iskin Й“een yimЙ“e Гұaamo !"
  56,9,"e wontirooЙ“e nano Й“een, bis e Й“een yimЙ“e nano !"
  56,10,"Ko adondiratnooЙ“e Й“een (e moЖҙЖҙere ka aduna), adoytee (naatneede Aljanna)."
  56,11,"Ko Й“een ngoni badnitaaЙ“e Й“een."
  56,12,"ka Aljannaaji ne'eminiiЙ—i,"
  56,13,"dental jeyaangal e [mofte] adinooЙ“e Й“een,"
  56,14,"e seeЙ—aaЙ“e jiyaaЙ“e e [mofte] sakkitiiЙ“e Й“een,"
  56,15,"heЙ“e e hoore danЙ—e yuЙ“Й“iraaЙ—e [kaЕӢЕӢe],"
  56,16,"hara heЙ“e soЙ“Й“indii e majje, feewtondirЙ“e."
  56,17,"SukaaЙ“e duuminaaЙ“e hino mbanngoo hakkunde maЙ“Й“e,"
  56,18,"wonndude e ГұedduЙ—e, e cataloy, e koroy e [hebbiniraakoy] beere ilatnde,"
  56,19,"Й“e muusetaake ko*e ndeer toon, Й“e ciwritaa;"
  56,20,"e muuyanteeЙ—i Й—i Й“e cuЙ“otoo,"
  56,21,"E teewu colli ngu Й“e tuuyatee."
  56,22,"E huurul'ayniiЙ“e -yaaja gite en Й“een."
  56,23,"nannduЙ“e e kaЕӢЕӢe lu'lu'u maraaЙ—e;(coomaaЙ—e)."
  56,24,"njoЙ“di ko Й“e ngollatnoo koon."
  56,25,"ЖҒe nanataa ndeer ton haala mhere, wonaa ko bakkondiЕӢta;"
  56,26,"si wonaa wi'aneede : "Salaaman! Salaaman!" [SaЙ—i mon! saЙ—i mon!]."
  56,27,"E wontirooЙ“e Гұaamo Й“een, ko ngoni Й“een yimЙ“e Гұaamo?"
  56,28,"[ЖҒe ngonat] e leЙ—Й—e jaaЙ“e neewЙ—uЙ—e,"
  56,29,"E banaanaje pawandirЙ—e."
  56,30,"E Й—owdi duumiindi,"
  56,31,"E ndiyam juuratЙ—am,"
  56,32,"e Й“iЙ“Й“e leЙ—Й—e Й—uuЙ—uЙ—e"
  56,33,"Й—e taЖҙondirtaa Й—e kaЙ—etaake."
  56,34,"E danЙ—e Й“amtaaЙ—e."
  56,35,"Ko minen tagi puЙ—Й—i Й“e (puЙ—Й—agol)."
  56,36,"Min mbaЙ—i Й“e curbaaЙ“e-boomi-."
  56,37,"yiЙ—uЙ“e worЙ“e mum, goreeЙ“e."
  56,38,"[Min marani Й“e] yimЙ“e Гұaamo Й“een."
  56,39,"Dental jiyaaЙ“e e [mofte] adinooЙ“e Й“een,"
  56,40,"E seeЙ—aaЙ“e jiyaaЙ“e e [mofte] sakkitiiЙ“e Й“een."
  56,41,"E wontirooЙ“e nano Й“een. Ko homЙ“e nhoni Й“een yimЙ“e nano?"
  56,42,"[ЖҒeen] no e nguleendi e patatЙ—am,"
  56,43,"E Й—owdi curki Й“awluki,"
  56,44,"wonaa Й“uuЙ“ndi, wonaa teddundi."
  56,45,"Ado Й—uum, hari ko Й“e neeminaaЙ“e."
  56,46,"Й“e laatino heЙ“e deppitoo e bakkaat mawЙ—i Й—iin,"
  56,47,"heЙ“e mbi'atnoo: "Enee, si min maayii, min ngontii mbullaari e Жҙi'e, hara ko min immintinoyteeЙ“e?"
  56,48,"hay baabiraaЙ“e amen adinooЙ“e Й“een?""
  56,49,"Maaku : "pellet, aramЙ“e e sakkitiiЙ“e Й“e."
  56,50,"ko mooЙ“oyteeЙ“e e Гұalaande anndaande waktu mum."
  56,51,"refti pellet, onon Й“ee majjuЙ“e yedduЙ“e [ummital],"
  56,52,"ko on ГұaamoyayЙ“e e leggal "Zaqquumi" ngal"
  56,53,"kebbiniron ngal deedi,"
  56,54,"njariron ngal kadi patatЙ—am,"
  56,55,"Njariron wa jargol ngelooba Й—omЙ—aamba"."
  56,56,"Ko Й—uum woni ko Й“e kottiigu !u! en Гұalnde njoЙ“di diina."
  56,57,"Ko Minen ngoni ko tagi on. HaЙ—i ngooЕӢЙ—ion [Min immintinat on]?"
  56,58,"On nj'ii on maniiyu mo ndufoton?"
  56,59,"Ko onon tagata mo? Kaa ko minen ngoni tagooЙ“e [Й—um]?"
  56,60,"Ko Minen koddiri maayde ndeen hakkunde mon. Min ngonaani adateeЙ“e"
  56,61,"E battitugol yeruuЙ“e mon, Min puЙ—Й—ira on e ko on ngannda."
  56,62,"GooЕӢЙ—ii hoЙ—on nganndi tageede aranun Й—um. Ko haЙ—i mbaajitoЙ—on?"
  56,63,"On nji'ii ko ko ndemoton?"
  56,64,"Ko onon puЙ—inta Й—um? Kaa ko Minen ngoni fuЙ—inooЙ“e Й“een?"
  56,65,"Si min kaajuno, pellet, Min mbaЙ—ayno ndu foron. Mbattinon hiЙ—on kaawoo [mbi'a] :"
  56,66,""Minen ko min lepteteeЙ“e perte ko min nafqi ko."
  56,67,"wurin ko min haЙ—aaЙ“e!"."
  56,68,"On yi'ii ndiyam Й—am njaroton Й—am?"
  56,69,"E ko onon njippiniri Й—am ka duule? Kaa ko minen njippini [Й—am]?"
  56,70,"Si Min kaajuno, Min mbaЙ—ayno Й—am kaaЙ—Й—am. Ko haЙ—i njetton [Allah]?"
  56,71,"On nj'ii yiite nge kuЙ“Й“oton ngen?"
  56,72,"E ko onon woodini waЙ—i leЙ—Й—e mum? Kaa ko Minen ngoodini [Й—e]?"
  56,73,"Min mbaЙ—ir ngen [yiite] waaju, e nafitor nge setotooЙ“e."
  56,74,"Subbunhinor innde Joomi maa, mawЙ—o oon!"
  56,75,"Mi wooЙ—ndirii mutirЙ—e koode Й—een."
  56,76,"Pellet, Й—uum ko woondoore mawnde, si hoЙ—on nganndunoo."
  56,77,"Pellet nee ko alqur'aanaare konde teddunde,"
  56,78,"won'de e deftere reenaande"
  56,79,"meemataa nden si wonaa laЙ“Й“inaaЙ“e Й“een;"
  56,80,"ko jippiniraande ka JeyЙ—o winndere ndeen."
  56,81,"E ko ndee yeewtere woЕӢki ko njeddoton onon?"
  56,82,"HoЙ—on mbaЙ—a arsike mon (toЙ“o ngon) ko on yeddooЙ“e [arsikuЙ—o On]?"
  56,83,"Ko haЙ—ata nde woЕӢkii yottii ka lookoЖҙere,"
  56,84,"hara onon hoЙ—on ndaara on tumba,"
  56,85,"hara non ko Minen Й“uri on Й“adaade mo, kono on nji'ataa."
  56,86,"Ko haЙ—ata on, si tawiino on njoЙ“etaake."
  56,87,"Ndutton kin [woЕӢkii], si tawii ko on goonguЙ“e?"
  56,88,"Si tawii on ko jiyaaЙ—o e Й“attinaaЙ“e Й“een,"
  56,89,"haray ko foftere, e moЖҙЖҙere, e Aljannaaji ne'ema (woodani mo)."
  56,90,"Si tawii kadi ko jiyaaЙ—o e yimЙ“e Гұaamo Й“een,"
  56,91,"haray [o jaЙ“Й“oroyte] : "Kisal maa" e Й“aЕӢge yimЙ“e Гұaamo Й“een."
  56,92,"Si tawii noon ko jiyanooЙ—o e yedduЙ“e majjuЙ“e Й“een,"
  56,93,"haray hoЙ—torde makko on ko patayЙ—am,"
  56,94,"E sumeede Jahiimi."
  56,95,"Pellet, ko Й—um woni goonga jananaaЙ—o oon."
  56,96,"Subbunhinor innde Joomi maa, mawЙ—o oon!"
  57,1,"Kala ko woni ka kammuuji e ka leydi seninii Allah. Ko KaЕӢko woni pooluЙ—o, Г‘eeГұo on."
  57,2,"Ko KaЕӢko heeranii laamu kammuuji Й—iin e lesdi ndin. Himo wuurna Himo wara, KanЕӢko O kattanЙ—o kala hu'unde."
  57,3,"Ko KaЕӢko woni arano e cakkitiiЙ—o, peeГұuЙ—o e birniiЙ—o, KaЕӢko ko O gannduЙ—o kala hu'unde."
  57,4,"Ko KaЕӢko tagi kammuuji Й—iin e leydi ndiin ndeer balЙ—e jeegoo, refti O fotondiri ka dow "Arsi"; Himo anndi ko mutata kon ka leydi, e ko Жҙawata e mayri, e ko jipporta ka kammu e ko Жҙawata e maggu. Homo wonndi e mon kala ka ngonЙ—on. Allah no reeni ko ngolloton kon."
  57,5,"Ko KaЕӢko heeranii laamu kammuuji Й—in e leydi ndin. Ko ka Allah fiyakuuji Й—in nduttirtee."
  57,6,"Himo naadia jemma on e ndeer Гұalawma on, o naadira Гұalama on kadi e ndeer jemma on. KaЕӢko ko O gannduЙ—o ko woni e ndeer Й“erЙ—e."
  57,7,"GooЕӢЙ—inee Allah e nulaaЙ—o makko on, nafqon kon ko o waЙ—iri on lomtinaaЙ“e e mum. GooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“een e mon, Й“e nafqi [jawle maЙ“Й“e Й—en], hino woodani Й“een njoЙ“di mawnundi."
  57,8,"E ko heЙ“i on, on ngooЕӢЙ—intaa Allah? E hino NulaaЙ—o on hino nodda on e gooЕӢЙ—ingol Joomi mon. GooЙ—ii [Allah] Жҙettii e mon ahadi, si on laatike gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e."
  57,9,"Ko KaЕӢko jippinta e jeyaaЙ—o makko on aayeeje Й“annguЙ—e, fii no o njaltinira on e niЙ“e fa'ade e ndaygu. Pellet, Allah ko jurmotooЙ—o on, jaafotooЙ—o."
  57,10,"E ko heЙ“i on, on cakkotaako fii laawol Allah ngol, e hino le ko Allah woodani ronugol kammuuji Й—iin e leydi ndin? Fotataa e mon, Й“en sakkinooЙ“e ado uddital ngal Й“e haЙ“idaa; ko Й“een Й“uri mawnude darja e dii Й“een sakkiiЙ“e Й“aawo Й—um Й“e haЙ“idaa. ЖҒe fof maЙ“Й“e noon, Allah fodii Й“e moЖҙЖҙere. Allah no humpitii ko ngolloton kon."
  57,11,"Ko hommbo Гұamlirta Allah Гұamaande labaande, o sowana mo nde, hara no woodani mo njoЙ“di teddundi?"
  57,12,"Г‘ande nji'oytaa gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e worЙ“e Й“een e gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e rewЙ“e Й“een, hara annoora maЙ“Й“e yaara ye'eso maЙ“Й“e e Гұaamo maЙ“Й“e (Й“e mbi'anee): "Weltaare mon hannde ko Aljannaaji, Й—i canЙ—i ilata senngo ley mum, ko on duumotooЙ“e ndeer ton". Ko Й—um woni malal mawngal ngal."
  57,13,"Г‘alnde naafiqiiЙ“e worЙ“e Й“een e naafiqiiЙ“e rewЙ“e Й“en mbi'anoyta gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“een: "kabbee min, min njalbinora annoora mon on". ЖҒe mbi'anee : "Yiltoree Й“aawo mon, Й—aЙ“Й“oyon annoora". Heedo waЙ—ee hakkunde maЙ“Й“e, ngo damal ngal yurmeende woni e nder mum, Й“aawo maggal noon, ko lepte woni e bannge mum."
  57,14,"HiЙ“e nodda Й“e : "E min ngondaano e mon?" ЖҒe mbi'a : "Ko non nhoniri. Ko woni tun, on fitinno ko'e mon, habbitaniЙ—on [gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“en bone], cikkitiЙ—on, yelaaji hodi on haa yamiroore Allah nden ari. Hodoowo on hodi on e moЖҙЖҙere Allah ndeen."
  57,15,"Hannde noon, on njaЙ“antaake coktorЙ—um wonaa e Й“een yedduЙ“e. Depporde mon nden ko ka Yiite : ko ngen woni ko hannduЙ—on. Nge bonii ruttorde."
  57,16,"E yontaani gooЕӢЙ—iiЙ“e Й“en nde Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en deeЖҙirta jantoore Allah nden e kon ko jippii immorde e goonga? Hara Й“e wa'aani wa Й“een okkanooЙ“e defte Й“en ko adii, dumunna on juutani Й“een, Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en njo'ori, ko Й—uuЙ—unoo e maЙ“Й“e ko ko faasiqiiЙ“e."
  57,17,"Nganndee pellet, Allah wuurnitay lesdi ndiin Й“aawo ndi yo'orii. GooЕӢЙ—ii Min Й“annginiranii on aayeeje Й—een, fii no haqqiliron."
  57,18,"Pellet, sakkotooЙ“e (jawЙ—e mum Й“een) ka worЙ“e e ka rewЙ“e Й“e Гұami Allah Гұamaande labaande, Й“e sowanoyte (mbarjaari) hara no woodani Й“e njoЙ“di mawndi."
  57,19,"ЖҒeen gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Allah e NulaaЙ—o makko on, ko Й“en woni goongiyaЕӢke en. SahodinЙ“e Й“en ka Joomi mun, hino woodani Й“en njoЙ“di maЙ“Й“e e annoora maЙ“Й“e. ЖҒeen noon yedduЙ“e Й“e njeddi aayeeje Amen Й—een, ko Й“een ngoni yimЙ“e Jahiimi ngen."
  57,20,"Ngnndee won'de nguurndam aduna Й—am ko fijindaaru, e mbeleeЙ—e, e cuЙ—aari, e Й“urondiro hakkunde mon e jawЙ—e e Й“iЙ“Й“e. Wano toЙ“o haawnungo remooЙ“e Й“en puЙ—i mum, refti ngo yo'ora, yi'aa hingo soyЙ—i; refti ngo wonta munciiЙ—um. Hino ka laakara, lette caЙ—tuЙ—e, e yaafuyee immorde e Allah e yarluyee. Nguurndam aduna Й—am wonaani, si wonaa dakammehoy hodo."
  57,21,"Ngadondiree e (golle) yaafaawuya ka Joomi mon, e Aljanna mo yaajeendi mun wa'i yaajeendi kammu ngun e leydi ndin, on maranaama Й“ren gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Allah e NulaaЙ“e makko Й“en. ЖҠuum ko Й“ural Allah ngal o okkata on mo O muuyani. Allah ko Joim Й“ural mawnungal."
  57,22,"Bone woo heЙ“ataa [on] e lesdi ndiin ma e pittaali mon Й—iin, si wonaa Й—uum woniino e deftere ado min tagude ndee [tagoore]. Pellet, Й—uum ko ko newanii Allah."
  57,23,"Ko fii wota on cuno e ko laawii on kon, ngonaa kadi weltorgol ko o okki on kon. Allah yiЙ—aa kala ГұaaЖҙoowo, mantiiЙ—o."
  57,24,"ЖҒeen wuddooЙ“e Й“e njamira yimЙ“e Й“een nguddam... kala Й—uurniiЙ—o, pellet, Allah kan ko Galo, jettiniiЙ—o."
  57,25,"GooЕӢЙ—ii Min nulirii NulaaЙ“e amen Й“een Й“anngannduyeeji, Min njippindinani Й“e defte e sariyaare, fii no yimЙ“e Й“een ГұiiЙ“ira e nunЙ—al. Min njippini kadi njamndi ndiin, ndi doole tiiЙ—uЙ—e woni e mum e nafooje wonan'de yimЙ“e Й“een, e no Allah feГұГұinira Й“een wallooЙ“e mo e NulaaЙ—o makko on ka wirnii. Pellet, Allah ko Jom demmbe, pooluЙ—o."
  57,26,"GooЕӢЙ—ii Min nulii Nuuhu e Ibraahiima, Min maЙ—i e geГұngol maЙ“Й“e ngol Annabaaku e defte. Hino e maЙ“Й“e feewuЙ“e, ko Й—uuЙ—i kon e maЙ“Й“e ko faasiqiiЙ“e."
  57,27,"Refti Min njokkindini e batteeji maЙ“Й“e Й—in, nulaaЙ“e amen [goo], Min njokkintiniri [Й“e] Iisaa geЙ—al Maryama on, Min ngokki mo Linjiila, Min mbaЙ—i e Й“erЙ—e jokkuЙ“e mo Й“en : yurmeende e giggol. Labbeyaagal ngal Й“e sinci ngal, Minen Min mbaЙ—Й—inaa ngal e maЙ“Й“e. [Min lamndaaki] si wonaa Й—aЙ“Й“ugol welayee Allah. Kono Й“e ayniraali Й—um no haani aynireede. Min ngokki njoЙ“di goiЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“een e maЙ“Й“e. Ko Й—uuЙ—unoo kon e maЙ“Й“e ko faasiqiiЙ“e."
  57,28,"Eey mon yo gooЕӢЙ—iiЙ“e! Kulee Allah, ngooЕӢЙ—inon NulaaЙ—o makko on; O yeЙ—ay on geЙ—e Й—iЙ—i e mbarjaari makko ndiin, O waЙ—ana on annoora mo ndayginorton, O haforana on. Pellet, Allah ko kaforoowo, jurmootooЙ—o."
  57,29,"Fii no yimЙ“e defte Й“een ngnndira won'de Й“e kattanaa hay hu'unde e Й“ural Allah ngal, e won'de Й“ural ngal ko e juuЙ—e Allah woni; Himo yeЙ—a ngal mo O muuyani. Pellet, Allah ko Joom Й“ural manngal."
  58,1,"Ko goonga Alla nani konngol oon duttondiroowo e ma haala ko faati e joom galle makko hombo wullito fa'ade e Alla; Alla na nana yeewtere mon nde pellet Alla ko nanoowo ji'oowo"
  58,2,"ЖҒeen nanndinooЙ“e suddiiЙ“e mum en e yummiraaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e, Й“een Й“e ngona yummiraaЙ“e maЙ“Й“Жҙe, woni yummiraaЙ“e mum en ko Й“een jibinЙ“e Й“e pellet hoЙ“e kaala paЕӢkare e penaande e pellet Alla ko jaafatooЙ—o jarlotooЙ—o bakkatuuji."
  58,3,"ЖҒeen nanndinooЙ“e rewЙ“e mum en refti Й“e ndutto ko Й“e mbiino ko yoЙ“e ndimЙ—in daande ko adi ndeЙ“e memandirta ko Й—um woni ko mbaajete Й—on ko, alla na kumpati ko ngollaton ko."
  58,4,"Kala mbo daГұaani yo o hoor lebbi Й—iЙ—i dewandirЙ—i ko adii ndeЙ“e mandirta kala mbo kattanaani yo o Гұammin miskineeЙ“e capanЙ—e njeegom, Й—uum ko ngam ngoonЙ—inon Alla e nelaaЙ—o makko ko Й—uum woni keerol Alla woodanii he'eferЙ“e lepte cattuЙ—e."
  58,5,"Pellet Й“een luundotooЙ“e Alla e nelaaЙ—o makko Й“e koynaama hono no adiiЙ“e Й“e koynirano, min tellinii aayeeje peeГұЙ—e, woodani he'eferЙ“e lepte koynooje."
  58,6,"Г‘ande o ummini Й“e kamЙ—e fof o holla Й“e koЙ“e ngolluno ko, o tonngii Й—uum Й“e njejji Й—uum Alla na seedii kala hu'unde."
  58,7,"Mbele a annda won'de Alla na anndi ko woni e ndeer kammuuji e ko woni e ndeer leydi, gunndo wonata hakkunde tata si wona o nayЙ“itaЙ“e ngo wonata hakkunde noyo si wona o wona jeegoЙ“o ngo wonata ko ja'asi Й—uum si wona o won'da e mum en toЙ“e mbaawi won'de fof, refti o habraЙ“e ko Й“e ngolli Гұande darnga, pellet Alla na anndi kala hu'unde."
  58,8,"Mbele a yiyaani Й“een kaЙ—aaЙ“e ndeeyu refti Й“e nduttoo koЙ“e kada ko Й“e ndeeyandira e bakkatuuji e aГұanaagal e woopde nelaaЙ—o, siЙ“i ngarii e ma Й“e calmanir ma na Alla salminiraani ma nih Й“e mbiya e pittaali mum en ko haЙ—i Alla leptira min ko min kaalata ko, yoniiЙ“e jahannama hoЙ“e naatne heen bonii wattannde."
  58,9,"Eey mon mon gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e si on ndeeydii e nelaaЙ—o wotee ndeeyde e makko e bakkaat e aГұanaagal e woopde nelaaЙ—o, ndeeydee e Й—iggere e kulol Alla mbo mooЙ“oyteЙ—on to makko."
  58,10,"Pellet gunndo ko e seytaane ngam o sunina Й“een gooЙ—inЙ“e o lorotaaЙ“e hay ndiga si wona e sakkitoore Alla, e dow Alla woni ko gooЕӢЙ—iЙ“e mbakkilto."
  58,11,"Eey mon mon gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e si on mbiyaama yaacne e joЙ—le yaacne Alla njaajnana mon, si on mbi'aama umme, ummЙ—on Alla Й“amta Й“een gooЕӢЙ—in Й“e e mon e joman en ganndal darajaaji, Alla na kumpatii ko ngolloton ko."
  58,12,"Eey mon gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e si on ndeeydii e nelaaЙ—o tottire e ndeeyu mon sadak, ko Й—uum Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude e mon ko Й—uum Й“uri laaЙ“de, si on keЙ“aani Alla de ko jaafatooЙ—o jurmotooЙ—o."
  58,13,"Mbele on kul tottirde sadaka saanga ndeeydaton e nelaaЙ—o, si on tottiraani Alla jaЙ“ani on tuubuubuya, ndarnee juulde toottiron askal Й—oftoЙ—on Alla e nelaaЙ—o makko, Alla na kumpatii ko ngolloton ko."
  58,14,"Mbele a yii'aani Й“een heedninЙ“e aade en Й“e Alla tikkani Й“e njeyaaka e mon Й“e njeyaako e maЙ“Й“e, hoЙ“e ngooЙ—ndira penaale te hoЙ“e nganndi."
  58,15,"Alla heblaniiЙ“e lepte caЙ—tuЙ—e pellet bonii koЙ“e ngolluno ko."
  58,16,"Й“e nanngarii goonЙ—dooje mum en Й—e heedo, Й“e palii laawol Alla ngol, woodaniiЙ“e lepte koynooje."
  58,17,"Pellet, Й“een yedduЙ“e, jawle maЙ“Й“e Й—en e Й“iЙ—Й“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en duncantaaЙ“e e lepte Alla Й—en hay hu'unde. Ko Й“een Й—oon ngoni yimЙ“e yiite Й“een, kamЙ“e ko Й“e luttooЙ“e toon."
  58,18,"Г‘ande Alla umminiЙ“e kamЙ“e fof, Й“e ngooЙ—ndana mbo hono noЙ“e ngooЙ—ndaranta mon nih, hoЙ“e cikka won koЙ“e ngoni e dow mum, Й“e tigi ngoni fenooЙ“e Й“e."
  58,19,"Seytaane tehriiЙ“e o yejjitini Й“e jaЕӢtaade Alla ko Й“ee tigi ngoni fedde seytaane, pellet ko fedde seytaane woni pertuЙ“e."
  58,20,"ЖҒeen haЙ“atooЙ“e Alla e nelaaЙ—o makko,ko Й“een Й“uri hoyde."
  58,21,"Alla Гұaawi ma ni fool miin e nelaaЙ“e am, pellet Alla ko cemmbuЙ—o tedduЙ—o."
  58,22,"A heЙ“atah yimЙ“e gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e e Гұalawma cakkatiiЙ—o na njiЙ—andira e luundiiЙ“e Alla e nelaaЙ—o makko haysi Й“e ngonii baabiraaЙ“e mum en wolla Й“iЙ“Й“e wolla musiЙ“Й“e, wolla gorol mum en, ko Й“e Й“erЙ—e mum en mbinnda iimaan O semmbiniЙ“e e ruuhu ummade e makko, O naatnaЙ“e aljannaaji na dogo ley majji caatli Й“e duumo toon haa pooma, Alla weleeЙ“e Й“e mbele Alla, ko Й“een ngoni fedde Alla, ko fedde Alla tigi woni malaaЙ“e."
  59,1,"Kala ko woni ka kammuuji e ka leydi seninii Allah. Ko KaЕӢko woni pooluЙ—o , Г‘eeГұo on."
  59,2,"Ko KaЕӢko yaltini Й“een he'efareeЙ“e joom en defte en e galleeji mum en e mooЙ“du adanuru ndu, on cikkaana maЙ“e njaltu, Й“e cikki galli mum en Й—i ndeenatЙ“e e Alla, O ardiЙ“e Й—oЙ“e cikkaana, O werlii e Й“erЙ—e mum en kulol, hoЙ“e njirbinira galleeji maЙ“Й“e juuЙ—e mum en e juuЙ—e gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e, teskee onon joman en kakkillaaji."
  59,3,"Si alla farlaana e mum en yaltineede ma o leptuЙ“e e aduna woodanaЙ“e lepte yiite."
  59,4,"ЖҠuum, ko fii kamЙ“e Й“e lunndike Alla e nulaaЙ—o makko on. "Kala noon lunndiiЙ—o Alla e nulaaЙ—o makko on, pellet, alla ko caЙ—tuЙ—o lepte"."
  59,5,"Kala ko taЖҙЙ—on e tamaroowi wolla ngaccuЙ—onki hoki dari e pooЙ“e makki, ko e yamiroore alla ngam o hoyna faasiqeeЙ“e."
  59,6,"Ko Alla rutti fa'ade e nelaaЙ—o makko ummaade e mum en, on keГұaraaki e mum pucci wolla geloobi, kono Alla na wuurta nelaaЙ“e makko e dow mbo o wela, Alla na hattani kala hu'unde."
  59,7,"Ko Alla neemini e nelaaЙ—o mum e yimЙ“e gure dow, na woodani Alla e nelaaЙ—o makko e Й“adiiЙ“e nelaado e alyatitm en e miskineeЙ“e e Й“iy laawol ngam Й—um wa'asa yiilaade hakkunde alЙ—uЙ“e mon, ko nelaaЙ—o totti on Й“ame ko o haЙ—i on ngacce, ndeene Alla, pellet Alla ko caЙ—tuЙ—o lepte."
  59,8,"Woodani wa'asЙ“e yaltinaaЙ“e galleeji mum en e jawЙ—eele mum en hoЙ“e Й—aЙ“Й“a Й“ural ummaade e Alla e weluya hoЙ“e mballa Alla e nelaaЙ—o makko, ko Й“een de ngoni gooЕӢЙ—uЙ“e tigi."
  59,9,"E Й“een telliiЙ“e e madiina e iimaan ko adii Й“e, hoЙ“e njiЙ—i oon perЙ—o fa'ade e maЙ“Й“e Й“e keЙ“atah e Й“erЙ—e mum en tikkere koЙ“e totta ko, hoЙ“e Й“urna e dow ko*e mum en haysi hoЙ“e ngondi e ba'asal, kala mbo Alla reeni fittaandu mum e Й—awre, ko Й“een de ngoni malaaЙ“e Й“e."
  59,10,"E Й“een arЙ“e caggal mu'en na mbi'a joomo amen yaafa amen minen e musiЙ“Й“e amen adiiЙ“e amen e iimaan wota waЙ— e Й“erЙ—e amen cokotaagal wonan'de Й“een gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e,joomi amen ko aan woni enЙ—iiЙ—o jurmotooЙ—o."
  59,11,"Mbelr a yiaani Й“een naafaqinЙ“e wiiЙ“e musibbe mum en yedduЙ“e jiyaaЙ“e e yimЙ“e defte, si on njaltii pellet ma min njaltid e mon, min Й—ototaako e dow mon hay gooto, si on kaЙ“aama ma min mballu mon Alla na seedo koЙ“e fenooЙ“e."
  59,12,"SiЙ“e njaltinaama Й“e njaltidtah e mum en si Й“e kaЙ“aama Й“e mballataa Й“e siЙ“e mballiiЙ“e maЙ“e ndunta refti Й“e mballetaake."
  59,13,"Ko onon Й“uri sattu kulo e Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e ga ni e Alla, waЙ—i noon koЙ“e yimЙ“e Й“e paamatah."
  59,14,"Й“e kaЙ“atah e mon si wonah hoЙ“e e gure taartinaaЙ—e galli wolla caggal mahdeele bone maЙ“Й“e hakkunde mu'en na satti haЙ—a sikka koЙ“e gootum kono Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e na ceerti waЙ—i noon koЙ“e yimЙ“e Й“e kakkiltah."
  59,15,"Hona yeru Й“een adiiЙ“e Й“e ko Й“adii Й“e meeЙ—i lepte fiyaaku mum en woodaniiЙ“e lepte caЙ—tuЙ—e."
  59,16,"Ko hono seytaane de wi'i neЙ—Й—aЕӢke o yeddu, nde o yeddi o wi'i miin komi kisЙ—o e ma, miin mbiЙ—o huli Alla joom binnde o."
  59,17,"Laati batte mu'en kanЙ“e Й—iЙ—a ko yiite saasooЙ“e toon, Й—uum ko njoЙ“di tooГұooЙ“e."
  59,18,"Eehey mon gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e ndeente Alla, yo fittaandu ndaar kondu ardinani jannga kule alla pellet alla ko kumpatiiЙ—o ko ngolloton ko."
  59,19,"Wote ngone hono Й“een yejjitЙ“e Alla, o yejjitini Й“e pittaali mum'en ko Й“een ngoni faasiqeeЙ“e."
  59,20,"YimЙ“e yiite e yimЙ“e aljanna potaanih, ko yimЙ“e aljanna ngoni foolЙ“e."
  59,21,"Si min tellinna o alquraana e dow hooseere ma a yiinde honde luli honde fetta ngam hulde Alla Й—i tinndi emin piyaniЙ—i yimЙ“e ko ngam Й“e miijo."
  59,22,"Ko KaЕӢko woni deweteeЙ—o deweteeЙ—o e goonga alah si wonah KaЕӢko, ganndo ko wirni e ka wirnaaki kaЕӢko woni joom yurmeende huftadinnde e yurmeende heeriinde."
  59,23,"Ko KaЕӢko Alla mbo deweteeЙ—o e goonga alah si wonah KaЕӢko laamЙ—o ceniiЙ—o kisЙ—o gooЕӢЙ—iЙ—o kiilndiiЙ—o tedduЙ—o cemmbinЙ—o mawЙ—o senaare woodanii Alla e koЙ“e ndenndinta mbo ko."
  59,24,"Ko KaЕӢko woni Alla takЙ—o gootnuЙ—o mbaadinЙ—o tagu woodanii mbo inЙ—e Й“urЙ—e moЖҙЖҙude, woodanii mbo ko woni e ndeer kammuuji e leydi ko KaЕӢko woni pooloowo mbo hay gooto foolatah Г‘eeГұЖҙuЙ—o."
  60,1,"Eehey mon gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e wote njaggire aГұЙ“e mi e aГұЙ“e mon heetЙ“e hoЙ—on mberno e mum en gilli te koЙ“e yedduЙ“e goongo garЙ—o o e mon, hoЙ“e njaltina nelaaЙ—o e onon sabu tan on ngooЕӢЙ—anii Alla joomi mon, tawde on njalti sabu jihaadi e laawol am e Й—aЙ“jude weluya am, hoЙ—on cuurtanaЙ“e kabaruuji juulЙ“e ngam Й“e mbele mon, mbiЙ—a anndi ko cuuЙ—oton e ko Й“anngiЙ—on, kala e mon baЙ—Й—o Й—uum o majji laawol peewngol."
  60,2,"SiЙ“e peewnatiima e mon Й“e ngonana mon aГұЙ“e Й“e mberta juuЙ—e maЙ“Й“e e Й—emЙ—e mu' en e mbaadi mbonndi Й“e njiЙ—iina nde ngonaton heefereeЙ“e."
  60,3,"Nafatah on enЙ—ameeje mon wona Й“iЙ“Й“e mon Гұande darnga O seernda hakkunde mon Alla na yi'a ko ngolloton ko."
  60,4,"Woodanii on Гұeemtinirde moЖҙЖҙere e Ibraahiima e Й“een wonduЙ“e e mum nde Й“e mbi'i pellet ko min hisЙ“e e mon e ko ndewaton ko wona Alla ko, min njeddii on feeГұi hakkunde men ngaГұngu e tikkere haa pooma haa ngooЕӢЙ—inon Alla gooto o, si wona konngol Ibraahiima wonan'de baaba makko pellet ma mi yaafnano ma, mi alanaama hay hu'unde ka Alla, joomi amen min mbakkaliima e ma ko e ma min ndutti e ko e ma woni wattande."
  60,5,"joomi amen wota waЙ— min fitina wonan'de Й“een yedduЙ“e, yaafa amen joomi amen pellet ko aan woni tedduЙ—o mbo fooletaake ГұeeГұЙ—uЙ—o."
  60,6,"GooЕӢЙ—i,woodani mon e maЙ“Й“e Гұeemtanirgal moЖҙЖҙal wonan'de oon joortiiЙ—o e Alla e Гұalngu La'akara, oon Й—uurniiЙ—o noon pellet Alla ko gala jettaaЙ—o."
  60,7,"Yaama nde Alla waЙ—ata hakkunde mon e Й“een Й“e ngaГұandirЙ—on e mu'en gilli, Alla ko kattanЙ—o Alla ko kafroowo bakkatuuji jurmotooЙ—o."
  60,8,"Alla haЙ—ataa mon Й“een Й“e kaЙ“aani e mon e diine Й“e njaltinaani on e galleeji mon nde Й—iggantonЙ“e nuunЙ—on fa'ade e maЙ“Й“e pellet Alla ko jiЙ—Й—o nuun'Й—uЙ“e."
  60,9,"Kono Alla haЙ—ata on ko Й“een haЙ“atooЙ“e on e diine yaltinooЙ“e on galleeji mon Й“e mballandiri e yaltinde on, nde keetnaton Й“e kala baЙ—Й—o Й“e keeda ko Й“een ngoni tooГұooЙ“e."
  60,10,"Eehey mon gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e si gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e rewЙ“e ngarii e mon njaribeeЙ“e Alla na anndi iimaan mu'en, si on nganndii koЙ“e gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e wotee ndutteeЙ“e e he'eferЙ“e Й“e ndaganaaki he'eferЙ“e Й“e heeferЙ“e Й“e kadi ndaganaaki Й“e, totteeЙ“e koЙ“e nafqi ko bakkaat ala e mon nde ndesaton Й“e si on tottii Й“e teЕӢe maЙ“Й“e wote nanngite piЙ“le rewЙ“e he'eferЙ“e naamnee ko nafquЙ—on kamЙ“e ne yo Й“e naamna ko Й“e nafqi ko, ko Й—uum woni Гұaawoore Alla hakkunde mon Alla ko gannda ГұeeГұЙ—uЙ—o."
  60,11,"Si hu'unde faatiima mon e rewЙ“e mon fa'ade e he'efareeЙ“e leptuЙ—on Й“e tottee Й“een Й“e rewЙ“e mu'en njahi fotde koЙ“e tottirno kulee Alla mbo ngoonЕӢЙ—in Й—on O."
  60,12,"Eehey ma annabi si rewЙ“e juulЙ“e ngari e ma hoЙ“e coodandira e ma nde Й“e ndenndinta Alla e hay gooto,ngujjata njinata, mbarata sukaaЙ“e mu' en,ngaddata fenaande fekindaande hakkunde juuЙ—e mu' en e koyЙ—e mum en,Й“e ngoopataa ma e moЖҙЖҙere ndeen de soodandir e mum 'en, yaafnanoЙ“e Alla, pellet Alla ko jaafatooЙ—o jurmotooЙ—o"
  60,13,"Eehey mjon goooЕӢЙ—iЙ“e wote keetne yimЙ“e Й“e Alla tikkani e dow mu'en, Й“e piЙ“tiima e La'akara hono no he'eferЙ“e piЙ“tari e yimЙ“e genaale."
  61,1,"Kala ko woni ka kammuuli e ka leydi seninii Allah. Ko KaЕӢko woni pooluЙ—o, Г‘eeГұo oon."
  61,2,"Eehey mon gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e ko waЙ—i hoЙ—on kaala ko on mbaЙ—ata."
  61,3,"Mawni tikkere ka Alla nde kaalaton ko on ngollata."
  61,4,"Pellet Alla na yiЙ—i Й“een haЙ“ateeЙ“e e laawol Alla heЙ“e ngoni saffeeji hono maadi fotndaandi."
  61,5,"Tumo nde o maakani yimЙ“e makko, yimЙ“e am holko taki hoЙ—on lora mi te hoЙ—on nganndi komi nelaaЙ—o Alla fa'ade e mon, ndeЙ“e ooГұi Alla ooГұi Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Alla feewnata yimЙ“e faasiqeeЙ“e."
  61,6,"E nde Iisa Й“iy Maryama maaki ehey mon Й“iЙ“Й“e Israa'iil komi nelaaЙ—o Alla tigi fa'ade e mon gooЕӢЙ—inЙ—o ko woni ko e ye'esam am Tawreet e beltinoowo nelaaЙ—o garoowo caggal hombo wiyee Ahmadu, nde o anndani Й“e hujjaaji laaЙ“Й—i Й“e mbi'ii Й—um ko mbilewu Й“anngungu."
  61,7,"Alah Й“urЙ—a tooГұde oon pekandiiЙ—o e dow Alla te hombo noddee e islaam, Alla feewnata tooГұooЙ“e."
  61,8,"HoЙ“e paala Гұifrude annoore Alla nde kunduЙ—e maЙ“Й“e, Alla ko timminoowo annoore makko nde haysi he'efareeЙ“e ngaГұii."
  61,9,"Ko Kanoko woni NulirЙ—o NulaaЙ—o makko on peewal e diina goonga, fii yo o Й“amtu ka e hoore kala diina, hay si sirkooЙ“e Й“en ngaГұii [Й—um]."
  61,10,"Ehey mon gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e mbele mi tinndinta on njulaagu ndaЙ—natngu on e lepte mu'usЙ—e."
  61,11,"NgooЕӢЙ—inon Alla e nelaaЙ—o makko mbaЙ—iron jihaadi e laawol makko jawdi mon e pittaali mon ko Й—uum Й“uri on moЖҙЖҙande si on ngonii annduЙ“e."
  61,12,"Alla hafrana on bakkatuuji mon, O naatna on aljannaaji Й—i caatli ndogata ley mum e koЙ—orЙ—e belЙ—e ka aljanna adan ko Й—uum woni malal manngal."
  61,13,"E goЙ—Й—um ko njiЙ—Й—on ballal ummaade e Alla e uddital Й“adingal weltin juulЙ“e Й“e."
  61,14,"Ehey mon gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e ngonee wallooЙ“e Alla hono no Iisa Ibnu Mariya maaki suЙ“aaЙ“e mum hombo wallata mi fa'ade e Alla suЙ“aaЙ“e mum mbii ko minen ngoni wallooЙ“e Alla, heen fedde e Banii Isra'iil goonЙ—ini won'de nde yeddi min cemmbini gooЕӢЙ—innde nde e dow aГұЙ“e mum en Й“e ngonti foolЙ“e."
  62,1,"Kala ko woni nder kammuuji e leydi hino seninnde Allah, LaamЙ—o, ceniiЙ—o, PooluЙ—o, Г‘eeГұo on."
  62,2,"Ko KaЕӢko nuli e humammbinneeЙ“e Й“een NulaaЙ—o jiyaaЙ—o e maЙ“Й“e, himo janngana Й“e Aayeeje makko Й—en, o laЙ“Й“ina Й“e, o anndina Й“e deftere nden e Sunna on, hay si tawiino ko adii Й—uum, Й“e laatino e majjere Й“anngude."
  62,3,"(O nuli mo) kadi e woЙ—Й“e goo e maЙ“Й“e, Й“e hawrondiraali e Й“een taho. Ko KaЕӢko woni pooluЙ—o, Г‘eeГұo on."
  62,4,"ЖҠuum ko Й“ural Allah, Homo okka ngal mo o muuyani. Allah ko Jom Й“ural mawnngal."
  62,5,"Misal ronndinaaЙ“e Tawreeta Й“een refti Й“e nigolliraali nde, no wa'i wa mbabba ronndii mba defte. Yeru yimЙ“e yeddooЙ“e aayeeje Alla Й—een bonii. Allah feewnataa yimЙ“e tooГұooЙ“e Й“een."
  62,6,"Maaku: "Ko onon yo HuudiЕӢkooЙ“e ! Si on aaЖҙike wonan'de ko on yiЙ—aaЙ“e Allah ko wanaa yimЙ“e heddiiЙ“e Й“en, haray njelee maayde, si tawii ko on ngoonguЙ“e"."
  62,7,"ЖҒe njelotaako nde muk, sabu ko juuЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en ngardini kon. Allah ko gannduЙ—o tooГұooЙ“e Й“een."
  62,8,"Maaku: "Ndee maayde nde ndogoton, pellet, ko nde hawraynde e mon. Refti ndutteЙ—on to oon gannduЙ—o ko wirnii e ko feeГұi, O kumpita on ko ngollaynoЙ—on kon"."
  62,9,"Ko onon yo gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e ! Si juulde nden noddinanaama Гұalnde Juma, njaccee e jaЕӢtagol Allah, ngacciton njeengu. Ko Й—uum Й“uri moЖҙЖҙannde on, si tawno ko on annduЙ“e !"
  62,10,"Si juulde nden gasii, haray ca,akitee ka leydi, Й—aЙ“Й“on Й“ural Allah ngal [woni arsike], jaЕӢtoron innde Allah ko Й—uuЙ—i, mbelajo'o on maloyte."
  62,11,"Si Й“e nji'ii njeeyngu maa fijindaaru, Й“e hammira toon, Й“e ngaccama hiЙ—a darii. Maaku: "Ko ko woni ka Allah kon Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude beleeЙ—e e njulaaku. Ko Allah Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude e arsikooЙ“e Й“een"."
  63,1,"Si naafiqiiЙ“e Й“een ngrii e maa, Й“e mbi'a: "MiЙ—en ceedii won'de ko a NulaaЙ—o Allah". Allah no anndi won'de pellet, ko a NulaaЙ—o makko; Allah no seedii won'de pellet, naafiqiiЙ“e Й“een ko fenooЙ“e."
  63,2,"ЖҒe njogitorri goondooje maЙ“Й“e Й—een heedo, Й“e paddii laawol Allah ngol. Pellet, fii ko Й“e ngollaynoo kon bonii!"
  63,3,"ЖҠuim noon ko tawde Й“e gooЕӢЙ—inii, refti Й“e njeddi, Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en notaa e mum; kamЙ“e on Й“e paamataa."
  63,4,"Si a yi'ii Й“e, Й“alli maЙ“Й“e welete; si Й“e wowlii, a nana konnguЙ—i maЙ“Й“e Й—in. HiЙ“e mba'i wa pecce Й“aaraaЙ—e, hiЙ“e cikka kala eewnaango ko e hoore maЙ“Й“e. Ko Й“een tigi ngoni aГұЙ“e Й“en, reenoЙ“e. Allah huЙ—ii Й“e ! Ko honno Й“e nkiiltiratool (e goonga) !"
  63,5,"Si Й“e mbianaama: "ngaree NulaaЙ—o Allah on imsinanoo on", Й“e hayla ko'e maЙ“Й“e Й—een, nji'aa hiЙ“e Й—uurnoo hara ko Й“e townitiiЙ“e."
  63,6,"Hino fota e maЙ“Й“e, foti a imsinani Й“e maa hara a imsinanaaki Й“e: Allah yaafotaako Й“e fes, pellet, Allah feewnataa yimЙ“e faasiqiiЙ“e Й“een."
  63,7,"Ko Й“een ngoni wiooЙ“e wote nafqee wonЙ“e e sera nelaaЙ—Г  haa Й“e ceerta na woodani Alla moftirЙ—i kammuuji e leydi kono tan naafiqeeЙ“e Й“e paamatah."
  63,8,"HoЙ“e mbia si en nduttiima Madiina ma Й“urЙ“e teddude njaltin Й“urЙ“e hoyde Й“e, woodanii Alla teddungal e nelaaЙ—o makko e gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“e, kono tan naafige en nganndah."
  63,9,"Eehey mon gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e woto sokli mon jawЙ—eele mon e Й“iЙ“Й“e mon gaa e innude Alla kala baЙ—Й—o Й—uum ko Й“een ngoni pertuЙ“e Й“e."
  63,10,"Nafqe ko Alla arsakini on ko, ko adii nde maayde arata e gooto e mon o wi'a joom am a leelnantaa kam haa e happu Й“adiiЙ—o mi sakkoro mi wona e moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e Й“e."
  63,11,"Alla neeЙ“nantah hay fittaandu wo'oturu si happu manndu arii Alla na humpatii ko ngolloton ko."
  64,1,"Ina subhinanoo Alla kala ko woni e kammuuji e ka lesdi, na woodani mbo laamu na woodani mbo jettooje ko O kattanЙ—o kala hu'unde."
  64,2,"Ko KaЕӢko tagi on ina e mon ke'efeera ina e mon gooЕӢЙ—inЙ—o Alla na yi'a ko ngolloton ko."
  64,3,"O tagrii kammuuji e leydi goongo o mbaadini on o moЖҙЖҙini mbaadiili mon ko e makko woni battane mon."
  64,4,"Hombo anndi ko woni e kammuuji e leydi hombo anndi ko mbirnaton e ko Й“annginton Alla na anndi ko woni e Й“erЙ—e."
  64,5,"Mbela araani e mon kabaruuji Й“een yeddunooЙ“e ko adi,Й“e meeЙ—i lepte fiyakuuji mum en woodaniiЙ“e lepte mu'usЙ—e."
  64,6,"Woni sabu Й—een lepte noon ko nelaaЙ“e mum en na ngaddanatnoo Й“e dallillaaji Й“annguЙ—i Й“e mbi'a ee ko Й“anndiyankooЙ“e peewnata min,Й“e njeddi, Alla yon'danii,Alla ko galo jettaaЙ—o."
  64,7,"He'eferЙ“e Й“e Й“e aaЖҙiima Й“e ummintaake,maaku oho kay ma on ummine mi wooЙ—ndirii joom am ma on ummine,refti ma on kumpite ko ngolluuЙ—on, Й—uum na newanii Alla."
  64,8,"NgooЕӢЙ—inee Alla e nelaaЙ—o makko e annoore nde o tellini pellet Alla ko kumpatiiЙ—o ko ngolloton ko."
  64,9,"Гұande o renndi mon Гұalngu denndingol oon woni Гұalngu basandiral, ka gooЕӢЙ—inЙ—o Alla o golli ko lobbi o momtone boneeji mum, o naatna mbo aljanaaji Й—i caatli ndogata les majji Й“e caasa toon haa pooma, ko Й—uum woni malal manngal."
  64,10,"Ko Й“een yedduЙ“e Й“e njeddi aayeeje amen ngoni yimЙ“e yiite saasooЙ“e e henge, nge bonii battane."
  64,11,"Musiiba heЙ“ata hay gooto si wona e sakkitoore Alla, kala gooЕӢЙ—inЙ—o Alla O feewna Й“ernde makko, Alla na anndi kala hu'unde."
  64,12,"ЖҠoftee Alla, Й—oftoЙ—on NulaaЙ—o on, ndeentoЙ—on ! Si on nduЕӢitii, nganndee pellet, ko fawii nulaaЙ—o Amen on tan, ko jottingol Й“anngina."
  64,13,"Allaahu alah deweteeЙ—o e goongo si wona KaЕӢko, ko e dow makko goonЙ—inЙ“e mbakkilato."
  64,14,"Eehey mon gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e pellet ina e yogo e suddiiЙ“e mon e Й“iЙ“Й“e mon ko aГұЙ“e mon ndeenteeЙ“e, si on njaafiima on njarliima noon Alla ko jaafatooЙ—o jurmotooЙ—o."
  64,15,"Ngandee pellet, jawЙ—e mon Й—een e Й“iЙ—Й“e mon Й“een ko fitina ina ka Alla njoЙ“di mawndi."
  64,16,"Kulee Alla ko kattanЙ—on nanee Й—oftaЙ—on nafqe ko Й—uum Й“uri moЖҙЖҙan'de pittaali mon, oon deenaaЙ—o fittaandu makko e Й—awre, ko Й“een ngoni malaaЙ“e Й“e."
  64,17,"Si on Гұamlii Alla Гұamaande moЖҙЖҙere o sowana Й—uum en nde, o yaafoЙ“e Alla ko jettoowo ko muГұЙ—o."
  64,18,"GannduЙ—o mbirniiЙ—i e feeГұuЙ—i, mawЙ—o, ГұeeГұЙ—o."
  65,1,"Eehey ma annabi si on ceerii suddiiЙ“e ceereeЙ“e e edda mu' en tonnge edda o, kulee Alla joomon wotee njaltineeЙ“e e cuuЙ—i mu'en wotoЙ“e njaltu si wona Й“e mbaЙ— paЕӢkare peeГұЙ—e ko Й—iin ngoni keeri Alla kala jawtuЙ—o keerol Alla o tooГұi hoore makko, a anndah yaama de Alla waЙ—ata caggal Й—uum fiyaaku."
  65,2,"Si Й“e njottinii edda mu'en nanngireeЙ“e no moЖҙЖҙi wollo ceerdonЙ“e no moЖҙЖҙi,ceednon seedeeji Й—iЙ—i ummaade e mon ndarnee seedanfaagal fii Alla ko Й—uum woni ko waajete wonan'de oon gooЕӢЙ—inЙ—o Alla e Гұalnde sakkatiinde kala deentiiЙ—o Alla,Alla waЙ—ana mbo yaltirde."
  65,3,"O arsikina mbo to o sikkaana, kala bakkaliiЙ—o e Alla yonii mbo, pellet yamiroore Alla nde ko yottotoonde, Alla waЙ—ani kala hu'unde fotde mum."
  65,4,"Й“een suddiiЙ“e mon fiЙ“tiiЙ“e fiilayru si on cikkatiima edda mu'en ko lebbi tati e Й“een Й“e piilataako edda mu' en ko lebbi tati, debadeedi en noon edda maЙ“Й“e gasata ko nde Й“e njibini, kala kulЙ—o Alla o waЙ—ana mbo newaare e fiyaaku makko."
  65,5,"Й—uum ko Гұaawoore Alla o tellaniinde e mon, kala kulЙ—o Alla o hafrana mbo bakkatuuji makko, o mawninana mbo njoЙ“di."
  65,6,"KoЙ—neeЙ“e Й—o koЙ—Й—on fotde kattane mon wotee loreeЙ“e ngam Й“ittinan'deЙ“e, nafqeeЙ“e ha Й“e keЙ“to tawde koЙ“e korinoo Й“e, si wonii Й“e muyninanii on njonnee Й“e njoЙ“di mu' en njandire moЖҙЖҙere hakkunde mon, si on cattiraama yo goЙ—Й—o muynin mbo."
  65,7,"Yo nafqu gala e ngalu makko he, oon paaЙ—aaЙ—o noon yo nafqu e ko Alla totti mbo ko,Alla fawata hay fittaandu si wona ko tottindu ko, ma Alla waЙ— caggal satteende newuya."
  65,8,"Heewii saare saliinde yamiroore joom mum e nelaaЙ“o mum, min kaasbii nde haasboore saЙ—tunde Min leptinnde lepte bon'Й—e."
  65,9,"Nde meeЙ—i e lepte golle mayre laati batte fiyaaku mayre ko perte."
  65,10,"Alla heblaniЙ“e lepte caЙ—tuЙ—e kulee Alla onon joom en kakkillaaji Й“een gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e, Alla tellinii e mu' en ko siftinta."
  65,11,"NelaaЙ—o taratooЙ—o e mon aayeeje Й“annguЙ—e ngam o yaltina Й“een gooЕӢЙ—in Й“e ngolluЙ“e golle lobbe ummaade e niwre fa'ade e annoore, kala gooЕӢЙ—inЙ—o Alla golli ko moЖҙЖҙi O naatna mbo aljannaaji Й—i caatli ilata les majji Й“e nduumo toon, ko goongo Alla moЖҙЖҙinanii mbo arsuka."
  65,12,"Alla talЙ—o kammuuji jeeЙ—iЙ—i e leydi yeru majji, yamiroore Alla na tello hakkunde majji ngam nganndon wonde Alla ko kattanЙ—o kala hu'unde Alla fiiltariima kala hu'unde e ganndal."
  66,1,"Ehey ma annabi ko taki ana harmina ko Alla daknan ma sabu Й—aЙ“Й“ude welnaade suddiiЙ“e ma, Alla ko jaafatooЙ—o jurmotooЙ—o."
  66,2,"Alla farlii e mon daktinde gooЙ—ndooje mon Alla ko keedo mon ko kaЕӢko woni ganndo Г‘eeГұЙ—o."
  66,3,"Tuma nde annabi deeyi fa'ade e yogo e suddiiЙ“e makko yeewtere, nde o habri yeewtere nde, Alla feГұГұinani mbo o anndini yogo e yeewtere he, o falii heen yogo, nde o habri mbo Й—um o wi'i hombo habru ma Й—uum o maaki habrii kam Gannda KumpatiiЙ—o."
  66,4,"Si on tuubi fa'ade e Alla sabu Й“erЙ—e mon Й—e ooГұinooma si on mballandirii e dow makko, ko Alla woni ballo makko e jIbriil e gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e e Malaeyka en caggal Й—uum koЙ—i ballooji."
  66,5,"Yaama de joom makko si o ceeriiЙ“e nde o wostantoo mbo Й“urЙ“e mon moЖҙЖҙude juulЙ“e gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й—oftiiЙ“e tuubooЙ“e rewooЙ“e Alla hoorooЙ“e SeemedЙ“e e boomi."
  66,6,"Ehey mon gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e ndeene ko'e mon e koreeji mon e yiite docate mannge ko yimЙ“e e kaaЖҙe ina e dow henge maleykaaji tekkuЙ—i cattuЙ—i Й—i ngoopata ko Alla yamariЙ—i te hoЙ—i ngolla ko Alla yamiriЙ—i."
  66,7,"Ehey mon he'eferЙ“e wote ngantinee hannde njoЙ“eteЙ—on tan koko ngollatna Й—on ko."
  66,8,"Ehey mon gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e tuubee fa'ade e Alla tuubgol laaЙ“ngol yaama joomi mon hafrana on bonЙ—i mon o naatna mon aljannaaji na ila ley majji caatli, Гұande Alla hoynata annabi e Й“een gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e wond'ude e mum, annoore mum en na yaha ye'esa mum en e Гұaama mu' en hoЙ“e mbiya joomi amen timminan amen annoore amen yaafa min pellet ko a kattanЙ—o kala hu'unde."
  66,9,"Ehey ma annabiijo, haЙ“ e he'eferЙ“e Й“en e naafiqiiЙ“e Й“en, saЙ—tinanaa Й“e; weerde maЙ“Й“e nden ko Jahannama, nge bonii ruttorde."
  66,10,"Alla fiyani yeru wonan'de Й“een yedduЙ“e soknaaja Nuuhu e luutu Й“e ngoniina e les jiyaaЙ“e amen Й—iЙ—o moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e Й“e njanfiiЙ“e Й—uum nafaaniЙ“e ka Alla hay hu'unde,Й“e mbi'e naatee yiite wond'ude e naatЙ“e Й“e."
  66,11,"Alla fiyani yeru gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“e debbo fir'awna nde o wiino joom am mahanam ka ma suudu ka aljanna ndaЙ—ndaa mi e fir'awna e golle mum, daЙ—ndam e yimЙ“e tooГұooЙ“e."
  66,12,"E Maryama Й“iy imraana oon deenЙ—o hoore makko e jina min ngutti heen ruuhu amen o gooЕӢЙ—ini konngi joomiiko e defte makko o tawa e Й—oftiiЙ“e Й“e."
  67,1,"Mo laamu woni e juuЙ—e mum mawnii, ko KaЕӢko woni kattanЙ—o kala hu'unde."
  67,2,"Oon tagirЙ—o maayde e nguurndam, fii ndaarndagol on ko hommbo e mo'on Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude golle. Ko KaЕӢko woni pooluЙ—o, kaforoowo on."
  67,3,"On takЙ—o kammuuji jeeЙ—iЙ—i pawondirЙ—i. A yi'ataa Й“ura-Й“urda e tagoore jom hinaraЕӢke On. Yiiltu ndaarЙ—e maa Й—en (daaraa). Taw si a yi'ay ce'ekol?"
  67,4,"Refti nduttaa ndaarЙ—e Й—en laaЙ“i Й—iЙ—i, gite maa Й—een nduttoto e maaЙ—a hara ko Й—e hoyЙ—e, taЖҙiiЙ—e."
  67,5,"GooЕӢЙ—ii Min cuЙ—inirii kammu aduna nguun [koode] pitilli, Min mbaЙ—i Й—e fiЙ—irЙ—e seytanuuji, Min kebilani Й“e lette huЙ“Й“unge nge."
  67,6,"Hino woodani Й“een yedduЙ“e Joomi mum, lette Jahannama. Nge bonii ruttorde !"
  67,7,"Si Й“e mbeddaama e ndeer magge, Й“e nanirat nge ha'acaango, hara henge fata."
  67,8,"Henge eЙ“Й“a fultagol, sabu tikkere ndeen. Tuma kala nde dental bugaa e magge, ayninaaЙ“e nge Й“een lamndoo Й“e : "E hara jeertinoowo araano e mo'on?""
  67,9,"ЖҒe mbi'a: "Pellet ! Jeertinoowo arno e amen tigi, kono min njeddi min mbi'i: Allah jippinaani hay e hu'unde, on ngonaani si wonaa e ndeer majjere mawnde"."
  67,10,"ЖҒe mbi'ita : "Si miЙ—en nanaynoo maa hara meЙ—en haqqilaynoo, min njeyetanooke e yimЙ“e HuЙ“Й“unge ngeen"."
  67,11,"ЖҒe qirritii bakkatuuji maЙ“Й“e Й—in. Halakuyee woodanii joom en HuЙ“Й“aynge ngen."
  67,12,"Pellet, hulooЙ“e Joomi mum Й“een ka wirnii, hino woodani Й“en haforaneede e njoЙ“di mawndi."
  67,13,"CuuЙ—ee konnguЙ—i mon maa Й“anninon Й—um. KaЕӢko on ko o gannduЙ—o ko woni e ndeer Й“erЙ—e."
  67,14,"E hara takЙ—o oon anndaa? Ko KaЕӢko le woni newiiЙ—o, kumpitiiЙ—o oon."
  67,15,"Ko KaЕӢko waЙ—ani on leydi ndin eeltaandi : haray njehee e seraaji mayri, Гұaamon e arsike makko. Ko ka makko woni ummital ngal."
  67,16,"E on kooli on gon'Й—o ka kammu nde o munnataa e mo'on leydi ndin, tawa yoo hindi dilla?"
  67,17,"Kaa on kooli On gon'Й—o ka kammu nde Oo wurtataa e mon henndu bippooru? Aray nde anndon ko honno woni jeertinaango am ngon."
  67,18,"Sellii adinooЙ“e Й“een Й—oon Й“en njeddiino. Taskii ko honno leЙ“te an Й—en mbattinirnoo!"
  67,19,"E Й“ee nji'aani colli Й—iin dow maЙ“Й“e, hiЙ—i fonta gabitannji Й—i Гұobba? [Won'de] jogitaaki Й—in si wonaa Joom hinaraЕӢke on. Pellet, ko o deenЙ—o kala hu'unde."
  67,20,"E ko hommbo woni on konuujo mum wallata on hara wonaa Jom hinaraЕӢke on? Tigi on, he'eferЙ“e Й“een ngonaani si wonaa e ndeer hodo."
  67,21,"E ko hommbo woni arsikoowo on, si o jogitike arsike makko on? si ko woni, Й“e duumike e Жҙaggere e goЙ—Й—itagol."
  67,22,"Kere ko on jahoowo no hippi ye'eso mum Й“uri feewde? Kaa ko on jahoowo no fotondiri e laawol pocciingol?"
  67,23,"Maaku: "Ko KaЕӢko woni ko fuЙ—Й—i oon, O waЙ—ani on nanЙ—e e giiЙ—e e Й“erЙ—e". Kono famЙ—ii ko njettoton [neema]."
  67,24,"Maaku: "Ko KaЕӢko woni ca'aktuЙ—o on leydi, ko ka makko kadi woni ko mooЙ“itoyteЙ—on"."
  67,25,"HeЙ“e mbi'a: "Ko honnde tuma woni ndee fodoore, si tawii ko on gooЕӢЙ—uЙ“e?""
  67,26,"Maaku : "nganndee anndugol [fii Darnagl] ko ka Allah woni. Miiin on ko Mi jeertinoowo [tan] Й“anngina"."
  67,27,"Nde Й“e nji'oyta (leЙ“te) Й—en ka Й“adii, j'eece yedduЙ“e Й“en suni j'eece he'eferЙ“e, [Й“e] mbi'anee : "Ko Й—uum Й—oo woni ko Й—aЙ“Й“atnoЙ—on"."
  67,28,"Maaku : "Yeetee kam, si Allah Жҙettitii kam miin e wonndiiЙ“e am maa o yurmaama min, ko hommbo daЙ—ndata he'eferЙ“e Й“een lepte mu'usuuЙ—e?""
  67,29,"Maaku : "Ko KaЕӢko Joom hinaraЕӢke oon. Min ngooЕӢЙ—inii mo, ko e makko kadi men fawii. Aray nde nganndon ko hommbo woni e majjere Й“anngunde"."
  67,30,"Maaku : "njeewtee kam , si ndiyam mon Й—am wattinii Й“eeЙ“uЙ—am, ko hommbo addanta on ndiyam ilatЙ—am?""
  68,1,"Nuun. Mi wooЙ—ndirii kuЙ—ol e ko Й“e mbinndirta ko!"
  68,2,"Aan a wonaa, sabu neema Joommaa o, kaangaaЙ—o."
  68,3,"Ko pellet, hino woodani-ma njoЙ“di ndi taЖҙondirtaa."
  68,4,"E ko pellet, haЙ—a e jikku mawЙ—o."
  68,5,"Aray nde nji'aa, Й“e nji'a kamЙ“e kadi"
  68,6,"ko hombo e mon woni kaangaaЙ—o oon."
  68,7,"Pellet, ko Joommaa Й“uri anndude majjuЙ—o on laawol makko ngol, ko KaЕӢko kadi Й“uri anndude feewЙ“e Й“e."
  68,8,"Wota a tefto yeddooЙ“e Й“en."
  68,9,"HeЙ“e njiЙ—i si a newantono (Й“e), Й“e newano-(maa)."
  68,10,"Wota a tefto kadi kala Й—uuЙ—uЙ—o woondugol, koyЙ—o."
  68,11,"Й—uuЙ—uЙ—o Гұo'ougol, Й—uuЙ—uЙ—o yaarugol baЙ—di."
  68,12,"Й—uuЙ—uЙ—o kaЙ—gol moЖҙЖҙere, jaggitoowo, bakkodi'Й—o."
  68,13,"yo'ora-Й“erndeejo e hoore Й—um, keЙ“iraaЙ—o nii(.Й“iy jina)."
  68,14,"fii o wonii joom jawdi e Й“iЙ—Й“e."
  68,15,"Si aayeeje amen Й—een janngaama e [tawnde] makko, o wi'a: "Ko tinndi adinooЙ“e"."
  68,16,"Aray nde min maandina mo e hoore kinal."
  68,17,"Min njarribor Й“e wano Min njarribornoo jeyЙ“e ngesa mba : fewndo Й“een ngooЙ—ndunoo pellet, Й“e coГұat ba subaka ko Й“e dawЙ“e."
  68,18,"Й“e itti tinaani [wi'ide] :"Si Allah jaЙ“ii"."
  68,19,"Jayngol immori ka Joomi maa ari huuЙ“iti ba tawi heЙ“e Й—aanii."
  68,20,"Ba wa'iti wa jemma Й“aleejo."
  68,21,"ЖҒe noddindiri bimmbi oon :"
  68,22,""Kori ndawee ta ngesa mon, si tawii ko on soГұooЙ“e"."
  68,23,"ЖҒe pokkiti heЙ“e Й—uumbo."
  68,24,"Won'de "miskiino woo naatataa e mabba hannde"."
  68,25,"ЖҒe ndawidi e Й—awugol [wa'asuЙ“e Й“een] ko Й“e eЙ“Й“uЙ“e."
  68,26,"Nde Й“e nji'unoo ba, Й“e mbi'i: "Pellet, min majjii [laawol ngol]"."
  68,27,"wurin ko min Й—awaaЙ“e!"."
  68,28,"ЖҒurЙ—o Й“e moЖҙЖҙude oon wi'i: "mi wi'anaano on : haanii ko cubbunhinoЙ—on?""
  68,29,"ЖҒe mb'i: "Senaare woodanii Joomi amen ! Pellet, hari ko min tooГұЙ“e"."
  68,30,"WoЙ—Й“e e maЙ“Й“e feewtiti Й“eya, heЙ“e pelindira."
  68,31,"ЖҒe mbi'i: "Ee bone amen ! Pellet, hari ko min bewЙ“e."
  68,32,"Hino gasa ka Joomi amen wattitana min Й“uri baan Й—on moЖҙЖҙude. Ko ka Joomi amen ko min reerЙ—ube e [ya'afeede] ."
  68,33,"Ko noon tigi woni leЙ“te Й—een; ko lette La'akara Й—een non Й“uri manude, sinno heЙ“e nganndunoo !"
  68,34,"Pellet, hino woodani gooЕӢЙ—uЙ“e Й“een ka Joomi maЙ“Й“e, Aljannaaji ne'ema."
  68,35,"Kere Min mbaЙ—ay jebbiliiЙ“e Й“een wano bonЙ“e Й“een?"
  68,36,"Ko heЙ“i on, si Й—on Гұaawira noon?"
  68,37,"Kaa hoЙ—on mari deftere, nde janngoton e mum?"
  68,38,"Pellet, ko woodani on e mayre, ko ko cuЙ“otoЙ—on."
  68,39,"Ka ko podooje woodani on e amen, koolniiЙ—e haa Г‘ande Darngal, won'de pellet, hino woodani on ko Гұaawoton kon?"
  68,40,"LaЙ“ndii Й“e ko hommbo e maЙ“Й“e fawtaniiЙ“e Й—uum?"
  68,41,"Kaa ko kafidiiЙ“e woodani Й“e? yoo Й“e ngaddu kafidiiЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en, si tawii ko Й“e gooЕӢuЙ“e !"
  68,42,"Г‘ande belenru Гұoroytee, Й“e noddee e cujjugol kono Й“e mbaawataa."
  68,43,"Hara gite maЙ“Й“e Й—een no heli, koyeera no suddi Й“e. Ko tawde Й“e noddeteno e cujjugol fewndo ka Й“e mbaawunoo...!"
  68,44,"Accidam e kala jedduЙ—o ndee yeewtere; aray nde Min suynira Й“e nokku ka Й“e nganndaa."
  68,45,"MiЙ—o neeЙ“nan Й“e. Pellet noon, pewje am Й—en ko tiiЙ—Й—e."
  68,46,"Kaa a laЙ“ndi Й“e njoЙ“di, hara ko yoЙ“ugol ndi teddani Й“e?"
  68,47,"Kaa Й“e nganndu fii wirniiЙ—i Й—iin, hara hiЙ“e mbinndira [Й—im hujjaaji maЙ“Й“e]?"
  68,48,"MuГұГұor Гұaawoore Joommaa nden, hara a wa'aali wa wonndiiЙ—o linngii ngii fewndo o noddunoo [Joom makko] homo sunii."
  68,49,"Si tawno moЖҙЖҙere immorde e Joomi makko hewtitanooki mo, ko pellet, o bugeteno e wulaa hara ko o pelniiЙ—o."
  68,50,"Joomi makko suЙ“ii mo, o waЙ—i mo e moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e Й“een."
  68,51,"Hay yedduЙ“e Й“een eЙ“Й“iinoo yuwirgol ma gite maЙ“Й“e Й—een, nde Й“e nanunoo JaЕӢtoore nden, hiЙ“e mbi'a: "on ko kaangaaЙ—o!"."
  68,52,"Ndee [AlqurвҖҷaanaare] wonaani, si wonaa waajo winndere nde!"
  69,1,"Darnga ngo."
  69,2,"Anndinat ma ko woni darnga?"
  69,3,"Ko honЙ—um anndin maa ko woni Darngal?"
  69,4,"Samuudu e Aadi en njeddii duЙ—Й—ugol Darnga."
  69,5,"Si ko Samuuda en, Й“e kalkira ha'acaango."
  69,6,"Aadi en kan, Й“e kalkira henndu bippooru hattinndu tiiЙ—ude."
  69,7,"O eelti ndu e hoore maЙ“Й“e jehmaaji jeeЙ—iЙ—i e Гұalawmaaje jeetati jokkondirЙ—e; nji'aa yimЙ“e Й“een no pukkii e Й—iin [koЙ—ooli] wa si tawii ko Й“e daЖҙЖҙe tamaro irtiiЙ—e."
  69,8,"Taw si a yi'anat Й“e ko keddii?"
  69,9,"Fir'awna e adinooЙ“e mo e ca'e junnitanooЙ—e Й—een ngardi e goopi."
  69,10,"Й“e njeddi nulaaЙ—o Joomi maЙ“Й“e on, o nanngiri Й“e nanngal cattungal."
  69,11,"Ko Minen nhoni, fewndo ndiyam Й—am hummbunoo, Min ndoondi on ka dogayka"
  69,12,"fii no Mon mbaЙ—irana Й—um waajo, nofru nanatndu nana Й—um."
  69,13,"Si wuttaama ka allaandu wuttaande wo'otere,"
  69,14,"leddi ndiin e pelle Й—een Й“amtee moГұГұe mo Й“ГұГұannde wo'otere."
  69,15,"Ndeen Гұande, Darnga ngo daroto,"
  69,16,"Kammu ngun se'ekoo, hara ko ngu lo'ungu ndeen Гұande."
  69,17,"Hara Malaa'ika'en ngontira ka seraaji maggu, njeetato [e maЙ“Й“e] ronndoo Arsi Joomi maa kiin e hoore maЙ“Й“e ndeen Гұande."
  69,18,"Ndeen Гұande ko on weeЙ“itetee; hay hu'unde e fii mon suuЙ—otaako."
  69,19,"Si ko jonnitiroyaaЙ—o talkuru mum ndun ka Гұaamo mum, o wi'oyay : "njaЙ“ee ! Janngon talkuru am nduun."
  69,20,"Miin mi fellitno mi kawroygol e hasboore am moЖҙЖҙere ndeen"."
  69,21,"Hara himo e nguurndam mbelЙ—am :"
  69,22,"E ndeer Aljanna toowЙ—o"
  69,23,"mo dimЙ—e mum Й“adii."
  69,24,""Г‘aamee yariron no newori, sabu ko ngardin-Й—on kon e ГұalaaЙ—e feЖҙЖҙuЙ—e"."
  69,25,"Si tawii noon ko jonntiiroyaaЙ—o talkuru mum nduun ka nano mum, on wi'oyay : "Haaaniino kam hara mi jonnitaaka talkuru am nduun !"
  69,26,"Hara mi anndaani ko woni Гұaawoore am."
  69,27,"Hara [maayde] ndeen wononu timmoode [am]."
  69,28,"Jawdi am ndiin duГұcanaani kam."
  69,29,"Mbaawko am koon halkirii kam!"."
  69,30,""Nanngee mbo kolmbon bmo."
  69,31,"Refti naatnon mbo Jahiimi,"
  69,32,"Refti naatnon mbo e jolokooje-callale- Й—e juuteendi mum woni cogone cappanЙ—e jeeЙ—iЙ—i."
  69,33,"Tawde o gooЕӢЙ—inaano Allah mawЙ—o on."
  69,34,"O reerЙ—intaano e Гұammin'ngol miskiino."
  69,35,"GiЙ—o alana Й—um Й—o hannde."
  69,36,"Wonaa Гұaamde, si wonaa e ЖҙiЖҙЖҙiЖҙiri"."
  69,37,"Г‘aamata ndin, si wonaa bakkondinЙ“e Й“een"."
  69,38,"Mi wooЙ—ndirii ko nji'oton kon,"
  69,39,"E ko on nji'ataa kon,"
  69,40,"won'de pellet, [Alqur'aana] ko konngol nulaaЙ—o tedduЙ—o,"
  69,41,"wonaa nde konnguЙ—i yimoowo; kono famЙ—ii ko ngooЕӢЙ—inton."
  69,42,"wonaa kadi nde konnguЙ—i bileejo, kono famЙ—ii ko mbaajitotoЙ—on."
  69,43,"ko jippinaande immi e JeyЙ—o einndere nde."
  69,44,"Si tawno o fekindino e amen yoga e konnguЙ—i,"
  69,45,"ko pellet, min nanngirayno mo doole."
  69,46,"Hooti Min taЖҙayno e makko Й—aЙ—ol Й“ernde ngol."
  69,47,"Alaa e mo'on hay gooto kaЙ—oowo Min e makko."
  69,48,"Pellet, nde [Alqur'aanaare] konde baajitorgol gooЙ—uЙ“e Й“en."
  69,49,"Haray kadi, MiЙ—en nganndi ina e mon yeddooЙ“e [nde] ."
  69,50,"ko pellet noon, Й—uum ko nimse e hoore yedduЙ“e Й“een."
  69,51,"pellet kadi, ko nde goonga jananaaЙ—o."
  69,52,"Haray subbunhinor innde Joom maa, mawЙ—o on!"
  70,1,"TorotooЙ—o toriima lepte janatЙ—e,"
  70,2,"wonan'de he'eferЙ“e Й“en, alaa duГұanoowo Й“e Й—e,"
  70,3,"ko immorde e Allah, joom ЖҙawruЙ—e."
  70,4,"Maleykaaji wond'ude e Jibriilu hiЙ—i Жҙawa fa'ade e makko, e ndeer Гұalaande nde eЙ“Й“oore mum woni duuЙ“i ujune cappanЙ—e jowi."
  70,5,"MuГұГұo tan, muГұal labangal."
  70,6,"KamЙ“e heЙ“e nji'a (lepte) Й—en ko goЙ—Й—uЙ—e."
  70,7,"MiЙ—en nji'a Й—e minen ko Й“adiiЙ—e,"
  70,8,"Г‘ande kammu nguun wa'oyta wa ko taaynaa."
  70,9,"pelle Й—een mba'oya wa hottolle kardaako,"
  70,10,"ka Й“adondiraaЙ—o laЙ“dotaako fii jeydaaЙ—o mum,"
  70,11,"HiЙ“e kollindiree. BonЙ—o on yeloto sottorde lepte Й—en nden Гұande, Й“iЙ—Й“e makko Й“een."
  70,12,"e gennda makko, e musiЙ—Й—o neene gooto makko on."
  70,13,"E gorol makko ngol moolatngol mo."
  70,14,"e kala wonЙ“e e lesdi Й“een, fii no Й—uum daЙ—ndira mo."
  70,15,"ЖҠuum gasataa. Ngen [Yiite] ko uuyunge,"
  70,16,"Й“oltatnge guri hoore."
  70,17,"Henge nodda oon Й—uurniiЙ—o o ruЕӢiti,"
  70,18,"o mooЙ“i (jawЙ—e) o mari e marirgel."
  70,19,"Pellet, neЙ—Й—o o tagaama ko o Й—enЖҙotooЙ—o;"
  70,20,"si bone memi mo, o faaya."
  70,21,"Si ko mo moЖҙЖҙere nde heЙ“i mo, o salora."
  70,22,"Si wonaa juulooЙ“e Й“een."
  70,23,"Й“een tawЙ“e ko Й“e duumiiЙ“e e juulde maЙ“Й“e ndeen."
  70,24,"E Й“een tawЙ“e hino ka jawЙ—e maЙ“Й“e haqqee ganndaaЙ—o,"
  70,25,"wonan'de torotooЙ—o e Й—awaaЙ—o."
  70,26,"e E Й“een gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Гұalaande njoЙ“di nde,"
  70,27,"E Й“een tawЙ“e ko Й“e huluЙ“e lepte Joomi maЙ“Й“e Й—en"
  70,28,"Tawde pellet, lepte Joomi maЙ“Й“e Й—en ngonaa koolniiЙ—e,"
  70,29,"E Й“een tawЙ“e ko reenЙ“e farjuuji maЙ“Й“e Й—iin"
  70,30,"si wonaa e rewЙ“e maЙ“Й“e maa Й“een horЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“e Й“e jeyiri Гұaame maЙ“Й“e, Й—oon on Й“e peletaake."
  70,31,"Kala noon Й—aЙ“Й“uЙ—o [ka dakmitora] caggal Й—uum, haray ko Й“een ngoni jaggituЙ“e Й“een."
  70,32,"E Й“een tawЙ“e ko aynituЙ“e koolaaje e aadiiji maЙ“Й“e Й—iin."
  70,33,"E Й“een tawЙ“e ko ГұiiЙ“uЙ“e e seedeeji mum."
  70,34,"E Й“een tawЙ“e ko reenooЙ“e e juulde maЙ“Й“e ndeen."
  70,35,"ЖҒeen Й—oon ko teddinoyteeЙ“e e aljannaaji."
  70,36,"E ko heЙ“i yedduЙ“e Й“een takko maaЙ—a, heЙ“e keГұora."
  70,37,"To nano e ka Гұaamo, ko Й“e dentoГұ-dentoГұ?"
  70,38,"Hara go'oto kala e maЙ“Й“e tamЖҙinoto naatoygol aljanna ne'emaaji?"
  70,39,"ЖҠum waЙ—ataa ! Min tagiriЙ“e ko Й“e nganndi."
  70,40,"Mi wooЙ—ndirii JeyЙ—o fuЙ—irЙ—e e mutirЙ—e on, pellet, ko Min hattanЙ“e."
  70,41,"wattitirgol Й“e ko Й“uri Й“e moЖҙЖҙude, Min siforaa ronkugol [Й—uum]."
  70,42,"AccuЙ“e Й“e njumpa, Й“e pija ha Й“e kawroya e Гұalaande maЙ“Й“e nde Й“e kammbirananoo."
  70,43,"Гұalnde Й“e njaltiroyta e genaale Й—ren heГұaare, wa si tawii ko kaaЖҙe (sanamu) Й“e ngoni wugganaade."
  70,44,"Hara gite maЙ“Й“e no keli, koyeera no cuddi Й“e. Ko nden Гұalaande woni ko Й“e kammbirananoo!"
  71,1,"Min nulii Nuuhu haa e yimЙ“e makko Й“een, won'de : "Jeertin yimЙ“e ma Й“en, ado lette mu'usuuЙ—e arde e maЙ“Й“e"."
  71,2,"O maakani [Й“e] : "ehey yimЙ“e am, miin ko mi jeertinoowo on Й“annguЙ—o."
  71,3,"won'de yo on ndewu Allah, kulon mo, Й—oftoЙ—on kam."
  71,4,"O haforanat on bakkatuuji i mon Й—in, O neeЙ“na on haa e lajal taЖҙaangal. [Ko woni tan] lajal Allah ngal si hewtii, ngal neeЙ“netaake, si tawii hoЙ—on nganndunoo!"."
  71,5,"O maaki : "Joomi am, miin mi noddirii yimЙ“e am Й“een jehma e Гұalawma,"
  71,6,"kono noddaandu am nduun Й“eydaani Й“e, si wonaa dogugol."
  71,7,"Tuma kala kadi nde mi noddi Й“e fii no kafaranaa Й“e, Й“e mbaЙ—at kolli maЙ“Й“e Й—iin ka ndeer noppi maЙ“Й“e, Й“e buumora comci maЙ“Й“e Й—iin, Й“e deppitoo, Й“e townitora townitaadee."
  71,8,"Refti mi noddirii Й“e e kene.(FeeГұi)."
  71,9,"Refti mi feГұГұinani Й“e, mi suuЙ—anii Й“e suuЙ—aandee."
  71,10,"Mi wi'i [Й“e] : "Imsinanee Joomi mon, tawde o siforii won'de kaforoowo."
  71,11,"O wurtira toЙ“o ngo e mon dewnindiral,"
  71,12,"O Й“eydira on jawЙ—e e Й“iЙ—Й“e, o waЙ—ana on gese, o waЙ—ana on caatli."
  71,13,"E ko heЙ“i on, on njoortaaki manngural Allah ngal,"
  71,14,"Jojji o tagir on taaЙ“e-taaЙ“e?"
  71,15,"E on nji'ataa no Allah tagiri kammuuji jeeЙ—iЙ—i tegondirЙ—i?"
  71,16,"O waЙ—i lewru ndun jalЙ“undu e majji, o waЙ—i na'ange ngen pitilol."
  71,17,"Ko Allah fuЙ—niri on ka lesdi puЙ—nugol."
  71,18,"Refti o ruttirat on e mayri, o yaltina on yaltinndee."
  71,19,"Allah waЙ—iranii on leydi ndiin weertaandi."
  71,20,"fii yo on naatir e mayri laabi jaacЙ—i"."
  71,21,"Nuuhu maaki : "Joomi am, Й“ee njeddii kam, Й“e njokkii on mo jawЙ—e mum e Й“iЙ—Й“e Й“eydaani Й—um si wonaa hayrugol."
  71,22,"ЖҒe pewji fehre mawnde."
  71,23,"Й“e mbi'i: "Wota on terto dey deweteeЙ—i mon Й—iin: wota on terto Wudda, e Suwaa'a, e Ya'uuqatha, e Nasr"."
  71,24,"Ko pellet, Й“e majjinii ko Й—uuЙ—i. [Joomi] wota A Й“eydir tooГұЙ“e Й“een, si wonaa majjere."
  71,25,"Ko sagu goopi maЙ“Й“e Й—iin Й“e njooliranoo, Й“e naatna Yiite, Й“e heЙ“anaano ko'e maЙ“Й“e paabotooЙ—o ga Allah"."
  71,26,"Nuuhu maaki kadi : "Joomi am, wota a accu e leydi ndin, hay keefeero dilloowo."
  71,27,"Ko pellet, si a accii Й“e, Й“e majjinat jiyaaЙ“e maa Й“en, Й“e njibinoytaako si wonaa bonnooЙ“e Й—uuЙ—uЙ“e jeddi."
  71,28,"Joomi am, kaforanam miin e jibinЙ“e kam Й“en, e Й“en gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e naatuЙ“e ka suudu am, e gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e worЙ“e Й“en e gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e rewЙ“e Й“een; wata A Й“eydir tooГұuЙ“e Й“een, si wonaa halakuyee."
  72,1,"Maaku : "Wahayinaama e am, won'de dental jinna keЙ—iimo [kam miЙ—o jannga Alqur'aana], Й—i wi'i: "Minen min nani janngeteende haawniinde."
  72,2,"Hende Й—owira e peewal. Min ngooЕӢЙ—inii nde. Min kafidatah e Joomi amen, hay e gooto."
  72,3,"E won'de manngural Joomi amen ngal mawnii, o siforaali jogitagol genndo, wonaa Й“iЙ—Й—o !"
  72,4,"E won'de [Ibuliisa] Й—ayЙ—o on e amen hino wowlaynoo penaale e hoore Allah."
  72,5,"Minen min cikkuno won'de yimЙ“e e jinna wowlataano fenaande e hoore Allah."
  72,6,"Hari le worЙ“e yimЙ“e hino mooloratnoo worЙ“e jinna, Й“e Й“esdi Й—i bewre."
  72,7,"KamЙ“e [yimЙ“e Й“een] Й“e cikkir no sikkirЙ—on noon, won'de Allah immintintah hay gooto."
  72,8,"E won'de min meemii kammu ngun, min tawi hingu hebbiniraa aynooЙ“e tiiЙ—uЙ“e e docote."
  72,9,"E won'de miЙ—en njooЙ—otonoo ton fii keЙ—agol. Kala non keЙ—itiiЙ—o jooni, o hawray e docotal tommbingal."
  72,10,"E won'de min nganndaa si ko bone fa'andanaa wonЙ“e ka leddi Й“en, kaa hara Joomi maЙ“Й“e faandani Й“e peewal."
  72,11,"E won'de hino e amen moЖҙЖҙuЙ—i, hino e amen kadi ko jaasi Й—um. Hari miЙ—en e laawi ceertuЙ—i."
  72,12,"E won'de min pellituno min laawotaako Allah ka hoore leydi, e won'de min laawortaa Mo dogugol."
  72,13,"E won'de nde min nanunoo peewal nagl, min ngooЙ—ini ngal. Kala gooЕӢЙ—inЙ—o Joomi mum, oon hulataa Й—uytaneede [moЖҙЖҙi] wonaa Й“eydaneede [bonЙ—i]."
  72,14,"E won'de hino e amen jebbiliiЙ—i, hino e amen kadi ooГұiiЙ—i. Kala jebbilii ngii, Й—in Й—oon faandike peewal."
  72,15,"OoГұiiЙ—i Й—iin kan, Й—i laatanike Jahannama oon carmalle."
  72,16,"E won'de si Й“e ГұiiЙ“uno e hoore laawol ngol, ko pellet, Min njarnayno Й“e ndiyam Й—uuЙ—uЙ—am,"
  72,17,"fii yo Min ndaarndoro Й“e heen. Kala Й—uurniiЙ—o e JaЕӢtoore Joomi mum nden, O naaday mo e lepte caЙ—tuЙ—e."
  72,18,"E won'de juulirЙ—e Й—een ko Allah leeranii. Wata on kafidu e Allah hay e gooto."
  72,19,"E won'de tuma jiyaaЙ—o Allah on darinoo himo rewa mo, Й—i Й—eЙ“uno waЙ—Й—ondirgol e hoore makko."
  72,20,"Maaku : "nganndee ko Joomi am (tan) mi ndewata, mi kafidataa mo kadi hay e gooto"."
  72,21,"Maaku : "Miin mi waawanaa on duГұude lorra, wonaa fii pooЙ—ugol nafa"."
  72,22,"Maaku : "Hay gooto waawaa daЙ—ndugol kam e Allah; mi heЙ“ataa ko woori mo ЖҙooГұorde"
  72,23,"si wonaa yottingol immorde e Allah e nule makko Й—een. Kala jedduЙ—o Allah e NulaaЙ—o makko on, haray ko Yiite Jahannama woodani mo, Й“e luttay e magge poomaa."
  72,24,"Haa si Й“e nji'ii ko Й“e kammbirananoo kon, Й“e aray anndude ko hombo Й“uri lo'ode ballo, Й“uri kadi famЙ—ude limoore."
  72,25,"Maaku : "Mi anndaa si ko kammbiranaЙ—on kon hino Й“adii, maa si koomi am waЙ—anat Й—uum dumunna."
  72,26,"Ko o ganndo wirniiЙ—i. O Жҙellintinantaa wirniiЙ—i makko Й—iin hay e gooto."
  72,27,"si wonaa mo o welanaa e NulaaЙ—o, o naadnay ye'eso on e Й“aawo makko tommbotooЙ“e."
  72,28,"fii yo o anndu won'de Й“en njottinii nule joomi maЙ“Й“e Й—een. O huЙ“indorii (anndugol) ko woni ka maЙ“Й“e kon, O mofti limoore kala hu'unde"."
  73,1,"Eey ma buumorЙ—o [comci mum]!r"
  73,2,"ЖҒaЕӢo (nguurnitaa) jehma o, si wonaa seeЙ—a [e makko];"
  73,3,"feccere makko, maa isytaa seeЙ—a e Й—uum;"
  73,4,"maa Й“esdaa Й—oon. Janngiraa Alqur'aanaare nden dewnindiral."
  73,5,"MiЙ—en caatii tellinnde e maaЙ—a konngol teddungol."
  73,6,"Pellet, ko dewal tummbo jehma ngal, Й“uri tiiЙ—ude batte e fooccaade konngol."
  73,7,"Anndu hino woodan-maa e Гұalawma oon, ferlitagol juutungol."
  73,8,"JaЕӢto innde Joomi maa nden, taЖҙo-Й—aa yahaa e makko haaЙ—tirde taЖҙagol."
  73,9,"JeyЙ—o on fuЙ—na'ange e hiirnaange.deweteeЙ—o woo alaa e si wona KaЕӢko,Jogito mo koolorteeЙ—o."
  73,10,"MuГұГұo e ko Й“e wowlata kon; ngoЙ—Й—ito-raa Й“e woЙ—Й—itannde labaande."
  73,11,"Accidam e yeddooЙ“e joomiraaЙ“e neemaaji Й“een; kabbito-Й—aa Й“e seeЙ—a."
  73,12,"Ko pellet, hino ka amen gaa : Tonngii e Jahiimi,"
  73,13,"E Гұaametee Й—eЙ—Й—oowo, e lepte mu'usuuЙ—e."
  73,14,"Г‘alnde lesdi ndiin e pelle Й—en dillata, pelle Й—een wa'a wa njaare ilayndi."
  73,15,"Min nelii e mon nelaaЙ—o haa o wona seede e dow mon hono no min nelduno fa'ade e Fir'awna nelaaЙ—o."
  73,16,"Fir'awna woopi nelaaЙ—o o min nanngi mbo nanngugol caЙ—tungol."
  73,17,"Hono ndeenraton pittaali mon si on njeddi Гұalawmo baЙ—oowo sukaaЙ“e danndalinde."
  73,18,"Kammu o na fetta e kulhuli hembo laatiima fodoore Alla ko wonoore."
  73,19,"Ko oon woni waaju goongo kala paalaaЙ—o daЙ—de nanngira joomiiko ruttorde."
  73,20,"Pellet joom ma na anndi haЙ—a juula ko Й“uri famЙ—ude e tataЙ“al jehma wollo feccere mammbo wond'ude e fedde e Й“een won'Й—uЙ“e e ma Alla hoddira jehma e Гұalawma O anndi on tonngataa mbo o yaafii mon, njannge ko newanii on e Quraana hombo anndi ma won e mon ГұawЙ“e goo ngona e Й—atngal ka lesdi hoЙ“e ndaarta Й“ural Alla woЙ“Й“e kadi na kaЙ“ano laawol Alla njannge ko newanii mon e hembo ndarnon juulde tottiron askal Гұamlon Alla Гұamaande moЖҙЖҙere kala ko mbaЙ—aЙ—on ko'e mon e jam tawon mbo ka Alla hombo Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude e mawnude njobdi njaafnee Alla sabu Alla ko jaafatooЙ—o ko jurmotooЙ—o."
  74,1,"Eey mon yo mojiiЙ—o !"
  74,2,"ЖҒaЕӢo mbaajo-Й—aa."
  74,3,"Fii Joom maa, mawnina."
  74,4,"Comci maa Й—iin, laЙ“Й“inaa."
  74,5,"Sanamuuji Й—iin, ngoЙ—Й—ito-Й—aa..."
  74,6,"Wota a okkir fii heЙ“ugol ko Й“uri Й—uum..."
  74,7,"Ko fii Joom maa, muГұГұortaa."
  74,8,"Si wuttaama e allaandu nd."
  74,9,"Nden Гұalnde woni, Гұalaande saЙ—tunde."
  74,10,"E hoore he'eferЙ“e Й“een, nde wanaa newiinde."
  74,11,"Accidam e oon mo mi tagi on kaГұun tan."
  74,12,"Mi mbaЙ—an mo jawdi Й—uuЙ—undi,"
  74,13,"E Й“iЙ“Й“e won'Й—uЙ“e e makko."
  74,14,"Mi yaacnani mo yaacnudee."
  74,15,"Refti homo tamЖҙinoo nde mi Й“eydata."
  74,16,"ЖҠuum waЙ—ataa ! tawde o laatino sanndalЙ—iiЙ—o e aayeeje amen Й—een."
  74,17,"Aray mi fawa mo lepte caЙ—tuЙ—e."
  74,18,"KaЕӢko oon, o miijiti o eЙ“Й“indii."
  74,19,"O huЙ—a hono no o hoddiri."
  74,20,"Refti o huЙ—a kadi hono o hoddiri."
  74,21,"Refti o ndaari."
  74,22,"Refti ГұirЙ“anii o Й“esdi ГұirЙ“inaade."
  74,23,"Refti o ruЕӢtii hombo mawnikini."
  74,24,"Й“e mbi'a: "ЖҠuum wonaani, si wonaa mbilewu Й“anngu ngu."
  74,25,"Mbo wona si wona konngol aade."
  74,26,"Ma mi naatnu mbo yiite saqara."
  74,27,"Hol ko anndinat ma ko woni Saqara."
  74,28,"Nge heddata nge ngaccata."
  74,29,"Sumoowe je'ece."
  74,30,"ina e dow mannge sappa e jeenay."
  74,31,"Min mbaЙ—aani aynooЙ“e yimЙ“e Yiite ngen, si wonaa Malaa'ika. Min mbaЙ—iraani limoore maЙ“Й“e si wonaa jarraborgol yedduЙ“e Й“en, e fii yo henan okkaaЙ“e defte Й“een, e fii no gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“een Й“eydora gooЕӢЙ—inal, e fii wata okkaaЙ“e defte Й“en e gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“en cikkito; e fii yo Й“een Й“e Гұawu woni e Й“erЙ—e mum e he'eferЙ“e Й“een mbi'u: "Hara ko holЙ—um Allah faandorii e ngal misaal?" Ko wano non Allah majjinirta mo o muuyani, homo feewna kadi mo O muuyani. Hay gooto anndaa yeru koneeli Joomi maa Й—iin, si wonaa KaЕӢko. Ngen [Yiite] wonaali, si wonaa waajo wonan'de neЙ—Й—aЕӢke."
  74,32,"Kono yo henane! mi wooЙ—ndirii lewru ndun,"
  74,33,"O wooЙ—ndirii jehma si mbo runtii ma."
  74,34,"E subaka si mo fooyni."
  74,35,"Ko mbo go'otel e mawЙ—i."
  74,36,"Ko nge ejertinirde wonan'de neЙ—Й—aЕӢke."
  74,37,"Wonan'de on njiЙ—uЙ—o e mo'on, nde o yaccotoo maa nennoo."
  74,38,"WoЕӢkii kala ko faggii kon nanngirte."
  74,39,"Si wonaa yimЙ“e Гұaamo Й“een."
  74,40,"hiЙ“e e ndeer gese, heЙ“e laЙ“ndondira"
  74,41,"fii bonЙ“e Й“een."
  74,42,""ko hoЙ—um naatni on Saqara?""
  74,43,"ЖҒen mbi'a: "Min njeyanooka e juulooЙ“e Й“een."
  74,44,"min njeyanooka kadi e ГұamminooЙ“e miskimЙ“e Й“een."
  74,45,"Hari min jumpidatno kadi e jumpooЙ“e Й“een."
  74,46,"Hari kadi min njeddatno fii Гұalaande njoЙ“di ndeen."
  74,47,"Haa [maayde] yananaande ndeen arani min"."
  74,48,"NafataaЙ“e tefnoore tefntooЙ“e."
  74,49,"Hol ko waЙ—i Й“e sirkuЙ“e na Й—uurno alquraana."
  74,50,"HoЙ“e mba'i e bamЙ—i laawatooЙ—i na ndoga."
  74,51,"DogatЙ—i mbaroodi."
  74,52,"Gooto e mu'en fof na faala totteede Й—eri caraaЙ—i."
  74,53,"Alah woni koЙ“e kulaani La'akara."
  74,54,"Ala Й—uum ko ciftanirgol."
  74,55,"Ko kala paalaaЙ—o waactoraade o waactaroo mbo."
  74,56,"Й“e mbaactaaka si wona Alla na haaja, ko KaЕӢko woni kaanduЙ—o e huleede ko KaЕӢko woni kaanduЙ—o e yaafaade."
  75,1,"MbiЙ—a woonЙ—dira Гұande ndarnga."
  75,2,"MbiЙ—a wooЙ—ndira fittaandu felooru."
  75,3,"Mbela aade sikkat min ndenndintah Жҙi'e makko."
  75,4,"Oho kay mbiЙ—a min kattani fotndude gulle peЙ—eeli makko."
  75,5,"Kono aade yiЙ—i konde o wonata saay ye'eso ka ye'eso makko."
  75,6,"HiЙ“e laЙ“ndoo : "Ko honnde woni Г‘alaande njoЙ“di kuuЙ—e?""
  75,7,"Si yitere nde majii."
  75,8,"Lewru ndu nanngaa."
  75,9,"Na'ange e lewru ndenndina."
  75,10,"Ndeen aade wi'a hoЙ—o dogirde ngoni."
  75,11,"Ala dokdu alah e oon Гұalngu."
  75,12,"Koto joom ma Гұande heen woni ruttorde nde."
  75,13,"Aade na habre Гұande heen ko ardini e golle e ko o leelni ko."
  75,14,"Ko woni ko aade o na seedii e fittaandu makko."
  75,15,"Hay si o addii ngantuuji makko Й—i."
  75,16,"Woto dillin heen Й—emngal ma haa njaawnaЙ—a e hembo."
  75,17,"Ko minen woodani renndinde mbo e jannginde mbo ma."
  75,18,"Si min njanngii mbo rew e jaЕӢde makko."
  75,19,"Refti ko e amen fawi firde mbo."
  75,20,"Ala woni ko hoЙ—on njiЙ—i aduna jaawЙ—o o ko gasata."
  75,21,"Ngaccon La'akara."
  75,22,"Je'ece malaaЙ“e Гұande heen na fooyni."
  75,23,"HoЙ—e ndaara fa'ade e joom mu' en."
  75,24,"E je'ece ГұirЙ“aniiЙ—e Гұande heen."
  75,25,"HoЙ—e cikka ma telline e mu' en musiiba mawЙ—o."
  75,26,"Ala sindu yottiima bororde."
  75,27,"Wi'e hombo woni moccaoowa."
  75,28,"O yananee ko Й—um ceergal e aduna."
  75,29,"Korlal ngal fiilto e korlal."
  75,30,"Ko ta joom ma Гұande heen woni ruttorde."
  75,31,"O gooЕӢЙ—inaani o juulaani."
  75,32,"Kono o yeddu o Й—uurnii."
  75,33,"Refti o yahi to koreeji makko hombo wasoo."
  75,34,"Halkaare woodaniima e halkaare."
  75,35,"Refti halkaare kadi woodanii ma e halkaare titi."
  75,36,"Mbele aade o sikku o accete hombo duda."
  75,37,"Mbele o wonaana toЙ“Й“e maniyyu juppateende e rannga."
  75,38,"Refti o wonti heЙ—Й—ere o tagi o fonndi."
  75,39,"O waЙ—I heen kuЙ“e Й—iЙ—i dewel e gorel."
  75,40,"Mbele oon hattanaani wuurtin'de maayЙ“e."
  76,1,"Mbele arii e aade tumo e yonta nde o wonaana hay hu'unde jaЕӢtateende."
  76,2,"Min tagii aade e toЙ“Й“ere jillunde ndiyam gorko e debbo min kumpitoo mbo min laatini mbo nanoowo ji'oowo."
  76,3,"Miin peewnii mbo e laawol o yetta wollo o yedda."
  76,4,"Pellet Miin keblinii he'eferЙ“e callalle e tonngi e yiite."
  76,5,"Pellet Й—igguЙ“e Й“e na njara e kaas jilluЙ—o kaafuur."
  76,6,"Sewnde nde jiyaaЙ“e Alla Й“allinaaЙ“e njarata heЙ“e ilnande ilnugol."
  76,7,"HeЙ“e kuuЙ“na takkere hoЙ“e kula Гұalawma mbo bone mum na saroo."
  76,8,"HoЙ“e Гұammina Гұamri wond'ude e yiЙ—de ndi miskiin e alyatiime e dahaaЙ—o."
  76,9,"Miin Гұamminirta mon ko sabi Alla miin faalaaka e mon njoЙ“di wona yetteede."
  76,10,"Pellet min kuli ummaade e joomi amen ko Гұalawma ГұirЙ“iniiЙ—o cattuЙ—o tumminaare."
  76,11,"Alla reeniЙ“e e bone oon Гұalawma o okkiЙ“e pummam labaЙ—am e weltaare."
  76,12,"Alla yoЙ“iri Й“e koЙ“e muГұi ko aljanna e (comci)hariir."
  76,13,"HoЙ“e tuugnii e fotooyji Й“e yi'atah heen na'ange wonah jaangol cattungol."
  76,14,"Na Й“adi e dow mu'en Й—owdi mammba Й“esnaaЙ—e mum na eeltanaaЙ“e eeltegol."
  76,15,"Ina taarneeЙ“e ngennduwoГұ kaalis e kaasyoГұ na feewnira weer."
  76,16,"Ka'aseeje kaalis hoЙ—e potndira potndegol."
  76,17,"HoЙ“e njarnee kaas njilludi mum ko janjabiil."
  76,18,"Sewnde na e hembo na innire Sal sabiil."
  76,19,"SukaaЙ“e saasnaaЙ“e na mbanngo e mum en si a yi'iiЙ“e cikka ko Й“e lu'u lu'u caraaЙ—o."
  76,20,"Si a yi'i toon nji'a neema e laamu manngu."
  76,21,"Ina e dow mu'en comci sundus Й—i mbaadi ha'aka hecco e istabraq Й“e Й“oorna jawe kaalis joom mu'en yarnaЙ“e njaram laaЙ“Й—am."
  76,22,"Pellet Й—um wonanii mon njoЙ“di golle mon kadi golle mon ngoniina mantaaЙ—e."
  76,23,"Ko minen tigi tellini alquraana e dow ma tellingol."
  76,24,"MuГұ e Гұaawoore joom ma woto Й—ofto e mum en bakkadinЙ—o wolla ke'efeera."
  76,25,"jaЕӢta inne joom ma subaka e kikiiЙ—a."
  76,26,"E jemma he cujjan mbo cubahinanЙ—aa mbo jehma juutЙ—o."
  76,27,"Pellet Й“e na njiЙ—i nguurndam aduna njaawЙ—am gasde Й—am Й“e ngacca caggal mum en Гұalawma nisЙ—o."
  76,28,"Ko minen tagi on min cemmbini terЙ—o si min kaajaama min ngostoroo on nandadiiЙ“e mon gostogol."
  76,29,"Ko nde woni waajo goongo kala paalaaЙ—o daЙ—de nanngira fa'ade e joomiiko ruttorde."
  76,30,"On paaletaake si wonaAlla haaje pellet Alla ko ganndo ko ГұeeГұo"
  76,31,"Homo naatna mbo o welaa e yurmeene makko o heblanii tooГұЙ“e Й“e lepte mu'usЙ—e."
  77,1,"Mi wooЙ—ndirii keneeli dewandirЙ—i hono sirka puccu."
  77,2,"E (keneeli)bippooji bippugol."
  77,3,"E carooji Й—i cargolo."
  77,4,"E ceerndooji Й—i ceerndugol."
  77,5,"E tellinooji Й—i wahyu."
  77,6,"Gantingol maa jeertingol."
  77,7,"GooЕӢЙ—i podante Й—on ko, ko goongo."
  77,8,"Г‘ande koode Й—e momta."
  77,9,"Si kammu o huuЙ“taama"
  77,10,"Si pelle Й—e nawaama."
  77,11,"Saanga nelaaЙ“e Й“e kappana waktu."
  77,12,"E Гұalawma oon dirtinaaЙ—o."
  77,13,"Wonan'de Гұalngu ceerndugol."
  77,14,"Holko anndinatma ma Гұalngu ceerndugol."
  77,15,"Nden Гұalnde, bone woodanii yedduЙ“e Й“een."
  77,16,"Mbele min kalkaani adinooЙ“e Й“e."
  77,17,"Refti mn ndewni heen sakkatiiЙ“e Й“e."
  77,18,"Ko hono nih nin mbaЙ—ata bonЙ“e Й“e."
  77,19,"Nden Гұalnde, bone woodanii yedduЙ“e Й“een."
  77,20,"Mbele min tagaani mon e ndiyam koyЙ—am."
  77,21,"Min mbaЙ—i Й—am e rannga kuЙ“andiinga."
  77,22,"Ha e happu ganndaaЙ—o."
  77,23,"Min koddiri mbo moЖҙЖҙi Й“e hoddirooЙ“e."
  77,24,"Nden Гұalnde, bone woodanii yedduЙ“e Й“een."
  77,25,"Mbele min mbaЙ—aani leydi coomoori mon."
  77,26,"WuurЙ“e e maayЙ“e(fof)."
  77,27,"Min mbaЙ—i e hendi peЕӢЙ—e toowЙ—e min njarni mon ndiyam mbelЙ—am."
  77,28,"Nden Гұalnde, bone woodanii yedduЙ“e Й“een."
  77,29,"Pokkitane fa'ade ko njeddatnaЙ—on."
  77,30,"Pokkitane fa'ade e Й—owdi ndi Й—emЙ—e tati."
  77,31,"Ndi Й—owdinta nafata e lew lewndu."
  77,32,"Honge werno peete mawe hono kuЙ“eeje."
  77,33,"Elle koЙ—e gelooЙ“i cooyi."
  77,34,"Nden Гұalnde, bone woodanii yedduЙ“e Й“een."
  77,35,"E o Гұalngu Й“e kaalata."
  77,36,"ЖҒe cakkitantaake saba Й“e ngantina."
  77,37,"Nden Гұalnde, bone woodanii yedduЙ“e Й“een."
  77,38,"O ko Гұalawma ceernduЙ—a min ndenndinii on wond'ude e adiiЙ“e Й“e."
  77,39,"Si tawii hoЙ—on njogi fehre pewjanee kam."
  77,40,"Nden Гұalnde, bone woodanii yedduЙ“e Й“een."
  77,41,"Pellet, gooЕӢЙ—uЙ“e Й“een ngonii e Й—owdiiji e Й“ulli."
  77,42,"E Й“esnooje koЙ“e tuuyate."
  77,43,"[ЖҒe mbi'anee] : "Гұaamee njarone, ko newi moЙ—du, sabu kon ko ngollaynoЙ—on."
  77,44,"Ko non woni ko min mbarjorta moЖҙЖҙimЙ“e Й“een."
  77,45,"Nden Гұalnde, bone woodanii yedduЙ“e Й“een."
  77,46,"Гұaame ndakmitaЙ—on seeЙ—a ko on bannddiiji."
  77,47,"Nden Гұalnde, bone woodanii yedduЙ“e Й“een."
  77,48,"SiЙ“e mbiyaama ndukЖҙe Й“e ndukЖҙatah."
  77,49,"Nden Гұalnde, bone woodanii yedduЙ“e Й“een."
  77,50,"Honde yeewtere caggal oon Й“e gooЕӢЙ—inta."
  78,1,"Hol ko Й“ee naamnandirta."
  78,2,"Ko fa'ati e kabaaru mawЙ—o."
  78,3,"MboЙ“e luhri e mum o."
  78,4,"Alaa wona noon, maЙ“e nganndu."
  78,5,"Refti yaama Й“e nganndu."
  78,6,"Mbela min mbaЙ—aani lesdi ndaЙ—Й—udi heblaandi."
  78,7,"E pelle Й—e ngona peЕӢЙ—e."
  78,8,"Min tagi on kuЙ“e (noonooji)."
  78,9,"Min mbaЙ—i Й—oyngol mon fo'oftere."
  78,10,"Min mbaЙ—i jehma o ko sutura."
  78,11,"Min mbaЙ—i Гұalawma ko yiilaraade nguure."
  78,12,"Min mahi dow mon(sanamuuji )jeeЙ—iЙ—i caЙ—tuЙ—i."
